NK023('a)001:0: 'dus pa chen po mdo'i sgrub khrigs bzhin dbang byang
NK023('a)001:1: lag len mkhas pa glan bsod nams mgon gyis mdzad
NK023('a)001:3: rig pa rang shar rgyud sham las //
NK023('a)001:4: bsrung ba'i dam tshig 'di lta ste //
NK023('a)001:5: lung zhig chu la mi btung zhing //
NK023('a)001:6: ma yengs ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7: 'jug pa'i sgo ni dag pa gsum //
NK023('a)001:8: bya ba dag pa rnam pa gsum //
NK023('a)001:9: dag pa rnam gsum gang zhe na //
NK023('a)001:10: lha dang dkyil 'khor dag pa dang //
NK023('a)001:11: rdzas dang yo byad dag pa dang //
NK023('a)001:13: rtogs pa'i lta ba 'di lta ste //
NK023('a)001:14: lha dang rnal 'byor dag pa gnyis //
NK023('a)001:15: rje dang 'bangs kyi tshul du bya //
NK023('a)001:17: spang ba'i rim pa 'di lta ste //
NK023('a)001:18: nya dang sha dang sgog pa dang //
NK023('a)001:19: de bzhin chang la sogs pa spong //
NK023('a)001:20: kri ya'i theg pa de ltar na //
NK023('a)001:21: u pa'i theg pa 'di lta ste //
NK023('a)001:22: lta ba yo gar lta ba la //
NK023('a)001:23: spyod pa kri yar spyod pa'o //
NK023('a)001:24: de phyir gnyis ka brgyud ces grags //
NK023('a)001:25: lta ba lha dang grogs po'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:28: // // 'dus pa mdo yi gsal shing gi cho ga snang /
NK023('a)001:29: spyir 'dus pa mdo'i dngos grub len pa'i /
NK023('a)001:30: ye shes lha'i dngos grub gsal shing la len la /
NK023('a)001:31: ya mtshan 'phrul gyi dngos grub rnal 'byor pas thob dgos pas /
NK023('a)001:32: de la zhi khro gnyis las /
NK023('a)001:33: dang po zhi ba lha'i dbang /
NK023('a)001:35: yang rdo rje me long nas /
NK023('a)001:36: dbang bskur rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK023('a)001:37: ma bcos rdo rje dbyings dkyil 'khor //
NK023('a)001:38: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor phyi rim ste //
NK023('a)001:39: bsgrub dang gdug pa 'dul phyir yin //
NK023('a)001:40: zhes gsungs pas de'i don ni /
NK023('a)001:41: khro bo la phyi rim zhes gsungs kyang /
NK023('a)001:42: don gyis zhi khro gnyis steng 'og tu yod pas /
NK023('a)001:43: steng gi ston pa kun tu bzang po gnas 'gyur nas 'og gi che mchog la thim /
NK023('a)001:44: gzhan thams cad gnas 'gyur du yod pas /
NK023('a)001:45: de'i 'od zer 'ju 'dul gyi tshul du yod pa'i phyir /
NK023('a)001:46: zhi ba'i lha rnams la gsal shing gi cho ga mi dgos /
NK023('a)001:47: zhes sregs pa rdo rje rgyal mtshan gsung ngo mo /
NK023('a)001:49: zhi khro lag pa'i lto rgyab kyi tshul yin pas len pa 'thad gsung par lta /
NK023('a)001:51: yang dag gi dus min pa gsal shing gi cho ga la gnad che rgyu med gsung par gda' /
NK023('a)001:52: de ltar gsum po phyag bzhes bag tsam mi mthun kyang /
NK023('a)001:53: zhu bsod nams sh+aakya'i zhal nas /
NK023('a)001:54: lha dgu kun gyi rtsa ba yin la /
NK023('a)001:55: spyir 'dus pa mdo bya ba 'di thams cad 'dus pa yin te /
NK023('a)001:56: lam theg pa rim pa dgu yang 'dus /
NK023('a)001:59: bskyed rdzogs gsum la sogs pa thams cad 'dus pa yin pa'i phyir te /
NK023('a)001:60: cis na bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi dbang du /
NK023('a)001:61: lha lnga brgya brgyad cu rtsa gsum la /
NK023('a)001:62: sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis so sor gsungs pa med cing gcig yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK023('a)001:63: khro bo'i lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad la sogs pa gzhan med de gcig yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK023('a)001:64: mtshams gcod pa'i dus kyi steng 'og phyogs mtshams kyi khro bo bcu yang gcig yin pa'i phyir te /
NK023('a)001:65: dper na sgyu 'phrul gyi zhi khro 'bring po yang 'dus /
NK023('a)001:66: yang dag drug cu rtsa brgyad pa'i lha tshogs thams
NK023('a)001:67: cad 'di la tshang pas gzhan don dbang bsgrub kyi
NK023('a)001:68: dkyil 'khor chen po drug kyang 'di la 'dus pas
NK023('a)001:69: / gsal shing la dngos grub len pa shin tu yang 'thad ces gsung skad de /
NK023('a)001:70: bla ma rim pa brgyud pa'i man ngag dam pa bzhin zhes gsung ngo //
NK023('a)001:71: de la 'dir 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dngos grub gsal shing la len pa'i dbang du gsungs te /
NK023('a)001:72: zhi ba'i lha khro bo la gnas 'gyur du yod pas /
NK023('a)001:73: khro bo blangs pa de ka zhi ba la blangs pa yin pas de'i phyag bzhes la /
NK023('a)001:74: 'brang rgyas la gsal shing gi rim pa bcu bzhir
NK023('a)001:75: mtho dman yod par gsal bar byas pa de la
NK023('a)001:77: mtshan ma rdzas gnyis ka 'byung bar bya ba yin te /
NK023('a)001:78: de'i cho ga'i rim pa la /
NK023('a)001:79: spyan drangs mchod dang bzlas pa dang //
NK023('a)001:80: bstod dang smon lam bsdu ba drug /
NK023('a)001:83: pho brang na dpal gyi mar me bkod pa de /
NK023('a)001:84: 'dus pa chen po khro bo'i lha tshogs dkyil 'khor na ji ltar yod pa bzhin gsal bar bskyed /
NK023('a)001:88: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs nyid spyan drang /
NK023('a)001:91: dang po spyan drang ba ni /
NK023('a)001:92: pho brang gi mar me la dbus na che mchog /
NK023('a)001:95: de ltar gsum pa yab yum dang bcas pa gsal bar bskyed pa de /
NK023('a)001:96: lcags kyu'i mu tra bcas la /
NK023('a)001:97: a kra ma h+aa kro ta sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK023('a)001:98: ka ta ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK023('a)001:99: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK023('a)001:100: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK023('a)001:101: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:102: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK023('a)001:103: badz+ra a gu sha dza dza /
NK023('a)001:104: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK023('a)001:105: zhes brjod la gsal shing la me spar /
NK023('a)001:106: me 'bar ba dang 'od dang sprul par bcas nas gsal shing gi rtse mor byon par bsam /
NK023('a)001:107: gnyis pa mchod pa dbul ba na /
NK023('a)001:110: rak+sha gsum po rtsa sngags kyis dbul po //
NK023('a)001:112: bskul tshig dang 'dzab bya ba gnyis yin te /
NK023('a)001:114: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum dang //
NK023('a)001:115: dbang mchog he ru yab yum dang //
NK023('a)001:116: badz+ra he ru yab yum dang //
NK023('a)001:117: gtso bo rnams kyi thugs kha nas //
NK023('a)001:118: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru brgyad shar //
NK023('a)001:119: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK023('a)001:121: phar 'phros dpal gyi thugs dam bskang //
NK023('a)001:122: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK023('a)001:123: a kra ma h+aa kro ta sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK023('a)001:124: ka ta ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK023('a)001:125: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK023('a)001:126: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK023('a)001:127: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK023('a)001:128: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK023('a)001:129: badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta sh+ri he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:130: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK023('a)001:131: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK023('a)001:132: g+hu ya dz+nya na b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h'u /
NK023('a)001:134: bcom ldan che mchog he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:135: bla med yum chen khro mo'i rgyal //
NK023('a)001:137: nyi shu rtsa gcig pa rnams gnon //
NK023('a)001:138: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis mngon sangs rgyas //
NK023('a)001:139: zhabs brgyad ting 'dzin dbyings su sbyor //
NK023('a)001:140: brgyan rnams ma lus sku la rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:141: khro rgyal sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK023('a)001:142: bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:143: dbu dgu phyag ni bco brgyad de //
NK023('a)001:144: stong pa bco brgyad yongs su rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:145: mthing nag dges pa chen po'i sku //
NK023('a)001:146: zhabs brgyad r+au tra pho mo gnon //
NK023('a)001:148: h'u rdo rje rigs mchog bdud bzhi 'dul ba'i gtso //
NK023('a)001:149: gdug pa chen po thabs kyis btul nas ni //
NK023('a)001:150: bdud kyi rigs rnams brdul du rlog mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:151: dpal chen yab yum sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK023('a)001:152: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK023('a)001:153: gu ya lnga pa smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK023('a)001:154: ho bcom ldan 'das che mchog he ru ka yab yum dang /
NK023('a)001:155: dbang mchog chen po yab yum dang /
NK023('a)001:156: dpal chen po badz+ra he ru ka yab yum la
NK023('a)001:157: sogs pa rnams la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo
NK023('a)001:158: ni / bdag cag rnal 'byor pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir 'tshogs pa rnams la /
NK023('a)001:159: shes bya'i chos thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK023('a)001:165: gzhan yang snang ba dang mi snang ba dang /
NK023('a)001:166: rdo rje'i spyan la sogs pa'i dngos grub thob pa dang /
NK023('a)001:168: thun mong gi dngos grub bu tsha dang /
NK023('a)001:174: zas nor la sogs pa 'byor pa'i yo byad thams
NK023('a)001:175: cad rgyas shing 'phel nas 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga
NK023('a)001:177: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang /
NK023('a)001:178: 'khor longs spyod thams cad 'phel zhing rgyas pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol lo //
NK023('a)001:179: khyad par gyi dngos grub rdo rje sems dpa' mtshan
NK023('a)001:180: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dngos grub kyi sku thob par
NK023('a)001:183: badz+ra a g+hu sha dza dza zhes pa lan gsum brjod pas /
NK023('a)001:186: gsum pa sku 'od du zhu nas bdag la thim pas /
NK023('a)001:187: bdag sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gzi byin dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK023('a)001:189: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed de //
NK023('a)001:190: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:191: mi gnyis don du mchog gi dngos grub rnams //
NK023('a)001:192: bdag la stsal zhing brtan par mdzad du gsol //
NK023('a)001:193: de nas gsal shing gi rim pa gnyis pa la /
NK023('a)001:194: rgyud kyi he ru ka bzhi'i dngos grub blang ste /
NK023('a)001:195: de la yang don drug gi dang po spyan drang ba ni /
NK023('a)001:196: pho brang gi mar me la rigs bzhi'i he ru ka phyogs bzhi na bskyed pa de /
NK023('a)001:197: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK023('a)001:199: b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK023('a)001:200: badz+ra a g+hu sha dza dza /
NK023('a)001:201: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK023('a)001:202: rat+na yab yum badz+ra a ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK023('a)001:203: pad+ma yab yum badz+ra a ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK023('a)001:204: karma yab yum badz+ra a gu ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK023('a)001:205: zhes brjod la gsal shing gnyis pa la me spar /
NK023('a)001:206: me 'bar ba dang gnyis su med par 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam /
NK023('a)001:207: gnyis pa mchod pa dbul ba ni /
NK023('a)001:208: rigs bzhi'i he ru ka la zhes pa dang /
NK023('a)001:209: gtor ma dang bdun rtsi rak+ta gsum dbul /
NK023('a)001:210: gsum pa la bskul tshig dang /
NK023('a)001:212: rigs bzhi'i he ru ka'i thugs kha nas /
NK023('a)001:213: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru brgyad shar //
NK023('a)001:214: snying po ru lu 'bru gu ya dz+nya na'i phar
NK023('a)001:215: 'phros dpal gyi thugs tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub
NK023('a)001:217: b+hud+d+ha rat+na pad+ma karma yab yum la ru lu re re dang gu ya re re gdags so //
NK023('a)001:219: chos dbyings dag pa phun tshogs 'dzin gsung mchog chos nan dbang drag shul bzhis bstod /
NK023('a)001:221: ho bcom ldan 'das rigs bzhi'i he ru ka yab yum la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK023('a)001:222: bdag cag rnal 'byor pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir 'tshogs pa rnams la /
NK023('a)001:223: shes bya'i chos thams cad la zhes pa yan chad 'agre'o //
NK023('a)001:224: drug pa bsdu ba gong bzhin bya'o //
NK023('a)001:225: de nas gsal shing rim pa gsum pa la /
NK023('a)001:226: lung gi he ru ka bzhi'i dngos grub blang ba'ang /
NK023('a)001:227: don drug gis ston pa'i dang po spyan drang ba ni /
NK023('a)001:228: pho brang gi mar me la lung gi he ru
NK023('a)001:229: yab yum mtshams bzhi'i rtsibs la bskyed pa de lcags
NK023('a)001:230: kyu'i mu tras spyan drang ste /
NK023('a)001:232: rak+sha kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK023('a)001:233: ru lu g+hu ya dz+nya na sa nu yab yum
NK023('a)001:234: ru lu g+hu ya g+hu ya yab yum ru lu
NK023('a)001:235: g+hu ya yag+sha yab yum ru lu g+hu ya dz+nya
NK023('a)001:236: na rnams sngags rim pas brjod la gsal shing rim
NK023('a)001:237: pa gsum pa la me spar /
NK023('a)001:238: 'bar ba dang gnyis su med par byon par bsam /
NK023('a)001:239: de nas gnyis pa mchod pa dbul ba ni /
NK023('a)001:240: lung gi he ru ka yab yum rnams la /
NK023('a)001:241: gtor ma bdud rtsi rak+ta gsum dbul /
NK023('a)001:242: gsum pa bskul tshig dang 'dzab gnyis kyi dang po bskul ba ni /
NK023('a)001:243: lung gi he ru'i thugs kha nas //
NK023('a)001:244: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru brgyad shar //
NK023('a)001:245: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK023('a)001:248: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK023('a)001:255: g+hu ya re re spel gyin gdags so //
NK023('a)001:257: h'u sbyor ba dam tshig gsang ba sgrol ba'i dbyings
NK023('a)001:258: log lta myong byed skye gnas reg bya 'joms 'ga'
NK023('a)001:259: na nyams pa mtshan ma sta na sgrol lung gi
NK023('a)001:260: khro rgyal tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK023('a)001:262: ho bcom ldan 'das lung gi he ru ka yab
NK023('a)001:263: yum gyi tshogs la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo
NK023('a)001:264: ni / bdag cag rnal 'byor pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir 'tshogs pa rnams la /
NK023('a)001:265: shes bya'i chos thams cad la zhes pa yan chad gong gis shes so //
NK023('a)001:266: drug pa bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK023('a)001:267: gsal shing gi rim pa bzhi pa la /
NK023('a)001:268: khro mo brgyad kyi si ti blang ba la drug gi dang po spyan drang ba ni /
NK023('a)001:269: mar me la khro mo brgyad bskyed pa de lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas spyan drang ba ni /
NK023('a)001:270: koo'u ri brgyad po'i rtsa sngags rdzogs par brjod la /
NK023('a)001:271: badz+ra am gu sha dza dza zhes pa brjod la ru lu dang g+hu ya bzlas /
NK023('a)001:272: sman raka gtor gsum kha'i koo'u ri brgyad kyi thugs
NK023('a)001:273: kha snying po g+hu ya dz+nya na'i 'od 'phros pas
NK023('a)001:274: / phar 'phros pas ni tshur 'dus bdag la 'dzab bya /
NK023('a)001:276: koo'u ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams ni //
NK023('a)001:277: gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul ba'i drag shul can //
NK023('a)001:278: sku mdog phyag rgya sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK023('a)001:279: ye shes khro mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK023('a)001:280: khro mo brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK023('a)001:281: zhes pa la sogs pa dang bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK023('a)001:282: gsal shing gi rim pa lnga pa la phra men
NK023('a)001:283: brgyad dang sgo ma bzhi'i pi ti blang pa la
NK023('a)001:284: drug gi dang po spyan drang ba ni /
NK023('a)001:285: pho brang gi mar me'i bar khyams dang po la
NK023('a)001:286: sing ha brgyad dang sgo ma bzhi bskyed la lcags
NK023('a)001:288: badz+ra sing ha mu kha he zhes rtsa sngags brgyad brjod /
NK023('a)001:289: badz+ra a gu sha dza dza /
NK023('a)001:291: yang sgo ma bzhi'i rtsa sngags badz+ra ar+ya te dza te nga dza la sogs pa bzhi brjod /
NK023('a)001:292: badz+ra a gu sha dza dza zhes brjod la gsal shing lnga pa la me sbar /
NK023('a)001:293: 'dong dang chas nas byon par bsam /
NK023('a)001:294: gnyis pa pu tsa sman raka gtor gsum gyis dbul /
NK023('a)001:295: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi bskul tshig ni /
NK023('a)001:296: sing ha phra men brgyad rnams dang /
NK023('a)001:297: sgo ma bzhi'i thugs kha nas /
NK023('a)001:298: snying po ru lu gu ya dz+nya na'i phar 'phros pas ni mchod /
NK023('a)001:299: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol /
NK023('a)001:301: sing ha brgyad po'i rtsa sngags dang sgo ma bzhi'i rtsa sngags ru lu spel la bzlas so //
NK023('a)001:304: h'u sing ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams ni /
NK023('a)001:305: ye shes las la 'gyed pa'i phra men ma /
NK023('a)001:306: rnam 'phrul las kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:307: seng ha phra men brgyad la phyag rta gdong la sogs sgo ma bzhi rnams ni //
NK023('a)001:308: tshad med bzhi yis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:309: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi thub par srung //
NK023('a)001:310: sgo skyong khro mo bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK023('a)001:312: phra men brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK023('a)001:313: shes bya'i chos thams cad ces pa dang /
NK023('a)001:314: drug pa bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK023('a)001:315: gsal shing gi rim pa drug pa la spor ma
NK023('a)001:316: brgyad dang gsang yum bzhi'i pi ti blang pa la
NK023('a)001:317: drug gi dang po spyan drang ba ni /
NK023('a)001:318: pho brang gi mar me'i bar khyams gnyis pa la bskyed pa de /
NK023('a)001:319: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK023('a)001:320: badz+ra a pra ti ar+ya ni /
NK023('a)001:322: a raka mo h'u zhes pa brgyad dang /
NK023('a)001:323: sh+ri badz+ra mud ka ra sha ru lu sh+ri badz+ra
NK023('a)001:324: ra ga sha ra ya ya na ma ru lu
NK023('a)001:325: sh+ri badz+ra g+han d+ha pra dza la ru lu ru
NK023('a)001:327: badz+ra a gu sha dza dza zhes brjod la gsal shing drug pa la me sbar /
NK023('a)001:328: 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam /
NK023('a)001:329: gnyis pa pu tsa sman rag gtor gsum sngags kyis dbul /
NK023('a)001:330: gsum pa la gnyis kyi bskul tshig ni /
NK023('a)001:331: spor byed chen mo brgyad rnams dang //
NK023('a)001:332: gsang yum bzhi yi thugs kha nas //
NK023('a)001:333: snying po ru lu gu ya dz+nya na'i phar 'phros pas mchod /
NK023('a)001:335: a rag mo h'u zhes pa brgyad dang /
NK023('a)001:336: ru lu dang gu ya spel la bzlas so //
NK023('a)001:338: h'u chos dbyings rnam dag ngang las rang snang ba'i //
NK023('a)001:339: sna tshogs cir yang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' zhing //
NK023('a)001:340: srid gsum zhing du sbyor bas g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK023('a)001:341: spor byed chen mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK023('a)001:342: bar khyams de'i shar lho nub byang sgor //
NK023('a)001:343: dgyes pa bskyed pa gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi //
NK023('a)001:344: gnyis med rol pa'i byin brlabs sna tshogs 'phro //
NK023('a)001:345: shes rab yum chen bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK023('a)001:347: ho spor ma chen mo brgyad dang gsang ba'i yum
NK023('a)001:348: chen bzhi la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni
NK023('a)001:349: zhes pa dang / drug pa bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK023('a)001:350: yang gsal shing gi rim pa bdun pa la dbang
NK023('a)001:351: phyug ma nyer brgyad kyi dngos grub blang ba la
NK023('a)001:352: don drug gis dang po spyan drang ba ni /
NK023('a)001:353: pho brang gi mar me'i bar khyams gsum pa la dbang mo nyer brgyad bskyed pa de /
NK023('a)001:354: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK023('a)001:355: b+h+yo ma nu rak+sha si b+h+yo la sogs pa'i rtsa sngags tshang bar brjod la /
NK023('a)001:357: badz+ra a gu sha dza dza zhes brjod la gsal shing bdun pa la me sbar /
NK023('a)001:358: 'dong dang chas nas byon par bsam /
NK023('a)001:359: gnyis pa pu tsa sman rag gtor gsum sngags kyi dbul /
NK023('a)001:360: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi dang po bskul ba ni /
NK023('a)001:361: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad thugs kha nas //
NK023('a)001:362: snying po ru lu gu ya dz+nya na'i 'od 'phros /
NK023('a)001:364: tshur 'dus bdag rtsa sngags nyer brgyad brjod la ru lu dang gu ya spel ma bzlos /
NK023('a)001:366: h'u mi srin la sogs dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK023('a)001:367: dregs pa lha chen rnams kyi chung ma ste //
NK023('a)001:368: dbang drag las la thogs pa med par spyod //
NK023('a)001:369: nyi shu rtsa brgyad tshogs la phyag lnga pa smon lam ni /
NK023('a)001:370: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni zhes pa dang /
NK023('a)001:372: gsal shing brgyad pa la mkha' 'gro so gnyis kyi
NK023('a)001:373: dngos grub blang ba la drug gi dang po spyan
NK023('a)001:374: drang ba ni / pho brang gi mar me la
NK023('a)001:375: bar khyams bzhi pa'i mkha' 'gro so gnyis su bskyed
NK023('a)001:376: drang ba ni / pa de / lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK023('a)001:377: e a ra li h'u zhes pa so gnyis brjod /
NK023('a)001:379: badz+ra a gu sha dza dza zhes brjod la gsal shing brgyad pa la me sbar /
NK023('a)001:380: 'od dang chas nas byon par bsam //
NK023('a)001:381: gnyis pa mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum sngags /
NK023('a)001:382: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi dang po bskul tshig ni /
NK023('a)001:383: mkha' 'gro so gnyis thugs kha nas /
NK023('a)001:384: snying po ru lu gu ya dz+nya na'i 'od 'phros pas /
NK023('a)001:385: phar 'phros pas tshur 'dus bdag e a ra li
NK023('a)001:386: h'u dang ru lu g+hu ya rnams spel la bzlas
NK023('a)001:387: so // bzhi pa bstod pa ni /
NK023('a)001:388: h'u nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK023('a)001:389: 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK023('a)001:390: ma sring byams ma'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:391: mkha' 'gro sum cu'i gnyis la phyag lnga pa smon lam ni /
NK023('a)001:392: mkha' 'gro so gnyis la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni zhes pa dang /
NK023('a)001:394: gsal shing dgu pa la ma mo bdun dang sring
NK023('a)001:395: mo bzhi'i dngos grub blang ba la drug gis dang
NK023('a)001:397: pho brang gi mar me'i bar khyams lnga pa la
NK023('a)001:398: ma mo bdun dang sring mo bzhi bskyed nas yod
NK023('a)001:399: pa de / lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK023('a)001:400: ma ma da du h'u bdun dang ru lu spel /
NK023('a)001:401: badz+ra dun ting b+h+yo zhes pa bzhi dang ru lu spel la /
NK023('a)001:402: badz+ra a gu sha dza dza zhes brjod la gsal shing dgu pa la me spar /
NK023('a)001:403: 'od dang chas nas byon par bsam /
NK023('a)001:404: gnyis pa mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi dang po bskul tshig ni /
NK023('a)001:405: ma bdun sring bzhi'i thugs kha snying rje ru lu
NK023('a)001:406: phar 'phros tshur 'dus ya ma da du h'u bdun
NK023('a)001:407: dang ru lu badz+ra dun+tim b+h+yo bzhi dang ru lu
NK023('a)001:410: h'u 'jig rten dregs pa 'dul ba ma mo'i tshogs //
NK023('a)001:411: phyi 'khor srung zhing nang 'khor skyong mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:412: dur khrod ma bdun las kyi sring mo bzhi //
NK023('a)001:413: bgegs srung ma mo rnams la lnga pa smon lam /
NK023('a)001:414: ma bdun sring bzhi la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK023('a)001:415: zhes pa dang drug pa bsdu ba gong dang 'dra'o //
NK023('a)001:416: gsal shing bcu pa la ging chen bco brgyad kyi
NK023('a)001:417: pi ti blang ba la drug gis dang po spyan
NK023('a)001:418: drang ba ni / pho brang gi mar me'i bar
NK023('a)001:419: khyams drug pa la ging chen bco brgyad bskyed pa
NK023('a)001:420: drang ba ni / de / lcags kyu'i mu tra bcas la /
NK023('a)001:421: ging ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu b+h+yo zhes pa bco brgyad dang /
NK023('a)001:423: badz+ra a gu sha dza dza zhes gsal shing rim pa dgu pa la me sbar /
NK023('a)001:424: 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam //
NK023('a)001:425: gnyis pa mchod pa sman raka gtor gsum pa bzlas pa'i skul tshig ni /
NK023('a)001:426: ging chen bco brgyad thugs kha nas //
NK023('a)001:427: snying po ru lu gu ya dz+nya na'i phar 'phros
NK023('a)001:428: tshul 'dus ging ka ra ha ha ru lu ru
NK023('a)001:429: lu b+h+yo zhes pa bco brgyad dang ru lu spel
NK023('a)001:431: h'u khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging chen bco brgyad ni //
NK023('a)001:432: srid gsum las la thogs med bsgrol la brtson //
NK023('a)001:433: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu gtan nas brlag par byed //
NK023('a)001:434: ging chen ging lcam tshogs la phyag lnga pa smon lam ni /
NK023('a)001:435: ging chen po bco brgyad la zhes pa dang drug pa bsdu ba 'dra'o //
NK023('a)001:436: gsal shing gi rim pa bcu gcig pa la steng
NK023('a)001:437: phyogs kyi khro bo khro mo drug cu'i dngos grub
NK023('a)001:438: blang ba la drug gis dang po spyan drang ba
NK023('a)001:439: ni / pho brang gi mar me'i bar khyams bdun
NK023('a)001:440: pa la khro bo khro mo drug cu bskyed pa
NK023('a)001:441: ni / de / lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK023('a)001:442: kro ta kro ti h'u zhes pa dang /
NK023('a)001:443: ru lu spel la drug cu bzlas /
NK023('a)001:444: badz+ra a gu sha dza dza zhes brjod la /
NK023('a)001:445: gsal shing bcu gcig pa la me sbar /
NK023('a)001:446: 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam //
NK023('a)001:447: gnyis pa pu tsa sman raka gtor gsum sngags kyis kha'i /
NK023('a)001:448: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi dang po bskul tshig ni /
NK023('a)001:449: khro bo khro mo drug cu'i thugs kha nas /
NK023('a)001:450: snying po ru lu g+hu ya dz+nya na'i phar 'phros tshur 'dus kro ta kro ti h'u /
NK023('a)001:451: ru lu g+hu ya spel la bzlas so //
NK023('a)001:453: bcom ldan h'u mdzad sa gsum brjid kyis gnon //
NK023('a)001:454: khams gsum 'dul mdzad ye shes lha yi lha //
NK023('a)001:455: 'jigs byed 'bar bas gdug pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms //
NK023('a)001:456: khro bo khro mo rnams la phyag lnga pa smon lam /
NK023('a)001:457: khro bo khro mo drug cu la dngos grub ces pa dang /
NK023('a)001:458: drug pa bsdu ba gong dang mthun no //
NK023('a)001:459: gsal shing rim pa bcu gnyis pa la phyogs bzhi'i
NK023('a)001:460: pho nya gnyis brgya dang bzhi bcu'i dngos grub blang
NK023('a)001:461: ba la drug gis dang po spyan drang ba ni
NK023('a)001:462: / pho brang gi mar me'i bar khyams brgyad pa la /
NK023('a)001:463: shar du rba na rba na a gu sha dza
NK023('a)001:464: zhes pa drug cus dung gi pho nya drug cu
NK023('a)001:465: / lhor ha la ha la pa sha h'u zhes
NK023('a)001:466: pa drug cus lcags dang gser gyi pho nya drug
NK023('a)001:467: / cu / nub phyogs su gardza gardza spo ta ba zhes pas bse'i pho nya drug cu /
NK023('a)001:468: byang phyogs su pa tsa pa tsa g+han d+ha ho zhes g.yu'i pho nya drug cu /
NK023('a)001:469: badz+ra a gu sha dza dza zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgya spyan drang /
NK023('a)001:470: gsal shing bcu gnyis pa la me sbar /
NK023('a)001:471: 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam /
NK023('a)001:472: gnyis pa mchod pa sman raka gtor gsum gyis dbul /
NK023('a)001:473: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis las bskul tshigs ni /
NK023('a)001:474: pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu'i thugs kha nas /
NK023('a)001:475: snying po ru lu g+hu ya dz+nya na'i phar phros
NK023('a)001:476: tshur 'dus rba na rba na a gu sha dza
NK023('a)001:477: / ru lu ha la ha la pa sha h'u /
NK023('a)001:478: ru lu gardza gardza spo ta ba /
NK023('a)001:479: ru lu pa tsa pa tsa g+han d+ha ho /
NK023('a)001:480: ru lu g+hu ya bzhi pa bstod pa ni /
NK023('a)001:481: h'u ye shes thugs rjes phyogs bcur khyab pa yi //
NK023('a)001:482: gdon bgegs 'dul ba'i las la thogs pa med //
NK023('a)001:483: ci bgyi bka' nyan las rnams myur mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:484: phyogs bzhi pho nya'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK023('a)001:486: phyogs bzhi'i pho nya gnyis brgya bzhi bcu la dngos
NK023('a)001:487: grub tu gsol ba'i zhes pa la sogs pa dang
NK023('a)001:489: gsal shing gi rim pa bcu gsum pa la /
NK023('a)001:490: 'og phyogs kyi ma mo drug cu'i dngos grub blang
NK023('a)001:491: ba la drug gi dang po spyan drang ba ni
NK023('a)001:492: / pho brang gi mar me la bar khyams dgu pa na /
NK023('a)001:493: ma ma sha ra h'u zhes ma mo drug cu bskyed pa de /
NK023('a)001:494: badz+ra a gu sha dza dza zhes lcags kyu'i mu tras spyan drang /
NK023('a)001:495: gsal shing bcu gsum pa la me sbar /
NK023('a)001:496: 'od dang bcas nas gsal shing gi rtse mor byon par bsam /
NK023('a)001:497: gnyis pa pu tsa sman rag gtor gsum gyi sngags kyis dbul /
NK023('a)001:498: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi dang po bskul tshig brjod pa ni /
NK023('a)001:499: ma mo drug cu'i thugs kha nas /
NK023('a)001:500: snying po ru lu g+hu ya dz+nya na'i phar 'phros tshur 'dus ma ma sha ra h'u /
NK023('a)001:501: ru lu g+hu ya bzhi pa bstod pa ni /
NK023('a)001:502: h'u stong khams yongs su las la dbang ba yi //
NK023('a)001:503: ma chen rgyal mo srid pa gsum gyi bdag /
NK023('a)001:504: yum chen las la dbang ba'i dbang mo che //
NK023('a)001:505: ma mo drug cu'i tshogs la phyag lnga pa smon lam ni /
NK023('a)001:506: 'og phyogs kyi ma mo drug cu la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK023('a)001:507: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK023('a)001:509: de nas gsal shing gi rim pa bcu bzhi pa la /
NK023('a)001:510: khro bo khro mo khra thabs rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang
NK023('a)001:511: gi dngos grub blang ba'ang don drug gi dang po
NK023('a)001:513: pho brang gi mar me'i bar khyams bcu pa na khro bo /
NK023('a)001:514: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ra gyi li h'u /
NK023('a)001:515: badz+ra yo gi ni gu ru sa ma ya dza
NK023('a)001:516: zhes rig 'dzin pa'i tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK023('a)001:517: bskyed pa de gsal shing gi rim pa bcu bzhi
NK023('a)001:518: pa la / badz+ra a gu sha dza dza zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la spyan drang /
NK023('a)001:519: gsal shing bcu bzhi pa la me sbar /
NK023('a)001:520: 'od dang bcas nas gsal shing gi rtse la byon par bsam /
NK023('a)001:522: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha hi /
NK023('a)001:524: ma h+aa b+ha lim ta kha hi /
NK023('a)001:525: zhes sman raka gtor ma dbul lo //
NK023('a)001:526: gsum pa bzlas pa la bskul tshig dang 'dzab gnyis kyi dang po bskul tshig ni /
NK023('a)001:527: man ngag mdo lung brgyud dang bcas pa yi /
NK023('a)001:528: rig 'dzin bla ma rnams kyi thugs ka nas /
NK023('a)001:529: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK023('a)001:532: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK023('a)001:534: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ra gyi li h'u /
NK023('a)001:535: badz+ra yo gi ni gu ru sa ma ya dza /
NK023('a)001:536: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK023('a)001:537: g+hu ya dz+nya na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h'u /
NK023('a)001:539: h'u rig 'dzin bla ma byin rlabs ldan pa'i tshogs //
NK023('a)001:540: lhun grub phyag chen tshe dbang rnam smin gyi //
NK023('a)001:541: rgya gar bod kyi grub thob tshogs bcas pa'i //
NK023('a)001:542: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi dngos grub 'dir stsol cig /
NK023('a)001:544: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi tshogs rnams la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK023('a)001:545: zhes pa la sogs pa rnams gong gi ji lta ba bzhin bya'o //
NK023('a)001:547: badz+ra a gu sha dza dza zhes lan gsum brjod pas /
NK023('a)001:550: gsum pas sku 'od du zhu nas bdag nyid la thim pas /
NK023('a)001:551: bdag sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gzi byin dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK023('a)001:552: de ltar cho ga'i rim pa rnams tshar ba dang gsal shing gi 'brang rgyas de /
NK023('a)001:553: dpon slob rnams grangs mnyam par gras la de'i bar la slob bu rnams khrus rim cig bya /
NK023('a)001:558: rnal 'byor pa rnams rol la dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:566: theg pa brgyad kyi bka' babs brgyud pa dang /
NK023('a)001:568: tshe dpal dang bcas pa'i dngos grub dus phyi ma
NK023('a)001:569: bsdad mi 'tshal bar da lta nyid du thob 'thob
NK023('a)001:571: 'di ni dbang bzhi pa zab dbang gsum pa'i theg dagu'o //
NK023('a)001:575: da ni thabs bstan par bya ste /
NK023('a)001:577: bcos ma'i dbang bskur ba'i thabs dang /
NK023('a)001:578: rnal ma'i dbang bskur thabs so //
NK023('a)001:579: de yang bcos ma'i sbyor ba la brten nas rnal ma'i don la 'jug par bya /
NK023('a)001:580: bcos ma'i dbang bskur rtags kyi bda' zhes bya ba 'byung ngo //
NK023('a)001:581: de yang tha ma'i don du phyogs 'dzin gyi mi brgyad de /
NK023('a)001:584: byang chub sems dpa'i dbang dang /
NK023('a)001:586: ma h+aa yo ga'i dbang dang /
NK023('a)001:587: a nu yo ga'i dbang dang /
NK023('a)001:589: nyan thos kyi dbang bskur ba'i thabs la gsum ste /
NK023('a)001:595: 'dod chags kyi blo bzlog nas smin mtshams su rus
NK023('a)001:596: pa'i thig le sran ma tsam gcig la shes pa
NK023('a)001:597: gtad la / de je che je che la lus po thams cad rus pa'i phung por bsams la /
NK023('a)001:598: de nyid la blo cog gis bzhag pa ni sgom pa'o //
NK023('a)001:599: de ni bskyed pa'i rim pa'o //
NK023('a)001:601: rus pa'i phung po de sbyor ba'i blos ci tsam lcogs tshad tshun chad du /
NK023('a)001:602: rus pa'i phung por gsal la shes pa rus pa'i
NK023('a)001:603: thig le snga ma tsam gcig smin mtshams na yod
NK023('a)001:604: pa de la ma 'phros par bzung nas yid la
NK023('a)001:607: rgyud las nye ba'i sras bzhi yis //
NK023('a)001:608: gnyan yod tshal ni nyams dga' bar //
NK023('a)001:609: keng rus lta ba dngos bzlog cing //
NK023('a)001:610: chags sdang spangs pa'i dgra bcom thob //
NK023('a)001:612: dbang po 'bring ni srog dang rtsol ba la slob pa ste /
NK023('a)001:613: dbugs phar 'gro tshur 'ong la shes pa gtad de /
NK023('a)001:615: dpa' lcags lta bur phyir phyung bas dang /
NK023('a)001:617: rlung de kha dog ni shel lta bu dang /
NK023('a)001:618: chab ron lta bu la shes pa gtad la yun ring par sbyangs nas /
NK023('a)001:619: shes pa kha nang du ltas nas de'i ngang la rtog pa mi 'gyur ba de ni sgom pa'o //
NK023('a)001:623: rlung gi rtsa ba gcod par bya zhes so //
NK023('a)001:624: nyan thos dbang po rab cig bdag 'dzin gyi blo bzlog ste /
NK023('a)001:627: skra'i rtse mo nas rkang mthil dang phyi nang bar gsum du brtsal kyang ma rnyed /
NK023('a)001:628: gzhan la btsal bas kyang ma rnyed /
NK023('a)001:629: gzhan rang yang ma rnyed de /
NK023('a)001:630: bdag gzhan stong par mthong ba de'i ngang la rtse gcig tu bsgom pa'o //
NK023('a)001:631: de yang nga dang bdag tu 'dzin pa mu stegs 'khrul pa'i lam zhes pa'o //
NK023('a)001:632: yang brten pa las kyi rlung bzung nas /
NK023('a)001:633: rang 'dod drag po'i rkam chags kyi //
NK023('a)001:634: dgra bcom lnga brgya'i dbang bskur thob //
NK023('a)001:636: rang rgyal ba'i dbang bskur thabs ni /
NK023('a)001:637: chos thams cad phyi nang rten 'brel bcu gnyis su 'dod de /
NK023('a)001:638: phyi rten cing 'brel bar byung ba bcu gnyis ni /
NK023('a)001:639: sa bon myu gu lo 'dab sdong po me tog 'bras bu dang drug /
NK023('a)001:640: 'byung ba lnga dus kyi 'gyur ba dang drug /
NK023('a)001:641: bcu gnyis po de rim par ded pas nam mkhar song bas /
NK023('a)001:642: nam mkha' la 'byung ba ma rnyed de stong pa'o //
NK023('a)001:643: nang rten cing 'brel bar byung ba bcu gnyis ni /
NK023('a)001:644: ma rig pa nas rga shi yan chad de /
NK023('a)001:645: dang po lus po 'di ci las byung brtags pas /
NK023('a)001:647: skyes pa ci las byung na yar ded pas ma rig pa la thug /
NK023('a)001:648: ma rig pa las 'byung ba ma rnyed /
NK023('a)001:649: de nyid brtags pas stong par mthong bas /
NK023('a)001:650: phyi nang gnyis stong par mthong la /
NK023('a)001:651: nyams su myong ba de la sems rtse gcig tu gnas te /
NK023('a)001:652: gnyid sad pa'i shes pa bzhin gnas pa ni sgom pa'o //
NK023('a)001:654: sngon gyi bag chags goms stobs kyis //
NK023('a)001:655: srid pa las ni srid par mtshams sbyar nas //
NK023('a)001:656: rten 'brel srid pa'i 'khor lor rtogs zhes 'byung ngo //
NK023('a)001:657: byang chub sems dpa'i dbang bskur ba'i thabs ni //
NK023('a)001:659: sems tsam pa'i dbang dang bcas pas /
NK023('a)001:661: dbu ma chen po'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:663: shes pa sna rtse la gtad de rtog pa chad pa de /
NK023('a)001:664: shes pa stong sang nge ba la gtad la /
NK023('a)001:665: shes pa gnas pa de dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:666: sems tsam pa la gnyis te /
NK023('a)001:667: rnam pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK023('a)001:669: rnam pa dang bcas pa ni me mar ram 'od de chu dang brlan ltar /
NK023('a)001:670: shes pa dang snang ba gnyis /
NK023('a)001:671: shes pa yod na snang ba yod /
NK023('a)001:672: snang ba yod na shes pa yod pa ste /
NK023('a)001:673: yul dang shes pa tha dad du mi 'dod /
NK023('a)001:674: tha mi dad pas snang bzhin du rtog pa ma zhugs pa de sgom pa'o //
NK023('a)001:676: shes pa la zhen pa'i blo bzlog ste /
NK023('a)001:677: rdzas dang rnam pa ni bem po'o //
NK023('a)001:678: sgom pa ni yi dam lha bsgom du bcug la mdun du man+dala byas la /
NK023('a)001:680: tha mar yi dam lha la btags pas /
NK023('a)001:681: lha'i ngo bo nam mkha' la sprin bzhin du gyur te /
NK023('a)001:682: rang gi rig pa gsal la mi rtog de sgom pa'o //
NK023('a)001:683: sgyu ma lta bu'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:684: yang dag pa la zhen pa'i blo bzlog ste //
NK023('a)001:685: snyug ma gcig la me long gcig btags la //
NK023('a)001:686: de la lta ru bcug la de la ltas pas
NK023('a)001:687: thams cad gzugs brnyan lta bur nyams su myong ste
NK023('a)001:688: / gzugs brnyan dran pa tsam gyis ci snang ba thams cad sgyu ma'i tshul du bya'o //
NK023('a)001:689: rmi lam brjed pa lta bu dang /
NK023('a)001:690: sgyu ma dran pa tsam gyi tshul du sgom pa'o //
NK023('a)001:691: dbu ma chen po'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:692: mchod rten gcig mdun du bzhag la de la phyogs cha drug gis gzhigs pas phyogs cha ma grub /
NK023('a)001:693: phyogs cha 'jal mkhan gyi shes pa la ltas pas ma grub ste /
NK023('a)001:694: grub pa dang ma grub pa dang dbu ma gsum
NK023('a)001:695: la mi gnas pas zhen 'dzin dang mtha' gang la
NK023('a)001:696: yang mi gnas par sgom pa'o //
NK023('a)001:698: dang po so sor lta ba'i rigs pa can //
NK023('a)001:699: bdag med gnyis kyis zhen bzlog cing //
NK023('a)001:700: zhi gnas lhag mthong 'brel ba yis //
NK023('a)001:701: lam lnga sa bcu rims kyis thob //
NK023('a)001:703: da ni 'bras bu'i dbang ston te /
NK023('a)001:710: gnyis ka'i rgyud kyi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:711: kri ya'i dbang ni rigs gsum gyi thang ka'am /
NK023('a)001:712: lung ma gcig la shes pa gtad du bcug la /
NK023('a)001:713: de tshun chad khams kyi tshad bzung la de brtan tu gzhug /
NK023('a)001:714: gsal ba gsum dbang bskur te /
NK023('a)001:715: dang po la mana dzu sh+ri mu bzlos su gzhug /
NK023('a)001:716: de nas sgra de la shes pa ma yengs par gtad du bcug la /
NK023('a)001:717: de nas sgra de brag cha lta bur rtogs pa de la shes pa gtad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:718: de gnyis ka la brtags pas mi rtog pa bskyed pa de la thugs so //
NK023('a)001:719: de dag la gsum gyis bstan te /
NK023('a)001:720: phyi dag pa khrus dang gtsang sbra /
NK023('a)001:721: dka' thub kyis rigs gsum gyi dkyil 'khor du zhugs la /
NK023('a)001:722: nang dag pa ni rigs gsum gsal ba'o //
NK023('a)001:723: don skye ba med pa'i rgyas gdab pa ni dag pa gsum mo //
NK023('a)001:724: gnyis ka'i rgyud la bzhi ste /
NK023('a)001:725: dang po bris sku la shes pa gtad pas mi rtog pa skye /
NK023('a)001:726: thugs rdo rje gcig la shes pa gtad pas mi rtog pa skye /
NK023('a)001:727: bzlas pa'i de kho na nyid ni /
NK023('a)001:728: rang sngags bzlos pa'i sgra la shes pa gtad mi rtog par gsal ba'o //
NK023('a)001:730: stobs chen 'byung ba'i gnas chen du //
NK023('a)001:731: dag pa gsum gyis gzhi bzung nas //
NK023('a)001:732: mthu chen lag na rdo rje yis //
NK023('a)001:733: rigs gsum stobs kyi dkyil 'khor bri //
NK023('a)001:735: da ni yo ga'i dbang bskur thabs ni /
NK023('a)001:736: cho ga yan lag bcu gcig dang //
NK023('a)001:737: rnam par snang mdzad bskyed de ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK023('a)001:738: ras sam ltor gzo la stim pa'i gzugs brnyan de
NK023('a)001:739: la shes pa sgrims te gtad pas rig pa gsal
NK023('a)001:740: mi rtog pa ni sgom pa'o //
NK023('a)001:741: de nyid la brtags pas lha gsal la ngo bo ma rnyed pa ni nyams su myong ba'o //
NK023('a)001:742: sngags nang pa la gnyis te /
NK023('a)001:743: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga'i dbang dang /
NK023('a)001:744: rdzogs pa la a nu yo ga'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:745: ma h+aa yo ga la gnyis te /
NK023('a)001:747: rdzogs pa bde ba'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:748: bskyed pa'i dbang bskur thabs la bzhi ste /
NK023('a)001:750: nus pa skyed pa'i dbang dang /
NK023('a)001:751: nyams myong bskyed pa'i dbang dang /
NK023('a)001:752: nyams myong brtan pa'i dbang dang /
NK023('a)001:753: bstan pa nyams su len pa'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:754: phan pa'i dbang bcu ni sa bon dang 'dra ste /
NK023('a)001:755: gang dag mos pa'i dkyil 'khor du bcug ste /
NK023('a)001:756: rang bzhin lha'i sku byin gyis brlabs la yi dam dbog spro bskyed de /
NK023('a)001:757: de nas byin gyis brlabs kyis nus pa skyed pa'i yon tan yod pas sa bon 'jog pa'o //
NK023('a)001:758: nus pa bskyed pa'i dbang lnga thob pas /
NK023('a)001:759: nyan pa dang sgom pa dang 'chad pa dang phrin
NK023('a)001:760: las dang rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi
NK023('a)001:761: dbang gis byed nus pas nus skyed pa'i dbang ngo
NK023('a)001:762: // nyams myong skyes pa gsang ba'i dbang ni steng sgo dang 'og sgo'o //
NK023('a)001:763: steng sgo 'khor lo la brten nas rlung las su rung dgos te /
NK023('a)001:766: de yang bem po'i rlung bzung nas /
NK023('a)001:767: rig pa'i rlung gsal bar byed pa ste /
NK023('a)001:768: de yang bzung thabs gnyis te /
NK023('a)001:769: btsan thabs su bzung ba dang /
NK023('a)001:771: btsan thabs su bzung ba ni bdag gi spyi bor rdo rje slob dpon sgom /
NK023('a)001:772: bdag nyid yi dam lhar sgom lus bde ba la stong pa'i rgyas btab nas 'jog ste /
NK023('a)001:773: de'i sgo nas nyams myong skyes pa ni ye shes btsan thabs kyi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:774: yang thabs las h'u gis khong rings kheg thag par yar drang ngo //
NK023('a)001:775: de yang ba yi man ngag de ltar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:776: lus sbram par mi stong bar bsam ste /
NK023('a)001:778: steng sgo tshangs pa'i bu ga yar har ba /
NK023('a)001:780: dper na snod zhabs phyung ba ltar byas la /
NK023('a)001:781: rlung dang shes pa drang bar bya ste 'dren tsa na 'og sgo bsdam /
NK023('a)001:782: lus sgrims la kha sna'i dbugs spyi gtsug tu drang /
NK023('a)001:783: de ltar sgoms pas bems po'i rlung dang rig pa'i rtsar zhugs pa'i byung ba pa ni /
NK023('a)001:787: ku co'i sgra sgrogs pa dang /
NK023('a)001:791: lus mi gtan te 'khyor ba rnams 'byung ste /
NK023('a)001:792: de yang ye shes btsan thabs kyi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:793: yang phyi rol du pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa gcig bsams la /
NK023('a)001:794: dbugs nang du zhugs tsa na pad+ma de yang nang du zhugs /
NK023('a)001:795: dbugs rgyu tsam na pad+ma de yang phyi krong nge yod par bsam mo //
NK023('a)001:796: sprul pa'i 'khor lo la mar khog stong na yar 'bar ba'o //
NK023('a)001:797: 'od gyen du song bas bde ba'i 'khor lo zhu nas 'dzag par bsam /
NK023('a)001:798: lus tsog pur sdad pa'i 'og nas gzhu rgyud kha gyen ltas gcig yod par bsams la /
NK023('a)001:799: de yang btsan thabs kyi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:800: 'jam rlung gi sgo nas yang bzung ba ni /
NK023('a)001:802: zhugs nas gnas pa'i rlung ngo //
NK023('a)001:803: 'grang ba'i rlung ni yun ring thung gi tshad do //
NK023('a)001:804: rlung je rings brlab ste 'jug pas rlung de yang bslabs pas a ba d+hu tir tshud do //
NK023('a)001:809: gnyid chung ba ni rlung zin pa'i rtags so //
NK023('a)001:810: 'og sgo la brten pa ni phyag rgya ma lo
NK023('a)001:811: bcu drug lon pa gcig la thig le dbab pa
NK023('a)001:812: dang rlung gis thig le rdo rje'i rtse mo nas
NK023('a)001:813: bzung dang / bzlog pa ste rtsa dbu mar drang ba dang /
NK023('a)001:814: drangs pa de rtsa gnas su 'grang ba'o //
NK023('a)001:815: de la mi rtog pa'i ye shes skyes pa ni dbang thob pa'o //
NK023('a)001:817: chags pa g.yas g.yon lam gyis bcing //
NK023('a)001:818: lkam chags rang gis srid par yong //
NK023('a)001:819: mtshan ma len pa'i lam du zhugs //
NK023('a)001:821: yang a nu yo ga'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:822: dang po nyid nas lhar gsal bar byas la /
NK023('a)001:823: de la shes pa ma yengs par gtad du bcug la /
NK023('a)001:824: de nas shes pa de btsal bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:825: de ni rig pa'i ye shes kyi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:826: rig pa chos kyi dbang ni nam mkha' stong pa la lta ru bzhug ste /
NK023('a)001:827: ltas na dngos po med de /
NK023('a)001:828: tha mal gyi rgyu ba chad pa de kho na'o //
NK023('a)001:829: bde ba chen po'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:830: thabs tha mal sbyor du bzhugs pa'o //
NK023('a)001:831: bcos ma'i dbang gi rim pa rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:832: bla ma chen po lha rje nya tshal ba'i lugs lags so //
NK023('a)001:836: zab dbang rnams kyi chog phrin mdo ltar 'di skad du /
NK023('a)001:837: bla ma bsod nams mgon pos sras sh+aakya mgon po la gnang ba'i zab rgyas las /
NK023('a)001:838: zhag bcu gcig tu 'gro ba'i nub bo //
NK023('a)001:839: rdzogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor pad+ma bcu drug lte ba dang bcu bdun la /
NK023('a)001:840: a bcu drug dang dbus su a kha sprod bris te /
NK023('a)001:841: bco brgyad la kun tu bzang po bco brgyad bkod /
NK023('a)001:842: de'i steng du bum pa gcig tu rdzas kun blugs
NK023('a)001:843: la kun tu bzang po yab yum sbyor ba'i b+ho
NK023('a)001:844: d+hi bsam / de'i shar du pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes mtshon /
NK023('a)001:845: dbus mthing ka la rgyal ba rigs lnga bkod /
NK023('a)001:846: de'i steng du thod pa bzang po gcig tu sngon
NK023('a)001:847: gyi sman gsang ba byang chub sems 'o ma dang
NK023('a)001:849: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum sbyor ba'i bo d+her bsam /
NK023('a)001:850: nub tu tshe'i dkyil 'khor 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lto ba dang bcas pa la /
NK023('a)001:851: de'i dbus su tshe'i 'brang rgyas la thabs shes rab bdud rtsi'i sman lta yod pa bshams la /
NK023('a)001:852: rigs lnga'i rang bzhin du bsams pa mchod pa gzhung bzhin du bsham mo //
NK023('a)001:855: kun bzang don gyi phrin las bya /
NK023('a)001:856: gsang dbang la zhi khro gzhung bsrang /
NK023('a)001:858: sh+ri ma h+aa su kha b+ho d+he badz+ra h'u ho zhes bzlas /
NK023('a)001:859: de nas dbang bskur te gzung ma lo nyi shu zhes so //
NK023('a)001:860: bo d+he slob ma'i lce thog tu bzhag pas /
NK023('a)001:861: h'u de rdo rje sems dpa' phra mor bsams la /
NK023('a)001:863: rigs drug tu skye bar byed pa'i sa bon sregs nas slar mi skye bar bsam mo //
NK023('a)001:864: de nas rang gi snying kha'i pad+ma 'dab ma bcu
NK023('a)001:865: drug gi a snang la rang bzhin med par bsam
NK023('a)001:866: / de rnams dbus kyi a la thim pas rtsis gdab dang bral bar bsam mo //
NK023('a)001:871: de rnams ni gdams yig nas byung ba bzhin du man ngag shes par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:872: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ra gyi li h'u zhes bzlas par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:875: las mkhan dang mched lcam gyis phyir gtor ma bskyang /
NK023('a)001:876: slob dpon dang rgyal theb kyis dug gsum sbyin sreg bya /
NK023('a)001:878: zhes gsungs pa rtsa ba rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:883: dang po bla mas yi dam la 'bum bsnyen /
NK023('a)001:884: bar du shes rab dang bcas pas 'bum snyen tshang bar bya ste /
NK023('a)001:886: gsang dbang bla ma las blang ba dang /
NK023('a)001:887: shes rab ye shes bla ma'i bka' dang byin brlabs ltar blang ba dang /
NK023('a)001:888: bde ba chen po dang shin tu brtan pa bla ma'i man ngag go //
NK023('a)001:889: 'dus pa mdo'i zab mo dbang gsum bskur bar 'dod pas /
NK023('a)001:890: rang gi rgyun khyer gang rlung steng du 'phyur stod tshangs sel ba dang mtshungs te /
NK023('a)001:892: rdo rje sems gtso khyod la 'dud //
NK023('a)001:893: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK023('a)001:894: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK023('a)001:895: mgon po dpa' bo skyabs gsol zhing //
NK023('a)001:896: theg chen khang par bzhugs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:897: mkhyen rabs ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK023('a)001:898: zhes bla ma la zhus pas /
NK023('a)001:899: bla mas kyang mtheb srin gyis lag pa nas bzung la /
NK023('a)001:900: bu 'dir shog cig ci bde bar /
NK023('a)001:901: las spyod rim par 'gro ba las /
NK023('a)001:902: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje zung /
NK023('a)001:903: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen po /
NK023('a)001:904: dmigs pa med par gnas phyir du /
NK023('a)001:905: ser sna med pa'i dang yid kyis /
NK023('a)001:906: gtong zhing rang sems brtan par zung /
NK023('a)001:907: ye shes rang gnas rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK023('a)001:913: dbang 'jug sgo yan chad gsang ba ltar bshad rgyud dang /
NK023('a)001:914: ma rgyud na gsal bar yod /
NK023('a)001:918: // // 'dus pa chen po mdo'i gsang dbang bskur ba /
NK023('a)001:919: de spyi mtshan dang ldan pa btsal khrus byas la /
NK023('a)001:920: brgyan gyis brgyan bla ma la dbul /
NK023('a)001:921: bla mas mdun du bzhag ste /
NK023('a)001:922: khrus bya sgrib bral lus stong pa nyid las kun tu bzang mor brlab /
NK023('a)001:923: de'i gnas lngar yum lnga bkod /
NK023('a)001:924: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi /
NK023('a)001:925: mkha' pa las pad+ma 'dab brgyad dbus su e mthing skya me yi 'od dang ldan par bsam /
NK023('a)001:927: yum dang 'dra bar yab la bkod /
NK023('a)001:928: de nas yum lhar gsal ba la dbu rgyan cod pan dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:929: de nas thal mo sbyar la /
NK023('a)001:930: rdo rje dga' ma bdag la dgongs //
NK023('a)001:932: dges pa chen po thabs lam gyis //
NK023('a)001:933: chu bo bzhi la bdag bsgrol mdzod //
NK023('a)001:936: bu khyod smros dang thabs lam 'di //
NK023('a)001:937: rgyal ba yongs kyis sbas pa yin //
NK023('a)001:938: thabs chen gsang ba'i theg pa ru //
NK023('a)001:939: gtsang sme'i 'ching ba sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:940: dri sha chu dang bza' btung dang //
NK023('a)001:941: nga yi cho ga'i ye shes bzhi //
NK023('a)001:942: 'o dang gzhig dang drang ba dang //
NK023('a)001:943: sems chu btung bar khyed nus sam //
NK023('a)001:945: e ma thabs lam ye shes phyir //
NK023('a)001:946: bdag ni ci la'ang mi nus med //
NK023('a)001:947: de dag bdag gis spyad par bgyi //
NK023('a)001:948: ji ltar sad phyir bdag la stsol //
NK023('a)001:950: de nas dam rdzas la 'dzem pa'i nyes dmigs bshad do //
NK023('a)001:953: de nas rol pa nyi shu'i cha rdzogs par bya /
NK023('a)001:954: rol pa 'dod pa'i dngos po spangs pas byas la /
NK023('a)001:959: byang sems tha mi dad pa de /
NK023('a)001:960: rdo rje lce gnyis gang rung gis blangs la /
NK023('a)001:961: slob bu brdas bos te sgyu 'phrul ltar tshig brjod la /
NK023('a)001:962: ba dang be'u dang bya dang bye'u tshul du lce'i rtse nas bstim /
NK023('a)001:963: khu ba h'u dkar po'am rdo rje sems dpa' 'ba' zhig tu 'phros /
NK023('a)001:966: slob bu'i sgo gsum ye shes su phar gsal /
NK023('a)001:967: shes pa h'u ring sa las /
NK023('a)001:969: mi 'gyur zhes brjod de lha gsal ba la dbang sbyin /
NK023('a)001:970: bde ba chen po'i chos sku zhes bshad do //
NK023('a)001:971: gnyer gtad la sgyu 'phrul dang mthun par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:973: mdo'i gsang dbang gi byang bu rtsa ba /
NK023('a)001:977: // // mi 'gyur rgyal ba'i ye shes gnas /
NK023('a)001:978: ma brtsal phyin pas bde ba'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:979: mkha' ltar gsal ba'i ye shes spyan //
NK023('a)001:980: gang na med pas kun gyi rje //
NK023('a)001:981: ye shes rang gnas bdal ba la //
NK023('a)001:982: mi 'gyur g.yung drung sa thob shog /
NK023('a)001:983: ma h+aa g+hu ya b+h+ru dz+nya na man+dala /
NK023('a)001:984: dz+ny+aa na g+hu h+ya sid d+hi sa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK023('a)001:986: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK023('a)001:987: bde ba'i 'bru tshogs gsal ba'i rgyun //
NK023('a)001:989: rtse nas bstim zhing dkyil 'khor bsgyur //
NK023('a)001:991: yig 'bru h'u gi tshogs zhes so //
NK023('a)001:992: bde ba chen po chos kyi sku //
NK023('a)001:993: shes rab thabs kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:994: 'di dang skye ba thams cad du //
NK023('a)001:995: dngos grub ster 'di ma spong zhig /
NK023('a)001:996: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK023('a)001:997: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas khyod la 'byung //
NK023('a)001:998: spangs na rdo rje dbyings phyug stsal //
NK023('a)001:999: bkug dang bstims pa ma shes na //
NK023('a)001:1000: rdo rje skal bar mthar rlags par //
NK023('a)001:1001: chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK023('a)001:1004: de ring phad chad bu khyod kyi //
NK023('a)001:1005: rdo rje sems dpa' nga yin pas //
NK023('a)001:1006: nga yis ji skad bsgo ba bzhin //
NK023('a)001:1007: bu khyod kyis kyang bya dgos so //
NK023('a)001:1010: // gsang sngags 'dus pa mdo'i bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur ba la /
NK023('a)001:1011: las kyi phyag rgya mtshan ldan rnyed na /
NK023('a)001:1014: de nas phyi'i dbang rnams bskur la lha bsgom du bzhug /
NK023('a)001:1017: de nas 'dod pa'i bstan chos kyi rim pa rnams bshad pa dang /
NK023('a)001:1018: rang gi bde ba dbab pa'i thabs /
NK023('a)001:1020: rtsa sgra thig le rnams dbab pa'i thabs gang bde ba rnams slabs la /
NK023('a)001:1022: sha chen gyi tshod ma dang /
NK023('a)001:1024: a ru ra dang nye shing gi khu ba btung ba dang /
NK023('a)001:1025: khrus byas shing lus snum dang dri zhim pos byug ste /
NK023('a)001:1026: khrus gsum byas nas rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan du rung ngo //
NK023('a)001:1027: de nas rgyan gyis brgyan nas gu ru la phul la /
NK023('a)001:1028: gu rus mdun du bzhag la /
NK023('a)001:1029: lus sems stong pa nyid las kun tu bzang mor brlab bo //
NK023('a)001:1031: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi bkod /
NK023('a)001:1033: e mthing skya me 'od dang ldan pa'o //
NK023('a)001:1034: bus rdo rje sems dpar bsgoms la /
NK023('a)001:1037: h'u las rdo rje dmar po rtse lnga pa bsgoms pa'i d+r+wa la /
NK023('a)001:1041: gsum gyi mdo ru phata do //
NK023('a)001:1042: de nas bus thal mo sbyar la /
NK023('a)001:1043: rdo rje dga' ma bdag la dgongs //
NK023('a)001:1045: dges pa chen po thabs lam gyis //
NK023('a)001:1046: chu bo bzhi las bdag sgrol cig /
NK023('a)001:1049: bu khyed smros dang thabs lam ni //
NK023('a)001:1050: rgyal ba yongs kyis sbas pa yin //
NK023('a)001:1051: thabs chen gsang ba'i theg pa ru //
NK023('a)001:1052: gtsang sme 'ching ba sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:1053: dri sha chu rnams bza' btung dang //
NK023('a)001:1054: nga yi ba ga'i ye shes bzhi //
NK023('a)001:1055: 'o dang gzhib dang drang ba dang //
NK023('a)001:1056: sems chu btung bar khyod nus sam //
NK023('a)001:1058: e ma ho thabs lam ye shes phyir /
NK023('a)001:1059: bdag ni ci yang mi nus med //
NK023('a)001:1060: de dag bdag gis spyad par bgyi //
NK023('a)001:1061: ji ltar spyad phyir bdag la gsol //
NK023('a)001:1063: dam rdzas la 'dzem pa'i nyes dmigs bshad nas byin la longs spyod do //
NK023('a)001:1064: de nas dri zhim pos sbrang gis sbyar ba'i ril lu mur zhing /
NK023('a)001:1065: gu rus chas rnams byas shing /
NK023('a)001:1066: pad+ma bltas te yongs su rgyas nas /
NK023('a)001:1067: bde ba chen po chos kyi sku //
NK023('a)001:1068: shes rab thabs kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:1069: 'di de skye ba thams cad du //
NK023('a)001:1070: dngos grub gter 'di ma spong shig /
NK023('a)001:1071: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK023('a)001:1072: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas khyod las byung //
NK023('a)001:1073: spangs na rdo rje dbyings phyug rgya //
NK023('a)001:1074: bkug dang bstan pa ma shes na //
NK023('a)001:1075: rdo rje bskal pa mtha' yas par //
NK023('a)001:1076: chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK023('a)001:1077: zhes pa'i tshig gis phyag rgya gtad /
NK023('a)001:1079: thabs dang ting nge 'dzin btang ngo //
NK023('a)001:1081: mam rgyal ba'i ye shes byas //
NK023('a)001:1082: zhes pa nas sa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK023('a)001:1084: de nas gnyis kyi lag nas bzung la /
NK023('a)001:1085: bu khyod 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las //
NK023('a)001:1086: grol zhing thar nas skad cig gis //
NK023('a)001:1087: rdo rje nam mkha'i ye shes che //
NK023('a)001:1088: bla ma chen po'i sa gnas su //
NK023('a)001:1089: thams cad rigs kyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:1090: spyi dpal bcu yi mnga' brnyes nas //
NK023('a)001:1091: bdal khyab chen po'i phrin las lngas //
NK023('a)001:1092: khams gsum sras su bzung bar byos //
NK023('a)001:1093: zhes dbugs dbyung la gtang rag gtang ngo //
NK023('a)001:1094: mdo dbang gi shes rab ye shes dbang gi rtsa ba rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:1097: // // bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po lhun gnas bde ba chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:1098: rnal ma'i dbang brten bcos ma ye rdzogs su //
NK023('a)001:1099: ye nas spyi blugs dgongs pa snyan brgyud gsal //
NK023('a)001:1100: dri med gzhung du bcos ma'i dbang brten nas //
NK023('a)001:1101: rnal mar brda bgrol 'dir ni cung zhig bstan //
NK023('a)001:1102: thun mong dbang gzhung mang yang khyad par cho ga ni //
NK023('a)001:1103: zab mo'i dbang gsum de las gsang dbang la //
NK023('a)001:1104: thun mong gzhung bskur thun min brda' bkrol lo //
NK023('a)001:1105: thun mong cho ga spyi don dgu ru gnas //
NK023('a)001:1106: dang po khrus la phyi nang gsang ba gsum //
NK023('a)001:1107: spos chu chos nyid rnam dag phyi yi khrus //
NK023('a)001:1108: dri chu bsang sbyang sngags bzlas nang gi khrus //
NK023('a)001:1109: 'o ma yi ge brgya pa gsang khrus so //
NK023('a)001:1110: sgo gsum las sgrib dag pa'i dgos ched yod //
NK023('a)001:1111: gnyis pa mig dgab dmar pos gdong g.yogs la //
NK023('a)001:1112: gsang ba'i brda' las mi nyams dgos ched yod //
NK023('a)001:1113: gsum pa sems bskyed 'bog par bya ba ni //
NK023('a)001:1114: e ma ho bde mchog dga' tshal 'dir /
NK023('a)001:1116: dga' ba byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK023('a)001:1117: gsang ba'i don 'di spyad par bya //
NK023('a)001:1118: lan gsum brjod rjes don dgrol lo //
NK023('a)001:1120: rdo rje rnal 'byor mchog gi lha //
NK023('a)001:1122: rdo rje can la phyag 'tshal te //
NK023('a)001:1123: byams mgon khyed la skyabs su mchi //
NK023('a)001:1124: zhabs la 'jus la lan gsum brjod //
NK023('a)001:1125: lnga pa gnang ba sbyin pa ni //
NK023('a)001:1126: sangs rgyas bde chen thams cad kyi //
NK023('a)001:1127: rdo rje gsang chen gsum las 'byung //
NK023('a)001:1128: srid pa gsum gyis phyag byas pa //
NK023('a)001:1129: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin //
NK023('a)001:1130: bla mas lan gsum brjod de bkrol //
NK023('a)001:1131: drug pa sgrib pa sbyong ba ni //
NK023('a)001:1132: bla ma kun bzang thugs kha nas //
NK023('a)001:1134: snying gi dkyil gyi bag chags sbyang //
NK023('a)001:1135: bdun pa lha ru bskyed pa ni //
NK023('a)001:1137: slob ma rdo rje sems dpa' 'am //
NK023('a)001:1138: 'bru brgyad sngags kyis he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:1139: slob bu gang mos lha ru bskyed //
NK023('a)001:1140: brgyad pa dam tshig 'bog pa ni //
NK023('a)001:1141: ka pa la ru bdud rtsi la //
NK023('a)001:1142: de nyid gsum gyis byin rlabs la //
NK023('a)001:1143: lce la lan gsum bzhag byas la //
NK023('a)001:1147: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab //
NK023('a)001:1148: bsrung mtshams cung zhig bstan par bya //
NK023('a)001:1149: dgu pa dam tshig ldan pa la //
NK023('a)001:1150: dbang bskur dngos gzhi'i rim pa ni //
NK023('a)001:1151: rin chen la sogs snod nang du //
NK023('a)001:1152: rdo rje sems sogs bar ma chad //
NK023('a)001:1153: byang sems rgyu phabs ldan pa la //
NK023('a)001:1154: dpa' bo ro yis sbyang byas te //
NK023('a)001:1155: bu ra ro dang ldan byas la //
NK023('a)001:1156: g+hu ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK023('a)001:1157: brgya rtsa brgyad kyis bsnyen byas la //
NK023('a)001:1158: mi bskyod he ru ga nga yang rung //
NK023('a)001:1159: sbyor mdzad 'od zhu chu rgyun gyur //
NK023('a)001:1160: gsang dbang yum shes rab ma bla ma la phul te /
NK023('a)001:1161: gsang ba'i dbang mchog bskur du gsol //
NK023('a)001:1163: khyod ni rtse gcig bzung ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:1164: gsang ba'i dbang mchog bskur bar bya //
NK023('a)001:1165: de nas yab yum lhar bskyed la //
NK023('a)001:1166: skye mched mkha' gsang byin gyis brlab //
NK023('a)001:1168: 'od du zhu nas bdag la thim //
NK023('a)001:1169: lus kyi lha rnams thim gyur nas //
NK023('a)001:1170: byang chub sems su babs pa de //
NK023('a)001:1171: slob ma'i spyir stim lhar bskyed la //
NK023('a)001:1173: ji ltar dus gsum rgyal ba yi //
NK023('a)001:1174: dam chos bdud rtsi char phab pas //
NK023('a)001:1175: skal ldan 'gro ba'i rgyud sbyang ltar //
NK023('a)001:1176: de ring rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK023('a)001:1177: bdag gi rgyud rnams sbyang ba dang //
NK023('a)001:1178: 'gro la phan phyir dbang bskur mdzod //
NK023('a)001:1180: khyod nyid brtse bzung 'gro don phyir //
NK023('a)001:1181: bla mas khyod la dbang bskur sbyin //
NK023('a)001:1183: bskul ba'i tshig 'di brjod par bya //
NK023('a)001:1184: h'u dga' ba byang chub sems chen po //
NK023('a)001:1185: kun tu tshim par byed pa'i ro //
NK023('a)001:1186: dkar dmar lhag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:1187: khyod kyi lce la bzhag pa 'di //
NK023('a)001:1188: snying gi dkyil du bzung bar byos //
NK023('a)001:1189: sngags brjod bdud rtsi lce la bzhag /
NK023('a)001:1190: snying gi dkyil du thim par 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:1191: rdo rje sems dpa' he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:1192: nyungs 'bru lta bu sha stag tu //
NK023('a)001:1193: gyur te rigs drug sa bon sbyangs //
NK023('a)001:1194: gnas ngan len pa kun sbyangs nas //
NK023('a)001:1196: rig pa gtad la bde ba sgom //
NK023('a)001:1197: bde dang ldan pa'i rtags byung na //
NK023('a)001:1198: bde stong gnyis med ye shes su //
NK023('a)001:1199: ngo sprod byin gyis brlab pa bya //
NK023('a)001:1200: de yis zab mo gsang dbang gi //
NK023('a)001:1201: thun mong cho ga yongs su rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:1202: de nas rnal mar brda' bkrol te //
NK023('a)001:1203: slob dpon kun tu bzang por bskyed //
NK023('a)001:1204: bsrung zhing bskrad pa drag tu bya //
NK023('a)001:1205: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK023('a)001:1206: gsang ba'i dbang mchog bskur du gsol //
NK023('a)001:1209: khyod ni rtse gcig bzung ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:1210: gsang ba'i dbang mchog bskul bar bya //
NK023('a)001:1211: gsol ba btab la gnang ba sbyin //
NK023('a)001:1212: bsgyur ba gsum gyi ngo sprod bya //
NK023('a)001:1213: snang ba bde bar bsgyur byas te //
NK023('a)001:1214: bde snang rang 'od brda' bkrol lo //
NK023('a)001:1215: bde ba stong par bsgyur byas te //
NK023('a)001:1216: stong pa spros bral brda' bkrol lo //
NK023('a)001:1217: stong pa gnyis med bsgyur byas te //
NK023('a)001:1218: gnyis med rig par brda' bkrol lo //
NK023('a)001:1219: de yis khyad par cho ga rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:1223: // // bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK023('a)001:1224: zab mo shes rab ye shes dbang //
NK023('a)001:1225: bdag la stsal bar mdzad du gsol //
NK023('a)001:1228: khyod nyid yid rtogs bya ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:1229: zab mo shes rab ye shes dbang //
NK023('a)001:1230: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK023('a)001:1231: gnyis pa shes rab ye shes la //
NK023('a)001:1232: slob dpon kun tu bzang por bsgom //
NK023('a)001:1233: slob ma sems dpa' he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:1234: yab yum gnyis med snyoms 'jug la //
NK023('a)001:1235: rig pa gtad cing bsgom du gzhug /
NK023('a)001:1236: +amo dz+nya na b+ao d+hi tsit+ta a b+hi shish+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:1237: bskul ba'i tshig 'di brjod par bya //
NK023('a)001:1238: h+aum rtsol med byang chub sems chen po //
NK023('a)001:1239: shes rab chen po rtsal gyi dbang //
NK023('a)001:1240: chos rnams rig par dbang bsgyur bas //
NK023('a)001:1241: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:1242: bde dang ldan pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK023('a)001:1243: rol par 'dod pa dga' ba ste //
NK023('a)001:1244: rol pa dngos ni mchog dga' 'o //
NK023('a)001:1246: thig le rdzogs pa dga' bral lo //
NK023('a)001:1247: lhan skyes dus su bde stong sprad //
NK023('a)001:1248: de yis thun mong cho ga rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:1249: de nas khyad par cho ga ni //
NK023('a)001:1250: rang lus kun tu bzang por bskyed //
NK023('a)001:1251: bsrung bskrad gsol gdab gnang ba sbyin //
NK023('a)001:1252: bsgyur ba rnam gsum sngar bzhin te //
NK023('a)001:1253: snga ma gnyis po bde bar bsgyur //
NK023('a)001:1254: rang 'od steng du brda' dkrol lo //
NK023('a)001:1255: dga' bral bde ba stong par bsgyur //
NK023('a)001:1256: spros bral steng du brda' bkral lo //
NK023('a)001:1257: lhan skyes stong pa gnyis med bsgyur //
NK023('a)001:1258: rig pa'i steng du brda' bkral lo //
NK023('a)001:1259: gnyis pa chags pa'i cha nas te //
NK023('a)001:1260: de bral bas na de stong ngo //
NK023('a)001:1261: des na de ru gnyis med do //
NK023('a)001:1262: de yang rim pa'i tshul can te //
NK023('a)001:1263: mthar bum tha mar brda' bkrol lo //
NK023('a)001:1266: // bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK023('a)001:1267: mthar thug bde ba chen po'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:1268: bdag la rtsal bar mdzad du gsol //
NK023('a)001:1271: bde ba chen po'i khyad par las //
NK023('a)001:1272: rmad byung bde ba chen po'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:1273: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:1274: mthar phyin bde ba chen po la //
NK023('a)001:1275: thun mong rnal ma'i cho ga ni //
NK023('a)001:1276: slob dpon kun tu bzang por bsgom //
NK023('a)001:1277: slob ma sems dpa' 'am he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:1278: yab yum gnyis med snyoms 'jug gis //
NK023('a)001:1279: thig le bzlog cing bde chen bskyal //
NK023('a)001:1280: ma h+aa su kha ka ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK023('a)001:1281: de la bde ba'i tshig 'dis bskul //
NK023('a)001:1282: h'u klong yangs nam mkha'i snying po la //
NK023('a)001:1283: sprin med nyi ma 'bum gyis brdal //
NK023('a)001:1284: cir snang ci yang ma yin pa'i //
NK023('a)001:1285: skye ba med pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:1286: snga ma'i dus su ngo sprad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:1287: bde stong gnyis med ye shes te //
NK023('a)001:1288: bzlog pas brtan par gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:1289: snga ma lam gyi dbang yin te //
NK023('a)001:1290: dran dang goms pa dgos phyir ro //
NK023('a)001:1292: de kho na nyid du gyur pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:1293: mthar phyin bskyed du dbyer med do //
NK023('a)001:1294: des ni thun mong cho ga rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:1295: de nas rnal ma'i cho ga la //
NK023('a)001:1296: rang lus kun tu bzang por bskyed //
NK023('a)001:1297: bsrung bskrad gsol btab gnang ba sbyin //
NK023('a)001:1298: bsgyur ba gsum po mthar phyin pas //
NK023('a)001:1299: sngar gyi brda' bkrol rnam gsum po //
NK023('a)001:1302: brda' bral stong nyid rang grol bzla //
NK023('a)001:1303: des ni rnal ma'i cho ga rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:1306: // // zab mo'i dbang gsum gyi cho ga /
NK023('a)001:1307: za hor gyi rgyal po pra ha pri la /
NK023('a)001:1308: smin pa'i lam blangs zhes pa zhi ba'i gzhung du yang bskur tu rung ste /
NK023('a)001:1309: khro bo dgongs pa gtso che ba'i gsang ba mdo'i dgongs pa'i steng du bkrol ba /
NK023('a)001:1310: dri med gsang ba'i sgron ma'i dbang gi byang bu /
NK023('a)001:1311: bcos ma'i dbang la brten nas rnal ma'i dbang brda' bkrol ba'i man ngag /
NK023('a)001:1315: // // gsang dbang yum shes rab ma bla ma la phul te /
NK023('a)001:1316: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK023('a)001:1317: gsang ba'i dbang mchog bskur du gsol //
NK023('a)001:1320: khyod ni rtse gcig bzung ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:1321: gsang ba'i dbang mchog bskur bar bya //
NK023('a)001:1322: de nas yab yum lhar bskyed la //
NK023('a)001:1323: skye mched mkha' gsang byin gyis brlab //
NK023('a)001:1325: 'od du zhu nas bdag la thim //
NK023('a)001:1326: lus kyi lha rnams thim gyur nas //
NK023('a)001:1327: byang chub sems su babs pa ste //
NK023('a)001:1328: slob ma'i spyir bstim lhar bskyed la //
NK023('a)001:1330: ji ltar dus gsum rgyal ba yi //
NK023('a)001:1331: dam chos bdud rtsi char phab pas //
NK023('a)001:1332: skal ldan 'gro ba'i rgyud sbyangs ltar //
NK023('a)001:1333: de ring rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK023('a)001:1334: bdag gi rgyud rnams sbyang ba dang //
NK023('a)001:1335: 'gro la phan phyir dbang bskur mdzod //
NK023('a)001:1337: khyod ni rtse bzung 'gro don phyir //
NK023('a)001:1338: bla mas khyod la dbang bskur sbyin //
NK023('a)001:1339: zhes brjod la dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:1340: de nas shes rab ye shes ni //
NK023('a)001:1341: mtshan ldan khrus bya byin brlabs brgyan //
NK023('a)001:1342: slob ma gnyis kyi lag bzung ste //
NK023('a)001:1343: legs par nyon cig rigs kyi bu //
NK023('a)001:1344: bde chen go 'phang bsgrub pa la //
NK023('a)001:1345: shin tu dad ldan shes rab ma //
NK023('a)001:1346: khyod kyi grogs kyi dpa' bar sbyin //
NK023('a)001:1347: rtag bde rol pa thabs ldan rtsol //
NK023('a)001:1348: bla mas sangs rgyas byang sems phab la bstim /
NK023('a)001:1349: phebs nas me long nang blangs la //
NK023('a)001:1350: phan tshun bstab cing bza' bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:1351: 'di ni rig pa brtul zhugs dbang //
NK023('a)001:1352: dbang mchog 'di rnams bskur dus su //
NK023('a)001:1353: lus la dris byugs rgyan rnams brtags //
NK023('a)001:1354: nam mkha' lha tshogs gang bar sgom //
NK023('a)001:1358: // // slob ma yab yum lag sbrel bla mas bskyangs //
NK023('a)001:1359: glan chen sh+aaka mgon dpal ldan chos seng dang //
NK023('a)001:1360: zur ban chos rje byams pa seng ge dang //
NK023('a)001:1361: 'bro yi grub thob d+harma rgyal mtshan lugs //
NK023('a)001:1365: lnga brgya bdun cu'i snying po yin /
NK023('a)001:1370: b+ho d+he na byang chub kyi sems /
NK023('a)001:1372: ma h+aa na skye rdzogs rnam pa gsum yin /
NK023('a)001:1373: su kha na bde ba yang yin /
NK023('a)001:1375: h'u na sku h'u na gsung h'u na thugs /
NK023('a)001:1377: na ro dang zla tshes la yab 'dus /
NK023('a)001:1379: g+hu ya la zhi ba yum 'dus /
NK023('a)001:1380: dz+nya na la ye shes ma 'gags pa thabs yab 'dus /
NK023('a)001:1381: b+ho d+hi na zhi khro gnyis ka'i byang chub kyi sems /
NK023('a)001:1382: tsit+ta na rat+na gur phub pa'i gnas /
NK023('a)001:1383: de ye shes kyi rlung gis bskyod nas dus gsum
NK023('a)001:1384: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad yang bde bas khyab
NK023('a)001:1385: / 'gro drug sems can thams cad la yang bde bas khyab /
NK023('a)001:1386: de gnyis so so tha mi dad dbyer med pas /
NK023('a)001:1388: 'khor 'das gnyis ka la spyod pas na su kha /
NK023('a)001:1389: h'u gsum ni sems can gyis dus gsum du 'khyer /
NK023('a)001:1390: sangs rgyas kyi sku gsum du 'khyer ro //
NK023('a)001:1391: ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK023('a)001:1392: g+hu ya mngon par byang chub pa'i sku /
NK023('a)001:1397: su kha dbyer med pa'i ngo bor cig /
NK023('a)001:1398: h'u gsum gyis thabs shes rab ma 'gags pa'i ngos nas sems can gyi don byed pa /
NK023('a)001:1399: de ltar gang zag gcig gis nyams su len na /
NK023('a)001:1403: lus snang stong sgra grag stong /
NK023('a)001:1406: rig pa la nyon mongs pa med pa /
NK023('a)001:1407: lus la bde chags med pas so //
NK023('a)001:1408: g+hu ya sems kyi sems nyid yin //
NK023('a)001:1409: g+hu ya chos kyi chos nyid yin //
NK023('a)001:1410: g+hu ya nam mkha'i mtshan nyid yin //
NK023('a)001:1411: zhes pas mdun gyi nam mkha' la che mchog tu
NK023('a)001:1412: gsal ba la thugs khar ye shes kyi rnam par
NK023('a)001:1413: gsal / g+hu ya zhes drangs pas 'od zer ljang
NK023('a)001:1414: dmar phar 'phros pa'i dus na thugs dam gyi rgyud
NK023('a)001:1415: gsal / bskul / thugs kha nas g+hu ya'i 'od zer smug nag 'phros /
NK023('a)001:1416: tshur 'dus pas bdag gi thugs khar thim /
NK023('a)001:1417: de'i byin rlabs kyis 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros pas /
NK023('a)001:1419: snang srid skye 'gro kun gyi dngos grub kyi bcud bsdus /
NK023('a)001:1420: bdag rnal 'byor pa la thim pas /
NK023('a)001:1421: de la dngos grub ces bya'o //
NK023('a)001:1422: +aahg+hu ya'i 'od zer rnams pa lha'i phyag rgyar gsal
NK023('a)001:1423: bas gong ma lta bu'i yi dam gsal ba'i dus
NK023('a)001:1424: na gsal btab kyin bzlas pas /
NK023('a)001:1425: lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bdag la thim pas dngos grub thob ces bya'o //
NK023('a)001:1426: g+hu ya dngos grub tu blang ba'o //
NK023('a)001:1427: +aahmh'u g+hu ya thugs kyi phrin las su bzlas pas bdud bzhi bcom pa zhes bya ste /
NK023('a)001:1428: g+hu ya thugs ye shes kyi snying po yin pas /
NK023('a)001:1429: 'das pa'i rgyal ba rnams kyis kyang bdud bcom zin la /
NK023('a)001:1430: da ltar gyi sgrub pa pos kyang g+hu ya'i don de bzhin du rtogs nas /
NK023('a)001:1431: rtogs pa'i don la rtse gcig gi ting nge 'dzin
NK023('a)001:1432: du ting nge 'dzin bar mtshams med pa'i bzlas brjod
NK023('a)001:1433: las su rung ba phung po khams dang skye mched
NK023('a)001:1434: lha'i rang bzhin du gsal bas phung po'i bdud bcom
NK023('a)001:1435: / g+hu yar gsal ba'i 'phro 'dus bag chags 'joms zhing sregs pas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK023('a)001:1436: de lta bu'i don blo la gsal zhing las su
NK023('a)001:1437: rung ba'i dus na log par lta ba'i mu stegs
NK023('a)001:1438: dang dregs pa can thams cad 'od zer gyis sgral
NK023('a)001:1440: g+hu ya de ru gsal zhing 'od zer lnga ru
NK023('a)001:1441: 'phros pas nyon mongs pa la phog pas nyon mongs
NK023('a)001:1442: pa'i bdud bcom / g+hu ya de ltar gsal bas thugs skye ba med pa'i ngang du 'dus pas /
NK023('a)001:1443: skye 'gag dang bral bas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom /
NK023('a)001:1446: mdzad spyod thams cad lha'i phrin las /
NK023('a)001:1447: bzlas brjod dang grags pa thams cad sngags kyi mthus
NK023('a)001:1448: dran pa thams cad g+hu ya'i rang bzhin mi 'gyur
NK023('a)001:1449: bas rdo rje tshe'i dngos grub kyi tshe /
NK023('a)001:1450: nam mkha' la gza' skar shar ba dang 'dra bas kun gzhi la g+hu ya ma 'gags par shar /
NK023('a)001:1451: 'od zer dbang po drug la shar bas mngon par shes pa 'char ro //
NK023('a)001:1453: 'di ni chos nyid byang chub kyi sems skye ba
NK023('a)001:1454: med pa'i ngang la g+hu ya rang 'byung ye shes
NK023('a)001:1455: kyi cho 'phrul du bstan pa yang yin /
NK023('a)001:1456: rgyal ba'i thugs yang dag pa'i man ngag ye shes kyi snying po'i don mtshon pa yang yin /
NK023('a)001:1457: 'o na rtse gcig gi ting nge 'dzin bar chod
NK023('a)001:1458: med pa'i bzlas brjod byas pas kun mkhyen ye shes
NK023('a)001:1459: kyi snang ba lhun gyi grub /
NK023('a)001:1460: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che dang 'dra /
NK023('a)001:1461: dmigs su med pa'i kha dog sna tshogs su shar /
NK023('a)001:1462: dper na shel la 'od phog pa dang 'dra /
NK023('a)001:1463: g+hu ya la ci'i skyon gyis ma gos /
NK023('a)001:1464: g+hu ya chos skur shar ba yin /
NK023('a)001:1466: gsal la ma yengs na sgom pa yin /
NK023('a)001:1467: spyod la ma chags na spyod pa yin /
NK023('a)001:1468: g+hu ya la thams cad 'byung bas yum yin /
NK023('a)001:1469: thams cad snang ba ma 'gags pas yab yin /
NK023('a)001:1470: so so tha dad med par thams cad 'byung bas sras yin /
NK023('a)001:1471: g+hu ya'i sngags kyi thugs kyi mgrin pa nas grags /
NK023('a)001:1472: klad pa dung khang gi gzhal yas su song bas /
NK023('a)001:1473: klad pa'i rtsa thams cad zhu byang chub sems su zhu bas /
NK023('a)001:1474: mar mgrin pa longs spyod 'khor lo'i gnas su thim pas de yang khengs nas /
NK023('a)001:1476: de yang khengs pas lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lor thim /
NK023('a)001:1477: de yang khengs pas rtsa thams cad khengs nas lus
NK023('a)001:1478: thams cad bde bas khengs pa ni 'khor lo'i bzlas
NK023('a)001:1479: pa'o // bdag che mchog tu gsal bas /
NK023('a)001:1480: yum gnam zhal ma dang gnyis /
NK023('a)001:1481: yum gyi pad+ma la nyi ma //
NK023('a)001:1482: yab kyi rdo rje la zla ba //
NK023('a)001:1483: zla ba'i steng na a dkar po //
NK023('a)001:1484: nyi ma'i steng na a dmar po //
NK023('a)001:1485: g+hu ya bzlas pas gsang ba'i dbugs bskyod nas yum gyi mkha' la babs /
NK023('a)001:1486: a dkar dmar byang chub kyi sems //
NK023('a)001:1487: yab yum gnyis med bde bas rgyas //
NK023('a)001:1492: de ltar bzlas pas yab yum gnyis su med pa'i bzlas pa'o //
NK023('a)001:1494: a ye nas chos nyid skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin nam /
NK023('a)001:1495: yang na a na ro la thim /
NK023('a)001:1496: na ro zla tshes la thim /
NK023('a)001:1497: zla tshes thig le la thim /
NK023('a)001:1498: thig le chos sku stong pa'am /
NK023('a)001:1500: sgra grag pa bzhin du g+hu ya'i sgra rig pa la ma 'gags par shar ba'o //
NK023('a)001:1505: mdo a ti yo ga'i gsang dbang don dam gnyis med zab mo lta ba'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:1506: thog ma khungs sems lung chen po rdzogs chen gyi mdo dang /
NK023('a)001:1507: rnam snang thig le dbang gi gab pa'i dbang le dang /
NK023('a)001:1509: a ti'i man ngag rgya cher gsungs cing /
NK023('a)001:1510: kun 'dus che mchog sku la chos kun yongs rdzogs kyi gdan zla ba nas /
NK023('a)001:1511: gtsug gi sangs rgyas nyer gcig gi rgyal mtshan tog las mtshon te bstan to //
NK023('a)001:1515: don sems nyid gsang ba gsum mo //
NK023('a)001:1516: tha ma don ni rig pa rang byung nyid de ltar du shar ba rnal 'byor pas myong ba'o //
NK023('a)001:1517: de'i phyir slob bu stan la rkang pa dkyil krung /
NK023('a)001:1520: dpung pa yid tsam dgye ba /
NK023('a)001:1521: mgrin pa cung tsam dgu ba /
NK023('a)001:1522: lce bzlog kha so thad ka /
NK023('a)001:1523: rlung yid mig sna rtser gtad pa la /
NK023('a)001:1524: phyi bzhin snying la sgoms la ngal sor bzhugs /
NK023('a)001:1527: phyi nang 'dres pa'i lus kyi snying la mngon par shes ldan gyis mthong ba'am /
NK023('a)001:1528: sngags 'chang pas sgom du rung ba'o //
NK023('a)001:1529: dang po dpe ni dkyil 'khor byang shar nas /
NK023('a)001:1530: pad+ma bcu drug gi 'dab ma can nam /
NK023('a)001:1531: 'khor lo rtsibs bcu drug pa dkar po'i steng du nyi ma dmar po las /
NK023('a)001:1532: lte bar a dkar gnyis kha sbyor /
NK023('a)001:1533: mthar a bcu drug dkar te bco brgyad po kun bzang yab yum bco brgyad dang /
NK023('a)001:1534: bla ma glu gsung pa'i gzugs der byon pa bco brgyad kyi ngo bor dgod /
NK023('a)001:1538: sdud pa po 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang bzhi spyi khyab bla ma sku bzhi'i ngo bo ste /
NK023('a)001:1539: sh+ri sing ha dang bod kyi bla ma dang bcas pa la /
NK023('a)001:1540: brgyud pa kun gyi ngo bor bum pa a dkar mtshan pa zhig bzhugs gnas su bya /
NK023('a)001:1542: thugs kyi gsang mtshan gsung rten gyi mtshan dang /
NK023('a)001:1543: mos rten gdung dbu skra 'am na baza'i tshal par bcas pa dgod /
NK023('a)001:1545: kun tu bzang po yab yum sbyor ba'i byang sems su bsam /
NK023('a)001:1547: pad 'khor gyi mthar mar snying dkar dmar gyi shun
NK023('a)001:1548: pa rtsa ba shar rtse mo nub tu bstan pa
NK023('a)001:1549: dang / steng du rtsa ris dang rtse mo pad gdan nyi ma dang a la reg par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:1553: khyams rdo rje sems dpa' yab dang yum /
NK023('a)001:1554: thub drug sgo ba dang bcas pa /
NK023('a)001:1558: lag chu rdo ra me ri mtha' rgyas grub bzhi lcags ri phyogs mdog dang bcas pa bya'o //
NK023('a)001:1559: las gzhung kun bzang don gyi phrin las kyis gsal btab /
NK023('a)001:1560: yi dam gang byed dang zhi ba bya /
NK023('a)001:1561: chos skyong rig 'dzin mkha' 'gro dang gzhi bdag bskang /
NK023('a)001:1563: bla ma la gsol ba drag tu gdab /
NK023('a)001:1564: rtogs pa skye ba'i slad du sgrib sbyong yig brgya /
NK023('a)001:1566: gzhung gong ma ltar sta gon rab gnas mjug chog byas na'ang bzang ngo //
NK023('a)001:1567: sngon du 'gro ba bstan zin to //
NK023('a)001:1568: da ni tha mar dngos gzhi la /
NK023('a)001:1569: rdzogs pa chen po'i skabs su dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:1574: man ngag tu gsung gin gda' 'o //
NK023('a)001:1575: snyan brgyud yi ge med pa +thii /
NK023('a)001:1576: dang po sems bzung ba ni /
NK023('a)001:1577: dbang chags pa'i rten gyi 'debs kas bya ste /
NK023('a)001:1578: dbang gso ba'i snyan brgyud las 'di skad du /
NK023('a)001:1579: a ti yo ga ngang sgom chen po'i thad kar sleb ste /
NK023('a)001:1580: de yang snying gi dkyil du thig le dkar po sgo nga tsam zhig sgom /
NK023('a)001:1581: 'od de spyi gtsug tshangs pa'i bu ga na yar skar mda' 'thon pa'i tshul du /
NK023('a)001:1582: de thig le zhig la thig phran bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phros nas /
NK023('a)001:1583: je che je che la stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten thams cad khengs par bsam /
NK023('a)001:1584: thig phran thams cad tshur 'dus nas /
NK023('a)001:1585: thig le bzhi po la thim pas thig phran dang bzhi'o gnyis su med pa /
NK023('a)001:1586: sras bde ba chen po'i ngang la gnas par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:1587: zhes bya ba ni kun la gces pa'i gdams ngag dbyig tu 'chang ba'o //
NK023('a)001:1593: yid kyis ma bslad par gsal la rtog pa med pa de ye shes so //
NK023('a)001:1595: khong klod kyin gda' tsam gsal 'debs pa'o //
NK023('a)001:1597: sgyeg mo me long lta ba bzhin //
NK023('a)001:1598: yang lta yang ltar sems la ltos //
NK023('a)001:1599: spang la g.yang mo skyong ba bzhin //
NK023('a)001:1600: yang skyong yang skyong sems la skyongs //
NK023('a)001:1601: byis pa sgong tshang nyul ba bzhin //
NK023('a)001:1602: yang nyul yang nyul sems la nyul //
NK023('a)001:1604: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK023('a)001:1605: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK023('a)001:1607: yang skabs 'dir gab pa'i dbang le las 'di skad 'byung ste /
NK023('a)001:1608: de nas rnal 'byor man ngag nges pa'i don la mkhas shing /
NK023('a)001:1609: ye shes lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin du gyur pas /
NK023('a)001:1610: rig pa'i rgyal po rang dbang du gyur pa dbang
NK023('a)001:1611: bskur yang mi dgos ma bskur yang rdzogs pa ste
NK023('a)001:1613: lha'i rgyal po gser 'gyur ni gser du ma btags kyang gter du snang zhing /
NK023('a)001:1614: gser gzhan la rgya stes spags la gser srang gcig
NK023('a)001:1615: zangs srang brgya la reg kyang gser du snang ba
NK023('a)001:1616: bzhin / bdag nyid chen po byang sems kyi dbang du gyur na /
NK023('a)001:1617: dbang ma bskur yang thams cad ye nas byang sems kyis sangs rgyas par bskur zhing /
NK023('a)001:1618: chos thams cad ye nas lhun gyis grub par rgyu 'bras kyi chos thams cad dbyer med la /
NK023('a)001:1619: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su med pa'i dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:1620: na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rang la ji ltar
NK023('a)001:1621: 'dod pa 'byung ba dang 'dra bar ye nas yangs
NK023('a)001:1623: gang yang mi dgos shing kun tu bzang po la cir yang mi rtog pas /
NK023('a)001:1624: lta ba ye 'byams kyi dbang bskur ba'i phyir 'di skad gsungs so //
NK023('a)001:1625: chos rnams thams cad nam mkha'i khams //
NK023('a)001:1626: dngos po mtshan ma kun las 'das //
NK023('a)001:1627: de la mkhas pas bcos su med //
NK023('a)001:1628: de bzhin sems kyi rnam pa kun //
NK023('a)001:1629: de bzhin nyid de bcos las 'das //
NK023('a)001:1630: 'di ltar ye nas yin rtogs na //
NK023('a)001:1631: dbang rnams bskur kyang ga la dgos //
NK023('a)001:1632: stong gsum ma bcos chos nyid klong //
NK023('a)001:1633: srid gsum ye nas rnam par dag /
NK023('a)001:1634: khams gsum phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
