NK023('a)001:1635: dug gsum bdud rtsi byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:1636: lus ngag yid gsum ye shes lha //
NK023('a)001:1637: thams cad skyon med yon tan snang //
NK023('a)001:1638: bde ba che las gzhan med pas //
NK023('a)001:1639: dbang rnams thams cad ma bskur rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:1640: sangs rgyas sems can thams cad kyang //
NK023('a)001:1641: rgyu dang 'bras bu la sogs pa //
NK023('a)001:1642: gnyis su med par ye shes pas //
NK023('a)001:1643: byang chub sems su dbang bskur yin //
NK023('a)001:1644: ming dang tshig dang yi ge dang //
NK023('a)001:1645: theg pa'i bye brag thams cad dang //
NK023('a)001:1646: don dam gcig pu sus shes pa //
NK023('a)001:1647: byang chub sems kyi dbang thob yin //
NK023('a)001:1648: bskal pa grangs dang bgrang med par //
NK023('a)001:1649: de snyed bye ba gcig 'das kyang /
NK023('a)001:1650: dus gsum 'gyur ba med shes na //
NK023('a)001:1651: byang chub sems kyi dbang thob yin //
NK023('a)001:1652: las dang las min la sogs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:1653: rtsol med bya ba ci byas kyang //
NK023('a)001:1654: byang chub don la brtsal med pas //
NK023('a)001:1655: sangs rgyas rnams kyis ma btsal bshad //
NK023('a)001:1656: nyon mongs las dang sdug bsngal dang //
NK023('a)001:1657: 'dzin rtog mtshan ma las rnams kyang //
NK023('a)001:1659: byang chub sems la gos pa med //
NK023('a)001:1660: dbang dang dam tshig thams cad kyang //
NK023('a)001:1661: de bzhin phrin las bya ba kun //
NK023('a)001:1662: byas na skyon med legs pa'i lam //
NK023('a)001:1663: ma byas na yang byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:1664: phyi nyid nang la nang nyid phyi //
NK023('a)001:1665: snang ba thams cad rang rig 'char //
NK023('a)001:1666: brjod pa'i tshig dang yi ge med //
NK023('a)001:1668: de bzhin ma bcos byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:1669: ma btsal bzhag pas gdod nas dag /
NK023('a)001:1670: 'gyur ba med pas lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:1673: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyi dbang rnam
NK023('a)001:1674: par snang mdzad kyi thig le dbang bskur rgyal po'i
NK023('a)001:1675: rgyud las / lta ba ye 'byams dbang gi le'u ste brgyad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:1676: de nas dam tshig nyams pa med pa'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:1677: thams cad rang gi sems yin par shes shing //
NK023('a)001:1678: ye kun tu bzang por sangs rgyas pa la //
NK023('a)001:1679: phyogs ris dang che chung bsgro bskur med par lung bstan par rtogs pas /
NK023('a)001:1680: dam tshig la nyams pa med pas dbang yang ma thob pa med /
NK023('a)001:1681: spyod pa ma spangs lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:1682: ci byas ci spyad 'gro log spyi gtsug gang byas kyang /
NK023('a)001:1683: snying po byang chub don las ma rtogs pas gang du yang 'gyur ba med pas /
NK023('a)001:1684: nam mkha' mtshon gyis mi zhen pa bzhin du /
NK023('a)001:1685: spyod pa ci spyad thams cad sangs rgyas kyi mdzad spyod lhun gyis grub la dbang thob bo //
NK023('a)001:1686: bsgrub pa mthar phyin pa'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:1687: skyon dang yon tan bde ba dang sdug bsngal gnyis med /
NK023('a)001:1688: gcig gi rgyan du gcig gyur te ci byas pa chud ma zos par /
NK023('a)001:1689: 'khor ba nyid mya ngan las 'das pa chen por
NK023('a)001:1690: lhun gyis grub par the tshom med par yid ches
NK023('a)001:1691: pas bsgrub pa mthar ma phyin pa yang med la
NK023('a)001:1693: phrin las bya brtsal med pa'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:1694: ye nas ye sangs rgyas pa yin na sol ba
NK023('a)001:1695: dang 'dra la ye nas sangs rgyas yin pas gser
NK023('a)001:1696: dang 'dra la / yin pa'i don la ma yengs par sems nyid sangs rgyas nyid yin pas /
NK023('a)001:1697: yin pa'i don la ma yengs shig /
NK023('a)001:1698: sems la mtha' dbus dang skye 'chi dang 'pho 'gyur med pa yin pas de la ma yengs shig /
NK023('a)001:1699: 'dzin rtog skyon thams cad ma skyes pa'i klong du
NK023('a)001:1700: shes pas 'khor ba yang med la du kha yang
NK023('a)001:1701: stobs / yon tan yang che bas ma yengs shig /
NK023('a)001:1702: des na phrin las brtsal du yang med pas dbang yang thob bo //
NK023('a)001:1703: dbang ni sangs rgyas kyi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:1704: yod ni rang gi sems la yod do //
NK023('a)001:1705: thob ni bla ma dam tshig ma nyams na thob bo //
NK023('a)001:1706: mthar ni ma yengs na phyin par 'gyur ro //
NK023('a)001:1707: grub ni ci la yang ma bcos ma slad ma btsal bas grub bo //
NK023('a)001:1708: don thams cad dgongs pa nyag cig tu gtugs so //
NK023('a)001:1709: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:1711: phyi yul dang nang sems gnyis med par ye shes su rang grol ba ngo 'phrod nas /
NK023('a)001:1712: gsum pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK023('a)001:1714: don dam byang chub sems chen po /
NK023('a)001:1715: bu mchog de yi snying la bzhag /
NK023('a)001:1716: ces pa la kha cig nas /
NK023('a)001:1717: lha dbang lus la bskur ba /
NK023('a)001:1718: sngags dbang ngag la bskur ba /
NK023('a)001:1719: chos dbang sems la bskur ba zhes bya ba lags te /
NK023('a)001:1720: 'dir lus la mi ltos 'da' ka ye shes /
NK023('a)001:1721: ngag la mi ltos dbugs kyi rgyun dang bral kyang /
NK023('a)001:1722: 'char sems la mi ltos mi rtogs ye shes la byungs 'debs pa'am /
NK023('a)001:1726: ming las a ti lta theg /
NK023('a)001:1727: gdams ngag las rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba'i man ngag /
NK023('a)001:1728: dpe rin po che gser gling du phyin pa lta bu snang srid chos skur mthong /
NK023('a)001:1729: nyon mongs pa blangs gyin lta 'jigs pa dang mi
NK023('a)001:1730: gtsang ba dang yul bzang ngan 'gal rkyen thams cad
NK023('a)001:1731: la / sems yengs su bcug gin lta'o //
NK023('a)001:1732: gnyis med ye shes rang shar ba de lta ba /
NK023('a)001:1733: de'i ngang la gnas pa de sgom pa /
NK023('a)001:1734: de dang mi 'bral ba de spyod pa /
NK023('a)001:1735: de las mi 'da' ba de dam tshig /
NK023('a)001:1736: cer cer lta tur tur dran par bya mi dgos pa de gnad /
NK023('a)001:1737: mtshan mar 'dzin brtsol rang sar grol ba de srog /
NK023('a)001:1738: rang gi mtshan nyid ma rtogs par tshig phyir 'brengs
NK023('a)001:1739: nas spyi mtshan du shor nas rdol chos lhug par
NK023('a)001:1741: zhes dang dbang don 'byed pa las /
NK023('a)001:1742: gnyis med don dam byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:1743: bu mchog de yi sems la bzhag /
NK023('a)001:1744: ces gsungs pa dran pa'am klags pa nyid kyis grol te /
NK023('a)001:1745: rdzogs pa chen por ma zad /
NK023('a)001:1747: gang gis rig pa de ni phyugs min sems kyi kun tu rtog pa dag las grol /
NK023('a)001:1750: thos pa'i bag chags chung ngu dang 'bring dang chen po yang thar ba'i sa bon du lta'o //
NK023('a)001:1752: sgom chen gyi 'dug tshul ni gdon ma zhugs pa'i rtog pa lta bu'o //
NK023('a)001:1753: nyams kyi ltangs ni shes bya chig chod kyi nyams 'char ro //
NK023('a)001:1756: gang gis gang la gang bstan pa //
NK023('a)001:1757: ci phyir dgos pa mchog dang ye gnas pa /
NK023('a)001:1758: 'di ni nang gi gags drug bstan pa yin //
NK023('a)001:1760: gang gis bkur ba'i slob dpon ni /
NK023('a)001:1761: chos sku kun bzang nas brgyud pa sel med gnyer
NK023('a)001:1762: ldan bka' babs kyi bla ma rang gis zhal mthong
NK023('a)001:1764: rtsa ba'i bla ma la gsol ba ma btab na
NK023('a)001:1765: brgyud pa bar chad pas byin brlabs chung dam pa
NK023('a)001:1767: rang gi rtsa ba'i bla ma bzhag nas dam pa rgya gar la gsol ba btab /
NK023('a)001:1769: gang la bskur ba'i slob ma ni /
NK023('a)001:1770: skal ldan rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa /
NK023('a)001:1771: dad brtson brtul zhugs can slob ma'i sems nyid la bskur zhes sngon du bstan pa ltar /
NK023('a)001:1772: gang du bskur ba gnas 'og min sogs gtad rgyar shes /
NK023('a)001:1773: dkyil 'khor bca' ba dang gang bskur ba'i rig pa rtsal dbang yang mtshungs so //
NK023('a)001:1774: 'on kyang shes bya mtha' gcod kyi rgyud las /
NK023('a)001:1775: chos nyid bsam du med la longs spyod kyang //
NK023('a)001:1776: 'dus byas dge ba'i rtsa ba rgyun mi bcad //
NK023('a)001:1778: bla mas gtso bum phyag tu bzhes la 'di skad du /
NK023('a)001:1779: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i dbang yin pas //
NK023('a)001:1780: rdzas dang tshig dang gang zag dang //
NK023('a)001:1781: kun rdzob dbang la rag ma lus //
NK023('a)001:1782: chos la sems kyis dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:1783: bden rigs skal ldan bu la gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i
NK023('a)001:1784: chu bos don dam rtsal med rtsal rdzogs kyi dbang
NK023('a)001:1786: rgyal ba rig 'dzin thams cad dang //
NK023('a)001:1787: srid gsum dbang can thams cad chos //
NK023('a)001:1788: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:1789: rdzogs pa chen po'i gdams ngag bshad //
NK023('a)001:1790: ces a ti'i dgongs pa gtad la smon pa /
NK023('a)001:1791: chos nyid dngos po med pa'i ye steng 'di //
NK023('a)001:1792: lta ba 'di dang mi 'bral 'grogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:1793: chos nyid nyams myong med pa'i bde stong 'di //
NK023('a)001:1794: sgom pa 'di dang mi 'bral 'grogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:1795: sems nyid 'chos pa med pa'i rang stong 'di //
NK023('a)001:1796: spyod pa 'di dang mi 'bral 'grogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:1797: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i rtog 'das 'di //
NK023('a)001:1799: ji ltar smon pa'i 'bras bu grub par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:1800: smon lam gyi mthu btsan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:1801: de kho na nyid kyi don blo la gnas par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:1803: bla ma zhi khro'i dbang bskur byin rlabs kyi sngags kyis dbang bum gyis dbang bskur byin rlabs bya /
NK023('a)001:1806: bla ma sangs rgyas rin po che la skyabs su mchi //
NK023('a)001:1807: zhes pa kho nas mdzad kyin bdog 'go 'jug rjes su /
NK023('a)001:1808: rje chos kyi sku la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK023('a)001:1809: rje longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK023('a)001:1810: rje sprul pa'i sku la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK023('a)001:1811: ma nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad
NK023('a)001:1812: bla ma sangs rgyas rin po che la skyabs su
NK023('a)001:1813: mchi'o // zhes dung ba zhig brjod nas de ka la phata ces gsungs nas lhod de bzhugs /
NK023('a)001:1814: rjes nas bla ma sangs rgyas rin po che'i go
NK023('a)001:1815: 'phang thob par bsngo ba re mdzad kyi gda' lags
NK023('a)001:1816: / ci'i phyir bskur ba gtan tshigs rgyu mtshan la /
NK023('a)001:1818: bla ma kun bzang yab yum kho na nyid ka rigs lnga'i steng du /
NK023('a)001:1819: phyogs bzhi'i sems dpa' zhi khro ste dgu'i rtsal thub
NK023('a)001:1820: pa drug pa dang pan chen nyi shu rtsa gcig
NK023('a)001:1821: dang / rtsa rgyud bla ma'i bar du gnas 'khor longs spyod dang bcas par shar ba yin no //
NK023('a)001:1822: de la gzhi don gyi kun gzhi dang yul chos kyi dbyings ni /
NK023('a)001:1823: kun bzang rdor sems yab yum yin la stong pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK023('a)001:1824: de yang theg chung mar chad la mi smra bar dkon mchog ces gsang zhing /
NK023('a)001:1825: theg chen la gzhi ye sangs rgyas yod ces dang /
NK023('a)001:1826: sngags 'chang la da ltar sangs rgyas yin zhes pa ni khyad par ro //
NK023('a)001:1827: sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi dang yul snod bcud
NK023('a)001:1828: rnam par snang mdzad ni me long lta bu'i ye
NK023('a)001:1829: shes yin gyi / rnam shes dang yul chos rin
NK023('a)001:1830: chen 'byung ldan ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes
NK023('a)001:1831: shes yin gyi / / nyon mongs pa can gyi
NK023('a)001:1832: yid dang yul nga bdag 'od dpag med ni so
NK023('a)001:1835: yul gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya don yod grub pa ni bya ba grub pa'i ye shes /
NK023('a)001:1840: lus sgo bzhi dbyings su sgrol ba'i ye shes /
NK023('a)001:1841: kun gzhi 'da' ka thugs kyi ye shes /
NK023('a)001:1842: yid kun gzhi dri bral mi gnas khyab pa'i ye shes /
NK023('a)001:1844: nyon yid klong du gyur pa'i ye shes dang /
NK023('a)001:1845: ye shes lnga'am dgu po yang /
NK023('a)001:1846: snang ba chos dbyings ye shes dang /
NK023('a)001:1847: rig pa rang byung ye shes la /
NK023('a)001:1848: a gnyis dbus kyi rtsa mdud la /
NK023('a)001:1849: de las ye shes bzhi yi rtsa /
NK023('a)001:1850: de'i g.yas g.yon la gsum gsum mdun brgyab la re re brgyad la /
NK023('a)001:1851: phyogs bzhir bzhi ldan gyi dga' ba bcu drug gi rtsa 'dab phyi rdul tshon dang /
NK023('a)001:1852: nang lus snying gsang ba sems kyi de kho na
NK023('a)001:1853: nyid bla ma'i thugs kyi dkyil 'khor la brtan pa
NK023('a)001:1854: thob pa'i phyir dbang bskur ba'o //
NK023('a)001:1857: yi ge 'khor lo ye shes bla ma'i sa thams
NK023('a)001:1858: cad mthar phyin pa'i phyir gcig shos kun grol lta
NK023('a)001:1860: bzhi pa da ni la bzla ste /
NK023('a)001:1861: thag bcad pa rdo rje sems dpa'i gtor bshags bya /
NK023('a)001:1862: dgongs nyams bsdur ba'i glu blangs tsaka lis dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:1865: rjes bya ba sangs rgyas pa spyi dang mthun /
NK023('a)001:1866: a ti'i rtsal dbang zur ha sh+aaka 'byung zin bris kun phan dge bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:1870: // // kun bzang don gyi phrin las /
NK023('a)001:1871: na mo bud+d+ha b+ha tra ma h+aa a ti yo ga /
NK023('a)001:1872: kun bzang don gyi phrin las stsal ba med pa'i don la /
NK023('a)001:1873: h'u mi rtog ye shes bgegs bsal nas //
NK023('a)001:1875: 'jigs pa thams cad de la yong //
NK023('a)001:1878: gzhi nyid ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa la //
NK023('a)001:1879: dgag sgrub gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK023('a)001:1880: bzang ngan gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK023('a)001:1881: ma bcos byang chub klong du bshags par bagyi'o //
NK023('a)001:1882: lta ba'i rang bzhin gza' gtad med pa la //
NK023('a)001:1883: gza' gtad gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK023('a)001:1884: yul sems gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK023('a)001:1885: rang sems byang chub klong du bshags par bagyi'o //
NK023('a)001:1886: sgom pa cog bzhag dmigs gtad med pa la //
NK023('a)001:1887: dmigs gtad gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK023('a)001:1888: bzhag 'jog gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK023('a)001:1889: cog bzhag byang sems klong du bshags par bagyi'o //
NK023('a)001:1890: spyod pa 'dzin med blang dor med pa la //
NK023('a)001:1891: blang dor gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK023('a)001:1892: gtsang sme gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK023('a)001:1893: lhug pa byang sems klong du bshags par bagyi'o //
NK023('a)001:1894: dam tshig srung med 'da' nyams med pa la //
NK023('a)001:1895: 'da' nyams gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK023('a)001:1896: bshags gso gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK023('a)001:1897: srung med byang sems klong du bshags par bagyi'o //
NK023('a)001:1898: sa lam bgrod med rtsol sgrub 'das pa la //
NK023('a)001:1899: brtsol bsgrub gnyis su 'dzin pa thang re chad //
NK023('a)001:1900: bgrod thob gnyis su lta ba nyon re mongs //
NK023('a)001:1901: bgrod med byang sems klong du bshags par bagyi'o //
NK023('a)001:1902: 'bras bu ji bzhin ye sangs rgyas pa la //
NK023('a)001:1903: yangs dog gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK023('a)001:1904: rgyu 'bras gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK023('a)001:1905: lhun gnas byang sems klong du bshags par bagyi'o //
NK023('a)001:1906: mchod gtor phud rnams byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK023('a)001:1909: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta h'u /
NK023('a)001:1910: ma h+aa b+ha lin ta h'u /
NK023('a)001:1921: h'u rmad 'byung byang chub sems kyi gnas //
NK023('a)001:1922: gzhal med khang mdzes de dag ni //
NK023('a)001:1924: nyi ma zla ba'i gdan dang 'od //
NK023('a)001:1925: zhing rnams gadanasama chen gsal ba dang //
NK023('a)001:1926: rin chen las byang shin tu snang //
NK023('a)001:1927: rang gi snying por rang byas la //
NK023('a)001:1928: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i sku //
NK023('a)001:1929: sangs rgyas mi bsgom bdag nyid sgom //
NK023('a)001:1930: rang gi lhar ni kun bzang bsgom //
NK023('a)001:1931: dus gsum bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK023('a)001:1933: dpal chen khrag 'thung ma mo'i tshogs //
NK023('a)001:1934: gzhan yang rnam pa mang po'i tshogs //
NK023('a)001:1935: lha dang lha min rlung lha dang //
NK023('a)001:1936: gshin rje klu dang lha rnams dang //
NK023('a)001:1937: gnod sbyin srin po 'byung po'i tshogs //
NK023('a)001:1938: dbang med dad pas 'dus pa dang //
NK023('a)001:1939: lha yi tshogs kyis gang ba rnams //
NK023('a)001:1940: rnal 'byor rang rig chen po yis //
NK023('a)001:1941: gsang ba'i lha rnams gcig tu sgom //
NK023('a)001:1942: ye shes rang 'byung byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:1943: sangs rgyas thams cad bdag gis byas //
NK023('a)001:1944: ye shes lha rnams rang las byung //
NK023('a)001:1945: 'di ni rmad du byung ba'i sku //
NK023('a)001:1946: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor dam pa yin //
NK023('a)001:1947: mi g.yo ba ni sku yi rgya //
NK023('a)001:1948: mi bskyod pa ni ye shes che //
NK023('a)001:1949: mi len pa ni bdag med cing //
NK023('a)001:1950: mi 'dir tshig bral mnyam nyid do //
NK023('a)001:1951: bde gshegs snying pos 'gro kun yongs la khyab //
NK023('a)001:1952: sems ni rgya che mchog tu rabs bskyed de //
NK023('a)001:1953: 'gro ba 'di dag ma lus sangs rgyas rgyu //
NK023('a)001:1954: 'di na snod med sems can gang yang med //
NK023('a)001:1955: bzhengs shig bzhengs shig stobs chen mnga' ba'i lha //
NK023('a)001:1956: dus las mi 'da' thugs rje dbang gis na //
NK023('a)001:1957: sems can don la dgongs pa'i dkon mchog gsum //
NK023('a)001:1958: yid kyis dmigs shing sems kyis sprul pa'i gnas 'di ru /
NK023('a)001:1959: rgyal ba 'khor bcas spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK023('a)001:1960: sangs rgyas mi gshegs bdag nyid gshegs //
NK023('a)001:1961: lha yang gzhan nas bod mi dgos //
NK023('a)001:1962: bya ba med pas las rnams zin //
NK023('a)001:1963: +aee ha hi ma h+aa ka ru ni ka tri sha ho /
NK023('a)001:1967: b+hud+d+ha pad tra ma h+aa a ti yo ga sa ma ya stom /
NK023('a)001:1970: gang la sangs rgyas mdzad pa yi //
NK023('a)001:1971: don de la yang phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:1972: gang gi don du mdzad pa yi //
NK023('a)001:1973: don mdzad de la'ang phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:1974: phyag rgya mi bskyod yan lag bskyod //
NK023('a)001:1975: rang byung mchog gi phyag rgya'o //
NK023('a)001:1976: rnam par grol ba'i phung po lnga yis mchod par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:1977: bdag las byung ba'i khu ba yis //
NK023('a)001:1978: bdag gis lus la rab brgyan te //
NK023('a)001:1979: dngos grub mchog rnams bdag las byung //
NK023('a)001:1980: sman mchog nad sel bder 'tsho ba //
NK023('a)001:1981: dug gsum sman mchog byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:1983: lhun gyis gnas pa mi sngo zhing //
NK023('a)001:1984: gdod nas dag pa'i bdud rtsi yin //
NK023('a)001:1985: b+hud+d+ha b+ha tra pany+tsa a mri ta kha hi /
NK023('a)001:1986: dus gsum bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas man chad bsdom tshig tu bya'o //
NK023('a)001:1988: mchod pas gzhan la mi mchod do //
NK023('a)001:1989: bdag nyid kun gyi lha yin pas //
NK023('a)001:1990: kun gyi mchod pas bdag la mchod //
NK023('a)001:1991: kun spyod yon tan rnam lnga yang //
NK023('a)001:1992: chos nyid dag pa'i rgyan du gsungs //
NK023('a)001:1993: mi bzung gtor bas gtor ma yin //
NK023('a)001:1994: bud+d+ha b+ha tra ma h+aa ba lin ta kha hi /
NK023('a)001:1995: gang gi don du byas pa'i don //
NK023('a)001:1996: de dag bdag la 'grub gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:1998: don de bdag nyid rig gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:1999: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam pa yi //
NK023('a)001:2000: sangs rgyas kun sangs rgyas gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:2001: snying po mi rjod bdag nyid brjod //
NK023('a)001:2002: rang gi snying po rang sngags kyi //
NK023('a)001:2003: grub pa'i snying po chud mi za //
NK023('a)001:2004: 'dzab dang snyen pa dbul mi dgos //
NK023('a)001:2005: dngos grub gzhan nas mi slong ste //
NK023('a)001:2006: mi gsung mnyam bzhag sngags tshig go //
NK023('a)001:2007: bud+d+ha b+ha tra ma h+aa a ti yo ga sa ma ya stom /
NK023('a)001:2008: shab+ta ru pa a bo su kha de ba shi shi /
NK023('a)001:2009: sangs rgyas pas dang sngar sangs rgyas //
NK023('a)001:2010: mi shes dri ma ye nas med //
NK023('a)001:2011: dpal gyi rnam rgyal de bzhin du //
NK023('a)001:2012: longs spyod dbang phyug dpal dang mnyam //
NK023('a)001:2013: rdo rje nyi ma'i gzi brjid dang //
NK023('a)001:2014: mdog sdug shin tu 'bar ba yi //
NK023('a)001:2015: bzhad cing dam du mdzad pa yi //
NK023('a)001:2016: dga' mgu rangs pa rnams su 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:2017: pad+ma bzhad pa'i chos kun gyi //
NK023('a)001:2018: rtogs mdzad sangs rgyas thams cad kyang //
NK023('a)001:2019: byang chub sems 'dis mnyes gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:2020: skad cig gcig la rtogs gyur te //
NK023('a)001:2021: snying po byang chub nyid du 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:2022: rdo rje'i gdan la yang sangs rgyas //
NK023('a)001:2023: sku med chos kyi sku ni stong gsum zil gyis gnon //
NK023('a)001:2024: gsung med rig pa'i gsung gis bstan pa rgyas par sgrogs //
NK023('a)001:2025: rtogs med ye shes thugs kyis cir yang sa le mkhyen //
NK023('a)001:2026: ston pa kun tu bzang la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK023('a)001:2027: chos kyi dbyings ni nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK023('a)001:2028: byang chub rnyed dka' rang la yod bzhin du //
NK023('a)001:2029: gsang ba'i snying po gang la gnas pa na //
NK023('a)001:2030: dam can rgya mtsho rnams kyang de na gnas //
NK023('a)001:2031: thugs rje rgya mtsho'i yon tan kun la khyab //
NK023('a)001:2032: lha dang klu yang bden pa'i bka' nyan to //
NK023('a)001:2033: mnyam pas rim pa bkod pa med //
NK023('a)001:2034: gcig pas phyogs su sngo dang bral //
NK023('a)001:2035: tshogs kyi brgyan rnams bkram pa dang //
NK023('a)001:2036: rang bzhin gnas pas 'bri ba med //
NK023('a)001:2037: yid kyis bsams pa'i yon bdag ste //
NK023('a)001:2038: ltas pa'i stobs ni bkram pa'o //
NK023('a)001:2039: h'u rnam par rtog med dus gsum rgyal ba'i thugs //
NK023('a)001:2040: nyon mongs zhen pa'i dbang gi rang 'thad kyang //
NK023('a)001:2041: don rtogs gsal ba'i skyes bu gnyis su med //
NK023('a)001:2042: chos nyid lha mo lha nger gsal ba'o //
NK023('a)001:2043: chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang du thams cad gcig /
NK023('a)001:2044: bde chen rgyal po lhun grub la //
NK023('a)001:2045: lhun grub mthar phyin mchod par bzhes //
NK023('a)001:2046: bud+d+ha b+ha tra kha hi zhes pa la sogs 'agre'o lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:2047: 'gyur ba ma yin drang por gnas //
NK023('a)001:2048: nam mkha' bzhin du mtha' mnyam zhing //
NK023('a)001:2049: gzhal la ltos 'gyur chos ma yin //
NK023('a)001:2050: bla ma mchod dang rtogs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:2051: de bzhin bsod nams thams cad dang //
NK023('a)001:2052: ma chags mi g.yo'i stobs med na //
NK023('a)001:2054: kun bzang don gyi phrin las dgongs pa'i gsal 'debs rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:2059: mdo rdzogs pa chen po la gsol ba gdab par bya ste /
NK023('a)001:2060: bla ma rnams bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi ngo bo yin no //
NK023('a)001:2061: seng ge brgyad 'jug bsnol gyis bteg pa'i khri /
NK023('a)001:2062: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs na //
NK023('a)001:2063: drin can rtsa ba'i bla ma nyid //
NK023('a)001:2064: na baza'i brgyan khyad par du 'phags pas brgyan pa la /
NK023('a)001:2066: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' /
NK023('a)001:2067: nyan thos rang rgyal mkha' 'gro dpa' bo chos skyong srungs ma /
NK023('a)001:2068: gnyen bshes longs spyod dang sems kyi zhen 'phro'i chos
NK023('a)001:2069: thams cad bstims la gsol ba gdab par bya ste
NK023('a)001:2070: / man ngag rdzogs pa chen po a ti'i brgyud pa ni /
NK023('a)001:2071: kun bzang rdor sems 'jam dpal dga' rab dang //
NK023('a)001:2072: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen rgyal po d+ha na ta //
NK023('a)001:2073: sras po thu bo sras mo sa ra ni //
NK023('a)001:2074: klu rgyal 'jog po gnod sbyin byang chub dang //
NK023('a)001:2075: a ra li dang ku ku 'bu ta sh+ri //
NK023('a)001:2076: 'bu ta sa ma ma h+aa ra dza dang //
NK023('a)001:2077: go ma de phyi blon po a lo ke //
NK023('a)001:2078: ma ha ra dza drang srong b+ha sha ti //
NK023('a)001:2079: bdag nyid ma dang klu grub ku ku ri //
NK023('a)001:2080: dgyes pa rdo rje 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi //
NK023('a)001:2081: dge bsnyen legs dang d+harma ra dza dang //
NK023('a)001:2082: 'bu ta kug ta sh+ri sing ha dang //
NK023('a)001:2083: b+hi ma la dang dge slong kun dga' ma //
NK023('a)001:2084: bee ro tsa na g.yu sgra snying po dang //
NK023('a)001:2085: dz+nya na ku ma sog po dpal ye dang //
NK023('a)001:2086: sangs rgyas ye shes rdzogs chen mdo lung brgyud //
NK023('a)001:2087: sgo gsum gus pa'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal zhing //
NK023('a)001:2088: rtse gcig gdung ba'i stobs kyis gsol 'debs kyis //
NK023('a)001:2089: thugs rje chen po'i zhags pas rjes bzung la //
NK023('a)001:2090: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang bskur byin gyis barlobasa //
NK023('a)001:2091: lung chen rjes su chags pa'i a nu theg pa rim pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK023('a)001:2092: kun bzang rdor sems rgyal sras sems khro dang //
NK023('a)001:2093: dam pa'i rigs can lnga dang rgyal po dza //
NK023('a)001:2094: u pa ra dza spu gri rnam gsum dang //
NK023('a)001:2095: ku ku ra dza phyi ma ri sa dang //
NK023('a)001:2096: ro langs bde ba rdo rje bzhad pa dang //
NK023('a)001:2097: za hor rgyal dang sh+aakya rnam gsum dang //
NK023('a)001:2098: h'u mdzad rdo rje sti ra ma ti dang //
NK023('a)001:2099: bde ba gsal mdzad sh+aakya b+ho d+he dang //
NK023('a)001:2100: mkhan po chos bdag rgyal ba d+ha ra dang //
NK023('a)001:2101: bru zha che btsan sangs rgyas ye shes dang //
NK023('a)001:2102: sgo gsum gus pa shes mdo rgyud chen ma h+aa yo ga theg pa rim pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK023('a)001:2103: kun bzang rigs lnga spyan ras gzigs //
NK023('a)001:2104: lha klu gnod sbyin srin po mi //
NK023('a)001:2105: ku ku ra dza in tra bo de dza //
NK023('a)001:2106: sh+aakya su tri sing ha u pa ra //
NK023('a)001:2107: sras mo go ma me tri ka ma la //
NK023('a)001:2108: 'dzi na mi tra rdo rje bzhad pa dang //
NK023('a)001:2109: mi 'byed seng ge sti ra ma ti dang //
NK023('a)001:2110: bde ba gsal mdzad sh+aakya bo de dang //
NK023('a)001:2111: sh+aakya d+he ba rdo rje sgyeg pa dang //
NK023('a)001:2112: chos blon d+he ba mkhan po chos rgyal skyong //
NK023('a)001:2113: sangs rgyas ye shes ma h+aa yo ga'i brgyud //
NK023('a)001:2114: mdo lung khyad par nang pa thabs kyi theg /
NK023('a)001:2115: sgo gsum mthun mod yon tan rgya mtsho ye shes rgya mtsho dang //
NK023('a)001:2116: blo gros byang chub tho dkar nam mkha' ste //
NK023('a)001:2117: zur chen zur chung ka bzhi gsang bdag dang //
NK023('a)001:2118: glan ston sh+aaka bzang sh+aakya byang chub dang //
NK023('a)001:2119: 'gar ston gzung nge srog ston rdo rje rgyal //
NK023('a)001:2120: glan ston rdor 'od glan ston bsod rgyal dang //
NK023('a)001:2121: sdong po kun rin dpal ldan chos seng dang //
NK023('a)001:2122: sangs rgyas dpal dang glan ston bsod nams mgon //
NK023('a)001:2123: bla ma'i mchog gyur bsam grub rdo rje yis //
NK023('a)001:2124: zur h+aa sh+aakya 'byung la bka' drin mdzad //
NK023('a)001:2125: lugs mang kun 'dus mdo lung chos kyi brgyud //
NK023('a)001:2126: sgo gsum gus mthun pa a /
NK023('a)001:2127: slob dpon ging ka ra sogs mtshan nyid rgyu'i theg /
NK023('a)001:2128: klu grub tsan ti ka sogs kri ya'i theg /
NK023('a)001:2129: pad+ma ku ma ti sogs yo ga'i theg /
NK023('a)001:2130: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i slob dpon te //
NK023('a)001:2131: phyi dbang brgya rtsa'i bla ma rtsa brgyad la //
NK023('a)001:2132: sgo gsum bla ma myang chen dpal ldan rdo rje dang //
NK023('a)001:2133: bla ma zur chen sh+aakya bzang sogs kyis //
NK023('a)001:2134: mdo dbang chos skor phyag bzhes du ma yis //
NK023('a)001:2135: zur h+aa sh+aakya 'byung la bka' drin mdzad //
NK023('a)001:2136: bstan pa'i mdzod 'dzin chos kyi mnga' bdag rje //
NK023('a)001:2137: 'dran gyi zla med sangs rgyas gnyis pa des //
NK023('a)001:2138: bu slob tha chung su gyur byang chub rin chen dang //
NK023('a)001:2139: bo de ma ti gnyis la bka' drin mdzad //
NK023('a)001:2140: bla ma'i grogs mched slob 'brel thams cad la //
NK023('a)001:2141: sgo gsum gus pa'i zhes sogs mthun de lta bu'i
NK023('a)001:2142: gsol 'debs 'di bdag sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyis sngon gyi
NK023('a)001:2143: tshig la 'phro mthud de gsol ba btab pa'o //
NK023('a)001:2144: dge bas bstan rgyas 'gro phan byang chub shog ///
NK023('a)001:2146: rdzogs pa chen po la gsol ba gdab par bya ste /
NK023('a)001:2147: bla ma rnams bskyed rdzogs gsum dang theg dgu'i ngo bo yin te /
NK023('a)001:2149: chos dkon mchog gi 'bul ba ni chos smra ba rnams la dbul ces dang /
NK023('a)001:2151: phyag rgya gsang chen snying po 'di //
NK023('a)001:2152: rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa //
NK023('a)001:2153: de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:2155: gang zag spangs na chos spong bar 'gyur ba ni
NK023('a)001:2156: chos ldan chos shes te mchod na'ang chos mchod par
NK023('a)001:2157: 'gyur ces gsung / de'ang seng ge brgyad la sogs
NK023('a)001:2158: pas btegs pa'i khri rin po che la pad+ma nyi
NK023('a)001:2160: mi 'jigs pa bzhi la sogs pa bla ma la ldan par mos pa dang /
NK023('a)001:2161: rang yang de lta bu thob par bya ba'i ched du'o //
NK023('a)001:2163: rgyan khyad du 'phags pa'i na bza' dang /
NK023('a)001:2164: yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang /
NK023('a)001:2165: dkon mchog gsum gyi ngo bo rtsa bar gnas pa la /
NK023('a)001:2166: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' /
NK023('a)001:2167: nyan thos rang rgyal lha mi'i gtso bo yang //
NK023('a)001:2168: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro chos skyong srungs ma dang //
NK023('a)001:2169: gnyen bshes longs spyod sems kyi zhen 'phro'i chos thams cad bstims la gsol ba gdab ste /
NK023('a)001:2171: jo bo sangs rgyas ye shes kyi rig 'dzin brgya
NK023('a)001:2172: rtsa brgyad du bshad pa'i dang po rdzogs chen shin
NK023('a)001:2174: a ti yo ga man ngag la brgyud pa ni /
NK023('a)001:2176: mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa lnga /
NK023('a)001:2177: bod kyi sa bon bzhi ste sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK023('a)001:2178: yang sprul dga' rab dang bi ma la dang rgya
NK023('a)001:2179: bod 'dres pa bzhi ste so brgyad mchis pa 'di
NK023('a)001:2180: skad du / chos sku kun bzang longs sku rdo rje sems //
NK023('a)001:2181: sprul sku 'jam dpal bka'i sdud pa po //
NK023('a)001:2182: yang sprul slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje ste //
NK023('a)001:2183: rgyal ba dgongs pa brgyud pa thams cad la //
NK023('a)001:2184: sgo gsum dang ba'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal zhing //
NK023('a)001:2185: rtse gcig gdung ba'i stobs kyis gsol 'debs kyis //
NK023('a)001:2186: thugs rje chen po'i shugs kyis rjes bzung la //
NK023('a)001:2187: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang byin dngos grub stsol //
NK023('a)001:2188: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen rgyal po d+ha na ta //
NK023('a)001:2189: sras po thu bo ra dza sras mo'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:2190: sa ra ni dang klu rgyal 'jog po dang //
NK023('a)001:2191: gnod sbyin byang chub gzungs ma a ra li //
NK023('a)001:2192: ku ku ra dza gzungs ma bud+d+ha sh+ri //
NK023('a)001:2193: gzungs ma bud+d+ha sa ma ti dang ni //
NK023('a)001:2194: o rgyan ma h+aa ra dza sras go ma //
NK023('a)001:2195: slob dpon a lo ke dang ku ku phyi //
NK023('a)001:2196: mkhan po chen po sgeg pa rdo rje dang //
NK023('a)001:2197: drang srong b+ha sha gzungs ma bdag nyid ma //
NK023('a)001:2198: klu grub snying po de ba ra dza dang //
NK023('a)001:2199: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi dang dge bsnyen legs //
NK023('a)001:2200: d+harma ra dza sangs rgyas gsang ba dang //
NK023('a)001:2201: sh+ri sing ha kun dga' dge slong ma //
NK023('a)001:2202: bi ma mi tra dang bcas nyi shu drug /
NK023('a)001:2203: rgya gar mkhas grub bla ma thams cad la //
NK023('a)001:2204: sgo gsum zhes pa tshig bzhi gong gis 'agre'o //
NK023('a)001:2205: b+hi ma la mi the ba nyer lnga dang /
NK023('a)001:2208: kun dga' dang gsum ma the bas nyer gsum dang /
NK023('a)001:2209: ku ku phyi ma de bzhag pas mkhas grub nyi shu rtsa gcig tu gtad rgya las bshad /
NK023('a)001:2210: bee ro tsa na rgyal po g.yu sgra dang //
NK023('a)001:2211: ye shes gzhon nu sog po dpal ye dang //
NK023('a)001:2212: sangs rgyas ye shes rin chen la sogs kyi //
NK023('a)001:2213: bod kyi sa bon bla ma thams cad la //
NK023('a)001:2214: sgo gsum 'gre mkhas grub bcud 'dus slob dpon pad+ma dang //
NK023('a)001:2215: rgyal mchog dbyangs dang sangs rgyas ye shes dang //
NK023('a)001:2216: mkhas grub bcud thob slob dpon h'u ka ra //
NK023('a)001:2217: nam mkha' snying po sangs rgyas ye shes dang //
NK023('a)001:2218: rgya bod bka' babs bla ma thams cad la //
NK023('a)001:2219: sgo gsum des rig 'dzin sum cu rtsa brgyad tshang ba'o //
NK023('a)001:2222: // // da ni rjes su chags pa'i rnal 'byor a nu
NK023('a)001:2223: yo ga lung gi theg pa rim pa dgu tshogs
NK023('a)001:2224: chen 'dus pa mdo ltar gyi brgyud pa ni /
NK023('a)001:2225: tan tra sde nyi shu rtsa gsum mam /
NK023('a)001:2226: tan tra sde nyi shu rtsa lnga yang spyi thems dgongs pa 'dus pa dang bcas pa de nyid /
NK023('a)001:2227: gsang bdag des rgyal po lung bstan rdo rje la bstan cing /
NK023('a)001:2228: li tsa dang yang mjal ba dang /
NK023('a)001:2229: lung bstan brnyes pas ku ku ra dza bar du mi dgos par mdzad la /
NK023('a)001:2230: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga ltar du tan tra sde
NK023('a)001:2231: bco brgyad kyang dge slong ku ku ra dzas rgyal
NK023('a)001:2232: po dza in dra bo d+hi la bstan ces ku
NK023('a)001:2233: ku ra dza dgos par mdzad /
NK023('a)001:2234: 'dir a nu'i gtad rgya las 'di skad du /
NK023('a)001:2235: chos sku kun bzang longs sku rigs lnga dang //
NK023('a)001:2236: rgyal ba zhi khro rgyal sras sems dpa' dang //
NK023('a)001:2237: bka' bsdud rigs gsum sprul sku thub pa drug /
NK023('a)001:2238: rgyal ba dgongs brgyud bla ma 'khor bcas la //
NK023('a)001:2239: sgo gsum gus pa'i stobs kyis 'gre /
NK023('a)001:2240: lha dang klu dang gnod sbyin rig 'dzin dang //
NK023('a)001:2241: lha mi gnyis ka'i rig 'dzin nyer lnga la //
NK023('a)001:2242: sgo gsum lha ni 'jam dpal rdo rje rnon po dang //
NK023('a)001:2243: grags ldan chos skyong rin chen 'od 'bar dang //
NK023('a)001:2244: skye dgu'i bdag po tshangs dang tshangs kun grol //
NK023('a)001:2245: tshangs pa gtsug phud 'dzin dang brgya byin bdun //
NK023('a)001:2246: klu ni chu bdag spyan ras gzigs dbang dang //
NK023('a)001:2247: g+h+ri na nag po klu srin khas 'dul ma //
NK023('a)001:2248: klu mo 'dul tshangs dga' bo 'jog po drug /
NK023('a)001:2249: gnod sbyin las ni phyag rdor gos sngon dang //
NK023('a)001:2250: gnod sbyin kun bzang lag na rdo rje dang //
NK023('a)001:2251: grags ldan chos skyong skar mda' gdong dang lnga //
NK023('a)001:2252: gnyis ka las ni gsang ba'i bdag po dang //
NK023('a)001:2253: lha las grags ldan mchog skyong klu 'jog po //
NK023('a)001:2254: bar snang lha srin bdag po gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong //
NK023('a)001:2255: srin po'i rgyal po lang ka mgrin bcu'ang mi'o //
NK023('a)001:2256: mi dge bsnyen li tsa dri med grags //
NK023('a)001:2257: nyer lnga 'khor tshogs tshom bu 'bum phrag bcas /
NK023('a)001:2258: sgo gsum mi yi rig 'dzin nyi shu 'di skad du //
NK023('a)001:2259: gsang bdag phyag rdor skal ldan rgyal po ni //
NK023('a)001:2260: dza zhes rgyal po lung bstan rdo rje dang //
NK023('a)001:2261: u pa ra dza de slob gsum mam bzhi //
NK023('a)001:2262: sras ni in tra sh+aakya su tri dang //
NK023('a)001:2263: na ga su tri 'gu ya su tri gsum //
NK023('a)001:2264: sing ha'i rgyal po sing ha su tri bzhi //
NK023('a)001:2265: sh+aakya ku ku ra dza phyi ma dang //
NK023('a)001:2266: ro langs bde ba rdo rje bzhad pa dang //
NK023('a)001:2267: za hor yul gyi rgyal po pra ha sti //
NK023('a)001:2268: slob dpon chen po d+ha na raka shi ta //
NK023('a)001:2269: slob dpon h'u mdzad sti ra ma ti dang //
NK023('a)001:2270: bde ba gsal mdzad sh+aakya d+harma b+ho d+he dang /
NK023('a)001:2271: rgya gar mkhan po chos rgyal skyong ba dang //
NK023('a)001:2272: slob ma rnam gsum ba su d+ha ra dang //
NK023('a)001:2273: rgya gar slob dpon gtsug lag dpal dge dang //
NK023('a)001:2274: bru zha'i mkhan po lots+tsha che btsan skyes /
NK023('a)001:2275: mdo lung khyad par bsgrub dbang rig 'dzin la //
NK023('a)001:2276: sgo gsum yang da na raka shi ti'i skabs de
NK023('a)001:2277: na sh+aakya gsum gyi gcig slob dpon pad+ma yin zhing
NK023('a)001:2278: / de ni da na raka shi yin gsungs pa ltar na sh+aakya seng ge rab byung /
NK023('a)001:2279: sh+aakya bshes gnyen te gsum ka'ang slob dpon pad+ma'i rnam 'phrul te /
NK023('a)001:2280: khyad par sh+aakya 'od ni slob dpon pad+ma yin par chos rgyal ba'i gter nas gsungs la /
NK023('a)001:2281: sh+aakya seng ge'ang slob dpon pad+mara gu ru chos dbang gi gter du bshad cing /
NK023('a)001:2282: bril bas a nu bzhi bcu zhe lnga snang ba /
NK023('a)001:2283: thams cad da ltar 'ang bzhugs zhes spyir stan cing /
NK023('a)001:2284: khyad par du d+ha na raka shi yan chad sangs rgyas ye shes kyi dus na bzhugs so //
NK023('a)001:2286: // da ni ma h+aa yo ga rnal 'byor chen po'i
NK023('a)001:2287: theg pa las mdo yongs rdzogs khyad par nang dbang
NK023('a)001:2288: 'byung ba'i chu bo la zhi ba'i lha dngos nyid
NK023('a)001:2289: bkod la / khro bo lung gi khro bo ma rtogs par mdzad pa gtso che ste /
NK023('a)001:2290: bkod kyang bskyed rims shas che tsam las bzung skad /
NK023('a)001:2292: chos kyi rgyal po kun bzang chos kyi sku //
NK023('a)001:2293: rgyal tshab rigs lnga longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK023('a)001:2294: rgyal sras sems dpa' sems ma sprul pa'i sku //
NK023('a)001:2295: khyad par rdo rje chos te dgongs pas brgyud //
NK023('a)001:2296: sgo gsum rig 'dzin rdo rje chos te spyan ras gzigs //
NK023('a)001:2297: dge slong ku ku ra dza chen po dang //
NK023('a)001:2298: in tra b+ho d+hi bar pa rgyal po dza //
NK023('a)001:2299: de yis rgyal bu sh+aakya su tri dang //
NK023('a)001:2300: sing ha ra dza gnyis la sing ha yis //
NK023('a)001:2301: u pa ra dza sras mo go ma de byi dang //
NK023('a)001:2302: sangs rgyas gsang ba b+hi ma mi tra sti //
NK023('a)001:2303: nang dbang 'byung ba'i nye brgyud grub thob bdun //
NK023('a)001:2304: sgo gsum kun bzang rdo rje sems dang rdo rje chos //
NK023('a)001:2305: slob dpon ku ku ra dza rgyal po dza //
NK023('a)001:2306: sh+aakya su tri sing ha ra dza dang //
NK023('a)001:2307: u pa ra dza go ma de byi dang //
NK023('a)001:2308: ka ma shi la 'dzi na mi tra dang //
NK023('a)001:2309: rdo rje bzhad pa nyi 'byed seng ge dang //
NK023('a)001:2310: slob dpon chen po bde ba gsal mdzad dang //
NK023('a)001:2311: sh+aakya de ba pakyo blo gros dang //
NK023('a)001:2312: rdo rje sgyeg pa chos blon d+he ba dang //
NK023('a)001:2313: mkhan po chos rgyal sangs rgyas ye shes la //
NK023('a)001:2314: sgo gsum de yang rgyud ma h+aa yo ga la
NK023('a)001:2315: brgyud pa ring lugs ltar nyi shu tham pa mchis
NK023('a)001:2316: te / ma h+aa ltar sh+aakya su tri dang sing
NK023('a)001:2317: ha ra dza gnyis slob dpon gcig pa dang sing
NK023('a)001:2318: ha la u pa ra dzas thob par bya /
NK023('a)001:2319: sti ra ma ti dang bde ba gsal mdzad gcig tu bgrang /
NK023('a)001:2320: lugs kha cig tu slob dpon h'u mdzad sti ra'i gong du mdzad /
NK023('a)001:2321: nyi 'byed dang mi 'byed gnyis ngo bo slob dpon gcig tu bshad /
NK023('a)001:2322: kha cig h'u mdzad a nu yin pas 'dir mi gsung zhing /
NK023('a)001:2323: sh+aakya bo de ni d+harma bo ter bshad /
NK023('a)001:2324: pakyo dang blo gros de ba gnyis gcig ces gsung /
NK023('a)001:2325: d+harma bo de logs na bla mas gab tshig tu bris dang /
NK023('a)001:2326: chos rgyal skyong la d+harma ra dza zhes bris pa gnyis sbas don yin /
NK023('a)001:2327: rgya gar chos rgyal skyong gi slob dpon gsal ba'i brgyan yin par gsal /
NK023('a)001:2328: bal po ba su dang rgya gar mkhan po gsal ba'i rgyan /
NK023('a)001:2330: bru zha che btsan skyes rnams /
NK023('a)001:2331: jo bo sangs rgyas kyi rtsa ba'i bla ma bzhi'o //
NK023('a)001:2332: d+ha na raka shi ra ni shan ta rag shi
NK023('a)001:2333: tar byas nas slob dpon pad+ma dang gcig pa dang
NK023('a)001:2334: mi gcig par 'dod pa gnyis ka snang ste /
NK023('a)001:2335: slob dpon d+harma bo de dang /
NK023('a)001:2336: slob dpon d+ha na raka shi ta ni mdo dgongs 'dus kyi bsham nas /
NK023('a)001:2337: slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes kyi bla ma yin par gsungs lags /
NK023('a)001:2338: yang in tra bo d+hi'ang snga phyi lan 'ga' byung
NK023('a)001:2339: sh+aakya su tri la'ang in tra zer ba a nu
NK023('a)001:2340: ltar du yin / me tri ka ma la zhes
NK023('a)001:2341: ka ma shi la dang me tri ba'ang cha 'ga'
NK023('a)001:2342: ltar du yin / byung bas / 'dir me tri ka ma gnyis gcig pa de yin /
NK023('a)001:2343: sti ra ma ti gtad rgya'i rgyud yig na mi
NK023('a)001:2344: snang yang tsa ka na snang bas chad pa yin
NK023('a)001:2346: h'u mdzad gtad rgya dang tsa ka li gnyis ka na mi snang bas ma bkod pa'o //
NK023('a)001:2347: se lugs la chos blon d+he ba ma h+aa las ma bshad na'ang /
NK023('a)001:2348: tsaka rnying pa dang gtad rgya gnyis ka na ma h+aa la bshad 'dug pas bkod pa'o //
NK023('a)001:2349: da ni bsgrub sde'i rig 'dzin rnams bstan par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:2350: de yang gshin rje ni slob dpon sangs rgyas ma byon gong du bee ro yin /
NK023('a)001:2351: sangs rgyas ye shes 'dir spyi'i rig 'dzin kyang /
NK023('a)001:2352: sgos su 'jam dpal gshin rje'i rigs yin gsung zhing /
NK023('a)001:2353: 'brog mi ni slob dpon sangs rgyas kyi dus na
NK023('a)001:2354: ma byon pas slob dpon 'o bran dpal du bshad
NK023('a)001:2355: la / rgyal po khri srong yang slob dpon sangs
NK023('a)001:2356: rgyas pas snga zhing bka' brgyad rig 'dzin du bshad
NK023('a)001:2357: la / kyang / 'dir mdo la spyi'i rigs su khrim srong bshad pas /
NK023('a)001:2359: ma h+aa nyi shu po a nu nyi shu la
NK023('a)001:2360: gril a ti nas bsham gyi lnga gang rung la
NK023('a)001:2361: sogs pa ma bgrangs kyang brgya rtsa brgyad mthun la
NK023('a)001:2362: / a nu'i stod nyer lnga spyir bzhag kyang brgya rtsa brgyad thim zhing /
NK023('a)001:2365: ma h+aa la nye rgyud bdun /
NK023('a)001:2366: rigs brgyud nyi shu ste brgya dang bcu yod kyang
NK023('a)001:2367: sh+aakya su tri dang sti ra ma ti ma bgrangs
NK023('a)001:2368: te brgya rtsa brgyad thim pa'o //
NK023('a)001:2369: slob dpon sangs rgyas kyi gong du tsaka li rig
NK023('a)001:2370: 'dzin brgya rtsa brgyad du bshad pas grangs bkod pa'o
NK023('a)001:2371: // sngar gyi rig 'dzin gyi yi ge na bka' brgyad kyi dang /
NK023('a)001:2372: kha bkang dril bas nyer tho ba'i brgya rtsa brgyad mdo'i rig 'dzin byas nas /
NK023('a)001:2373: a nu nyi shu ma bris pa gda' ba'i tsaka li'ang mthong /
NK023('a)001:2374: spyir du brgya dang sum cu so lngar mdzad pa lags par gda' /
NK023('a)001:2376: sngon gyi rgyal sras da lta'i rig 'dzin tshul //
NK023('a)001:2377: bsgrub pa mthar phyin nga rgyal dregs bsnyems kyang //
NK023('a)001:2378: dregs 'gying skyon med snyon rmongs ye shes gsal //
NK023('a)001:2379: dngos grub thob phyir dges spro mnyes mchod rigs //
NK023('a)001:2380: 'jam dpal gshin rje'i 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang //
NK023('a)001:2381: bee ro sangs rgyas ye shes sku yi rig 'dzin la /
NK023('a)001:2382: sgo gsum spyan ras pad+ma dbang chen klu grub dang //
NK023('a)001:2383: btsun pa ngag lam rgyal mchog gsung rig 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:2384: dpal chen badz+ra he ru h'u ka ra //
NK023('a)001:2385: nam mkha' snying po yang dag thugs rig 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:2386: kun bzang che mchog b+hi ma mi tra dang //
NK023('a)001:2387: dz+nya na ku ma bdud rtsi yon tan rigs //
NK023('a)001:2388: rdo rje gzhon nu za hor pra ha sti //
NK023('a)001:2389: mkhar chen mtsho rgyal phur bu phrin las rigs //
NK023('a)001:2390: gsang bdag phyag rdor rom bu gu ya dang //
NK023('a)001:2391: dpal gyi seng ge 'jig rten mchod rten rigs //
NK023('a)001:2392: gtum po stobs chen shan ting garba dang //
NK023('a)001:2393: bee ro tsa na drag sngags dmod pa'i rigs //
NK023('a)001:2394: kun tu bzang mo mngon rdzogs ma mo'i rigs //
NK023('a)001:2395: d+ha na sa kri 'o bran dpal gzhon nu //
NK023('a)001:2396: e ma tshe dang spyi yi rig 'dzin pad+ma 'byung //
NK023('a)001:2397: gsang sngags phyi brgyud bo d+hi sa t+wa dang //
NK023('a)001:2398: mtshan nyid theg gsal 'dzi na mi tra dang //
NK023('a)001:2399: tshogs chen 'dus pa g.yu sgra snying po dang //
NK023('a)001:2400: bka' brgyad sgrub rdzogs dz+nya na ku ma dang //
NK023('a)001:2401: phrin las shar ba'i sog po dpal ye shes //
NK023('a)001:2402: bshad bsgrub mkhas pa dar rje dpal grags dang //
NK023('a)001:2403: mkhas grub phyag bzhes zhang chen rgyal yon tan //
NK023('a)001:2404: 'dus pa mdo yi khri srong lde'u btsan bcas //
NK023('a)001:2405: kha bskang rig 'dzin grub thob nyi shu lnga //
NK023('a)001:2406: phyag rdor sprul pa skar chung khri ral bcas //
NK023('a)001:2407: brgya dang sum cu rtsa lnga 'khor bcas la //
NK023('a)001:2408: sgo gsum dang ba'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal zhing //
NK023('a)001:2409: rtse gcig gdung ba'i stobs kyis gsol 'debs kyis //
NK023('a)001:2410: thugs rje chen po'i shugs kyis rjes bzung la //
NK023('a)001:2411: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang byin dngos grub stsol //
NK023('a)001:2412: da ni bod kyi rig 'dzin rnams 'di las rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK023('a)001:2414: slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes rin chen gyi //
NK023('a)001:2415: slob ma bzhi dang dge mched bco lnga dang //
NK023('a)001:2416: rin chen gsum dang 'khor brgyad la sogs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:2417: bstan pa snga dar rig 'dzin thams cad la //
NK023('a)001:2418: sgo gsum dang ba'i shugs yon tan rgya mtsho ye shes rgya mtsho dang //
NK023('a)001:2419: rgya ston blo gros byang chub gzhon nu dang //
NK023('a)001:2420: tho gar nam mkha' lde dang zhu bsod nams //
NK023('a)001:2421: bla ma du ma'i bka' babs zur sh+aaka 'byung //
NK023('a)001:2422: zur chung shes grags rtse mo sgom chen mchog /
NK023('a)001:2423: thugs sras ka bzhi gdung brgyad bcud 'dus pa'i //
NK023('a)001:2424: gsang bdag sh+aakya seng ge sgro phug pa'i //
NK023('a)001:2425: gcen po rgyal tsha sh+aaka rdor rtsal sh+aaka 'byung //
NK023('a)001:2426: sgro phug dngos slob 'gar ston gzung nge dang //
NK023('a)001:2427: sregs ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan la sogs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:2428: glan gyi ston pa rdo rje 'od kyi gsan //
NK023('a)001:2429: bla chen bsod nams rgyal ba'i mtshan can dang //
NK023('a)001:2430: bla ma dpal ldan chos kyi seng ge dang //
NK023('a)001:2431: bla ma lha rje sangs rgyas dpal gyis ni //
NK023('a)001:2432: bla ma bsod nams mgon po nyid la gnang //
NK023('a)001:2433: slob ma myang ston bla ma dpal ldan dang //
NK023('a)001:2434: zur ston bla ma sh+aakya bzang po dang //
NK023('a)001:2435: bka' drin rtsa ba'i bla chen bsam grub rdo rje ste //
NK023('a)001:2436: de ltar gsum kas zur h+aa sh+aakya 'byung la gnang //
NK023('a)001:2437: bstan pa bar dar rig 'dzin thams cad la //
NK023('a)001:2438: sgo gsum dang ba'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal zhing //
NK023('a)001:2439: rtse gcig gdung ba'i stobs kyis gsol 'debs kyis //
NK023('a)001:2440: thugs rje chen po'i shugs kyis rjes bzung la //
NK023('a)001:2441: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang byin dngos grub stsol ////
NK023('a)001:2442: rdo rje klu'i mtshan byang snang /
NK023('a)001:2444: dngos grub brnyes pa'i slob dpon rnams kyis mdo ha rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK023('a)001:2445: rgyal po d+ha he ta na los mdo ha rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK023('a)001:2446: tsan+dana nags tshal du nam gyi gung la blangs pa /
NK023('a)001:2447: h'u 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid ni //
NK023('a)001:2448: kun gzhi ma bcos byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:2450: snang ba'i gzugs med byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:2451: ci la'ang mi spyad rtog pa mi bzung zhing //
NK023('a)001:2452: sems kyi rang bzhin bsam med mkha' 'dra la //
NK023('a)001:2453: ma yengs ma bslad bcos pa med par bzhag /
NK023('a)001:2454: sgom du med pa'i chos nyid dbyings chen la //
NK023('a)001:2455: bsam du med pa'i rig pa ma yengs bzhag /
NK023('a)001:2456: sgom du rdul yang 'di las med par khums //
NK023('a)001:2457: skye mang brgyud nas rgyal por bdag skyes te //
NK023('a)001:2458: d+ha he ta lo nga rgyal bcag pa dang //
NK023('a)001:2459: sngon chad byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK023('a)001:2460: sems dang chos gnyis 'dres pa'i bro blang zhing //
NK023('a)001:2461: sgyu ma'i phung po da ltar bsnyil ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:2462: kun bzang thugs kyi 'od zer bdag la shar //
NK023('a)001:2463: g+hi ta ma ko l+la pa ho zhes glu blangs so //
NK023('a)001:2467: // // sras thu bo ra tsa ha stis tsan+da gor shi sha'i shing rta'i kha ru /
NK023('a)001:2468: mdo ha rdo rje'i glu nam gyi cha stod la gsungs pa /
NK023('a)001:2469: h'u kun gzhi ye nas ma bcos stong pa ji bzhin dbyings //
NK023('a)001:2470: rang byung ye shes mkha' 'dra mnyam pa chen po'i ngang //
NK023('a)001:2471: tshig dang yi ge sgra las 'das pas kun tu bzang //
NK023('a)001:2472: sems dang chos nyid mnyam nyid dbyer med na //
NK023('a)001:2473: lus ngag yid gsum mtshan mas ci bslad kyang //
NK023('a)001:2474: chos nyid byang chub sems la 'gyur med te //
NK023('a)001:2475: rnam rtog skyon spangs kun gzhi byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:2476: ma bcos ngang la zhag pa las //
NK023('a)001:2477: sgom pa gud na med par khums //
NK023('a)001:2478: sgyu ma'i phung po da lta bsnyil ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:2479: kung bzang thugs kyi 'od zer bdag la shar //
NK023('a)001:2480: g+hi ta ma ko l+la pa ho /
NK023('a)001:2485: // // sras mo pa ra nis me tog ku mu ta'i tshal du /
NK023('a)001:2486: rdo rje'i glu nam gyi cha smad la gsungs pa /
NK023('a)001:2487: h'u kun gzhi ma bcos ye nas byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:2488: rgyu dang rkyen gyis ma bskyed 'jigs 'bral med //
NK023('a)001:2489: rang byung lhun gyis grub pa bcom ldan 'das //
NK023('a)001:2490: gzung 'dzin yul las 'das pas rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs //
NK023('a)001:2491: ye nas ma bcos chos kyi dbyings nyid la //
NK023('a)001:2492: rang byung rig pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK023('a)001:2493: ma bslad ye nas bzhag pa ni //
NK023('a)001:2494: rdo rje sems dpa'i dgongs pa ste //
NK023('a)001:2495: bdag gis dgongs pa 'di las med par 'jal //
NK023('a)001:2496: sgyu ma'i phung po da ltar bsnyil ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:2497: kun bzang thugs kyi gter chen bdag la babs //
NK023('a)001:2498: g+hi ta ma ko l+la pa ho /
NK023('a)001:2499: zhes glu blangs so rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:2502: // // klu'i rgyal po 'jog pos rgya mtsho'i gting du skya rengs dang po shar tsam na /
NK023('a)001:2504: h'u mtha' dang dbus med nam mkha' lta bu'i thugs //
NK023('a)001:2505: smra bsam yul las 'das pa chos kyi sku //
NK023('a)001:2506: srid 'byung skye 'gro rnam par dag byas na //
NK023('a)001:2507: ma bcos rnam par dag pa kun gzhi byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:2508: ma btsal mnyam par bzhag na sgom pa'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:2509: rig pa chos kyi dbyings su ma bcos las //
NK023('a)001:2510: rnam par grol ba'i lam mchog gzhan med de //
NK023('a)001:2511: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa'i dgongs pa nyid //
NK023('a)001:2512: dpag cing gzhal yang 'di las med par 'jal //
NK023('a)001:2513: bdag gi phung po gdos bcas 'di bsnyil nas //
NK023('a)001:2514: kun bzang dbye ba med pa'i sa la mchis //
NK023('a)001:2515: g+hi ta ma ko l+la pa ho /
NK023('a)001:2516: zhes glu blangs so rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:2519: // // khyi'i rgyal po ku ku ra dzas /
NK023('a)001:2520: rgya mtsho'i gling la skya rengs gnyis pa shar tsam na rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK023('a)001:2521: h'u ye nas lhun grub kun tu bzang po'i ngang //
NK023('a)001:2522: gsal la rtog med spros bral byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:2523: mi 'gyur mi dmigs chos kyi dbyings nyid la //
NK023('a)001:2524: rig pa mi 'gyur ma bslad mnyam bzhag na //
NK023('a)001:2525: ci la'ang mi gnas gang la'ang mi gnas 'byung //
NK023('a)001:2526: mchog tu gsang ba'i byang chub sems nyid ni //
NK023('a)001:2527: rna bas gnyon pa'i spyod yul yod ma yin //
NK023('a)001:2528: kun gzhi mi 'gyur dbyings chen la //
NK023('a)001:2529: rig pa mi 'gyur ma yengs bzhag /
NK023('a)001:2530: bsgom pa 'di las med par khums //
NK023('a)001:2531: khams gsum rang sar grol bas btsal zhing bsgrub mi dgos //
NK023('a)001:2532: re zhing dogs pa med pas bdag nyid sangs rgyas yin //
NK023('a)001:2533: g+hi ta ma ko l+la pa a ho /
NK023('a)001:2534: zhes glu blangs so rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:2537: // // gu ru n+aa ga dz+hu nas /
NK023('a)001:2538: rgyan phyag gsal gyi gnas su /
NK023('a)001:2539: skya rengs gsum pa shar tsam na rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK023('a)001:2540: h'u snang ba thams cad ye nas dbyings chen la //
NK023('a)001:2541: rig pa 'pho 'gyur med pa'i dur btab na //
NK023('a)001:2542: dbyings nyid mi 'gyur rig pa mi bslad de //
NK023('a)001:2543: ma yengs mi 'gyur mkha' ltar dag pa la //
NK023('a)001:2544: ma yengs ma bcos yong gis gsal ba la //
NK023('a)001:2545: sgom pa'i ming du btags pa gud na med par khums //
NK023('a)001:2546: bdag gi phung po gdos bcas 'di //
NK023('a)001:2547: dbye ba med pa'i sa la 'chi //
NK023('a)001:2548: g+hi ta ma ko l+la pa a ho /
NK023('a)001:2553: // // khyi'i rgyal po ku ku ra dza phyi ma rgya
NK023('a)001:2554: mtsho'i gling la dmar rengs dang po shar tsam na
NK023('a)001:2556: h'u chos nyid byang chub sems nyid 'byung ba lnga yin te /
NK023('a)001:2557: ma bcos rang bzhin gsal bas mkha' ltar dag /
NK023('a)001:2558: 'gro ba'i gzung 'dzin sreg pas me ltar gnas //
NK023('a)001:2559: dmigs med gdod nas dag pas rlung ltar gnas //
NK023('a)001:2560: gzung 'dzin skyon dang bral bas chu ltar gnas //
NK023('a)001:2561: cis kyang bskyod pa med pas sa ltar gnas //
NK023('a)001:2562: 'byung ba lnga nyid ye nas chos nyid byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:2563: gdod nas dag pas nam mkha' 'dra ba la //
NK023('a)001:2564: dmigs pa med par ma yengs gnas pa las //
NK023('a)001:2565: sgom pa 'di las med par rtogs //
NK023('a)001:2566: bdag gi phung po gdos bcas 'di //
NK023('a)001:2567: dbye ba med pa'i sa la 'chi //
NK023('a)001:2568: g+hi ta ma ko la pa a ho /
NK023('a)001:2569: zhes glu'i rtogs pa brjod do //
NK023('a)001:2573: // // gnod sbyin mo byang chub kyi rgya mtsho'i gling la
NK023('a)001:2574: dmar rengs gnyis pa shar tsam na mdo ha rdo
NK023('a)001:2576: h'u chos nyid byang chub sems la lta zhing snang med de /
NK023('a)001:2577: lta ba'i gzugs med yongs la gsal bar snang //
NK023('a)001:2578: cis kyang bcos su med de spyad du med //
NK023('a)001:2579: sems kyi rang bzhin ci la'ang mi gnas te //
NK023('a)001:2580: rig pa byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin te //
NK023('a)001:2581: ji ltar bslad kyang dbyings las 'gyur ba med //
NK023('a)001:2582: dbyings nyid rig pas mi btsal te //
NK023('a)001:2583: sems nyid mkha' ltar dag pa de //
NK023('a)001:2584: ma bcos rang bzhin med pa las //
NK023('a)001:2585: sgom pa 'di las med par bdag gis rtogs //
NK023('a)001:2586: bdag gi phung po gdos bcas 'di bsnyil nas //
NK023('a)001:2587: kun bzang thugs kyi 'od zer bdag la shar //
NK023('a)001:2588: g+hi ta ma ko l+la pa a ho zhes glu blangs so //
NK023('a)001:2592: // // smad 'tshong ma 'bu ta sa ma yas /
NK023('a)001:2593: shing nal byi gsal ba'i rtsar /
NK023('a)001:2594: dmar rengs gsum pa shar tsam na rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK023('a)001:2595: e ma ho chos nyid byang chub sems /
NK023('a)001:2596: brtag tu med de spyad du med //
NK023('a)001:2597: btsal zhing gnyen pos bcos su med //
NK023('a)001:2598: sems las sangs rgyas logs na med //
NK023('a)001:2599: btsal bas mi rnyed sems la sangs rgyas med //
NK023('a)001:2600: sems kyi rang bzhin ma bcos sangs rgyas yin //
NK023('a)001:2601: gdod nas ma btsal byang chub snying po la //
NK023('a)001:2602: ting 'dzin ma bslad ngang gis gsal ba las //
NK023('a)001:2603: sangs rgyas dgongs pa 'di las med par khums //
NK023('a)001:2604: bdag gi phung po gdos bcas 'di bsnyil phyir //
NK023('a)001:2605: kun bzang thugs kyi 'od zer bdag la shar /
NK023('a)001:2606: g+hi ta ma ko l+la pa a ho zhes glu blangs so //
NK023('a)001:2611: shing ne kro ta'i rtsar srod kyi thun las bzhengs nas glu blangs pa /
NK023('a)001:2612: h'u kun gzhi yangs pa'i dbye thang la //
NK023('a)001:2613: dag pa klong nas nyi ma shar //
NK023('a)001:2614: shar ba'i dus na nub mtha' med //
NK023('a)001:2615: shar nas ma bcos gsal ba las //
NK023('a)001:2616: sangs rgyas chos nyid snga phyi gsum //
NK023('a)001:2617: gang du btsal yang rnyed mtha' med //
NK023('a)001:2618: kun gzhi yangs pa'i chos nyid la //
NK023('a)001:2619: rig pa sems kyi nyi shar ba //
NK023('a)001:2620: ma bcos nub pa med pa la //
NK023('a)001:2621: sgom du 'di las med par khums //
NK023('a)001:2622: myong na sems kyi bdud rtsi myong //
NK023('a)001:2623: lta na rig pa'i ye shes ltos //
NK023('a)001:2624: pad+ma ko l+la sha a ho //
NK023('a)001:2629: // // a tsar+ya a lo kes dpag bsam shing gi grib
NK023('a)001:2630: ma la tho rangs ka mnyam pa la bzhengs nas
NK023('a)001:2632: h'u byang chub sems ni nam mkha' lta bu'i klong //
NK023('a)001:2633: gsal la rtog pa med pa'i ye shes ni //
NK023('a)001:2634: phyi dang nang med kun la gsal bar snang //
NK023('a)001:2635: gdod nas dag pas nam mkha'i klong 'dra las //
NK023('a)001:2636: rnam rtog sreg pa'i ye shes gsal shar bas //
NK023('a)001:2637: skye 'gags spangs nas rang bzhin med pa las //
NK023('a)001:2638: sangs rgyas dgongs pa 'di las med par 'jal //
NK023('a)001:2639: za na sems kyi bdud rtsi zo //
NK023('a)001:2640: gon na chos nyid gos su gon //
NK023('a)001:2641: e ko l+la sha a ho zhes glu blangs so //
NK023('a)001:2645: // // dbu brgyan gyi mkhan po d+ha hes rin po che'i
NK023('a)001:2646: gling la nam gung yol la rdo rje'i glu gsungs
NK023('a)001:2647: pa / h'u sems nyid sangs rgyas yin pa las //
NK023('a)001:2648: sangs rgyas sems las logs na med //
NK023('a)001:2649: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas las //
NK023('a)001:2650: rig pa mi 'gyur rang bzhin med pa de //
NK023('a)001:2651: zab don dam zab mo chos dbyings don dam mi brjod gsal //
NK023('a)001:2652: rgya mtsho che ltar chos nyid zab mo las //
NK023('a)001:2653: rig pa mi 'gyur bzod cig nang nas 'char //
NK023('a)001:2654: kun gzhi gtan nas sbyong ba'i nyi chen po //
NK023('a)001:2655: mkha' ltar dag pas yongs la khyab par brdal //
NK023('a)001:2656: chos nyid ye nas dag pa sbyang du med pa las //
NK023('a)001:2657: rig pa mi 'gyur gdod nas gsal bar shar //
NK023('a)001:2658: phyin ci log gis ma bslad gsal ba las //
NK023('a)001:2659: bde bar gshegs pa'i dgongs pa 'di las med par 'jal //
NK023('a)001:2660: chos nyid nam mkha' che ba la //
NK023('a)001:2661: rnal 'byor khyung chen gshog pa lding //
NK023('a)001:2662: kar ma ko la sha a ho //
NK023('a)001:2667: // // drang srong ba na tis na kro ta'i dgon par
NK023('a)001:2668: srod yol ba'i dus su rdo rje'i glu blangs pa
NK023('a)001:2669: / h'u ma bcol mkha' la gza' skar kun 'phyo bas //
NK023('a)001:2670: gdod nas dag pas mkha' ni mi bskyod de //
NK023('a)001:2671: byang chub sems nyid mkha' ltar dag pa la //
NK023('a)001:2672: mtshan ma'i rnam rtog sgyu mas ci bslad kyang //
NK023('a)001:2674: chos dbyings bdal ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK023('a)001:2675: rig pa ye shes dur pa btab pas na //
NK023('a)001:2676: gsal ba 'od kyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar 'char //
NK023('a)001:2677: shar ba nyid kyi don de ma yengs pas //
NK023('a)001:2678: sangs rgyas rnams la dgongs pa 'di las med //
NK023('a)001:2679: rig pa ye shes rlung chen gyis //
NK023('a)001:2680: rnam par rtog pa'i mun pa dengs //
NK023('a)001:2681: i ka sha ko l+la ma a ho /
NK023('a)001:2686: // // sras mo g+ho ma de byis ra dza'i dgon gnas
NK023('a)001:2687: su nam gyi cha smad du rdo rje'i glu gsungs
NK023('a)001:2688: pa / h'u sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs nyid yi ge a yin te /
NK023('a)001:2689: a yi dngos gzhi ye nas byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:2690: 'pho 'gyur 'du 'bral med par rtog sa na sangs rgyas te //
NK023('a)001:2691: smra bsam yul las 'das pa'i dbyings nyid la //
NK023('a)001:2692: a ltar skye ba med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:2693: ma bcos ma yengs mnyam par bzhag pa la //
NK023('a)001:2694: bdag gis sgom pa 'di las med par 'jal //
NK023('a)001:2695: chos nyid dbye thang chen po la //
NK023('a)001:2696: rig pa ye shes rta pho rgyug /
NK023('a)001:2697: ka pa la ko l+la pa sha a ho //
NK023('a)001:2698: zhes glu blangs so rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:2701: // // kha che'i mkhan po rab snang gis tsan+da sdong po'i
NK023('a)001:2702: rtsar nam gyi gung thun la rdo rje'i glu gsungs
NK023('a)001:2703: pa / h'u byang chub sems nyid ye nas chos kyi sku //
NK023('a)001:2704: mkha' dang 'dra bar kun la khyab par snang //
NK023('a)001:2705: snang ba nyid kyang stong pa ste //
NK023('a)001:2706: stong pa'i cho 'phrul cir yang snang //
NK023('a)001:2707: bsam du brdul yang med pa la //
NK023('a)001:2708: brjod bral med par ma yengs zhog /
NK023('a)001:2709: chos nyid sems kyi bdud rtsi yis //
NK023('a)001:2710: khams gsum 'khor ba'i nad pa gsos //
NK023('a)001:2711: ka ma ko l+la sha a ho //
NK023('a)001:2712: zhes glu blangs so rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:2715: // // lha'i rgyal po de ba ra tsas grong khyer dpal yon du srod thun phyed kyi dus su /
NK023('a)001:2717: h'u snang srid chos rnams mngon du ltos pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:2718: yang dag nyid du 'di ltar sgom par bya //
NK023('a)001:2719: snang srid thams cad ye nas kun tu bzang po'i ngang //
NK023('a)001:2720: 'di las gzhan med ma lus snying po'i rgya //
NK023('a)001:2721: snang ba mtha' dag skye med bdud rtsi sku gsung thugs //
NK023('a)001:2722: skye med ngang la ma yengs mnyam bzhag pa //
NK023('a)001:2723: sgom par bya ba 'di las med par rtogs //
NK023('a)001:2724: lus ni sgyu ma'i phung po mi gtsang ste //
NK023('a)001:2725: sems ni ye shes chen po gson //
NK023('a)001:2726: tsan tra de ba ko l+la pa a ho /
NK023('a)001:2731: // // dar ma ra tsas me tog gi tshal du nam gyi cha stod la rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK023('a)001:2732: h'u sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas mdzod chen las //
NK023('a)001:2733: gang ltar rtags shing ji ltar snang ba las //
NK023('a)001:2734: 'byung 'jug rgyu ba thams cad kun tu bzang //
NK023('a)001:2735: gnyis su med pa'i rig pa de //
NK023('a)001:2736: kun tu bzang po'i sems la gnas //
NK023('a)001:2737: rig pa'i dbyings las ma bslad pas //
NK023('a)001:2738: sgom zhing gnas pa 'di las med //
NK023('a)001:2739: kye ma ho ma rtogs snying re rje /
NK023('a)001:2740: bdag nyid rang sar grol ba a la la /
NK023('a)001:2741: mdo ha ko la pa a ho /
NK023('a)001:2746: // // 'bu ta kug tas dbyen pa chen po'i gnas su rdo rje'i glu gsungs pa /
NK023('a)001:2747: h'u chos rnams ma bcos kun tu bzang po la /
NK023('a)001:2748: gsal la 'gyur ba med pas byang sems ngang de la /
NK023('a)001:2749: mtshan ma'i rnam par rtog pas mi bslad de //
NK023('a)001:2750: rnam rtog rang byung rang zhir gnas pa las //
NK023('a)001:2751: sgom pa 'di las gud na med par rtogs //
NK023('a)001:2752: sems kyi me long ma ltas na //
NK023('a)001:2753: rnam rtog dri mas gos pa re //
NK023('a)001:2754: prad dz+nya ko l+la pa a ho /
NK023('a)001:2759: // // sh+ri sing has bsam gtan gyi khang par tshogs kyi mchod pa'i dus su rdo rje'i glu blangs pa /
NK023('a)001:2760: h'u ji ltar bsams kyang sgom du med //
NK023('a)001:2761: ji ltar smras kyang spyad du med //
NK023('a)001:2762: ye shes chen po'i dbyings nyid la //
NK023('a)001:2763: btsal ba med par 'od shar te //
NK023('a)001:2764: bsam du med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK023('a)001:2765: yengs pa med par mnyam par bzhag /
NK023('a)001:2766: sgom pa 'di las med par khums //
NK023('a)001:2767: rig pa ye shes mdung rtse yis //
NK023('a)001:2768: rnam rtog dgra bo brdul du barloga /
NK023('a)001:2769: rat+na ko l+la pa a ho /
NK023('a)001:2774: // // rig pa lus la shar ba'i bee ro tsa na bdag /
NK023('a)001:2775: rdo rje sems dpa'i man ngag dbyings nas brdol //
NK023('a)001:2776: las 'phro skal bar ldan pa'i khri srong lde'u btsan gyis /
NK023('a)001:2777: chos dang sems su ldan pa'i bee ro tsa na la /
NK023('a)001:2778: yon dang dad par ldan pas gser gyi pa tra byin /
NK023('a)001:2779: bgrod dka' 'jigs par ldan pa'i yul dgal te //
NK023('a)001:2780: las dang thugs rjer ldan pa'i sems phyogs btsal //
NK023('a)001:2781: bee ro tsa nas rdo rje'i glu bcu dgu btsad po la thugs kyi gter du phul lo //
NK023('a)001:2782: btsad pos kyang 'di las zab pa med par dgongs nas /
NK023('a)001:2783: bsam yas kyi ka ba'i nang du bse sgrom la rgya bzhi btab nas sbas so //
NK023('a)001:2784: dus dus su brten cing gzigs so //
NK023('a)001:2785: btsad pos rnubs nam mkha'i snying po sku srungs yin pas gnang ngo //
NK023('a)001:2786: des dz+nya na ku ma ra la /
NK023('a)001:2787: des sog po lha dpal gyi ye shes la /
NK023('a)001:2788: des rnubs thugs sangs rgyas la gnang /
NK023('a)001:2789: des yon tan rgya mtsho yab sras la gnang /
NK023('a)001:2790: des nyang chen nyang chung la /
NK023('a)001:2791: des zur po che la gnang /
NK023('a)001:2792: yang mdo rdzogs chen gyi brgyud pa zur la'ang bzhugs /
NK023('a)001:2793: rdo rje glu'i bsam gtan zhes bya ba rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:2796: // // rdo rje glu'i bsam gtan bco brgyad la /
NK023('a)001:2797: dang po chos nyid klong rdol glu'i bsam gtan dang /
NK023('a)001:2798: rig pa ye shes bde ba byang sems dbyings 'byung
NK023('a)001:2799: lnga dngos grub brtsal med gsang ba nam mkha' phrin
NK023('a)001:2800: las rang byung skye med chos sku sku gsung thugs
NK023('a)001:2801: grol ba shes rab klong rdol klu'i bsam gtan dang
NK023('a)001:2802: bco brgyad do // rin po che klong brdol gyi glu'i bsam gtan 'di ni kun gyi spyi'o //
NK023('a)001:2803: rdo rje glu'i mtshan byang rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:2806: // // na mo gu ru a ti 'di la /
NK023('a)001:2810: me cig ma gang bde ba gyer nas /
NK023('a)001:2812: glu len pas grub pa'ang mdzad kyin gda' /
NK023('a)001:2813: a ti rtsal dbang mdo lugs /
NK023('a)001:2814: zur ha sh+aaka 'byung ziin bris rtsa ba i th+ai //
NK023('a)001:2816: // gtad rgya lnga'i go don gyi brjed byang gi 'grel pa bzhugs so //
NK023('a)001:2818: mdus pa mdo dbang gi gtad rgya'i go don rgyas par brjed byang 'grel du 'dod pas /
NK023('a)001:2819: gnas dben par sngon dbang bskur ba'i zhi dkyil dang /
NK023('a)001:2822: slob dpon gyis dgongs pa bya /
NK023('a)001:2823: slob bu rang nyid kyis zhi ba gzhung bsrang /
NK023('a)001:2825: rgyas par phrin gzhung dong sprugs nas kun bzang don yan chad bya'o //
NK023('a)001:2827: zhi ba 'bring po thon pa'i rjes su /
NK023('a)001:2828: slob bu sngar dbang rdzogs pa theg dgu mdo lugs su thob pa la bskur gyi /
NK023('a)001:2829: de ma thob pa la bskur na /
NK023('a)001:2830: dmangs rigs la steng 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i gdan dang bka' rtags byin pa dang 'dra'o //
NK023('a)001:2831: sngar thob kyang dbang bskyar dgos pas bskyar te bskur ba'am phyis zhu ba'i mdun pa byed du gzhug /
NK023('a)001:2832: slob dpon 'os pa la gtad do //
NK023('a)001:2833: 'dul ba gzhung gi dge tshul bstan pa 'di la /
NK023('a)001:2834: lo bdun ma lon pa dang /
NK023('a)001:2835: grangs gsum pas mang ba dang /
NK023('a)001:2836: lo lon kyang bya rog bskrod mi nus pa la dge slong dge tshul mi byed /
NK023('a)001:2837: las gral gyi dge slong lo nyi shu mngal bcas
NK023('a)001:2838: dbyug pa lo 'gor byas pa ma song ba la
NK023('a)001:2839: mi byed / gnas kyi bla ma dge slong lo lnga lon pa dang /
NK023('a)001:2840: slob pa'i mkhan po dge slong lo bcu lon pa mkhas shing phan thogs kyis byed dgos pa dang /
NK023('a)001:2841: mkhan slob dge 'dun thams cad thugs mthun pas nyes
NK023('a)001:2842: pa mchis na gang yang snang bas zhar la tshe
NK023('a)001:2844: 'dir bstan 'dzin sus byed mi shes pas rgyun mi nyams pa'i slad du bstan pa la bsams nas /
NK023('a)001:2845: sngar dbang thob pa la phal pa la'ang mdzad do //
NK023('a)001:2846: de nas thar pa'i lam mtshon pa'i dar ram ras
NK023('a)001:2847: dkar po phyis rkyong dang bsdur nyan pa cig la
NK023('a)001:2848: / gnas brtan bla ma'i drung nas kha lta ba'i phyogs dkar pa nas /
NK023('a)001:2849: rim par sa bcu gsum gyi tshom bu ming don dran cing /
NK023('a)001:2850: myur bar sa thob nges par 'dun pas /
NK023('a)001:2851: me tog gam 'bras bu'am rin po che'am sman gyi tshom bu bcu gsum ste /
NK023('a)001:2852: mas rims kyis sngags mtshan nyid kyi ming thun mongs pa ni /
NK023('a)001:2853: lha mo nag mo'i mdo gzungs dang /
NK023('a)001:2854: rgyud gzhan dag las kyang gsungs pa 'di skad du /
NK023('a)001:2855: nam yang 'khor bar mi ltung zhing //
NK023('a)001:2856: mya ngan 'das pa thob pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:2857: nyan thos sa rnams non pa dang //
NK023('a)001:2858: rten 'brel bcu gnyis shes par bya //
NK023('a)001:2859: byang chub sems dpa'i sa rnams ni //
NK023('a)001:2861: sbyang dka' mngon gyur ring du song //
NK023('a)001:2862: mi g.yo legs pa chos kyi sprin //
NK023('a)001:2863: phyag rgyas sa chen bla na med //
NK023('a)001:2864: bcu gnyis sa yongs thob 'gyur te //
NK023('a)001:2868: las kyi 'od dang dpe med pa //
NK023('a)001:2869: dpe ldan pa dang shes rab 'od //
NK023('a)001:2870: thams cad mkhyen dang rang rig ste //
NK023('a)001:2871: bcu gnyis sangs rgyas sa rnams kyang //
NK023('a)001:2872: 'di tshe byung na myur du thob //
NK023('a)001:2873: ces pa bcu gnyis bstan la /
NK023('a)001:2874: de'ang sbyin dang tshul khrims bzod brtson 'grus //
NK023('a)001:2875: ser sna 'chal khro le lo bral //
NK023('a)001:2876: bsam gtan shes rab thabs stobs kyis //
NK023('a)001:2877: g.yeng rmugs mi mkhas rgol ba sel //
NK023('a)001:2878: smon lam ye shes pha rol phyin //
NK023('a)001:2880: ye shes lnga dang chos kyi dbyings //
NK023('a)001:2881: rang byung ye shes bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:2883: kor bdun bcu gsum rdo rje 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:2884: bla ma'i sa skor sku gsung thugs //
NK023('a)001:2885: yon tan phrin las dbyings shes bdun //
NK023('a)001:2889: sa bcu'i mdo ltar rgyas par de tshe'i don bshad kyang rung /
NK023('a)001:2891: khrus bya bgegs bskrad tshe srung skyo ba dang dad pa bskyed /
NK023('a)001:2892: de nas bla ma'i drung du yon gser zho gang bas mi nyung ba'i rdzas kyis brgyan byas te /
NK023('a)001:2894: rin po che kar sha pa ni rgyal po'i rgya can /
NK023('a)001:2897: bod kyi ya tshe na me tog yod do //
NK023('a)001:2898: gang ltar na'ang slongs mo pa yin kyang /
NK023('a)001:2899: rgya 'di bsgrub par bya ste re zhig g.yar bas
NK023('a)001:2900: kyang 'grub ste btsun gsar gyi gos dang lhung bzed
NK023('a)001:2901: ltar ro // de nas slob dpon gyis gnang ba zhu ba dang /
NK023('a)001:2902: bzod gsol yid kyis rang gi bla ma dang dkyil 'khor la byas la /
NK023('a)001:2903: man+dala de'ang mchod pa bsnan pa cung zhig dang bcas nas dbul zhing /
NK023('a)001:2904: rdzas de'ang chud mi za bar srung spel don 'gyur mkho cha bya'o //
NK023('a)001:2906: gzhan mas gang grub bya ba'ang spyan ras gzigs kyi 'grel pa nas bshad do //
NK023('a)001:2907: de nas bu rnams gral la 'dug la skyabs 'gro sems bskyed dang gsol 'debs byed du gzhug /
NK023('a)001:2908: dmigs pa ma yengs pas 'dzab ci rigs pa'ang bgrang /
NK023('a)001:2909: rgyas par drug gsum bco brgyad pa dang /
NK023('a)001:2911: sngags kyi kras gdang ngam dbang po rnams skabs 'adi'am
NK023('a)001:2912: gzhan du 'chad pa'am nyan dgos snyan rgyud 'di bsgrag
NK023('a)001:2913: go // de'ang sngon 'gro 'di dran du bzhugs par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:2914: shar phyogs mngon dga' na sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa /
NK023('a)001:2915: lho phyogs dpal ldan na sangs rgyas rin 'byung /
NK023('a)001:2916: nub phyogs bde ba can du sangs rgyas 'od dpag med /
NK023('a)001:2917: byang phyogs rnam dag na sangs rgyas gdon mi za bar grub pa /
NK023('a)001:2918: steng phyogs dbus byang chub kyi snying po can du sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad /
NK023('a)001:2919: dbus mi mjed du sangs rgyas thub pa'i dbang po dang /
NK023('a)001:2920: 'go thal bas khebs par sangs rgyas thal ba'i dbang po'i dbyangs dang /
NK023('a)001:2921: byung tshul rnams dgongs 'dus kyi gleng gzhi tsho bsgrag pa'am /
NK023('a)001:2924: shes rgyud la nges pa rnyed par brjod pa gal che'o //
NK023('a)001:2925: gal te dgongs 'dus sgrog na dbang thob rjes yin cing bkra shis kyi slad du /
NK023('a)001:2926: kyee ma kyi hud dang sangs rgyas grongs pa'i gtam
NK023('a)001:2927: dang tshig smre sngags kyi rjes bzlos mi brjod pa
NK023('a)001:2928: dang / bdud thul ba la sogs pa'i skabs kyi
NK023('a)001:2929: 'phrod bzang ba la mgo gzugs pa dang mtshams bzhag
NK023('a)001:2930: dang / par bya'o // ran pa dang mtshams par bshad par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:2931: +thii zhing khams thams cad du grags par mos pa bya //
NK023('a)001:2933: // ston pa gsang ba'i bdag po la gtad rgya snyan rgyud ni phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:2934: ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thugs rje che la thabs mkhas pa des /
NK023('a)001:2935: lha'i gnas dga' ldan nas mi'i grong khyer chen po ser skyar 'khrungs nas /
NK023('a)001:2936: skye 'gro'i nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong gi
NK023('a)001:2937: gnyen por chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong
NK023('a)001:2938: bka' stsal / nyan thos kyi theg pa chu bo na ra dza rar bka' stsal /
NK023('a)001:2939: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa kun dga' ra bar bka' stsal /
NK023('a)001:2940: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa bya rgod phung po'i ri'am rgyal po'i khab tu bka' stsal /
NK023('a)001:2941: kri ya ba ra na ser bka' stsal /
NK023('a)001:2942: u pa ya ri rab kyi rtse la bka' stsal /
NK023('a)001:2943: yo ga me ri 'bar bar bka' stsal /
NK023('a)001:2944: u nu yo ga bsil ba'i tshal du babs /
NK023('a)001:2945: a ti yo ga d+ha na ko sha'i gling du babs /
NK023('a)001:2946: ma h+aa yo ga rgyal po dza'i khang steng du babs /
NK023('a)001:2947: sems can ma smin pa smin pa dang /
NK023('a)001:2948: smin pa grol ba'i lam la bkod nas /
NK023('a)001:2949: sku mya ngan las 'da' bar dgongs nas gsang sngags phyis 'byung bar lung bstan pa /
NK023('a)001:2950: nga ni 'di na mi gnas nas /
NK023('a)001:2951: lo ni brgya dang bcu gnyis na //
NK023('a)001:2952: 'dzam bu gling gi lho phyogs na //
NK023('a)001:2953: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK023('a)001:2954: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK023('a)001:2955: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK023('a)001:2956: thugs rje mthun pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK023('a)001:2957: gsang sngags 'byung ba'i lung bstan pa'o //
NK023('a)001:2958: mi las dam pa skal bzang rnams //
NK023('a)001:2959: lung de la ni bsnyan par gyis //
NK023('a)001:2960: zhes gsungs te mya ngan las 'das nas lo nyer brgyad kyi dus su /
NK023('a)001:2961: rgyal po dza dang dam pa'i rigs can lnga la gsang ba'i bdag po dngos su byon nas /
NK023('a)001:2963: lho nub rnga yab gling gi ri bo ma la ya'i rtse mor chos kyi 'khor lo bskor te /
NK023('a)001:2964: gdams pa'i mdzod gsum a nu'i chos skor dang /
NK023('a)001:2965: tan tra sde chen po bco brgyad ma h+aa yo
NK023('a)001:2966: ga'i chos skor la sogs pa phye nas de'i man
NK023('a)001:2967: ngag dang 'grel pa dang phra mo la sogs par
NK023('a)001:2968: phye nas bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi bstan pa dar bar
NK023('a)001:2969: mdzad do // dus de tsam na rgyal khams yongs kyi rje la /
NK023('a)001:2970: mchog tu gces pa'i nor dang longs spyod ni mang zhing che /
NK023('a)001:2971: rgyu'i chos rab tu zab pa'i bstan chos rnams ni dar zhing rgyas /
NK023('a)001:2972: dbyig tu sgrub pa'i gsang sngags bla na med pa rnams ni ma byung ba'i dus de tsam na /
NK023('a)001:2973: yab rgyal po d+ha na ko sha zhes bya ba'i
NK023('a)001:2974: bu mo srid pa g.yung drung mtsho zhes bya ba
NK023('a)001:2975: / chos mdzad yongs kyi dgon gnas d+ha na ko sha'i gling phug rin chen g.yu ldings tshal du /
NK023('a)001:2976: rab tu byung nas chos la byon pas lam du gser bya gshog pa g.yu la byas pa /
NK023('a)001:2977: mchu sder lcags la byas pa /
NK023('a)001:2978: lus po byin po gser la byas pa'i bya ngur pa zhig byung nas /
NK023('a)001:2979: srid pa g.yung drung mtsho'i snying khar mchu lan gsum btsugs te /
NK023('a)001:2981: srid pa g.yung drung mtsho khyod la do nub mi
NK023('a)001:2982: ring dkar po zhig byin gyis barloba tu yong gis
NK023('a)001:2983: / de'i ngag ma bcag cig zer nas bya ngur pa de 'phur skad /
NK023('a)001:2984: ngur pa de bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa'o //
NK023('a)001:2985: bu mo de ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro ma dngos yin gsung ngo //
NK023('a)001:2986: de'i nub mo gzims tsa na /
NK023('a)001:2987: mi ring dkar po zhig cis chu bum pa gang la byin rlabs byas nas /
NK023('a)001:2988: g.yung drung mtsho'i spyi bo na mar blugs pa rmi skad /
NK023('a)001:2989: mi de ni bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' dngos yin gsung skad /
NK023('a)001:2990: nang par sgo rtsar phyin tsa na sgo 'dan gyi
NK023('a)001:2991: kha na 'dug pa de dpung pa ru chags nas
NK023('a)001:2992: 'di skad do // srid pa g.yung drung mtsho khyod
NK023('a)001:2993: lo'i dus zla ba'i dus nang du khye'u ngo mtshar
NK023('a)001:2995: de la rtsa gci legs par gyis shig zer skad /
NK023('a)001:2996: de nas g.yung drung mtsho lus ji mi bde ba la sogs pa las /
NK023('a)001:2997: zla ba dgu ngo bcu na bu zhig skyes pa de /
NK023('a)001:2998: thugs kha rtsibs ma'i go bar mchan khung g.yas nas
NK023('a)001:2999: gser gyi rdo rje zhig rang 'khrungs su byon pa
NK023('a)001:3000: dang // yum la rma med par ltam ste /
NK023('a)001:3001: de nyid la ltas pa tsam gyis gser gyi rdo rje rang zhig pa'i nang nas /
NK023('a)001:3002: khye'u mtshan dpe dang ldan pa /
NK023('a)001:3003: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che //
NK023('a)001:3004: zhal thon du mdzad cing bzhad pa zhig byung ba
NK023('a)001:3005: dang yum gyis khong rang gi yab la sngar gyi
NK023('a)001:3008: 'di ni sprul pa'i sku dngos su byon pa yin gsung nas shin tu mnyes te /
NK023('a)001:3009: mtshan yang sprul sku dga' rab rdo rjer mnga' gsol /
NK023('a)001:3010: kha cig tu badz+ra ha sa rdo rje bzhad pa zhes kyang zer ba de dkrun pa dang /
NK023('a)001:3011: ma na re g.yog mo la nga btsun ma zhig
NK023('a)001:3012: la pha med pa'i bu 'di 'dra ba skyug bro
NK023('a)001:3013: thal khung du skyur la shog gsung nas /
NK023('a)001:3014: g.yog mo dge ldan ma bya ba des thal khung du bskyur /
NK023('a)001:3015: der zhag drug lon pa dang /
NK023('a)001:3016: ma na re sha la chad pa'i bu tsha yang yin /
NK023('a)001:3017: snying rje bar du 'dug gis ma shi bar 'dug na long la shog gsung nas /
NK023('a)001:3018: g.yog mos phyin pas thal khung na 'phra shags ling
NK023('a)001:3019: ling 'dug nas blangs te mtshan yang ro langs thal
NK023('a)001:3021: snang srid bde ba la bkod pas ro langs bde ba bya bar yang grags pa des /
NK023('a)001:3022: rgyal po d+ha hi na zhes bya ba'i bu mo
NK023('a)001:3023: rin chen gsal sgron zhes bya ba grogs su khrid
NK023('a)001:3024: nas / dang po zla kham 'od 'phro seng ge nags stengs kyi tshal du /
NK023('a)001:3025: slob dpon chen po gying ka ra la /
NK023('a)001:3026: rtsal chen gyi dbang zhes bya ste /
NK023('a)001:3027: pha rol du phyin pa mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang nos so //
NK023('a)001:3028: de nas pad+ma me tog ljon shing gi tshal du
NK023('a)001:3029: slob dpon chen po klu grub tsan ti ka la
NK023('a)001:3030: / gtan tshigs sgro gleng gi dbang zhes bya ste /
NK023('a)001:3031: kri ya'i dbang mchog nyi shu rtsa drug nos /
NK023('a)001:3032: de nas lha bya skad snyan ljon shing gi tshal du /
NK023('a)001:3033: slob dpon chen po pad+ma ku ma ti la yo
NK023('a)001:3034: ga bkra shis drug cu rtsa bzhi pa'i dbang nos
NK023('a)001:3035: / de ltar phyi dbang brgya rtsa brgyad nos so //
NK023('a)001:3036: de nas slob dpon chen po rab tu gsal ba la /
NK023('a)001:3037: gdan bzhi ni zhabs drung na 'khrigs /
NK023('a)001:3038: phyogs bzhi nas brgyan rin po che rnams ni 'bar /
NK023('a)001:3039: mi nor sna dgu ni sa gzhi la dod /
NK023('a)001:3040: sdug mdzes kyi me tog sna tshogs ni sa gzhi la 'khrungs /
NK023('a)001:3041: mdzes pa'i dar bkra ni dpag bsam gyi shing las byung /
NK023('a)001:3042: 'bru sna dgu ni ljon shing gi yal ga la ltung /
NK023('a)001:3043: de ltar 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i rgyud ma spangs
NK023('a)001:3044: pa'i phun sum tshogs pas mnyes par byas pa dang
NK023('a)001:3045: / slob dpon gyi rgyud chen po gcig la /
NK023('a)001:3046: sku yi rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor //
NK023('a)001:3047: gsung gi rgyud zla gsang thig le //
NK023('a)001:3048: thugs kyi rgyud gsang ba 'dus pa //
NK023('a)001:3049: yon tan gyi rgyud dpal mchog dang po /
NK023('a)001:3050: phrin las kyi rgyud karma ma le /
NK023('a)001:3051: kri ya thams cad kyi rgyal po cha gsum /
NK023('a)001:3052: mtshams thams cad kyi rgyal po srung ba'i 'khor lo /
NK023('a)001:3053: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi rgyal po yang dag dgu pa /
NK023('a)001:3054: rdzas thams cad kyi rgyal po lha mo gnas dkar /
NK023('a)001:3055: ma tang gzhom gshin rje gsal zhing /
NK023('a)001:3056: sman thams cad kyi rgyal po bdud rtsi bum lung /
NK023('a)001:3057: zhi ba thams cad kyi rgyal po rin chen d+r+wab /
NK023('a)001:3058: khro bo thams cad kyi rgyal po bskyed rdzogs chen po /
NK023('a)001:3059: sgom pa thams cad kyi rgyal po ya mtshan mi g.yo ba /
NK023('a)001:3060: dbang thams cad kyi rgyal po nor bu phreng ba /
NK023('a)001:3061: gzhan yang 'jug don bshags pa dang snying po dang
NK023('a)001:3062: dkyil 'khor bkod pa la sogs pa tan tra dang
NK023('a)001:3063: bstan chos thams cad kyi bka' babs so //
NK023('a)001:3064: de nas byu ru dmar po chu mig dgu sgril gyi tshal du /
NK023('a)001:3065: ro langs bde ba dang rin chen gsal sgron la dbang bzhi rdzogs par bskur te /
NK023('a)001:3066: phyi yo byad zang zing rdzas kyi dbang rdzogs par bskur /
