NK023('a)001:3067: nang rig pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang dang /
NK023('a)001:3069: gsang ba byang sems chos nyid thugs kyi dbang bzhi bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:3070: de nas rtogs tshogs lha'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur nas /
NK023('a)001:3071: shel gyi chag shing rin po che sna lngas brgyan pa zhig dbang rtags su byin no //
NK023('a)001:3072: grogs mo la 'phrul gyis snang srid me long la
NK023('a)001:3073: 'dzam bu gling dus cig tu gsal ba zhig dbang
NK023('a)001:3075: de nas rin chen g.yu lding tshal du log nas /
NK023('a)001:3076: rgya gar yul gyi pha rol o rgyan yul gyi tshu rol /
NK023('a)001:3077: ma ra ti ka'i brag phug tu /
NK023('a)001:3078: o rgyan gyi rgyal po d+harma ya dang /
NK023('a)001:3079: klu'i bu mo rgya mtsho gnyis kyis /
NK023('a)001:3080: o rgyan gyi yul nas slob ma bsdus nas tshogs
NK023('a)001:3081: bsgrubs pas mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa 'ba'
NK023('a)001:3082: zhig byung ngo // des za hor gyi rgyal pos bstan nas dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3083: des sing nga'i rgyal po la /
NK023('a)001:3084: des dge slong pakyo d+he ba la /
NK023('a)001:3085: des slob dpon chen po drag po rtsal zhes bya ste sgeg pa rdo rje la bstan /
NK023('a)001:3086: des chos blon d+he ba la /
NK023('a)001:3087: des mkhan po chos rgyal skyong la /
NK023('a)001:3088: de dag ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang mi gnyis zhing /
NK023('a)001:3089: ye shes lhas mngon sum du dbang bskur ba /
NK023('a)001:3090: sangs rgyas la bka' mchid mi bzhin du mol zhing /
NK023('a)001:3091: da ltar yang rig 'dzin gyi gral na bzhugs pa yin no //
NK023('a)001:3092: des slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la bstan te /
NK023('a)001:3093: slob dpon des rgya gar du lan lnga byon nas /
NK023('a)001:3094: grub thob mang po dang mjal zhing /
NK023('a)001:3095: grub thob mang po'i ro myangs /
NK023('a)001:3096: mkhas pa mang po'i bcud phyin /
NK023('a)001:3097: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub brnyes //
NK023('a)001:3098: khro bo stobs po che yis dngos su dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3099: stobs po che'i phyag gi rdo rje de /
NK023('a)001:3100: nam mkha'i mthongs nas rang babs nas //
NK023('a)001:3101: nga'i lag pa g.yas su byung /
NK023('a)001:3102: dga' zhing spro nas lan gsum gsor //
NK023('a)001:3104: gzhan yang dri za phru gu bzung //
NK023('a)001:3105: klu yi rgyal pos chos ston drangs //
NK023('a)001:3106: gsang ba'i bdag po lag na rdo rje gtso 'khor dgu'i zhal gzigs /
NK023('a)001:3107: gzhan yang grub pa mang po brnyes shing /
NK023('a)001:3108: lha srin sde brgyad la dbang thob //
NK023('a)001:3109: da lta yang rdo rje 'chang gi gral na bzhugs pa lags skad /
NK023('a)001:3110: a mes sangs rgyas kyi thugs kyi sras mtsho bzhi bya bar grags pa las /
NK023('a)001:3111: khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho la dbang gi gdams ngag gi bka' babs /
NK023('a)001:3112: bla ma de yang sprul pa mang po'i zhal gzigs /
NK023('a)001:3113: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub khyad par can rnyed /
NK023('a)001:3114: snang srid kyi lha 'dre thams cad bka' nyan /
NK023('a)001:3115: zag med bde ba'i nyams dang ldan pa lags skad /
NK023('a)001:3116: pa kor slob dpon chen po 'phags gsal la dbang bskur zhing bshad /
NK023('a)001:3117: de la gzhung gi bka' babs /
NK023('a)001:3118: so ye shes dbang phyug la lta ba'i bka' babs /
NK023('a)001:3119: sru legs pa'i sgron ma la dbang bzhi chu bo'i bka' babs /
NK023('a)001:3120: des bod ye shes byang chub dang /
NK023('a)001:3121: g.yar gsal ba'i byang chub dang /
NK023('a)001:3122: rgya blo gros gzhon nu dang /
NK023('a)001:3124: zhu bsod nams sh+aakya la sogs dge mched mi lnga'am /
NK023('a)001:3125: dge mched mi bco lnga la 'dus pa chen po'i
NK023('a)001:3126: dbang bskur nas thams cad smin pa dang grol bas
NK023('a)001:3127: lam la bkod / phrin las kyi bdag por mnga' gsol lo //
NK023('a)001:3129: lha rje chen po zur sh+aakya 'byung gnas la dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3130: lha rje chen po de yang /
NK023('a)001:3131: sangs rgyas rnams kyis bstan pa'i bdag por lung bstan /
NK023('a)001:3133: bka' phyi nang gi chos la mnga' brnyes pa lags skad /
NK023('a)001:3134: des lha rje zur chung shes rab grags pa la dbang bskur ba yin /
NK023('a)001:3135: de yang lta dgongs kyi rtse mor gyur cing /
NK023('a)001:3136: shes bya'i gnas la thogs pa med par spyod pa zhig lags skad /
NK023('a)001:3137: des glan sh+aakya byang chub gsang sngags kyi bdag po la gnang /
NK023('a)001:3138: des zur sh+aakya seng ge gsang bdag phyag rdor la gnang /
NK023('a)001:3140: yang zur chung gis lha rje glan sh+aakya bzang po gnyis la gnang /
NK023('a)001:3141: de yang snang grags kyi chos la byan tshud cing snang ba sgyu mar mkhyen pas /
NK023('a)001:3142: phrin las la thogs pa med pa mnga' ba zhig lags par gda' /
NK023('a)001:3143: de yis lha rje 'gar ston zung po la gnang /
NK023('a)001:3144: de yang ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro mas dngos su
NK023('a)001:3145: dbang bskur byin gyis rlabs shing zag med kyi nyams
NK023('a)001:3147: des bla ma rdo rje rgyal mtshan la gnang /
NK023('a)001:3148: de la dbang gi chu bo bzhi char gyi bka' 'dus /
NK023('a)001:3149: yon tan chen po du ma mnga' //
NK023('a)001:3150: khyad par du dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po mdzad nas phyag bzhes thams cad phul du gyur pa mkhyen /
NK023('a)001:3151: thugs rje'i spyan mngon shes thogs pa med pa mnga' ba lags par gda' /
NK023('a)001:3152: des bla ma chen po lha rje glan rdo rje 'od nya tshal ba chen po la gnang /
NK023('a)001:3153: de yang rig pa'i gnas gang la yang thogs pa med cing /
NK023('a)001:3154: chos kyi spyan mig mnga' ba lhag pa'i lha gsang ba'i bdag po'i zhal gzigs shing dbang bskur ba /
NK023('a)001:3155: rab tu byung ba thar pa'i rgyal mtshan can gsung
NK023('a)001:3156: phu sne'u thog gi mkhan po mdzad par zhu phul
NK023('a)001:3157: ba'i dus su / sngags kyi don che bar dgongs
NK023('a)001:3158: nas sprul pa'i sku khyim pa'i tshul gyis 'gro ba
NK023('a)001:3159: rnams thar pa'i lam la bkod pa /
NK023('a)001:3160: mkhan btsun mang po'i gtugs sa lags par gda' /
NK023('a)001:3161: des bla ma chen po glan bsod rgyal la'o //
NK023('a)001:3162: des rig pa 'dzin pa chos kyi sdong po la gnang /
NK023('a)001:3163: de yang phrin las la thogs pa med pa snang grags thams cad sgyu mar mkhyen pas /
NK023('a)001:3164: dregs pa can bdud kyis bar mi chod cing mngon
NK023('a)001:3165: par shes pa lnga dang ldan pa lags par gda'
NK023('a)001:3166: zhing / des bla ma chen po glan bsod nams
NK023('a)001:3167: rgyal po la yang gdams pa la sogs pa mang
NK023('a)001:3168: zhing / du phul nas / khong gi zhabs spyi
NK023('a)001:3169: bos len cing dam tshig rin po che la gces
NK023('a)001:3170: zhing / du phul nas / spras mdzad pa /
NK023('a)001:3171: bla ma dam pa rnams sangs rgyas rnams dang mi
NK023('a)001:3172: gnyis par khur ba lags gda' /
NK023('a)001:3173: de ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas da
NK023('a)001:3174: ltar gyi bla ma chen po chos kyi spyan mig
NK023('a)001:3175: can / yar 'khums su tha mal gyi sel med par /
NK023('a)001:3176: grub thob kyi bka' srol chen po gangs kyi thigs
NK023('a)001:3177: pa lta bur zang za ra tshags su brgyud pa'i
NK023('a)001:3178: brgyud khungs dang gtad rgya'i man ngag ste /
NK023('a)001:3179: tha ma la dgos pa'i lag cha zhes bya ba'i mdo'i la gces pa'i cha zhig lags so //
NK023('a)001:3180: lha rje glan chen po'i zhal nas 'khrungs pa /
NK023('a)001:3185: bla ma chen po bsod rgyal des khong rang gi
NK023('a)001:3186: yab kyis sna drangs pa'i mkhas btsun thams cad la
NK023('a)001:3187: thug / bka' dang rgyu 'bras kyi chos mtha' dag la mkhas shing /
NK023('a)001:3188: skye ba med pa la shes pa'i rgyud sbyangs pa /
NK023('a)001:3189: yi dam gyi lhas dngos su dbang bskur nas dbang gi chu bo rdzogs pa /
NK023('a)001:3190: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis lung bstan pa /
NK023('a)001:3191: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa thugs su chud pa /
NK023('a)001:3192: phrin las ji ltar spyod kyang bar chod kyis mi
NK023('a)001:3193: tshugs shing mkhas btsun mang po'i 'du sar gyur par
NK023('a)001:3194: gda' / des dpal ldan chos kyi seng ge la /
NK023('a)001:3195: de'ang mkhas pa phul du gyur cing rtogs pa'i gdengs dang ldan /
NK023('a)001:3196: ting nge 'dzin gyi drod dang ldan pa dge bshes
NK023('a)001:3197: sngags pa kun gyis bkur ba'i 'os su gyur pa
NK023('a)001:3198: lags par gda' / des glan sangs rgyas dpal la gnang /
NK023('a)001:3199: de'ang dam pa'i mdzod lta sgom dam tshig gsum 'dzin cing /
NK023('a)001:3200: dbang gi chu bo rdzogs pa bla ma'i phyag bzhes mang po mkhyen /
NK023('a)001:3206: thams cad gsal bar mnga' ba lags par gda' /
NK023('a)001:3207: des bla ma glan bsod nams mgon po gnang /
NK023('a)001:3208: de yang bskyed rdzogs gsum gyis mnga' bdag tu gyur cing shes bya thogs med du mkhyen /
NK023('a)001:3209: o rgyan pad+mas lung bstan pa bzhin /
NK023('a)001:3210: bsam yas pe dkar gling nas zab chos shog ril bco lnga phyung /
NK023('a)001:3211: bla ma sman lungs dbus pa la phul /
NK023('a)001:3212: snyigs ma'i dus su yang mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan 'gro don mdzad pa zhig lags /
NK023('a)001:3216: des glan bsod nams mgon la gdams pa gtad rgya dang bcas pa gnang ngo //
NK023('a)001:3217: des bla ma bzhi la gnang ste /
NK023('a)001:3218: bla ma rin po che 'brog ston bsam grub rdo
NK023('a)001:3219: rje sngags gsar rnying bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi grub pa
NK023('a)001:3220: thob / rig pa'i gnas lnga mkhyen pa dang gcig /
NK023('a)001:3221: bla ma myang ston dpal ldan rdo rje rgyud lung rnams kyi phyag bzhes dang /
NK023('a)001:3222: gshin rje thugs bsgrub phyag rdor mdo lugs /
NK023('a)001:3223: rnam 'joms dkar po la grub pa thob pa dang gnyis /
NK023('a)001:3224: bla ma zi ston sh+aakya bzang po mdo yang dag dang /
NK023('a)001:3225: phrin las shar ba la grub pa thob /
NK023('a)001:3226: mgon po stag zhon lha mos las ci bsgo byed par khas blangs pa dang gsum /
NK023('a)001:3227: shangs mad'i bla ma grags she ba mkhas grub mang
NK023('a)001:3228: po la gtugs shing gshin rje gshed a kro nyin
NK023('a)001:3232: lo gsum bcu lhag tu grub pa dang bzhi la /
NK023('a)001:3234: de'i tha mas zur chos kyi seng ge la /
NK023('a)001:3235: gtad rgya dang bcas gnang ba'i tshul ni /
NK023('a)001:3236: jo mo slob dpon sras las /
NK023('a)001:3237: bdag sh+aaka 'byung gis cung tsam rig cing mos pa bgyis /
NK023('a)001:3238: kha cig 'di la ci rigs gsung yang ste dag snang sbyangs pas rig go //
NK023('a)001:3239: bka' dbang bskur zhus pa mi bdog /
NK023('a)001:3240: gnyis pa shangs gur phyogs bla ma dpal ldan pa sbres pas sngags spyi la mkhas par gda' bas /
NK023('a)001:3241: bdag sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyis mdo yi dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3242: glan gyi phur pa man ngag drug pa dang bcas
NK023('a)001:3243: pa dbang bsgrub brgya go gnyis zhal phye nas thob
NK023('a)001:3244: / mdo'i gtad rgya ni ma gson gda' lags /
NK023('a)001:3245: dang po rta nag mda' sa bla ma bsam 'grub pas /
NK023('a)001:3248: na rag dong sprugs dbang bsgrub /
NK023('a)001:3249: yang dag gzhan don dang me zhig ma rnams gsan gda' bas zhus nas thob /
NK023('a)001:3250: gtad rgya gsan pa ma grub gda' bas /
NK023('a)001:3251: glan bla ma bsod nams mgon pa'i phyi tshar gyi slob ma gsum pa /
NK023('a)001:3252: bla ma gyong khang sh+aakya bzang po des mdo dbang mdzad pa ni med na'ang /
NK023('a)001:3253: bla ma bsam grub rdo rje ba la mdo yongs
NK023('a)001:3254: rdzogs kyi phyag bzhes bstan cing bka' thob tsam dang
NK023('a)001:3255: / mdo yongs rdzogs kyi gtad rgya gtad cing gnang bas /
NK023('a)001:3256: bka' drin che go gyong khang pa min na ni bka' 'chad pa 'dug /
NK023('a)001:3257: da sngags rnying ma'i bstan pa 'di /
NK023('a)001:3258: nga rgad po ci la la thugs kyang dar rgyas su byed gsung nas mdzad do //
NK023('a)001:3263: chos skyong mkha' 'gro zhal gzigs dang grub rtags ni du ma bdog go //
NK023('a)001:3265: bdag zur ha sh+aakya 'byung gnas dang /
NK023('a)001:3266: sring cig zur mo dge 'dun 'bum la gtad rgya dang bcas gnang ngo //
NK023('a)001:3267: bdag snyon pa'i col dang rmi nyams la /
NK023('a)001:3268: ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa
NK023('a)001:3269: ni ba glang spyod kyi gling na khri rtsig pa'i
NK023('a)001:3271: badz+ra he ru mdzod thod bsnams pa 'jigs pa zhig snang /
NK023('a)001:3274: pad+ma he ru bkrag mdangs gsal /
NK023('a)001:3275: karma he ru sna tshogs par gda' /
NK023('a)001:3276: zhi dang rig 'dzin mkha' 'gro chos skyong ni /
NK023('a)001:3277: mi dang mi min nam mkha'i lus can gang du'ang rdzu zhing 'phrul ston kyin gda' lags /
NK023('a)001:3278: lha bdud 'dam kha ma nor ba gal che he gsung par gda' /
NK023('a)001:3279: bstan pa'i bdag nyid rin po che ba'i drung nas /
NK023('a)001:3280: bdag rgyal khams pa gnyis la dgos bzhin du gtad rgya dang bcas pa zhig /
NK023('a)001:3281: dbang skyar gnyis te gsum gnang ba //
NK023('a)001:3282: 'dus pa mdo'i gtad rgya'i snyan brgyud kun la med pa'i man ngag khyad par can rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:3286: de nas slob bu rnams langs te /
NK023('a)001:3287: phyag byas thal mo sbyar nas /
NK023('a)001:3290: e ma kye ma ho zhes gdung ba'i skad gdangs phyung la /
NK023('a)001:3292: dkyil 'khor dang bsgrub rdzas dpon slob rnams gcig la gcig tu lta zhing /
NK023('a)001:3293: gcig sems gcig la zhugs pas 'bral mi phod par /
NK023('a)001:3294: gcig la gcig gdung ba'i stobs kyis phan na lus kyi sha dang /
NK023('a)001:3295: stobs kyi srog kyang gtong phod la sa gzhan gol sa na gnas kyang /
NK023('a)001:3296: dkyil 'khor dang mched grogs 'dzab 'dren par bdag med sems nyid snang la /
NK023('a)001:3297: 'di phyi bar dor 'bral mi phod zhing so sor 'phen pa'i stobs kyis bskal nas /
NK023('a)001:3299: so sor lus pa'i skyo bsangs dang /
NK023('a)001:3300: yun du phyis kyang 'grogs pa'i rten 'brel dang //
NK023('a)001:3301: kun la gcig gis phan te sgrub pa'i thabs 'di ni /
NK023('a)001:3303: bar do'i skyel ma bzhin don che bas dgongs 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:3304: sngon rgyal ba rigs lnga'i ngo bo dam pa'i rigs can /
NK023('a)001:3310: ri bo ma la ya'i rtser sangs rgyas bstan pa'i khur bzung /
NK023('a)001:3311: ston pa la mi phyed pa'i dad pa bskyed /
NK023('a)001:3312: chos mched dam sems can rnams la blos ma phod par chos srid gsum kun tu /
NK023('a)001:3314: nag po'i phyogs kun tu snub pa'i slad du gdung tshig nyi shu rtsa gsum smras pa ltar /
NK023('a)001:3316: bla ma brgyud pa'i rnam thar bzang po bskyang 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:3320: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i nga rgyal gyis /
NK023('a)001:3321: theg dgu lus la tshang par bkod /
NK023('a)001:3322: rol mo dang bcas te yig brgya bzlas la /
NK023('a)001:3323: dkyil 'khor sngar bsgrub pa'i zhi dkyil de /
NK023('a)001:3324: stegs sam gdan la bzhag ste /
NK023('a)001:3325: rgyal ba rig 'dzin thams cad dang //
NK023('a)001:3326: srid gsum dbang can thams cad chos //
NK023('a)001:3327: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:3328: rdzogs pa chen po'i gdams ngag bshad //
NK023('a)001:3330: slob bu'i lag tu gtad la mgo bos gtugs /
NK023('a)001:3332: dbang rtags phyag mtshan snying gi thad du reg cing dkyil 'khor dang lhan du bzung /
NK023('a)001:3334: dkyil 'khor dgongs 'dus dbang rtags dang bcas pa la gus pa cher bya /
NK023('a)001:3335: las kyi rdo rje slob dpon nam rgyal theb phyag
NK023('a)001:3336: rdor ram rdor sems su gsal bas bzung ba'ang mdzad
NK023('a)001:3337: kyi bdog / gang ltar kyang brtan zhing grims pas gdan drang po nas bzung la /
NK023('a)001:3338: mchod bstod ci rigs su dbul /
NK023('a)001:3339: glegs bam dbang chen zhes bya ba /
NK023('a)001:3340: theg dgu spyi'i pod lung gnang lung thob pas /
NK023('a)001:3341: rgyal po dza ltar byin rlabs kyi gnad che ba'o //
NK023('a)001:3342: de nas bu rnams blo rgya bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK023('a)001:3343: zhing khams bstan pa sngar ma brjod na 'dir brjod kyang nyan /
NK023('a)001:3344: 'dod pa'i skyon spangs skye la dbang mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:3345: steng phyogs khro chen h'u ka ra //
NK023('a)001:3346: ma byin len spangs yo byad dbang mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:3347: shar phyogs khro chen rnam par rgyal //
NK023('a)001:3348: srog gcod skyon spangs tshe la dbang mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:3349: lho phyogs khro chen gshin rje gshed //
NK023('a)001:3350: phra ma'i skyon spangs chos la dbang mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:3351: nub phyogs khro chen rta mgrin dpal //
NK023('a)001:3352: ngag rtsub skyon spangs las la dbang mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:3353: byang phyogs khro chen bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK023('a)001:3354: log par lta spangs ye shes dbang mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:3355: shar lho khro chen dbyug sngon can //
NK023('a)001:3356: rdzun gyi skyon spangs mos la dbang mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:3357: lho nub khro chen mi g.yo mgon //
NK023('a)001:3358: ngag 'khyal skyon spangs sems la dbang mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:3359: nub byang khro chen 'dod pa'i rgyal //
NK023('a)001:3360: gnod sems skyon spangs rdzu 'phrul dbang mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:3361: byang shar khro chen khams gsum rgyal //
NK023('a)001:3362: rnabs sems skyon spangs smon lam dbang mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:3363: 'og phyogs khro bo stobs po che //
NK023('a)001:3364: zhes rgyu dge ba bcu'i thun mong gi 'bras bu'am /
NK023('a)001:3366: mchog gi lam 'bras khro bo bcu /
NK023('a)001:3367: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing bston pa de bzang ngo //
NK023('a)001:3368: de nas gom pa'i bcu'i 'dug pa dang bcu gsum la /
NK023('a)001:3369: mos spyod tshogs sbyor ba dang po gsum /
NK023('a)001:3370: nyan rang byang sems kyi lam la /
NK023('a)001:3371: bla ma slob dpon mched grogs rdzas dgra gnyen /
NK023('a)001:3373: de nas sgom lam kri yog pa gnyis gsum bzhi
NK023('a)001:3374: lnga drug bdun brgyad dgu rnams ni bla ma slob
NK023('a)001:3375: dpon mched grogs rdzas dgra gnyen longs spyod rdzogs skus
NK023('a)001:3376: khrid / bskyed rdzogs gsum gyis mthar lam tshom bu'i sa bcu nas /
NK023('a)001:3377: bla ma slob dpon mched grogs rdzas dgra gnyen chos sku dbyer med rdo rje /
NK023('a)001:3378: mngon par byang chub skus khrid /
NK023('a)001:3379: bcu gsum pa la gtad rgya ni bla ma kun tu bzang pos khrid par mos pas /
NK023('a)001:3381: sbyin pa rin chen 'byung ba'i rigs //
NK023('a)001:3382: nga ni thabs kyi mnyan pa mkhan //
NK023('a)001:3383: bdag gzhan snang sems ma 'dres te ser sna //
NK023('a)001:3384: 'khor ba'i chu bo mtha' med las //
NK023('a)001:3385: srid gsum bsgral bar dam bcas kyis //
NK023('a)001:3387: tha ma lan gsum brjod nas gdan gril gong du spo //
NK023('a)001:3388: nga ni thabs kyi mig mkhan te //
NK023('a)001:3389: 'jig rten long ba dpag med rnams //
NK023('a)001:3390: ling tog gsal bar dam bcas kyis //
NK023('a)001:3392: nga ni thabs kyi sman pa ste //
NK023('a)001:3393: grong khyer gsum gyi nad pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:3394: cong rnying sbyong bar dam bcas kyis //
NK023('a)001:3396: nga ni thabs kyi sa mkhan te //
NK023('a)001:3397: 'gro ba lam log lam stor rnams //
NK023('a)001:3398: ma nor 'khrid par dam bcas kyis //
NK023('a)001:3400: nga ni thugs rje'i spyan ras mkhan //
NK023('a)001:3402: thams cad skyabs par dam bcas kyis //
NK023('a)001:3404: nga ni rdo rje rdzogs chen te //
NK023('a)001:3405: 'khor ba'i g.yul chen dmag dpung las //
NK023('a)001:3408: nga ni thabs kyi tshong dpon te //
NK023('a)001:3409: 'dod pa rgya mtshos mi ngoms rnams //
NK023('a)001:3410: gter chen sbyin par dam bcas kyis //
NK023('a)001:3412: nga ni thabs kyi sgron ma ste //
NK023('a)001:3413: mun nag smag tu 'khyams pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:3414: mun nag bsal bar dam bcas kyis //
NK023('a)001:3416: nga ni yid bzhin nor bu ste //
NK023('a)001:3417: gang dag yid bzhin 'dod pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:3418: yid bzhin bskang bar dam bcas kyis //
NK023('a)001:3420: nga ni bka' yis lde mig ste //
NK023('a)001:3421: bka' sgrom tha ram gsang ba rnams //
NK023('a)001:3422: rnam par 'byed par dam bcas kyis //
NK023('a)001:3424: nga ni bka' yig 'grel pa ste //
NK023('a)001:3425: gsung gi glegs bam zab mo rnams //
NK023('a)001:3426: nges par bgrol bar dam bcas kyis //
NK023('a)001:3428: rnam dag lam mchog kun sgrol 'dir //
NK023('a)001:3429: skal ldan gang zhig su zhugs pa //
NK023('a)001:3431: nges par 'char gyis brtson par gyis //
NK023('a)001:3432: de nyid sems kyi me long ste //
NK023('a)001:3433: mngon sum gsal bar rtogs ma thag /
NK023('a)001:3434: 'gro ba'i lus la sangs rgyas yin //
NK023('a)001:3435: rdo rje gsang chen gsang ba'i mdzod mchog rnams //
NK023('a)001:3436: 'dir bsgros gsal bar bshad sbyar bas //
NK023('a)001:3437: lha dang mi yi rig 'dzin las //
NK023('a)001:3438: rim par brgyud de grags par 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:3439: lha mi'i 'jig rten thams cad kyi //
NK023('a)001:3440: mun pa'i gdung ba kun bsal nas //
NK023('a)001:3442: da ni bla ma dang dkyil 'khor la 'bral mi phod pa'i dad pa bskyed /
NK023('a)001:3443: stor ba rnyed pa lta bu'i dga' ba yang bya /
NK023('a)001:3444: rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gyi bdag por gyur to zhes spro ba bskyed /
NK023('a)001:3445: lag gi rten yang stegs bu la gus pas sgrims la bzhag /
NK023('a)001:3446: dpon mched kun la brtse ba dang gdung sems phyung la thugs spyod gcig pas /
NK023('a)001:3447: mya ngan las mi 'da' chos kyi 'khor lo rab
NK023('a)001:3448: tu rgyas pa bskor zhing yun du bzhugs pa'i sku
NK023('a)001:3449: tshe phrin las byin gyis rlobs par gsol ba drag
NK023('a)001:3450: tu btab la / phata ces brjod la bu rnams
NK023('a)001:3451: bla ma'i gdan khri la mgo btud de 'dug go
NK023('a)001:3452: tu btab la / // de nas bla mas 'di skad du /
NK023('a)001:3453: ci phyir gdung ba'i mun par zhugs //
NK023('a)001:3454: thub pa mya ngan 'das gsungs pa //
NK023('a)001:3455: de ni nam mkha'i sku mnga' ba //
NK023('a)001:3458: de skad sprul pa'i sgra byung bas //
NK023('a)001:3459: sngon du byung ba'i rigs can rnams //
NK023('a)001:3460: lus brgyud shin tu gus sbyar nas //
NK023('a)001:3464: bstod pa 'di yi rjes bzlos bya'o //
NK023('a)001:3465: mtshan mo mun nag sprin rum nas //
NK023('a)001:3466: glog 'gyus bar snang ston lta bur //
NK023('a)001:3467: thog ma tha ma med pa yi //
NK023('a)001:3468: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK023('a)001:3469: rnam dag lam chen 'di nyid du //
NK023('a)001:3470: byung ba'i skyes bu don grub khyod //
NK023('a)001:3471: dam pa rnams kyi gsang 'dzin cing //
NK023('a)001:3472: gsang ba pa yi bdag por grags //
NK023('a)001:3474: bu rnams phyag byas la mnga' gsol ba'i phyir 'khod de /
NK023('a)001:3475: bstan pa 'dzin pa'i slob dpon dang /
NK023('a)001:3476: rgyal theb skyong ba'i rgyal po dang //
NK023('a)001:3477: rgyal mo srung ba'i rig 'dzin dang //
NK023('a)001:3478: gtso mo rnams rgyal ba lnga ltar gdan khri dang bcas pa la rdo rje dril bu gtad /
NK023('a)001:3479: de'i las kyi rdo rje'i mngag gzhug dang /
NK023('a)001:3480: 'tsho ba sbyor ba'i blon po rnams ni sems dpa' dang khro bo ltar /
NK023('a)001:3481: gdan dang stegs la 'chad mkhan la 'khor lo dang 'chad shing gtad /
NK023('a)001:3482: las mkhan la rgya gram dang /
NK023('a)001:3483: rnga dang ral gri mda' dar sman rag gtor ma la sogs gtad /
NK023('a)001:3484: phal pa sgom pa dang nyan pa dag la /
NK023('a)001:3485: 'gro ba drug gi thub pa ltar pad gdan gting ba la /
NK023('a)001:3487: nyan pa'i po ti gtad do //
NK023('a)001:3488: kun kyang rang rang gi dbu rgyan dbang rtags cod pan rnams dang bcas pa /
NK023('a)001:3489: dkyil 'khor gyi lha chas pa ltar brgyan mngar la brjid cing sgyings pas gnas pa dang /
NK023('a)001:3491: tshe rdzas dang bkra shis kyi rdzas dang byin can gyi rdzas gsar la bkram /
NK023('a)001:3493: mtshams bcad bkra shis gsol te /
NK023('a)001:3494: +aahmh'u s+w+aa h+aa zhes bgegs gtor btang /
NK023('a)001:3495: h'u bi sha badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la man+dala h'u phata ces bgegs bskrad /
NK023('a)001:3496: h'u zhes khro bcus mtshams bcad la /
NK023('a)001:3497: bla ma re'i bsham la brgyud pa'i mtshams su gsol 'debs mchod pa re bya zhing bstim /
NK023('a)001:3498: smon lam yig brgya re brjod /
NK023('a)001:3499: chos sku kun bzang longs sku rigs lnga dang //
NK023('a)001:3500: sprul sku rigs gsum yang sprul dga' rab sogs //
NK023('a)001:3501: ye shes sku mchog rgyal ba dgongs pas brgyud //
NK023('a)001:3502: rgyal ba dgongs pa brgyud pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:3503: grags ldan chos skyong klu rgyal 'jog po dang //
NK023('a)001:3504: gnod sbyin srin po li tsa dri med sogs //
NK023('a)001:3505: thugs rjes gdung 'tshob rig 'dzin rig pas brgyud //
NK023('a)001:3506: rig 'dzin rig pas brgyud pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:3507: rgya gar mkhas grub pan chen brgyud pa dang //
NK023('a)001:3508: bstan pa'i srog shing bod kyi brgyud pa sogs //
NK023('a)001:3509: dpang gyur rdo rje gang zag snyan khung brgyud //
NK023('a)001:3510: gang zag snyan khung brgyud pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:3511: ces brgyud pa'i bkra shis dang /
NK023('a)001:3512: gzhan yang gang shes kyi bkra shis bya'o //
NK023('a)001:3514: de kho na nyid nges pa'i theg pa chen po 'di /
NK023('a)001:3515: gnas skabs gnyis dang bcur 'byung ste /
NK023('a)001:3516: gang rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba na yang 'byung //
NK023('a)001:3517: gang 'jig rten gyi sgron ma bkod pa na yang 'byung //
NK023('a)001:3518: gang gis nges pa rnyed pa na yang 'byung //
NK023('a)001:3519: snying po byang chub nyid du nges pa na yang 'byung //
NK023('a)001:3520: dgongs pa rnam par 'grel pa na yang 'byung //
NK023('a)001:3521: gdul bya'i skabs la bab pa'i tshe na yang 'byung //
NK023('a)001:3522: byin gyis brlabs kyis snang ba na yang 'byung //
NK023('a)001:3523: brgyud pa thabs kyi grags pa na yang 'byung //
NK023('a)001:3524: gang gi ched du mdzad pa na yang 'byung //
NK023('a)001:3525: lung chen nges par bstan pa na yang byung //
NK023('a)001:3526: las brgyud yongs su gcod pa na yang byung //
NK023('a)001:3527: dgongs pa rnam par grol ba na yang byung //
NK023('a)001:3528: de dag ni thams cad kyi thams cad nas thams cad du /
NK023('a)001:3529: kun tu yongs su rnam par snang ngo //
NK023('a)001:3532: zhes bka' stsal pas dri ba dang po'i rtog pa
NK023('a)001:3533: yongs su chad pa de bzhin du bkra shis par
NK023('a)001:3536: bkra shis dang tshe rdzas rol /
NK023('a)001:3539: rgyas pa gtad rgya mdzad pa'i gsang mtshan ma bgrangs /
NK023('a)001:3540: bla ma la phyag phul te bka' drin che'o brjod /
NK023('a)001:3541: yon dbul ba sangs rgyas su bsngo //
NK023('a)001:3542: kun tu sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams 'dzin skyong srung ba la 'bad /
NK023('a)001:3545: 'dus pa mdo'i gtad rgya'i phyag len 'di ni phyag
NK023('a)001:3546: len rgyas pa klags chog ma bya ba lags so
NK023('a)001:3547: // bla ma'i bka' rdzogs pa'i rgya /
NK023('a)001:3549: bstan pa dgongs 'dus kyi 'khor dam pa'i rigs can bzhi drang ba'i rgya /
NK023('a)001:3550: bsgrub rdzas zhi dkyil me tog yul lugs kyi bca' thang dbul ba'i rgya /
NK023('a)001:3551: bka'i gnyer gtad mnga' gsol ba'i rgya dang bzhi /
NK023('a)001:3552: zhu ba po rang gis zhi ba'i gzhung mchod tshogs dbul ba'i rgya dang lnga mchis pas /
NK023('a)001:3553: gtad rgya lnga'i go don gyi brjed byang 'grel pa
NK023('a)001:3554: 'di ni bla ma sangs rgyas rin po che'i drung
NK023('a)001:3555: du / lan mang du thob bka' yis gnang ba'i gsung bzhin /
NK023('a)001:3556: zur h+aa sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyis bkod pa kun phan dge rgyas byung legs don mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:3560: // // mdo dbang gi gtad rgya gsang mtshan ma bzhugs so //
NK023('a)001:3561: na mo rat+na gu ru h'u /
NK023('a)001:3563: bka' rdzogs pa chen po byang chub kyi sems /
NK023('a)001:3564: ye nas kun tu bzang pos byin gyis brlabs pa /
NK023('a)001:3565: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang la /
NK023('a)001:3566: dang po ston pa kun tu bzang pos /
NK023('a)001:3567: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la byin /
NK023('a)001:3568: rdo rje sems dpas 'phags pa 'jam dpal la byin /
NK023('a)001:3569: 'jam dpal gyis tshig dang yi ger bsdebs nas rig 'dzin gyi slob dpon rnams la brgyud pa'o //
NK023('a)001:3570: de yang gnas chos kyi dbyings su ston pa kun tu bzang pos /
NK023('a)001:3571: longs sku rdo rje sems dpa' la byin gyis brlabs kyis bshad /
NK023('a)001:3572: yon du rig pa'i me tog phul lo //
NK023('a)001:3573: rdo rje sems dpa' 'og min gyi gnas su /
NK023('a)001:3574: sprul pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rje la rang gi ngo bos bshad /
NK023('a)001:3575: yon du 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga phul /
NK023('a)001:3576: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal //
NK023('a)001:3577: de yan chad rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa'o //
NK023('a)001:3578: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje o rgyan gyi rin chen g.yu stengs su /
NK023('a)001:3579: de 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la tshig sdebs sbyor legs pas bshad cing dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3580: yon du rang gi mgo dang snying phul /
NK023('a)001:3581: gsang mtshan gzhon nu rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:3582: des rgyal po d+ha na ta lo la /
NK023('a)001:3583: yul d+ha he na'i tshal bdag gi nags su dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3584: yon du rgyal srid rin po che sna bdun phul /
NK023('a)001:3585: gsang mtshan rdo rje dga' byed rtsal //
NK023('a)001:3586: dgung lo stong chig brgya bzhes so //
NK023('a)001:3587: des sras thu bo ra tsa hasti la dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3588: yul tsan tan gyi nags su yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che phul /
NK023('a)001:3590: dgung lo brgyad ba rgya bzhes /
NK023('a)001:3591: de'i zhor la shin tu brtan pa la bshad do //
NK023('a)001:3592: des sras mo pa ra ni la yul a nu
NK023('a)001:3593: rta'i tshal du lus kyi rgyan rnams phul nas zhus
NK023('a)001:3596: zhor la rgyal po gser mkhar can la gnang ngo //
NK023('a)001:3597: des klu'i rgyal po 'jog po la /
NK023('a)001:3599: yon du gtsug gi nor bu phul /
NK023('a)001:3602: zhor la klu mo yak+sha kha 'dul la bshad do //
NK023('a)001:3603: des gnod sbyin mo byang chub la /
NK023('a)001:3604: d+ha he na'i rtsar bu dang rgyal srid phul /
NK023('a)001:3607: zhor la bram ze mo blo gros la bshad do //
NK023('a)001:3608: des smad 'tshong ma a ra li la /
NK023('a)001:3609: yul d+ha na ko sha'i shar phug tu dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3613: zhor la rgyal po glog gi 'od la byin no //
NK023('a)001:3614: des khyi'i mkhan po ku ku ra tsa la /
NK023('a)001:3615: yul d+ha he na'i 'du khang du dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3616: gser gyi dril bu g.yer kha stong phul /
NK023('a)001:3619: zhor la rgyal po dza la bshad do //
NK023('a)001:3620: des smad 'tshong ma b+hud+ha sa ma ya la /
NK023('a)001:3621: d+ha he na'i gling phug tu rin po che sna lnga phul /
NK023('a)001:3624: zhor la bram ze mo nyi ma la bshad do //
NK023('a)001:3625: des smad 'tshong ma b+hud+d+ha sa ma ti la /
NK023('a)001:3626: yul u ta'i tshal du rta dang glang po bdun phul /
NK023('a)001:3629: des o rgyan gyi mkhan po ma h+aa ra tsa
NK023('a)001:3630: la o rgyan gyi rin chen g.yu ldings tshal du
NK023('a)001:3634: zhor la rgyal po thor cog can la byin no //
NK023('a)001:3635: des sras mo go ma de byi la /
NK023('a)001:3636: yul pad+ma'i me tog tshal du /
NK023('a)001:3637: yon rta dang glang po phul /
NK023('a)001:3640: zhor la bram ze mo gsal ba'i brgyan la gnang ngo //
NK023('a)001:3641: des a tsar+ya a lo ke la /
NK023('a)001:3643: yon gser phye phud do phul //
NK023('a)001:3646: zhor la rgyal po su mi ta la bshad do //
NK023('a)001:3647: des mi'i mkhan po ma h+aa ra tsa la /
NK023('a)001:3649: lha'i bdud rtsi 'chi med dang nor bu bsam 'phel phul /
NK023('a)001:3651: zhor la blo gros mtha' yas la bshad do //
NK023('a)001:3652: des drang srong b+ha sha ti la /
NK023('a)001:3653: yul chu bo gang ga'i bye mar gnang /
NK023('a)001:3657: zhor la stobs chen 'bar ba byin /
NK023('a)001:3658: des smad 'tshong ma bdag nyid ma la /
NK023('a)001:3659: shing nal byi'i rtsar rang gi lus dang longs spyod phul /
NK023('a)001:3662: zhor la bram ze mo sman gyi blo gros la bshad do //
NK023('a)001:3663: des ru na ga dz+hu na la /
NK023('a)001:3664: yul d+ha he na'i nyi ma khud du /
NK023('a)001:3668: zhor la rgyal po grub pa'i snying po la bshad do //
NK023('a)001:3669: des d+hu d+he ba ra tsa la lha'i dpag bsam shing gi rtsar /
NK023('a)001:3672: zhor la lha'i dbang po la gnang ngo //
NK023('a)001:3673: de la 'jam dpal bzangs zhes kyang bya /
NK023('a)001:3674: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi ma la /
NK023('a)001:3675: d+ha he na'i g.yu lung du /
NK023('a)001:3676: rta dang glang po che rin po che shar bu phul /
NK023('a)001:3679: zhor la bdud rtsi 'bebs la bshad do //
NK023('a)001:3680: des rig 'dzin chen po dge bsnyen legs la /
NK023('a)001:3684: zhor la d+harma b+ho de la dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:3685: des ru d+harma ra tsa la /
NK023('a)001:3686: rin chen bde ba'i gnas su /
NK023('a)001:3687: rin po che bsil mchog phul /
NK023('a)001:3689: des ru 'a bu ta kug ta la /
NK023('a)001:3690: kug tas khang dgu thog tu /
NK023('a)001:3691: yon bdud rtsi bsil mngar gzhong pa gang phul /
NK023('a)001:3694: zhor la mu la ku dza la byin no //
NK023('a)001:3695: des pan+di ta sh+ri sing ha la /
NK023('a)001:3696: yul d+ha he na'i 'du khang du /
NK023('a)001:3700: des dge slong ma kun dga' ma la /
NK023('a)001:3701: d+ha he na'i kha rag yul du u b+hi'i mkhar dang /
NK023('a)001:3705: des gu ru b+hi ma la la /
NK023('a)001:3706: rnam dag chos kyi sprin du //
NK023('a)001:3707: gser ka zhu tsam zhig phul //
NK023('a)001:3710: rig 'dzin rnams rig pas brgyud pa'o //
NK023('a)001:3711: sh+ri sing has lo ts+aa ba b+he ro tsa na la /
NK023('a)001:3712: d+ha he na'i 'du khang du dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3713: yon gser phye ba min gyi ra do dang /
NK023('a)001:3714: gser gyi pa tra brgyad phul /
NK023('a)001:3715: gsang mtshan rdo rje khyung gshog rtsal //
NK023('a)001:3717: zhor la brtsang legs grub la bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:3718: des rgyal po g.yu sgra snying po la /
NK023('a)001:3719: rgyal mo tsha rong gi brag lha mgon por /
NK023('a)001:3720: yon du rang gi rgyal srid phul //
NK023('a)001:3721: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde 'byams rtsal //
NK023('a)001:3722: zhor la rgyal mo gru la gnang ngo //
NK023('a)001:3723: des gnyags dz+nya na ku ma ra te ye shes gzhon nu la /
NK023('a)001:3724: yul mchims phu brag dkar du /
NK023('a)001:3725: yon du mchims yul brag dgu dago'u ru /
NK023('a)001:3726: phra men gyi yol skyogs gnyis chang gis bkang ba dang /
NK023('a)001:3728: gsang mtshan rdo rje grub pa'i gter //
NK023('a)001:3729: spyi ru 'di la dbang gi chu bo chen po
NK023('a)001:3730: bzhi babs pa lags te gong ma gcig de lags
NK023('a)001:3733: // slob dpon dga' rab nas sh+ri sing ha'i bar kun la'ang gtugs /
NK023('a)001:3734: rtsal dbang thob pa'i slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas rdo rje thod phreng rtsal gyis /
NK023('a)001:3735: khri srong lde'u btsan rje 'bangs nyi shu rtsa lnga la /
NK023('a)001:3736: mchims phu rdza gnyis dge ba'i dben tshar dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3737: de'i nang nas ngan lam rgyal mchog dbyangs kyis lha
NK023('a)001:3738: sa yer par gzi yi slug ma dang 'dod yon
NK023('a)001:3740: gsang mtshan rdo rje grub pa rtsal //
NK023('a)001:3742: slob dpon chen po h'u ka ra la bod kyi
NK023('a)001:3743: dge slong mi lngas gser brag bya skyungs tshal du
NK023('a)001:3744: dbang nos so // de'i nang nas gnubs nam mkha'
NK023('a)001:3745: snying pos mnyal gyi dge ri brag tu dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:3746: dbang nos so // / rta zeg pa gcig phul /
NK023('a)001:3747: gsang mtshan thig le gshog rgod rtsal //
NK023('a)001:3749: slob dpon b+hi ma la mi tra bod du byon pa'i dus su /
NK023('a)001:3750: yul yar lungs kyi yang thog tu gser gyi thog tu gser gyi bya 'dab tshad ma dang /
NK023('a)001:3751: dngul gyi bya 'dab tshad mas sna drangs nas /
NK023('a)001:3753: gsang mtshan dri med zla shar rtsal /
NK023('a)001:3754: de ltar dbang gi chu bo chen po bzhi mnga' ba lags so //
NK023('a)001:3757: ma sum za sgron gyi blo gros //
NK023('a)001:3758: mgrin pa na sme ba'i rdo rje rgya gram yod pa /
NK023('a)001:3761: sgra tshad kun la mkhas pa lags so //
NK023('a)001:3762: des khang sog po dpal gyi ye shes la /
NK023('a)001:3763: yar lungs shel brag tu dbang bskur //
NK023('a)001:3764: yon du bla ma'i sku dgra lan gsum btul /
NK023('a)001:3767: gsang mtshan rdo rje bzhad pa'i gter ram /
NK023('a)001:3768: gsang mtshan rdo rje khyung gshog rtsal //
NK023('a)001:3769: yul yar 'brog rus pa khang pa //
NK023('a)001:3772: mi chos kyi ming ni khang stag zil /
NK023('a)001:3774: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub thob pa lags skad do //
NK023('a)001:3776: gra'i sman sgang du bka' byas so //
NK023('a)001:3779: // // na mo rat+na gu ru h'u /
NK023('a)001:3780: ma h+aa yo ga'i rnal 'byor nang pa thabs kyi rgyud kyi theg pa'i dbang la /
NK023('a)001:3781: chos sku kun tu bzang po rgyal tshab rigs lnga la bshad /
NK023('a)001:3782: des rgyal sras sems dpa' dang sems ma la brgyud cing dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3783: de'i nang nas rdo rje sems dpas rdo rje chos
NK023('a)001:3784: spyan ras gzigs la gsang sngags kyi rgyud kyi rgyal
NK023('a)001:3785: por dbang bskur / rig pa 'dzin pa mi ma yin pa dang /
NK023('a)001:3786: mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis ka la brgyud de /
NK023('a)001:3787: srin po blo gros thabs ldan gyis yi ger bsdus nas /
NK023('a)001:3788: rgyal po dza la ltas snang ba yan chad sgyu 'phrul gyi babs kyi lo rgyus su shes so //
NK023('a)001:3789: de'ang tshe'i gleng gzhi lo rgyus las /
NK023('a)001:3790: lha mo dpal mos lung bstan te //
NK023('a)001:3791: ku ku ra dzas po ti /
NK023('a)001:3792: rgyal po dzas rnyed pa de la mjal nas don rtogs te bsgrub pas rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK023('a)001:3794: ku ku ra dza in tra b+ho d+he dang /
NK023('a)001:3795: sing ha u pa ra dza dang /
NK023('a)001:3797: lam rims su bshad cing dpal mo ni rdo rje sems kyi 'khor yin /
NK023('a)001:3798: a nu ltar du ku ku ra gong du mi bzhed kyang /
NK023('a)001:3801: li ts+aa dri med rnams la tan tra bco brgyad ltar tshom bu la bstan te /
NK023('a)001:3802: dbang bskur bsgrubs pas rdo rje 'chang gi sa thob ces bshad cing /
NK023('a)001:3803: mdo a nu ltar du ku ku dza'i gong du mi bzhed kyang /
NK023('a)001:3804: ma h+aa ltar du ku ku ra dza in tra b+ho d+he dang /
NK023('a)001:3805: sing ha u pa ra dza dang /
NK023('a)001:3807: lam rims su bshad cing dpal mo ni rdo rje sems kyi 'khor yin /
NK023('a)001:3808: de'i dus su khyi'i mkhan po dge slong ku kur dzas /
NK023('a)001:3809: mchod rten rnam dag gi drung du bsgrubs pas rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal mthong /
NK023('a)001:3810: dngos grub thob nas rdo rje sems dpas /
NK023('a)001:3811: rdo rje chos spyan ras gzigs la gsang sngags rgyud kyi rgyal por dbang bskur ba ltar /
NK023('a)001:3812: rdo rje chos kyis ku ku ra dza la dbang
NK023('a)001:3813: bskur bas tan tra sde bco brgyad la dgongs pa
NK023('a)001:3815: de'i yul za hor gyi nye 'khor na yab rgyal po la gzhu thung /
NK023('a)001:3816: yum rgyal mo skra'i la ba can gyi bu sangs
NK023('a)001:3817: rgyas sh+aaka thub kyi dge slong ste thub pa la'ang
NK023('a)001:3818: dbang bzhi thob pa tshe lo stong thub la /
NK023('a)001:3819: byang chub sems dpa' rin chen mang gi sprul pa des /
NK023('a)001:3820: yon du rig pa'i me tog dang phyag dang mchod pa phul /
NK023('a)001:3821: gas nga mtshan rdo rje bde mchog rtsal //
NK023('a)001:3822: tsaka rnying pa cig na rdo rje che mchog rtsal zer /
NK023('a)001:3823: mngon par shes pa lnga dang ldan pa des /
NK023('a)001:3824: tshom bu 'bum dang bcas te tshogs bsgrubs pas rdo rje 'chang gi sa la gshegs so //
NK023('a)001:3825: des za hor gyi rgyal po in tra b+ho d+he zhes kyang bya /
NK023('a)001:3827: rgyal po dza la a su ra'i brag phug tu dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3828: yon du rang gi rgyal srid 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga phul /
NK023('a)001:3829: gsang mtshan rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal //
NK023('a)001:3830: tshom bu khri dang bcas nas tshogs bsgrubs pas rdo rje 'chang gi sa la gshegs so //
NK023('a)001:3831: des sh+aakya su tri la grong khyer skyid pa'i 'byung gnas su dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3832: yon du lha'i longs spyod bsam 'phel phul /
NK023('a)001:3833: gsang mtshan rdo rje gsal mdzes rtsal /
NK023('a)001:3834: tshom bu lnga stong dang bcas nas tshogs bsgrubs pas phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin brnyes so //
NK023('a)001:3835: gzhan yang in tras sing g+ha la'i rgyal po sing nga ra dza la /
NK023('a)001:3836: sin d+hu'i rgya mtsho'i 'gram du dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3838: gsang mtshan rdo rje grags pa rtsal /
NK023('a)001:3839: tshom bu stong dang bcas nas tshogs bsgrubs pas /
NK023('a)001:3840: rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK023('a)001:3841: des o rgyan gyi rgyal po u pa ra dza la /
NK023('a)001:3843: d+ha na ko sha'i gling phug tu dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3845: rdo rje yang dag grub pa rtsal /
NK023('a)001:3846: tshom bu lnga brgya dang bcas te tshogs bsgrubs pas rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK023('a)001:3847: des sras mo go ma de byi la /
NK023('a)001:3848: o rgyan gyi rin chen g.yu ldings tshal du /
NK023('a)001:3851: tshom bu brgya dang bcas te tshogs bsgrubs pas rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK023('a)001:3852: des mdo theg pa rim 'jug ltar /
NK023('a)001:3853: mi tri ru ka ma la zhes kyang bya /
NK023('a)001:3854: ka ma la shi la zhes bya ba la /
NK023('a)001:3855: dbus 'gyur tsan+da tshal du gser gyi pa tra brgyad phul gnang /
NK023('a)001:3856: rdo rje khyung chen rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:3857: des a tsar+ya 'dzi na mi tra la rdo rje gdan du gser phul gang phul /
NK023('a)001:3858: rdo rje nges pa rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:3859: des rdo rje bzhed pa'i dri med la /
NK023('a)001:3860: u ta pa ra'i tshal du rin po che phul /
NK023('a)001:3861: rdo rje bde byed rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:3862: des ru mi phyed seng ge la /
NK023('a)001:3863: ga bu rong gi shar ta pa ra'i tshal du rin po che phul /
NK023('a)001:3864: rdo rje gsang chen rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:3865: des slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad la /
NK023('a)001:3869: sri ra ma ti dang bde ba gsal mdzad gnyis a nu ba gnyis su 'dod /
NK023('a)001:3870: ma h+aa ba gcig tu 'dod do //
NK023('a)001:3871: des slob dpon sh+aakya bo d+he la /
NK023('a)001:3874: rdo rje dngos grub mchog rtsal //
NK023('a)001:3875: des ru pog kya de ba la /
NK023('a)001:3876: 'bri ka ma la shi lar gnang /
NK023('a)001:3878: rdo rje dad pa rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:3879: des slob dpon rdo rje sgeg pa la /
NK023('a)001:3880: dbus 'gyur tshal du gser gyi rdo dngos rtse lnga pa phul /
NK023('a)001:3882: de la rdo rje dril bu rtsal kyang zer /
NK023('a)001:3883: rdo rje sgeg pa rtsal kyang zer /
NK023('a)001:3884: rdo rje grags pa rtsal kyang zer //
NK023('a)001:3885: des slob dpon chos blon de ba la /
NK023('a)001:3889: des mkhan po chos rgyal skyong la /
NK023('a)001:3890: dbus 'gyur tshal du 'dod pa'i yon tan phul nas dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3891: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal //
NK023('a)001:3893: mdo'i dbang lha min nas ma h+aa'i bar theg pa rim 'jug ltar yul dbus 'gyur tshal du /
NK023('a)001:3894: gser sra nga lnga bcu phul nas dbang nos so //
NK023('a)001:3895: gsang mtshan rdo rje yang dbang gter du btags /
NK023('a)001:3896: nye brgyud nang dbang gi grub thob bdun la /
NK023('a)001:3897: sras mo go ma bde ba bzod med rtsal gyis /
NK023('a)001:3898: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba bcud mchog rdzogs pa rtsal /
NK023('a)001:3899: des slob dpon b+hi ma la mi tra rdo rje dbang rdzogs stsal /
NK023('a)001:3900: des slob dpon sog po rdo rje bzhad pa /
NK023('a)001:3901: slob dpon de yan chad nye brgyud bdun zer /
NK023('a)001:3902: slob dpon dz+nya na ku ma ra dri med zla shar la /
NK023('a)001:3903: sangs rgyas ye shes rdo rje yang dbang la'o //
NK023('a)001:3906: // // na mo rat+na gu ru h'u /
NK023('a)001:3907: lung a nu yo ga'i theg pa'i rim pa'i dbang bsgrod pa /
NK023('a)001:3908: rgyal bu rgyas sar bton pa'i lta bu'i dbang la /
NK023('a)001:3909: rgyal ba rig 'dzin gang zag gsum //
NK023('a)001:3910: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK023('a)001:3912: dang po rgyal ba dgongs pas brgyud pa ni /
NK023('a)001:3913: chos kyi rgyal pos rgyal tshab la //
NK023('a)001:3914: dgongs pa gsang ba nges par brgyud //
NK023('a)001:3916: dang po ston pa kun tu bzang po rdo rje 'chang che na des /
NK023('a)001:3917: rgyal tshab rigs lnga la dbang bskur //
NK023('a)001:3918: des rgyal sras sems dpa' sems ma la dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:3921: rim par brgyud de grags par 'gyur ces pas /
NK023('a)001:3922: gnyis pa rig 'dzin rigs pas brgyud pa la gnyis te /
NK023('a)001:3923: mi ma yin pa la brgyud pa ni /
NK023('a)001:3924: rigs gsum mgon pos lha klu gnod sbyin gyi gnas
NK023('a)001:3925: su dam pa'i mchod gsum bshad de grags par gyur
NK023('a)001:3926: to // mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis ka la brgyud pa ni /
NK023('a)001:3927: sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das nas /
NK023('a)001:3928: lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dus su /
NK023('a)001:3929: ri ma la ya'i rtser dam pa'i rigs can lnga la sogs pas gdung ba bton pas /
NK023('a)001:3930: ston pa gsang bdag byon nas dbang bskur zhing chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'o //
NK023('a)001:3931: gang zag snyan khung brgyud pa ni /
NK023('a)001:3932: srin po blo gros thabs ldan gyis gsang sngags kyi gzhung rin po che /
NK023('a)001:3933: gser gyi glegs bam la bee d+aur+ya zhun mas yi ger bris te bsdus pas /
NK023('a)001:3934: byin gyis brlabs kyis za hor gyi rgyal po in
NK023('a)001:3935: tra b+ho d+hi zhes kyang bya las can rgyal po
NK023('a)001:3936: dza la rmi ltas bdun snang ba ni /
NK023('a)001:3937: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK023('a)001:3938: chos kyi sgro ba byas pa dang //
NK023('a)001:3939: rin chen char du babs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:3940: kun gyis dam par basngagasa pa dang //
NK023('a)001:3941: rin chen glegs bam babs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:3942: mchod pa chen po byas pa dang //
NK023('a)001:3943: sangs rgyas pa la lung bstan pa'o //
NK023('a)001:3945: de yang gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje nyid kyis
NK023('a)001:3946: dam pa'i rigs can lnga la ma la ya'i rtser
NK023('a)001:3947: dbang bskur te / lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis lha'i bdud rtsi 'chi med phul /
NK023('a)001:3948: klu'i rgyal po 'jog pos gtsug gi nor bu phul /
NK023('a)001:3949: gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong gis gnod sbyin gyi gsang tshig phul /
NK023('a)001:3950: srin mo lang ka mgrin bcus lus kyi rgyan phul /
NK023('a)001:3951: mi dge slong li tsa byi dri ma med par
NK023('a)001:3952: grags pas mi'i rin po che sna lnga phul lo
NK023('a)001:3953: // gsang mtshan ni rim pa bzhin du lha blo gros 'dus pa rtsal /
NK023('a)001:3954: klu blo gros nges pa rtsal /
NK023('a)001:3955: gnod sbyin blo gros dad pa rtsal /
NK023('a)001:3956: srin mo blo gros thabs ldan rtsal /
NK023('a)001:3957: mi blo gros rab zhi rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:3959: rgyal po dza la a su ra'i brag phug tu dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:3960: yon du rin po che in tra ni la khru gang ba phul /
NK023('a)001:3961: gsang mtshan rdo rje gsang mchog rtsal /
NK023('a)001:3963: de'i byin gyis brlabs kyis gsang sngags kyis po ti dang glegs bam rnams /
NK023('a)001:3964: brag phug gi yang stengs su skar mda' thang la ltung ba bzhin du babs so //
NK023('a)001:3965: rab tu dga' ba'i tshul gyis don khyad par can
NK023('a)001:3966: zhig yod snyam nas brtags pas tshig 'bru gcig kyang
NK023('a)001:3967: brda' ma 'byal bas mug ste ngus nas /
NK023('a)001:3968: rgyal po u pa ra dza la sogs pa mkhyen
NK023('a)001:3969: pa can rnams la bstan pas kyang ma rtogs skad
NK023('a)001:3970: / la la dag dge slong ku ku ra dzas brtags gsung /
NK023('a)001:3971: der rgyal po dzas bsang sbyang byas pas sgyu 'phrul dra ba las /
NK023('a)001:3972: rdo rje sems dpa' bsgrub pa'i le'u dang /
NK023('a)001:3973: zhal mthong gi le'u rtogs te /
NK023('a)001:3974: brag phug tu bsgrubs pas zla ba drug na rdo
NK023('a)001:3975: rje sems dpa'i zhal mthong ste dngos grub ci 'dod
NK023('a)001:3976: gsung / po ti 'di rnams kyi don rtogs par 'tshal zhes zhus pas /
NK023('a)001:3977: rang gi rgyud sbyongs shig phyag na rdo rje lung ston par 'gyur ro zhes lung bstan no //
NK023('a)001:3978: der rin po che smug po las grub pa'i phyag na rdo rje'i sku zhig rnyed de /
NK023('a)001:3979: yi dam du bzung nas bsgrubs pas phyag na rdo rje mngon du byon /
NK023('a)001:3980: cho 'phrul bstan sgrib pa sbyangs te dbang bzhi rdzogs
NK023('a)001:3981: par bskur te dper med kyi don rtogs nas gsang
NK023('a)001:3982: sngags la mkhas par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:3983: des rgyal po u pa ra dza la grong khyer
NK023('a)001:3984: dpal yon can du rgyal srid rin po che sna
NK023('a)001:3985: bdun phul / rdo rje yang dag rtsal //
NK023('a)001:3986: des su tri gsum la bshad de /
NK023('a)001:3987: rgyal po dza'i sras sh+aakya su tri /
NK023('a)001:3989: na ga su tri gsum la grong khyer skyid pa'i 'byung gnas su /
NK023('a)001:3990: yon du lha'i rin po che bsam 'phel phul /
NK023('a)001:3991: rgyal po'i sras sh+aakya su tri'i gsang mtshan rdo rje gsal mdzes rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:3992: klu'i rgyal po na ga su tri'i gsang mtshan thig le bskyod med rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:3993: gu ya su tri'i gsang mtshan rdo rje gsal 'phro rtsal te gsum //
NK023('a)001:3994: sing ha su tri sing ha rgyal po'i gsang mtshan rdo rje 'od zer rtsal te bzhi'o //
NK023('a)001:3995: sras in+d+ra dang sh+aakya su tri gcig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:3996: sh+aakya su tris khyi'i rgyal po ku ku ra dza la /
NK023('a)001:3997: phyi'i rgya mtsho'i 'gram du dril bu g.yer kha stong phul nas gnang /
NK023('a)001:3999: des ro langs bde ba'i dngos grub la glang po che'i sna'i brag phug tu /
NK023('a)001:4001: rdo rje bde chen dngos grub rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:4002: des rdo rje bzhed pa la /
NK023('a)001:4003: u ta pa ra'i tshal du rin po che phul /
NK023('a)001:4005: des za hor gyi rgyal po pra ha sti la
NK023('a)001:4006: chu bo sin d+hu'i 'gram du rin po che ke
NK023('a)001:4007: ke ru phul / rdo rje dga' rab rtsal //
NK023('a)001:4008: de la slob ma mi gsum gyis nos te /
NK023('a)001:4012: sh+aakya mi tra ste yo ga mkhan dang /
NK023('a)001:4013: sh+aakya pra b+ha ba gsum gyis za hor rgyal po'i khab tu rang rang gi longs spyod phul lo //
NK023('a)001:4014: yang bshos khang du thog tu bdud rtsi bsil mchog phul kyang zer te /
NK023('a)001:4015: d+ha na rak+shi ta seng ge sgra sgrogs rtsal du btags pa /
NK023('a)001:4016: sh+aakya seng ges tu h'u mdzad rdo rje la o
NK023('a)001:4017: rgyan rdo rje phug tu rdzas mchog bzang po phul
NK023('a)001:4019: des ru sti ra ma ti la ga'u rang gi brag phug tu rin po che gser phul /
NK023('a)001:4021: des ru bde ba gsal mdzad la /
NK023('a)001:4022: grong khyer dpal yon du mnyes pa phul /
NK023('a)001:4024: des sh+aakya bo de zhes kyang bya mdo mkhan d+harma bo de la /
NK023('a)001:4025: yul ma ga tar rta dang glang po phul /
NK023('a)001:4026: rdo rje gsal mdzes chos mchog rtsal //
NK023('a)001:4027: des rgya gar chos rgyal la dpal shi le na len trar 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga phul /
NK023('a)001:4029: des bal po'i rgyal po ba su d+ha ra dang /
NK023('a)001:4030: bru zha'i lo ts+wa ba che btsan skyes la rgyal po'i khab tu dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:4031: yon du gser srang gi bkor cha phul /
NK023('a)001:4032: bal po'i gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4033: bru zha'i chos grub rtsal zhes btags so //
NK023('a)001:4034: de'i dus na rgya gar gtsug lag dpal dges kyis kyang thob ste /
NK023('a)001:4035: gsang mtshan rdo rje gtsug tor rtsal to //
NK023('a)001:4036: de gsum ka la slob dpon sangs rgyas kyis mdo dbang gnas yig gda' lags //
NK023('a)001:4037: de'i dus su yul bsgregs kyi zung mkhar ba /
NK023('a)001:4039: gdung rus gnubs ma mchims mo bkra shis mtsho /
NK023('a)001:4042: mi chos kyi ming rdo rje khri gtsug /
NK023('a)001:4043: slob dpon rnams kyis mkhas pa chen po 'byung bar lung bstan pa /
NK023('a)001:4044: chung nas dad pa dang shes rab tu ldan pa des /
NK023('a)001:4045: lha dpal gyi ye shes la dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:4046: mchims phu dang phung po ri bo cher khrab 'khyag
NK023('a)001:4047: pa dkar pos sna drangs nas bzhi brgya phul te
NK023('a)001:4048: dbang nos so // yang sangs rgyas ye shes des
NK023('a)001:4049: lo nyi shu pa la ldum ra gser du dkrum
NK023('a)001:4050: ste khyed du gril nas bal po'i mthil du byon
NK023('a)001:4051: dbang nos so // / bal po ba su d+ha ra dang mjal sgra shes te /
NK023('a)001:4052: rgyud sde dang bsgrub thabs mang du zhus so //
NK023('a)001:4054: rgya gar gyi mkhan po chos rgyal skyong la zhus shig par lung bstan /
NK023('a)001:4055: rgya gar gyi yul du byon te ru chos rgyal skyong la mjal bar byas nas zhus pas /
NK023('a)001:4056: rgyud dang dbang bsgrub thabs mang du gnang ngo //
NK023('a)001:4058: ru chos rgyal skyong la dbang zhus pas /
NK023('a)001:4059: slob dpon gsal ba'i rgyan la zhus shig par lung /
NK023('a)001:4060: 'dir ni slob dpon chen po gsal ba'i brgyan bya
NK023('a)001:4061: ba lo stong drug brgya lon pa zhig bzhugs kyis
NK023('a)001:4062: khyed de'i spyan sngar song zhig gsung pa ltar du
NK023('a)001:4063: rgya gar du byon nas 'dus pa chen po mdo
NK023('a)001:4064: theg pa dgu'i dbang yang gsan /
NK023('a)001:4065: sngags kyi bsgrub sde dang rgyud sde mang po gsan
NK023('a)001:4066: ces bla ma glan bsod nams mgon gyi dbang byang
NK023('a)001:4067: na gsungs gda' / mdo'i dbang bskur zhus shing gnang
NK023('a)001:4068: zhes pa ni gu ru chos rgyal skyong de bal
NK023('a)001:4070: de'ang bal po'i rgyal po ba su d+ha ra nor 'dzin la dbang zhus pa'i tshe nga yi /
NK023('a)001:4072: rgya gar mkhan po chos rgyal skyong bru zha'i yul du spyan drangs der gshegs te /
NK023('a)001:4075: gsum la bru zha'i mkhan po che btsan skyes kyis bru zha'i khrom du bsgyur bar byas /
NK023('a)001:4076: mos pa chungs bas dang po ma 'gyur skad /
NK023('a)001:4077: de nas rgya gar yul du byon te /
NK023('a)001:4078: bal po ba su d+ha ra dang /
NK023('a)001:4079: bru zha'i lo ts+aa ba che btsan skyes dang /
NK023('a)001:4080: gnubs yang dbang gsum gyis zhus pas gnang ste /
NK023('a)001:4081: dbang gi chu bo bzhi rdzogs par bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:4082: de'i byin gyis brlabs kyis phyi mkhan po chos rgyal dang /
NK023('a)001:4084: bru zha'i lo ts+tsha ba che btsan skyes dang /
NK023('a)001:4086: phyis ring lugs shan ta raka k+shi ta slob dpon
NK023('a)001:4087: pad+ma'i bka' dang sbyar nas bru zha'i yul gyi khrom
NK023('a)001:4088: du bsgyur nas gnubs sangs rgyas la bshad do //
NK023('a)001:4089: rigs brgyud lo rgyus de skad zer yang /
NK023('a)001:4090: mgon po'i dbang rgyud dang sbyar bas mdo dbang gi
NK023('a)001:4091: phyag cha rnams btang nas ru bde ba gsal mdzad
NK023('a)001:4092: la'ang gnubs sangs rgyas kyis zhus pa 'dra bas spyad
NK023('a)001:4093: do // de yang jo bo sangs rgyas kyi rnam
NK023('a)001:4094: thar spyir du 'di la shel brag ngos la bsgoms
NK023('a)001:4095: do // pa'i tshe / phyag na rdo rjes ye shes rdo rjes dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:4096: 'om mo'i tshal du bsgoms pa'i tshe /
NK023('a)001:4097: dri za'i phru gus sangs rgyas ye shes rin po cher ming btags te ming gis dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:4098: gang bzangs gnas la sgoms pa'i tshe /
NK023('a)001:4099: gnod sbyin phru gus che ba'i yon tan gyis dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:4100: gnubs mtsho gling dgur sgoms pa'i tshe /
NK023('a)001:4101: klu phru gus dug dang gdug pa sel ba'i dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:4102: dur khrod lhas su sgoms pa'i tshe /
NK023('a)001:4103: yi dwags phru gus mthu rtsal brnyes pa'i dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:4104: d+ha na sa kri ta la sogs pa pan+di ta mang pos dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:4105: rgya nag ha shang ma h+aa ya nas kyang dbang dang gdams ngag mang po gnang /
NK023('a)001:4106: rgya gar d+ha na ta la bod du byon te dbang gdams ngag mang po gnang /
NK023('a)001:4107: rgya gar gyi yul du lan bdun byon /
NK023('a)001:4108: lan drug chos dang bstan srungs drag sngags bsgyur /
NK023('a)001:4109: lan cig zhu tig mdzad skad /
NK023('a)001:4110: sa gzhi sa non pa dang /
NK023('a)001:4112: mkhas pa chen por grags pa lags so //
NK023('a)001:4113: de la slob ma mang yang thugs zin pa thugs kyi sras bzhi la brgyud de //
NK023('a)001:4115: nyang stod kyi 'bre khro chu nyang shor chen mchog
NK023('a)001:4116: nyang chung ye shes 'byung ba zur sh+aakya 'byung dang
NK023('a)001:4117: bzhi'o zer te / de rnams kyi 'bre dang /
NK023('a)001:4118: myang chen gnyis shin tu zhal mthong ba snga la /
NK023('a)001:4119: myang chung dang zur gnyis phyi bas zhal mthong tsam mo //
NK023('a)001:4120: la la na re slob dpon sangs rgyas kyis shangs
NK023('a)001:4121: kyi stong tshab byang chub rin po che la sogs
NK023('a)001:4122: pa rin po che gsum la gnang /
NK023('a)001:4123: des brgya gzhon nu bshes gnyen dang /
NK023('a)001:4124: me gnyag mchog gi rin chen dang /
NK023('a)001:4125: stong tshab 'phags pa rgya mtsho dang /
NK023('a)001:4126: lha rje 'ug pa lung pa zur chen sh+aakya 'byung
NK023('a)001:4127: gnas bzhi la sku tshe yi stod la bskur ces
NK023('a)001:4128: mdo se lugs ltar bzhed do //
NK023('a)001:4129: 'dir ni jo bo sangs rgyas kyi zhal nas /
NK023('a)001:4130: shes rab kyi nags ma la yon tan gyi sdong po 'khrungs //
NK023('a)001:4131: gcig gis ni rtsa ba khyer so ye shes dbang phyug smin rdo rje dbyings chen gter /
NK023('a)001:4132: gcig gis ni sdong po khyer pa kor blon rje 'phags pa smin rdo rje gnam lcags rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4133: gcig gis ni lo ma khyer sru legs pa'i sgron ma smin /
NK023('a)001:4135: gcig gis ni 'bras bu khyer snubs yon tan rgya
NK023('a)001:4136: mtsho smin rdo rje rig 'dzin gter ces gsung skad
NK023('a)001:4137: do // yang gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes rin
NK023('a)001:4138: po che sku tshe'i smad la bstan pa bka' shog
NK023('a)001:4139: rgya bo che bzhag nas 'di skad gsung /
NK023('a)001:4140: tsan+da gyi sdong po la spa kor gyis rtsa ba khyer /
NK023('a)001:4144: khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho lha rje gnubs chung gis rangs pa khyer ces gsung //
NK023('a)001:4145: dan ni co ro dan phug gi yon tan mchog ste /
NK023('a)001:4146: glan nya tshal ba ni mdo dbang yon tan rgya mtsho nas brgyud de /
NK023('a)001:4147: rong snar gyi yang gsang brag phug tu /
NK023('a)001:4148: dbang gi chu bo bzhi rdzogs par bskur /
NK023('a)001:4149: dbang gi yig smad bco brgyad gtad /
NK023('a)001:4150: dbang rtags su dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud byin no //
NK023('a)001:4151: yon du spa dro dang pu rangs dang li shin
NK023('a)001:4152: ti sogs lho stod kyi la sgo gsum blan nas
NK023('a)001:4157: la rdzas dang rtsi sman mang du phul lo //
NK023('a)001:4158: gsang mtshan rdo rje gter bzhad rtsal du btags so //
NK023('a)001:4159: des sras ye shes rgya mtsho la /
NK023('a)001:4160: khu lung 'phar lung du dbang dang bshad pa bka' bya'o //
NK023('a)001:4163: tha ma zang zing gis mnyes par mdzad do //
NK023('a)001:4164: gsang mtshan rdo rje dbang bsgrub rtsal du btags so //
NK023('a)001:4166: des rngog shes rab skyong la zer ba yang yod do //
NK023('a)001:4169: des dbyar gsal ba'i byang chub /
NK023('a)001:4170: des rgya blo gros byang chub /
NK023('a)001:4171: des zur che chung zer ba yang yod /
NK023('a)001:4172: yang so ye shes dbang phyug /
NK023('a)001:4175: dan yon tan gnubs yon tan /
NK023('a)001:4185: skyo ston dar ma rgyal mtshan te bco lnga ni gnubs sangs rgyas kyi slob ma'am /
NK023('a)001:4186: spyir dus mtshungs kyi dge mched bco lnga'o //
NK023('a)001:4188: thams cad mdo dbang gi mched ma lags dpon slob dus mtshungs so //
NK023('a)001:4190: spa kor gyis beg gsal ba'i byang chub des rngog
NK023('a)001:4191: mi shes rab skyong des dmar yon tan byang chub
NK023('a)001:4192: des rgya blo gros gzhon nu des zhu bsod nams
NK023('a)001:4193: sh+aaka des zur po che zer ro //
NK023('a)001:4194: yang rgya blo gros sras gzhon nus zur po che zer ba'ang snang ngo //
NK023('a)001:4195: yang sru'i slob ma bzhi la dbyar gsal ba'i byang chub rdo rje mtshams byed rtsal dang /
NK023('a)001:4196: rgya blo gros gzhon nu rdo rje dbang rdzogs rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4197: sngags pa rgya sh+aakya mchog rab rdo rje gzi 'bar rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4198: zhu bsod nams sh+aakya phrin las mthar phyin rtsal dang bzhi'o //
NK023('a)001:4199: zhes mdo se lung las bshad /
NK023('a)001:4200: yang sangs rgyas ye shes la 'khor brgyad gru gu 'jig rten la sogs pa'o //
NK023('a)001:4202: 'dir ye shes rgya mtshos byang chub rnam pa gsum la bshad de mar pa yon tan byang chub /
NK023('a)001:4203: rgya blo gros gzhon nu zer kyang /
NK023('a)001:4204: rgya blo gros byang chub yin skad /
NK023('a)001:4205: sna nam tshul khrims byang chub da nga gsum la bka' byo skad /
NK023('a)001:4206: khu lung mkhar lung du dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:4209: sna nam gyis khrab dang lha rdzas phul /
NK023('a)001:4210: gsang mtshan mar pa ni rdo rje lhun grub rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4211: rgya rdo rje las grub rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4212: sna nam rdo rje grub mchog rtsal du btags so //
NK023('a)001:4213: mar pa nas mang po ma 'phel lo //
NK023('a)001:4214: rgya yis sku tshe'i stod la sna nam zhal yon pa la sogs pa bzhi la bshad zer te /
NK023('a)001:4215: rgyal po'i btsun mo sna nam za'i pha ming gi rgyud pa yin pas zhang /
NK023('a)001:4216: mi g.yo bas zhang yon pa yin skad /
NK023('a)001:4217: yul lho brag pa lags skad /
NK023('a)001:4218: shangs kyi stong tshab 'phags pa rgya mtsho dang /
NK023('a)001:4219: sna nam gyi 'gar chung tshul khrims bzang po dang gsum /
NK023('a)001:4220: 'o bdug pa g.yar gsal ba'i byang chub dang bzhi la bshad do //
NK023('a)001:4221: rgya blo gros byang chub 'di gnubs kyi slob ma
NK023('a)001:4222: dge mched kyi gseb la sras gzhon nu dang bcas
NK023('a)001:4223: pa'ang yod pa'o // sku tshe'i bar du khra bo
NK023('a)001:4224: che khyil phyogs kyi tho khar nam mkha' lde la
NK023('a)001:4225: pa'ang yod pa'o // / tha ma nyang smad rgyal
NK023('a)001:4226: chen gyi zhu bsod nams sh+aakya la bka' stsal lo
NK023('a)001:4227: pa'ang yod pa'o // / // gsang mtshan phrin las mthar phyin rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:4228: gzhan rnams kyi dbang yon dang gsang mtshan mi gda' 'o //
NK023('a)001:4229: rgya blo gros byang chub kyis tho gar nam mkha'
NK023('a)001:4230: lde la nyang stod phung po ri bo cher dbang
NK023('a)001:4231: bskur / dbang yon du glang bzang po gcig dang nas khal brgya phul lo //
NK023('a)001:4232: gsang mtshan rdo rje dngos grub gter ces btags so //
NK023('a)001:4236: des chos lung gi nyang ye shes 'byung gnas la sgyu 'phrul sems phyogs zhus /
NK023('a)001:4237: dge gong gi lce sh+aakya mchog la bdud rtsi zhus /
NK023('a)001:4238: yul gsar gyi gnya' nag dbang drags la thabs lam zhus skad /
NK023('a)001:4239: nyang stod lhab lhab kyi 'bre khro chung la lam
NK023('a)001:4240: rim dang spar khab la sogs pa zhus te ka
NK023('a)001:4241: dag dang lhun grub kyi chos skad kyang de nas
NK023('a)001:4242: byung skad / de gsum la nags tshal sgre gsum gyi bla ma zer bar gda' /
NK023('a)001:4244: sku tshe'i stod la bka' sdod ye shes snying po
NK023('a)001:4245: la mdo dgongs 'dus la sogs pa gsan te bka'
NK023('a)001:4246: sde zur bar de nas grags gsungs /
NK023('a)001:4247: bar du tho gar nam mkha' lde la sgrol gyi
NK023('a)001:4248: se to'i phur dbang dang rgyud kyi bshad pa zhus
NK023('a)001:4249: / dbang yon rta gcig gis sna drangs nas mang du phul /
NK023('a)001:4250: gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal du btags so //
NK023('a)001:4251: sku tshe'i smad du zhu bsod nams sh+aakya la zhus
NK023('a)001:4252: nas gsang sngags sku yon du 'khor gsum yongs dag
NK023('a)001:4253: tu rang nor skya ba dang gza' ru gos lham
NK023('a)001:4254: tsam yang ma lus par phul zhing mdo nyid kyi
NK023('a)001:4255: gsang mtshan bde gshegs zhi ba rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:4256: de ltar sngags kyi bla ma mang po la dbang
NK023('a)001:4257: zhus nas gsang sngags pra yas su song ba rnams
NK023('a)001:4258: bsdus / rgyud dang bsgrub thabs dbang dang gdams ngag tu sdebs nas /
NK023('a)001:4259: 'bangs rtse mo bzhi rtse rkog brgyad la sogs pa
NK023('a)001:4260: la bshad de nyi zla ltar grags par mdzad do
NK023('a)001:4261: // rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pas spyan ras gzigs nyid du lung bstan /
NK023('a)001:4262: grub rtags nam mkha' la byon nas rdo la rdzis te zhabs rjes gsal bar bzhag /
NK023('a)001:4263: sku tshab yi dam dpal chen zhal gzigs ltar du bzhengs shing byin rlabs 'gro don mdzad /
NK023('a)001:4264: bla ma brgya rtsa brgyad la 'khor gsum yongs dag grub bo //
NK023('a)001:4266: lta dgongs kyi rtse mo brag rgya bo'i zur chung shes rab grags pa /
NK023('a)001:4267: mkhyen rgya'i rtse mo la stod ra swa'i zhang 'gos chung ba rdo rje lhun grub rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4268: sgyu 'phrul gyi bshad pa phyogs gcig gi rtse mo
NK023('a)001:4269: bres kyi me gnyag 'byung grags rdo rje bde ba
NK023('a)001:4270: rtsal / sgom sgrub kyi rtse mo mtsho nya'i bzang
NK023('a)001:4271: sgom shes rab rgyal po rdo rje gzi 'bar rtsal
NK023('a)001:4272: rtsal / // pho po'i rtse mo bram gyi gtsags bla ma dang lnga'o yang zer //
NK023('a)001:4273: de las bder gshegs rgya bo bas 'ug pa lung du lo nyi shu rtsa gsum bzhugs /
NK023('a)001:4274: dbang dang gdams ngag thams cad zhus so //
NK023('a)001:4277: longs spyod kyang mang po phul /
NK023('a)001:4278: gsang mtshan rdo rje lhun grub rtsal tu btags so //
NK023('a)001:4279: gsang sngags kyi mkhyen pa bsam gyis mi khyab cing
NK023('a)001:4280: bstan 'dzin gyi khang bur dgongs pa rlung su gyur
NK023('a)001:4281: / rdo rje khang bur rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal mthong /
NK023('a)001:4282: pram pa sgrub khang du zur po ches yang dag
NK023('a)001:4283: lo bsgrub mdzad pa'i tshe 'ol ba gdong nas gnyan
NK023('a)001:4284: pas ru lu'i sgra chung du ma song ba dang
NK023('a)001:4285: / rtse mo bzhis dgongs pa 'gran pas skra dkyil
NK023('a)001:4286: krung bcas nas nam mkha' la 'phags pa des 'bangs
NK023('a)001:4287: ka chen bzhi dang gdung ma brgyad la sogs pa
NK023('a)001:4288: / la brgyud do // ka ba bzhi ni /
NK023('a)001:4289: phrin las kyi ka ba mda' phu'i 'da' tig jo sh+aaka /
NK023('a)001:4290: sgyu 'phrul gyi ka ba chu dbar gyi glan sh+aakya bzang po /
NK023('a)001:4291: mdo'i ka ba sgyed lung gi yang khyer bla ma /
NK023('a)001:4292: sems phyogs kyi ka ba gong phu'i skyo ston sh+aakya ye shes so //
NK023('a)001:4293: de rnams la g.yas ru'i mkha' 'gro lha khang du dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:4294: mnyes pa'i yo byad mang du phul /
NK023('a)001:4295: gsang mtshan 'da' tig gi rdo rje grub mchog rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4296: glan rdo rje myu gu rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4297: yang khyeng gi thig le 'gyur med rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4298: skyo'i rdo rje snying po rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4299: gdung ma glan sh+aakya byang chub rdo rje drag po rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4300: la sogs pa ka gdung kun la zur sh+aakya seng
NK023('a)001:4301: ge gsang bdag sgro phug pas gsan cing brnyes pa'i
NK023('a)001:4302: yon gsung rabs rgyas 'bring gis sna drangs longs spyod
NK023('a)001:4303: mang du phul te bstan pa'i gnyer mdzad /
NK023('a)001:4304: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'jigs med rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4306: yang brgyud pa lung gcig ni /
NK023('a)001:4307: sh+ri sing has bee ro tsa na des sangs rgyas
NK023('a)001:4308: mgon po des rba raka shi ta des ya zi
NK023('a)001:4310: zer mo dge slong ma bde gnas gnyis la gnang /
NK023('a)001:4311: de nas pho rgyud mo rgyud kyi rdzogs chen gnyis gyes pa la /
NK023('a)001:4312: mo rgyud ni dge slong ma la mar pa khrom rgyal gyis gsan /
NK023('a)001:4314: ya zis myang ston sra ba /
NK023('a)001:4315: des mar pa khrom rgyal des mar chung shes rab 'od la gnang ba'o //
NK023('a)001:4316: yang sras ye shes rgya mtshos khu lung du sna
NK023('a)001:4317: nam tshul khrims byang chub la bka' stsal cing dbang
NK023('a)001:4318: bskur / des mar chung shes rab 'od la gtam
NK023('a)001:4319: shul bya ze'i dgon par gnyegs kyi g.yu dmar bya
NK023('a)001:4320: ba g.yu bzang po gcig dang /
NK023('a)001:4322: na bza' bzang po gcig phul /
NK023('a)001:4323: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde grub rtsal zhes btags so //
NK023('a)001:4324: des shangs 'chums kyi ban grong pa shang nag lang
NK023('a)001:4325: za bsod nams dar la shangs su byon nas dbang
NK023('a)001:4326: bskur / de yang lha rje zur chung pa la mar chung shes rab 'od pas /
NK023('a)001:4327: sems phyogs dbang gdeng sgro ba nag po'i skor zhu ru byon pas /
NK023('a)001:4328: mar pa tshad nad drag pos bsnyung ba la /
NK023('a)001:4329: shangs gnag grwa sa rnying par bzhugs pas bsdo gral mdzad pas gdangs te der drin lan du /
NK023('a)001:4330: rdzogs chen brgyud pa tha ma'i chos skor kun byed la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK023('a)001:4331: mdo la 'grel pa lung bstan dang /
NK023('a)001:4332: mdo phra mo mang du gnang /
NK023('a)001:4333: sgyu 'phrul la rdo rje me long la sogs pa bshad rgyud sde bzhi /
NK023('a)001:4334: man ngag rnams bkod zab mo dbang gi chos skor rnams gnang skad do //
NK023('a)001:4335: des lha rje sgro phug pa la gnang ste /
NK023('a)001:4336: nya ri rgya ston bya ba shangs gnag dang gnyis ka'i slob ma zhig la /
NK023('a)001:4337: lha rjes chos kyi lo rgyus thos pas chos la mos nas /
NK023('a)001:4338: rgya ston gyis 'tshag sbyor byas te /
NK023('a)001:4339: sgro phug tu gdan drangs dbang dang chos mang po zhus /
NK023('a)001:4340: g.yu gcig gis sna drangs nas zhabs tog bgyis /
NK023('a)001:4341: gsang mtshan bde byed gzhon nu rtsal zhes btags so //
NK023('a)001:4342: de rnams mdo khyad par dbang gi brgyud pa lags so //
NK023('a)001:4345: // // de yang a nu chos kyi rgyal pos rgyal tshab la /
NK023('a)001:4346: dgongs pa gsang ba nges par bsgyur //
NK023('a)001:4347: 'dir bsgro gsal bar bshad sbyar ba //
NK023('a)001:4348: lha dang mi yi rig 'dzin la //
NK023('a)001:4349: rim par brgyud de grags par 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:4350: lha klu gnod sbyin srin mo dang //
NK023('a)001:4351: mi las dge slong li tsa byi //
NK023('a)001:4352: rgyal po dza dang u pa ra dza dang //
NK023('a)001:4353: sh+aakya su tri ku ku ra dza phyi //
NK023('a)001:4354: ro langs bde ba rdo rje bzhad pa dang //
NK023('a)001:4355: pra chen ha sti d+ha na rak+shi dang //
NK023('a)001:4356: h'u mdzad rdo rje sti ra ma ti dang //
NK023('a)001:4357: bde ba gsal mdzad sh+aakya bo de dang //
NK023('a)001:4358: mkhan po chos rgyal skyong sogs rgya gar brgyud //
NK023('a)001:4359: bal po'i rgyal po ba su d+ha ra dang //
NK023('a)001:4360: bru zha'i mkhan pa che btsan skyes sogs kyis //
NK023('a)001:4361: jo bo sangs rgyas nyid la legs par brgyud //
NK023('a)001:4362: yon tan rgya mtsho ye shes rgya mtsho dang //
NK023('a)001:4363: blo gros byang chub tho kar nam mkha' lde //
NK023('a)001:4364: zur chen sh+aakya 'byung zur chung shes rab grags //
NK023('a)001:4365: ka chen bzhi yis sh+aakya seng ge la //
NK023('a)001:4366: rim par brgyud de nyi zla lta bur grags //
NK023('a)001:4367: yang ni ye shes rgya mtsho tshul khrims byang chub la /
NK023('a)001:4368: mar chung shes rab 'od kyis shangs nag la //
NK023('a)001:4369: shangs nag lang zas lha rje sgro phug pa //
NK023('a)001:4370: sgro phug sh+aakya seng ges glan sh+aaka bzangs //
NK023('a)001:4372: zur sh+aakya seng ge dang glan sh+aakya bzang po gnyis kyis /
NK023('a)001:4373: 'go gdong gi lha rje 'gar ston gzung nge la gnang /
NK023('a)001:4374: des grub pa thob nas nga ni 'ug pa lung
NK023('a)001:4375: du bla ma zur pa can 'gro gsung nas gshegs
NK023('a)001:4376: tsa na / sa chen g.yos sgra drag po thos
NK023('a)001:4377: nas ltas pas btsad po yur kha'i ri la nam
NK023('a)001:4378: mkha' la skor ba mdzad cing bla ma mnyes par
NK023('a)001:4379: tsa na / mdzad / brag la phur pa thebs /
NK023('a)001:4384: sgyu 'phrul kun la mkhas shing grub pa thob pa'o //
NK023('a)001:4385: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK023('a)001:4386: des preg ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan la gnang /
NK023('a)001:4388: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'jigs med rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4390: yon du slongs mo sna tshogs dang /
NK023('a)001:4391: ro khur 'dze ros byin pa'i gser par bu gang
NK023('a)001:4392: gayu'o chos sna grangs chos phyogs su sprugs te gsang
NK023('a)001:4393: mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal /
NK023('a)001:4394: des sras glan gtson seng dang glan bsod rgyal ba
NK023('a)001:4395: gnyis dang sdong po dkon mchog rin chen dang gsum
NK023('a)001:4396: la gnang / bla ma'i gdan sa bskyangs so gdung bzung ngo //
NK023('a)001:4397: gsum ka'i gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:4398: dpal ldan chos seng des mdo dbang ni glan bsod rgyal la gsan la /
NK023('a)001:4399: gtad rgya ni glan bsod rgyal dang sdong po dkon mchog rin chen phar slob tshur slob yin pas /
NK023('a)001:4400: glan gyis sdong po la gnang des dpal ldan chos seng la gnang ste /
NK023('a)001:4401: zhabs thog brgyud pa dang bcas pas mdzad /
NK023('a)001:4402: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:4403: dpal ldan chos seng des glan sangs rgyas dpal la gnang /
NK023('a)001:4404: rab bsgrub la 'bring lus ngag tha ma zang zing gi zhabs thog phyogs med du mnyes par mdzad /
NK023('a)001:4405: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal //
NK023('a)001:4406: des glan bsod nams mgon po la gnang /
NK023('a)001:4407: shangs phyogs kyi sngags 'chang tsam gyi mgon dang mnyes par mdzad /
NK023('a)001:4408: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK023('a)001:4409: de'i yab kyang grub thob lags te //
NK023('a)001:4410: yab slob dpon lha 'bum gyis dpon g.yog bcu gsum mdzad nas /
NK023('a)001:4411: nyin gcig la sprul pa'ang bcu gsum ste /
NK023('a)001:4413: myang stod kyi cog dpe la sogs lha khang bcu
NK023('a)001:4414: gsum gyi rab gnas dus gcig la mthong bar mdzad
NK023('a)001:4415: nas / bde bar gshegs pa'i dus na sprul pa gsum /
NK023('a)001:4418: tshong 'dus su nyo chang gsum nyin gcig la mdzad gsung /
NK023('a)001:4419: de'i sras bla ma bsod nams mgon gyis /
NK023('a)001:4420: bla ma 'phags pa'i btsun pa mdzad /
NK023('a)001:4421: dru rdo rje seng ge'i drung du glu rtog grol /
NK023('a)001:4422: mdo'i dbang dbus gtsang du lan bcu gcig mdzad /
NK023('a)001:4423: log 'dren dang chom rkun chos skyong gis tshar bcad /
NK023('a)001:4424: mtshan mo dang sku bsrang nas bzhugs te mi gzims la /
NK023('a)001:4425: mdo mgon ma bsgrubs kyang mgo bar byung bas dgongs 'dus bshad bka' rgyas /
NK023('a)001:4426: de nyid kyi las kyi slob dpon bla ma dpal
NK023('a)001:4427: ldan pas bla ma pa rang bzhung nas las kyi
NK023('a)001:4428: slob dpon khri thog tu langs shing /
NK023('a)001:4429: dbang mchog rgyab yig sgrogs pa dang phrin gzhung mang du mdzad gsung /
NK023('a)001:4430: bla ma glan bsod nams mgon po des /
NK023('a)001:4431: mdo yongs rdzogs sgyu 'phrul rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum /
NK023('a)001:4432: dong sprugs tshang pa yang dag gzhan don rnams bla ma bsam grub rdo rje ba la snang zhing /
NK023('a)001:4433: yon du dngos po zang zing sna tshogs dang /
NK023('a)001:4435: rjes kyi rten la skud gser dang rab gnas /
NK023('a)001:4437: bla ma dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bor gzigs /
NK023('a)001:4438: lha tshogs rang nyid kyi thugs la thim par gsal bzhin pa'i ngang nas dbang rnams thob /
NK023('a)001:4439: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde chen rtsal yin /
NK023('a)001:4440: sgos kyi mdo'i gtad rgya ni glan bsod nams mgon po des /
NK023('a)001:4441: bla ma gyong khang pa zi ston sh+aakya bzang po la gnang /
NK023('a)001:4442: dbang skyar zhu ba gser zho gang gi 'bul thang mdzad /
NK023('a)001:4443: bka' bzhin sras la thugs gnyer gyi slob dpon mdzad /
NK023('a)001:4444: bla ma gshegs rjes na zhal lta bzhin dbang gos
NK023('a)001:4445: dang gsal 'debs mdo yongs rdzogs kyi mnga' gsol mdzad
NK023('a)001:4446: / des bla ma bsam grub pa la gnang /
NK023('a)001:4447: yon du dar gyi dbang gos phod ka sngon po phul lo //
NK023('a)001:4450: bdag zur h+aa sh+aakya 'byung gnas dang /
NK023('a)001:4452: lcam sring la gtad rgya dang bcas pa gnang /
NK023('a)001:4453: sku drin zhu ba la rgya bod kyi na bza' dang sman sna thab chas kyi nas 'bru phul /
NK023('a)001:4454: gtad rgya la gos yug dang gser phul bas /
NK023('a)001:4455: nga'i bla ma'i bu dang bu mo'i bu lon dag tu chug gsung nas de ltar bsgrubs so //
NK023('a)001:4456: de'i tshe bu ni yul gzhan du song dpon du
NK023('a)001:4457: 'dzin pa'ang med kyi bla ma gsung pa grub bo
NK023('a)001:4458: // bka' bzhin du dbang bskur dang /
NK023('a)001:4459: bla ma bzang po pa la /
NK023('a)001:4460: byang sems dang ma h+aa a nu sgos su zhus /
NK023('a)001:4461: bla ma dpal ldan pa la tshang pa zhus /
NK023('a)001:4462: bla ma bsam grub rdo rje la dbang tshar bzhi sgos kyi gtad rgya lan gsum thob /
NK023('a)001:4463: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal lo //
NK023('a)001:4464: mad'i dbang bskur drin can ma shes rab skyid khams
NK023('a)001:4465: pa chos gling pa bla ma dge bshes tshul rgyal
NK023('a)001:4466: / myang smad bla ma drags pa blo gros /
NK023('a)001:4467: shangs pa bla ma tsa ri ba zhi ba bzang po khus dbon /
NK023('a)001:4468: gyong khang pa slob dpon tshul khrims 'byung gnas /
NK023('a)001:4469: pa tshab rtse rgyal du jo btan bla ma g.yag sde dbon po nam mkha' grags /
NK023('a)001:4470: de rnams kyi thugs dgongs tshim par bsgrubs shing /
NK023('a)001:4472: nyi phug pa bla ma bzang po pa dang /
NK023('a)001:4473: bla ma dngos grub pa la'ang phul /
NK023('a)001:4474: zha lu ri phug gi nye 'khor du /
NK023('a)001:4475: sde dang 'gro ba mang po'i rim 'gro sngags 'chang spyi yis zhus nas tshar gcig phul /
NK023('a)001:4476: rta nag tu rog pa tshang pa bla ma kun
NK023('a)001:4477: legs pa yang bka' thob tsam mdzad kyin gda' nas
NK023('a)001:4478: phul / rtse chen du ta'i swi d+hu ba khu dbon yum sras rnams kyis sbyin bdag mdzad nas /
NK023('a)001:4479: bla ma g.yag lung pa shes rab rgya mtsho ba dang /
NK023('a)001:4480: slob dpon sman ri ba dpal ldan byang chub 'od la sogs pa rnams la tshar gcig bgyis /
NK023('a)001:4481: chu pho byi lo ma bla ma rin po che
NK023('a)001:4482: sangs rgyas spyi gzugs can bsam grub pa byon pa'i
NK023('a)001:4484: bla ma g.ye dmar ri phug pa tshe'i rgyal mtshan la rgun dang /
NK023('a)001:4485: bla ma gu ru ba dang bla ma lho brag shar pa la ston kha bgyis /
NK023('a)001:4486: sgrub khang dang chos phug dang yang dben du tshar res sa non /
NK023('a)001:4487: dge bshes khams pa rdo rje tshul khrims dang /
NK023('a)001:4488: nya ri'i bla ma zla ba pa dang /
NK023('a)001:4489: ri khrod ldan yul ba slob dpon rigs ldan bzang po la /
NK023('a)001:4490: stag gru ga'i pa dang nye bar chos lung spang pa po bla ma dpal ldan pa /
NK023('a)001:4491: spa kor lha ldings pa slob dpon dpal dang /
NK023('a)001:4492: sman ri ba dge bshes mgon dang //
NK023('a)001:4493: dar rje dpal grags kyi rgyud pa slob dpon chos skyong dpal dang /
NK023('a)001:4494: zur mo sras btsun rnams zhu nas tshar gcig bgyis /
NK023('a)001:4495: yang dmyal ba bla ma bde legs dpal dang /
NK023('a)001:4496: bla ma gter 'don rdo rje gling pa dang /
NK023('a)001:4497: yan du bstan pa spyi'i rim 'gror tshar gcig bgyis /
NK023('a)001:4498: yang bstan pa spyi'i rim 'gror ram mi nub par bya ba'i phyir /
NK023('a)001:4499: me mo sbrul gyi lo la spog pa dgon pa'i
NK023('a)001:4500: bla ma gnyag sprul sku bkra shis rgyal mtshan la
NK023('a)001:4501: gtad rgya dang bcas pa gnang ngo //
NK023('a)001:4502: yang nga dang dus mtshungs par gnyos tshul khrims rgyal
NK023('a)001:4503: mtshan la gtad rgya dbang bskyar dang bcas pa bstan
NK023('a)001:4504: pa'i ched dam mi nub par bya ba'i phyir me
NK023('a)001:4505: sprul zla ba gsum pa la gtad de /
NK023('a)001:4506: dbang yon gser srang phyed snam bu gos lham dbu zhwa dang bcas pa phul lo //
NK023('a)001:4507: de nas las stod lho'i rdo rje gling pa zur
NK023('a)001:4508: tshod stod pa'i dge bshes byang chub rin chen dang
NK023('a)001:4509: / byang chub blo gros gnyis la sa pho rta'i lo la gtad rgya dang bcas pa gnang /
NK023('a)001:4510: lag yon du rams zho do phul /
NK023('a)001:4511: sa mo lug gi lo la nya ri sgro phug
NK023('a)001:4512: tu bla ma gong ma'i gdan sar du dben sha
NK023('a)001:4513: rdo rje bkra shis pa yab yum dang /
NK023('a)001:4514: rdzong rtse ba dge slong lha seng la tshar gcig bgyis /
NK023('a)001:4515: lcags mo bya la bod kyi rim 'gro byas /
NK023('a)001:4516: de bla ma zur rdo rje rgyal mtshan la bka' thob byas /
NK023('a)001:4517: des bka' rgyas pa ma grub pas phyis sla chos su sogs dgos nas /
NK023('a)001:4518: rgyas par yang dben du bla ma rin po che zam bu pa la tshar gcig bgyis so //
NK023('a)001:4519: yang sa pho khyi'i lo la bdag las stod pa gnyis kyis dbang skyar zhus te /
NK023('a)001:4520: zla ba lnga pa nas brtsams nas tsaka li rgyab yig rnams kyi dag dang /
NK023('a)001:4521: phyag dpe 'thor ba rnams blo chung bdag nyid kyi
NK023('a)001:4522: go bder phyag len bzhin phyogs gcig tu sdebs nas
NK023('a)001:4523: / dbang skyar lan gnyis dang bcas pa rdzogs par
NK023('a)001:4524: rgyal gyi zla ba yan chad la grub par gnang
NK023('a)001:4525: / ngo // kun phan dge legs ldan no //
NK023('a)001:4528: // // bla ma dam pa rnams la na mo //
NK023('a)001:4529: sku lnga lhun grub ston pa'i bdag /
NK023('a)001:4530: bla ma kun bzang yab yum gyis //
NK023('a)001:4531: skal ldan 'di la dbang zhig bskur //
NK023('a)001:4532: sku gsung thugs kyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK023('a)001:4533: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK023('a)001:4534: bcom ldan rgyal ba rigs lnga yis //
NK023('a)001:4535: skal ldan 'di la dbang zhig bskur //
NK023('a)001:4536: sku gsung thugs kyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK023('a)001:4537: 'jam dpal rdo rje chos nyid ni //
NK023('a)001:4538: gsang mtshan rdo rje chos rnon po //
