NK023('a)001:4539: rjes 'jug skal ldan 'di la dbang zhig bskur //
NK023('a)001:4540: de yi rig 'dzin srungs mas byin gyis rlobs //
NK023('a)001:4541: 'og ma rnams des 'agre'o tshangs pa dung gi thor tshugs la sogs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:4542: lha dang klu yi rig 'dzin thams cad kyis //
NK023('a)001:4543: rjes 'jug skal ldan de yi rig 'dzin slob dpon dri med grags pa yang //
NK023('a)001:4544: bzhugs ni 'og min gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:4545: rjes 'jug de yi rig 'dzin slob dpon dga' rab
NK023('a)001:4546: rdo rje bzhugs ni rjes 'jug de'i rig slob dpon
NK023('a)001:4547: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bzhugs ni rjes de'i rig bla
NK023('a)001:4548: ma ku ku ra tsa bzhugs ni rjes de'i rig
NK023('a)001:4549: rgyal po u pa ra tsa bzhugs ni de'i rig
NK023('a)001:4550: rgyal po o rgyan thor cog can //
NK023('a)001:4551: bzhugs ni rjes de'i rgyal po sing h+aa ra tsa
NK023('a)001:4552: bzhugs ni rjes de'i rgyal po in+t+ra bo d+hi bzhugs
NK023('a)001:4553: ni rjes de'i mkhan po ma h+aa ra tsa bzhugs
NK023('a)001:4554: ni rjes de'i rgyal po mi 'byed seng ge bzhugs
NK023('a)001:4555: ni rjes de'i slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba bzhugs
NK023('a)001:4556: ni rjes de'i slob dpon bi ma la mi tra
NK023('a)001:4557: // bzhugs ni rjes de'i zhang chen dz+nya bzhugs ni
NK023('a)001:4558: rjes de'i dpal gyi ye shes bzhugs ni rjes de'i
NK023('a)001:4559: sangs rgyas ye shes bzhugs ni rjes de'i sru legs
NK023('a)001:4560: pa'i sgron ma bzhugs ni rjes de'i sras gzhon nu
NK023('a)001:4561: snying po bzhugs ni rjes de'i ker chung shes rab
NK023('a)001:4562: ye shes bzhugs ni rjes de'i blub ston shes rab
NK023('a)001:4563: 'phags bazhugasani rjes de'i rgya ston chos kyi gzi byin
NK023('a)001:4564: bzhugs ni rjes de'i lha rje jo 'ber bzhugs ni
NK023('a)001:4565: rjes de'i rgya 'khor lo 'bar bzhugs ni rjes de'i
NK023('a)001:4566: rgya bsod nams 'bar bzhugs ni rjes de'i rgya dkon
NK023('a)001:4567: mchog seng ge bzhugs ni rjes de'i rgya rdo rje
NK023('a)001:4568: seng ge bzhugs ni rjes de'i gu ru badz+ra ke
NK023('a)001:4569: du bzhugs ni rjes de'i bla ma g+hu na sh+ri
NK023('a)001:4570: bzhugs ni rjes de'i bla ma shes rab rgyal mtshan
NK023('a)001:4571: bzhugs ni rjes de'i bla ma tshul khrims rgyal mtshan
NK023('a)001:4572: bzhugs ni rjes de'i zur h+aam sh+aakya 'byung gnas ni
NK023('a)001:4573: // // bzhugs ni bstan pa'i bdag por bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:4574: rjes 'jug skal ldan de'i thugs sras dpal ldan bzang po yang //
NK023('a)001:4575: bzhugs ni rgyal tshab mkhan por bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:4576: rjes 'jug de'i rig 'dzin rin chen bla ma skar ma'i tshogs //
NK023('a)001:4577: sprin bral mkha' la bkod lta bu //
NK023('a)001:4578: skal ldan byang chub rin chen bdag /
NK023('a)001:4579: snying nas dga' bas gsol ba 'debs //
NK023('a)001:4580: bla ma tshul khrims rgyal mtshan pa la //
NK023('a)001:4581: rin po che zur h+aam sh+aakya 'byung gnas pa dang /
NK023('a)001:4582: lcam mo zur mo mkhan btsun dge 'bum pa dang /
NK023('a)001:4583: slob dpon dpal ldan bzang po dang gsum la /
NK023('a)001:4584: dbang phyug len phyag dpe gtad rgya dang bcas pa mdzad tra ba la /
NK023('a)001:4585: rin po che pa la gtad rgya bka' rgya can
NK023('a)001:4586: mdzad nas gtad rgya ma rtogs pa rin po che
NK023('a)001:4587: bas bdag las stod pa byang chub rin chen la
NK023('a)001:4588: gnang zhing / gtad rgya ni slob dpon pa'i drung
NK023('a)001:4589: du nan can zhus pas tshar bar gnang nas da
NK023('a)001:4590: ni zhu 'phrig chod pa lags so //
NK023('a)001:4594: mdo yongs rdzogs kyi tsa ka li ni drug gsum bco brgyad pa dang /
NK023('a)001:4595: dbang mchog rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK023('a)001:4596: 'di ngan song bag chags dang bcas pa dag par byed pa'o //
NK023('a)001:4597: bu dmyal ba'i rgyu yi ge du bsgom /
NK023('a)001:4600: du na ra ka b+hud+d+ha tsakyu pra we sha ya phata a a /
NK023('a)001:4606: kye ma kye hud gang nas byon //
NK023('a)001:4607: 'gro mgon thugs rjes bdag skyobs shig /
NK023('a)001:4608: dbang ma chog rgyal pos bsgral du gsol //
NK023('a)001:4609: slan chad mi 'chab mi bgyid do //
NK023('a)001:4610: bla mas lag tu rdo rje gtad //
NK023('a)001:4611: rigs kyi bu khyod 'dir shog cig /
NK023('a)001:4612: rang gi nyams dang bzlas nyams pa //
NK023('a)001:4613: na rag dmyal bar ltung ba las //
NK023('a)001:4614: skyabs phyir dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:4617: da ha da ha sarba na ra ka he tu h'u phatah ces brjod /
NK023('a)001:4618: ram yam kham a zhes dang /
NK023('a)001:4619: bden brjod rigs kyi bu 'di'i rgyu nyon mongs pa
NK023('a)001:4620: zhe sdang dang rkyen du srog bcad pa la sogs
NK023('a)001:4621: kyi dmyal bar skye ba'i sa bon bag chags thams
NK023('a)001:4622: cad skad cig la byang zhing dag par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:4623: / 'og ma yi dwags dud 'gro gnyis la'ang des 'agre'o //
NK023('a)001:4624: pre ta ka tsakyu mgon po yi /
NK023('a)001:4625: thugs rje chen pos bdag skyobs shig /
NK023('a)001:4626: pa tsa pa tsa sarba pre ta ka te he
NK023('a)001:4627: tu h'u phatah 'dod chags ser sna rkyen ma byin
NK023('a)001:4628: len pa las / tir+ya ka te tsakyu /
NK023('a)001:4630: ma tha ma tha sarba tir+ya ka te he du
NK023('a)001:4631: h'u phatah gti mug dang log lta la sogs dag
NK023('a)001:4632: / ngan 'gro'i spyir bcad dur ka ni yang bzlas /
NK023('a)001:4633: lugs thams cad kyi spyi dbang /
NK023('a)001:4634: gnyis ka rgyud gtso brgyad che ba /
NK023('a)001:4635: gsang bdag phyag mtshan bcu drug la /
NK023('a)001:4637: phyag rgya dbu rgyan rdo rje sdigs mdzub dang /
NK023('a)001:4638: gsang ba rdo rje dril bu dang /
NK023('a)001:4639: bum phreng cod pan thur ma me long /
NK023('a)001:4644: rin chen sna bdun ldan pa la lung bstan dang /
NK023('a)001:4645: ral gri dang mda' gzhu dang seng ge dang nyi zla'i gdan dang rdzas brgyad de bcu drug go //
NK023('a)001:4647: yungs dkar zho dur li khri dang /
NK023('a)001:4648: me long dung dkar g+hi wang bil /
NK023('a)001:4649: phyag rgya sku dbang byin ye shes te /
NK023('a)001:4650: rtsa ba dang yan lag lha dgu /
NK023('a)001:4651: rdor dril phyag mtshan dang sngags phreng las /
NK023('a)001:4655: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs nas /
NK023('a)001:4656: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rjes phyag rgyas bcings te /
NK023('a)001:4658: sha za ma stong gi tshogs skrag nas byer ba de bzhin du dbang bskur te /
NK023('a)001:4667: karma a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah ye shes rin chen dbu rgyan 'di //
NK023('a)001:4668: sangs rgyas rgyal ba kun 'dus pa //
NK023('a)001:4669: gzi byin rig sngags rgyal ba'i dbu //
NK023('a)001:4670: bu khyod gtsug na nor bu 'bar //
NK023('a)001:4671: rat+na +aa b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo phyogs bcu dus
NK023('a)001:4672: bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bden pa'i
NK023('a)001:4673: byin gyi brlabs kyis rigs kyi bu la dbu rgyan
NK023('a)001:4675: khams gsum chos kyi rgyal po'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4676: lha dang rdzas bsgrags pa 'di ka'o //
NK023('a)001:4679: 'du 'bral med pa gsang ba'i dbang gis byang chub
NK023('a)001:4680: kyi myu gu sngo skams su gyur la thug pa
NK023('a)001:4681: de sos nas / de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po can du byin gyis rlabs zhes pas /
NK023('a)001:4682: rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK023('a)001:4683: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa dang //
NK023('a)001:4684: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gis //
NK023('a)001:4685: bdag por khyod kyis dbang bskur gyis //
NK023('a)001:4686: b+hud+d+ha +aa b+hi shiny+tsa +aah bden rigs gsang ba'i dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:4687: byang chub kyi myu gu sngo skams la thug pa
NK023('a)001:4688: sos nas byang chub kyi snying po can du gyur
NK023('a)001:4689: te gsang ba'i bdag po'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:4690: / badz+ra pa ni h+aum phatah ces sogs basngagasa dbog rdor dril sbyin //
NK023('a)001:4692: rin chen sna tshogs rgyu byas la //
NK023('a)001:4693: kha dog dbyibs dang ldan pa yis //
NK023('a)001:4694: shes rab yum gyi bum pa 'dis //
NK023('a)001:4695: dbang mchog 'di ni dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:4696: b+hud+d+ha ka la k+sha a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK023('a)001:4697: bden rigs bum pas dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:4698: nad rnams bkrus nas dag cing byang ste rang gi
NK023('a)001:4699: sems spros pa dang bral zhing ye shes rnam pa
NK023('a)001:4701: 'gro ba'i don chu bo'i rgyun byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4702: byang chub yan lag me tog 'thor //
NK023('a)001:4703: khams gsum btsun pa'i bdag po ste //
NK023('a)001:4704: bde gshegs mchod pa thob pa dang //
NK023('a)001:4705: 'gro don byed par dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:4706: bden rigs me tog thod kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:4707: tshul khrims kyi tshogs yongs su rdzogs pas /
NK023('a)001:4708: ngan song gis sgrib pa'i tshogs yongs su byang ba'i dbang dam par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4709: skyabs 'gro bslab bya 'bog kyang sngar ma nges na 'dir nges par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:4711: ye shes bdag nyid cod pan 'di //
NK023('a)001:4712: klu gdug gnod pas mi bardzi zhing //
NK023('a)001:4713: 'khor ba'i nyes pas mi gos pa'i //
NK023('a)001:4714: dbang mchog de ni dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:4715: badz+ra sa t+wa a b+hi mam sa na a b+hi
NK023('a)001:4716: shiny+tsa hrih na mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin
NK023('a)001:4717: gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i bdag nyid byin
NK023('a)001:4718: gyi brlabs kyis rigs kyi bu la cod pan dang
NK023('a)001:4719: na bza' rin chen sbrul rgyan gyis dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:4720: / khams gsum du gnas kyang mya ngan las 'das nas /
NK023('a)001:4721: khams gsum na gnas pa'i bsam sbyor ngan pa'i du kha'i bag chags dang bral bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4722: sngon gyi mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK023('a)001:4723: ma rig ling tog bsal ba ltar //
NK023('a)001:4724: bu khyod kyis ni mi shes pa'i //
NK023('a)001:4725: ling tog rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK023('a)001:4726: bden rigs rnam pa lnga'i thur mas dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:4727: ma rig pa'i ling tog bsal te shes rab kyi
NK023('a)001:4728: spyan dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4729: mig rna ba sna dbug lce lus kyi mgo nas rkang sgyid bcad pa'i bar gyi skyon bsal lo //
NK023('a)001:4730: chos kun gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK023('a)001:4731: rten 'brel mthu las snang ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:4732: brjod med rang bzhin dag pas na //
NK023('a)001:4733: don dam chos nyid brjod par 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:4735: tshe dang ldan pas khyod la me long gis dbang bskur bas chos thams cad gzugs brnyan ltar /
NK023('a)001:4736: rten 'brel sgyu ma mthong ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4739: brjod pa'i don du 'bru bkod nas //
NK023('a)001:4740: gzhan don 'di la phan bya'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:4741: rgyal ba'i 'khor lo bskor bar mdzod //
NK023('a)001:4742: bden rigs 'khor los dbang bskur bas rkang lag bcom
NK023('a)001:4743: pa'i sgrib pa dag ste rdzu 'phrul gyis rkang pa
NK023('a)001:4744: dang ldan pa khams gsum thams cad du 'gro nus
NK023('a)001:4745: par gyur te 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal thabs thob
NK023('a)001:4746: par gyur cig / rtsibs bcu gnyis la rten 'brel bris zhes so //
NK023('a)001:4747: chos dung rgyas pa dbus nas ni //
NK023('a)001:4748: 'jig rten sems can skal pa la //
NK023('a)001:4749: rnal bsal sdig sbyangs chos thos pa'i //
NK023('a)001:4750: skyobs pa'i mgon po tshangs skad sgrogs //
NK023('a)001:4751: bden rigs dung gis dbang bskur bas tshangs pa'i sgra
NK023('a)001:4752: skad phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:4753: / rdo rje 'di ni sna tshogs te //
NK023('a)001:4754: las rnams rgya mtsho dbang bskur gyis //
NK023('a)001:4755: de rigs thams cad bu khyod kyis //
NK023('a)001:4757: bden rigs rdo rje rgya gram gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:4758: phyogs bcu dus gsum na gnas pa'i sngags 'chang rnams
NK023('a)001:4759: kyis rtag tu bsrung ba'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK023('a)001:4760: gyur cig / 'khor lo rin po che rtsibs stong
NK023('a)001:4761: dang ldan pa gcig gis lag tu dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:4762: gyur cig / / sangs rgyas kyi sa la nges par lung bstan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4763: lag pa g.yon du btsun mo spyan gsum rin po
NK023('a)001:4764: ches gzungs dang ting 'dzin la 'dres nas bden pa
NK023('a)001:4765: ma nor ba don dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4766: dpral bar dmag dpon rin po ches phas kyi rgol ba rnams zil gyis mnan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4767: lag pa g.yas par blon po rin po ches chos blo dang brtson 'grus su ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4768: rkang par rta mchog rin po ches mi gnas pa'i dbyings su thogs pa med par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4769: glang po rin po ches snas rigs drug sems can
NK023('a)001:4770: rnams thar pa'i gnas su 'deg nus pa'i thabs dang
NK023('a)001:4772: gtsug tu nor bu rin po ches bsam pa yid
NK023('a)001:4773: bzhin du 'grub pa'i yon tan dang ldan par gyur
NK023('a)001:4774: cig / rin po che sna bdun lus la rdzogs
NK023('a)001:4775: par dbang bskur bas phyir mi ldog par 'khor lo
NK023('a)001:4776: bsgyur ba'i rgyal po sprin phung zhes bya bar gyur
NK023('a)001:4777: cig / to // de dang mthun par slob bu
NK023('a)001:4778: rnams la rin po che sna bdun gyis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:4779: bas de lta bu'i 'khor lo bsgyur ba thob par
NK023('a)001:4780: cig / to // gyur cig / ye shes kyi
NK023('a)001:4781: ral gri lag tu byin pas dug gsum 'khrugs pa
NK023('a)001:4782: rgyun bcad de bag chags thams cad byang bar gyur
NK023('a)001:4783: cig / to // gyur cig / to // de
NK023('a)001:4784: bzhin slob bu la'ang bskur bas de bzhin du dbang
NK023('a)001:4786: thabs shes rab kyi mda' gzhu lag tu gtad de
NK023('a)001:4787: dbang bskur bas thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel
NK023('a)001:4788: nas / ye shes dag pa'i rtse mo la gnas par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:4789: de bzhin du slob bu la yang dbang bskur bas de bzhin du dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4790: brjid pa'i seng ge shin tu myur ba yis //
NK023('a)001:4791: gzugs can gcig ni lag tu byin pa yis //
NK023('a)001:4792: gsung rab rgya mtsho kun gyis sgra sgrogs te //
NK023('a)001:4793: log pa'i phyogs kun zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK023('a)001:4794: badz+ra sing ha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aumh bden rigs seng
NK023('a)001:4795: ges dbang bskur bas gsung rab rgya mtsho'i sgra skad
NK023('a)001:4796: sgrogs pas / log pa'i phyogs thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang dang /
NK023('a)001:4797: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po zhes bya bar gyur to //
NK023('a)001:4798: de bzhin du dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4799: steng phyogs mnga' mdzad thugs rje nyi zla'i bdal //
NK023('a)001:4800: thugs rje mun sel thugs rje zla ba'i 'od //
NK023('a)001:4801: stong gsum mun pa dus gcig bsal nas ni //
NK023('a)001:4802: 'jig rten kun tu snang ba bskyed par shog /
NK023('a)001:4804: bden rigs nyi zlas dbang bskur bas skye 'gro ma
NK023('a)001:4805: lus pa'i sems can gyi rgyud la ye shes kyi
NK023('a)001:4806: 'od zer gyis dus dang rnam pa thams cad du
NK023('a)001:4807: shar te dro zhing 'char ba dang khams gsum gyi
NK023('a)001:4808: mun pa dus dang rnam pa thams cad du sel
NK023('a)001:4809: ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:4810: gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyas nas ni //
NK023('a)001:4811: yun ring gnas par gyur pa yi //
NK023('a)001:4812: bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang mchog ni //
NK023('a)001:4813: gnang ba chen po sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:4814: yungs dkar rdo rje bgegs mchog 'dul //
NK023('a)001:4815: bgegs rnams 'joms pa'i mthu stobs ldan //
NK023('a)001:4816: dgra bgegs kun las rgyal ba yis //
NK023('a)001:4817: byin rlabs chen po'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:4818: zho ni kun gyis snying por gyur pa ste //
NK023('a)001:4819: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtogs te //
NK023('a)001:4820: yon tan kun gyi snying por gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:4821: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir zhi bar shog /
NK023('a)001:4822: dur ba tshe ni 'phel bar byed pa ste //
NK023('a)001:4823: rdo rje tshe ni rab grub pas //
NK023('a)001:4824: skye shi'i sdug bsngal rgyun bcad de //
NK023('a)001:4825: dur ba'i bkra shis de ni tshe brtan shog /
NK023('a)001:4826: dur ba'i bkra shis tshe ni rab brtan no //
NK023('a)001:4827: li khri dmar ba dbang gi rin chen te //
NK023('a)001:4828: chos rnams ma lus dbang du gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:4829: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu brtan gyur pa //
NK023('a)001:4830: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir brtan par shog /
NK023('a)001:4831: dung gis chos kyi sgra rnams sgrog pa'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:4832: yon tan rgya mtsho bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK023('a)001:4833: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK023('a)001:4834: bkra shis de ni tshig la longs spyod shog /
NK023('a)001:4835: g+hi wang dug gsum 'joms pa'i sman yin te //
NK023('a)001:4836: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs gyur te //
NK023('a)001:4837: nyon mongs zug rngu med par gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:4838: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK023('a)001:4839: me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK023('a)001:4840: ye shes rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK023('a)001:4841: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK023('a)001:4842: bkra shis de ni tshigs la longs spyod shog /
NK023('a)001:4843: bil ba rgyu rkyen 'bras bu bcas pa'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:4844: 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa kun //
NK023('a)001:4845: byang chub snying po mchog tu gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:4846: bkra shis de ni 'jig rten 'grub par shog /
NK023('a)001:4847: phyag na rdo rje'i mchog dbang rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:4850: // // lha mi'i theg pa'i rdzas dbang phyi dbang nas btus pa ni /
NK023('a)001:4851: ka rin po che'i cod pan dbu rgyan gyis dbang
NK023('a)001:4852: bskur bas chos kyi rgyal tshab chen po byed pa'i
NK023('a)001:4853: dbang dang ldan par gyur cig kha /
NK023('a)001:4854: a ma yum gyi phyag gis reg cing dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:4855: bas slob ma 'di zhes bya ba nyon mongs pa
NK023('a)001:4856: na tsa'i sdug bsngal thams cad zhi bar gyur cig
NK023('a)001:4857: ga / seng ge phru gu zung gcig gis dbang
NK023('a)001:4858: bskur bas sdang ba'i phyogs zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:4860: glang po rin po che phru gu zung gcig gis
NK023('a)001:4861: dbang bskur bas 'jig rten 'degs pa'i stobs dang ldan
NK023('a)001:4862: pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig ca /
NK023('a)001:4863: na bza' ka shi'i ras kyis dbang bskur bas mkhyen
NK023('a)001:4864: pa'i ye shes gsal zhing ma 'dres pa'i dbang dang
NK023('a)001:4866: rdzas bum pa'i chu 'dis dbang bskur bas slob ma
NK023('a)001:4867: 'di yi nyon mongs pa bag chags kyi dri ma
NK023('a)001:4868: dag pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig ja /
NK023('a)001:4869: ming gi dbang bskur bas shes bya ye shes la
NK023('a)001:4870: ma rmongs pa dbang gzhon nu don 'grub ltar du
NK023('a)001:4871: dbang thob par gyur cig nya /
NK023('a)001:4872: rgyan gyi bye brag gis dbang bskur bas 'gro ba
NK023('a)001:4873: thams cad shes pa dang ldan par byed pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:4874: dam pa thob par gyur cig ta /
NK023('a)001:4875: yig shing gi dbang bskur ba chos kyi sgra sgrogs pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig tha /
NK023('a)001:4876: mda' gzhu ste gnam rus dbang bskur bas snyan pa'i
NK023('a)001:4877: sgra sgrogs shing bdud dpung 'dul ba'i 'phong rtsal dang
NK023('a)001:4879: btsun mo'i dbang bskur bas slob ma 'dis theg pa
NK023('a)001:4880: mtho ris kyis bstan pa'i rigs mi nub cing ji
NK023('a)001:4881: ltar 'dul ba bzhin du 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i
NK023('a)001:4883: de ltar dbang bcu gcig ni lha mi mtho ris kyi chas su bcug pa'o //
NK023('a)001:4884: kye kye lha mi'i theg pa rdzas dbang yi ge
NK023('a)001:4885: 'di rnams rgya yig bod yig cha gnyis byung ba
NK023('a)001:4886: ni / thog ma rgya yig kun bzang /
NK023('a)001:4887: longs sku lha yul gyi yig 'bru mtshon /
NK023('a)001:4888: de nas bod yig thub pa sprul sku'i bstan pa
NK023('a)001:4889: phyogs dus kun tu rgyas nas thams cad skad du
NK023('a)001:4890: chos ston pas thos pa mtshon /
NK023('a)001:4891: tsa ka'i ka kha'i dbang gis skabs der yig 'bru rgyal bu don 'grub spyi bor bkod pa /
NK023('a)001:4892: slob dpon slob ma dang bcas pa ste bum pa
NK023('a)001:4893: rin po che yi ge dang bcas pa yod pa
NK023('a)001:4894: nas bla ma dang tsa ka la thim pa dang
NK023('a)001:4895: slob ma la thim pas yang mar me gcig la
NK023('a)001:4896: gnyis su mched pa lta bu /
NK023('a)001:4897: dbang grub nas bla ma'i nus pa dang tsa ka
NK023('a)001:4898: li'i rab gnas gso zhing bum chu btung khrus bya'o
NK023('a)001:4900: a ni ma skyes ye shes yin //
NK023('a)001:4901: rang bzhin thams cad stong par ston //
NK023('a)001:4902: ka ni bya ba'i ye shes te //
NK023('a)001:4903: las kyi thams cad grol bar bshad //
NK023('a)001:4904: kha ni khyab par byed pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4905: mi dmigs thams cad grol bar ston //
NK023('a)001:4906: ga ni don du gyur pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4907: yul med thams cad grol bar ston //
NK023('a)001:4908: g+ha ni gnas pa'i sgo yin te //
NK023('a)001:4909: gcig tu ma nges grol bar ston //
NK023('a)001:4910: nga ni 'dzin pa med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4911: 'dzin bral thams cad grol bar ston //
NK023('a)001:4912: tsa ni 'gag pa med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4913: cir yang snang bas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4914: tsha ni 'da' ba med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4915: bral ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4916: dza ni ma byung ba yi sgo //
NK023('a)001:4917: mi gnas pas ni thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4918: dz+ha ni rnyog pa med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4919: dri ma dag pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4920: nya ni dpyod dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4921: bya ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4922: ta ni tha snyad med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4923: brjod pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4924: tha ni rten dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4925: gnas pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4926: da ni rtog dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4927: len pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4928: d+ha ni rang bzhin med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4929: mtshan nyid med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4930: na ni yul dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4931: 'dzin pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4932: ta ni nga rgyal med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4933: ngo bo med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4934: tha ni sgyu rtsal med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4935: byed pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4936: da ni 'dren pa med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4937: rtsod pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4938: d+ha ni slu ba med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4939: sgyu ma thams cad grol bar byed //
NK023('a)001:4940: na ni kun tu gyur pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4941: g.yo ba skyobs pa'i las rnams grol //
NK023('a)001:4942: pa ni nges par 'byung ba'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4943: 'gags pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4944: pha ni dngos po med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4945: cir yang med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4946: ba ni brjod pa med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4947: brjod pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4948: b+ha ni b+ha ga ta'i rdul dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4949: rtog pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4950: ma ni chags pa med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4951: rtag pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4952: ya ni chags pa med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4953: gos pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4954: wa ni rgyu rkyen med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4955: 'bras bu med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4956: ra ni rkyen dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4957: dor ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4958: la ni blang ba med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4959: yon tan med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4960: sha ni spros pa bral ba'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4961: zhi bas thams cad grol bar byed //
NK023('a)001:4962: sha ni khur dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4963: lci ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4964: sa ni yang dag gsang ba'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4965: nges pa thams cad grol bar byed //
NK023('a)001:4966: ha ni rgyud dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4967: rkyen dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4968: k+sha ni khams dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4969: mtshan nyid med pas grol bar byed //
NK023('a)001:4970: i i ni mthong ba med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4971: gzugs dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4972: u +au ni thos pa med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4973: sgra dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4974: e +aee ni tshor ba med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4975: dri dang bral bas grol bar byed //
NK023('a)001:4976: o +aoo ni tshor ba med pa'i sgo //
NK023('a)001:4977: reg dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4979: cir yang snang bas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4980: ces pa'i 'grel par yul dang yul can gnyis su bshad //
NK023('a)001:4981: cir yang snang bas thams cad grol //
NK023('a)001:4983: yod mthong snang grags chos thams cad //
NK023('a)001:4984: yi ge'i tshogs su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK023('a)001:4985: yi ger ma gyur gang yang med //
NK023('a)001:4986: h'u chos nyid nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK023('a)001:4987: yig 'bru sna tshogs phra bkod pas //
NK023('a)001:4988: dus gsum rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:4992: rdo rje rigs kyi zhing du grags //
NK023('a)001:4993: zhes gsungs de rnams dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:4995: gsung rab gnas las gzugs kyi sku //
NK023('a)001:4996: chos kyi sku ru mnga' gsol to /
NK023('a)001:4998: ka ni dbang byed sgrol ba'o //
NK023('a)001:5000: khams gsum gyis sems can thams cad la dbang byed cing /
NK023('a)001:5001: nyon mongs pa dang sgrol bar byed pa lags te /
NK023('a)001:5002: de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos kyi sku'i don gyis gsung gis gzugs brnyan du byung ba'i tshe /
NK023('a)001:5003: tshig gis gsung 'dis kyang sems can thams cad la
NK023('a)001:5004: dbang byed cing nyon mongs pa las sgrol ba'i dbang
NK023('a)001:5005: dang ldan par gyur cig kha /
NK023('a)001:5006: kha ni khams gsum kun gyis brgyan //
NK023('a)001:5008: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyi rgyan du byung ba yin te /
NK023('a)001:5009: de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis don gyi gsung gi gzugs
NK023('a)001:5010: brnyan tshig gi gsung 'dis sems can gyi rgyan du
NK023('a)001:5011: gyur te / 'khor ba las sgrol bar mdzad pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig ga /
NK023('a)001:5012: ga ni ma chags dag par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:5014: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5015: ci la ma chags shing dag par dag pa yin
NK023('a)001:5016: pas / de'i byin brlabs kyi chos kyi sku'i gsungs
NK023('a)001:5017: 'dis kyang ci la yang ma chags shing rnam par
NK023('a)001:5018: dag pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig nga /
NK023('a)001:5019: nga ni nga med nga las rgyal //
NK023('a)001:5021: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5022: mnyam pa'i ngang las ma g.yos shing mtshan ma las
NK023('a)001:5024: de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos dbyings mnyam pa nyid
NK023('a)001:5025: kyi ngang las ma g.yos shing mtshan ma las rgyal
NK023('a)001:5026: ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig ca /
NK023('a)001:5027: ca ni gnyis med don rtogs te //
NK023('a)001:5029: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5030: de ni mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med pa gnyis
NK023('a)001:5031: su med pa'i don yin te /
NK023('a)001:5032: de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos kyi sku mtshan ma
NK023('a)001:5033: dang mtshan ma med pa gnyis su med pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:5034: dang ldan par gyur cig cha /
NK023('a)001:5035: cha ni thabs dang shes rab ste //
NK023('a)001:5037: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5038: las thabs dang shes rab kyi sprul pa ji snyed
NK023('a)001:5039: gcig byung nas 'gro ba'i don byed pa yin te
NK023('a)001:5040: / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos sku thabs dang
NK023('a)001:5041: shes rab zung du 'brel pa'i dbang dang ldan par
NK023('a)001:5042: / gyur cig ja / ja ni ma gos dag par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:5044: dus gsum gyi chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5045: de'i bag chags kyis ma gos zhing rnam par dag
NK023('a)001:5046: pa yin te / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis /
NK023('a)001:5047: chos kyi sku la bag chags kyis ma gos zhing
NK023('a)001:5048: dag pa'i dbang dam pa dang ldan par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:5049: nya / nya ni chos nyid gdar sha gcod //
NK023('a)001:5051: dus gsum du chos nyid rgya mtsho dang 'dra ba
NK023('a)001:5052: la rig pa'i ye shes dang 'dra bas gdar sha
NK023('a)001:5054: de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos nyid kyi rgya mtsho
NK023('a)001:5055: la rig pa'i ye shes kyi dbang dang ldan par
NK023('a)001:5056: gyur cig ta / ta ni mkhas pa'i 'od zer can //
NK023('a)001:5058: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5059: de las thugs rje'i 'od zer 'byung ba yin te
NK023('a)001:5060: / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos kyi sku bde
NK023('a)001:5061: ba chen po thugs rje'i 'od zer 'byung ba dbang
NK023('a)001:5062: dang ldan par gyur cig tha /
NK023('a)001:5063: tha ni dkon mchog 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK023('a)001:5065: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5066: las dgongs pa zab mo'i ye shes 'byung ba yin
NK023('a)001:5067: te / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos kyi sku'i
NK023('a)001:5068: dgongs pa zab mo'i ye shes 'byung ba'i dbang dang
NK023('a)001:5070: da ni rgyu 'bras gnyis med pa //
NK023('a)001:5072: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5073: las rgyu'i chos dang 'bras bu'i chos gnyis su med
NK023('a)001:5074: pa yin te / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis /
NK023('a)001:5075: chos kyi 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gtan nas spongs te
NK023('a)001:5076: ngang gis bde ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:5077: na / na ni sdug bsngal med pas bde //
NK023('a)001:5079: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5080: las 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal med cing ngang gis bde
NK023('a)001:5081: ba yin te / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos
NK023('a)001:5082: kyi sku'i byin gyis brlabs cing 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal
NK023('a)001:5083: gtan nas spangs te ngang gi bde ba'i dbang dang
NK023('a)001:5085: pa ni thams cad bskyed par byed //
NK023('a)001:5087: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po las rig pa'i ye shes bskyed pa yin te /
NK023('a)001:5089: chos kyi sku'i gsung 'di mthong ba tsam gyis gzhan
NK023('a)001:5090: rig pa'i ye shes bskyed pa'i dbang dang ldan par
NK023('a)001:5091: gyur cig pha / pha ni pha rol phyin ma nas //
NK023('a)001:5093: chos kyi sku 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad kyi
NK023('a)001:5094: pha rol tu phyin cing mi gnas pa'i mya ngan
NK023('a)001:5096: de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos kyi sku bde ba
NK023('a)001:5097: chen po 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyi pha rol tu
NK023('a)001:5098: phyin cing mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK023('a)001:5099: dbang dang ldan par gyur cig ba /
NK023('a)001:5100: ba ni bde ba chen po ste //
NK023('a)001:5102: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5103: de ni dngos po dang mtshan ma thams cad la
NK023('a)001:5104: mnyam pa chen po'i ngang du bde ba'i dbang dang
NK023('a)001:5106: ma ni srid gsum yongs kyi ma //
NK023('a)001:5108: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5109: de yang kun gyi gzhi mar gyur pa yin te
NK023('a)001:5110: / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos kyi sku srid
NK023('a)001:5111: pa gsum yongs las rgyal zhing kun gyi gzhi mar
NK023('a)001:5112: gyur pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig tsa /
NK023('a)001:5115: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5116: de ni sku dang ye shes stobs dang mi 'jigs
NK023('a)001:5117: pa lags pa 'du 'bral med pa'i gnas yin te
NK023('a)001:5118: / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos kyi sku dang
NK023('a)001:5119: 'du 'bral med pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:5120: / tsha / tsha ni don dam lus la rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:5122: don dam pa chos kyi sku ni rgyu dang 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rdzogs pa yin te /
NK023('a)001:5123: de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos kyi sku'i rgyu dang
NK023('a)001:5124: 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:5125: dza / dza ni 'bar ba'i yum la gnas //
NK023('a)001:5127: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5128: de thugs rjes 'od zer 'byung ba'i gnas yin te
NK023('a)001:5129: / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos kyi sku thugs
NK023('a)001:5130: rje 'od zer 'byung ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK023('a)001:5131: / cig wa / wa ni mya ngan thams cad 'dul //
NK023('a)001:5133: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5134: de 'khor ba'i mya ngan thams cad 'dul ba yin
NK023('a)001:5135: te / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos kyi sku
NK023('a)001:5136: las 'khor ba'i mya ngan thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang
NK023('a)001:5137: dang ldan par gyur cig zha /
NK023('a)001:5138: zha ni gzhal yas khang chen po //
NK023('a)001:5140: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5141: de ni thams cad kyi gnas dang gzhal yas khang
NK023('a)001:5142: dang bde ba chen por gyur pa yin te /
NK023('a)001:5144: gnas dang gzhal yas khang bde ba chen po'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig za /
NK023('a)001:5145: za ni skye med chos la 'phags //
NK023('a)001:5147: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5148: de ni chos thams cad rgyu rkyen las ma skyes
NK023('a)001:5149: pa yin te / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis /
NK023('a)001:5150: chos nyid gsal ba'i ye shes kyis nyon mongs pa
NK023('a)001:5151: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'i dbang dang ldan
NK023('a)001:5153: 'a ni goms pa'i tshogs la brtson //
NK023('a)001:5155: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po'i ngang du brtson pa yin te /
NK023('a)001:5157: gsung gi tshogs rang bzhin med par sgra sgrogs pa
NK023('a)001:5158: la goms pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig ya
NK023('a)001:5159: / ya ni thar byed pho nya'i bdag /
NK023('a)001:5161: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5162: de las gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis kyis pho nya
NK023('a)001:5163: byung nas 'gro ba sems can gyi don byed pa
NK023('a)001:5164: yin te / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis /
NK023('a)001:5165: chos kyi sku las sprul pa'i sku 'byung nas 'gro
NK023('a)001:5166: ba sems can gyi don byed pa'i dbang dang ldan
NK023('a)001:5168: ra ni spyod byed yul la dbang //
NK023('a)001:5170: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5171: de ni ye shes kyi spyad par bya ba'i yul
NK023('a)001:5172: yin te / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis /
NK023('a)001:5173: chos kyi ye shes kyi spyod pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig la /
NK023('a)001:5174: la ni mnyam nyid sprul pa'i sku //
NK023('a)001:5176: dus gsum du chos kyi sku mnyam pa nyid la
NK023('a)001:5177: ye shes sprul pa'i sku byung nas sems can gyi
NK023('a)001:5180: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid las ye shes sprul pa'i
NK023('a)001:5181: skur byung nas 'gro ba sems can gyi don byed
NK023('a)001:5182: pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig sha /
NK023('a)001:5183: sha ni snang byed mkha' la shar //
NK023('a)001:5185: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po'i
NK023('a)001:5186: mkha' las ye shes kyi bye brag ji snyed cig
NK023('a)001:5187: shar nas 'gro ba sems can gyi don byed pa
NK023('a)001:5188: yin te / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis chos kyi
NK023('a)001:5189: sku las ye shes kyi bye brag shar nas sems
NK023('a)001:5190: can gyi don byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK023('a)001:5191: yin te / cig sa / sa ni 'khor lo'i rang bzhin te //
NK023('a)001:5193: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK023('a)001:5194: de las chos kyi 'khor lo la sogs pa sna
NK023('a)001:5195: tshogs byung nas 'gro ba sems can gyi don byed
NK023('a)001:5196: pa yin te / de'i byin gyi rlabs kyis /
NK023('a)001:5197: thugs phyag mtshan sna tshogs byung nas 'gro ba sems
NK023('a)001:5198: can gyi don byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK023('a)001:5199: cig ha / ha ni thabs kyi mkha' dbyings nas byon //
NK023('a)001:5201: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po'i
NK023('a)001:5202: dbyings nas thabs mkhas pa'i mdzad spyod bsam gyis mi
NK023('a)001:5203: khyab pas 'gro ba sems can gyi don mthar phyin
NK023('a)001:5204: pa yin te / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis /
NK023('a)001:5205: chos kyi skus 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig a /
NK023('a)001:5206: a ni skye med chos kyi dbyings //
NK023('a)001:5208: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po'i
NK023('a)001:5209: chos kyi dbyings rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i dbyings nas
NK023('a)001:5210: 'gro ba'i don ma 'gags par shar nas sems can
NK023('a)001:5211: gyi don mthar phyin pa yin te /
NK023('a)001:5213: chos kyi skus 'gro ba sems can gyi don byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5214: phyi mtshams la sgo rgyal chen dang dbus rnam snang gi tsa ka'i 'dod gsol ni /
NK023('a)001:5215: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK023('a)001:5216: chos dbyings rnam dag rdo rje'i sku //
NK023('a)001:5217: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya mdzad //
NK023('a)001:5218: phyag 'tshal rnam par snang mdzad la'o //
NK023('a)001:5219: de yi dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:5221: dpal ldan rgyal po yul 'khor srung //
NK023('a)001:5222: phyag mtshan rin chen pi wam bsnams //
NK023('a)001:5223: dri za bsnol ba'i khri la bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:5224: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5226: tri ta ra tsa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5227: dpal ldan rgyal po 'phags skyes po //
NK023('a)001:5228: phyag mtshan ral gri 'bar ba bsnams //
NK023('a)001:5229: gshin rje bsnol ba'i khri la bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:5230: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5232: b+he tu ta ka ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5233: dpal ldan rgyal po spyan mi bzang //
NK023('a)001:5234: phyag mtshan ri rab mchod rten bsnams //
NK023('a)001:5235: klu rnams bsnol ba'i khri la bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:5236: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5238: b+he tu b+hag k+sha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5239: dpal ldan rgyal po rnam thos sras //
NK023('a)001:5240: phyag mtshan rin chen be con 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:5241: gnod sbyin bsnol ba'i khri la bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:5242: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5244: b+he sh+r+aa ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5246: res 'ga' sngon du 'gro ba tshogs ma bu'i dkyil 'khor bdun mdzad /
NK023('a)001:5248: theg pa chen po'i phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la skyabs 'agro'ang byed /
NK023('a)001:5249: phyi mtshams la phyogs skyong bcu dang rgyal chen bzhi ka bkod /
NK023('a)001:5250: dkyil 'khor bdun gyi rnam grangs la /
NK023('a)001:5251: bsod nams rnal 'byor sbyin gyi dkyil 'khor dang gcig /
NK023('a)001:5252: 'bar ba mtshams kyi dkyil 'khor dang gnyis /
NK023('a)001:5253: phrin las mtshams sbyor gyi dkyil 'khor dang gsum /
NK023('a)001:5254: rtsa ba zhi khro las kyi dkyil 'khor dang bzhi /
NK023('a)001:5255: gzhung mthun mchod pa'i dkyil 'khor dang lnga /
NK023('a)001:5256: longs spyod tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang drug /
NK023('a)001:5257: lhag ma mjug sdud kyi dkyil 'khor dang bdun no //
NK023('a)001:5258: gtso bo rnams snang rdor sems phyag rdor sogs skabs sbyar sngon 'gro mtshams i thi /
NK023('a)001:5259: lha mi'i theg pa'i lha dbang ni //
NK023('a)001:5260: rgya che rol par rgyal bu nyid //
NK023('a)001:5261: lha khang byon pa'i skabs dang sbyar //
NK023('a)001:5262: sangs rgyas rnams ni lhas phyag 'bul //
NK023('a)001:5263: sems can kun gyis lha mchod 'os //
NK023('a)001:5264: khams gsum lhas skyabs dpal 'byor thob //
NK023('a)001:5266: mchod 'os rnams kyis mchod gnas dam pa lha'i lha mchog de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:5267: lha mi'i gtso bo 'og min du dbang phyug chen
NK023('a)001:5268: po na longs spyod rdzogs pa sku mdog dkar po
NK023('a)001:5269: / rnam par snang mdzad kun rig ston pa /
NK023('a)001:5270: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya'am chos 'chad mdzad pas
NK023('a)001:5271: sems can thams cad ngan song dang ngan 'gro sbyong
NK023('a)001:5272: zhing mngon shes dus gsum da ltar gsal ba /
NK023('a)001:5273: rdzu 'phrul dang bcas pa ster ba /
NK023('a)001:5274: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5276: bden rigs phyogs dus kun tu mi'i khyu mchog mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams na /
NK023('a)001:5277: sprul pa'i sku sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa'am mi 'khrugs
NK023('a)001:5278: pa de sku mdog mthing kha g.yon rdo rje mnyam
NK023('a)001:5279: bzhag dang / g.yas kyi phyag sa gnon mdzad par bstan pa /
NK023('a)001:5283: dran pa thams cad kyis mi ngas dang sdig sgrib
NK023('a)001:5284: dang ngan 'gro thams cad sel cing mtho ris thar
NK023('a)001:5285: pa thob par bka' stsal par mdzad pa /
NK023('a)001:5286: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5287: bden rigs steng gi lha rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa /
NK023('a)001:5289: sa gnon mnyam bzhag lhung bzed gang ba can yin te /
NK023('a)001:5290: de nyid kyis sngon sbyin pa'i bsod nams thob pa las bsngosa te /
NK023('a)001:5291: nyid mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas kyi sa brnyes pa na /
NK023('a)001:5292: nyid kyis 'khor rnams 'tsho bas mi brel bas smon
NK023('a)001:5293: lam 'grub pa'i byin rlabs kyis stong la bsnyen gnas
NK023('a)001:5294: srungs pas / phyogs dus gnas skabs thams cad du mu ge'i bskal pa nas thar bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5295: bden rigs nya'i lha snang ba mtha' yas sku mdog
NK023('a)001:5296: dmar po phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag tshe bum gang ba
NK023('a)001:5298: de nyid kyis sngon thos bsam bsgoms pa'i shes rab kyis bsod nams thob pa la bsngosa te /
NK023('a)001:5299: de nyid mngon par sangs rgyas kyi sa brnyes pa
NK023('a)001:5300: na nyid kyi 'khor rnams kyis zhing khams bde ba
NK023('a)001:5301: can du phyir mi bzlog pa'i 'phags pa thob par
NK023('a)001:5302: smon lam grub pa'i byin rlabs kyis nya la bsnyen
NK023('a)001:5303: gnas bgyis pas phyogs dus gnas skabs thams cad du
NK023('a)001:5304: mtshon gyi bskal pa nas thar bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5305: bden rigs tshes brgyad sman gyi lha bee d+aur+ya sku mdog mthing kha g.yas mchog sbyin a ru ra /
NK023('a)001:5306: g.yon mnyam bzhag gi steng du bdud rtsi lhung bzed can yin te /
NK023('a)001:5307: de'i sngon gyi smon lam chen po'i mthu las gang gis de'i mtshan lan bdun brjod cing /
NK023('a)001:5308: phyag 'tshal bskor ba dang bsnyen gnas bgyis pas phyogs dus gnas skabs thams cad du /
NK023('a)001:5309: rmi lam mtshan ma rtsub pa dang mi ngas dang
NK023('a)001:5310: the tshom yid gnyis dang nad kyis bskal pa las
NK023('a)001:5311: thar bar gyur cig bden rigs nyin byed shar ba
NK023('a)001:5312: shar gyi phyogs / shar phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub
NK023('a)001:5313: pa'i chos dang chos ldan gang zag skyong bar 'dzam
NK023('a)001:5314: bu'i gling du mnga' gsol ba /
NK023('a)001:5315: dkar po pi wam sgrog pa lha'i rgyal po yul
NK023('a)001:5316: 'khor bsrung 'khor bcas de'i dbang mchog thob par shog
NK023('a)001:5317: / bden rigs nyin byed 'phel ba lho yi phyogs //
NK023('a)001:5318: lho phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang chos
NK023('a)001:5319: ldan dang gang zag skyong bar 'dzam bu'i gling du
NK023('a)001:5320: mnga' gsol ba / sngon po ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK023('a)001:5321: grul bum gyi rgyal po 'phags skyes pa 'khor bcas de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5322: bden rigs nyin byed bgrod pa nub kyi phyogs //
NK023('a)001:5323: nub phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang chos
NK023('a)001:5324: ldan dang gang zag skyong bar 'dzam bu'i gling du
NK023('a)001:5325: mnga' gsol ba / dmar po mchod rten sbrul zhags can //
NK023('a)001:5326: klu'i rgyal po mig ngan po 'khor bcas de'i dbang
NK023('a)001:5327: mchog thob par shog bden rigs dbus na lhun por
NK023('a)001:5328: nyi ma byang // byang phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub
NK023('a)001:5329: pa'i chos dang chos ldan dang gang zag skyong bar
NK023('a)001:5330: 'dzam bu'ii gling du mnga' gsol ba /
NK023('a)001:5331: gser ljang rgyal mtshan dang ne'u le can /
NK023('a)001:5332: gnod sbyin gyi rgyal po rnam pas mang thos kyi bu 'khor bcas de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5333: bden rigs shar phyogs lha'i dbang po brgya byin sku
NK023('a)001:5334: mdog dkar po phyag g.yas pa nor bu rin po
NK023('a)001:5335: che bsnams nas mchod sbyin brgya gtong ba thugs la
NK023('a)001:5336: ye shes mnga' ba'i rtags su /
NK023('a)001:5337: g.yon rdo rje gdengs pas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5338: btsun mo ko'u rgyud mang bsnams pa 'gro ba sems
NK023('a)001:5339: can thams cad la bde ba ster bar mdzad pa
NK023('a)001:5340: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5341: yum du shes rab phar phyin la //
NK023('a)001:5342: phyag 'tshal de ni kun mkhyen gyis //
NK023('a)001:5343: ye shes la ni phyag 'tshal gces //
NK023('a)001:5344: ko 'u shi ka la bka' stsal //
NK023('a)001:5345: tshangs pa sku ste khyab 'jug gsung //
NK023('a)001:5346: dbang phyug thugs gces 'dod pa bkod //
NK023('a)001:5347: de re'ang yum mngag pho nya rtse'o //
NK023('a)001:5348: rgyal chen bcas pas mtho ris bsdus //
NK023('a)001:5349: rgyal mchog lnga po gcig la'ang bskor //
NK023('a)001:5350: snying po dur rga ka nir bsdus /
NK023('a)001:5351: bden rigs shar gyi gling gi g.yas phyogs na /
NK023('a)001:5352: brgya byin gyi mngag gzhugs pa /
NK023('a)001:5353: 'gro ba kun gyi yid du 'ong ba'i lha kun
NK023('a)001:5354: tu snang ba sku mdog ljang khu phyag g.yas na
NK023('a)001:5356: 'gro ba kun gyi nyon mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa /
NK023('a)001:5357: de'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:5359: lha chen 'di rnams gtso bo ri rab la rgyab gtad pa'i g.yas dang /
NK023('a)001:5360: gtso bo sangs rgyas 'khor la gzigs pa'i g.yas te 'di shar lho'o //
NK023('a)001:5361: bden rigs shar gyi gling gis g.yon phyogs na brgya
NK023('a)001:5362: byin gyi pho nya rab tu myur ba'i shugs can
NK023('a)001:5363: / sku mdog sngon mo phyag g.yas na mdung rtse gsum pa bsnams pa /
NK023('a)001:5364: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal las grol ba /
NK023('a)001:5365: de'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:5367: bden rigs lho phyogs 'dzam bu'i gling na lha tshangs
NK023('a)001:5368: pa sku mdog ser po 'dod khams kyi nyon mongs
NK023('a)001:5369: pa'i tsha ba'i sdug bsngal dang bral zhing /
NK023('a)001:5370: 'khor ba gyod 'khrin dang 'dra ba'i skyon gyis ma gos pas /
NK023('a)001:5371: tshangs pa 'gu d+he spyi blugs g.yas kyi phyag gis bsnams pa /
NK023('a)001:5372: btsun mo tshangs ma phyag g.yon 'gu d+he bsnams pa de'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya /
NK023('a)001:5374: lho yi gling gi g.yon phyogs na lha tshangs pa'i mngag gzhug byed pa /
NK023('a)001:5375: 'gro ba'i yid du 'ong bas sku mdog ljang sngon
NK023('a)001:5376: phyag g.yas pas ral gri bsnams pas nyon mongs pa'i
NK023('a)001:5378: g.yon sdigs mdzub bgegs la ston pa de'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:5380: lho'i gling gi g.yon phyogs na /
NK023('a)001:5381: lha tshangs pa'i pho nya mngag pa yin te /
NK023('a)001:5382: sku mdog dmar po g.yas na pad ma dkar po bsnams pa 'gro ba'i nyon mongs sel ba /
NK023('a)001:5383: de'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:5386: thugs kyis kun tu khyab pa phrin las kyis kun tu khyab pas na'ang khyab 'jug /
NK023('a)001:5387: sku mdog mthing kha phyag na 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK023('a)001:5388: btsun mo dpal lha mo phyag na gsal shing bsnams pa de'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:5390: nub kyi gling gi g.yas phyogs na lha khyab 'jug
NK023('a)001:5391: gi mngag gzhugs pa rdo rje bde ba sku mdog
NK023('a)001:5392: dkar ljang du bzhugs pa phyag g.yas na nyon mongs
NK023('a)001:5393: pa gcod pa'i mche ba bsnams pa /
NK023('a)001:5394: de'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:5396: nub kyi gling gi g.yon phyogs na /
NK023('a)001:5397: pho nya rdo rje ded dpon sku mdog ljang ser
NK023('a)001:5398: phyag g.yas na 'khor lo bsnams pa 'gro ba sems
NK023('a)001:5399: can rnams la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul
NK023('a)001:5400: ba / de'i dbang mchog bskur bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:5402: byang phyogs na lha dbang phyug chen po sku mdog
NK023('a)001:5403: dmar po lha yi rgyal po yin pa'i phyir na
NK023('a)001:5404: dbang phyug / g.yas na dri shul rtse gsum dug gsum thams cad 'joms par byed pa /
NK023('a)001:5405: btsun mo dka' thub bzlog pa'i rgyal mo phyag na
NK023('a)001:5406: pad+ma kha phye ba bsnams pa de'i dbang mchog thob
NK023('a)001:5407: par shog / a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:5408: byang gi gling gi g.yas phyogs na lha dbang phyug chen po'i mngag gzhugs pa /
NK023('a)001:5409: ded dpon nag po mdung thogs pas /
NK023('a)001:5410: 'gro ba sams can sdug bsngal las sgrol bar bskul ba de'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:5412: byang gi gling gi g.yon phyogs na lha dbang phyug
NK023('a)001:5413: chen po'i pho nya rnam pa drang srong khros pa'i
NK023('a)001:5414: cha lugs can sku mdog dkar po phyag g.yas g.yon
NK023('a)001:5415: mda' gzhu 'gengs pas 'gro ba sems can kun la
NK023('a)001:5416: rnam par snang ba de'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5419: lha mi'i theb bum bkra shis ni /
NK023('a)001:5420: yon tan kun ldan byang chub sems dpa'i rigs //
NK023('a)001:5421: bcom ldan rjes dran smon lam grub pa'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:5422: dri ma kun 'khru legs pa mthar phyin pa'i //
NK023('a)001:5423: sku tshe ring ba'i dbang gis bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:5424: lha mi'i theg pa rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:5425: gtso bo lnga la dal lnga 'am //
NK023('a)001:5426: gcig la 'khor dang rdzas mthun to //
NK023('a)001:5427: nyan thos kyi theg pa'i rdzas dbang kha bskang phyi dbang ltar /
NK023('a)001:5428: khrus bum la dkon mchog gsum gyi rdzas su brlabs
NK023('a)001:5429: te snying po mu ne brjod dkon mchog gsum dran
NK023('a)001:5430: pas khrus bya ste 'di skad du /
NK023('a)001:5431: bden rigs bum pa'i chu'i rdzas 'dis dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:5432: slob ma 'di'i nyon mongs pa'i bag chags kyi dri
NK023('a)001:5433: ma dag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:5434: / ming gis dbang bskur bas shes bya ye shes
NK023('a)001:5435: la ma rmongs pas dbang gzhon nu don 'grub dang
NK023('a)001:5436: 'phags pa dang rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa'i go 'phang
NK023('a)001:5437: gi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5438: shing rta la sogs pa'i 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i dbang
NK023('a)001:5439: pos dbang bskur bas 'dzam bu gling bzhi la dbang
NK023('a)001:5440: bsgyur zhing / skye rgas na 'chi mi rtag pa'i sdug bsngal la sun phyung bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5441: chibs 'dis dbang bskur bas rab tu byung zhing nyon
NK023('a)001:5442: mongs pa las grol ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:5443: / bshan ral gris dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i
NK023('a)001:5444: sgrib pa'i dra ba gcod pa'i dbang thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:5445: / cig / bcom ldan 'das kyi gseg spar rdzas
NK023('a)001:5446: kyis dbang bskur bas bdag dang 'gro ba'i don mthar
NK023('a)001:5447: phyin pa rdzogs pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5448: bcom ldan 'das kyi na bza' ngur smrig gi rdzas
NK023('a)001:5449: 'dis dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i 'khor ba las
NK023('a)001:5450: skyobs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5451: bkra shis pa'i sbrang rtsi 'dis dbang bskur bas 'bras
NK023('a)001:5452: bu phun sum tshogs pa'i bkra shis pa'i mchog dang
NK023('a)001:5454: 'o thug 'bras chan gyi dbang bskur bas mtshan dang
NK023('a)001:5455: dpe byed dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK023('a)001:5456: gyur cig / r+ts+wa'i gding ba'i rdzas 'dis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:5457: bas bkra shis thob pa dang bar chad kyis mi
NK023('a)001:5458: tshugs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5459: ji ltar bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa yang
NK023('a)001:5460: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa mngon
NK023('a)001:5461: par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa sh+aakya'i rgyal po sh+aakya'i
NK023('a)001:5462: gtso bo de rab tu byung ba'i na bza' ngur
NK023('a)001:5463: smrig gi chos gos 'di mkhan po nga sa khyod
NK023('a)001:5464: la bkon gyis / khyod kyis 'di phangs zhing brtses
NK023('a)001:5465: pa'i tshad ni mig gi 'bras bu ltar gyis la
NK023('a)001:5466: la bkon gyis / / mi 'bral ba'i tshad ni sha dang rus pa ltar gyis la gon cig /
NK023('a)001:5467: khyod kyis gos kyis bya ba gyis la bag yod par spyod cig /
NK023('a)001:5468: byas la phrag pa g.yon pa la bkal la bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:5470: bcom ldan 'das kyi na bza' ngur smrig gi rgyal
NK023('a)001:5471: mtshan 'dis tshe dang ldan pa rnams la dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:5472: bas tshe rabs thams cad du ngo tsha 'khrel 'dzem
NK023('a)001:5473: gyi gos gon te tshul khrims rnam par dag pa
NK023('a)001:5474: dang ldan pa'i dbang thob nad kyi bskal pa las
NK023('a)001:5476: dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yi /
NK023('a)001:5483: mi skya'am zhes gsung pa dang /
NK023('a)001:5484: mkhan slob dpa' bo rnams kyis /
NK023('a)001:5489: ji ltar bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa mngon par
NK023('a)001:5490: rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa de'i zhal zas kyi bya
NK023('a)001:5492: da ltar dge slong khyod la dbang bskur gyis /
NK023('a)001:5493: khyed kyi zhal zas kyi bya ba gyis la 'di
NK023('a)001:5494: zas kyi 'gengs pa bzhin du khyed kyi rgyud yon
NK023('a)001:5495: tan gyi chos kyis gang bar gyis shig /
NK023('a)001:5496: ces gseg shang g.yas su gtad /
NK023('a)001:5497: lhung bzed g.yon du gtad do //
NK023('a)001:5499: bcom ldan 'das kyi mkhar sil dang lhung bzed kyis
NK023('a)001:5500: dbang bskur bas mtshon dang mu ge'i bskal pa las
NK023('a)001:5502: na mo dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang
NK023('a)001:5503: bden pa chen po'i byin gyi brlabs kyis 'gro ba'i
NK023('a)001:5504: gtso bo skye dgu bla ma thub pa chen po'i
NK023('a)001:5505: dbang bskur bas skal ldan rigs kyi bu dang rigs
NK023('a)001:5506: kyi bu mo rnams tshe rabs kun tu byang chub
NK023('a)001:5507: chen po'i sangs rgyas mthong ba dang mi 'bral ba
NK023('a)001:5508: dang / des dam pa'i chos thos pa dang mi 'bral ba dang /
NK023('a)001:5509: des 'phags pa'i dge 'dun dang 'grogs pa dang mi 'bral bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5512: bcom ldan gtso bos dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:5513: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal grol bar shog /
NK023('a)001:5514: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5515: gtso 'khor gsum gyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:5516: shes rab can dang rdzu 'phrul bcas //
NK023('a)001:5517: don dam kun rdzob 'phags skye bo //
NK023('a)001:5518: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal grol bar shog /
NK023('a)001:5519: dus gsum sangs rgyas ji lta ji snyed kyi //
NK023('a)001:5520: 'das dang ma byon da ltar sangs rgyas ni //
NK023('a)001:5521: rgyal ba 'khor bcas rnams kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:5522: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal grol bar shog /
NK023('a)001:5524: dge bsnyen pho mo dge slong pho mo yi //
NK023('a)001:5525: sdug bsngal bden pa nyer len phung po dang //
NK023('a)001:5526: kun 'byung bden pa las dang nyon mongs dang //
NK023('a)001:5527: 'gog pa'i bden pa sdug bsngal zhi ba dang //
NK023('a)001:5528: lam gyi bden pa gang zag bdag med la //
NK023('a)001:5529: 'khor ba rgyu 'bras spang zhing bden pa bsgrubs //
NK023('a)001:5530: phung po lhag bcas lhag med mya ngan 'das //
NK023('a)001:5531: 'das nas dgra bcom sa la phyin par shog /
NK023('a)001:5532: rigs kyi bu khyod la sangs rgyas kyi 'khor bden
NK023('a)001:5533: pa bzhis dbang bskur bas 'phags pa'i sa dgra bcom
NK023('a)001:5534: pa chen po'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5535: rgyun du zhugs dang phyir mi 'ong //
NK023('a)001:5536: lan gcig phyir 'ong dgra bcom gyi //
NK023('a)001:5537: rgyun zhugs 'bras gnas sprul rang rgyud //
NK023('a)001:5538: 'phags pa brgyad kyi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5540: mu ne bden rigs gdugs sam pad+ma'i sdong bu can
NK023('a)001:5541: 'phags pa sgra gcan 'dzin gyis dbang bskur bas ston
NK023('a)001:5542: pa bcom ldan 'das kyi sras thu bo mchog gis
NK023('a)001:5544: bden pa phyag na gdub bu can nam sdub bu can gcung dga' bos dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:5545: sh+aakya'i gcung mdzes pa'i mtshan sum cu dang ldan pa'i mchog gi dbang thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5547: bden pa phyag na bsil yab can /
NK023('a)001:5548: kun dga' bo'i gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:5549: rtag tu thub pa'i zhabs 'breng rim gro ba mchog gi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5552: spu gri'am chan gri ban phyag gnyis kyis skra dang kha spu 'breg pa ltar mdzad pa'i /
NK023('a)001:5553: tshe dang ldan pa ming can nam ming chen gzugs
NK023('a)001:5554: kyis dbang bskur bas sangs rgyas kyi bka' yi 'phags
NK023('a)001:5555: pa'i nang nas mchog gi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5556: mu ne 'di lnga sde bzang po'i tha ma ming can yin skad /
NK023('a)001:5557: sh+aakya'i ming can 'phags pa ma 'gag pa dang spun /
NK023('a)001:5558: thub chen dang yab spun de yin zhes kyang gsungs /
NK023('a)001:5560: 'khor yang lnga brgya btag pa'i steng nas /
NK023('a)001:5562: ma'i phyogs gnyis te lnga'i pha phyogs gsungs /
NK023('a)001:5563: sh+aakya lnga brgya rab byung 'debs phyi'ang gsung /
NK023('a)001:5564: bden pa phyag na pad+ma can tshe dang ldan pa
NK023('a)001:5565: mo'u 'gal gyi bus dbang bskur bas rdzu 'phrul mchog
NK023('a)001:5567: mu ne bden pa phyag na rin po che can /
NK023('a)001:5568: sha ri'i bu yis dbang bskur bas shes rab chen po'i mchog gi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5569: mu ne 'gre bden pa phyag na zla tshes can
NK023('a)001:5570: 'phags pa rab 'byor bu yis dbang bskur bas 'dri
NK023('a)001:5571: zhing lan ldon mkhas pa mchog gi dbang thob shog
NK023('a)001:5572: / mu ne bden pa phyag na me long can
NK023('a)001:5573: ma 'gag pa yis dbang bskur bas rdzu 'phrul spyan
NK023('a)001:5574: lnga thob pa'i mchog gis dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5575: mu ne bden pa phyag na 'khor lo can /
NK023('a)001:5576: 'char ka yis dbang bskur bas khyim pa 'dul ba'i mchog gi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5577: mu ne bden pa phyag na rin po che yi
NK023('a)001:5578: sgrom bu can cang shes ko'u di na yas dbang
NK023('a)001:5579: bskur bas ston pa la chos thos grol ba thob
NK023('a)001:5580: pa snga ba'i mchog gi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5581: mu ne 'di lnga sde bzang po'i thob gong yin skad /
NK023('a)001:5582: bden pa phyag na phreng ba can rta thul gyi
NK023('a)001:5583: gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas bdud kyi gtso bo dad
NK023('a)001:5584: pa skye ba'i spyod la mdzes pa'i mchog gi dbang
NK023('a)001:5585: thob par shog / mu ne bden pa phyag na
NK023('a)001:5586: spar bu can nye ba 'khor gyi gzugs kyis dbang
NK023('a)001:5587: thob par shog / bskur bas / chos 'dul ba 'dzin pa'i mchog gi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5588: mu ne bden pa phyag na drang srong ste me'i
NK023('a)001:5589: pad+ma can tshe dang ldan pa ba glang bdag gis
NK023('a)001:5590: dbang bskur bas 'gog pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis mchog
NK023('a)001:5592: mu ne bden pa phyag na pad sdong bcu gsum
NK023('a)001:5593: can 'od srung chen po'i gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:5594: zhal lta ba sku bsgres kyi mchog ste /
NK023('a)001:5595: gnas brtan rgyal tshab mchog gi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5596: mu ne bden pa phyag na rin po che rkyal
NK023('a)001:5597: pa can tshe dang ldan pa nor 'dzin gyis dbang
NK023('a)001:5598: bskur bas rang dang gzhan gyi bslab pa la gus
NK023('a)001:5599: pa'i zhal lta ba mchog gi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5600: mu ne bden pa phyag na rin po che 'bar
NK023('a)001:5601: ba can tshe dang ldan pa gang pos dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:5602: bas / sbyangs pa'i yon tan rnams gnang ba dang
NK023('a)001:5603: bkag pa ma nor bar shes te 'dzin pa'i mchog
NK023('a)001:5606: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5608: bcom ldan 'das kyi gnas brtan bcu drug ni /
NK023('a)001:5609: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po b+aa ra d+ha tsha bsod snyoms len dang gcig /
NK023('a)001:5610: gser be'u phar tsha dang gnyis /
NK023('a)001:5615: 'das pa dang bcas dus ldan te bdun /
NK023('a)001:5616: b+aa ra d+ha tsha gser can dang brgyad /
NK023('a)001:5619: lam phran brtan dang bcu gcig /
NK023('a)001:5620: sgra gcan zin dang bcu gnyis /
NK023('a)001:5622: zur gyi zhes pa nags na dang gnas dang zhes pa'am gnas na gnas dang bcu bzhi /
NK023('a)001:5623: ma pham pa dang bco lnga /
NK023('a)001:5625: d+harma pha la dang bcu bdun /
NK023('a)001:5626: pad zla la mkhar sil lhung bzed can da ltar sangs rgyas /
NK023('a)001:5627: thub pa'i bstan pa yang ma byon sangs rgyas /
NK023('a)001:5628: byams pa'i bar dang srid pa ji srid du skyong
NK023('a)001:5629: bas dbang bskur bas de'i dbang mchog thob par shog
NK023('a)001:5630: / tsun d+ha dge tshul yin pas snam sbyar med /
NK023('a)001:5631: d+harma pa la spyi'i dge bsnyen yin pas khyim pa'i gzugs zhes gsungs /
NK023('a)001:5632: mtshan jo bo rjes shing kun dang /
NK023('a)001:5636: sbed byed ces pa dang bde byed ces pa dang gcig /
NK023('a)001:5638: rdo rje ma'i bu dang gsum /
NK023('a)001:5639: ba ku la dang bzhi bshad /
NK023('a)001:5640: nyan thos kyi theg pa rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:5642: brgyad dang mchog dang gnas brtan no //
NK023('a)001:5644: rang rgyal gyi sgra tshig ni rdzas dbang kha skong bsdus pa ni /
NK023('a)001:5646: drang srong chen po'i rdzas yin pa shes pas brlabs te /
NK023('a)001:5647: mngon par shes pa lnga dang ldan pa rdzu 'phrul
NK023('a)001:5648: rnams la dbang thob pa'i drang srong chen po dran
NK023('a)001:5649: pas snying po brjod khrus bya ste /
NK023('a)001:5650: 'di skad du phyi dbang brgya rtsa las /
NK023('a)001:5651: bden rigs pa bum pa'i chu'i rdzas 'dis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:5652: bas slob ma 'di yi nyon mongs pa'i bag chags
NK023('a)001:5653: kyi dri ma dag pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:5654: / ming gis dbang bskur bas shes bya ye shes
NK023('a)001:5655: la ma rmongs pa'i rang byang chub kyi dbang thob
NK023('a)001:5656: / par gyur cig / chibs 'dis dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:5657: rab tu byung zhing nyon mongs pa las grol ba'i
NK023('a)001:5658: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5659: bshan ral gris dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa'i dra ba gcod par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5660: na bza' ngur smrig gi rdzas 'dis dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:5661: nyon mongs pa'i 'khor ba las skyobs pa'i dbang thob
NK023('a)001:5662: par gyur cig / bkra shis pa'i rdzas sbrang rtsi
NK023('a)001:5663: 'dis dbang bskur bas 'bras bu phun sum 'tshogs pa'i
NK023('a)001:5664: bkra shis mchog dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5665: rtsa gding ba'i rdzas 'dis dbang bskur bas bkra shis
NK023('a)001:5666: thob pa dang bar chad kyis mi tshugs pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:5668: rgyas par rang rgyal sgrags tshigs bram ze rgyal rigs
NK023('a)001:5669: ma gtogs rigs ngan la rang rgyal mi yong bas
NK023('a)001:5670: lha mi dang sngon nyan thos dge slong bzod 'breng
NK023('a)001:5671: yin pas nyan thos kyi rnam pa bsnan no //
NK023('a)001:5672: shin tu bsdus na rang rgyal la rten 'brel sgrags tshig bsnan pa khyad par ro //
NK023('a)001:5673: nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis ni /
NK023('a)001:5674: ma rig pa rgan mo long ba 'dra /
NK023('a)001:5677: ming gzugs gru stong skye mched drug /
NK023('a)001:5678: grong stong lta bu'i reg 'o byed /
NK023('a)001:5679: nang gi nang nas nang du rten 'brel drug /
NK023('a)001:5680: tshor ba pus mor mda' gzugs 'dra //
NK023('a)001:5682: len pa me tog thu ba 'dra //
NK023('a)001:5683: srid pa bu che skye bu skye //
NK023('a)001:5685: nang gi phyi yi rten 'brel drug /
NK023('a)001:5686: phyi yi rten 'brel bcu gnyis las //
NK023('a)001:5687: mkha' rlung me chu sa khams lnga //
NK023('a)001:5688: dus kyis 'gyur dang drug phyi nam //
NK023('a)001:5689: rgyu dang 'brel pa drug las ni //
NK023('a)001:5690: sa bon myu gu sdong po dang //
NK023('a)001:5691: yal ga me tog 'bras bu drug /
NK023('a)001:5693: sa bon ma rig 'gog bden rigs //
NK023('a)001:5694: las dang nyon mongs sdug bsngal gyis //
NK023('a)001:5695: lus ngag sems rnams chung gsum dang //
NK023('a)001:5696: 'bring gsum che gsum chen po che //
NK023('a)001:5697: gnas skabs bcu gnyis rig par shog /
NK023('a)001:5698: bse ru dang ni ne tso lta bu 'di //
NK023('a)001:5699: 'bras bu la sogs phyi yi rten 'brel dang //
NK023('a)001:5700: ma rig la sogs nang gi rten 'brel las //
NK023('a)001:5701: lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras spang byas shing //
NK023('a)001:5702: lugs bzlog 'das pa'i rgyu 'bras bsgrub bya ste //
NK023('a)001:5703: 'jig rten sa drug nyan thos pa dang bdun //
NK023('a)001:5704: 'das nas rang rgyal byang chub phyin par shog /
NK023('a)001:5705: ye d+harma he tu pra b+ha wa he dun te /
NK023('a)001:5706: shan ta tha ga te h+y+aa ba dad de shany+tsa
NK023('a)001:5707: yo ni ro da e bam b+ha ti ma h+aa
NK023('a)001:5708: sh+r+aa ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5711: rigs kyi bu khyod la rten 'brel gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:5712: rang nyid byang chub yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi sa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:5713: bden rigs bcom ldan gtso bo'i dbang bskur bas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal grol bar shog /
NK023('a)001:5714: drang srong chen po rnams kyis rjes zhugs te //
NK023('a)001:5715: slob dpon med kyang byang chub mchog thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5716: ye d+har bden pa rang sangs rgyas bse ru lta
NK023('a)001:5717: bu'am ne tso lta bus dbang bskur bas gcig pur
NK023('a)001:5718: bsam gtan la gnas pa dang /
NK023('a)001:5719: tshogs spyod kyi grogs la brten te /
NK023('a)001:5720: bsam gtan la gnas pa gnyis mthar phyin pa /
NK023('a)001:5721: rang byang chub yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi sas
NK023('a)001:5722: 'gro ba gdul bya rnams thar pa la 'god par
NK023('a)001:5723: shog / ye d+harma bden pa rigs rang sangs rgyas 'jigs byed rdo rje rtse dgus dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:5724: 'khor ba skrag par byed pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5725: ye d+harma a b+hi shiny+tsa h'uh bden pa snang brtseg
NK023('a)001:5726: rin po ches dbang bskur bas ting nge 'dzin snang
NK023('a)001:5728: ye d+harma bden pa nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba sel
NK023('a)001:5729: ba'i dug gis dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa dug
NK023('a)001:5730: lnga'i gdung ba sel ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5731: ye d+harma bden pa dpa' bo 'dul ba rdo rje
NK023('a)001:5732: rtse lnga yis dbang bskur bas 'khor ba mi bsnyel
NK023('a)001:5734: ye d+harma bden pa ri'i rgyal po rin po che'i
NK023('a)001:5735: snye mas dbang bskur bas 'khor ba'i rlung gis mi
NK023('a)001:5736: bskyod pa'i dbang thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5737: ye d+harma bden pa rangs sa sgra chen cha lang
NK023('a)001:5738: gis dbang bskur bas gsung gi sgra dang ldan pa'i
NK023('a)001:5740: ye d+harma bden pa rigs kyi bu slob ma khyed
NK023('a)001:5741: la rdo rje slob dpon bdag gis rang sangs rgyas
NK023('a)001:5742: bse ru lta bu bsam gtan gyi phyag rgya mdzad
NK023('a)001:5743: pas dbang bskur bas ting nge 'dzin rtse gcig tu
NK023('a)001:5744: gyur pa mthar phyin pa'i dbang thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5745: ye d+harma bden pa shes rab mgyogs byed zla tshes kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:5746: shes rab rtsal dang ldan pa'i dbang thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5747: ye d+harma bden pa seng ge lta bu'i rdo rjes
NK023('a)001:5748: dbang bskur bas 'jigs pa thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK023('a)001:5750: ye d+harma a b+hi bden pa yid myur bsil yab
NK023('a)001:5751: kyis dbang bskur bas ting nge 'dzin myur ba'i dbang
NK023('a)001:5752: thob shog / ye d+harma bden pa nyon mongs dug sel bsil yab kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:5753: nyon mongs pa dug lnga 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5754: ye d+harma bden pa bden pa'i rjes la /
NK023('a)001:5755: rang sangs rgyas rdzu 'phrul cher ston me ris dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:5756: sprul pa'i cho 'phrul dang ldan pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:5757: ye d+harma rang byang chub kyi theg pa rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:5758: gtso bo sprul pa'i sku la gsum ni /
NK023('a)001:5759: 'khor bse ru dang ne tso gnyis te /
NK023('a)001:5760: ne tso la tshogs spyod che chung bar gsum dang /
NK023('a)001:5762: 'khor bcu gnyis ni phyi nang rten 'brel dang /
NK023('a)001:5763: phyi nang re la'ang phyi nang gnyis dang /
NK023('a)001:5764: de re re la'ang gsum ste bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:5765: bde bar gshegs pa byang chub sems dpa'i rdzas dbang
NK023('a)001:5766: mdzad pa nyi shu po gtad pa'i dbang ni thugs
NK023('a)001:5767: rje chen po dang ldan pa rnams la phyag 'tshal
NK023('a)001:5768: lo // byang chub sems dpa'i dbang tsag gi rgyab yig la /
NK023('a)001:5769: bcom ldan gser mdog chos 'chad g.yas //
NK023('a)001:5770: g.yon pa mnyam bzhag phyag rgyar ldan //
NK023('a)001:5771: rdo rje skyil krung gtsug tor bcas //
NK023('a)001:5772: spyan yang mthing kha mdzod spur ldan //
NK023('a)001:5775: de yi byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK023('a)001:5776: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5777: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5780: pad zla rgyas steng yum chen mo //
NK023('a)001:5781: longs spyod rgyan ldan rdo rje'i dkyil //
NK023('a)001:5782: gser mdog sku ni shin tu rgyas //
NK023('a)001:5783: phyag bzhi'i dang po'i mnyam bzhag phyag /
NK023('a)001:5785: g.yon pa po ti bsnams nas ni //
NK023('a)001:5786: 'gro ba sems can don mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:5787: de yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK023('a)001:5788: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5789: d+hi pra sa t+wa me ya ni de pra dud pra me b+hi shud+d+he b+h+ya /
NK023('a)001:5790: d+harma d+har tu ba ga ban dza h'u bam ho /
NK023('a)001:5792: a mri ta a pa ra pra ti dza h'u /
NK023('a)001:5795: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan steng nas //
NK023('a)001:5796: phyag na rdo rje zhi ba'i zhal //
NK023('a)001:5797: mthing kha g.yas na rdo rje 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:5799: rin chen brgyan ldan sems dpa'i skyil //
NK023('a)001:5800: de yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK023('a)001:5801: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5802: badz+ra tsan ta ma h+aa ro sha na h'u phatah a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK023('a)001:5803: nub phyogs pad ma'i 'dab ma nas //
NK023('a)001:5804: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs nas //
NK023('a)001:5805: shwa ri gser mdog dka' thub gzugs //
NK023('a)001:5806: chos gos gsum ldan bsil byed g.yos dka' thub gzugs //
NK023('a)001:5807: pus gtsugs g.yon pa lhung bzed bsnams //
NK023('a)001:5808: lus ngag yid gsum bsdams pa'i ngang //
NK023('a)001:5809: de yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK023('a)001:5810: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5811: b+ha ga b+aan pra ba t+aa th+aa ga ta bi sha ya swa b+ha ba s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5813: 'di'i dka' thub gzugs gzer ba ni bsdom brtson rab
NK023('a)001:5814: byung gi tshul gzugs yin te rgas rid ni ma
NK023('a)001:5815: yin no // sangs rgyas rgyas pas gzhon pa'o //
NK023('a)001:5817: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan steng nas //
NK023('a)001:5818: spyan ras dkar po byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:5819: rgyan mdzes sems dpa'i dkyil krung bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:5820: g.yas na pad+ma mchod sbyin dang //
NK023('a)001:5822: de yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK023('a)001:5823: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5824: sarba ta tha ga t+aa a ba lo ki te ka tu na ma ra ya badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5826: des byang sems lha lnga'i lugs tshang zhing /
NK023('a)001:5827: sems tsam dang rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma ltar yum gyis gtso mdzad /
NK023('a)001:5828: dbu ma tsam yod dang mdo sde spyod pa'i dbu ma ltar thub pas gtso mdzad /
NK023('a)001:5829: gtso dang phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas te bcu gcig /
NK023('a)001:5830: lnga dang phyogs bcu ste bco lnga /
NK023('a)001:5832: sems ma bzhi bcu ma the bas drug cu pa ste dal lnga'am bcu'o //
NK023('a)001:5833: gzhal yas lha snam shar phyogs kyis //
NK023('a)001:5834: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK023('a)001:5835: bde gshegs dkon mchog 'byung gnas ni //
NK023('a)001:5836: sku mdog shel ltar dkar ba la //
NK023('a)001:5837: phyag g.yas rin chen mchod sbyin mdzad //
NK023('a)001:5838: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad kar ni //
NK023('a)001:5839: mthil ni gzhan la ston par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:5840: de yi byin brlabs thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5841: de yi dbang mchog bskur bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:5842: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a yu su ra ga ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5844: gzhal yas lha snam lho phyogs kyi //
NK023('a)001:5845: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK023('a)001:5846: bde gshegs mya ngan med pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:5847: sku mdog nam mkha'i mdog can la //
NK023('a)001:5849: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad kar ni //
NK023('a)001:5850: 'gro la bstan pas nyon mongs sel //
NK023('a)001:5851: de yi byin rlabs thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5852: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5853: rba ta th+aa ga t+aa rat+na a tsi ya ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5855: gzhal yas lha snam nub phyogs kyi //
NK023('a)001:5856: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan steng nas //
NK023('a)001:5858: sku mdog gangs ri ltar dkar ba //
NK023('a)001:5859: g.yas pas mche ba gtsig pa bsnams //
NK023('a)001:5860: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad kar ni //
NK023('a)001:5862: de yi byin rlabs thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5863: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5864: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa tri ti sha ga pa ri bi shwa ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5866: gzhal yas lha snam byang phyogs kyi //
NK023('a)001:5867: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs nas //
NK023('a)001:5868: bde gshegs rgyal ba'i dbang po ni //
NK023('a)001:5869: sku mdog in+t+ra ni la'i mdog /
NK023('a)001:5871: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad kar ni //
NK023('a)001:5872: 'gro la bstan pas mun pa sel //
NK023('a)001:5873: de yi byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK023('a)001:5874: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5875: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa bi shwa rat+na san ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5877: gzhal yas snam bu'i shar lho nas //
NK023('a)001:5878: bde gshegs pad+ma dam pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:5879: sku mdog dung ltar dkar ba'i mdangs //
NK023('a)001:5880: g.yas pa pad+ma dmar po bsnams //
NK023('a)001:5881: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad kar ni //
NK023('a)001:5883: de yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK023('a)001:5884: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5885: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa du du ma le ke ta do ba ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5887: gzhal yas snam bu'i lho nub nas //
NK023('a)001:5888: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan steng nas //
NK023('a)001:5889: nyi ma snang ba dam pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:5890: sku mdog mar rgad dmar smug la //
NK023('a)001:5891: phyag g.yas mun sel nyi ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:5892: g.yon pa sku la brten mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:5893: de yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK023('a)001:5894: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5895: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mug ti bi mug te ma rgad du sha ma ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5897: gzhal yas snam bu'i nub byang nas //
NK023('a)001:5898: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan steng nas //
NK023('a)001:5899: sangs rgyas gdugs chen dam pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:5900: sku mdog in+d+ra n+ai la'i mdangs //
NK023('a)001:5901: phyag g.yas sna tshogs rdo rje 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:5902: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad kar ni //
NK023('a)001:5903: mthil ni gzhan la ston par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:5904: de yis byin de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5905: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa sur+ya b+hi la ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5907: gzhal yas snam bu'i byang shar nas //
NK023('a)001:5908: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK023('a)001:5909: ting 'dzin glang po dam pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:5910: sku mdog gser ltar 'tsher ba la //
NK023('a)001:5911: phyag g.yas chos 'chad phyag rgya brten //
NK023('a)001:5912: g.yon pas chos gos 'dzin mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:5913: de yis byin gyis de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5914: sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+ha ga wa te bi shwa ya s+w+aa b+ha ba s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5916: gzhal yas snam bu'i shar stod du //
NK023('a)001:5917: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs nas //
NK023('a)001:5918: dga' bar byed pa'i sangs rgyas ni //
NK023('a)001:5919: sku mdog ut+pala sngon po'i mdangs //
NK023('a)001:5920: phyag g.yas rin chen bum pa bsnams //
NK023('a)001:5921: g.yon pas sku la brten mdzad pa /
NK023('a)001:5922: de yis de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5923: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa ti ra ma ti badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5925: gzhal yas snam bu'i nub smad du //
NK023('a)001:5926: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK023('a)001:5927: bde gshegs pad+mo'i dpal gyis ni //
NK023('a)001:5928: sku mdog gser ltar 'tsher ba'i mdangs //
NK023('a)001:5929: phyag g.yas pad+ma dmar po bsnams //
NK023('a)001:5930: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad kar ni //
NK023('a)001:5931: mthil ni phyir bstan gdung ba sel //
NK023('a)001:5932: de yi byin gyis brlab du gsol //
NK023('a)001:5933: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:5934: sarba ta tha ga t+aa pad+ma b+ha la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5936: zhes pa 'di dag ni dbang bskur bas rgyab yig gi lugs so //
NK023('a)001:5937: 'di gzhung srong tsa na a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sngags mi dgos /
NK023('a)001:5938: byang chub sems dpa'i chog gzhung i thi /
NK023('a)001:5939: dkyil 'khor la 'god dus na dbus la gtso bo 'dab bzhi ste lha lnga /
NK023('a)001:5940: khyams phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas de bco lnga'o //
NK023('a)001:5941: lha bcu gcig ma ltar dbus dang pad+ma bcu gcig go //
NK023('a)001:5942: pad+ma brgyad ldan ltar du gtso bo thub pa sems
NK023('a)001:5943: tsam dang yum chen mo dbu ma ltar gang rung
NK023('a)001:5944: la 'khor phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dbus dang phyogs bcu
NK023('a)001:5945: re re'ang brgyad brgyad de bargya'o //
NK023('a)001:5946: gru chad glo 'bur mchod lha sgo ma khyams phyogs skyongs bcu bkod pa'o //
NK023('a)001:5947: yang lugs gcig lha bcu gcig ma ltar seng khrir yum chen mo ser /
NK023('a)001:5949: gnyis pa gnyis ka po ti'o //
NK023('a)001:5952: d+ha pradz+ny+aa ma h+aa pradz+ny+aa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:5955: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bcu po de'i sngags lha bco lnga dang mthun no //
NK023('a)001:5956: ma lcogs na bsdus par lha brgya ma dang mthun par ga te bzlas te /
NK023('a)001:5957: yum chen mo shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:5960: pa ra ga ta ga te /
NK023('a)001:5961: pa ra sang ga te b+ho d+hi ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:5964: yum chen mo la sras phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis
NK023('a)001:5965: bskor ba bskyed pa ni a sing las seng ge
NK023('a)001:5968: de'i dbus su +aa las zla ba'i gdan rnams bsams /
NK023('a)001:5969: de dkyil yi ge d+hi bkod de /
NK023('a)001:5970: bde bar gshegs pa'i yum gyur pa //
NK023('a)001:5971: shes rab pha rol phyin ma yum //
NK023('a)001:5972: sku mdog dung ltar dkar ba la //
NK023('a)001:5973: g.yas pa mchog rnams sbyin mdzad cing //
NK023('a)001:5974: g.yon pa'i phyag na gnas pa yis //
NK023('a)001:5975: pad ma la gnas glegs bam ste //
NK023('a)001:5976: rgyan rnams kun gyis rnam par brgyan //
NK023('a)001:5979: gsal bar gyur nas phyogs kun tu //
NK023('a)001:5980: byang chub sems dpa' nyan thos gzugs //
NK023('a)001:5982: steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad du //
NK023('a)001:5983: rang rang mdog dang mtshan ma bskyed //
NK023('a)001:5985: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bskyed pa ni //
NK023('a)001:5986: shar phyogs pad gnas zla dkyil du //
NK023('a)001:5987: bde gshegs dkon mchog 'byung gnas nyid //
NK023('a)001:5988: sku mdog dkar skya lta bu la //
NK023('a)001:5989: g.yas pa rin chen mchod sbyin mdzad //
NK023('a)001:5990: g.yon pa lte ba kun tu bstan //
NK023('a)001:5991: lho phyogs pad gnas zla dkyil du //
NK023('a)001:5992: bde gshegs mya ngan med pa ni //
NK023('a)001:5993: sku mdog nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK023('a)001:5995: g.yon pa lte ba kun tu bstan //
NK023('a)001:5996: nub phyogs pad gnas zla dkyil du //
NK023('a)001:5998: sku mdog dkar po dung lta bu //
NK023('a)001:5999: g.yas pa mche ba gtsig pa bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6000: g.yon pa lte bar kun tu bstan //
NK023('a)001:6002: byang phyogs bde gshegs rgyal ba'i dbang po ni /
NK023('a)001:6003: sku mdog ljang khu lta bu la //
NK023('a)001:6004: g.yas pa pad+ma dkar po bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6005: g.yon pa byang shar ting 'dzin glang po dam pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:6006: sku mdog gser btso lta bu la //
NK023('a)001:6007: phyag g.yas chos ni 'chad pa spel //
NK023('a)001:6009: shar lho bde gshegs pad+ma dam pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:6010: sku mdog dkar g.yas pa pad+ma dmar po la //
NK023('a)001:6011: g.yon pa lho nub nyi ma snang ba dam pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:6012: sku mdog dmar gad lta bu la //
NK023('a)001:6013: phyag g.yas nyi ma bsnams pa ste //
NK023('a)001:6014: g.yon pa kun tu bstan pa mdzad //
NK023('a)001:6015: nub byang sangs rgyas gdugs chen dam pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:6016: sku mdog ljang khu lta bu la //
NK023('a)001:6017: phyag g.yas sna tshogs rdo rje ste /
NK023('a)001:6018: g.yon pa lte ba steng phyogs pad gnas zla dkyil du //
NK023('a)001:6019: dga' bar byed pa'i sangs rgyas ni //
NK023('a)001:6020: sku mdog ut+pala sngon po la //
NK023('a)001:6021: phyag g.yas rin chen bum pa bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6022: g.yon pa kun tu bstan pa'o //
NK023('a)001:6023: 'og phyogs pad gnas zla dkyil du //
NK023('a)001:6024: sangs rgyas pad+ma'i dpal sku mdog ser g.yas pa pad+ma dmar po 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6025: g.yon pa lte bar bstan pa'o //
NK023('a)001:6026: lha bcu gcig ma'i tshig dang sngags chog zhu iita&a&a&a /
NK023('a)001:6027: byang sems pad+ma brgyad ldan lha tshogs lnga //
NK023('a)001:6028: rnam dag pad+ma dbus kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK023('a)001:6029: gser mdog bcom ldan bde gshegs dgra bcom pa //
