NK023('a)001:6030: yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub //
NK023('a)001:6031: sa gnon mnyam bzhag gseg shang par bu can //
NK023('a)001:6032: yum chen gser mdog phyag bzhi g.yas ral gri //
NK023('a)001:6033: mchod sbyin steng na bum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:6034: g.yon dang po ut+pala steng na po ti mthar phreng ba //
NK023('a)001:6035: rdo rje skyil krung seng khri pad zla'i gdan //
NK023('a)001:6036: shar dkar lho sngo nub dmar byang ljang gu //
NK023('a)001:6037: rigs bzhi'i sangs rgyas ting 'dzin glang po dang //
NK023('a)001:6038: rin chen 'byung dang pad+ma dam pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:6039: ting 'dzin rgyal po phyag g.yon mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK023('a)001:6040: rdo rje skyil krung phyag g.yas thugs dkar 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6041: rdo rjes chos 'chad rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK023('a)001:6042: mtshams bzhir yum bzhir dkar ser dmar ljang ni //
NK023('a)001:6043: rdo rje rin chen chos la phyag mtshan thub //
NK023('a)001:6044: mnyam pa'i skyil krung bol snol re mig tshul //
NK023('a)001:6045: 'gro kun thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK023('a)001:6046: byin brlabs sgrib sbyangs dbang bskur gsol //
NK023('a)001:6047: mu ne dang ga te brjod shar phyogs sangs rgyas dkon mchog 'byung gnas dkar //
NK023('a)001:6048: mchod sbyin 'khor lo skyabs sbyin g.yon lte bar //
NK023('a)001:6049: mthil ni mnyam pa'am gzhan la mchod sbyin mdzad //
NK023('a)001:6050: gtsug tor chos gos gdan zla pad seng khri //
NK023('a)001:6051: shar lho nub byang dkar sngo dmar ljang gu //
NK023('a)001:6052: chos kyi rgyal mtshan chu srin rgyal mtshan bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6053: dbang phyug rgyal po phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6054: bkod pa'i rgyan ni mdzes pa'i me tog bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6055: rin chen 'od 'phro rin chen 'bar ba bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6056: rdo rje rin chen chos la sems ma bzhin //
NK023('a)001:6057: sems dpa' phyed skyil nyan thos chos zhu'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:6058: shar nub sems tshul lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK023('a)001:6059: rab byung khyim pa sna tshogs tshul mtshon pa'o //
NK023('a)001:6060: 'gro kun thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK023('a)001:6061: byin rlobs sgrib sbyang dbang bskur gsol //
NK023('a)001:6062: mu ne ga te brjod lho phyogs sangs rgyas mya ngan med pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:6063: mdog sngo rin chen skyabs sbyin thugs kar ston //
NK023('a)001:6064: g.yon pa mnyam pa'am lte bar mthil mchod sbyin //
NK023('a)001:6065: gtsug tor chos gos gdan zla pad seng khri //
NK023('a)001:6066: shar lho nub byang dkar sngo dmar ljang ku //
NK023('a)001:6067: sems dpa' snang ba'i mchog ni rdo rje bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6068: phyag rgya'i rgyal po rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6069: spos kyi glang pos phyag na 'bud dung bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6070: spob pa brtsegs pa gser g.yu'i tog dang bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6071: chos bskor shar lho'i mtshams dkar ser dmar ljang //
NK023('a)001:6072: rdo rje rin chen chos la sems ma bzhi //
NK023('a)001:6073: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6074: shar nub sems tshul lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK023('a)001:6075: 'gro kun thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK023('a)001:6076: sgrib sbyong byin rlabs dbang bskur gsol //
NK023('a)001:6078: nub phyogs sangs rgyas rin chen 'od 'phro dmar //
NK023('a)001:6079: pad+ma 'am mi 'jig skyabs sbyin thugs dkar bstan //
NK023('a)001:6080: g.yon pa mnyam pa'am lte bar mthil mchog sbyin //
NK023('a)001:6081: gtsug tor chos gos gdan zla pad seng khri //
NK023('a)001:6082: shar lho nub byang dkar sngo dmar ljang khu //
NK023('a)001:6083: pad+ma'i rgyal po pad ma'i sgrom bu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6084: pad+ma dam pa pad ma kha phye bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6085: rdo rje mi g.yo phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6086: thogs med rgyal po phyag na ral gri bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6087: chos bskor shar lho'i mtshams dkar dmar ser ljang //
NK023('a)001:6088: rdo rje rin chen chos la sems ma bzhi //
NK023('a)001:6089: chos 'chad rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK023('a)001:6090: shar nub sems tshul lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK023('a)001:6091: sems ma'ang lho nub byang nub mtshams btsun ma'o //
NK023('a)001:6092: 'gro kun thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK023('a)001:6093: sgrib sbyangs byin rlabs dbang bskur gsol //
NK023('a)001:6095: byang phyogs sangs rgyas rgyal ba'i dbang po ni //
NK023('a)001:6096: mdog ljang nyi mas phyag mtshan mi 'jig sbyin //
NK023('a)001:6097: g.yon lter mnyam pa'am mthil ni mchod sbyin mdzad //
NK023('a)001:6098: gtsug tor chos gos gdan zla pad seng khri //
NK023('a)001:6099: shar lho nub byang dkar sngo dmar ljang ser //
NK023('a)001:6100: rin chen dbang phyug rin chen zur brgyad 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6101: grub pa'i las ni rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6102: dga' ba ston pa me long rgya gram 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6103: mi g.yo ba yi mtha' ni mnyam bzhag rgya //
NK023('a)001:6104: chos bskor shar lho'i mtshams dkar ser dmar ljang //
NK023('a)001:6105: rdo rje rin chen chos las sems ma bzhi //
NK023('a)001:6106: chos 'chad rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK023('a)001:6107: shar nub sems tshul lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK023('a)001:6108: sems ma'ang shar lho nub byang mtshams sems tshul //
NK023('a)001:6109: 'gro kun thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK023('a)001:6110: byin rlabs sgrib sbyang dbang bskur gsol //
NK023('a)001:6113: byang shar sangs rgyas ting 'dzin glang po dam pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:6114: mdog ljang phyag g.yas po ti thugs kar chos 'chad bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6115: g.yon pa mnyam pa'am lte bar mthil ni mchod sbyin ston //
NK023('a)001:6116: gtsug tor chos gos gdan zla pad+ma seng ge'i khri //
NK023('a)001:6117: shar lho nub byang dkar sngo dmar ljang ser //
NK023('a)001:6118: phyag na rdo rje'am rdo rje rtse dgu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6119: spyan ras gzigs dbang pad+ma dkar po 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6120: nam mkha'i snying po rin chen za ma tog /
NK023('a)001:6121: sa yi snying po rin chen myu gu 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6122: chos skor shar lho'i mtshams dkar ser dmar ljang //
NK023('a)001:6123: rdo rje rin chen chos la sems ma bzhi //
NK023('a)001:6124: chos 'chad rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK023('a)001:6125: shar nub sems tshul lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK023('a)001:6126: 'khor sems re re'ang rab byung khyim tshul mtshon //
NK023('a)001:6127: 'gro kun thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK023('a)001:6128: byin rlabs sgrib sbyang dbang bskur gsol //
NK023('a)001:6130: shar lho'i sangs rgyas pad mo dam pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:6131: dkar ser phyag g.yas pad steng pad+ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6132: kun tu bzang po rin chen sdong po bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6133: 'jam dpal gzhon nu phyag na ut+pala bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6134: sgrib pa rnam sel phyag na po ti bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6135: byams pa me tri phyag na 'gun d+he bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6136: zhes de 'gun d+he ni bum pa spyi blug /
NK023('a)001:6137: sems ma bzang po rin chen sdong po bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6138: sems la sogs sngar dang mthun /
NK023('a)001:6141: sems dpa'i mtshan mdo gzhan du'o //
NK023('a)001:6142: lho nub sangs rgyas nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor snang ba dam pa'i dpal /
NK023('a)001:6143: sku mdog dmar po phyag g.yas nyi ma thugs dkar bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6144: sems dpa' mthu chen thob ni rdo rje bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6145: sman pa'i rgyal po sman gyi bum pa bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6146: yon tan snying po rin chen snye ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6147: mthong na dga' ba klu shing lo ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6149: nub byang sangs rgyas gdugs mdzes dam pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:6150: sku mdog dmar ljang phyag g.yas gdugs kyis 'gyebs //
NK023('a)001:6151: phyag g.yon mnyam pa'am lte bar mthil mchod sbyin //
NK023('a)001:6152: gtsug tor chos gos gdan la pad seng khri //
NK023('a)001:6153: sems dpa' gzhon nu dbu rgyan me tog ud //
NK023('a)001:6154: skyes bu dam pa phyag na ku mu ta //
NK023('a)001:6155: seng ge sgra ni 'bud dung rnga yab bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6156: rdo rje'i rgyan ni phyag na spyan gsal bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6157: zhes te sems ma bzhi dang mthun /
NK023('a)001:6158: shar nub phyag mtshan zhu tig 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6162: ku mu ta yin nam dag cig 'tshal /
NK023('a)001:6163: steng phyogs sangs rgyas dga' ba'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:6164: ces pa dkar po phyag g.yas rgyal mtshan g.yon gdan mthun sems mdog sngar mthun /
NK023('a)001:6166: dkon mchog 'byung gnas rin chen sgrom bu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6167: dpa' bar 'gro ba ral gri phyag na 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6168: zla 'od gzhon nu zla tshes dkar po bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6169: sems ma sngar dang mthun tsaka rnying pa ltar //
NK023('a)001:6170: sarba ta tha ga ta ri ti badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:6171: tra pa le tra pa le s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:6172: rat+na swa b+ha wa d+ha ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:6173: shu ra ga me pa ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:6174: tsan tra pra sa ku ma ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:6175: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa
NK023('a)001:6176: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dga' ba'i dpal
NK023('a)001:6177: dang / byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po bzang skyongs dang /
NK023('a)001:6181: sems mar bcas pa de rnams kyis thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK023('a)001:6186: sku mdog phyag mtshan tsa kar nges dgos pa /
NK023('a)001:6189: spyi bsnyen dang sku mdog phyag mtshan bris so //
NK023('a)001:6190: 'og phyogs sangs rgyas pad mo'i dpal ces pa //
NK023('a)001:6191: sngo nag pad+ma chos can kha phye bas //
NK023('a)001:6192: g.yon lter mchod sbyin yang na mnyam bzhag bshad //
NK023('a)001:6193: gtsug tor chos gos gdan zla pad+ma seng ge'i khri //
NK023('a)001:6194: shar lho nub byang dkar sngo dmar ljang ser //
NK023('a)001:6195: sems dpa' ye shes tog ni tog dkar bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6196: sems dpa' mya ngan 'joms pa ral gri 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6197: blo gros mi zad phyag na po ti 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6198: ye shes 'od zer phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6199: chos skor shar lho'i mtshams dkar ser dmar ljang //
NK023('a)001:6200: rdo rje rin chen chos las sems ma bzhi //
NK023('a)001:6201: chos 'chad rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK023('a)001:6202: lha rgyan tshul dang mi'i rab byung tshul //
NK023('a)001:6203: gang 'dul gang mos tshul gyis don mdzad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:6204: de rnams kyis thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK023('a)001:6208: khyams la phyogs skyong bstan bsrung bcu //
NK023('a)001:6209: shar skyongs brgya byin dkar po ni //
NK023('a)001:6210: glang chen khri steng rdo rje gdengs //
NK023('a)001:6211: lho shar me lha dmar ser ni //
NK023('a)001:6212: ra skyes khri steng bgrang phreng 'dren //
NK023('a)001:6213: lho skyong gshin rje sngon po ni //
NK023('a)001:6214: ma he'i khri steng thod dbyug 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:6215: lho nub srin po smug po ni //
NK023('a)001:6216: gyad mi khri steng ral gri 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6217: nub skyongs chu lha dmar po ni //
NK023('a)001:6218: chu srin khri steng sbrul zhag 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6219: nub byang rlung lha dud kha ni //
NK023('a)001:6220: sha ba'i steng na ba dan 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:6221: byang skyong gnod sbyin ljang khu ni //
NK023('a)001:6222: rta mchog khri steng dbyug tho 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:6223: byang shar dbang ldan dkar po ni //
NK023('a)001:6224: glang bu khyu mchog steng rtse gsum //
NK023('a)001:6225: steng skyong nyi mar zla dkar ni //
NK023('a)001:6226: dur ngang khri stengs pad+ma dmar //
NK023('a)001:6227: me tog ku mu dkar po 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6228: 'og skyong sa yi lha mo ser //
NK023('a)001:6229: phag pa'i khri steng gter bum bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6230: 'gro kun thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK023('a)001:6231: byin rlobs sgrib sbyangs dbang bskur gsol //
NK023('a)001:6232: mu ne ga te bzlas so //
NK023('a)001:6233: sngon gyi tsaka rnying pa la lha re'i bskyed sngags
NK023('a)001:6234: dang 'dod gsol lhug par bshad na'ang bla ma'i gsung
NK023('a)001:6235: bzhin bris so // glo 'bur gru chad mchod lha sgo ma ni //
NK023('a)001:6236: sems dpa' phyogs skyong ltar du phyed skyil bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:6237: yang na sgo ma zhal phyir rkyang skum bzhengs //
NK023('a)001:6238: phyogs skyong sems yab g.yas bskum yum g.yon skum //
NK023('a)001:6239: shar nas sgeg mo phreng thog glu gar ma //
NK023('a)001:6240: me long phreng ba pi wam gar chas 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6241: spos dang me tog mar me dri chab ma //
NK023('a)001:6242: bdug spos me tog sgron me dung phor dri //
NK023('a)001:6243: sgo ma'ang lcags kyu zhag sgrog dril 'khrol ma //
NK023('a)001:6244: kha dog phyogs mtshams sems mtshungs gtso la gzigs //
NK023('a)001:6245: lha yi rgyan chas pad zla'i gdan la 'khod //
NK023('a)001:6246: mchod rdzas gdul bya ngo mtshar du mas 'khrigs //
NK023('a)001:6247: 'gro la thugs rjes gzigs su gsol //
NK023('a)001:6248: byin rlob sgrib sbyang dbang bskur gsol //
NK023('a)001:6249: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne s+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:6250: ga te ga te pa ra ga te pa ra sam ga te b+ho d+hi ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:6251: byang sems theg pa'i rgyab yig zur byams pa dang
NK023('a)001:6252: bla ma bzang po'i bka' la brten nas bla ma'i
NK023('a)001:6253: gsung kun phan sangs rgyas shog /
NK023('a)001:6255: ha gsum dang lha drug ste bdun dang /
NK023('a)001:6257: rgyas pa ste lugs 'ga' snang ngo //
NK023('a)001:6259: thugs rje'i rtags su sku mdog zla ba'i 'od //
NK023('a)001:6260: ma chags skyon gyis ma gos pad+ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6261: spyan ras gzigs kyi bkra shis gang lags pa //
NK023('a)001:6262: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK023('a)001:6263: yon tan rgyas pa sku mdog gser dang mtshungs //
NK023('a)001:6264: shes rab rtags su po ti ral gri bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6265: 'phags pa 'jam dpal shes bya gang yin pa //
NK023('a)001:6266: bkra shis dam pa deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK023('a)001:6267: chos nyid mi 'gyur rtags su sku mdog mthing nag ste //
NK023('a)001:6268: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med rtags su rdo rje 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6269: dpal ldan phyag na rdo rje'i bkra shis gang lags pa //
NK023('a)001:6270: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK023('a)001:6271: lha gtso bo gang yang rung ba zhig bskyed pa dbus yin la /
NK023('a)001:6272: 'khor yi ge'i kha dog can lha drug gtsug tor chos gos can no //
NK023('a)001:6273: sbyangs pa'i lha bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa thal
NK023('a)001:6274: mo khong stong thugs kar sbyar ba sna a dkar
NK023('a)001:6275: po can rnam snang ngo bo de yi dbang thob
NK023('a)001:6276: shog / spel ba'i lha rnam par snang mdzad smin
NK023('a)001:6277: mtshams rin chen sgrom gyi phyag rgya khang sngon po
NK023('a)001:6278: can mi bskyod pa'i ngo bo'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:6279: mos par bsgyur ba'i lha bdud rtsi 'khyil pa 'bar
NK023('a)001:6280: ba'i phyag rgya kha'i thad du dza dmar po can
NK023('a)001:6281: / snang mtha'i ngo bo'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:6282: so sor thob pa'i lha rgyal chen shugs ldan 'od
NK023('a)001:6283: kyis rgya mchod sbyin mdzub sgreng g.yas na bcas par
NK023('a)001:6284: tram ngams pa ser po can rin chen 'byung ldan
NK023('a)001:6286: thams cad tshim pa'i lha don grub ye shes skar
NK023('a)001:6287: mad'i rgya g.yon mchod sbyin g.yas khu tshur skyabs sbyin
NK023('a)001:6288: g.yon du bcas par ha ljang khu don 'grub ngo
NK023('a)001:6290: thams cad rtsod pa mi byed par bdag gi dbang
NK023('a)001:6291: du byed pa'i lha phyag na rdo rjes dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:6292: bas 'khor lo rgyal po'i sor mo nang bsdams kyi
NK023('a)001:6293: nang du dza dmar po can rdor sems rigs gang
NK023('a)001:6294: gis las kyi lha'i ngo bo de'i dbang thob shog
NK023('a)001:6295: / kri ya don gyi lha drug phyag rgya drug yi ge drug don drug go //
NK023('a)001:6296: kri ya'i lha lnga gsum bco lnga ni /
NK023('a)001:6297: rigs bdag thugs mchog mi bskyod pa //
NK023('a)001:6298: chos nyid mi 'gyur sku mdog sngo //
NK023('a)001:6299: sa gnon chen po'i phyag rgya mdzad //
NK023('a)001:6301: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:6302: g.yon mnyam bzhag phyag na rdo rje'i thugs rigs gtso /
NK023('a)001:6304: dam tshig rdo rje'i phyag rgya can //
NK023('a)001:6305: de'i dbang g.yon dril bu rigs kyi yum chen kun tu bzang /
NK023('a)001:6307: phyag mtshan rdo rje rtse gsum bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6308: de'i dbang yang na yum chen ma ma ki //
NK023('a)001:6310: g.yon dril bu'am sman gyis bum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:6311: de'i dbang rigs kyi khro rgyal bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK023('a)001:6312: yang na bdud rtsi thal sbyor ni //
NK023('a)001:6313: ljang la rgya gram de'i g.yon pa dril bu'am bum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:6314: rigs kyi pho nya rdo rje khro bo ni //
NK023('a)001:6315: mthing nag rdo rje de'i yang na rdo rje lcags kyu yang bshad g.yon sdigs mdzub /
NK023('a)001:6316: rgyas par yum la bka' sdod do //
NK023('a)001:6317: pho nya la lha chen po dang /
NK023('a)001:6318: rigs sngags lha mo ni g.yon sku la brten pa'o //
NK023('a)001:6319: rdo rje lha mo stobs chen mo /
NK023('a)001:6320: sku mdog nag la phyag mtshan rdo rje rtse gcig bsnams /
NK023('a)001:6321: de'i dbang rigs sngags lha mo rnam rgyal ma //
NK023('a)001:6322: dkar la phyag mtshan phyag na 'khor lo bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6323: de'i lha chen khyab 'jug 'khor lo ni //
NK023('a)001:6325: phyag mtshan phyag na 'khor lo bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6326: de'i dbang mchog badz+ra pa ni h+aum phatah gtsug tor gdugs dkar na gsungs gda' ba 'dir mdzad /
NK023('a)001:6327: yang na badz+ra pa ni h'u phatah bod skad byed na phyag na rdo rje'o //
NK023('a)001:6329: rigs bdag gsung mchog snang mtha' yas //
NK023('a)001:6330: thugs rjes chags pa sku mdog dmar //
NK023('a)001:6331: bsam gtan mchog gi phyag rgya mdzad //
NK023('a)001:6333: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:6334: spyan ras gzigs dbang gsung rigs gtso //
NK023('a)001:6336: pad+ma de la g.yas pa mchod sbyin /
NK023('a)001:6337: rigs kyi yum chen gos dkar mo //
NK023('a)001:6338: dmar la phyag mtshan phyag na pad+ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6339: de la g.yon dril bu'am bum pa /
NK023('a)001:6340: rigs kyi khro rgyal rta mgrin ni //
NK023('a)001:6342: yang na ral gri'am be con nam sbrul zhags zhes so //
NK023('a)001:6343: rigs kyi pho nya rdo rje phur pa ni /
NK023('a)001:6344: dmar nag phur pa bsnams pa /
NK023('a)001:6345: yang na pad+ma'i mdangs can seng ge bcibs //
NK023('a)001:6346: dmar la pad ma kha phye bsnams /
NK023('a)001:6348: rgyas pa bka' sdod rig sngags lha mo dang //
NK023('a)001:6349: lha chen po ni g.yon sku brten //
NK023('a)001:6350: lha mo chen mo grags ldan ma //
NK023('a)001:6351: dkar la pad+ma kha phye bsnams /
NK023('a)001:6353: rigs sngags lha mo lu gu rgyud /
NK023('a)001:6355: lha chen ma ha de wa ni /
NK023('a)001:6356: dmar la dri shul rtse gsum bsnams /
NK023('a)001:6357: de la ma ni pad+me h+aum h+r+aih zhes thugs rjes
NK023('a)001:6358: chen pos brgyud nas h+r+aih yod la khyad zab bshad
NK023('a)001:6360: ma ni pad+me h+aum h+r+aih zhes so //
NK023('a)001:6361: bod skad du yid bzhin nor bu skyon bral steng zhes so //
NK023('a)001:6362: rigs bdag sku mchog rnam snang mdzad //
NK023('a)001:6363: nyes pa'i skyon bral sku mdog dkar //
NK023('a)001:6364: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK023('a)001:6366: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:6367: byang chub mchog dang chos 'chad gang rung ngo //
NK023('a)001:6368: bcom ldan 'jam dpal sku yi rigs kyi gtso //
NK023('a)001:6370: phyag mtshan phyag na ral gri bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6371: de la phyag 'tshal yang na ral gri ut+pala bsnams zhes /
NK023('a)001:6372: rigs kyi yum chen sangs rgyas spyan //
NK023('a)001:6373: dkar la phyag mtshan thor tshug spyan gsal bsnams /
NK023('a)001:6374: de la g.yas 'khor lo yis sras /
NK023('a)001:6376: rigs kyi khro rgyal gshin rje gshed //
NK023('a)001:6377: smug nag bde mchog bde chen /
NK023('a)001:6378: de la yang na dbyug do bsnams zhes so //
NK023('a)001:6380: rigs kyi pho nya rdo rje rnon po ni /
NK023('a)001:6381: sngo nag ral gri de la yang na pho nya sgra gcan nye ba'i sgra gcan ni /
NK023('a)001:6384: rgyas par bka' sdod dang rig sngags lha mo dang /
NK023('a)001:6385: lha chen po ni g.yon sku brten /
NK023('a)001:6386: dpal gyi lha mo chen mo ni /
NK023('a)001:6387: sku mdog dkar ser phyag na pad+ma de la rigs lha mo mdzod sprul ma /
NK023('a)001:6388: dkar la yid bzhin nor bu bsnams /
NK023('a)001:6389: de la lha chen tshangs pa chen po ni /
NK023('a)001:6390: ser la phyag na ril ba spyi blug bsnams /
NK023('a)001:6391: de la wa gi shwa ri mum zhes 'jam dpal du gsungs /
NK023('a)001:6392: bod skad gsung gi dbang phyug tu brjod /
NK023('a)001:6393: bdag po'i dbu rgyan rigs gtso dkyil /
NK023('a)001:6394: yum shar khro lho pho nya byang /
NK023('a)001:6395: pho nya 'dam kha nub mtshams la /
NK023('a)001:6396: gang bder rig sngags lha dang /
NK023('a)001:6397: lha chen bkod pa ni bla ma dpal ldan pa'i bka'o /
NK023('a)001:6399: bkra shis kyi mchod lha ni phyag gnyis gus 'dud de /
NK023('a)001:6400: shar phyogs dpal ldan pad+ma can //
NK023('a)001:6402: phyag mtshan phyag na dpal be'u bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6403: de la shar phyogs 'jig byed 'jig bral ba //
NK023('a)001:6404: sngo la 'khor lo de la lho phyogs lho mo 'od ldan ma /
NK023('a)001:6405: dkar la pad+ma de la lho phyogs bkra shis rnam rgyal ma //
NK023('a)001:6407: de la nub phyogs bkra shis mdangs can ma //
NK023('a)001:6409: de la nub phyogs bdud rtsi tri ned mtsho //
NK023('a)001:6410: ljang la bum pa de la byang phyogs rgyal ba'i gsung sgrogs ma //
NK023('a)001:6411: sngo la 'bud dung de la byang phyogs lha mo yid bzang ma //
NK023('a)001:6412: ljang sngon rdzu 'phrul gser nya de la phyag 'tshal mchod par 'bul /
NK023('a)001:6413: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:6414: kri ya'i rigs gsum gang rung gtso la 'khor gsum gnyis te gtso bo gsum dang /
NK023('a)001:6415: gang gtso la 'khor drug ste lha bdun la 'khor gnyis dang /
NK023('a)001:6416: nang gtso la 'khor bcu bzhi ste bco lnga mtha' rgyan dang bcas pa ste /
NK023('a)001:6417: gtso bo re'ang 'khor lugs gsum byung bas dal dagu'ang so so dang gcig gang lcogs mdzad /
NK023('a)001:6418: kri ya'i rdzas dbang nyi shu rtsa drug sgos kyi yin /
NK023('a)001:6420: chab rdor glu gtor gyi sman sgrub yod na sman dbang bya'o //
NK023('a)001:6421: kri ya'i lha dbang rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:6422: byang sems dang kri yog spyi'i mgon lha bskal bzang
NK023('a)001:6423: sems dpa' bcu drug g.yon thugs kar phyed thal mo
NK023('a)001:6424: dang mchod sbyin dang sku brten gang rung ngo //
NK023('a)001:6425: shar phyogs dpa' bar 'gro ba ni //
NK023('a)001:6426: sku mdog dkar la ral gri bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6427: de la kun tu bzang po ni dkar rin chen
NK023('a)001:6428: snye ma de la zla 'od gzhon nu dkar zla
NK023('a)001:6429: ba bzang skyongs kun la skyongs /
NK023('a)001:6430: dkar bum pa de la lho phyogs d+r+wa ba can gyi 'od //
NK023('a)001:6431: sngo dra ba de la sems dpa' nam mkha' mdzod
NK023('a)001:6432: sngo rin chen sgrom bu de la nam mkha'i snying
NK023('a)001:6433: po ni / sngo rdo rje rtse gsum de la
NK023('a)001:6434: sems dpa' 'od dpag med sngo rin chen 'bar ba
NK023('a)001:6435: nub phyogs mya ngan kun 'joms ni //
NK023('a)001:6436: dmar ral gri de la sems dpa' ye shes tog
NK023('a)001:6437: dmar rin chen tog de la spobs pa brtsegs pa
NK023('a)001:6438: ni / dmar rin chen 'bar ba de la blo gros mi zad pa /
NK023('a)001:6440: de la byang phyogs byams pa me tri ni //
NK023('a)001:6441: ljang 'gyu d+he spyi blug de la spos kyi glang po ni /
NK023('a)001:6442: ljang khu 'bud dung de la ngan song kun 'dren ni /
NK023('a)001:6443: ljang lcags kyu de la byang phyogs sems dpa' don yod grub //
NK023('a)001:6445: phyag mtshan phyag na rgya gram bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6447: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:6449: yang bla ma'i phyag len du /
NK023('a)001:6450: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa chos kyi sku //
NK023('a)001:6451: 'gro drug sems can rnams la spyan ras gzigs //
NK023('a)001:6452: nam mkha' lta bur khyab pa'i bcu gcig zhal //
NK023('a)001:6453: gzi brjid 'od dpag med la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:6456: zhes rnam dag phar phyin bcu pa dbang stobs phyogs
NK023('a)001:6457: bcu sogs lhar bstan pa'i ming yin gyi zhal gcig
NK023('a)001:6458: yin gsung / sku 'jam dpal yon tan rgyas phyir ser /
NK023('a)001:6459: phyag rdor phrin las kyi rnam 'joms ljang khu dud kha dang thugs mthing kha /
NK023('a)001:6460: gsung thugs rjes spyan ras dmar po dang /
NK023('a)001:6462: dpal gyi 'byung gnas 'jam dpal kun gyi dpal //
NK023('a)001:6463: mtha' dag yongs la khyab pa 'joms pa'i ngang //
NK023('a)001:6464: 'jam dang dpal du grags pa'i don dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:6465: 'jam dpal yang dag dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:6467: h'u lcang lo can gyi gnas mchog dam pa nas //
NK023('a)001:6468: gsang sngags rig sngags kun gyi bdag po ste //
NK023('a)001:6469: log 'dren bgegs kyi tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:6470: bcom ldan rdo rje bsnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:6473: rdzas dbang kri ya bkra shis nyer drug go //
NK023('a)001:6474: 'di yi las kyi lha mi g.yo bas byed ces slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas bshad /
NK023('a)001:6475: kri ya la rigs lnga dkyil 'khor la 'god pa yod kyang /
NK023('a)001:6476: lha dbang rigs lngas mi bskur rigs gsum yin /
NK023('a)001:6477: yum lnga'ang khrus bum pa 'dzin pa yab lnga'ang dgongs nas byin rlabs mdzad par mos gus byed gsungs /
NK023('a)001:6479: byang chub mchog dang sa gnon dang //
NK023('a)001:6480: mchog sbyin mnyam pa'i phyag rgyar ldan //
NK023('a)001:6481: skyabs kyi phyag rgya la sogs lngas //
NK023('a)001:6482: mi 'di phyag rgya'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:6484: spros med spros bral chos kyi dbyings //
NK023('a)001:6485: bum pa zlum po yum gyi gter //
NK023('a)001:6486: phan byed sman pa'i mchog yin te //
NK023('a)001:6487: 'gro ba'i nad sel bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:6489: h'u don dam bden pa'i chos nyid las //
NK023('a)001:6490: mi g.yo sems dpa'i mngon sum du //
NK023('a)001:6491: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gnas pa //
NK023('a)001:6492: u pa ya yi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:6496: pad+ma a mi de ba hrih karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi ah a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK023('a)001:6497: bden rigs u pa ya yis dbang bskur bas rigs
NK023('a)001:6498: bzhi rdo rje 'chang gi go 'phang thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:6499: cig / rigs lnga ni yo ga dbu rgyan can dbu skra lcang lo can longs spyod rdzogs sku /
NK023('a)001:6500: rnam snang dkar po phyag rgya byang chub mchog ni
NK023('a)001:6501: gnyis te g.yas kyis g.yon gyi mdzub mo bzung ba
NK023('a)001:6502: dang / chos 'chad gang rung gi steng na 'khor lo /
NK023('a)001:6503: mi bskyod pa sngo sa gnon drung na rdo rje 'dzin /
NK023('a)001:6504: rin 'byung ser mchod sbyin steng na rin po che /
NK023('a)001:6505: 'od dpag med dmar mnyam bzhag steng na pad+ma /
NK023('a)001:6506: don grub ljang skyabs sbyin phyag rgyan rgya gram mo
NK023('a)001:6507: rigs bzhi ni 'khor lo ma rtogs pa'i phyag rgya
NK023('a)001:6509: rdzas dbang dang mgron lha kri yog la bsdus nas 'dir mi bskur bas gda' lags /
NK023('a)001:6510: rigs bzhi ni sku gsung thugs ye shes sems dpa' dang bzhi /
NK023('a)001:6512: lha du ma yod na gang gtso bo la tshangs
NK023('a)001:6513: par sku gsung thugs ye shes bzhi yin u pa
NK023('a)001:6514: ya rdzogs so // u pa ya yi dkyil 'khor dang dbu rgyan dang /
NK023('a)001:6515: sku'i bum gcig sku rkyang dang /
NK023('a)001:6516: gsung gi bum gcig yig 'bru rkyang dang /
NK023('a)001:6517: thugs kyi bum gcig thugs kyi phyag mtshan rkyangs dang /
NK023('a)001:6518: de gsum ka tshangs pa'i ye shes nges pa'i gzugs brnyan ltar dal lugs bzhi'o //
NK023('a)001:6519: sku gsung thugs ye shes rdo rje gtsor gang byed kyang ye shes kyi sku ni /
NK023('a)001:6520: sku gsung thugs gsum ka tshangs pa ste lugs ni /
NK023('a)001:6521: zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhir yo ga lugs /
NK023('a)001:6525: ye shes ser po la tshe'i dbus la'o //
NK023('a)001:6526: lha ni rnam par snang mdzad la //
NK023('a)001:6527: sprul pa'i phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK023('a)001:6528: sngon 'gro la mchog dbang bskur ba dang /
NK023('a)001:6529: 'dir thog 'og gang thob kyis bskor ba'i dbang khyad par mdzad do //
NK023('a)001:6530: yo ga tsa ka li'i rgyab yig /
NK023('a)001:6531: h'u snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK023('a)001:6532: chos dbyings ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK023('a)001:6533: byang chub mchog gis phyag rgya mdzad //
NK023('a)001:6534: phyag 'tshal rnam par snang mdzad la'o //
NK023('a)001:6535: de yi dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:6537: rdo rje dbyings sku mdog dkar po rnam snang kun tu zhal lo //
NK023('a)001:6539: dbus kyi dbus seng ge'i khri /
NK023('a)001:6541: me long ye shes byin rlabs las /
NK023('a)001:6542: sems ma rdo rje phyag rgya ste /
NK023('a)001:6543: rdo rje ser dmar dkar po rtsa lnga pa //
NK023('a)001:6544: bstod cing gus pas phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6545: de yi dbang mchog sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:6550: h'u mnyam nyid ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK023('a)001:6551: rat+na sems ma'i phyag rgya ste //
NK023('a)001:6552: rat+na ser po zur brgyad la //
NK023('a)001:6553: bstod cing gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:6554: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:6556: rat+na badz+ra yum ma ma ki ser dbus kyi lho /
NK023('a)001:6557: h'u kun rtog ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK023('a)001:6558: chos kyi sems ma'i phyag rgya ste //
NK023('a)001:6559: pad+ma dkar dmar bcu drug la //
NK023('a)001:6560: bstod cing gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:6561: de yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:6563: pad+ma badz+ra yum na bza' dkar mo dmar dbus kyi nub /
NK023('a)001:6564: h'u bya grub ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK023('a)001:6565: las kyi sems ma'i phyag rgya ste //
NK023('a)001:6566: rdo rje rgya gram ljang khu las //
NK023('a)001:6567: bstod cing gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:6568: de yi dbang mchog thob gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:6571: yum sgrol ma ljang dbus kyis brgyan byang /
NK023('a)001:6572: h'u gzung 'dzin rdoo rje bstan pa ni //
NK023('a)001:6573: me long ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK023('a)001:6574: rdoo rje sa gnon phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:6575: phyag 'tshal rdo rje mi bskyod la'o //
NK023('a)001:6576: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:6581: h'u rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK023('a)001:6582: rdo rje de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku //
NK023('a)001:6583: rdo rje dang po kun tu bzang //
NK023('a)001:6584: phyag 'tshal phyag na rdo rje la'o //
NK023('a)001:6587: badz+ra sa t+wa sems dkar shar mdun no //
NK023('a)001:6588: h'u rdo rje rgyal po sangs rgyas mchog /
NK023('a)001:6589: rdo rje lcags kyu de bzhin gshegs //
NK023('a)001:6590: nges pa'i rgyal po rdo rje mchog /
NK023('a)001:6592: de yi dbang mchog thob gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:6594: badz+ra ra tsa rgyal po ser shar gyi g.yas /
NK023('a)001:6595: h'u rdo rje chags pa bde chen po //
NK023('a)001:6596: rdo rje mda' ni dbang byed pa //
NK023('a)001:6597: bdud kyi 'dod pa rdo rje che //
NK023('a)001:6598: phyag 'tshal rdo rje gzhu khyod la'o //
NK023('a)001:6599: de yi dbang mchog sbyin gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:6601: badz+ra ra ga chags dmar shar gyi rgyab /
NK023('a)001:6602: rdo rje legs pa sems dpa' mchog /
NK023('a)001:6603: rdo rje mgu ba dga' ba che //
NK023('a)001:6604: rab dges rgyal po rdo rje mchog /
NK023('a)001:6605: phyag 'tshal rdo rjes dges khyod la'o //
NK023('a)001:6606: de yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:6608: badz+ra sa du legs ljang shar gyi byang /
NK023('a)001:6609: h'u rat+na rdo rje 'bar ba'i mes //
NK023('a)001:6610: mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK023('a)001:6611: rdo rje mchog sbyin phyag rgya mdzad //
NK023('a)001:6613: de yi dbang mchog thob gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:6616: rin chen 'byung ldan ser rta mchog khri lho'i dbus /
NK023('a)001:6617: h'u rdo rje rin chen rdo rje don //
NK023('a)001:6618: rdo rje nam mkha' nor bu che //
NK023('a)001:6619: nam mkha' snying po rdo rje 'byung //
NK023('a)001:6620: phyag 'tshal rdo rje snying po la'o //
NK023('a)001:6621: de yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:6623: badz+ra rat+na rin chen dkar lho'i mdun /
NK023('a)001:6624: h'u rdo rje gzi brjid che 'bar ba //
NK023('a)001:6625: rdo rje nyi ma rgyal ba'i 'od //
NK023('a)001:6626: rdo rje gzi brjid 'od zer che //
NK023('a)001:6628: de yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:6630: badz+ra sur+ya badz+ra te dza nyi ma'am gzi brjid ser lho yi g.yas /
NK023('a)001:6631: h'u rdo rje sems can don rab gsal //
NK023('a)001:6632: rdo rje rgyal mtshan rab dga' byed //
NK023('a)001:6633: rdo rje chen po rin chen dpal //
NK023('a)001:6634: phyag 'tshal rdo rje dpal khyod la'o //
NK023('a)001:6635: de yi dbang mchog sbyin gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:6637: badz+ra ke tu rgyal mtshan dmar lho rgyab /
NK023('a)001:6638: h'u rdo rje bzhad mo bzhad pa che //
NK023('a)001:6639: rdo rje 'dzum pa ngo mtshar che //
NK023('a)001:6640: dga' zhing rab dga' rdo rje ston //
NK023('a)001:6641: phyag 'tshal rdo rje dga' khyod la'o //
NK023('a)001:6642: de yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:6646: h'u 'dod chags rdo rje chos kyi sku //
NK023('a)001:6647: kun rtog ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK023('a)001:6648: rdo rje ting 'dzin phyag rgya mdzad //
NK023('a)001:6649: phyag 'tshal snang ba mtha' yas la'o //
NK023('a)001:6650: de yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:6652: a mi d+he ba h+r+aih 'od dpag med dmar rma bya'i khri //
NK023('a)001:6654: h'u rdo rje chos rab rdo rje don //
NK023('a)001:6655: rdo rje pad+ma rab dga' byed //
NK023('a)001:6656: 'jig rten dbang phyug chos rab mdzes //
NK023('a)001:6657: phyag 'tshal rdo rje spyan khyod la'o //
NK023('a)001:6658: de yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:6660: badz+ra d+harma chos dmar dmar skya nub kyi mdun /
NK023('a)001:6661: h'u rdo rje rnon po theg pa che //
NK023('a)001:6662: rdo rje ral gri mtshon chen po //
NK023('a)001:6663: 'jam dpal rdo rje rab tu dga' //
NK023('a)001:6664: phyag 'tshal rdo rje blo khyod la'o //
NK023('a)001:6665: de yi dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:6667: badz+ra tig sna rnon po nub kyi g.yas /
NK023('a)001:6668: h'u rdo rje rgyu dang snying po che //
NK023('a)001:6669: rdo rje 'khor lo tshul chen po //
NK023('a)001:6670: rab skor rdo rje rang las byung ba //
NK023('a)001:6672: de yi dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:6674: badz+ra he du badz+ra tsakra 'khor lo'am rgyu mtshan /
NK023('a)001:6675: gtan tshig dam nub kyi rgyab /
NK023('a)001:6676: h'u rdo rje gsung ba rang rig mchog /
NK023('a)001:6677: rdo rje bzlos pa rab grub sbyin //
NK023('a)001:6678: mi gsung rdo rje mchog grub smra //
NK023('a)001:6679: phyag 'tshal rdo rje gsung khyod la'o //
NK023('a)001:6680: de yi dbang mchod sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:6682: badz+ra bag sha smra ba ljang nub kyi g.yon /
NK023('a)001:6683: h'u phrag dog rdo rje bskyed mdzad klu //
NK023('a)001:6684: bya grub ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK023('a)001:6685: rdo rje skyabs sbyin phyag rgya mdzad //
NK023('a)001:6686: phyag 'tshal rdo rje gsung khyod la'o //
NK023('a)001:6687: de yi dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:6690: don yon grub pa ljang shang shang gi khri byang gi dbus /
NK023('a)001:6691: h'u rdo rje las rab rdo rje'i bka' //
NK023('a)001:6692: las kyi rdo rje kun rab 'gro //
NK023('a)001:6693: rdo rje nges pa rgya che ba //
NK023('a)001:6694: phyag 'tshal rdo rje kun khyod la'o //
NK023('a)001:6695: de yi dbang mchog sbyin par bya /
NK023('a)001:6697: rdo rje karma las dkar ljang byang gi mdun /
NK023('a)001:6698: h'u rdo rje bsrung ba brtan pa che //
NK023('a)001:6699: rdo rje go cha sra ba che //
NK023('a)001:6700: brtson 'grus rdo rje thugs kha ba //
NK023('a)001:6702: de yi dbang mchog khyed la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:6704: badz+ra rak+sha srung ba ser byang gi g.yas /
NK023('a)001:6705: h'u rdo rje gnod sbyin thabs chen po //
NK023('a)001:6706: rdo rje mche ba gtsig pa che //
NK023('a)001:6707: bdud 'joms rdo rje mi bzad pa //
NK023('a)001:6708: phyag 'tshal rdo rje drag po la'o //
NK023('a)001:6709: de yi dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:6712: gnod spyin dmar byang gi rgyab /
NK023('a)001:6713: h+aum rdo rje mtshams sbyor rab tu 'dul //
NK023('a)001:6714: rdo rje bcings par rab grol byed //
NK023('a)001:6715: rdo rje khu tshur dam tshig mchog /
NK023('a)001:6716: phyag 'tshal rdo rje khu tshur la'o //
NK023('a)001:6717: de yi dbang mchog thob gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:6719: rdo rje khu tshur gyis 'bebs pa'i phyag rgyas thams cad gcig tu sangs rgyas su byed /
NK023('a)001:6720: sku mdog ljang byang gi g.yon /
NK023('a)001:6721: h+aum shar phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK023('a)001:6723: phyag mtshan phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6724: de la bstod de phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK023('a)001:6725: de yi dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:6728: h+aum lho phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK023('a)001:6730: phyag mtshan phyag na zhags pa bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6731: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6732: de yi dbang mchog spyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:6735: h+aum nub phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK023('a)001:6737: phyag mtshan phyag na lcags sgrog bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6738: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6739: de yi dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:6742: h+aum byang phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK023('a)001:6744: phyag mtshan phyag na dril bu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6745: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6746: dbang mchog dam pa bskur bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:6749: h+aum shar phyogs lha mo la se ma //
NK023('a)001:6751: phyag gnyis khu tshur me long 'chang //
NK023('a)001:6752: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6753: dbang mchog dam pa bskur bar bya //
NK023('a)001:6757: h+aum lho phyogs lha mo ma le ma //
NK023('a)001:6759: phyag gnyis rin chen phreng ba bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6760: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6763: h+aum nub phyogs lha mo g+hirti ma //
NK023('a)001:6765: phyag gnyis pi wam rgyud ldan bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6766: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6767: dbang mchog a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:6769: h+aum byang phyogs lha mo nirti la //
NK023('a)001:6771: phyag gnyis phyag rgya gar bsgyur ma //
NK023('a)001:6772: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6773: dbang mchog a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:6775: h+aum shar lho lha mo d+hu pe ma //
NK023('a)001:6777: phyag mtshan phyag na spos khang thogs //
NK023('a)001:6778: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6779: dbang mchog a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:6781: h+aum lho nub lha mo pup+pe ma //
NK023('a)001:6782: phyag mtshan phyag na me tog bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6783: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6784: dbang mchog a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:6786: h+aum nub byang lha mo a lo ke //
NK023('a)001:6788: phyag mtshan phyag na mar me bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6789: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6790: dbang mchog a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:6792: h+aum byang shar lha mo g+han d+he ma //
NK023('a)001:6794: phyag mtshan phyag na dri chab bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6795: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6796: dbang mchog dam pa a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:6798: dpa' bar 'gro ba la sogs pa //
NK023('a)001:6799: bska la bzang sems dpa' bcu drug dang //
NK023('a)001:6800: rdo rje dpal ldan la sogs pa //
NK023('a)001:6801: bkra shis lha mo brgyad rnams dang //
NK023('a)001:6802: brgya byin dbang po la sogs pa //
NK023('a)001:6803: phyogs skyongs chos skyongs thams cad dang //
NK023('a)001:6804: nyan thos rang rgyal la sogs pa //
NK023('a)001:6805: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs thams cad kun //
NK023('a)001:6807: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:6808: mdo dbang yo ga rdo rje dbyings lugs gcig tu /
NK023('a)001:6809: dbus dkar po chos dbyings ye shes dang /
NK023('a)001:6810: de nas shar lho mtshams dang shar gang rung la /
NK023('a)001:6811: rdo rje sems dpa' dkar po bshad /
NK023('a)001:6812: lugs gnyis pa dbus gser mdog thub pa chos dbyings dang /
NK023('a)001:6813: shar dkar lho sngo nub dmar byang ljang ste /
NK023('a)001:6814: rdo rje sems ma ni gtso bo'i kha dog ser mor kyang gsal zhing dkar mor kyang mdzad /
NK023('a)001:6815: lugs gsum par de gnyis gang byed kyang gtso bo
NK023('a)001:6816: kun tu zhal gtso 'khor lugs re re la'ang lngas
NK023('a)001:6817: bskor na kha dog kyang lnga'o //
NK023('a)001:6818: gral thabs lugs la gtso bo yang zhal gcig dang sems dpa' bcu drug phyogs mdog mdzad /
NK023('a)001:6819: 'dir rnam snang gser mdog lugs kyi rgyab yig ni dbus phyogs snying po rnam snang mdzad /
NK023('a)001:6820: sku mdog gser po gser gyi 'od //
NK023('a)001:6821: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya mdzad //
NK023('a)001:6823: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:6826: shar phyogs mngon par dga' ba mi bskyod pa //
NK023('a)001:6827: sku mdog dkar po gangs dkar ri //
NK023('a)001:6828: sa gnon chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK023('a)001:6829: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6831: lho phyogs dpal ldan rin chen 'byung //
NK023('a)001:6832: sku mdog sngon po nam mkha' mdzod //
NK023('a)001:6833: mchog sbyin chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK023('a)001:6834: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6836: nub phyogs dpal ldan snang mtha' yas //
NK023('a)001:6837: sku mdog dmar po byi ru'i mdog /
NK023('a)001:6838: bsam gtan chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK023('a)001:6839: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6840: a mi de ba h+r+aih byang phyogs rnam dag gdon mi za //
NK023('a)001:6841: sku mdog ljang ku in tra'i mdog /
NK023('a)001:6842: skyabs sbyin chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK023('a)001:6843: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6844: a mo g+ha sid d+hi a /
NK023('a)001:6845: shar phyogs yum chen sangs rgyas spyan //
NK023('a)001:6847: dam tshig phyag rgya rdo rje bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6848: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:6850: lho phyogs yum chen ma ma ki //
NK023('a)001:6851: sku mdog sngo la rin chen de la rat+na badz+ri /
NK023('a)001:6852: nub phyogs yum chen na bza' dkar //
NK023('a)001:6853: sku mdog dmar la pad+ma de la pad+ma badz+ri /
NK023('a)001:6854: byang phyogs yum chen dam tshig sgrol //
NK023('a)001:6855: sku mdog ljang la rgya gram karma badz+ri /
NK023('a)001:6856: yum bzhi le tshe'i zur bzhi ste //
NK023('a)001:6857: lugs gcig rdo rje rin chen chos la sems ma zer //
NK023('a)001:6858: le tshe'i phyogs kyi re mig nang du 'khor lo
NK023('a)001:6859: rtsibs bzhi la gtso 'khor du sems dpa' bcu drug
NK023('a)001:6860: / bya ba'am gral thabs lugs kyi 'khor lo rtsibs bcu drug pa'am /
NK023('a)001:6861: khyams kyi phyogs dang gru'i logs la bkod de /
NK023('a)001:6862: rgyal sras rdo rje sems dpal ni //
NK023('a)001:6864: dam tshig phyag rgya rdo rje bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6866: rgyal sras rdo rje rgyal po ni //
NK023('a)001:6867: dkar lcags kyu badz+ra ra tsa /
NK023('a)001:6868: rgyal sras rdo rje chags pa ni //
NK023('a)001:6869: dkar mda' gzhu badz+ra ra ga /
NK023('a)001:6870: rgyal sras rdo rje legs pa ni //
NK023('a)001:6873: yang na dkar sngo dmar ljang shar gyi mdun g.yas rgyab g.yon du'o //
NK023('a)001:6874: lhor sngo dmar dkar ljang dkar po'am //
NK023('a)001:6875: rgyal sras rdo rje rin chen ni //
NK023('a)001:6877: dam tshig phyag rgya rin chen bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6879: rgyal sras rdo rje gzi brjid ni //
NK023('a)001:6882: yang na rdo rje nyi ma ni /
NK023('a)001:6884: rgyal sras rdo rje rgyal mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:6887: rgyal sras rdo rje bzhad pa ni //
NK023('a)001:6891: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:6892: lugs gcig tu 'khor lo mdun lnga dkar /
NK023('a)001:6895: rgyab lnga dmar ba yang yin par bshad /
NK023('a)001:6896: rgyal sras rdo rje mchog gi mchog /
NK023('a)001:6898: dam tshig phyag rgya pad+ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6900: rgyal sras rdo rje rnon po ni //
NK023('a)001:6901: dmar ral gri badz+ra tig sna hrih rgyal sras rdo rje 'khor lo ni //
NK023('a)001:6904: rdo rje ru mtshon snying po ni /
NK023('a)001:6906: rgyal sras rdo rje smra ba ni /
NK023('a)001:6907: dmar dam tshig phyag rgya rdo rje'i lce /
NK023('a)001:6909: yang na dmar ljang dkar sngo /
NK023('a)001:6910: nub kyi mdun g.yas rgyab g.yon tu'o //
NK023('a)001:6911: byang du ljang dkar sngo dmar po'am //
NK023('a)001:6912: rgyal sras rdo rje las rab ni //
NK023('a)001:6914: dam tshig phyag rgya rgya gram bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6916: rgyal sras rdo rje srung ba ni //
NK023('a)001:6917: ljang go cha badz+ra rak+sha a /
NK023('a)001:6918: rgyal sras rdo rje gnod sbyin ni //
NK023('a)001:6919: ljang rdo rje mche ba badz+ra yak+sha a /
NK023('a)001:6920: rgyal sras rdo rje khu tshur ni //
NK023('a)001:6921: ljang rdo rje khu tshur bsnams /
NK023('a)001:6924: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:6926: shar phyogs rdo rje sgeg mo ni //
NK023('a)001:6928: dam tshig phyag rgya me long bsnams //
NK023('a)001:6930: lho phyogs rin chen phreng ba ni //
NK023('a)001:6931: sngo la rin chen phreng ba badz+ra ma le /
NK023('a)001:6932: nub phyogs rdo rje sgra dbyangs ma //
NK023('a)001:6935: byang phyogs rdo rje gar bsgyur ma //
NK023('a)001:6938: shar lho lha mo bdug pa ma /
NK023('a)001:6939: dkar la spos khang badz+ra d+hu pam /
NK023('a)001:6940: lha nub rdo rje me tog ma /
NK023('a)001:6941: sngo la me tog badz+ra pus pam /
NK023('a)001:6942: nub byang rdo rje mar me ma /
NK023('a)001:6943: dmar la sgron me badz+ra di pam /
NK023('a)001:6944: byang shar rdo rje dri chab ma /
NK023('a)001:6945: ljang la dri'i dung chos badz+ra g+han d+ham /
NK023('a)001:6946: shar phyogs sgo skyong lcags kyu ma /
NK023('a)001:6947: dkar lcags kyu badz+ra am ku sha dza /
NK023('a)001:6948: lho phyogs sgo skyong zhags pa ma /
NK023('a)001:6949: sngo la zhags pa badz+ra pa sha h'u /
NK023('a)001:6950: nub phyogs sgo skyong lcags sgrogs ma /
NK023('a)001:6951: dmar la lcags sgrog badz+ra spo tra bam /
NK023('a)001:6952: byang phyogs sgo skyongs dril bu ma /
NK023('a)001:6953: ljang la dril bu badz+ra g+han te ho /
NK023('a)001:6955: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:6957: sku mdog dang rgyab yig lugs gnyis byung yang /
NK023('a)001:6958: rdor dbyings su dkyil 'khor gcig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:6959: yo ga lha dbang gis thog ma'am rjes la dngos
NK023('a)001:6960: dang tsa ka'i rab gnas bsos la rdzas dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:6961: te / thog mar chu'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:6962: bum chu gtso bum du bsdus las tshar ba dang
NK023('a)001:6963: bum pa dung chos lta bu gcig gis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:6964: ba ni / lha grangs kyi bum pa sogs de
NK023('a)001:6965: ltar du gtso bo rigs lnga rigs ma bzhi ni
NK023('a)001:6967: phung po lnga 'byung ba chen po bzhi zhes pa yo ga rigs lngar bzhed pa dang /
NK023('a)001:6968: mtshan nyid du nam mkha' 'byung bar mi bzhed pa dang mthun /
NK023('a)001:6969: skabs 'dir gtso bo lnga yang yum ye shes dkyil 'khor sku 'khor gsung gtso bo /
NK023('a)001:6973: bdag dam tshig bar ting nge 'dzin /
NK023('a)001:6974: dbyer med rdo rje sems dpa' bzhi las /
NK023('a)001:6975: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs gcig tu mdzad nas badz+ra
NK023('a)001:6976: sa t+wa h'u zhes yo ga dpal mchog tu gsungs
NK023('a)001:6977: pa de / yo ga rdo rje dbyings kyi lha spyi'i snying por mdzad kyang /
NK023('a)001:6978: de'i gtso bo mchog snang mdzad kyis thugs chos dbyings ye shes kyi rang 'dod /
NK023('a)001:6979: chos kyi dbyings kyi dbang phyug mar shar ba de rnam snang gis rang 'od rig mar byas /
NK023('a)001:6983: bla ma ngas bum pa gcig bkra shis kyi yo
NK023('a)001:6984: byad kyis bkang ba slob ma'i spyi bor bzhag ste
NK023('a)001:6985: dbang bskur bas las dang nyon mongs pa'i bag chags
NK023('a)001:6986: dang bral zhing byang chub kyi sems rtogs pa'i brlan
NK023('a)001:6987: gyis bla na med pa'i byang chub tu ma thar
NK023('a)001:6988: phyin pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:6989: sgrib pa dag byed bdud rtsi dri med chu //
NK023('a)001:6990: bkra shis mdzes pa'i bum pa rab bkang ste //
NK023('a)001:6991: rigs kyi sangs rgyas kun du rab grub phyir //
NK023('a)001:6992: bum pa'i dbang gis khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:6993: b+hud+d+ha ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK023('a)001:6994: badz+ra ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:6995: rat+na ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa tram /
NK023('a)001:6996: pad+ma ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih karma ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK023('a)001:6998: yum lngar byas na chos dbyings gtso bo kha dog phyag na 'khor lo can du gsal lo //
NK023('a)001:7001: rna ltag g.yas par dar mthing ga bzhags /
NK023('a)001:7002: rna ltag g.yon par dar leb brgan bzhag /
NK023('a)001:7003: mgo la rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas kyis dbu rgyan bcings te /
NK023('a)001:7004: rdo rje slob dpon ngas slob bu la cod pan dang bcas pa'i dbu rgyan gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7005: tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'bral bu mthar phyin
NK023('a)001:7006: pa'i rgyal ba rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas myur du thob
NK023('a)001:7007: pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7008: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK023('a)001:7009: mkhyen pa'i ye shes rab rgyas pa //
NK023('a)001:7010: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas myur du rab 'grub phyir //
NK023('a)001:7011: dbu rgyan dbang gis khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:7016: pad+ma hrih karma a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK023('a)001:7017: gsum pa bdag po'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:7018: slob dpon du dbang bskur te /
NK023('a)001:7019: lag pa g.yas par 'khor lo sbyin /
NK023('a)001:7021: bla ma ngas slob bu la rigs thams cad kyi
NK023('a)001:7022: bdag po dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi byed pa pos
NK023('a)001:7023: dbang bskur bas / tshe rabs brgyud pa rnams su
NK023('a)001:7024: 'gro ba'i shes rgyud la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK023('a)001:7025: zhing nye ring med par thos pa'i chos kyi sgra
NK023('a)001:7026: sgrog par rdo rje slob dpon thob par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:7027: dbang bskur bas / / chos la dbang bsgyur bdag po dang //
NK023('a)001:7028: dkyil 'khor kun gyis byed pa po'i //
NK023('a)001:7029: sangs rgyas kun tu rab 'grub phyir //
NK023('a)001:7030: bdag po'i dbang gis khyod dbang bskur //
NK023('a)001:7031: badz+ra tsakra a d+hi pa di stom /
NK023('a)001:7036: bzhi pa 'khor gyi phyag rgya'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:7037: rigs lnga'i 'khor dang rigs gang rung gis skabs sbyar ro //
NK023('a)001:7038: sems dpa' bcu drug gi dbang phyag mtshan nam rims kyis slob ma'i lag tu byin zhing /
NK023('a)001:7039: slob dpon ngas slob ma khyod la rdo rje sems
NK023('a)001:7040: dpa'i phyag mtshan rdo rje byin te dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:7041: ye shes su rtogs nas mtha' gnyis su mi 'gyur
NK023('a)001:7042: ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7043: sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:7044: de ring khyod la bskur bar 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:7045: sangs rgyas kun tu rab 'grub phyir //
NK023('a)001:7046: rdo rje'i ming gis khyod dbang bskur //
NK023('a)001:7047: badz+ra a ti pa ti stom /
NK023('a)001:7049: tish+ta badz+ra sa ma ya stom /
NK023('a)001:7050: 'og ma kun la yang sngags 'dis sbyar /
NK023('a)001:7051: slob dpon slob ma dang dbang bskur bar mthun pa la /
NK023('a)001:7052: rdo rje rgyal po dang rdo rje chags pa dang
NK023('a)001:7053: rdo rje legs pa dang zhes dang tshig bshad kyang
NK023('a)001:7054: mthun pa las / sangs rgyas kun gyi lcags kyu'i dbang /
NK023('a)001:7056: se gol dbang zhes so sor sbyar /
NK023('a)001:7058: rdo rje rgyal po'i phyag mtshan lcags kyu byin pas dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7059: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad gnas nas spyan 'dren
NK023('a)001:7060: cing sems can thams cad 'khor ba nas bsdus nus
NK023('a)001:7061: pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7062: chags pa'i phyag mtshan me tog gi mda' lag tu
NK023('a)001:7063: byin te dbang bskur bas chos kyi dbyings las 'big
NK023('a)001:7064: pa'i shes rab kyis dus gsum rgyal ba rnams la
NK023('a)001:7065: thugs dam gyis rgyud bskul ba'i dbang dang ldan par
NK023('a)001:7066: gyur cig / rdo rje legs pa'i phyag mtshan lag tu se gol byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7067: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i dga' bas gzengs bstod pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7068: rdo rje rin chen gyi phyag mtshan rin po che 'bar ba lag tu byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7069: dus gsum gyi chos kyi rgyal mtshan chen por dbang sgyur nus pa'i mthu dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7070: rdo rje nyi ma'i phyag mtshan nyi ma 'khor lo lag tu byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7071: gti mug mun pa sel ba'i rgyal ba thams cad
NK023('a)001:7072: kyi rgyal thabs can gyi 'od byed pa'i dbang dang
NK023('a)001:7074: rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyi phyag mtshan rgyal mtshan lag tu byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7075: sbyin pa'i pha rol du phyin pa dang yongs su
NK023('a)001:7076: rdzogs pa'i mtshan nyid dbul ba gcod pa'i dpal gyis
NK023('a)001:7077: dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7078: rdo rje bzhad pa'i phyag mtshan po'i phreng ba lag
NK023('a)001:7079: tu byin te dbang bskur bas skyes bu chen po'i
NK023('a)001:7080: 'dzum gyis lung bstan pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK023('a)001:7081: cig / rdo rje chos kyi phyag mtshan pad+ma byin
NK023('a)001:7082: te dbang bskur bas 'dod chags rnam par dag pa'i
NK023('a)001:7083: mtshan nyid chos thams cad la mi chags pa'i ngo
NK023('a)001:7084: bo nyid du gzigs pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK023('a)001:7085: cig / cig / rdo rje rnon po'i phyag mtshan ral gri byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7086: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gsung gis rjes
NK023('a)001:7087: su 'brang ba'i shes rab dam pa yongs su rdzogs
NK023('a)001:7088: pa nyon mongs pa gcod pa'i dbang dang ldan par
NK023('a)001:7089: gyur cig / rdo rje 'khor lo'i phyag mtshan rgyu'i phyag mtshan 'khor lo byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7090: sems bskyed ma thag tu sems can gyis don la
NK023('a)001:7091: phyir mi ldog pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i
NK023('a)001:7092: dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7093: rdo rje smra ba'i phyag mtshan lce rdo rjes mtshan
NK023('a)001:7094: pa byin te dbang bskur bas gdul bya'i bsam pa
NK023('a)001:7095: dang sbyar nas ldem po ngag tu chos ston pa'i
NK023('a)001:7096: dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7097: rdo rje las kyis phyag mtshan rdo rje rgya gram
NK023('a)001:7098: lag tu byin te dbang bskur bas 'phags pa mchod
NK023('a)001:7099: pa dang sems can gyis don bya ba'i phrin las
NK023('a)001:7100: lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:7101: / rdo rje go cha'i phyag mtshan go cha byin
NK023('a)001:7102: te dbang bskur bas 'jigs pa chen po brgyad las
NK023('a)001:7103: thar cing mtha' gnyis su mi ltung par bsrung ba'i
NK023('a)001:7104: dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7105: rdo rje gnod sbyin gyis phyag mtshan phag rgod kyi mche ba lag tu byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7106: bdud thams cad 'dul zhing gdug pa thams cad rtsad nas gcod pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7107: rdo rje khu tshur gyis phyag mtshan khu tshur lag tu byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7108: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis sku gsung thugs
NK023('a)001:7109: gcig tu 'dus par rtogs pa'i dbang dang ldan par
NK023('a)001:7110: gyur cig / lnga pa kun 'gro mchod lha bcu gnyis kyi dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:7111: slob dpon sti ra ma ti sa mdzad pa'i yo ga mya ngan dam pa las /
NK023('a)001:7112: sgo ma bzhi bsdu ba rnam par bzhi dang /
NK023('a)001:7113: mchod lha tshad med bzhi dang /
NK023('a)001:7114: gzungs ma bzhi ye shes bzhir gsungs shing /
NK023('a)001:7115: tshig bsgyur ba dang sngags gong dang 'agree'o //
NK023('a)001:7116: lcags kyu ma'i phyag rgya lcags kyu byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7117: sbyin pas bsdus pa phun sum 'tshogs pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7118: zhags pa ma'i phyag rgya zhags pa byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7119: don dang mthun par smra bas bsdud pa phun sum 'tshogs pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7120: lcags sgrog ma'i phyag rgya lcags sgrog byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7121: don spyod pas bsdu ba phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7122: dril bu ma'i phyag rgya dril bu byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7123: snyan par smra bas bsdu ba phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7124: d+hu pe ma'i phyag rgya spos byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7125: byams pa tshad med kyis thabs dang shes rab kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7126: pup+pe ma'i phyag rgya me tog byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7127: snying rje tshad med pa thabs dang shes rab kyis dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7128: a lo ke'i phyag rgya sgron me byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7129: dga' ba tshad med pa dang thabs dang shes rab kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7130: g+han d+he ma'i phyag rgya tsan d+han bdud rtsi dung
NK023('a)001:7131: chos byin te dbang bskur bas btang snyoms tshad med
NK023('a)001:7132: pa dang shes rab kyis dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK023('a)001:7133: cig / gzungs ma la s+ye ma'i phyag rgya me long tu byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7134: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis sgeg mo'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7135: gzung ma ma l+ye ma'i phyag rgya phreng ba lag
NK023('a)001:7136: tu byin te dbang bskur bas mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK023('a)001:7137: ye shes phreng ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:7138: / gzungs ma girti ma'i phyag rgya pi wam lag
NK023('a)001:7139: tu byin te dbang bskur bas sor rtog ye shes
NK023('a)001:7140: glu dbyangs mkhan ma'i dbyangs dang ldan par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:7141: / / gzungs ma nirti ma'i phyag rgya gar chas can lag tu byin te dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7142: bya ba grub pa'i nan tan ye shes kyi gar
NK023('a)001:7143: mkhan gzi brjid thob pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK023('a)001:7144: cig / bzhi pa ming dbang 'gro don gyis rdzas gnyis ni /
NK023('a)001:7145: ming dbang ni rdo rje las gras pa'i ming btags la /
NK023('a)001:7146: lag pa g.yas g.yon du me long dang mda' gzhu byin te /
NK023('a)001:7147: kye rdo rje dbang phyug che ge mo khyod kyis
NK023('a)001:7148: chos thams cad gzugs brnyan dang 'dra bar ltos la
NK023('a)001:7149: / thabs kyi gzhu dang shes rab kyi mdas 'gro
NK023('a)001:7150: ba'i don byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:7151: / / sangs rgyas rnams kyis ming gis dbang //
NK023('a)001:7152: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK023('a)001:7153: sangs rgyas kun tu rab bsgrubs phyir //
NK023('a)001:7154: ming gi dbang gis khyod dbang bskur //
NK023('a)001:7155: badz+ra ba sa t+wa a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK023('a)001:7157: a b+hi she ka ta a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK023('a)001:7158: de'i rting la bdun pa rdzas spyi rgyas pa dang /
NK023('a)001:7159: bsdus pa las bsdus par bkra shis rdzas brgyad dang /
NK023('a)001:7160: rin po che sna bdun gyi dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:7161: rgyas par phyi dbang brgya rtsa brgyad kyis dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:7162: mtshams par yo ga bkra shis drug cu rtsa gnyis su dbang bskur bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:7163: phyi dbang brgya rtsa'i rkang grangs /
NK023('a)001:7164: yo ga la gtso bor dkar dang ser dang /
NK023('a)001:7165: 'khor tshom bu dang gral thabs gang byas kyang rtsa
NK023('a)001:7166: ba so bdun dang mtha' rdzas lha du yod kyang
NK023('a)001:7167: dal gcig tu byed rig gcig yin gsungs /
NK023('a)001:7168: yo ga'i rdzas dbang sgos kyi drug cu rtsa gnyis
NK023('a)001:7169: spyir du dbang grangs dbang don rgyas pa na gsal
NK023('a)001:7170: / phyi dbang dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa lnga ni /
NK023('a)001:7182: tshogs ma bu ni phyi cha gsum /
NK023('a)001:7183: rdo rje sems dpa' 'khor dang 'gron thams cad la gcig /
NK023('a)001:7184: bsod nams gtor sbyin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK023('a)001:7186: phrin las mtshams sbyor zhi khro dang /
NK023('a)001:7187: rtsa ba zhi khro phrin las dang /
NK023('a)001:7190: lhag ma mjug sdud de bdun no //
NK023('a)001:7191: lha mi la rnam snang gis ngan 'gro sbyong ba dang /
NK023('a)001:7192: mi 'khrugs pas zhing sbyong ba dang /
NK023('a)001:7193: sman lha nad zhi bar dang /
NK023('a)001:7194: snang mtha' mtshon 'khrug zhi ba dang /
NK023('a)001:7195: sh+aaka thub mu ge zhi ba dang lnga'o //
NK023('a)001:7196: nyan thos la 'khor gnyis rab byung dang khyim pa ste 'phags pa dang skye bo mtshon pa /
NK023('a)001:7203: 'khor lo bcu drug mchog ye shes bcu drug dang /
NK023('a)001:7205: mchog nas gtan sprul pa'am rang rgyud do //
NK023('a)001:7207: bse ru ne tso phyi nang dang /
NK023('a)001:7208: 'khor gnyis bse ru ne tso la gsum phyi nang re'ang tra te bzhi dang /
NK023('a)001:7214: lha brgya rnams gtso bo dang mthun pa dang /
NK023('a)001:7215: yum chen mo lugs gnyis so //
NK023('a)001:7217: lha drug lha bco lnga ma gsum gtso bos phye ba dagu'o //
NK023('a)001:7218: u pa ya sku gsung thugs ye shes gtso bo bzhi'o //
NK023('a)001:7221: byang sems bya spyod rnal 'byor gyi rdzas dbang lags /
NK023('a)001:7223: phyi dbang brgya rtsa brgyad du bskur zhes so //
NK023('a)001:7225: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK023('a)001:7226: phyi dbang brgyud kyi chu bo bya //
NK023('a)001:7228: lha mi la le'u bcu gcig /
NK023('a)001:7230: byang chub sems dpa' le'u gnyis /
NK023('a)001:7231: de thams cad byang chub sems dpa' don 'grub gyi mdzad pa nyi shu'o //
NK023('a)001:7232: sngon byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po
NK023('a)001:7233: de dga' ldan gyis gnas nas yum sgyu ma lha
NK023('a)001:7234: mdzes kyi lhums su gshegs pa'i dus su /
NK023('a)001:7235: dbu la rin po che'i srog zhu phud nas mi
NK023('a)001:7236: pham mgon po la chos kyi rgyal tshab tu lha
NK023('a)001:7237: rnams kyi ston pa mdzad par dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:7238: de dang rjes su mthun par rin po che'i cod
NK023('a)001:7239: pan gyis dbang bskur bas chos kyi rgyal tshab chen
NK023('a)001:7240: po dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7241: h+aum tog dkar dbu la rin chen cod pan bshus //
NK023('a)001:7242: de nyid phyag gis kho bo'i dbu la bzhag /
NK023('a)001:7243: mi pham mgon po chos kyi rgyal tshab rje //
NK023('a)001:7244: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po byed par shog /
NK023('a)001:7245: chos kyi dbyings nas byung nas gang na bar //
NK023('a)001:7246: sprul sku kun khyab yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK023('a)001:7247: dang po tshogs rdzogs yongs la mthar phyin pa //
NK023('a)001:7248: 'di ni bsod nams rdzogs pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste dang po'o //
NK023('a)001:7250: // sngon byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po
NK023('a)001:7251: de yum sgyu ma lha mdzes kyi lhums na bzhugs
NK023('a)001:7252: pa dang / yum gyi phyag gis sems can thams cad la reg cing dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7253: sems can thams cad kyi las dang nyon mongs pa
NK023('a)001:7254: dang na tsha'i sdug bsngal thams cad zhi bar gyur
NK023('a)001:7255: to // de dang rjes su mthun par yum gyi
NK023('a)001:7256: phyag gis reg cing dbang bskur bas slob ma 'di
NK023('a)001:7257: zhes bya ba nyon mongs pa na tsha'i sdug bsngal
NK023('a)001:7258: thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7259: sgyu ma lha mdzes lha'i lcam /
NK023('a)001:7260: lha'i lus la rin chen mdzes /
NK023('a)001:7261: nyon mongs sdug bsngal kun zhi nas //
NK023('a)001:7262: na tsha'i sdug bsngal thar bar shog /
NK023('a)001:7263: byin rlabs yum chen shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK023('a)001:7264: kun la byams snyoms thugs rjes che ba'i ma //
NK023('a)001:7265: gzhan la phan mdzad don gnyis lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:7266: 'di ni grub pa'i dbang gi bkra shis gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7268: // sngon byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po
NK023('a)001:7269: de tshal lhum pa'i tshal du yum gyi lhums nas
NK023('a)001:7270: bltams pa dang seng ge phru gu zung gcig gis
NK023('a)001:7271: bskor ba byas shing dbang bskur bar bsdo ba'i phyogs
NK023('a)001:7272: zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang thob bo //
NK023('a)001:7273: de dang rjes mthun par seng ge phru gu zung
NK023('a)001:7274: gcig gis dbang bskur bas bsdo ba'i phyogs thams cad
NK023('a)001:7275: zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7276: seng ge nga ro skad chen thogs med pas /
NK023('a)001:7277: 'jigs pa med pa'i sgra rnams bsgrags nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:7278: bar du gcod pa'i bdud kyi sde btul te //
NK023('a)001:7279: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK023('a)001:7280: thams cad zil gnon cho 'phrul che ba'i lha //
NK023('a)001:7281: yon tan kun tshangs gdugs pa zil gyis gnon //
NK023('a)001:7282: che ba'i mthu stobs kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK023('a)001:7283: 'di ni che btsan mthu stobs dbang gi bkra shis gsum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7285: // sngon yum sgyu ma lha mdzes grong khyer ser skya na bzhugs pa la /
NK023('a)001:7286: glang po che phru gu gnyis kyis sna phug cing dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7287: 'jig rten 'degs pa'i stobs dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7288: de dang rjes su mthun par glang po che phru
NK023('a)001:7289: gu zung gcig gis dbang bskur bas 'jig rten 'degs
NK023('a)001:7290: pa'i stobs dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK023('a)001:7291: gyur cig / 'jig rten 'degs pa'i stobs ldan zhing //
NK023('a)001:7292: theg pa bzhi yi don rtogs nas //
NK023('a)001:7293: bye brag phyed pa'i stobs rdzogs te //
NK023('a)001:7294: stobs kyi pha rol rdzogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:7295: mthu stobs phun sum 'tshogs ldan pa'i //
NK023('a)001:7296: rin chen gser rgyan kun gyis brgyan //
NK023('a)001:7297: dpe byad mtshan rdzogs glang po'i stobs //
NK023('a)001:7298: 'di ni stobs bcu ldan pa yis //
NK023('a)001:7299: bdag gi bkra shis bzhi pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7301: // sngon byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po de /
NK023('a)001:7302: byang chub kyi shing brgyan 'byams kyi tshal rab tu yum gyi lhums nas bltams pa la /
NK023('a)001:7303: tshangs pa dang brgya byin gyis blangs nas na bza'
NK023('a)001:7304: ka shi ka gsol te dbang bskur bas mkhyen pa'i
NK023('a)001:7305: bye brag la gsal zhing ma 'dres pa'i dbang thob
NK023('a)001:7306: par gyur te / de dang rjes su mthun par bza' ka shi ka'i ras kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7307: mkhyen pa'i ye shes gsal zhing ma 'dres pa'i dam pa thob par gyur gcig /
NK023('a)001:7308: nyon mongs skyon spangs ka shi'i ras /
NK023('a)001:7309: legs pa'i yon tan kun rdzogs te //
NK023('a)001:7310: nyes pa'i skyon las skyobs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:7311: mkhyen pa'i bye brag gsal bar shog /
NK023('a)001:7312: tshangs pa brgya byin bsod nams dag pa'i lha //
NK023('a)001:7313: lha yi rgyal po blon po tshangs pa'i sku //
NK023('a)001:7314: mngon shes lnga ldan mchod pa'i zhu ba'i bdag /
NK023('a)001:7315: 'di ni yon tan bkra shis dbang gi bkra shis lnga pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7317: // sngon bcom ldan 'das yum gyi lhum na bltams pa las /
NK023('a)001:7318: klu'i rgyal po dga' bo dang nye dga' bo gnyis
NK023('a)001:7319: kyis lho phyogs su chu rta rnga 'dzin nas bdud
NK023('a)001:7320: rtsi'i chu blangs nas rgyal bu la khrus gsol bas
NK023('a)001:7321: nyon mongs pa'i bag chags kyi dri ma dag pa'i
NK023('a)001:7322: dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7323: de dang rjes su mthun par rdzas 'dis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:7324: bas slob ma 'di yi nyon mongs pa bag chags
NK023('a)001:7325: kyi dri ma dag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK023('a)001:7326: gyur cig / klu'i rgyal pos bdud rtsi'i chu bcus te /
NK023('a)001:7327: bcom ldan 'das kyis drin lan blan pa dang /
NK023('a)001:7328: bag chags dri ma yongs su dag bya'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:7329: bag chags skyon gyi dri ma dag par shog /
NK023('a)001:7330: yon tan kun ldan byang chub sems dpa'i rigs //
NK023('a)001:7331: bcom ldan rjes dran smon lam grub pa'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:7332: dri ma kun 'khru legs pa mthar phyin pa'i //
NK023('a)001:7333: 'di ni sku tshe ring pa'i dbang gi bkra shis drug pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7335: // 'dir byang chub sems dpa'i bum dbang bya'o //
NK023('a)001:7336: lha mi nyan rang gis bum dbang yang 'di ka yin no //
NK023('a)001:7337: sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa des /
NK023('a)001:7338: yum gyi lhums nas bltams nas dgung bdun lon pa dang /
NK023('a)001:7339: rgyal po sh+aakya'i rigs kun tshogs nas gzhon nu don
NK023('a)001:7340: 'grub tu ming btags nas dbang bskur bas shes bya
NK023('a)001:7341: la ma rmongs pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7342: de dang rjes su mthun par slob ma 'di la
NK023('a)001:7343: ming gis dbang bskur bas shes bya ye shes la
NK023('a)001:7344: ma rmongs pa'i dbang gzhon nu don 'grub tu dbang
NK023('a)001:7346: rigs kyi bu khyod ding phan chad /
NK023('a)001:7347: ming mchog grags pas dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:7348: gzhon nu don grub yin pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:7349: rgyal bu don 'grub yin par shog /
NK023('a)001:7350: rgyal khrims gtsang ma rgyal bu kun 'dus pas //
NK023('a)001:7351: lha mi kun la dbang bskur rgyal bur bskos //
NK023('a)001:7352: kun las 'phags pa'i rgyal dbang dam pa ste //
NK023('a)001:7353: 'di ni kun gyis rgyal bu dbang gi bkra shis bdun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7355: // skabs 'dir slob bu de byang chub sems dpa' dang sems ma dang rgyal ba'i sras zhes ming brjod /
NK023('a)001:7356: byang sems la phar phyin dang /
NK023('a)001:7357: nyan rang la dkon mchog dang /
NK023('a)001:7358: lha mi la mtho ris kyis ming yang skabs 'dir thob pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7359: sngon rgyal bu don grub la sru mo ko'u ta
NK023('a)001:7360: mas rgyan gyi bye brag gi rgyan gyis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:7361: bas / sa dang rda la gnas pa'i bsam mno
NK023('a)001:7362: med pa rnams phyag tshur 'tshal ba'i dbang dam pa
NK023('a)001:7364: de dang rjes su mthun par rgyan gyi bye brag
NK023('a)001:7365: gis dbang bskur bas 'gro ba thams cad shes pa
NK023('a)001:7366: dang ldan par byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK023('a)001:7367: gyur cig / mdzes pa'i rgyan rnams myur du brtag nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:7368: legs pa'i yon tan kun tshangs ye shes sku //
NK023('a)001:7369: ma rig thar lam ma lus 'dren pa'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:7370: rtogs pa'i ye shes mchog dang ldan par shog /
NK023('a)001:7371: yon tan kun ldan sru mos mdzes pa'i rgyan //
NK023('a)001:7372: legs pa kun rdzogs yon tan mthar phyin kyang //
NK023('a)001:7373: che ba'i yon tan gnas phyir mi langs te //
NK023('a)001:7374: 'di ni legs pa kun rdzogs dbang gi bkra shis brgyad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7376: // sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa des yig
NK023('a)001:7377: dpon kun gyi bshes gnyen la yi ge slob pa'i
NK023('a)001:7378: dus su tsan dan sbrul gyi snying po'i yig shing
NK023('a)001:7379: gser gyi g.yang dmig rtags nas rin po che sna
NK023('a)001:7380: tshogs kyis brgyan nas yi ge slob pa'i dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:7381: bas yig dpon gyis kyang ma thub la /
NK023('a)001:7382: lha dang mi'i yi ge thams cad la mkhas pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7383: de dang rjes su mthun par yig shing gis dbang
NK023('a)001:7384: bskur bas chos kyi sgra sgrogs pa'i dbang dam pa
NK023('a)001:7386: tsan dan sbrul gyi yig shing la //
NK023('a)001:7387: rin chen gser gyi g.yang dmig rtags //
NK023('a)001:7388: 'gro ba'i don byed yi ge'i mthu //
NK023('a)001:7389: pha rol zil gnon chos nyid kun las rgyal //
NK023('a)001:7390: 'di 'dra'i yon tan gzhan na med pa yis //
NK023('a)001:7391: 'di ni yi ge'i tshogs dbang gi bkra shis dgu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7393: // sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa de bdud lhas sbyin dang rtsal 'gran pa'i dus su /
NK023('a)001:7394: mes chen po seng ge 'gram gyi gnam rus dbang
NK023('a)001:7395: bskur bas sgra'i bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK023('a)001:7396: 'byung zhing bdud sgyu rtsal gyis 'dul ba'i dbang thob
NK023('a)001:7397: par gyur to // de dang rjes su mthun par
NK023('a)001:7398: slob ma 'di la gnam rus dbang bskur bas snyan
NK023('a)001:7399: pa'i sgra sgrogs shing bdud dpung 'dul ba'i 'phong rtsal
NK023('a)001:7401: snyan pa'i sgra sgrogs gnam ru mchog /
NK023('a)001:7402: 'gro ba kun gyis yid tshim zhing //
NK023('a)001:7403: gnod pa'i bdud rnams bcom nas ni //
NK023('a)001:7404: bdud rnams 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:7405: thams cad kun 'dul mthu stobs phun sum tshogs //
NK023('a)001:7406: rdzu 'phrul thabs kyis pha ro la zil gyis gnon //
NK023('a)001:7407: don dang mi 'gal gdug pa zhi mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:7408: 'di ni gnam rus dbang gi bkra shis bcu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7410: // sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa des rgyal
NK023('a)001:7411: srid khab tu bzhes pa'i dus su btsun mo sa
NK023('a)001:7412: mtsho ma phyag tu phul te dbang bskur bas rigs
NK023('a)001:7413: mi nub cing 'gro ba sems can khyim dang 'du
NK023('a)001:7414: 'dzis 'dul ba'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7415: de dang rjes su mthun par btsun mos dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:7416: bas slob ma 'di bstan pa'i rigs mi nub cing
NK023('a)001:7417: ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin du 'gro ba'i don byed
NK023('a)001:7418: pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7419: nor bu rin chen byi dor byas shing gsal //
NK023('a)001:7420: sh+aakya sa mtsho ma bkab phyar na yang //
NK023('a)001:7421: blo mos yid lcug dngas pas sems bskyed de //
NK023('a)001:7422: dgongs pa'i don rnams yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:7423: khyim dang 'du 'dzi 'dul bar gzigs pa yis //
NK023('a)001:7424: khab dang rgyal srid 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:7425: khams gsum khyim pa rnams kyi don mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:7426: 'di ni btsun mo dbang gi bkra shis bcu gcig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7427: sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa de 'khor
NK023('a)001:7428: lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal por bskos nas shing rtas dbang
NK023('a)001:7429: bskur bas 'dzam bu gling bzhi la 'khor los bsgyur
NK023('a)001:7430: bar gyur nas 'khor ba'i chos thams cad mi rtag
NK023('a)001:7431: par mkhyen pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7432: de dang rjes su mthun par shing rta la sogs
NK023('a)001:7433: pa'i 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i dbang pos dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:7434: 'dzam bu gling bzhi la dbang bsgyur zhing skye shi
NK023('a)001:7435: mi rtag pa'i sdug bsngal las sun phyung bar gyur
NK023('a)001:7436: cig / rgyal srid longs spyod dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:7437: 'gro ba'i don mdzad 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i lha //
NK023('a)001:7438: lha mi yongs kyi spyod pa bsam mi khyab //
NK023('a)001:7439: skye shi mi rtag pa las bzlog par shog /
NK023('a)001:7440: rgyal srid longs spyod dpal dang ldan pa'i lha //
NK023('a)001:7441: gling bzhi mtha' bskor skye rgas na 'chi spong //
NK023('a)001:7442: 'khor ba'i skyon shes sdug bsngal sel mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:7443: 'di ni shing rta dbang gi bkra shis le'u bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7445: // sngon rgyal bu don thams cad 'grub pa de khab
NK023('a)001:7446: nas khab med par rab tu byung ba'i dus su
NK023('a)001:7447: / 'bangs mo sa la can gyis chibs rin po che lnga ldan phyung nas phul bas /
NK023('a)001:7448: srod gcig la dpag tshad brgyad khri 'das nas rab
NK023('a)001:7449: tu byung nas nyon mongs pa las thar nas dbang
NK023('a)001:7450: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7451: de dang rjes su mthun par chibs 'dis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:7452: bas rab tu byung zhing nyon mongs pa las grol
NK023('a)001:7453: ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7454: gang yang thogs med brtson 'grus myur ba'i shugs //
NK023('a)001:7455: tshangs pa brgya byin mthu byin che ba'i lha //
NK023('a)001:7456: rgyal chen rigs bzhi 'degs pa'i stobs dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:7457: thogs med tshangs par spyod pa'i mthu ldan shog /
NK023('a)001:7458: 'khor ba'i chos ni 'chil snabs thal bar gzigs //
NK023('a)001:7459: 'khor ba'i nyes pa dgra rnams gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:7460: 'dod pa'i rgyu spong rnam rtog 'bor mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:7461: 'di ni chibs kyis dbang gi bkra shis pa'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7463: // sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa de rnam
NK023('a)001:7464: dag mchod rten gyi 'gram du khab nas khab med
NK023('a)001:7465: par rab tu byung ba las sum cu rtsa gsum
NK023('a)001:7466: gyi lha'i bu mdzes pa'i tog gis bshan ral gri
NK023('a)001:7467: phyag tu phul te dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i
NK023('a)001:7468: d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thos par gyur
NK023('a)001:7469: to // de dang rjes su mthun par bcom ldan
NK023('a)001:7470: 'das kyi bshan ral gris dbang bskur bas nyon mongs
NK023('a)001:7471: pa'i sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i dbang dam pa
NK023('a)001:7473: nyon mongs d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i ral gri ste //
NK023('a)001:7474: mi shes nyon mongs rgyu rnams bcad nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:7475: bla med byang chub gnas su 'god pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:7476: nyon mongs sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod par shog /
NK023('a)001:7477: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus bcom nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:7478: bde ba'i don rtogs nags khrod dben par gnas //
NK023('a)001:7479: bdag don lhun grub gzhan don mthar phyin pa'i //
NK023('a)001:7480: 'di ni tshul khrims dbang gi bkra shis kyi le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7482: // sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa chu bo ne
NK023('a)001:7483: ra dza ra'i 'gram du dka' thub rdzogs pa la
NK023('a)001:7484: / sum cu rtsa gsum lha yi bu yid bzhin
NK023('a)001:7485: 'byung bas gseg shang dang spar bu phul bas 'gro
NK023('a)001:7486: ba'i don mthar phyin pa rdzogs pa'i dbang thob bo
NK023('a)001:7487: / // de dang rjes su mthun par bcom ldan
NK023('a)001:7488: 'das kyi gseg spar gyi rdzas kyis dbang bskul bas
NK023('a)001:7489: bdag dang 'gro ba'i don mthar phyin par rdzogs pa'i
NK023('a)001:7490: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7491: ser sna'i mdud pa grol phyir gseg spar bsnams //
NK023('a)001:7492: chog shes gang ba sla phyir spar bu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:7493: bsod nams tshogs rdzogs byang chub nyid kyi sku //
NK023('a)001:7494: bdag dang gzhan don mthar phyin rdzogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:7495: bkra shis kyi le'u bco lnga pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7497: // sngon bcom ldan 'das bsnyen pa rdzogs pa la sum
NK023('a)001:7498: cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i bu zhig gis na bza'
NK023('a)001:7499: ngur smrig gsol bas nyon mongs pa'i 'gro ba srid
NK023('a)001:7500: las skyob pa'i dbang dam pa gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7501: de dang rjes su mthun par bcos ldan 'das kyi
NK023('a)001:7502: na bza' ngur smrig gi rdzas 'dis dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:7503: nyon mongs pa'i 'khor ba las skyobs pa'i dbang dam
NK023('a)001:7505: ngan 'gro skyobs phyir chos gos na bza' gsol //
NK023('a)001:7506: mi shes rmongs pa ma lus bsal ba dang //
NK023('a)001:7507: bag chags skyon gyi dri mas ma gos pa'i //
NK023('a)001:7508: 'bras bu byang chub gnas su 'grub par shog /
NK023('a)001:7509: na bza' ngur smrig bkra shis kyi le'u ste bcu drug pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7511: // sngon bcom ldan 'das yul ma ga da'i rgyal khams su bsod snyoms la gshegs pa la /
NK023('a)001:7512: spre'u rgyal pos sbrang rtsi lhung bzed gang drangs pas
NK023('a)001:7513: bkra shis pa'i rdzas mchog dam pa dang ldan par
NK023('a)001:7514: gyur te / de dang rjes su mthun par mi
NK023('a)001:7515: 'di zhes bya ba la bkra shis pa'i rjas 'dis
NK023('a)001:7516: gyur te / dbang bskur bas / 'bras bu phun
NK023('a)001:7517: sum tshogs pa'i bkra shis pa'i mchog dang ldan par
NK023('a)001:7518: gyur te / dbang bskur bas / gyur cig / rgyal rigs spre'u'i rgyal po yis //
NK023('a)001:7519: sbrang rtsi phul ba'i bsod nams mchog /
NK023('a)001:7520: thugs mthun pa yi byin rlabs kyis //
NK023('a)001:7521: bkra shis stobs mchog ldan par shog /
NK023('a)001:7524: // sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa chu bo ne
NK023('a)001:7525: ra dza na'i 'gram du dka' thub lo gsum mdzad
NK023('a)001:7526: / lo gcig 'bras sa lu'i ljang pa nyag re gsol /
NK023('a)001:7527: lo gcig chu thigs pa re gsol /
NK023('a)001:7528: lo gcig ci yang ma gsol na yang sbrims shing skyems pa mi mnga' bas las /
NK023('a)001:7529: grong khyer gyi byis pas kyang tho brtsam pa la
NK023('a)001:7530: nyid la tshor ba rgyu dub kyang mi mnga' ste
NK023('a)001:7531: / sku skam zhing rid pa las /
NK023('a)001:7532: grong pa legs 'ong ma'i bu mo legs skyes mas
NK023('a)001:7533: 'bral chen gang gzhong gang drangs te gsol bas sku
NK023('a)001:7534: gser gyi brtan pa phyis pa bzhin du gyur nas
NK023('a)001:7535: mtshan dang dpe byad du ldan par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7536: de dang rjes su mthun par ming 'di zhes bya
NK023('a)001:7537: ba la 'o thug 'bras chen gyis dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:7538: mtshan dang dpe byad du ldan pa'i dbang dam pa
NK023('a)001:7540: nyon mongs med pa 'bras bu'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:7541: zhi ba'i ngang la rab tu gnas //
NK023('a)001:7542: bsod nams thob phyir bsngosa pa 'dis //
NK023('a)001:7543: mtshan dang dpe byad rjogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:7546: // sngon bcom ldan 'das byang chub kyi shing drung gi rtsar gshegs pa'i dus su /
