NK023('a)001:7547: rtsa 'tshong bkra shis kyis rtsa rma bya'i mgrin pa ltar sngo ba phyag tu phul bas /
NK023('a)001:7548: bcom ldan 'das kyi gdan du bting bas bdud kyis
NK023('a)001:7549: mi tshugs pa'i bkra shis pa'i rdzas dang ldan par
NK023('a)001:7550: gyur to // de dang rjes su mthun par rdzas
NK023('a)001:7551: 'dis dbang bskur bas bkra shis pa dang bar chad
NK023('a)001:7552: thams cad kyis mi tshugs pa'i dbang dam pa dang
NK023('a)001:7554: sngon gyi drang srong rnams kyis grub pa yis //
NK023('a)001:7555: bkra shis r+ts+wa mchog rma bya'i mgrin pa 'dra //
NK023('a)001:7556: legs pa kun rdzogs nyes pa med pa ste //
NK023('a)001:7557: 'gro ba'i don du bkra shis rdzogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:7560: // sngon bcom ldan 'das skyes bu gyad kyis nye 'khor na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK023('a)001:7561: byang phyogs kyi tshong pa nye mgon dang meg skyabs
NK023('a)001:7562: kyis bu ram shing shun dang ma bral ba dang
NK023('a)001:7563: sbrang rtsi yon du phul ba shin tu bkra shis
NK023('a)001:7564: pa'i rdzas dam pa dang ldan par gyur te /
NK023('a)001:7565: de dang rjes su mthun par ming 'di zhes bya
NK023('a)001:7566: ba la bkra shis pa'i rdzas 'dis dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:7567: bkra shis skye 'chi med pa'i dbang dam pa thob
NK023('a)001:7568: par gyur cig / thams cad kun gyi snying po yon mchog ste //
NK023('a)001:7569: dad pa skyes nas mchod gnas byas pa dang //
NK023('a)001:7570: 'bras bu smon lam myur du thob pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:7571: 'di dag bkra shis myur du rdzogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:7572: yon tan mthar rdzogs sangs rgyas sa la gnas //
NK023('a)001:7573: go 'phang bla med rgyal thabs spyod pa can //
NK023('a)001:7574: 'gro don mthar phyin 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon //
NK023('a)001:7575: shes rab mthar phyin bkra shis dbang ste nyi shu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7577: // 'di yan chad rgya chen rol pas 'gro ba 'dul
NK023('a)001:7578: ba'i dbang ste rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:7579: ngo // byang sems mdzad pa nyi shu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7581: // 'di na mar kri ya'i dbang la /
NK023('a)001:7582: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa ri rab kyi
NK023('a)001:7583: zom la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dus su
NK023('a)001:7584: dpa' phyag na rdo rje la rin po che sna
NK023('a)001:7585: lnga'i ri rab kyis dbang bskur bas mthu stobs phun
NK023('a)001:7586: sum tshogs pa dang ldan te mi 'gyur ba'i sku
NK023('a)001:7588: de dang rjes su mthun par rin po che sna
NK023('a)001:7589: lnga'i ri rab kyis dbang bskur bas mthu stobs phun
NK023('a)001:7590: sum tshogs pa dang ldan te mi 'gyur ba'i sku
NK023('a)001:7592: gzi brjed lhun sdug ri rab mchog gi sku //
NK023('a)001:7593: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa dbang rim mchog /
NK023('a)001:7594: thams cad gnas pa'i ri bo chen po la //
NK023('a)001:7595: mthun stobs mi 'gyur sku rnams rdzogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:7596: skye bzhi 'gro drug khams gsum kun gyi srog /
NK023('a)001:7597: kha dog mdzes ldan rin chen sna tshogs gzhi //
NK023('a)001:7598: phyogs bzhi dbus dang rigs kyis skur bstan pa //
NK023('a)001:7599: 'di ni ri rab dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste nyi shu rtsa gcig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7601: // sngon bcom ldan 'das mdzad pa bcu gnyis rdzogs par
NK023('a)001:7602: mdzad pa'i dus su u dum wa ra'i me tog
NK023('a)001:7603: dang sbyar nas dpal phyag na rdo rje la ri
NK023('a)001:7604: bzhin gyi mchod rten dang sprul pa'i mchod rten la
NK023('a)001:7605: sogs pas dbang bskur bas rnam par mi rtog pa
NK023('a)001:7606: chos kyi sku thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7607: de dang rjes su mthun par mchod rten chen pos
NK023('a)001:7608: dbang bskur bas chos kyi sku thob pa'i dbang dang
NK023('a)001:7610: dran pa nye bar bzhag pa'i bem rim dang //
NK023('a)001:7611: skye 'gag med pa'i bum pa zlum po dang //
NK023('a)001:7612: chos kyi 'khor lo ma 'dres tog la sogs //
NK023('a)001:7613: rnam par mi rtog chos kyi sku thob shog /
NK023('a)001:7614: lta ba'i sa dang mngon par byang chub mtshungs pa mi mnga' bas /
NK023('a)001:7615: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor dang cho 'phrul ston la sogs //
NK023('a)001:7616: lha yul gnas gshegs ston pa mya ngan gar gnas pa'i //
NK023('a)001:7617: stobs bcu'i byin rlabs dbang gi mchod rten dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste nyi shu gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7619: // sngon bcom ldan 'das yul gyad kyi nye 'khor na
NK023('a)001:7620: bzhugs pa'i dus su dpal phyag na rdo rje la
NK023('a)001:7621: dpag bsam shing gis dbang bskur bas dgongs pa'i don
NK023('a)001:7622: yid bzhin du 'grub par gyur te /
NK023('a)001:7623: de dang rjes su mthun par dpag bsam shing gis dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7624: ming 'di zhes bya ba dgongs pa'i don rnams yid bzhin du 'grub par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7625: gang la ji 'dod dpag bsam shing lta bu //
NK023('a)001:7626: yon tan yid bzhin zad med gter dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:7627: rten pa'i rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tshul yin te //
NK023('a)001:7628: dgongs pa'i don rnams yid bzhin 'grub par shog /
NK023('a)001:7629: lha yi re skongs dpag bsam ljon shing ltar //
NK023('a)001:7630: 'phags pa'i yon tan brjod kyis mi langs te //
NK023('a)001:7631: re ba yid bzhin phun sum tshogs pa'i rdzas //
NK023('a)001:7632: 'di ni dpag bsam shing gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste nyi shu rtsa gsum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7634: // sngon bcom ldan 'das rgya mtsho chen po'i gling la
NK023('a)001:7635: gshegs pa'i dus su dpal phyag na rdo rje la
NK023('a)001:7636: rgya mtsho chen pos dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7637: chos skye ba med pa zab cing rgya che ba shes pa'i rgyud la ston par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7638: de dang rjes su mthun par rgya mtsho chen pos
NK023('a)001:7639: dbang bskur bas chos skye ba med pa zab cing
NK023('a)001:7640: rgya che ba'i don rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob
NK023('a)001:7641: par gyur cig / gting dpag zab cing rgya mtsho yangs pa yis //
NK023('a)001:7642: kun tu snyems pa'i yon tan chen po ste //
NK023('a)001:7643: skye 'gags med pa'i rgya mtsho chen po la //
NK023('a)001:7644: zab cing rgya che'i chos don rtogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:7645: chos nyid zab mo rgya mtsho lta bur thugs chud pas //
NK023('a)001:7646: zab cing rting dpag dka' ba'i rgya mtsho la //
NK023('a)001:7647: yid bzhin nor bu kha dog mdzes pa'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:7648: 'di ni rgya mtsho dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste nyi shu rtsa bzhi pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7650: // sngon bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gdan drung na bzhugs pa la /
NK023('a)001:7651: dpal phyag na rdo rje la sa gzhi chen po
NK023('a)001:7652: gnas kyis dbang bskur bas bkra shis la byin chags
NK023('a)001:7653: pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7654: de dang rjes su mthun par ming 'di zhes bya
NK023('a)001:7655: ba la sa gzhi skye gnas kyis dbang bskur ba
NK023('a)001:7656: gnas bkra shis shing byin chags pa'i dbang dam pa
NK023('a)001:7658: rab tu dben pa'i gnas mchog dam pa ste /
NK023('a)001:7659: me tog dri bsung mang po skye ba dang //
NK023('a)001:7660: yon tan ma lus tshangs par kun rdzogs te //
NK023('a)001:7661: dben pa'i bkra shis chen po'i gnas su shog /
NK023('a)001:7662: me tog mdzes ldan yid 'ongs brgyan pa'i gnas //
NK023('a)001:7663: bkra shis skad snyan bya skad sna tshogs sgrogs //
NK023('a)001:7664: yon tan ldan pa ston pas brlabs pa'i gnas //
NK023('a)001:7665: 'di ni sa gzhi gnas kyi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste nyi shu rtsa lnga pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7667: // sngon bcom ldan 'das ba ra na se na bzhugs
NK023('a)001:7668: pa la dpal phyag na rdo rje la bdud rtsi
NK023('a)001:7669: chus dbang bskur bas skye shi mi mnga' ba'i sku
NK023('a)001:7670: thob bo // de dang rjes su mthun par bdud
NK023('a)001:7671: rtsi bum pa'i chus dbang bskur bas skye shi med
NK023('a)001:7672: pa sku'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7673: bdud rtsi chu rgyun 'gro ba'i gsos kyi mchog /
NK023('a)001:7674: nyon mongs sdug bsngal nad du che ba sel //
NK023('a)001:7675: ma rig dag pa'i bdud rtsi chu mchog ste //
NK023('a)001:7676: skye shi med pa dag pa'i sku thob shog /
NK023('a)001:7677: bum pa'i kha rgyan dpag bsam shing //
NK023('a)001:7678: dbang bskur bum pa spyi blug pas //
NK023('a)001:7679: bdud rtsi dam pa 'dir stsol cig /
NK023('a)001:7680: 'di ni bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun dbang gis le'u ste nyi shu rtsa drug pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7681: 'dir kri ya'i bum dbang bya ste rdzas dbang kri
NK023('a)001:7682: ya u pa ya gcig tu byed pas u pa
NK023('a)001:7684: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyi zom la bzhugs
NK023('a)001:7685: pa la lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis chos zhu
NK023('a)001:7686: ba'i phyir dar bu khad kyis za ra tshags phul
NK023('a)001:7687: bas / chos sgra chen po sgrogs pa'i byin dang ldan par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7688: de dang rjes su mthun par rdzas 'dis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:7689: bas chos kyi sgra chen po sgrogs pa'i dbang thob
NK023('a)001:7690: par gyur cig / chos kyi rgyal srid chen po mnga' brnyes shing //
NK023('a)001:7691: ma rig mun pa ma lus gsal ba dang //
NK023('a)001:7692: brgya byin shes pa ma lus bgrol ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:7693: chos rnams thams chad go zhing sgrogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:7694: mnyen 'jams reg bde dar gyi za ra tshags //
NK023('a)001:7695: rigs kyi kha dog sna bdun shin tu mdzes //
NK023('a)001:7696: yid 'ongs legs par brgyan pa'i bkra shis rdzas //
NK023('a)001:7697: 'di ni dar gyi za ra tshags kyi dbang gi le'u ste nyer bdun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7699: // sngon bcom ldan 'das sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas
NK023('a)001:7700: su lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis chos kyi 'khor
NK023('a)001:7701: lo bskor ba'i dus su rin po che'i khri rkang
NK023('a)001:7702: phul nas bzhugs pas chos shes pa'i rgyud la go
NK023('a)001:7704: de dang rjes su mthun par rin po che'i khri
NK023('a)001:7705: rkang gis dbang bskur bas chos go ba sgrogs pa'i
NK023('a)001:7707: rin chen gser gyi khri stengs su //
NK023('a)001:7708: chos sgra chen po sgrogs pa yis //
NK023('a)001:7709: 'gro ba rnams kyi mi shes bgrol //
NK023('a)001:7710: chos rnams go bar sgrogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:7711: tshad med bzhi ldan 'degs pa gser gyi khri //
NK023('a)001:7712: yon tan tshogs rdzogs rin chen sna tshogs spras //
NK023('a)001:7713: yon tan yid bzhin zad med dgos 'dod skongs //
NK023('a)001:7714: 'di ni rin chen gser khri dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste nyer brgyad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7716: // sngon bcom ldan 'das chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba
NK023('a)001:7717: la lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis me tog gi
NK023('a)001:7718: chun po bres pas sems can 'khor ba las bslu
NK023('a)001:7719: zhing 'drid pa'i mchog dam pa dang ldan par gyur
NK023('a)001:7720: to // de dang rjes su mthun par me tog
NK023('a)001:7721: gi chun pos dbang bskur bas 'khor ba las bslu
NK023('a)001:7722: bar byed pa'i mdzes pa'i rgyan mchog dam pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:7724: sdug cing mdzes pa'i me tog dam pa 'di kha dog ma 'dres so sor gsal ba'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:7725: sems can kun gyis lta bar 'os pa yi //
NK023('a)001:7726: mdzes pa'i rgyan mchog dam pa ldan par shog /
NK023('a)001:7727: me tog chu skyes thang skyes dam pa dang //
NK023('a)001:7728: shing dang nags skyes 'dzam gling 'bru mchog 'di //
NK023('a)001:7729: rin chen phreng ltar mkha' la char 'bebs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:7730: 'di ni me tog chun po'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste nyer dgu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7732: // sngon bcom ldan 'das chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba las /
NK023('a)001:7733: ri rab kyi rtse khang bu na brtsegs pa'i khang bzangs na bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK023('a)001:7734: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i bu 'od dam pa
NK023('a)001:7735: zhes bya bas rnga yab kyi g.yab pas dges pa
NK023('a)001:7736: chen po'i gzi mdangs dang ldan par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7737: de dang rjes su mthun par rnga yab kyis dbang
NK023('a)001:7738: bskur bas dgos pa chen po'i gzi mdangs dang ldan
NK023('a)001:7739: pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7740: snyan pa'i sgra rnams myur du sgrogs pa dang /
NK023('a)001:7741: nyon mongs rdul gyi dri ma ma lus sel //
NK023('a)001:7742: thams cad myur du go ba'i blo thob nas //
NK023('a)001:7743: bkra shis gzi mdangs mchog dang ldan par shog /
NK023('a)001:7744: rgyal ba'i sku la nyes pas ma gos kyang //
NK023('a)001:7745: dag cing bsang bar bya phyir rnga yab 'dis //
NK023('a)001:7746: sku'i ljan ljin dri mas phyag dar phyir //
NK023('a)001:7747: 'di ni rnga yab dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste sum cu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7749: // sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab nas bzhugs pa
NK023('a)001:7750: la sum cu rtsa gsum lha'i bu kun nas 'od
NK023('a)001:7751: zer 'byung bas rdul yab kyis rdul g.yab pas chos
NK023('a)001:7752: nyid la skyon gyis ma gos so //
NK023('a)001:7753: de dang rjes su mthun par lha'i rdul g.yab kyi
NK023('a)001:7754: rdzas kyis dbang bskur bas chos nyid zab mo'i don
NK023('a)001:7755: la 'jug pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:7756: / nyon mongs rdul rnams ma lus phyi ba dang //
NK023('a)001:7757: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK023('a)001:7758: bag chags skyon gyi dri ma gsal ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:7759: bkra shis gtsang ma'i ras kyis sku phyis pas //
NK023('a)001:7760: 'di ni rdul g.yab dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste sum cu gcig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7762: // sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal dgon pa na bzhugs
NK023('a)001:7763: pa la sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i bu zhig
NK023('a)001:7764: gis sbrang g.yab kyis sbrang bu g.yab pas sems can
NK023('a)001:7765: 'dzin chags kyi skyon las grol lo //
NK023('a)001:7766: de dang rjes su mthun par sbrang g.yab kyi rdzas
NK023('a)001:7767: 'dis dbang bskur bas 'dzin chags kyi skyon las grol
NK023('a)001:7768: ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7769: nyon mongs sems can ma rig gsal ba dang //
NK023('a)001:7770: 'bras bu thar pa'i go 'phang thob pa dang //
NK023('a)001:7771: bde bar gshegs pa'i zhabs drung 'khor ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:7772: 'dzin chags skyon gyis sgrib pa dag par shog /
NK023('a)001:7773: drang srong chen po bsam gtan gnas pa la //
NK023('a)001:7774: srog chags gdug pa'i gzugs can bsal ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:7775: rnga yab rgyal ba'i ring bsrel bskor ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:7776: 'di ni sbrang yab dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste sum cu rtsa gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7778: // sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs pa
NK023('a)001:7779: la 'khor rnam bzhis bla res bris te nyon mongs
NK023('a)001:7780: pa'i gdung ba zhi bar gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7781: de dang rjes su mthun par bla res dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:7782: bas nyon mongs pa'i rdul gyi dri mas mi gos
NK023('a)001:7783: par gyur cig / chos kyi 'khor lo bskor phyir bla res bris /
NK023('a)001:7784: mi'i rgyal po seng ge bzhugs pa'i sa //
NK023('a)001:7785: dbang phyug dam pa'i mnga' bdag chen po ste //
NK023('a)001:7786: nyon mongs rdul gyi dri ma med par shog /
NK023('a)001:7787: dpag bsam ljon shing me tog lo 'dab rgyas //
NK023('a)001:7788: nyi zla mang pos sprin gseb nas //
NK023('a)001:7789: bkra shis bya skad mang po'i 'phur lding ba'i //
NK023('a)001:7790: 'di ni dar zab dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste sum cu rtsa gsum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7792: // sngon bcom ldan 'das bya rgod phung po'i ri la
NK023('a)001:7793: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bas tshe 'khor rnam bzhis
NK023('a)001:7794: rgyal mtshan chen po btsugs pas che ba'i yon tan
NK023('a)001:7795: nub pa'i dus med par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7796: de dang rjes su mthun par bkra shis pa'i rdzas
NK023('a)001:7797: 'dis dbang bskur bas che ba'i yon tan rgyal mtshan
NK023('a)001:7798: gyi rtse mo ltar nub pa'i dus med par gyur
NK023('a)001:7799: cig / lhun grub sku mnyes rdzogs pa'i rgyal mtshan te /
NK023('a)001:7800: nub pa'i dus med zad pa med pa yis //
NK023('a)001:7801: yon tan che bas khyad par kun las 'phags //
NK023('a)001:7802: che ba'i yon tan nub pa med par shog /
NK023('a)001:7803: spa brjid mdzes pas 'jig rten yongs kyi rgyan //
NK023('a)001:7804: bdud dang mu stegs bdud dpung 'joms par byed //
NK023('a)001:7805: rgyal ba'i sku dang dbyer med tshul gcig pa'i //
NK023('a)001:7806: 'di ni rgyal mtshan dbang gi le'u ste sum cu rtsa bzhi pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7808: // sngon bcom ldan 'das skyed mos tshal du gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK023('a)001:7809: 'khor rnams kyis tsha ba'i gdung ba la gdugs dka'
NK023('a)001:7810: bas tsha bas gdung ba'i sdug bsngal zhi bar gyur
NK023('a)001:7811: to // de dang rjes su mthun par gdugs kyis
NK023('a)001:7812: dbang bskur bas tsha ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad zhi
NK023('a)001:7813: ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7814: gdugs kyis tsh+wa ba'i gdung ba kun sel cing //
NK023('a)001:7815: grang zhing bsil ba'i gdugs mchog dam pa ste //
NK023('a)001:7816: 'gro ba'i nyon mongs sel cing tsha ba'i gsos //
NK023('a)001:7817: rims dang tsha ba'i sdug bsngal thar bar shog /
NK023('a)001:7818: ji ltar nyon mongs tsha bas gdungs pa la //
NK023('a)001:7819: gdugs kyis tsh+wa ba'i bsdug bsngal skyobs pa ltar //
NK023('a)001:7820: 'khor bar nyes pa'i sdug bsngal skyobs pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:7821: 'di ni gdugs kyis bkra shis dbang gi le'u ste sum cu rtsa lnga'o //
NK023('a)001:7823: // sngon bcom ldan 'das yangs pa can gyi grong khyer
NK023('a)001:7824: spre'u rtsang gis 'grams khang bu brtsegs pa'i khang bzang
NK023('a)001:7825: na bzhugs pa'i tshe bram ze khams pa bos sngon
NK023('a)001:7826: gyis nyes pa brdas nas nya ba rnams kyis zin
NK023('a)001:7827: pa'i tshe / nya ba rnams kyis 'gyod pa rjes
NK023('a)001:7828: su dran pa nya rgyar 'jug pa che chung phul
NK023('a)001:7829: bas nya pa lnga brgyas sangs rgyas par gyur to
NK023('a)001:7830: pa'i tshe / // de dang rjes su mthun par
NK023('a)001:7831: nya rgya'i rtags dar gyis lda ldis dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:7832: ngan song gsum du skye nges pa gcig yod na
NK023('a)001:7833: yang de las thar te sangs rgyas pa'i dbang dam
NK023('a)001:7835: dar gyi lda ldi nyon mongs kun spangs te //
NK023('a)001:7836: legs pa'i yon tan ma lus tshogs rdzogs nas //
NK023('a)001:7837: ma rig 'khrul pa'i shes pa blo dag cing //
NK023('a)001:7838: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i gnas las thar bar shog /
NK023('a)001:7839: 'khor ba'i nyes pa dag bya'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:7840: sdug bsngal rgya mtsho bkra shis rdzas //
NK023('a)001:7841: sdug bsngal bag chag sbyang slad du //
NK023('a)001:7842: 'di ni lda ldi bkra shis dbang gis le'u ste sum cu rtsa drug pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7844: // sngon bcom ldan 'das skyes mos tshal du gshegs pa'i tshe khyim bdag lha'i bu mo bzang ldan mas /
NK023('a)001:7845: a sa po'i sku reg gsol bas sku brtan pa'i mchog dang ldan par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7846: de dang rjes su mthun par bkra shis sku regs
NK023('a)001:7847: kyi rdzas 'dis dbang bskur bas lus brtan pa'i mchog
NK023('a)001:7849: dri ma dag pa'i sku regs rtsang ba'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:7850: khyim bdag dad pas phul ba'i sku regs 'dis //
NK023('a)001:7851: sku la bcings shing rab tu bsdams pas kyang //
NK023('a)001:7852: mi 'gyur brtan pa'i sku mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:7853: thar pa mchog gi legs par gang gsungs pa //
NK023('a)001:7854: mi dmigs dag pa'i ye shes chen po yis //
NK023('a)001:7855: nyon mongs dri med bde ba'i sku brten pa'i //
NK023('a)001:7856: 'di ni sku regs dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste sum cu so bdun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7858: // sngon bcom ldan 'das ri kha ba can na bzhugs pa la /
NK023('a)001:7859: gnod sbyin rnams kyis spos rnam pa lnga phul te /
NK023('a)001:7864: du rus ka dang lnga phul bas dbang po tshim zhing bkra shis par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7865: de dang rjes su mthun par spos rnam pa lngas
NK023('a)001:7866: dbang bskur ba dbang po tshim pa'i don gyi bkra
NK023('a)001:7868: dbang po tshim byed bdug pa'i spos mchog ste /
NK023('a)001:7869: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa mchod pa dang //
NK023('a)001:7870: 'gro ba ma lus dbang po kun tshim zhing //
NK023('a)001:7871: dri zhim 'phags pa'i sku dang ldan par shog /
NK023('a)001:7872: dri zhim ngad ldan yon tan phun sum tshogs //
NK023('a)001:7873: mkha' la sprin dpung mchod pa brtibs pa ste //
NK023('a)001:7874: yongs su khyab pa'i bdug pa dam pa 'di //
NK023('a)001:7875: 'di ni dbang po tshim byed dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste sum cu so brgyad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7877: // sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal chen po la bzhugs pa la /
NK023('a)001:7878: klu'i rgyal po rnams kyis snying po lnga phul te /
NK023('a)001:7883: til dang lnga phul bas snying po mi zad pa'i mdzod du bkra shis par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7884: de dang rjes su mthun par snying po rnam pa lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:7885: tshe mi zad pa'i mdzod du bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7886: snying po lnga ni gsos kyi mchog /
NK023('a)001:7887: mi bzad pa yi dbyig thog ste //
NK023('a)001:7888: legs pa'i yon tan mthar phyin nas //
NK023('a)001:7889: tshe dang longs spyod spel bar shog /
NK023('a)001:7890: 'di ni longs spyod ldan pa'i bkra shis le'u ste so dgu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7892: // sngon bcom ldan 'das yul gru 'dzin gyi ri la bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK023('a)001:7893: gnod sbyin gter 'chang la sogs pas rin po che rnam pa lnga phul te /
NK023('a)001:7894: gser dngul zangs lcags la sogs pa dang g.yu dang
NK023('a)001:7895: lnga phul bas dkor nor mi bzad pa'i mdzod dang
NK023('a)001:7897: de dang rjes su mthun par rin po che lngas
NK023('a)001:7898: dbang bskur bas dkor nor zad mi shes pa'i mdzod
NK023('a)001:7899: dam pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7900: rin chen gser dang dngul mchog dang //
NK023('a)001:7901: lcags dang zangs dang g.yu la sogs //
NK023('a)001:7902: mi zad pa yi nor mchog ste //
NK023('a)001:7903: zad pa med pa'i nor mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:7904: dgos pa'i don 'byin rin chen sna tshogs mchog /
NK023('a)001:7905: zad pa med pa'i gter dang ldan pa ste //
NK023('a)001:7906: sdug bsngal dbul 'phongs kun las thar ba ste //
NK023('a)001:7907: 'di ni dgos 'dod bskongs pa'i dbang gi le'u ste bzhi bcu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7909: // sngon bcom ldan 'das yul ang g+ha mang g+ha d+ha
NK023('a)001:7910: na bzhugs pa la rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis 'bru
NK023('a)001:7911: sna rnam pa lnga phul te /
NK023('a)001:7916: til dang lnga phul bas mu ge'i sdug bsngal zhi ste bkra shis par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7917: de dang rjes su mthun par ming 'di zhes bya
NK023('a)001:7918: ba la 'bru rnam pa lngas dbang bskur bas mu
NK023('a)001:7919: ge'i sdug bsngal zhi ste bkra shis par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:7920: / rin chen 'bru mchog 'gro ba'i gsos lags so //
NK023('a)001:7921: mu ge'i sdug bsngal kun las thar ba dang //
NK023('a)001:7922: sbyin pa longs spyod rtag tu 'phel ba dang //
NK023('a)001:7923: zas la sogs te mi bzad gter dang ldan par shog /
NK023('a)001:7924: longs spyod tshogs ldan 'byor pa kun 'tshangs pa //
NK023('a)001:7925: gang la ci 'dod pa yis gter 'byung ba //
NK023('a)001:7926: phun sum 'tshogs ldan dge ba'am 'bru skyed pa //
NK023('a)001:7927: 'di ni longs spyod ldan pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste zhe gcig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7929: // sngon bcom ldan 'das tsan dan gyi nags tshal du gshegs pa na /
NK023('a)001:7930: gcan gzan gyi rgyal po stag gis sman bya kri phul bas bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK023('a)001:7931: ming 'di zhes bya ba la stag tsher bas dbang bskur bas bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7932: bya kri sman mchog stag gis phul ba ste /
NK023('a)001:7933: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK023('a)001:7934: byol song gti mug kun kyang go mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:7935: sman mchog nad rnams kun la sel bar shog /
NK023('a)001:7936: sems can gdugs pa ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:7937: thabs kyis cho 'phrul kun la cir yang ston //
NK023('a)001:7938: thugs rje chen pos gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:7939: 'di ni cho 'phrul ston pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7941: // sngon bcom ldan 'das seng ldeng gi shing gseb tu
NK023('a)001:7942: gshegs pa las gcan gzan gyi rgyal po seng ge'i
NK023('a)001:7943: seng khri phyag tu phul bas sman gyi mchog tu
NK023('a)001:7945: de dang rjes su mthun par seng ldeng gi tsher
NK023('a)001:7946: mas dbang bskur bas sman mchog dam pa yon tan
NK023('a)001:7947: du bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7948: seng khri sman mchog seng ges phul ba ste /
NK023('a)001:7949: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK023('a)001:7950: byol song gti mug kun kyang go mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:7951: sman mchog nad rnams kun las sel bar shog /
NK023('a)001:7952: gzi brjid 'gro mkhas 'gyings ba'i rdzu 'phrul can //
NK023('a)001:7953: glal bzhi 'gyings pas byol song rgyal po ste //
NK023('a)001:7954: sgra skad 'tsher bas sder chag zil gyis gnon //
NK023('a)001:7955: 'di ni mu stegs 'dul ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bzhi bcu rtsa gsum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7957: // sngon bcom ldan 'das ri gtang zung chen mor klu'i
NK023('a)001:7958: rgyal po 'jog pos 'bri ha ti phyag tu phul
NK023('a)001:7959: bas sman mchog rnam pa lnga ru bkra shis par
NK023('a)001:7960: gyur te / de dang rjes su mthun par shu
NK023('a)001:7961: dag dkar pos dbang bskur bas sman mchog dam pa
NK023('a)001:7962: bkra shis thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:7963: shu dag sman mchog klu yi phul ba ste //
NK023('a)001:7964: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK023('a)001:7965: klu yi gti mug kun kyang go mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:7966: sman mchog nad rnams kun las sel bar shog /
NK023('a)001:7967: rigs pa'i cha ldan byang chub sems dpa' yis //
NK023('a)001:7968: 'gro ba'i re skong gtsug na rin chen mchog /
NK023('a)001:7969: thabs kyis don mdzad mthu dpung che ba'i klu //
NK023('a)001:7970: 'di ni nad rnams sel ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7972: // sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal
NK023('a)001:7973: du lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis ha sa de
NK023('a)001:7974: ba phul bas / sman mchog snying por bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK023('a)001:7975: ming 'di zhes bya ba la dbang po lag pas
NK023('a)001:7976: dbang bskur bas sman mchog dam pa don gyis bkra
NK023('a)001:7978: dbang po lag pas brgya byin phul ba ste /
NK023('a)001:7979: bcon ldan thugs rje chen po byin rlabs kyis //
NK023('a)001:7980: brgya byin lha yi sems kyang go bar mdzad //
NK023('a)001:7981: sman mchog nad rnams kun las sel bar shog /
NK023('a)001:7982: sum cu rtsa gsum lha yi gnas mchog nas //
NK023('a)001:7983: longs spyod ldan pa lha dbang brgya byin mchog /
NK023('a)001:7984: sum cu rtsa gsum lha las rnam rgyal ba'i //
NK023('a)001:7985: 'di ni longs spyod dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bzhi bcu zhe lnga pa'o //
NK023('a)001:7987: // sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal chen po'i shing gseb
NK023('a)001:7988: tu gshegs pa'i dus su shing gi lha mo 'od
NK023('a)001:7989: 'chang mas kan d+ha ka ri phul nas sman mchog
NK023('a)001:7990: snying por bkra shis par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:7991: de dang rjes su mthun par kan d+ha ka ris
NK023('a)001:7992: dbang bskur bas snying po don gyi sman du bkra
NK023('a)001:7994: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK023('a)001:7995: shing gi lha mo sems kyang go bar mdzad //
NK023('a)001:7996: kan d+ha ka ris lha mos phul ba ste //
NK023('a)001:7997: sman mchog nad rnams kun las sel bar shog /
NK023('a)001:7998: nags tshal chen po'i shing gseb nas //
NK023('a)001:7999: bde ba dges pa'i re bskong ba //
NK023('a)001:8000: dad pa chen pos rab phul nas //
NK023('a)001:8001: 'di ni legs par rdzogs pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bzhi bcu rtsa drug pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8003: // 'di yan chad kri ya'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:8004: gzhan don mthar phyin pa'i dbang thob bo //
NK023('a)001:8005: 'di rnams kri ya'i dbang nyi rtsa drug po lags so //
NK023('a)001:8007: sngon ri rab ri'i rtse mo rin po che kham
NK023('a)001:8008: bu 'bar ba'i gnas su dpal kun rig rnam par
NK023('a)001:8009: snang mdzad kyis / 'khor gyi byang chub sems dpa'
NK023('a)001:8010: don thams cad 'grub pa la sogs pa la phyag
NK023('a)001:8011: rgya chen po lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:8012: rig lnga ye shes lnga ru mthar phyin pas dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8013: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya chen po
NK023('a)001:8014: lnga'i dbang bskur bas ye shes lnga mthar phyin rdzogs
NK023('a)001:8015: longs spyod pa'i sku thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8016: byang chub mchog dang sa gnon dang //
NK023('a)001:8017: mchog sbyin mnyam pa'i phyag rgyar ldan //
NK023('a)001:8018: skyabs kyi phyag rgya la sogs lngas //
NK023('a)001:8019: mi 'di phyag rgya'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:8020: rgyal po phyag rgya mchog gi rgya //
NK023('a)001:8021: phyag rgya'i dbang mchog mi 'di la //
NK023('a)001:8022: ye shes lnga dang rigs lnga'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:8023: dbang gnyis rdzogs pa'i bkra shis le'u ste bzhi bcu rtsa bdun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8024: sku gsung thugs phyag rgya'i dbang dang po'i /
NK023('a)001:8026: sngon bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor
NK023('a)001:8027: rnams la snying po sngags kyis dbang bskur bas rtogs
NK023('a)001:8028: pa'i ye shes tshe phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan
NK023('a)001:8029: par gyur to // de dang rjes su mthun par
NK023('a)001:8030: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs ye shes kyi byin gyis
NK023('a)001:8031: brlabs pa'i snying po sngags kyis dbang bskur bas rtogs
NK023('a)001:8032: pa'i ye shes tshe phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan
NK023('a)001:8033: par gyur to // par gyur cig / thugs kyi sa bon 'bru mchog ste /
NK023('a)001:8034: sngags kyi byin rlabs bsam mi khyab //
NK023('a)001:8035: ye shes thugs kyi sa bon mchog /
NK023('a)001:8036: 'bras bu sngags kyi bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8037: snying po rigs lnga sangs rgyas kun gyi mchog /
NK023('a)001:8038: gsung mchog sngags kyi phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK023('a)001:8039: byin rlabs chen po gzhan na med pa yi //
NK023('a)001:8040: 'di ni dbang rnams thob pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8045: hri pad+ma a mi d+he wa /
NK023('a)001:8046: a karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi /
NK023('a)001:8047: zhes bka' brgyad bde 'dus nas kyang bshad /
NK023('a)001:8048: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis
NK023('a)001:8049: 'khor rnams la gser gyi thur mang gis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:8050: bas ma rig pa'i ling tog byang nas shes rab
NK023('a)001:8051: kyi mig gsal bar gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8052: de dang rjes su mthun par gser gyi thur mas
NK023('a)001:8053: dbang bskur bas ma rig pa'i ling tog byang nas
NK023('a)001:8054: shes rab kyi mig gsal bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8055: gser gyi thur ma thogs byas te //
NK023('a)001:8056: mig mkhan rgyal pos dbang bskur bzhin //
NK023('a)001:8057: bu khyod ma rig mi shes pa'i //
NK023('a)001:8058: rab rib rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK023('a)001:8059: thugs kyi gzungs gser gyi thur ma'o //
NK023('a)001:8060: rang bzhin gyis dbang bzhi sna la yongs lags so //
NK023('a)001:8061: dbang po dbang gnyis thugs ye shes //
NK023('a)001:8066: rin chen gser gyi thur ma yis //
NK023('a)001:8067: 'bar ba'i ye shes gsal phyi nas //
NK023('a)001:8068: nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK023('a)001:8069: shes rab mchog gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bzhi bcu dgu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8071: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis
NK023('a)001:8072: 'khor rnams la me long gis dbang bskur bas chos
NK023('a)001:8073: thams cad snang la rang bzhin med par gyur to
NK023('a)001:8074: // de dang rjes su mthun par me long gis
NK023('a)001:8075: dbang bskur bas chos thams cad gzugs brnyan rten 'brel
NK023('a)001:8076: sgyu ma tsam du mthong bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8077: chos sku gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK023('a)001:8078: rten 'brel mthu las snang ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:8079: brjod med rang bzhin dag pa'i don //
NK023('a)001:8080: chos nyid sgyu mar gsal zhing ston par shog /
NK023('a)001:8081: snang gsal dri ma sel ba dang //
NK023('a)001:8082: mi mngon dbang po gsal ba dang //
NK023('a)001:8083: ye shes gsal ba'i me long gis //
NK023('a)001:8084: 'di ni me long dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste lnga bcu tham pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8086: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis
NK023('a)001:8087: 'khor rnams la 'khor los dbang bskur bas 'gro ba'i
NK023('a)001:8088: don la thogs pa med par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8089: de dang rjes su mthun par 'khor los dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:8090: bas 'khor ba'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang ldan
NK023('a)001:8091: nas khams gsum gyi gnas thams cad du 'gro ba'i
NK023('a)001:8092: don la chags thogs pa med par 'gro bar gyur
NK023('a)001:8093: cig / 'og tu gser gyi 'khor lo dag /
NK023('a)001:8094: brjod pa'i don du 'bru bkod nas //
NK023('a)001:8095: gzhan gyi don la phan pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:8096: rgyal ba'i 'khor lo bskor bar shog /
NK023('a)001:8097: nyon mongs ma lus gzhom pa dang //
NK023('a)001:8098: legs pa'i yon tan rdzogs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:8100: de ni dbang rnams thob pa'i bkra shis le'u ste lnga bcu gcig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8102: // sngon rnam par snang mdzad kyis ri rab ri'i rtser
NK023('a)001:8103: 'khor rnams la dung gi dbang bskur bas tshangs pa'i
NK023('a)001:8105: de dang rjes su mthun par dung gi dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:8106: bas tshangs pa'i dbyangs lta bu'i sgra sgrogs pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:8107: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8108: chos dung rgyal bas bus nas ni //
NK023('a)001:8109: 'jig rten sems can bskal can la //
NK023('a)001:8110: rnams gsal sdig byang chos thob pa'i //
NK023('a)001:8111: tshangs pa'i sgra skad sgrogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:8112: skyobs pa'i mgon po tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK023('a)001:8114: 'jig rten gsum du rgyas pa yis //
NK023('a)001:8115: 'di ni bcom ldan gsung gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste lnga bcu rtsa gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8117: // sngon bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la me tog phreng bas dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:8118: tshul khrims kyi phreng ba yongs su rdzogs par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8119: de dang rjes su mthun par me tog gi phreng
NK023('a)001:8120: bas dbang bskur bas tshul khrims kyi phreng ba yongs
NK023('a)001:8121: su rdzogs pas ngan song las ldog pa'i dbang dam
NK023('a)001:8123: sdug cing mdzes pa'i me tog rgyan //
NK023('a)001:8124: dgos pa'i don rnams myur bar 'byin //
NK023('a)001:8125: thams cad kun gyi yid du 'ong //
NK023('a)001:8126: 'byor pa'i longs spyod rgyan du shog /
NK023('a)001:8127: kha dog dbyibs legs rin chen me tog 'di //
NK023('a)001:8128: nam mkha' gang zhing sa gzhi khebs pa yi //
NK023('a)001:8129: mchod pa'i sprin dpung dus su char 'babs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:8130: 'di ni me tog mdzes pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste lnga bcu rtsa gsum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8132: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtse mo nas rnam par snang
NK023('a)001:8133: mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la phyag rgya bzhi las rdo
NK023('a)001:8134: rje'i dbang bskur bas thugs rdo rje'i rigs kyi dbang
NK023('a)001:8135: dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8136: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya chen po
NK023('a)001:8137: bzhi las rdo rje'i dbang skur bas thugs ye shes
NK023('a)001:8138: rdo rje lta bu dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa
NK023('a)001:8140: sku yi phyag rgya'i rtags bstan pa /
NK023('a)001:8141: ye shes rdo rje lta bu ste //
NK023('a)001:8142: rdo rje thugs kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK023('a)001:8143: me long ye shes thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:8144: rdo rje'i rigs mchog rdo rje sems ma ste //
NK023('a)001:8145: dkar la dag pas shar phyogs sangs rgyas shing //
NK023('a)001:8146: bde ba chen po'i rgyan du bstan pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8147: 'di ni thugs kyi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste nga bzhi pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8149: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtse mo nas dpal kun rig
NK023('a)001:8150: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la phyag rgya
NK023('a)001:8151: chen po bzhi las rin po che'i dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:8152: yon tan rin po che lta bu dang ldan pa'i
NK023('a)001:8153: dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8154: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya bzhi las
NK023('a)001:8155: rin po che'i dbang bskur bas yon tan rin po
NK023('a)001:8156: che'i dbang bskur bas yon tan rin po che dang
NK023('a)001:8157: lta bu dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK023('a)001:8158: gyur cig / sku yi phyag rgya rtags bstan pa //
NK023('a)001:8159: 'gro ba kun gyi re ba bskongs //
NK023('a)001:8160: yon tan rin chen rang bzhin te //
NK023('a)001:8161: mnyam nyid ye shes thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:8162: rin chen rigs mchog yon tan sems dpa' ste //
NK023('a)001:8163: ser la dag pa lho phyogs sangs rgyas shing //
NK023('a)001:8164: bde ba chen po'i rgyan du bstan pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8165: 'di ni yon tan dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste nga lnga pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8167: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK023('a)001:8168: kyis 'khor rnams la pad+mas dbang bskur bas gsung pad+ma
NK023('a)001:8169: rigs kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8170: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya chen po
NK023('a)001:8171: bzhis las pad+ma'i dbang bskur bas 'gro ba'i don mdzad
NK023('a)001:8172: na yang 'gro ba'i nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos
NK023('a)001:8173: pa'i gsung pad+ma lta bu dang ldan pa'i dbang dam
NK023('a)001:8175: sku yi phyag rgya rtags bstan pa //
NK023('a)001:8176: pad+ma dbang gis rang bzhin te //
NK023('a)001:8177: gsung gi rang bzhin 'byung po'i mdzod //
NK023('a)001:8178: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:8179: pad+ma rigs mchog chos kyi sems dpa' ste //
NK023('a)001:8180: dmar la dag pas nub phyogs bde ba can gyi zhing //
NK023('a)001:8181: bde ba chen po'i rgyan du bstan pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8182: 'di ni gsung gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste nga drug pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8184: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtse mor dpal rnam par snang
NK023('a)001:8185: mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la phyag rgya bzhi las rgya
NK023('a)001:8186: gram gyis dbang bskur bas phrin las kyi rigs kyi
NK023('a)001:8188: de dang rjes su mthun par rgya gram gyis dbang
NK023('a)001:8189: bskur bas phrin las kyi rigs dang ldan pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:8190: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8191: sku yi phyag rgya'i rtags bstan pa //
NK023('a)001:8192: las rnams ma lus rdzogs pa'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:8193: phrin las don yod grub pa ste //
NK023('a)001:8194: bya ba nan tan ye shes thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:8195: las kyi rigs mchog las kyi sems dpa' ste //
NK023('a)001:8196: ljang khu dag pas byang phyogs sangs rgyas shing //
NK023('a)001:8197: bde ba chen po'i rgyan du bstan pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8198: 'di ni las kyi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste lnga bcu rtsa bdun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8200: // sngon dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la
NK023('a)001:8201: bdud rtsi bum pas dbang bskur bas rnam par rtog
NK023('a)001:8203: de dang rjes su mthun par de bzhin gshegs pas
NK023('a)001:8204: thugs rje byin gyis brlabs pa'i bdud rtsi bum pas
NK023('a)001:8205: dbang bskur bas / lus dang khong mi bde ba'i
NK023('a)001:8206: nad rnams bkrus nas dag cing byang bar gyur cig
NK023('a)001:8207: dbang bskur bas / / spros med spros bral chos kyi dbyings //
NK023('a)001:8208: bum pa zlum po yum gyi gter //
NK023('a)001:8209: phan byed sman pa'i mchog yin te //
NK023('a)001:8210: 'gro ba'i nad sel bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8211: bum pa zlum po spros med chos kyi dbyings //
NK023('a)001:8212: thugs rje chen pos phan mdzad yum gyi tshul //
NK023('a)001:8213: 'khor ba gnas skyobs dri ma dag mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:8214: 'di ni sgrib pa sel ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste lnga bcu rtsa brgyad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8217: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la seng ges dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:8218: log pa'i phyogs zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8219: de dang rjes su mthun par seng ges dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:8220: bas gsung rab rgya mtshos sgras log pa'i phyogs thams
NK023('a)001:8221: cad zil gyis gnon nas skad gcig ma gcig la
NK023('a)001:8222: stong spyi phud kyi sems can mngon par rdzogs par
NK023('a)001:8223: sangs rgyas par byed pa'i bcom ldan 'das kun tu
NK023('a)001:8224: bzang po zhes bya bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8225: gzugs bzang sems can kun gyi gtso bo ste //
NK023('a)001:8226: zil gnon sgra 'byin sder chags skrags par byed //
NK023('a)001:8227: phyogs rnams kun bskyed seng ge dpal dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:8228: zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:8229: seng ge'i nga ro sgra chen thogs med pas //
NK023('a)001:8230: 'jigs med 'joms pa'i sgra rnams bsgrags nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:8231: bdud kyi dpung rnams zil gyis gnon mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:8232: 'di ni mthu dpung che'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste lnga bcu rtsa dgu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8234: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK023('a)001:8235: kyis 'khor rnams la nyi mas dbang bskur bas ma
NK023('a)001:8236: rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'i dbang dam pa thob
NK023('a)001:8237: par gyur to // de dang rjes su mthun par
NK023('a)001:8238: nyi mas dbang bskur bas skye 'gro ma lus pa'i
NK023('a)001:8239: sems kyi rgyud la ye shes kyi 'od zer chen
NK023('a)001:8240: pos dus mtha' med par 'char ba'i skal ba dang
NK023('a)001:8242: nyi ma mun sel shes rab sgron //
NK023('a)001:8243: kun la gsal ba'i rin po ches //
NK023('a)001:8244: thams cad kun gyi dpal du shar //
NK023('a)001:8245: ma rig gsal ba'i sgron me shog /
NK023('a)001:8246: ye shes gsal bas phyogs bcur khyab par dro //
NK023('a)001:8247: thugs rje che bas mun pa sel bar byed //
NK023('a)001:8248: 'od gsal phro bas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:8249: 'di ni shes rab dbang gi bkra shis rjes su le'u ste drug cu tham pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8251: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK023('a)001:8252: kyis 'khor rnams zla bas dbang bskur bas mun pa
NK023('a)001:8253: sel ba'i dbang dang tsha ba'i sdug bsngal sel ba'i
NK023('a)001:8255: de dang rjes su mthun par zla ba lag tu
NK023('a)001:8256: byin pas stong khams thams cad kyi mun pa dus
NK023('a)001:8257: gcig tu byang nas kun tu gsal bar byed par
NK023('a)001:8258: gyur cig / thams cad kun sel chu shel lta bu ste /
NK023('a)001:8259: dgos pa'i don 'byin dkar la dag pa'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:8260: tshad med thabs kyi zla ba rin po che //
NK023('a)001:8261: ma rig mun sel dbang mchog bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8262: dkar la dag pa'i zla ba dri med pa //
NK023('a)001:8263: thabs kyi mtshan nyid skyon gyis ma gos te //
NK023('a)001:8264: yongs su dag pas mun sel bsil ba'i sman //
NK023('a)001:8265: 'di ni thabs kyi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste drug cu rtsa gcig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8267: // 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po 'khor lo rin po che'i tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhe na /
NK023('a)001:8268: rgyal po rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:8269: gso sbyong gi nyi ma bco lnga la dbus khrus
NK023('a)001:8270: byas te dbus su gnas shing /
NK023('a)001:8271: steng gi khyams btsun mo'i 'khor na gnas pa'i tshe /
NK023('a)001:8272: shar phyogs nas 'khor lo rin po che rtsibs stong
NK023('a)001:8273: yod pa lte ba mu khyud du gser las grub
NK023('a)001:8274: pa 'gar bzos ma byas shing rang byung ba nam
NK023('a)001:8275: 'phang du ta la bdun gyis srid tsam zhig rgyal
NK023('a)001:8276: po'i phyag g.yas pa'i mthil du rang babs te /
NK023('a)001:8277: de yi tshe rgyal po bsam pa /
NK023('a)001:8278: rtags 'di dang sbyar nas bdag ni 'khor lor bsgyur
NK023('a)001:8279: ba'i rgyal po yin nges so snyams nas lag pa
NK023('a)001:8280: g.yas pas 'khor lo bskor te rdzu 'phrul gyis nam
NK023('a)001:8281: mkha' la 'gro zhing phyag na 'khor lo gnas te
NK023('a)001:8282: rgyal po dpung gi tshogs dang bcas pa yang gnas
NK023('a)001:8283: par gyur te / gling bzhi la gnas pa'i rgyal
NK023('a)001:8284: rigs thams cad kyis mdun bsu zhing gnas pa'i tshe
NK023('a)001:8285: par gyur te / / mi thams cad dge ba
NK023('a)001:8286: bcu yi las kyi las la bkod cing 'dzum par
NK023('a)001:8287: par gyur te / / byed pa / nangs par khye'u sus la /
NK023('a)001:8288: dga' ba nyam du myong bar byed /
NK023('a)001:8289: de dang rjes su mthun par 'khor lo rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:8290: mi 'di la chos kyi 'khor lo rin po che bskor te /
NK023('a)001:8291: 'jig rten gsum gyi 'gro ba ma lus pa rnams
NK023('a)001:8292: rnam par grol ba'i lam la bkod cing so so'i
NK023('a)001:8293: skal ba ji lta ba bzhin du sems kyi rgyud
NK023('a)001:8294: la yongs su smin par byed cing 'khor lo bsgyur
NK023('a)001:8295: ba'i rgyal srid kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:8296: / dus gsum rgyal bas bskor ba'i 'khor lo 'di //
NK023('a)001:8297: mi khom rgyun chad rgyu dang 'bras bu ston //
NK023('a)001:8298: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i dbang phyug rin po che //
NK023('a)001:8299: bla med 'khor lo dam pa bskor gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8300: stong nyid ye shes gsal ba'i 'khor lo la //
NK023('a)001:8301: chos nyid dbyings las phrin las cir yang ston //
NK023('a)001:8302: sems can kha lo gyen du bsgyur mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:8303: 'di ni chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste drug cu rtsa gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8305: // 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rta rin po che tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhe na /
NK023('a)001:8306: mdog rin po che in+t+ra ni la ltar sngon por gnas pa /
NK023('a)001:8308: zhon na gus par byed pa /
NK023('a)001:8310: gser gyi d+r+wa bas g.yogs pa /
NK023('a)001:8311: rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa zhig nam mkha' la 'gro ba /
NK023('a)001:8312: sbrul gyi shugs 'chang ba zhes bya /
NK023('a)001:8313: rta'i rgyal po de nyams sad pa'i phyir rgyal po'i nyi ma shar khar rta la zhon te /
NK023('a)001:8314: gling bzhi'i rgya mtsho mtha' bskor de /
NK023('a)001:8316: khye'u gzugs kyis dga' ba nyams su myong ngo //
NK023('a)001:8317: de dang rjes su mthun par rta rin po che
NK023('a)001:8318: 'di byin pas mi 'di zhes bya ba rdzu 'phrul
NK023('a)001:8319: gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan te gzhon pa dang
NK023('a)001:8320: ldan nas thams cad la dga' mgur 'gro ba la
NK023('a)001:8321: thogs pa med par gyur cing /
NK023('a)001:8322: 'khor ba'i chu bo 'jigs pa bzhi las sgrol //
NK023('a)001:8323: brtson 'grus myur ba'i rdzu 'phrul shugs kyis 'gro //
NK023('a)001:8324: cang shes sprin gyi shugs 'chang rin po che //
NK023('a)001:8325: mi gnas ye shes yid bzhin spyod par shog /
NK023('a)001:8326: rdzu 'phrul thogs med kun tu myur ba'i shugs //
NK023('a)001:8327: gang yang bsgrod pa'i don la myur ba dang //
NK023('a)001:8328: rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs kun tu ston pa yi //
NK023('a)001:8329: 'di ni thogs pa med pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste drug cu rtsa gsum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8331: // 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i glang po rin po che tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhe na /
NK023('a)001:8332: kha dog shes bcag pa'i 'phro bzhin du dkar ba /
NK023('a)001:8333: yan lag bdun du shin tu gnas pa rin po che gtsug gis brgyan pa /
NK023('a)001:8334: gser gyi d+r+wa bas brgyan pa /
NK023('a)001:8335: rdzu 'phrul dang ldan zhing nam mkha' la 'gro ba /
NK023('a)001:8336: lha dang lha ma yin gyis g.yul 'gyed pa na /
NK023('a)001:8337: g.yul de dag las rgyal ba'i mthu dang ldan pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8338: de dang rjes su mthun par glang po rin po
NK023('a)001:8339: che 'di byin pas bsdo ba'i phyogs thams cad zil
NK023('a)001:8340: gyis gnon pa'i mthu dang ldan zhing rgyal bar gyur
NK023('a)001:8341: cig / theg pa don dam bla med ston pa'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:8342: yan lag bdun mdzes ku mu da'i mdog /
NK023('a)001:8343: gdul dka' stobs chen glang po rin po che //
NK023('a)001:8344: khyu mchog brlabs chen stobs lnga rdzogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:8345: stobs mchog pha rol gnon pa'i mthu mnga' ba //
NK023('a)001:8346: gdugs pa chen po gzhan gyis mi gnod pa'i //
NK023('a)001:8347: pha rol gzhan gyis rdzu 'phrul gnan mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:8348: 'di ni mthu stobs ldan pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste drug cu rtsa bzhi pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8350: // nor bu rin po che tshul ji lta bu dang
NK023('a)001:8351: ldan zhe na thams cad du sngo ba bee d+aur+ya
NK023('a)001:8352: 'i rang bzhin du gnas pa zur brgyad yod pa
NK023('a)001:8353: yon tan stong dang ldan pa byung ste /
NK023('a)001:8354: shin tu sbyangs pa de nam gyi gung la mun pa rab tu gnag pa la /
NK023('a)001:8355: nyams sad pa'i phyir rgyal mtshan rtse mo la btags
NK023('a)001:8356: te 'od ma tshal du btsug nas skyed mos tshal
NK023('a)001:8357: du gzigs mo'am rnam pa thams cad lta bar 'dod
NK023('a)001:8358: na yang nor bu rin po che'i 'od kyi dpung
NK023('a)001:8359: gis tshogs yan lag bzhi pa yan chad bag tshad
NK023('a)001:8360: kyis tshun chad gang bar gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8362: de dang rjes su mthun par nor bu rin po
NK023('a)001:8363: che 'di byin pa shes rab rnam par dag pa
NK023('a)001:8364: dang ldan te kun nas nyon mongs par gyur pa'i
NK023('a)001:8365: mun pa thams cad gsal ba'i sgron ma dang ldan
NK023('a)001:8366: nas lhag mthong gi ye shes rin po che dang
NK023('a)001:8368: dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan yid bzhin gter //
NK023('a)001:8369: 'khor ba'i mun sel bde ba'i snying po 'byung //
NK023('a)001:8370: dgongs pa mchod sbyin nor bdun phun sum tshogs //
NK023('a)001:8371: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen spyod par shog /
NK023('a)001:8372: dgos 'dod bskong ba'i nor bu rin po che //
NK023('a)001:8373: thams cad kun gyi yid dang mthun pa yis //
NK023('a)001:8374: che ba'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa yi //
NK023('a)001:8375: 'di ni yid bzhin re ba bskong ba'i dbang gi bkra shis te drug cu rtsa lnga pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8377: // blon po rin po che'i tshul ji ltar du ldan zhe na /
NK023('a)001:8382: dpag tshad tshun chad du rin po che gter yod pa mthong ste /
NK023('a)001:8383: rin po che'i gter chu'i nang na yod pa dang /
NK023('a)001:8384: skam sa na yod pa dang /
NK023('a)001:8386: bdag po med pa thams cad mthong ste /
NK023('a)001:8387: des 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po la gsol ba /
NK023('a)001:8388: lha dkar po nor la thugs khral chung bar mdzod cig /
NK023('a)001:8390: nam ci tsam na bzhed pa bka' rtsol cig /
NK023('a)001:8391: de skad ces gsol ba dang /
NK023('a)001:8392: rgyal po'i dges pa thams cad sgrub bo //
NK023('a)001:8393: de dang rjes su mthun par blon po rin po
NK023('a)001:8394: che 'dis dbang bskur bas ming 'di zhes bya ba
NK023('a)001:8395: la lha'i mig rnam par dag pa thob ste 'phags
NK023('a)001:8396: pa'i nor bdun dang ldan zhing bdag dang gzhan gyi
NK023('a)001:8397: don phun sum tshogs pa'i dgongs pa thams cad mthar
NK023('a)001:8398: phyin pa dang / shes bya la thogs pa med pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8399: gang la ci 'dod dpag bsam shing bu la //
NK023('a)001:8400: 'gro la snying brtse tshogs gnyis rdzogs par smon //
NK023('a)001:8401: dbang phyug btsun pa'i nor bu rin po che //
NK023('a)001:8402: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal thabs thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:8403: 'dzangs pa'i 'phrul 'byin blon po rin po che //
NK023('a)001:8404: legs nyes kun mkhas rtsod pa'i don la mkhas //
NK023('a)001:8405: yo gal ngo sprod 'dzangs pa'i 'phrul bag can //
NK023('a)001:8406: 'di ni blon po dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste drug cu rtsa drug pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8408: // 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i btsun mo rin po che yul ji lta bu dang ldan zhe na /
NK023('a)001:8409: rgyal bu rgyal rigs su skyes pa gzugs mdzes pa lta na sdug pa /
NK023('a)001:8410: tshul shes pa kha dog gis mdzes pas rgyas pa /
NK023('a)001:8411: mi'i mdog las 'das na lha'i mdog thob pa ste /
NK023('a)001:8412: pags pa'i mdog kyang sri yang ku ltar 'dug pa /
NK023('a)001:8413: lus ran cing dbyibs legs pa /
NK023('a)001:8414: sha ran cing ba spu'i bu ga nas tsan dan
NK023('a)001:8415: gyi dri bsung dang a ka ru'i dri'i 'byung ba
NK023('a)001:8416: / kha nas ut+pala'i ngad ldang ba /
NK023('a)001:8417: lus kyang bya ka tsa lin d+ha ka lter reg na bde ba /
NK023('a)001:8418: grang ba'i dus na reg na dro ba /
NK023('a)001:8419: tsha ba'i dus na reg na bsil ba /
NK023('a)001:8420: de ni sngon du bya ba dang phyi nas ci
NK023('a)001:8421: bya ba'i lung ma nor bar yid du 'ong bar
NK023('a)001:8422: byed pa / snyan par smra ba la mkhas te
NK023('a)001:8423: yid kyis mgu ba yang 'khor lo'i bsgyur ba'i rgyal
NK023('a)001:8424: po yid dang 'gal bar mi byed na /
NK023('a)001:8425: lus dang ngag lta ga la byed de /
NK023('a)001:8426: bud med thams cad kyi skyon sel ba ste /
NK023('a)001:8427: dper na skar ma pa ba sangs kyis skar ma thams cad zil gyis gnon pa bzhin no //
NK023('a)001:8428: de dang rjes su mthun par btsun mo rin po
NK023('a)001:8429: che 'di byin pas ming 'di zhes bya ba ting
NK023('a)001:8430: nge 'dzin zhi ba'i chos la dbang 'byor to //
NK023('a)001:8431: 'phags pa'i 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lam spyod yul
NK023('a)001:8432: yongs su dag pas bdag dang gzhan gyis don bden
NK023('a)001:8433: pa bsdud pa la yid bzhin du 'byor pa'i dpal
NK023('a)001:8435: pha rol phyin bcu skyobs pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:8436: shes rab gzung 'dzin btsun mo rin po ches //
NK023('a)001:8437: bsdu ba rnam bzhi tshad med bzhi po yis //
NK023('a)001:8438: tshe dang longs spyod gter rnams spyod par shog /
NK023('a)001:8439: shes rab dbyings las sprul pa'i lha //
NK023('a)001:8440: dgos pa'i don 'grub btsun mo ste //
NK023('a)001:8441: mthu dang dad pas 'brel pa yis //
NK023('a)001:8442: 'di ni btsun mo dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste drug cu rtsa bdun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8444: // dmag dpon rin po che tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhe na /
NK023('a)001:8449: rgyal po'i bsam pa bzhin byed nus pa /
NK023('a)001:8451: dgra thams cad kyi sbyor ba la mkhas pa /
NK023('a)001:8452: sde pa thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i go cha bgos pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8453: de dang rjes su mthun par dmag dpon rin po
NK023('a)001:8454: che 'di byin pas ming 'di zhes bya ba thabs
NK023('a)001:8455: dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa mthar
NK023('a)001:8456: phyin nas 'jigs tshogs kyi lta ba thams cad legs
NK023('a)001:8457: par spyod pa'i ye shes phun sum tshogs pa dang
NK023('a)001:8459: gnod pa'i dpung 'joms brtson 'grus go bgos te //
NK023('a)001:8460: 'jigs pa'i skyobs byed mgo la mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK023('a)001:8461: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa'i dmag dpon 'dis //
NK023('a)001:8462: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul dpung gis bsrung bar shog /
NK023('a)001:8463: drag shul dreg pas pha rol 'joms mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:8464: nyon mongs mi shes g.yul ngo gsal ba yis //
NK023('a)001:8465: rnam par rtog pa cis kyang mi tshugs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:8466: 'di ni gnyen po 'dul ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste drug cu rtsa brgyad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8468: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis
NK023('a)001:8469: 'khor rnams la ye shes kyi ral gris dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:8470: bas / nyon mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8471: de dang rjes su mthun par ye shes kyi ral
NK023('a)001:8472: gri lag tu byin pas sdug bsngal gyi rgyu 'drul
NK023('a)001:8473: bcad de / bag chags thams cad yongs su byang bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8474: sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:8475: mi shes d+r+wa ba gcod tshul du //
NK023('a)001:8476: rnon pos bag chags gcod pa ste //
NK023('a)001:8477: thams cad kun las rgyal bar shog /
NK023('a)001:8478: sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:8479: ye shes rnon pos gar yang thogs pa med //
NK023('a)001:8480: mi shes bag chags rtsa ba gcod pa yis //
NK023('a)001:8481: 'di ni sdug sngal gcod pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste drug cu dgu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8483: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK023('a)001:8484: kyis 'khor rnams la mda' gzhus dbang bskur bas thabs
NK023('a)001:8485: dang shes rab kyi dbang thob bo //
NK023('a)001:8486: de dang rjes su mthun par mda' gzhus dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:8487: bas thabs dang shes rab rnam par thar ba'i rgya
NK023('a)001:8488: mtsho myur du thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8489: sde pa'i tshogs 'joms myur ba'i shug 'chang zhing //
NK023('a)001:8490: thabs kyis 'dul la nyes pas ma gos te //
NK023('a)001:8491: dngos po kun 'joms pha rol 'bigs pa ste //
NK023('a)001:8492: thabs kyis 'dul ba'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:8493: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med gcig pa yi //
NK023('a)001:8494: thugs rje myur ba'i thabs kyis 'gro la 'byung //
NK023('a)001:8495: yang rab rtsal mchog blo yis gnon pa ste //
NK023('a)001:8496: 'di ni shes rab thogs med dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bdun cu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8498: // sngon dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la
NK023('a)001:8499: snam ral rin po ches dbang bskur bas bar du
NK023('a)001:8500: gcod pa'i bdud 'joms par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8501: de dang rjes su mthun par snam ral rin po
NK023('a)001:8502: ches dbang bskur bas bar du gcod pa'i bdud dpung
NK023('a)001:8503: 'joms pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8504: stobs ldan dbang phyug mthu stobs chen mnga' ba'i //
NK023('a)001:8505: bdud dpung phas kyis bsdo ba kun btul nas //
NK023('a)001:8506: che btsan chen po'i kun las rgyal ba dang //
NK023('a)001:8507: thams cad mthu stobs kun la dbang byed shog /
NK023('a)001:8508: rin chen rgyan mdzes gnam ral rin po che //
NK023('a)001:8509: logs pa'i phyogs dang bsdo ba zil gyis gnon pa dang //
NK023('a)001:8510: thabs la mkhas pa'i bdud dpung che ba ste //
NK023('a)001:8511: 'di ni kun las rgyal ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bdun cu rtsa gcig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8512: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK023('a)001:8513: kyis 'khor rnams la gshan nye ba'i rin po ches
NK023('a)001:8514: dbang bskur bas 'khor ba'i sgrib pa gcod pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:8515: dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8516: de dang rjes su mthun par gshan nye ba'i rin
NK023('a)001:8517: po ches dbang bskur bas 'khor ba'i sgrib pa gcod
NK023('a)001:8518: pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8519: nyon mongs sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa dang //
NK023('a)001:8520: dngos po mtshan ma ma lus gzhom pa dang //
NK023('a)001:8521: mi shes rnam par rtog pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:8522: gdug pa 'joms pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:8523: rin chen mdzes pa'i bshan mchog rin po che //
NK023('a)001:8524: legs pa rno la pha rol nyes pa gcod //
NK023('a)001:8525: ye shes rnon po kun gyis yid du yong //
NK023('a)001:8526: 'di ni sdug bsngal gcod pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bdun cu rtsa gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8528: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser kun rig rnam par snang
NK023('a)001:8529: mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la zha nye ba'i rin po
NK023('a)001:8530: ches dbang bskur bas bgegs dang log 'dren med par
NK023('a)001:8531: tshe'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8532: de dang rjes su mthun par zha nye ba'i rin
NK023('a)001:8533: po ches dbang bskur bas bgegs dang phyin ci log
NK023('a)001:8534: cis kyang mi tshugs pa'i tshe'i g.yung drung gi dbang
NK023('a)001:8537: gdung ba sel ba'i dbang mchog ste //
NK023('a)001:8538: 'bral bu thar pa thob pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:8540: rin chen rgyan mchog dbu zhwa rin po che //
NK023('a)001:8541: 'jigs pa bzhi skyobs log pa'i skyon las grol //
NK023('a)001:8542: mi 'gyur g.yung drung tshe yi dbang thob pa //
NK023('a)001:8543: 'di ni g.yung drung dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bdun cu rtsa gsum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8545: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis
NK023('a)001:8546: 'khor la tshangs pa'i khab skud kyis dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:8547: legs pa'i yon tan 'dod pa'i dbang thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:8548: to // de dang rjes su mthun par tshangs pa'i
NK023('a)001:8549: khab skud nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:8550: legs pa'i yon tan grub pa'i dbang dam pa thob
NK023('a)001:8551: to // par gyur cig / tshangs pa'i khab skud nye ba'i bkra shis te //
NK023('a)001:8552: legs pa'i yon tan tshangs par rdzogs pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:8553: nyes pa kun skyobs phyir na bkra shis te //
NK023('a)001:8554: thams cad rdzogs pa'i dbang mchog bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8555: tshangs pa'i khab skud legs pa'i dgos pa grub //
NK023('a)001:8556: gang la yid dang 'tshams par byed //
NK023('a)001:8557: don la thugs rje chen po che ba'i rtags //
NK023('a)001:8558: 'di ni legs pa tsha ba'i dab nga gi bkra shis le'u ste bdun cu rtsa bzhi pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8560: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK023('a)001:8561: kyis 'khor rnams la na bza' nye ba'i rin po
NK023('a)001:8562: ches dbang bskur bas grang pa'i sdug bsngal las skyobs
NK023('a)001:8563: pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8564: de dang rjes su mthun par na bza' nye ba'i
NK023('a)001:8565: rin po ches dbang bskur bas 'di dang pha rol
NK023('a)001:8566: gnyis kar grang ba'i nyon mongs pa zhi ba'i dbang
NK023('a)001:8568: nyes pa kun skyobs na bza' rin po che //
NK023('a)001:8569: bde mchog yid bzhin zad pa med pa ste //
NK023('a)001:8570: yon tan tshangs pa'i na bza' dam pa 'dis //
NK023('a)001:8571: 'di dang pha rol gnyis su gon par shog /
NK023('a)001:8572: rin chen na bza' ji ltar bltas pas sdug /
NK023('a)001:8573: che chung dbyibs ran 'gro la mdzes par gro //
NK023('a)001:8574: yon tan bla med 'phags pa'i sku dang mtshungs //
NK023('a)001:8575: 'di ni chos kyi rtags kyi dbang gi le'u ste bdun cu rtsa lnga pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8577: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtse dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK023('a)001:8578: kyis chags nye ba'i rin po ches bskur bas thugs
NK023('a)001:8579: rjes 'gro ba'i don la chags pa'i dbang dam pa
NK023('a)001:8581: de dang rjes su mthun par chags nye ba'i rin
NK023('a)001:8582: po ches dbang bskur bas 'gro ba'i don la zhabs
NK023('a)001:8583: kyis bcag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:8584: / rin chen chags kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:8585: kun la snyoms pa'i thugs rje yis //
NK023('a)001:8586: sems can don la thogs med de //
NK023('a)001:8588: rin chen mdzes pa'i chag mchog dam pa 'dis //
NK023('a)001:8589: gar yang thogs med phyogs bcur bgrod nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:8590: don rnams ma lus rdzogs par bya ba yis //
NK023('a)001:8591: 'di ni yongs la khyab pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste don drug pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8593: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par
NK023('a)001:8594: snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la khri snyan sa le'i
NK023('a)001:8595: pags pa nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:8596: / snying rjes sems can 'dren pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8597: de dang rjes su mthun par khri snyan sa le'i
NK023('a)001:8598: pags pa nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:8599: thugs rjes sems can gyi don byed pa'i dbang dam
NK023('a)001:8601: khri snyan sa le'i pags pa bkra shis te //
NK023('a)001:8602: thams cad snyoms pa'i bkra shis dam pa des //
NK023('a)001:8603: yon tan tshangs par rdzogs pa'i bkra shis pa //
NK023('a)001:8604: snying rjes don byed dbang mchog bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8605: snying rje chen pos sems can kun la dgongs //
NK023('a)001:8606: nyams thag 'phongs pa kun gyis don byas te //
NK023('a)001:8607: sems can 'khor ba'i gnas nas 'don mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:8608: 'di ni 'gro don rdzogs pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bdun cu rtsa bdun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8610: // dpe rgyal srid rin chen bdun dang nye ba'i rin chen bdun tshang ngo //
NK023('a)001:8611: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyis nyungs dkar 'thor byed kyis
NK023('a)001:8612: rgyal po bgegs kyi gnyen por byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK023('a)001:8613: rdzas 'di rdo rje slob dpon ngas byin pas slob
NK023('a)001:8614: ma'i lus sems kyi rgyud la bgegs stong phrag brgyad
NK023('a)001:8615: cu'i bsam sbyor ngan pas mi tshugs shing bgegs thams
NK023('a)001:8616: cad 'dul ba'i mthu stobs phun sum tshogs pa dang
NK023('a)001:8617: ldan pa'i don gyis bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8618: nyungs dkar rdo rje'i rigs mchog chen po ste //
NK023('a)001:8619: rtog bral mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje yis //
NK023('a)001:8620: rtog pa'i bgegs rnams rab tu 'joms mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:8621: bkra shis des kyang bgegs rnams zhi bar shog /
NK023('a)001:8622: nyungs dkar rdo rjes bgegs mchog 'dul //
NK023('a)001:8623: bgegs rnams 'dul ba'i mthu stobs ldan //
NK023('a)001:8624: dgra bgegs kun las rgyal ba yis //
NK023('a)001:8625: 'di ni byin rlabs che ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bdun cu rtsa brgyad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8627: // bcom ldan 'das la khyim bdag bzang skyong gis zho
NK023('a)001:8628: phul bas gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i rdzas 'di rdo
NK023('a)001:8629: rje slob dpon ngas slob ma khyod la byin par
NK023('a)001:8630: khyod kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi bcud dang bsod nams
NK023('a)001:8631: kyi gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i don gyis bkra shis
NK023('a)001:8632: par gyur cig / zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pa ste //
NK023('a)001:8633: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtog ste //
NK023('a)001:8634: yon tan kun gyi snying por gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:8635: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir zhi bar shog /
NK023('a)001:8636: bkra shis byin ldan rdzas mchog zho mchog 'dis //
NK023('a)001:8638: nyon mongs 'phongs pa bgrangs shing tshim byed pa //
NK023('a)001:8639: 'di ni longs spyod ldan pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bdun cu rtsa dgu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8640: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bram ze go'u da lis
NK023('a)001:8641: rtsa dur ba phul de dur ba ji ltar rgyu
NK023('a)001:8642: chung ngu la yal ga dang lo 'dab dang mang
NK023('a)001:8643: po 'phel bar byin gyis brlabs pa'i rdzas 'di slob
NK023('a)001:8644: ma la byin pas chos rgyu 'bras las ma rmongs
NK023('a)001:8645: shing dge ba'i rtsa ba chung ngu la brten nas
NK023('a)001:8646: bsod nams kyi 'bras bu phun sum tshogs pa 'phel
NK023('a)001:8647: ba'i don gyis bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8648: dur ba tshe ni 'phel bar byed pa ste /
NK023('a)001:8649: rdo rje tshe ni rab grub pas //
NK023('a)001:8650: skye shi sdug bsngal rgyun bcad de //
NK023('a)001:8651: dur bas bkra shis de ni tshe brtan shog /
NK023('a)001:8652: dur ba'i r+ts+wa mchog bsod nams mang por 'phel //
NK023('a)001:8653: bkra shis mdog legs 'bras bu yang dag byas //
NK023('a)001:8654: yid la ci bsam 'dod pa'i bkra shis pa //
NK023('a)001:8655: 'di ni 'dod pa 'byung ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgyad cu tham pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8657: // sngon bcom ldan 'das la sa yi lha mos mtshal
NK023('a)001:8658: li khri phul bas ji ltar li khri dmar po
NK023('a)001:8659: chags pa zhen pa'i ngo bor gnas pa bzhin du
NK023('a)001:8660: thugs rje chen pos sems can thams cad mi gtong
NK023('a)001:8661: bar byin gyis rdzas 'di ngas slob ma khyod la
NK023('a)001:8662: byin pas khyod kyis sems can gyi don byed cing
NK023('a)001:8663: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad la spyod bzhin ma chags
NK023('a)001:8664: pa'i don gyis bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8665: li khri dmar po dbang gis rang bzhin te //
NK023('a)001:8666: chos kun ma lus dbang du gyur pa ste //
NK023('a)001:8667: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu brtan 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:8668: bkra shis des kyang rgyal srid brtan gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8669: kha dog dmar po nub phyogs pad+ma'i rigs //
NK023('a)001:8670: chags pa gnyis ldan bdag don gzhan don 'grub //
NK023('a)001:8671: gsung gi bdag nyid don ston bkra shis rdzas //
NK023('a)001:8672: 'di ni tshe'i dbang gis bkra shis le'u ste brgyad cu rtsa gcig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8674: // sngon bcom ldan 'das kyis kun gzhi'i rnam par shes
NK023('a)001:8675: pa gnas lan gsum du gyur pa me long lta
NK023('a)001:8676: bu'i ye shes brnyes nas mngon par rdzogs pa'i rdzas
NK023('a)001:8677: 'di slob ma khyod la byin pas khyod kyi bag
NK023('a)001:8678: chags kyi sgrib pa bag la nyal cha phra mo
NK023('a)001:8679: yan chad rdo rje rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis bcom
NK023('a)001:8680: nas kun gzhi gnas 'gyur te me long lta bu'i
NK023('a)001:8681: ye shes mthong nas mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas
NK023('a)001:8682: pa'i don gyis bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8683: me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK023('a)001:8684: ye shes rgya mtsho bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK023('a)001:8685: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK023('a)001:8686: bkra shis des kyang sgrib pa dag gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8687: me long gdong bstan bzhin gyi dri ma sel //
NK023('a)001:8688: de bzhin nyon mongs shes bya'i dri ma sel //
NK023('a)001:8689: gsal la rang bzhin med pa chos nyid la //
NK023('a)001:8690: 'di ni ye shes gsal ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgyad cu rtsa gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8692: // sngon bcom ldan 'das la lha'i dbang po brgya byin
NK023('a)001:8693: gyis dung gtsug phud g.yas su 'khyil ba phul bas
NK023('a)001:8694: rdo rje spo la gshegs te chos sgra chen pos
NK023('a)001:8695: gsung dbyangs pas na yan lag drug cu dang ldan
NK023('a)001:8696: pa'i 'khor lo bskor ba'i rdzas 'di slob ma la
NK023('a)001:8697: byin pas tshangs pa'i sgra skad phun sum 'tshogs pa
NK023('a)001:8698: sgrogs shing chos kyi 'khor lo sgrogs pa'i don gyis
NK023('a)001:8700: dung gis chos kyi sgra rnams sgrogs pa'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:8701: yon tan rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid mchog gyur na //
NK023('a)001:8702: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK023('a)001:8703: bkra shis de ni tshigs la longs spyod shog /
NK023('a)001:8704: chos sgra chen por phyogs bcur grags pa dang //
NK023('a)001:8705: rgyal ba'i gsung mchog dung gi sgra bus te //
NK023('a)001:8706: ma lus 'gro ba kun gyi rgyud grol ba //
NK023('a)001:8707: 'di ni 'phags pa'i gsung gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgyad cu rtsa gsum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8709: // sngon bcom ldan 'das la glang po che'i sa srungs
NK023('a)001:8710: kyi g+hi ham phul te bee d+aur+ya dang ldan pa'i
NK023('a)001:8711: sman bdud bzhi las grol bar byed pa'i byin gyis
NK023('a)001:8712: brlabs pa'i rdzas 'di ngas slob ma la byin pas
NK023('a)001:8713: slob ma'i nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi las thar zhing
NK023('a)001:8714: nad thams cad sel bar byed pa'i mthu phun sum
NK023('a)001:8715: tshogs pa dang ldan pa'i don gyis bkra shis par
NK023('a)001:8716: gyur cig / gi ham dug gsum 'joms pa'i sman yin te //
NK023('a)001:8717: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs gyur nas //
NK023('a)001:8718: nyon mongs zug rngu med par gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:8719: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK023('a)001:8720: yon tan ldan pas bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi sel //
NK023('a)001:8721: sman mchog skye 'gro ma lus kun gyi gsol //
NK023('a)001:8722: byin gyis brlabs pas bkra shis tshe yi gsos //
NK023('a)001:8723: 'di ni tshe ring nad med dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgyad cu rtsa bzhi pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8725: // sngon bcom ldan 'das la shing gi lha mo 'od 'chang mas shing bil ba phyag tu phul te /
NK023('a)001:8726: ji ltar shing bil ba smin cing 'bras bu ngo bor gnas pa de bzhin du /
NK023('a)001:8727: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis sku dang stobs dang
NK023('a)001:8728: mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa 'bras bu'i chos thams
NK023('a)001:8729: cad yongs su rdzogs par byin gyis brlabs pa'i rdzas
NK023('a)001:8734: sku dang ye shes dang mtshan dang dpe byad la
NK023('a)001:8735: sogs te 'bras bu'i chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs
NK023('a)001:8736: par rgyas pa'i don gyis bkra shis par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:8737: / bil ba rgyu rkyen 'bras bu bcas pa'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:8738: 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa kun //
NK023('a)001:8739: byang chub snying po mchog tu gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:8740: bkra shis de ni 'jig rten 'grub par shog /
NK023('a)001:8741: yal ga lo 'dab me tog g.yur lo 'khyil //
NK023('a)001:8742: 'bras bu yid 'ongs 'byor pa'i longs spyod ldan //
NK023('a)001:8743: kun dang mthun par spyod pa yis //
NK023('a)001:8744: 'di ni phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgyad cu rtsa lnga pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8746: // don rnams 'grub par gyur pa'i rdzas //
NK023('a)001:8747: 'dod dgu re bskongs rin po che //
NK023('a)001:8748: rgyal srid rin chen snang bdun gyis //
NK023('a)001:8749: rgyal po mchog tu dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:8750: des bkra shis rdzas brgyad thob nas /
NK023('a)001:8751: da bkra shis rtags brgyad spongs te thun mong gi
NK023('a)001:8752: rdzas brgyad rtags brgyad thams cad kyi rgyab yig 'dis
NK023('a)001:8753: len pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das la byang chub
NK023('a)001:8754: shing drung du bdud kyis brgal ba'i dus su bkra
NK023('a)001:8755: shis pa'i rtags brgyad dang ldan te thugs dpal be'ura
NK023('a)001:8756: bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK023('a)001:8757: slob ma'i thugs dpal be'ura bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8758: dpal be thugs kyi sa bon te //
NK023('a)001:8759: 'dren pa rnams kyis thugs la sbas //
NK023('a)001:8760: bla med thar lam drang ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:8761: thugs kyi dpal be'u'i bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8762: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:8763: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK023('a)001:8764: thugs kha nyid las gsal bar mngon par ston //
NK023('a)001:8765: 'di ni dpal be'u'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgyad cu rtsa drug pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8767: // ston pa la bdud kyi bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK023('a)001:8768: thugs ni dpal be'u'i bkra shis gyur //
NK023('a)001:8769: de ring khyod la dpal be 'us //
NK023('a)001:8770: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:8771: thugs ka dpal be'usa bkra shis pas thams cad mkhyen pa'i bkra shis pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8772: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyis brgal ba'i dus su bkra shis kyi rtags brgyad byung ste /
NK023('a)001:8773: phyag dang zhabs kyi mthil 'khor lo bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK023('a)001:8774: mi 'di zhes bya ba la 'khor los dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:8775: bas phyag dang zhabs kyi mthil 'khor lor bkra shis
NK023('a)001:8776: par gyur cig / 'khor lo bkra shis phyag zhabs mthil //
NK023('a)001:8777: skyobs pa'i sangs rgyas 'dren pa'i lha //
NK023('a)001:8778: nyon mongs sems can dman pa'i gsos //
NK023('a)001:8779: phyag zhabs 'khor lo bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8780: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:8781: sdo ba'i phyogs las kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK023('a)001:8782: phyag zhabs mthil la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:8783: 'di ni 'khor lo dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgyad cu rtsa bdun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8786: phyag zhabs 'khor los de ring 'khor lo bskor ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:8788: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:8789: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyis bdud kyis brgal ba'i dus su bkra shis kyi rtags brgyad byung ste /
NK023('a)001:8790: ljags pad mar bkra shis pa de bzhin du pad mas dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:8791: ming 'di zhes bya ba la ljags pad mar bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8792: gsung mchog pad+ma chos kyi rgyal //
NK023('a)001:8793: nyon mongs ma gos pad+ma'i sku //
NK023('a)001:8794: thams cad sgrol ba'i gsung lags te //
NK023('a)001:8795: ljags mchog pad mar bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8796: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:8797: sdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK023('a)001:8798: ljags kyi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:8799: 'di ni pad+ma'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgyad cu rtsa brgyad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8804: thogs pa med pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:8806: cis kyang gos pa med pa'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:8807: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis brgal ba'i dus su bkra shis kyi rtags brgyad byung ste /
NK023('a)001:8808: sku rgyal mtshan du bkra shis pa de bzhin du
NK023('a)001:8809: rgyal mtshan gyis dbang bskur bas mi 'di zhes bya
NK023('a)001:8810: ba sku rgyal mtshan du bkra shis par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:8811: / mi nub rgyal mtshan 'dren pa'i sku //
NK023('a)001:8812: thams cad bdud kyi sde btul nas //
NK023('a)001:8813: dpung bcom sangs rgyas sku stod de //
NK023('a)001:8814: sku mchog rgyal mtshan bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8815: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:8816: sdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK023('a)001:8817: sku yi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:8818: 'di ni rgyal mtshan dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgyad cu rtsa dgu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8823: bdud bzhi pham byed bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8825: bdud bzhi las rgyal ba'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:8826: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis brgal ba'i dus su bkra shis pa'i rtags brgyad byung ste /
NK023('a)001:8827: mgul bum par bkra shis par de bzhin du bum
NK023('a)001:8828: pas dbang bskur bas ming 'di zhes bya ba la
NK023('a)001:8829: mgul bum par bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8830: bkra shis bum pa dam pa 'dis //
NK023('a)001:8831: bcom ldan 'das kyi mgul lags te //
NK023('a)001:8832: mgul mchog bkra shis 'di byin pas //
NK023('a)001:8833: bum pa'i bkra shis thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:8834: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:8835: sdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK023('a)001:8836: mgur gyi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:8837: 'di ni bum pa dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste dgu bcu tham pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8842: snying rjes 'dzin pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:8844: thugs rjes thams cad 'dzin pa'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:8845: bum pa snod bcud thig le yi //
NK023('a)001:8846: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas yin //
NK023('a)001:8847: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis brgal ba'i dus su bkra shis kyi rtags brgyad byung ste /
NK023('a)001:8848: dbu skra gdugs su bkra shis pa de bzhin du
NK023('a)001:8849: gdugs kyis dbang bskur bas ming 'di zhes bya ba
NK023('a)001:8850: dbu skra gdugs su bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8851: gdugs kyis tsha ba'i sdug bsngal kun bsal te //
NK023('a)001:8852: nyon mongs ma lus kun las rgyal ba dang //
NK023('a)001:8853: che ba'i yon tan ma lus brgyas pa ste //
NK023('a)001:8854: log pa'i phyogs rnams zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK023('a)001:8855: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:8856: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK023('a)001:8857: dbu skra'i mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:8858: 'di ni gdugs kyi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste go gcig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8863: gdung ba sil byed gdugs thams cad bsil bar byed pa'i /
NK023('a)001:8864: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis brgal ba'i dus su bkra shis pa'i rtags brgyad byung ste /
NK023('a)001:8865: gsung dung du bkra shis pa de bzhin du gdugs
NK023('a)001:8866: kyis dbang bskur bas ming 'di zhes bya ba gsung
NK023('a)001:8867: dung du bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8868: snyan pa'i sgra rnams phyogs bcur sgrogs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:8869: mu stegs log pa'i phyogs rnams skrag pa dang //
NK023('a)001:8870: sems can kun gyi shes pa dgrol ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:8871: gsung mchog dung gi rgyal por bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8872: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:8873: sdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK023('a)001:8874: gsung gi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:8875: 'di ni gsung gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste dgu cu rtsa gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8880: brgol ba spa bkong dbang thob bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8882: rgol ba thams cad spa bskongs pa'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:8883: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis brgal ba'i dus
NK023('a)001:8884: su bkra shis kyi rtags brgyad byung ste phyag dang
NK023('a)001:8885: zhabs kyi nya sha bkra shis kyi nyar bkra shis
NK023('a)001:8886: pa de bzhin du ming 'di zhes bya bas nyas
NK023('a)001:8887: dbang bskur bas phyag dang zhabs kyi nya sha bkra
NK023('a)001:8888: shis pa'i nyar bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8889: phyag zhabs nya shar bkra shis te /
NK023('a)001:8891: nyon mongs gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:8892: nya sha bkra shis nyar ni shog /
NK023('a)001:8893: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:8894: sdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK023('a)001:8895: nya sha bzhi las mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:8896: 'di ni nya yi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste dgu bcu rtsa gsum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8901: 'khor ba nyams nga med par shog /
NK023('a)001:8902: 'gro ba'i don mdzad nyams nga med pa'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:8903: gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyas nas ni //
NK023('a)001:8904: yun ring gnas par 'gyur ba yis //
NK023('a)001:8905: bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang thob kyang //
NK023('a)001:8906: gnang ba chen po sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:8909: dbang mchog dam pa'i bu mchog dang //
NK023('a)001:8910: don rnams 'grub pa'i bkra shis phyir //
NK023('a)001:8911: bdud 'dul bkra shis rdzas mchog rnams //
NK023('a)001:8912: rtags kyi brgyan te sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:8914: zhes 'di ni nang dbang la'ang rgyab yig mthun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8915: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams
NK023('a)001:8916: la ri rab ri'i rtse mo rdo rje rgya gram
NK023('a)001:8917: gyis dbang bskur bas phrin las 'grub par gyur to
NK023('a)001:8918: // de dang rjes su mthun par rdo rje rgya
NK023('a)001:8919: gram gyis dbang bskur bas phyogs bcu nas sngags 'chang
NK023('a)001:8920: rnams kyis rtag tu srung bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8921: dogs dang som nyi med pa la //
NK023('a)001:8922: gtsug tu rgya gram dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:8923: rdo rje 'dzin pas rnams kyis kyang //
