NK023('a)001:8924: bsrung ba mdzad pa nyid du shog /
NK023('a)001:8925: phrin las thogs pa med pa yis //
NK023('a)001:8926: bya ba nan tan ye shes las //
NK023('a)001:8927: dgos pa'i don rnams kun 'grub pa'i //
NK023('a)001:8928: 'di ni sngags 'chang dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste go bzhi pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8930: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK023('a)001:8931: kyis 'khor rnams la dar gyi cod pan gyis dbang
NK023('a)001:8932: bskur bas rdul gyi bag chags dang bral bar gyur
NK023('a)001:8933: to // de dang rjes su mthun par dar gyi
NK023('a)001:8934: cod pan gyis dbang bskur bas sbyor ba khams gsum
NK023('a)001:8935: na gnas na yang rdul gyis bag chags dang bral
NK023('a)001:8936: to // bar gyur cig / bkra shis rtags ldan dar gyi cod pan 'dis //
NK023('a)001:8937: dbang gi rang bzhin dmar po 'bar ba ste //
NK023('a)001:8938: dbang bskur spyi bor rtags pa'i yon tan gyis //
NK023('a)001:8939: dbang gi bkra shis dam pa thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:8940: chos nyid dar dang 'dra bar mtshungs pa yis //
NK023('a)001:8941: don dam nyid du rtogs pa mngon byung ba //
NK023('a)001:8942: 'di ni legs par chos nyid don ston pa //
NK023('a)001:8943: 'di ni byin rlabs che ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste dgu bcu rtsa lnga pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8945: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK023('a)001:8946: 'khor rnams la mchod pa rnam pa lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:8948: las kyi karma'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8949: de dang rjes su mthun par mchod pa rdzas kyis
NK023('a)001:8950: dbang bskur bas rdo rje rgyal thebs dang las kyi
NK023('a)001:8951: karma mtha' dag byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK023('a)001:8952: gyur cig / thabs chen stobs ldan mchod yon dam pa ste /
NK023('a)001:8953: dmigs pa lnga dang ting 'dzin cha dbye ste //
NK023('a)001:8954: rkyen dang mtshams pa'i mchod pa dam pa 'dis //
NK023('a)001:8955: thams cad 'bul ba'i stobs mchog bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:8956: dri chab dri bsungs me tog mdzes par bkram //
NK023('a)001:8957: bdug spos yid tshim arga bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK023('a)001:8958: lha bshos bro ldan 'od gsal mar me ste //
NK023('a)001:8959: 'di ni mchod pa rnam lnga dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste go drug pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8961: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par
NK023('a)001:8962: snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la nyan pa'i dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:8963: bas gsang sngags kyi rgyud mtha' dag nyan pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:8964: dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8965: de dang rjes su mthun par ka ba lis dbang
NK023('a)001:8966: bskur bas gsang sngags kyi rgyud mtha' dag nyan pa'i
NK023('a)001:8967: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:8968: gdung ba sems skyed dad pa'i shugs byung nas //
NK023('a)001:8969: brtson 'grus shugs kyis thams cad thob pa dang //
NK023('a)001:8970: dad pa'i shugs kyis kun tu nyan pa dang //
NK023('a)001:8971: shes rab stobs kyis thams cad shes par shog /
NK023('a)001:8972: shes rab rgya che nyan pa'i phyogs med byed //
NK023('a)001:8973: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' zhes rjes su slobs //
NK023('a)001:8974: sems dang chos nyid gnyis su med pa yis //
NK023('a)001:8975: 'di ni nyan pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste go bdun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8977: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par
NK023('a)001:8978: snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la chags shing gis dbang
NK023('a)001:8979: bskur bas theg pa mtha' dag 'chad pa'i dbang thob
NK023('a)001:8980: par gyur to // de dang rjes su mthun par
NK023('a)001:8981: rin po che chags shing gis chos 'chad par dbang
NK023('a)001:8982: par gyur to // bskur bas / theg pa mtha'
NK023('a)001:8983: dag 'chad pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:8984: par gyur to // bskur bas / / rin chen chags shing 'gro ba'i kha lo 'dren //
NK023('a)001:8985: ma lus thar lam gnas su 'dren par bya //
NK023('a)001:8986: skyes mchog dug sel sman pa'i rgyal po ste //
NK023('a)001:8987: ma rig rmongs pa'i 'gro ba 'dren par shog /
NK023('a)001:8988: gti mug rmongs pas shes pas bkrol nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:8989: ma rig log par rtog pa bkrol mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:8990: thugs rje che bas shes pa'i rgyud 'grol ba'i //
NK023('a)001:8991: 'di ni theg pa sna tshogs 'chad pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste dgu cu rtsa brgyad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:8993: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par
NK023('a)001:8994: snang mdzad kyis dar ma po tis dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:8995: chos kyi sgo mo thams cad la mkhas pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:8996: dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:8997: de dang rjes su mthun par dar ma po tis
NK023('a)001:8998: dbang bskur bas chos kyi sgo thams cad la mkhas
NK023('a)001:8999: shing rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:9000: / gsung rab po ti chos kyi gzugs brnyan te //
NK023('a)001:9001: legs pa'i yon tan ma lus bskyed mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:9002: thams cad kun gyi dbang pos sgrol ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:9003: chos rnams thams cad 'chad pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9004: gsung rab chos 'chad po ti glegs bam la //
NK023('a)001:9005: chos nyid sgra sgrogs yi ge phreng bas bskor //
NK023('a)001:9006: blo la rab 'bring ji ltar 'tshams par ston //
NK023('a)001:9007: 'di ni dar ma po ti'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste go dgu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9009: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par
NK023('a)001:9010: snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la rdo rje dril bus
NK023('a)001:9011: dbang bskur bas ye shes lnga dang chos kyi dbyings
NK023('a)001:9013: chos kyi sku thob nas 'gro ba'i don byed par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:9014: de dang rjes su mthun par rdo rje dril bus
NK023('a)001:9015: dbang bskur bas ye shes lnga dang chos nyid kyi
NK023('a)001:9016: don rtogs nas chos kyi sku thob nas 'gro ba'i
NK023('a)001:9018: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med chos kyi sku //
NK023('a)001:9019: 'du 'bral med pa chos kyi dbang mchog ste //
NK023('a)001:9020: 'bras bu stobs ldan phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK023('a)001:9021: rdo rje dril bu 'chang ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9022: rig pa ye shes rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NK023('a)001:9023: ye shes lnga po rtags kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK023('a)001:9024: g.yon pa dril bu gsung rab rgya mtsho sgrogs //
NK023('a)001:9025: 'di ni rdo rje dril bu 'chang ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgya tham pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9027: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par
NK023('a)001:9028: snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la rin po che'i dbu
NK023('a)001:9029: rgyan gyis dbang bskur bas chos kyi rgyal srid chen
NK023('a)001:9030: po la mnga' brnyes pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK023('a)001:9031: gyur to // de dang rjes su mthun par dbu
NK023('a)001:9032: rgyan gyis dbang bskur bas chos kyi rgyal srid la
NK023('a)001:9034: mya ngan 'das pa thugs rje'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:9035: rin chen dbu rgyan chos kyi rgyal //
NK023('a)001:9036: dbang dang byin rlabs sbyin rlabs sbyin pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:9037: chos kyi rgyal srid byed par shog /
NK023('a)001:9038: rin chen sna tshogs mdzes pa'i dbu rgyan mchog /
NK023('a)001:9039: legs par kun skyobs chos kyi rgyal srid byed pa'i mthu //
NK023('a)001:9040: phyag rgya rigs lnga mthu dang ldan byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:9041: 'di na rin po che dbu rgyan gyi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgya dang gcig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9043: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par
NK023('a)001:9044: snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la rin po che'i dpung
NK023('a)001:9045: rgyan gyis dbang bskur bas mi 'jigs pa bzhi la
NK023('a)001:9047: de dang rjes su mthun par dpung rgyan gyis dbang
NK023('a)001:9048: bskur bas mi 'jigs pa bzhi la mnga' brnyes par
NK023('a)001:9049: gyur cig / mi 'jigs phas kyi bsdo ba thub pa dang //
NK023('a)001:9050: mdzes pa'i rgyan mchog bkra shis thub pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9051: mnga' mdzes phung po rtags kyi dam pa ste //
NK023('a)001:9052: rgyan mchog dam pa ston pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9053: rin chen dpung rgyan sha ru ra'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK023('a)001:9054: chos nyid don rtogs mthun pa bstan pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:9055: dgos pa ting 'dzin legs par dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9056: 'di ni dpung rgyan gyi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgya dang gnyis pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9058: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par
NK023('a)001:9059: snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la zhabs gdub kyis dbang
NK023('a)001:9060: bskur bas / stobs bcu la mnga' brnyes pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:9061: de dang rjes su mthun par zhabs gdub kyis dbang
NK023('a)001:9062: bskur bas stobs bcu la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:9063: / rgyan gyi bye brag rgyal po'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:9064: rdo rje zhabs kyi chas rab 'dis //
NK023('a)001:9065: khyod kyis zhabs la dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9066: 'gro ba'i don la chag par shog /
NK023('a)001:9067: rin chen zhabs gdub dam pa 'dis //
NK023('a)001:9068: legs par mdzes pa'i yon tan gyis //
NK023('a)001:9069: nges par mdzad pa'i yon tan grub //
NK023('a)001:9070: 'di ni zhabs gdub dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgya dang gsum pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9072: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par
NK023('a)001:9073: snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la phyag gdub kyis dbang
NK023('a)001:9074: bskur bas tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i dbang thob
NK023('a)001:9075: par gyur to // de dang rjes su mthun par
NK023('a)001:9076: phyag gdub kyis dbang bskur bas tshul khrims rnam par
NK023('a)001:9077: dag pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9078: bsil snyan mdzad pa'i rgyan lags te //
NK023('a)001:9079: yid gnyen pa yi phyag gdub 'di //
NK023('a)001:9080: 'bras bu thob pa'i dbang mchog ste //
NK023('a)001:9081: 'gro ba'i yid 'ong dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9082: rin chen phyag gdub dam pa 'dis //
NK023('a)001:9083: nges par legs pa'i yon tan 'grub //
NK023('a)001:9084: 'di ni phyag gdub dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgya dang bzhi pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9086: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par
NK023('a)001:9087: snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la rin chen phreng ba'i
NK023('a)001:9088: do shal gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:9089: che ba'i yon tan thams cad rgyas pa la mnga' brnyes pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:9090: de dang rjes su mthun par rin po che do
NK023('a)001:9091: shal gyi dbang bskur ba che ba'i yon tan thams
NK023('a)001:9092: cad rgyas pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9093: rin chen phreng bas 'gro ba'i re ba bskongs //
NK023('a)001:9094: phreng ba do shal 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:9095: sku yi rgyan mchog yon tan sku la brgyan //
NK023('a)001:9096: phreng thag ma chad rgyan chad mi mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:9097: 'di ni phreng ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgya dang lnga pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9099: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK023('a)001:9100: kyis 'khor rnams la dar dpyangs kyis dbang bskul bas
NK023('a)001:9101: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK023('a)001:9102: cad la dbang thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:9103: de dang rjes su mthun par dar dpyangs kyis dbang
NK023('a)001:9104: bskur bas 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK023('a)001:9105: chos thams cad la dbang bsgyur bar gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9106: dar dpyangs gyen du 'phur ba ni /
NK023('a)001:9107: chos kyi sku dang gnyis su med //
NK023('a)001:9108: 'phred dang mthur gnyis sku gnyis te //
NK023('a)001:9109: longs spyod rdzogs dang sprul sku thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9110: dmar po g.yas phur chos nyid gyen du rtogs //
NK023('a)001:9111: sngon po 'phred phur phrin las rnam bzhi mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9112: mthing kha dmar phyang klu gdug zil gyis gnon //
NK023('a)001:9113: 'di ni dar dpyangs dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgya dang drug pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9115: // sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK023('a)001:9116: kyis 'khor rnams la rdo rje ming gis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:9117: bas rig pa nges pa'i sras su gyur nas rdo
NK023('a)001:9118: rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur to //
NK023('a)001:9119: de dang rjes su mthun par rdo rje ming gis
NK023('a)001:9120: dbang bskur bas mi 'gyur ba'i dbang gis dbang thob
NK023('a)001:9121: par gyur cig / rdo rje ming mchog mkhas pa'i dpal las grags //
NK023('a)001:9122: thugs la gsung du byung nas btags pa 'dis //
NK023('a)001:9123: dag cing tshul bzhin yid la bskur ba yis //
NK023('a)001:9124: thams cad ston pa'i ming mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9125: ston pa'i thugs rje nges pa'i ming btags pa //
NK023('a)001:9126: thugs kyi ngang nas nges pa'i sras su mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9127: rdo rje 'chang gi dbang thob ming gi dbang //
NK023('a)001:9128: 'di ni rdo rje ming gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgya dang bdun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9130: // 'dir ming yig yod na ming btags /
NK023('a)001:9136: sngon ri rab ri yi rtser byang chub sems dpa'
NK023('a)001:9137: sems dpa' chen po don thams cad 'grub pa la
NK023('a)001:9138: rigs bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyis mngon par shes pa lngas
NK023('a)001:9139: dbang bskur bas / 'bras bu ri rab ri'i rtse
NK023('a)001:9140: mor rin po che'i khang par rnam par snang mdzad
NK023('a)001:9141: la rdo rje dbyings su mngon par byang chub pa
NK023('a)001:9143: 'bras bu ri rab rtser mngon par sangs rgyas par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9144: mngon shes lnga ldan 'bras bu sa bcu 'das //
NK023('a)001:9145: yi ge 'khor lo rdzogs pa che la gnas //
NK023('a)001:9146: 'bras bu dam pa sangs rgyas te //
NK023('a)001:9147: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9148: dbang mchog thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa yi //
NK023('a)001:9149: 'bras bu chos rnams thams cad ma lus thob pa ste //
NK023('a)001:9150: rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang mchog der rdzogs pas //
NK023('a)001:9151: 'di ni phyi dbang rdzogs pa'i dbang gi le'u ste brgya dang brgyad pa rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:9153: // yo ga'i dbang drug cu rtsa gnyis po lags so //
NK023('a)001:9159: tha ma 'di yi tsa ka la stong nyid gru gsum dkyil na e dang /
NK023('a)001:9162: rdo rje rnam snang zhal gcig /
NK023('a)001:9163: chos 'chad phyag rgya rnams byang chub lnga'o //
NK023('a)001:9164: h'u tram h+r+ai a ni mngon shes lnga'o //
NK023('a)001:9165: sa ser po rdo rje rgyal po'i gdan no //
NK023('a)001:9166: phyi dbang brgya rtsa brgyad pa rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:9168: // yo ga rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor 'di ni kun byed du sems dpa'i rnal 'byor ces gsung /
NK023('a)001:9169: da ni kun 'dus dbang don gyi dbang bcu la'ang
NK023('a)001:9170: sems pa'i rnal 'byor yo ga rdo rje dbyings zhes
NK023('a)001:9171: bya ste / bka' yi chad mdo las /
NK023('a)001:9172: slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas dang //
NK023('a)001:9173: slob ma'i dam pa b+hi ma mi tra yis //
NK023('a)001:9174: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor zhal phyes tshe //
NK023('a)001:9175: rdo rje dbyings kyi bsrungs ma 'khor bcas kyis //
NK023('a)001:9177: ke'u ri dmar brgyad lhag ma dang /
NK023('a)001:9179: chos 'byung du rgyud sde lngar gsungs pa 'dod de /
NK023('a)001:9180: bya ba dang spyod pa dang rnal 'byor dang /
NK023('a)001:9181: rnal 'byor bla med dang lngar b+hi ba pa bzhed /
NK023('a)001:9182: ces gsungs pa dang mthun no //
NK023('a)001:9183: yang spyan ras gzigs kyi dri med 'od du gsal
NK023('a)001:9184: ba'i dkyil 'khor la 'jig rten gyi dmod pa yongs
NK023('a)001:9185: su spangs pa'i slad du lha'i gzugs brnyan ni bri
NK023('a)001:9186: bar mi bya'o // bdag po'i sa bon dgod ces te /
NK023('a)001:9187: gsang ba ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK023('a)001:9188: gsang ba rnal 'byor bla med ces ston pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9189: de nas phyi dbang 'dis thabs shes tha dad du bris pa dang mthun no //
NK023('a)001:9190: rnal 'byor bla med la gsum ste /
NK023('a)001:9192: thabs dang shes rab ma ning rgyud //
NK023('a)001:9193: bstan pa'i yig lam rkyen du 'dod //
NK023('a)001:9194: ces ma ning gis rgyud dam thabs shes rab gnyis kyi rgyud gsang mchog a ti yo ga /
NK023('a)001:9195: shes rab ma rgyud gsang chen a nu yo ga /
NK023('a)001:9196: thabs pha rgyud dam gsang ba ma h+aa yo ga
NK023('a)001:9197: dang gsang ba rnal 'byor bla med ces ston pa'o
NK023('a)001:9198: // sems pa'i rnal 'byor yo ga dang bzhi las /
NK023('a)001:9201: yang rgyud bdun la rtog pa'i rgyud byang sems dang /
NK023('a)001:9202: bya ba'i rgyud kri ya dang /
NK023('a)001:9203: spyod pa'i rgyud u pa ya dang /
NK023('a)001:9209: bya spyod rnal 'byor bla med bzhi ka rdo rje theg pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9210: phyi dbang gi tsa ka'i rgyab yig /
NK023('a)001:9211: ma skyes rdo rje thabs la rol //
NK023('a)001:9212: don dam dbyer med rol mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:9213: thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:9214: rdo rje sems dpa' bdag la dgongs //
NK023('a)001:9215: rnam shes phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:9216: rdo rje'i rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:9217: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs yin pas //
NK023('a)001:9218: rdo rje sems dpa'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9219: 'byung ba nam mkha' sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:9220: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:9221: rdo rje rigs kyi yum yin pas //
NK023('a)001:9222: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9224: theg drug skabs sbyar 'dis lha mi'i gong du'ang mdzad /
NK023('a)001:9226: dang po rgyal po bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:9228: kun gyis 'da' bar dka' ba yi //
NK023('a)001:9229: tshig btsan yul la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK023('a)001:9230: rgyal po bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:9231: sku lnga yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:9236: phyag rgya gzugs brnyan de'i spyi bor bzhag /
NK023('a)001:9238: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK023('a)001:9239: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo bya //
NK023('a)001:9242: rigs kyi khyod la phyag rgya che ge mo'am sum
NK023('a)001:9243: cu rtsa gsum rang sa tha dad kyis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:9244: bas sku lnga yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang thob par
NK023('a)001:9245: gyur cig / yang lha mi'i gzugs sku /
NK023('a)001:9246: nyan rang gi chos sku dang gzugs sku /
NK023('a)001:9247: byang sems rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma dang /
NK023('a)001:9248: mdo sde spyod pa'i dbu ma ni /
NK023('a)001:9249: chos longs spyod sprul pa'i sku gsum /
NK023('a)001:9250: phyi rgyud rdo rje'i sku'am ngo bo nyid sku dang bzhi /
NK023('a)001:9251: phyi dbang dus mngon par byang chub pa'i sku /
NK023('a)001:9252: khams gsum chos kyi rgyal po dang sku lnga'o //
NK023('a)001:9253: zhar la nang dbang skabs na /
NK023('a)001:9256: rang gzhan bde ba chen po /
NK023('a)001:9257: bsgrub dbang thams cad bde ba chen po'i sku ni sku drug pa khyad par 'phags pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9258: de la ma h+aa a nu a ti lha zung 'brel lo //
NK023('a)001:9259: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes ni //
NK023('a)001:9260: 'joms byed rdo rje rang snang bar //
NK023('a)001:9261: rdo rje sems dpa'i bdag nyid che //
NK023('a)001:9262: mi phyed rdo rje'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9263: skal ldan rigs kyi bu khyod la rdo rje'i rigs
NK023('a)001:9264: rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag mtshan rdo rjes dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:9265: bas stong pa nyid kyi ye shes rdo rje sems
NK023('a)001:9266: dpa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dbang thob par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:9267: / ma h+aa shu nye ta dz+nya na badz+ra s+w+aa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK023('a)001:9269: de yang phyi yo ga dmar chad ltar me long lta bu de gtso bor byas /
NK023('a)001:9270: sngags nang ltar stong pa nyid gtso bor byas /
NK023('a)001:9271: phyi dbang dang po phyag rgya'i lha dbang /
NK023('a)001:9272: phyi dbang gnyis pa phyag mtshan gyi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:9273: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
NK023('a)001:9274: 'khor lo chen po rang snang bas //
NK023('a)001:9275: rnam par snang mdzad bdag nyid che //
NK023('a)001:9276: chos kyi 'khor los khyod dbang bskur //
NK023('a)001:9277: skal ldan khyod la de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs /
NK023('a)001:9278: rnam par snang mdzad kyis phyag mtshan gser gyi 'khor
NK023('a)001:9279: los dbang bskur bas me long lta bu'i ye shes
NK023('a)001:9280: rnam par snang mdzad kyis sku gsung gi dbang thob
NK023('a)001:9281: par gyur cig / a ta ri sha /
NK023('a)001:9282: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes nyid //
NK023('a)001:9283: yid gzhin nor bur rang snang bas //
NK023('a)001:9284: rin chen 'byung ldan bdag nyid de //
NK023('a)001:9285: dgos 'dod sbyin pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9286: skal ldan khyod la rin po che'i rigs rin chen
NK023('a)001:9287: 'byung ldan gyis phyag mtshan rin po ches dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:9288: bas mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes rin chen 'byung
NK023('a)001:9289: ldan gyi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9291: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes nyid //
NK023('a)001:9292: bag chags med par rang snang bas //
NK023('a)001:9293: snang ba mtha' yas bdag nyid de //
NK023('a)001:9294: spyod bzhin ma chags dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9296: skal ldan khyod la pad+ma'i rigs kyi sangs rgyas snang
NK023('a)001:9297: ba mtha' yas kyis phyag mtshan pad+mas dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:9298: / gsung gi rang bzhin snang ba mtha' yas kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9300: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes nyid //
NK023('a)001:9301: ral gri dngos por rang snang ba //
NK023('a)001:9302: don yod grub pa'i ngo bo ste //
NK023('a)001:9303: sgrib pa gcod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9305: skal ldan khyod la las kyi rigs don yod grub pa'i phyag mtshan ral gris dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:9306: phrin las don yod grub pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi sgrib pa gcod pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9307: ma h+aa kri ta a nu sta na /
NK023('a)001:9309: rigs kyi phyag rgya'i rang snying las /
NK023('a)001:9310: so so'i rab gnas ldan par sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9311: rigs rnams so so'i brgyud 'dzin cing //
NK023('a)001:9312: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:9313: sbyor ba chen pos phyag mtshal te //
NK023('a)001:9314: dam tshig phyag rgyar rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:9315: smon lam rjes su mthun par sbyar //
NK023('a)001:9316: rol mo'i sgra yang de bzhin no //
NK023('a)001:9319: phyag mtshan lngas dbang bskur bas rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9320: rgyal po phyag rgya mchog gi rgya //
NK023('a)001:9321: phyag rgya'i dbang mchog mi 'da' ba //
NK023('a)001:9322: ye shes lnga dang rigs lnga'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:9323: dbang gnyis rdzogs pa'i bkra shis te zhe bdun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9324: gsum pa shes rab gzung ma'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:9326: shes rab gzungs kyi dbang mchog ni //
NK023('a)001:9327: rtogs dang ldan par gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9328: mtha' gnyis don du mi rtogs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:9329: gzungs ma'i rgyal mo chen mo yis //
NK023('a)001:9330: gzungs kyi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9331: don dam rang bzhin spros dang bral //
NK023('a)001:9332: dri med rang bzhin rnam dag byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:9333: cis kyang dgos med rig pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:9334: skal ldan rnal 'byor khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9336: gnyis med yongs su rdzogs pas na //
NK023('a)001:9337: thams cad bde ba chen po'i ngang //
NK023('a)001:9338: byang chub sems dang don du 'brel //
NK023('a)001:9339: shes rab chen po'i rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9340: dril bu 'am phyag rgya ma nyid gtad do //
NK023('a)001:9343: rang 'od kyi rig ma yid kyi yum ye shes
NK023('a)001:9344: kyi phyag rgya dang dngos kyi phyag rgya las kyi
NK023('a)001:9345: phyag rgya gnyis su med pa bde ba chen pos
NK023('a)001:9346: phyag rgya chen mo'i yum gyis thabs kyis mtha' gnyis
NK023('a)001:9347: mi rtog pa dang don dam byang chub sems dang
NK023('a)001:9348: rdzogs pa chen po'i spyod pa la 'jug pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:9350: gnyis pa bkra shis bum pa'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:9351: bkra shis chen po'i bum dbang 'dis //
NK023('a)001:9352: bde gshegs bzhugs pa'i pho brang ste //
NK023('a)001:9353: dkyil 'khor rdzogs par gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9354: dbang mchog de yang sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:9355: bskur bas dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9356: badz+ra ka la sha a b+hi she ka h'u /
NK023('a)001:9360: pad+ma hrih karma ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK023('a)001:9362: che ge mo la bum pas dbang bskur bas phyi
NK023('a)001:9363: nang gi sgrib pa ma lus pa dag nas dkyil
NK023('a)001:9365: spros med spros bral chos kyi dbyings //
NK023('a)001:9366: bum pa zlum po yum gyi gter //
NK023('a)001:9367: phan byed sman pa'i mchog yin te //
NK023('a)001:9368: 'gro ba'i nad sel bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:9370: gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyas nas ni //
NK023('a)001:9371: yun ring gnas par gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9372: bkra shis rdzas kyis dbang mchog kyang //
NK023('a)001:9373: gnang ba chen po sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:9375: bkra shis pa'i rdzas kyis dbang bskur bas 'phags pa'i
NK023('a)001:9376: lam yan lag brgyad po thob pa la dbang ba'i
NK023('a)001:9377: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9378: bkra shis la smon lam rgyud dang phyi dbang gi lugs gnyis gdab /
NK023('a)001:9379: ting 'dzin dur bas bsod nams kun tu 'phel //
NK023('a)001:9380: ji ltar drang srong chen po a ka tas //
NK023('a)001:9381: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtsa mchog dur ba 'dis //
NK023('a)001:9382: reg pas nad rnams thams cad bsal gyur nas //
NK023('a)001:9383: nad kyis gdung ba kun las rgyal bar shog /
NK023('a)001:9385: dur bas dge ba'i rtsa ba gags med pa'i dbang thob nas bkra shis pa /
NK023('a)001:9386: dur bas tshe ni 'phel bar byed pa ste /
NK023('a)001:9387: rdo rje'i tshe ni rab grub pas //
NK023('a)001:9388: skye shi'i sdug bsngal rgyun bcad de //
NK023('a)001:9389: dur ba'i bkra shis de ni tshe brtan shog /
NK023('a)001:9390: yang dag las kyi mtha' ni chags shing ral gris 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:9391: rdo rje dang ni rin chen chu skyes dang //
NK023('a)001:9392: de bzhin las kyi rigs kyi dbang bskur ba'i //
NK023('a)001:9393: kha dog bzang mdzes li khri 'dis //
NK023('a)001:9394: lha mi'i 'dod yon dbang du 'dus par shog /
NK023('a)001:9396: li khris dbang bskur bas lha mi mang po dbang 'dus nas bkra shis kyi 'dre /
NK023('a)001:9397: li khri dmar po dbang gi rang bzhin te //
NK023('a)001:9398: chos kun ma lus dbang du gyur pa ste //
NK023('a)001:9399: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu brtan gyur pa //
NK023('a)001:9400: li khri'i bkra shis des kyang brtan gyur shog /
NK023('a)001:9401: yang dag lta bas bden gnyis me long ston //
NK023('a)001:9402: de grub de thob de las 'da' mi mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9403: chos rnams sgyu ma lta bu ste //
NK023('a)001:9404: rang bzhin dag pas ya ma barlara shes na //
NK023('a)001:9405: gti mug mun pa'i bag chags bsreg sbyangs te //
NK023('a)001:9406: me long lta bu'i ye shes thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9408: me long gis dbang bskur bas chos kun sgyu ma
NK023('a)001:9409: bzhin du rab tu snang zhing dag par rtogs nas
NK023('a)001:9410: bkra shis pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9411: me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK023('a)001:9412: ye shes rgya mtsho bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK023('a)001:9413: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyad pas //
NK023('a)001:9414: bkra shis des kyang sgrib pa dag gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9415: yang dag ngag gi sgra skad tshangs pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9416: ji ltar na ra ya nar lha chen gyis //
NK023('a)001:9417: dung sgra bsgrag nas rims nad sel ba ltar //
NK023('a)001:9418: dam chos bdud rtsi dung gis sgra bsgrag pas //
NK023('a)001:9419: nad kyis gdung ba kun las rgyal bar shog /
NK023('a)001:9421: dung gis dbang bskur bas 'jig rten gsum du chos
NK023('a)001:9422: sgra sgrogs shing bkra shis pa'i dbang thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:9423: cig / dung gi chos kyi sgra rnams sgrogs pa'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:9424: yon tan rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK023('a)001:9425: rnam dag chos la thogs med spyod pa yi //
NK023('a)001:9426: bkra shis de ni tshig la longs spyod shog /
NK023('a)001:9427: shes bcu srog gi dbang po thob nas ni //
NK023('a)001:9428: yang dag dran pa g+hi ham nad gsob mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9429: ji ltar g+hi ham khyu mchog glang po yis //
NK023('a)001:9430: srog gi dbang po gnyen du gyur nas ni //
NK023('a)001:9431: rnam par dkar ba'i dam pa'i chos 'dzin ltar //
NK023('a)001:9432: shes bcu srog gi dbang po thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9434: g+hi ham gis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9436: shes bcu rnam dag 'chang ba po //
NK023('a)001:9438: sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK023('a)001:9439: dang por sems bskyed pa dang las dang po //
NK023('a)001:9440: rnal 'byor spyod dang cher skyes rnal 'byor dang //
NK023('a)001:9441: sbyor ba dang ni bsam pa phun sum tshogs //
NK023('a)001:9442: gzhon nu rgyal tshab rgyal por dbang bskur dang //
NK023('a)001:9443: skye ba gcig gis theg pa'i byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:9444: zhes gsungs pa ltar gong 'phel du thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9445: 'jug sgor chud cing lta thos bsam //
NK023('a)001:9446: sgom pa'i rnal 'byor stong chen dang //
NK023('a)001:9447: cher skyes kun snang sbyor rgyu ring //
NK023('a)001:9448: bsam pa tshogs sgrubs gzhon nu ni //
NK023('a)001:9449: mthong lam bsgom lam rgyal tshab ni //
NK023('a)001:9450: sa brgyad dgu bcu dag pa'i sa //
NK023('a)001:9451: rgyal po sa bcu rgyun mtha' dang //
NK023('a)001:9452: skyes gcig byams mgon lta bu 'o //
NK023('a)001:9453: skyes gcig gis theg pa'i byang chub //
NK023('a)001:9455: g+hi ham dug gsum 'joms pa'i sman yin te /
NK023('a)001:9456: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs gyur te //
NK023('a)001:9457: nyon mongs zug rngu med par gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9458: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK023('a)001:9459: yang dag rtogs pa bil ba 'bras bu'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:9460: de thob de grub de las 'da' mi mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9461: ji ltar rgyu dang sa bon myu gu la //
NK023('a)001:9462: 'bras bu cher smin shing mchog bil ba ltar //
NK023('a)001:9463: de bzhin dge ba'i rgyu mchog chung ngu las //
NK023('a)001:9464: 'bras bu rgya che dpag med dam pa thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9466: bil bas dbang bskur bas mtshungs pa med pa'i rang
NK023('a)001:9467: bzhin thob nas bkra shis pa'i dbang thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:9468: cig / bil ba rgyu rkyen 'bras bur bcas pa'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:9469: 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa kun //
NK023('a)001:9470: byang chub snying por mchog tu gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9471: bkra shis des ni 'jig rten 'grub par shog /
NK023('a)001:9472: yang dag 'tsho ba rnams ni 'dod zho yin //
NK023('a)001:9473: lha dbang brgya byin bdag nyid chen po yis //
NK023('a)001:9474: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rdzas mchog gis //
NK023('a)001:9475: nad rnams thams cad 'joms pa'i grub rdzas 'dis //
NK023('a)001:9476: rnam par rgyal ba'i grub rdzas dang po 'dis //
NK023('a)001:9477: bsam gtan ting 'dzin bcud dang ldan par shog /
NK023('a)001:9480: bsam gtan ting 'dzin bcud dang ldan pa'i dbang thob nas bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9481: zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pa ste //
NK023('a)001:9482: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtogs te //
NK023('a)001:9483: yon tan kun gyi snying por gyur pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9484: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir nad zhi shog /
NK023('a)001:9485: yang dag rtsol ba nyungs dkar bdud bzhi 'joms //
NK023('a)001:9486: bde bar gshegs pas byin gyis brlabs pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9487: bgegs rnams 'joms pa'i grub rdzas dang po yis //
NK023('a)001:9488: bar du gcod pa'i bgegs kyi tshogs bcoms nas //
NK023('a)001:9489: deng 'dir bkra shis mchog nyid thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9491: nyungs dkar gyis dbang bskur bas bdud bzhi la sogs
NK023('a)001:9492: pa bar du gcod pa'i bgegs kyis tshogs bcom nas
NK023('a)001:9493: bkris pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9494: nyungs dkar rdo rjes bgegs tshogs 'dul //
NK023('a)001:9495: bgegs rnams 'joms pa'i mthu stobs ldan //
NK023('a)001:9496: dgra bgegs kun las rgyal ba yis //
NK023('a)001:9497: byin brlabs chen po'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9498: bdun pa rgyal srid rin po che dang /
NK023('a)001:9499: phyi dbang drug pa rin po che sna bdun gyi dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:9501: 'dod rgu re skong rin po che //
NK023('a)001:9502: rgyal srid rin chen sna bdun gyis //
NK023('a)001:9503: rgyal po mchog tu dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:9506: rgyal srid rin chen sna bdun gyis dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:9507: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun gyis rgyal srid rin
NK023('a)001:9508: po che'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9509: dam chos rnam par 'byed pa'i 'khor lo ste //
NK023('a)001:9510: de thob de grub de las 'da' mi mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9511: 'khor lo rin chen bstan pas ni //
NK023('a)001:9512: sa bcu dag la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK023('a)001:9513: theg pa rnam gsum rtogs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:9514: chos kyi rgyal po chen por shog /
NK023('a)001:9517: theg pa rnam gsum rtogs nas sa bcu la dbang
NK023('a)001:9518: bsgyur ba'i chos kyi rgyal po'i dbang thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:9519: cig / ting 'dzin mi 'gyur stobs kyi glang po ste //
NK023('a)001:9520: de thob de grub de las 'da' mi mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9521: glang po rin chen bstan pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9522: stobs bcu dag la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK023('a)001:9523: theg pa rnam gsum rtogs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:9524: byang chub snying por gnas par shog /
NK023('a)001:9526: glang pos theg pa rnam gsum rtog nas stobs bcu la dbang bsgyur zhing /
NK023('a)001:9527: byang chub snying por gnas pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9528: brtson 'grus myur mgyogs shugs 'chang rdzu 'phrul rta //
NK023('a)001:9529: de thog de grub de las mi 'da' mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9530: rta mchog rin chen bstan pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9531: rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis dbang thob nas //
NK023('a)001:9532: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho sgrol ba dang //
NK023('a)001:9533: thar pa'i 'bras bu thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9536: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi yis 'khor ba'i sems
NK023('a)001:9537: can thar bar sgrol ba'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK023('a)001:9538: gyur cig / dran pas rang gi phyogs 'dzin gzhan 'joms dmag /
NK023('a)001:9539: de thob de grub de las 'da' mi mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9540: dmag mi rin chen bstan pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9541: mi 'jigs bzhi yi dbang thob nas //
NK023('a)001:9542: phas kyi rgol ba tshar bcad nas //
NK023('a)001:9543: go cha chen po bgos par shog /
NK023('a)001:9545: dmag dpon gyis mi 'jigs pa bzhi yis rgol ba
NK023('a)001:9546: tshar bcad nas go cha chen po'i dbang thob par
NK023('a)001:9547: gyur cig / tshim byed lus sems shin tu sbyangs pa'i btsun mo yin //
NK023('a)001:9548: de thob de grub de las 'da' mi mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9549: btsun mo rin chen bstan pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9550: shes rab dbyings kyi mchog thob ste //
NK023('a)001:9551: skye 'gags med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK023('a)001:9552: byang chub snying por gnas par shog /
NK023('a)001:9554: shes rab dbyings skye 'gags med pa'i don rtogs nas
NK023('a)001:9555: byang chub snying por gnas pa'i dbang dam pa thob
NK023('a)001:9556: par gyur cig / 'dul bar mkhas pa'i khyim bdag 'dul bar dga' ba yin /
NK023('a)001:9557: de thob de grub de las 'da' mi mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9558: blon po rin chen bstan pas ni //
NK023('a)001:9559: sum cu rtsa gsum dbang phyug rje //
NK023('a)001:9560: rdzu 'phrul chen po brgya byin ltar //
NK023('a)001:9561: lha yi rgyal po chen por shog /
NK023('a)001:9563: rdzu 'phrul chen po lha'i rgyal po chen po'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9564: btang snyoms yang dag don mdzad rin chen yin //
NK023('a)001:9565: de thob de grub de las 'da' mi mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9566: nor bu rin chen bstan pas ni //
NK023('a)001:9567: 'jig rten dbang du de bzhin gshegs //
NK023('a)001:9568: dpe byad mtshan gyis brgyan pa dang //
NK023('a)001:9569: gser gyi kha dog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9571: nor bu rin po che mtshan dang dpe byad kyis
NK023('a)001:9572: brgyan pa'i gser gyi kha dog 'od zer du ma
NK023('a)001:9573: 'phro ba dang ldan pa'i sku'i dbang thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:9575: dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan yid bzhin gter /
NK023('a)001:9576: 'khor ba'i mun sel bde ba'i snying po 'byung //
NK023('a)001:9577: dgos pa'i mchod sbyin nor bu phun sum tshogs //
NK023('a)001:9578: yid bzhin rgyal srid rin chen nor bu spyod par shog /
NK023('a)001:9581: dad dang shes rab gtong dang thos pa dang //
NK023('a)001:9582: bag yod ngo tsha shes dang tshul khrims kyis //
NK023('a)001:9583: 'phags pa'i nor bdun gyis 'phongs pa rgyun bcad de
NK023('a)001:9584: dgos 'dod la longs spyod pa'i dbang dam pa thob
NK023('a)001:9585: par gyur cig / phyi dbang lnga pa khyad par gdan khri dang //
NK023('a)001:9586: rang rig rtogs pa'i ye shes ni //
NK023('a)001:9587: cis kyang ma gos thams cad 'joms //
NK023('a)001:9588: seng ge'i gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9589: mi 'jigs bzhi yi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9590: sems nyid rtogs pa'i rig pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9591: mtshan ma thams cad zil gyis gnon //
NK023('a)001:9592: glang chen gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9593: sangs rgyas stobs bcu'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9594: thams cad sems su rtogs gyur na //
NK023('a)001:9595: gar ma bgrod par kun tu phyin //
NK023('a)001:9596: rta yi gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9597: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9598: nyon mongs sems su gang shes pa //
NK023('a)001:9599: phyogs bzhin mi gos dbang du byed //
NK023('a)001:9600: rma bya'i gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9601: rgyal ba'i dbang bcu thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9602: shes bya bdag tu gang rtogs pa //
NK023('a)001:9603: ltos pa med par thams cad gsal //
NK023('a)001:9604: shang shang khyung gis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9605: shes bya thogs med dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9606: seng ge la sogs pa'i sems can chen po lnga'i gdan khris dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:9607: che ge mo'i yon tan lnga lhun gyis grub ste
NK023('a)001:9608: mthar phyin pa'i sa non pa'i dbang yon bdag dang
NK023('a)001:9609: sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9611: rin chen pad+ma seng ge'i khri //
NK023('a)001:9612: bla mar gyur pa'i gdan mchog ste //
NK023('a)001:9613: khyad par chen po gyur pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:9614: khri chen dag la bzhag par bya //
NK023('a)001:9615: sems nyid dgos 'dod lhun grub pa //
NK023('a)001:9616: rtog pas ma btsal rang la snang //
NK023('a)001:9617: rin chen khri yis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9618: yon tan brtan pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9625: thabs phar phyin bcu shes rab stong nyid /
NK023('a)001:9626: dbyer med ye shes bco brgyad kyi 'bras bu thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9627: rgyal po rgyal thebs la rin chen khri nyi zla ste lnga brtsegs /
NK023('a)001:9628: 'khor la pad+ma la sogs phal pa la rin chen gdan no //
NK023('a)001:9630: dar gyi cod pan phreng la sogs //
NK023('a)001:9631: dbang mchog brjid pa'i rgyan gyis blug /
NK023('a)001:9632: dbu rgyan do shal se mo do //
NK023('a)001:9633: dpung rgyan rkang gdub lag gdub rnams //
NK023('a)001:9634: dbang mchog rgyal po de la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9635: so so'i yon tan 'grub par smon //
NK023('a)001:9636: chos nyid cir yang snang ba'i longs spyod rgyan //
NK023('a)001:9637: rigs lnga'i rin chen dbu rgyan 'di bcings pas //
NK023('a)001:9638: ye shes lnga dang rigs lnga dbyer med pa'i //
NK023('a)001:9639: rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9640: sarba ta tha ga ta g+hu h+ya b+hud+d+ha badz+ra rat+na
NK023('a)001:9641: pad+ma karma sa t+wa sa b+ha ba at+ma ko&a ham
NK023('a)001:9642: / zhe sdang chen po nga yi sems /
NK023('a)001:9644: byang chub phyogs rnams rtogs pa'i rgyan //
NK023('a)001:9645: mtshan dang dpe byed la sogs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:9646: 'bras bu'i chos la dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9647: phyi dbang brgyad pa zhi ba'i brgyan cha gdags pa'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:9648: dbang thob mdzes pa brjid pa'i dbang po ste //
NK023('a)001:9649: dbang phyug yin pas de la kun phyag 'tshal //
NK023('a)001:9650: rdo rje dbang phyug dbang phyug ces par ni //
NK023('a)001:9651: kun gyis sgra cher 'bod cing bsgrags par bya //
NK023('a)001:9653: skal ldan khyod la rdo rje ming gis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:9654: bas sangs rgyas dang rig 'dzin dang byang chub sems
NK023('a)001:9655: dpa' zhing khams thad du dbang phyug mchog tu grags
NK023('a)001:9656: pa'i ming gi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9657: ston pa'i thugs rjes nges pa'i ming btags pa //
NK023('a)001:9658: thugs kyi ngang nas nges pa'i sras su mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9659: phyi dbang dgu pa rdo rje'i ming gi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:9660: phyi dbang bcu pa 'khor lo'i dbang ni //
NK023('a)001:9661: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs 'khyud ldan pa gcig /
NK023('a)001:9662: rgyal po de yi lag tu bskur nas ni //
NK023('a)001:9663: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la sbyin byas pas //
NK023('a)001:9664: 'jig rten kun la 'khor los bsgyur ba yi //
NK023('a)001:9665: dbang mchog rgyal po de yang sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:9666: dbang mchog rgyal po 'di yang thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9667: yongs la dbang bsgyur dbang gi mchog /
NK023('a)001:9668: gang la'ang ma chags 'dod dgur bsgyur //
NK023('a)001:9669: gnyis su med pa'i pho brang du //
NK023('a)001:9670: spong len med par dbang bsgyur ro //
NK023('a)001:9672: brjod pa'i don du 'bru bkod nas //
NK023('a)001:9673: gzhan don 'di la phan pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:9674: rgyal ba'i 'khor lo bskor bar mdzod //
NK023('a)001:9675: brjod pa med pa'i don du 'bru bkod ces pa'ang snang /
NK023('a)001:9676: badz+ra tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK023('a)001:9678: skal ldan khyod la 'khor lo'i dbang bskur bas 'khor
NK023('a)001:9679: lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal thabs kyis 'jig rten dang 'jig
NK023('a)001:9680: rten las 'das pa'i chos kyi khams gsum mtha' yas
NK023('a)001:9681: kyi kha lo gyen du bsgyur ba'i dbang dam pa
NK023('a)001:9683: lnga bcu phyi dbang bcu 'khor mo ming phye ba bcu gcig go //
NK023('a)001:9685: de yan chad kyis phyi dbang bcu gcig 'khor lo dang ming sdom pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9686: da ni nang dbang bcu gcig bskur te /
NK023('a)001:9689: dbang rin chen phreng ba las /
NK023('a)001:9690: bu gus rdo rje drang byas la //
NK023('a)001:9691: gsang ba chen po'i rigs tshogs su //
NK023('a)001:9692: deng nas bdag gis bzung bar bya //
NK023('a)001:9693: phyir mi ldog par gyur thob phyir //
NK023('a)001:9694: bdag la gsang sgo dbye bar gsol //
NK023('a)001:9696: shin tu gsang ba'i rdzas dang ldan gyur nas //
NK023('a)001:9697: gsang sgo gang 'dod don rnams de ltar zhu //
NK023('a)001:9698: gsang ba chen po'i rtags su byin gyis brlabs //
NK023('a)001:9699: slob bu 'byung gnas rab gnas gsal ba la //
NK023('a)001:9700: gsang ba'i don la nyan cing slob pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:9701: dbang mchog skal ldan de la sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:9702: bdud rtsi'i chu 'dis rna ba'i gsang sgor dbye //
NK023('a)001:9703: glegs bam zab mo la sogs thams cad rnams //
NK023('a)001:9704: rigs kyi bu mchog de la sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:9705: sarba ta th+aa ga ta d+harma sid d+hi ho /
NK023('a)001:9706: tram gsang ba'i sgo ru 'di zhugs nas //
NK023('a)001:9707: po ti lag tu sbyin byas pas //
NK023('a)001:9708: dam pa'i mdzod chen theg pa gsum //
NK023('a)001:9709: ma lus nyan pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9710: sarba ta tha ga ta rgarba sarba d+harma si ti h'u /
NK023('a)001:9711: nang dbang bcu gcig las nyan pa'i dbang ste dang po'o //
NK023('a)001:9712: gsang ba gsang chen gsang ba rnams //
NK023('a)001:9713: ston pas nges par gsung ba'i don //
NK023('a)001:9714: nyan cing yid la 'dzin pa yis //
NK023('a)001:9715: ma 'dres ston pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9717: bu khyod la nyan pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:9718: gsang ba'i bka' mtha' dag nyan pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9720: gnyis pa phrin las kyi dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:9722: zhi rgyas dbang dang drag po yis //
NK023('a)001:9723: rigs su gyur pa ma lus pa //
NK023('a)001:9724: khyod kyi dgos pa thams cad byed par 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:9725: dbang rin chen phreng ba las /
NK023('a)001:9726: de ni 'gro ba'i don byed nus pas na //
NK023('a)001:9727: bu mchog de ni don 'grub gsal byas la //
NK023('a)001:9728: las rnams rgya mtsho thams cad nus pa'i rtags //
NK023('a)001:9729: rdo rje rgya gram la sogs rnam bzhi'i rdzas //
NK023('a)001:9730: bu mchog 'di la thabs kyis sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:9731: zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod dang //
NK023('a)001:9732: phrin las drag dal gang byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:9733: las rnams kun gyis byed pa por //
NK023('a)001:9734: las rnams kun gyi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9736: phrin las kyis dbang bskur bas rnam bzhi byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9738: gsum pa la 'chad pa'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:9739: hri gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong mu khyud ldan //
NK023('a)001:9740: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la sbyin byas pas //
NK023('a)001:9741: 'jig rten kun la kha lo bsgyur ba'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:9742: dbang bsgyur 'khor lo'i dbang chen thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9743: lo ka tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK023('a)001:9745: slob bu smra byed h+r+ai las mtha' yas byed //
NK023('a)001:9746: gzhan gyi re 'dod bskong ba'i bu mchog des //
NK023('a)001:9747: rgyal po rgyal rigs brgyud du byung ba bzhin //
NK023('a)001:9748: rgyal tshab chos kyi brgyud du byung bas na //
NK023('a)001:9749: tan tra la sogs dam pa'i mdzod gsum sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9750: rjes mthun smon lam bden pas drangs te gdab //
NK023('a)001:9752: bka' gsang theg pa mtha' dag 'chad pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9754: bzhi pa rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:9756: bzhi pa rdo rje rgyal dbang spyi bo la /
NK023('a)001:9757: de bzhin rigs kyi dbang bskur dang sgrag tshig sbyin /
NK023('a)001:9759: h'u rdo rje'i rigs dang de bzhin rigs gnyis thugs dang sku ste 'dam kha'am gnyis ka'o //
NK023('a)001:9760: h'u bu des slob ma'i tshogs kun skyongs nus pa'i phyir /
NK023('a)001:9761: h'u las rdo rje sems dpa' gsal byas las /
NK023('a)001:9762: bstan pa sgrogs pa'i sa la gnas bya'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:9763: rdo rje rgyal po dpal gyi dbang mchog 'dis //
NK023('a)001:9764: theg pa dgu yi rtags dang bcas de sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9766: glegs bam 'on te rdo rje rtse dgu pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9768: slob bu khyod rdo rje slob dpon byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9769: lnga pa gdan khri'i dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:9770: lnga pa zil gnon gdan dbang rkang pa la //
NK023('a)001:9771: dbang phyug la sogs dregs pa'i tshogs //
NK023('a)001:9772: smon lam chen po brtan byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:9773: dregs pa bsnol ba'i dbang gdan 'dis //
NK023('a)001:9774: brten pas zil gnon dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9776: lha chen po'i gdan gyis dbang bskur bas khams gsum
NK023('a)001:9777: gyi dregs pa can zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang thob
NK023('a)001:9778: par gyur cig / mtha' gnyis mun pa sel ba yi //
NK023('a)001:9779: nyi zla gnyis kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9780: thabs dang shes rab 'brel pa yi //
NK023('a)001:9781: bdag gzhan don kun rdzogs par shog /
NK023('a)001:9783: nyi zlas thabs dang shes rab 'brel pas don byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9784: mnyam rdzogs brtul zhugs chen po yis //
NK023('a)001:9785: thams cad la yang thogs med phyir //
NK023('a)001:9786: dom gyi gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9787: brtul zhugs gsum gyis dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9788: rang snang yon tan mang pos brjid //
NK023('a)001:9789: rtsol ba zil gyis gnon byed phyir //
NK023('a)001:9790: khyu mchog gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9791: thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9792: phung po khams sogs don rigs pas //
NK023('a)001:9793: yon tan mang po brjid snang phyir //
NK023('a)001:9794: ma he gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9795: kun la mdzes pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9796: thabs kyi rol pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK023('a)001:9797: gdul bya kun la mthun 'jug phyir //
NK023('a)001:9798: gzig gi gzugs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9799: thabs la mkhas pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9800: rgyu 'bras gnyis med sems nyid la //
NK023('a)001:9801: sa dang sa yi rim bral phyir /
NK023('a)001:9802: stag gi gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:9803: khyad par 'phags pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9804: sa rnams non po'i rta mchog gdan khri'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:9805: lha chen la sogs zhing chen nyi zlar bcas //
NK023('a)001:9806: khyu mchog seng ge ma he gzig dang stag /
NK023('a)001:9807: gtum pa don gyis spar te sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:9808: khams gsum zil gnon thabs dang shes rab dang //
NK023('a)001:9809: bsdo ba zil gnon gzhan bsgrag yon tan brjid //
NK023('a)001:9810: mthun 'jug las mkhan mngon sum pa yi dbang //
NK023('a)001:9811: brtul zhugs chen po thogs med 'jug pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:9812: smon lam yid kyis zin par sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:9814: thun mong ma yin pa'i rin po che sna bdun gyi dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:9816: skye ba rnam bzhi rgyun gcod pa'i //
NK023('a)001:9817: de ring khyod la sbyin byas pas //
NK023('a)001:9818: skye bzhi sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9820: yi dam lha yab 'khor lo dbang bskur bas mngal
NK023('a)001:9821: rdzus drod sgong skyes bzhi'i skye ba rnam pa bzhi
NK023('a)001:9822: las 'gro bsgrol ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:9823: cig / sngar ltar bardzusa skyes chen po la ni nam mkha'i skye gnas gces so //
NK023('a)001:9824: dbyings phyug la sogs bde ba'i yum //
NK023('a)001:9825: thugs rje'i gzungs kyi rig ma ste //
NK023('a)001:9826: de ring khyod la sbyin byas pas //
NK023('a)001:9827: thabs la spyod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9829: yi dam lha'i yum gyis dbang bskur bas mtshan nyid
NK023('a)001:9830: du 'byung ba chen po bzhi la rang dbang thabs
NK023('a)001:9831: kyis spyod pa la 'jug pa'i dbang thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:9832: cig / sngar ltar sa chu me rlung nam mkha'i dbyings phyug ma lnga'o //
NK023('a)001:9833: chos rnams kun la thogs med pa'i //
NK023('a)001:9834: blo gros kun ldan rdo rje sems //
NK023('a)001:9835: de ring khyod la sbyin byas pas //
NK023('a)001:9836: shes bya mkhyen pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9838: rigs kyi bu khyod la rdo rje'i dbang bskur bas sems dpa'i rdo rje blo gros phun sum tshogs /
NK023('a)001:9840: dga' ba mnyam snyoms pa'i tshad med bzhi'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9841: khams gsum bsdo ba kun 'dul ba //
NK023('a)001:9842: stobs chen khro bo chen po ste //
NK023('a)001:9843: de ring khyod la sbyin byas pas //
NK023('a)001:9844: dpung bzhi 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9846: stobs po ches dbang bskur bas stobs po che tshad med bzhi'i 'gal zla rnam par 'tshe ba dang /
NK023('a)001:9847: gnod sems dang phrag dog dang nga rgyal rnams glang po dang /
NK023('a)001:9848: rta pa dang shing rta dang /
NK023('a)001:9849: rkang thang du dmag tu snang ba'i dpung bzhi 'dul ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9850: theg pa mtha' la gnas pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:9851: zil gnon theg chen glang chen gzugs //
NK023('a)001:9852: de ring khyod la sbyin byas pas //
NK023('a)001:9853: bsdo ba zil gnon dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:9855: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis glang pos dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:9856: bas stobs bcu'i dbang dang phas kyis bsdo ba zil
NK023('a)001:9857: gyis gnon pa'i dbang lus tshor ba sems dran pa
NK023('a)001:9858: nye bar bzhags nas bdag dang gzhan dang chos dang
NK023('a)001:9859: 'grogs pa'i don bzhi 'grub par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:9860: stobs bcu'i 'grel pa pin dar las //
NK023('a)001:9861: gnas dang gnas min yang dag mkhyen //
NK023('a)001:9862: dus gsum las dang rnam smin mkhyen //
NK023('a)001:9863: khams rnams sna tshogs mkhyen pa'i stobs //
NK023('a)001:9864: dbang po mchog dang mchog min mkhyen //
NK023('a)001:9865: pha rol mos pa mkhyen pa'i stobs //
NK023('a)001:9866: zag pa zad med sems grol mkhyen //
NK023('a)001:9867: bsam gtan thar dang nyon mongs mkhyen //
NK023('a)001:9869: 'di bcu stobs bcu gyur pas na //
NK023('a)001:9870: 'bras bu mngon shes drug yin no //
NK023('a)001:9872: gzhan du lha yi rna ba dang //
NK023('a)001:9873: spyan gyi mngon par shes pa dang //
NK023('a)001:9874: sngon gnas rjes su dran pa dang //
NK023('a)001:9875: pha rol rnams kyi sems shes dang //
NK023('a)001:9877: rdzu 'phrul shes pa'ang zag zad shes //
NK023('a)001:9879: thams cad bdag nyid khyab pa po //
NK023('a)001:9880: dbang phyug kun 'gro rta yi gzugs //
NK023('a)001:9881: de ring khyod la sbyin byas pas //
NK023('a)001:9882: thogs med rdzu 'phrul thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:9884: khro bo rta mgrin gyis dbang bskur bas gang la'ang
NK023('a)001:9885: thogs pa med pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi
NK023('a)001:9886: yi rkang pa dge ba bskyed /
NK023('a)001:9888: sdig pa mi byed sdig pa bshags pa la mdun
NK023('a)001:9889: brtson rtog dpyod kyis dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:9890: cig / kun rdzob byang chub sems nyid rigs par rtogs //
NK023('a)001:9891: bsam pas 'byung ba'i rin po che //
NK023('a)001:9892: de ring khyod la sbyin byas pa //
NK023('a)001:9893: gdul bya ma lus re skongs shog /
NK023('a)001:9895: byang chub sems dpa' rdo rje rin chen gyis dbang
NK023('a)001:9896: bskur bas gdul bya'i re ba yid bzhin du skong
NK023('a)001:9897: ba sbyin pa rnam pa bzhi'i zang zing chos mi
NK023('a)001:9898: 'jigs pa byams pa'i sbyin pa bzhi'i dbang dam pa
NK023('a)001:9900: rgyal po yin pa'i rtags ni rnams pa bdun //
NK023('a)001:9901: skye la dbang bsgyur rgyal po mnyes pa'i gzungs //
NK023('a)001:9902: pha rol dpung 'joms srid thub 'joms pa dang //
NK023('a)001:9903: bdag gzhan don 'grub rdzu 'phrul rkang par ldan //
NK023('a)001:9904: dgos 'dod yid bzhin bskong ba'i rin po che //
NK023('a)001:9905: rgyal po de la thabs kyis sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:9906: yi dam lha yab yum dang byang chub spos glang po //
NK023('a)001:9907: stobs chen khro bo sems dpa' rdo rje rin //
NK023('a)001:9908: rta mgrin khro bo rin chen rnam bdun gyis //
NK023('a)001:9909: rab gnas byas nas de la gtad par bya //
NK023('a)001:9912: bdun pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor gyis dbang ni //
NK023('a)001:9913: de ni rgyal ba'i sras po yin pas na //
NK023('a)001:9914: phyag rgya chen po'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:9915: ras sam 'bur ram blugs su blug pa yi //
NK023('a)001:9916: phyag rgya gzugs brnyan de yi spyi bor bzhag /
NK023('a)001:9917: lung a nu'i bsgrub dbang la rigs bdag kun bzang 'di gtso bor mdzad /
NK023('a)001:9920: kun tu bzang po ni dang po yum la 'khyud //
NK023('a)001:9921: bar pa rdo rje dril bu /
NK023('a)001:9922: tha ma ni mnyam pa'i phyag rgya can no //
NK023('a)001:9923: rigs lnga ni rang rtags kyis phyag rgya lnga /
NK023('a)001:9924: dril bu dang de dag go bsnol bar bstan ces te /
NK023('a)001:9925: thams cad byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK023('a)001:9926: zhes kun bzang rigs bdag la /
NK023('a)001:9927: dang po byang chub phyag rgyas 'khyud par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:9928: sku mdog zhal dbus thugs mthing /
NK023('a)001:9931: rin chen seng khri pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan la yab rdo rje skyil krung la /
NK023('a)001:9932: yum brtul zhugs kyis 'khyud gsang ba sbyar ba'o //
NK023('a)001:9933: sems can lnga gdan gyis don tshangs pa'o //
NK023('a)001:9934: h'u byang chub sems mchog ye shes rdo rje'i thugs //
NK023('a)001:9935: srid gsum dbang bsdud thams cad mkhyen pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:9936: bsnyongs pa mi mnga' 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:9937: kun bzang rdo rje yid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:9940: rigs pa tshul snang sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:9941: sangs rgyas thams cad bskyed mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:9942: kun tu bzang po'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9945: a a a badz+ra ba tra sa man ta +aa /
NK023('a)001:9947: gdod nas ma byung ma skyes chos kyi rgyal //
NK023('a)001:9948: ma skyes mi 'gags dngos por 'dzin dang bral //
NK023('a)001:9949: 'byung ba thams cad bskyed pa yum gyi tshul //
NK023('a)001:9950: bzang mo bya ba mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:9951: dbyings kyi yum la sangs rgyas pa //
NK023('a)001:9952: snang srid thams cad chos kyi dbyings //
NK023('a)001:9953: thabs dang shes rab 'brel pa'i yum //
NK023('a)001:9954: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9955: rigs bdag ma h+aa gsang bdag rdo rje rtse lnga dang a nu sgrub dbang rdo rje rtse dagu'o //
NK023('a)001:9956: rgyud ma h+aa dkyil 'khor gtso bo rdor sems //
NK023('a)001:9957: ma skyes rdo rje thabs la rol //
NK023('a)001:9958: don dam dbyer med rol mdzad pas //
NK023('a)001:9959: thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:9960: rdo rje sems dpa' bdag la dgongs //
NK023('a)001:9961: rnam shes phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:9962: rdo rje rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:9963: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs yin pas //
NK023('a)001:9964: rdo rje sems dpa'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9965: 'byung ba nam mkha' sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:9966: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbyings phyug ma'i //
NK023('a)001:9967: rdo rje rigs kyi yum yin pas //
NK023('a)001:9968: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9972: a ti bla mas gang lung bstan brgyud mthun no //
NK023('a)001:9975: phyi dbang so sor a nu ltar du /
NK023('a)001:9976: sems lung chen po'i rgyud lung las //
NK023('a)001:9978: gnag dang dmar dang dkar ba'i zhal //
NK023('a)001:9979: mi 'khrugs dbang bskur rnam par brgyan //
NK023('a)001:9980: rdo rje chen po rtse dgu pa //
NK023('a)001:9982: chu skyes dag ni 'dzin pa'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:9983: dril bu nor bu ral gri bsnams //
NK023('a)001:9984: g.yon pa'i phyag na bsnams par bsam //
NK023('a)001:9986: zla nyi pad rin khri seng ge /
NK023('a)001:9988: gzugs kyi phung po gnas dag pa //
NK023('a)001:9989: de bzhin rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:9990: sangs rgyas kun gyis sku 'dzin pas //
NK023('a)001:9991: rnam par snang mdzad dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:9992: 'byung ba sa gzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:9993: rdo rje dbyings kyi dbyings phyug mar //
NK023('a)001:9994: bde gshegs rigs kyi yum yin pas //
NK023('a)001:9995: sangs rgyas spyan gyis dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10000: phyogs ni rnam par snang bar mdzad //
NK023('a)001:10001: dkar dang dmar dang nag chen po //
NK023('a)001:10002: mi 'khrug pa yis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:10003: 'khor lo rdo rje pad mo dkar //
NK023('a)001:10004: dril bu nor bu ral gri bsnams //
NK023('a)001:10005: g.yon pa'i phyag tu rnam par bsam //
NK023('a)001:10007: zla nyi pad rin chen glang chen //
NK023('a)001:10008: g.yas nag g.yon dmar po chan las bshad /
NK023('a)001:10009: tshor ba'i phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10010: rin chen rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:10011: sangs rgyas kun gyis yon tan yin //
NK023('a)001:10012: rin chen 'byung ldan dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10013: 'byung ba chu rnams sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10014: rin chen rigs kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:10015: rin chen rigs kyis yum yin pas //
NK023('a)001:10016: ma ma ki'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10021: rat+na d+h+rig sa bon las bskyed nas ni /
NK023('a)001:10022: ser dang dmar dang dkar ba'i zhal //
NK023('a)001:10025: g.yas kyi phyag tu bsgom par bya //
NK023('a)001:10026: dril bu ral gri pad+ma ser //
NK023('a)001:10027: g.yon gyis phyag tu bsgom par bya //
NK023('a)001:10028: rdo rje sems dpa'i g.yas phyogs kyis //
NK023('a)001:10029: rin chen dbus su rnam par bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:10031: rta mchog pad zla nyi pad rin chen khri //
NK023('a)001:10032: g.yon dmar g.yas dkar du chan las bshad /
NK023('a)001:10033: yum brtul zhugs kyi dkyil krung bol bsnol ba'i zhabs khri ri mig ma'o //
NK023('a)001:10034: phyag rig mas yab kyi rdo rje rnams a nu rtse dgu dang ma h+aa rdo rje lngar mdzad /
NK023('a)001:10035: 'du shes phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10036: pad+ma rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:10037: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung yin pas //
NK023('a)001:10038: snang ba mtha' yas dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10039: 'byung ba me las sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10040: pad+ma dbyings kyis dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:10041: pad+ma rigs kyi yum yin pas //
NK023('a)001:10042: gos dkar mo'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10046: rdo rje snang ba mtha' yas bskyed //
NK023('a)001:10047: dmar dang gnag dang dkar ba'i zhal //
NK023('a)001:10048: mi 'khrug pas ni cod pan brgyan //
NK023('a)001:10049: phyag drug pas ni bsgom par bya //
NK023('a)001:10051: dril bu dkur brten phar phyin te //
NK023('a)001:10052: g.yas pas pad+ma skyong mdzad cing //
NK023('a)001:10054: g.yas gnyis 'khor lo rdo rje dang //
NK023('a)001:10055: g.yon gnyis rin chen ral gri bsnams //
NK023('a)001:10057: g.yon nag g.yas dkar mchan du bshad //
NK023('a)001:10058: gnag zer ba thams cad khro tshul zhi ma khror mtshon pa ste /
NK023('a)001:10059: ngo bo mthing nag tu mche ba phyed rtsig ye
NK023('a)001:10060: shes gcig tu dbu rgyan mi 'khrug pa stong pa
NK023('a)001:10061: nyid tshogs bsgrubs zer te a nu'i mtshon to //
NK023('a)001:10062: zla nyi pad+ma rin chen khri rma bya la yab rdo rje'i skyil krung pa'o //
NK023('a)001:10063: 'du byed phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10064: pad+ma las kyi rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:10065: sangs rgyas phrin las mchog yin pas //
NK023('a)001:10066: don yod grub pa'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10067: 'byung ba rlung las sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10068: las kyi rigs kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:10069: sna tshogs 'dul ba'i yum yin pas //
NK023('a)001:10070: dam tshig sgrol mas dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10072: tam badz+ra ra ti a b+hi sems lung du rdo rje gdon mi za bar byed /
NK023('a)001:10073: ljang khu gnag dang dkar ba'i zhal //
NK023('a)001:10074: ral gri rdo rje rgya gram dang //
NK023('a)001:10075: 'khor lo g.yas pa'i phyag tu bsam //
NK023('a)001:10076: dril bu pad+ma stong bcas dang //
NK023('a)001:10077: nor bu g.yon pa'i phyag tu bsam //
NK023('a)001:10078: gru gsum dkyil 'khor dbus su ni //
NK023('a)001:10079: rdo rje sems dpa'i g.yon phyogs su //
NK023('a)001:10080: rdzun tshig smra ba'i lam gnas pa'i //
NK023('a)001:10081: sems can thams cad kun tu sbyongs //
NK023('a)001:10083: shang shang khri 'degs zla nyi pad rin chen //
NK023('a)001:10085: sku dmar ljang dbang gtso che ba la bstan //
NK023('a)001:10086: mig gis rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10087: byang chub chen po mthong ba'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:10088: bdag gi mig las bskyed byas pas //
NK023('a)001:10089: sa'i snying po'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10090: gzugs su snang ba sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10091: byang chub lha mo dkar mo'i sku //
NK023('a)001:10092: phyi yi gzugs las bskyod byas pas //
NK023('a)001:10093: lha mo la s+ye'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10095: h'u la s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK023('a)001:10096: a b+hi sa snying dkar po phyag g.yas rin chen myu gu 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:10097: sems skyil sgeg mo g.yon pa me tog 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:10098: rin chen zhun ma shel la sogs gang las skyes pa de bzo ma byas pas myu gu'o //
NK023('a)001:10099: sems dpa' sems ma thams cad phyed skyil gdan nyi zla pad+ma sum brtseg /
NK023('a)001:10100: yab kyi g.yon pa dang yum gyi g.yas pa dril bu'am 'khyud tshul lo //
NK023('a)001:10101: rna ba'i rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10102: byang chub chen po thos pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:10103: bdag gi rna ba las bskyed byas pas /
NK023('a)001:10104: nam mkha'i snying po'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10105: sgra yi yul rnams sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10106: byang chub lha mo bee d+aur+ya //
NK023('a)001:10107: yum gyi sgra las bskyed byas pas //
NK023('a)001:10108: lha mo ma le'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10110: tram ma l+ye sa ma ya stram /
NK023('a)001:10111: a b+hi a zhes byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i
NK023('a)001:10112: snying po lce la bkod pa'i dus na phrin las
NK023('a)001:10113: su bshad pas / phyag rdor dzim zhes pa rin chen rigs sngags te gnyis kyi 'dam kha'o //
NK023('a)001:10114: de dus sna dbug nam mkha' snying po sngo //
NK023('a)001:10115: rna ba phyag rdor ljang khu rdo rje rgyud du bshad //
NK023('a)001:10116: 'dir nam snying ser phyag g.yas ral gri 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:10117: sems dkyil phreng ba lag g.yon rin chen phreng //
NK023('a)001:10118: sna yi rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10119: byang chub chen po snom pa'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:10120: bdag gis sna las bskyed byas pas //
NK023('a)001:10121: spyan ras gzigs kyis dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10122: tshor zhing yul rnams sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10123: byang chub lha mo re ka tis //
NK023('a)001:10124: tshor mchog yul las sangs rgyas bskyed byas pas //
NK023('a)001:10125: lha mo girti'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10126: hri ha ho pad+ma b+ha d+ha ma /
NK023('a)001:10128: a b+hi spyan ras gzigs dmar phyag g.yas pad+ma dkar //
NK023('a)001:10129: sems dkyil glu dbyangs len ma g.yon pi wam //
NK023('a)001:10130: lce yi rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10131: byang chub chen po myong ba'i dpal //
NK023('a)001:10132: bdag gi lce las bskyed byas pas //
NK023('a)001:10133: phyag na rdo rje yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10134: bro zhing yul rnams sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10135: byang chub lha mo in+d+ra ni //
NK023('a)001:10136: bro mchog yul las bskyed byas pas //
NK023('a)001:10137: lha mo nirti'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10138: dz+him ku tu pa na hrih a nirti ra ho ham /
NK023('a)001:10139: a b+hi shiny+tsa h'uh phyag na rdo rje mthing kha g.yas rdo rje //
NK023('a)001:10140: sems dkyil gar bsgyur phu dung phyag rdor dril //
NK023('a)001:10141: mthong ba'i dbang po sangs rgyas dpal //
NK023('a)001:10142: byang chub chen po mthong bar byed //
NK023('a)001:10143: de nyid las ni bskyed byas pas //
NK023('a)001:10144: byams pa m+aee tri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10145: dbyar dgun ston dpyid sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10146: dus bzhi'i yul rnams sems ma'i sku //
NK023('a)001:10147: de nyid las ni bskyed byas pas /
NK023('a)001:10148: badz+ra d+hu pe'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10149: m+aee d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10150: badz+ra d+hu pe pra be sha ya /
NK023('a)001:10151: a b+hi byams pa dkar ser phyag g.yas klu shing 'gun d+he 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:10152: sems dkyil d+hu pe g.yon pa bdug spos 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:10154: thos pa'i dbang po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10155: byang chub chen po thos par byed //
NK023('a)001:10156: thos pa'i dbang po des bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10157: sgrib pa rnam sel dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10158: de bzhin nyid las sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10159: lha mo 'od ldan mdzes ma'i sku //
NK023('a)001:10160: de nyid las ni bskyed byas pas //
NK023('a)001:10161: badz+ra pup+pe dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10162: th+l+him ni sa ram pa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10163: h+aum pup+pe a be sha ya /
NK023('a)001:10164: a b+hi sgrib sel dmar ser phyag g.yas po ti 'khor lo 'dzin /
NK023('a)001:10166: po ti glegs shing la 'khor lo rtsibs bcu gnyis yod par bshad /
NK023('a)001:10167: tshor ba'i dbang po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10168: byang chub chen po sgom byed pa //
NK023('a)001:10169: dbang po de las bskyed byas pas //
NK023('a)001:10170: kun tu bzang po'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10171: yul dus bzhi yang sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10172: lha mo mun sel 'od kyis mchog /
NK023('a)001:10173: yul de nyid las bskyed byas pas //
NK023('a)001:10174: badz+ra +aa lo ka'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10175: h+aum s+w+aa ra tsa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10176: bam de pam su ki ni /
NK023('a)001:10177: a b+hi kun bzang dmar ljang rin chen snye ma 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:10178: sems ma dmar ser a lo ke sgron me bsnams /
NK023('a)001:10179: nas 'bras gro sogs 'bru rin po che yi snye ma'o //
NK023('a)001:10180: myong ba'i dbang po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10181: byang chub chen po myong byed pa //
NK023('a)001:10182: dbang po de las bskyed byed pa //
NK023('a)001:10183: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10184: dus bzhi'i dus nyid sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10185: lha mo 'jam des bde ldan ma //
NK023('a)001:10186: dus de yul las bskur byed pas //
NK023('a)001:10187: badz+ra g+han d+he'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10188: mum sh+r+ai a ram ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10190: a b+hi 'jam dpal dkar ljang ut+pala 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:10191: sems dkyil g+han+d+he tri'i dung chos 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:10192: phyi phyin phyi log bzhi sangs rgyas pas /
NK023('a)001:10193: 'joms byed khro bo reg shes te //
NK023('a)001:10194: reg shes nyid las sangs rgyas skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10195: gshin rje gshed po'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10196: de yi yul bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10197: rtag par ma yin khro bo ste //
NK023('a)001:10198: de nyid las ni skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10199: ro langs ma'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10200: h+aum ya man+ta krit+ta h+aum phatah badz+ra d+ha ra ma
NK023('a)001:10201: h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phatah
NK023('a)001:10202: a b+hi ro langs lcags kyu mi pham zhag /
NK023('a)001:10203: ral gcig lcags sgrog khro gnyer dril //
NK023('a)001:10204: slob dpon b+hi ma lhas bdud rtsir bshad /
NK023('a)001:10205: rdo rje brag steng pad nyi gdan //
NK023('a)001:10206: gshin rje gshed po smug nag n+ri mgo gdengs //
NK023('a)001:10207: stobs chen ser nag rdo rje rtse lnga gdengs //
NK023('a)001:10208: rta mgrin dmar nag thod pa sbrul dkris bsnams //
NK023('a)001:10209: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang nag rgya gram gnon //
NK023('a)001:10210: phyin ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10211: 'joms byed khro bo reg byed de //
NK023('a)001:10212: reg byed nyid las skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10213: dpal ldan gzhan gyis mi thub dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10214: de yi yul bzhi'i sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10215: chad par ma yin khro bo ste //
NK023('a)001:10216: de nyid las ni skur byed pas //
NK023('a)001:10217: mi pham ma'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10218: h+aum pra nyan ta krid phatah h'u rat+na d+ha ra
NK023('a)001:10219: ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum
NK023('a)001:10220: phatah a b+hi phyin ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pas
NK023('a)001:10221: // 'joms byed khro bo reg bya byung //
NK023('a)001:10222: reg bya nyid las skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10223: khro chen rta mgrin dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10224: de yi yul bzhi'i sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10225: bdag tu ma yin khro mo nyid //
NK023('a)001:10226: yul de nyid las skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10227: ral gcig ma yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10228: h+aum pad+ma ta krid phatah h'u pad+ma d+ha ra ma
NK023('a)001:10229: h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phatah
NK023('a)001:10230: a b+hi phyin ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10232: reg pa nyid las skur bskyed pa //
NK023('a)001:10233: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10234: h+aum big nan ta krid phatah karma d+ha ra ma
NK023('a)001:10235: h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phatah
NK023('a)001:10236: a b+hi yid kyi rnam shes gnas dag pas //
NK023('a)001:10237: byed po kun tu bzang po byung //
NK023('a)001:10238: de nyid las ni skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10239: kun tu bzang po'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10240: drug pa kun tu bzang po 'di rdo rje'i rigs su mthing kha'i rigs su byas nas /
NK023('a)001:10241: dang po rdo rje dril bu byed pa rdo rje
NK023('a)001:10242: sems dpa' a lta bu la yab mnyam bzhag phyag
NK023('a)001:10244: g.yas rdo rje g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa dang yab mnyam bzhag 'pham pa'i steng rdo rje dang /
NK023('a)001:10245: yum thal mo mnyam par rdo rje dril bu 'dzin pa dang /
NK023('a)001:10250: ye shes rtse lnga chos khams dril //
NK023('a)001:10251: thugs kar brtan par nyid du gsungs //
NK023('a)001:10252: zhes te thebs chen gyis srin lag dbang mo'i rtsa ba mnan pa la rdo rje thal mo ste /
NK023('a)001:10254: yum la yab 'khyud nub tu dang //
NK023('a)001:10255: phyag drug 'dod pa'i lugs yod pa'o //
NK023('a)001:10256: 'dir phyag gnyis la yab rkyang shar //
NK023('a)001:10259: a b+hi chos kyi skye mched sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10260: bya ba kun tu bzang mor byung //
NK023('a)001:10261: de nyid las ni skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10262: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10263: a a a badz+ra b+ha tra sa man+ta +aa /
NK023('a)001:10264: a b+hi nga rgyal thams cad sangs rgyas pa /
NK023('a)001:10265: brgya byin lha yi dbang por byung //
NK023('a)001:10266: de nyid rgyu las skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10267: lha yi thub pa'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10269: a b+hi shiny+tsa dkar po pi wang sgreng glu len //
NK023('a)001:10270: phrag dog thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10271: lha ma yin lag thag bzang ris //
NK023('a)001:10272: de nyid las ni skur bskyod pas //
NK023('a)001:10273: lha min thub pa'i dbang mu ne h+aum drum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10275: mthing kha go cha mdung thung 'phen //
NK023('a)001:10276: 'dod chags thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10277: bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa byung //
NK023('a)001:10278: de nyid rgyu las skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10279: mi'i thub pa'i dbang mu ne srung s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10281: ser mdog gseg shang spar bu can //
NK023('a)001:10282: gti mug nyid las skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10283: sangs rgyas seng ge'i dam bstan byung //
NK023('a)001:10284: de nyid rgyu las skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10285: byol song thub pa'i dbang mu ne brem s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10286: a b+hi shiny+tsa dmar nag po ti chos 'chad tshul //
NK023('a)001:10287: ser sna thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10289: ser sna nyid las skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10290: yi dwags thub pa'i dbang mu ne k+sham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10291: a b+hi ser nag rin chen sgrom zas byin //
NK023('a)001:10292: zhe sdang ye nas sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10293: ston pa chos kyi rgyal po byung //
NK023('a)001:10294: zhe sdang rgyu las skur bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10295: dmyal ba thub pa'i dbang mchog mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10296: a b+hi dud kha me 'bar chu bum 'bebs //
NK023('a)001:10297: dang por sbyin pa 'di yin te //
NK023('a)001:10299: gnas bkod yongs su gyur pa las //
NK023('a)001:10300: ye shes rtags kyi phyag rgya sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10301: tshig bzhi po 'di tsaka pod rnying pa na gda' ba 'di phyi dbang gi rgyab yig yin /
NK023('a)001:10302: nang dbang la dang po nyan dbang yod pa'o //
NK023('a)001:10303: des na phyi dbang yo ga /
NK023('a)001:10306: bsgrub dbang a ti bzhi ka'i zhi ba 'dir byas /
NK023('a)001:10307: bzhi ka'i khro bo dang bsgrubs rigs 'dzin pa yang sbrel bdog /
NK023('a)001:10308: khyad par phyi dbang gtso rkyang dang /
NK023('a)001:10309: nang dbang gtso bo zung 'brel rigs lnga gang rung dang /
NK023('a)001:10310: gsang dbang gtso bo rig bdag zung 'brel la zhi ma khro'o //
NK023('a)001:10311: sgrub dbang gtso bo kun khyab bla mar kun tshangs
NK023('a)001:10312: dang gzhi la 'khor rgyas dus du mar nges pa
NK023('a)001:10313: yi khyad par gyis shan phye'o //
NK023('a)001:10314: zung 'brel thabs dang shes rab ni rtags bda' dbang
NK023('a)001:10315: yin la don bde ba chen po'i ste bde stong
NK023('a)001:10316: dang 'brel ba med pas zung 'brel ni lha gcig
NK023('a)001:10317: la'ang sbyar ro // phyi dbang gtso bo kun khyab bla mar kun tshang dang gzhi la /
NK023('a)001:10318: phyi dbang gtso rkyang ni sngon gyi tsa ka la
NK023('a)001:10319: rigs lnga yab 'khri can yum lnga khri med zur
NK023('a)001:10320: la / sems khro'ang yang yum rang sa nyi zla
NK023('a)001:10321: pad gdan rgyab yig la phyi dbang nang dbang 'dra
NK023('a)001:10322: la / bar snang lags / kun gyis 'da' bar dka' ba yis //
NK023('a)001:10323: tshig btsun yul las dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK023('a)001:10324: rgyal po'i bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:10325: sku lnga yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:10326: bden pa 'dre phyag rgya bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis
NK023('a)001:10327: dbang bskur bas sku lnga yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:10329: h+aum rnam shes phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10330: rdo rje rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:10331: 'byung ba nam mkha' sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10332: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:10333: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po 'dis //
NK023('a)001:10334: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:10337: mthing kha rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK023('a)001:10338: dril bu ral gri pad ma 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:10339: yum 'khyud dril bu seng khri la'o //
NK023('a)001:10340: sems dpa' rdo rje dbyings la blta //
NK023('a)001:10341: brtan pa rdo rje 'gyur ba med //
NK023('a)001:10342: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po 'dis //
NK023('a)001:10343: de ring khyod la 'gre badz+ra sa t+wa badz+ra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:10345: rdo rje rin chen chos don gsal //
NK023('a)001:10346: rdo rje brtan ma dbyings su sbyor //
NK023('a)001:10347: rtags de ring badz+ra ran+ta h+aum /
NK023('a)001:10349: chos kyi rdo rje chos don rigs //
NK023('a)001:10350: rdo rje bsdud ma mtha' gnyis srog /
NK023('a)001:10351: rtags de ring d+harma badz+ra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:10353: las kyi rdo rje dbyings su sbyor //
NK023('a)001:10354: rdo rje bskyod ma cir mi gnas //
NK023('a)001:10355: rtags de ring karma badz+ra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:10357: yang na tsan da dz+wa la h'u /
NK023('a)001:10360: gtso zung 'brel ba'i phyag rgya ste //
NK023('a)001:10361: sor rtser 'chang ba thugs kar brtan //
NK023('a)001:10362: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma gri //
NK023('a)001:10364: 'bar ma sdud ma bsdud mchu lho //
NK023('a)001:10365: rgyud bkrugs chu ni ma ni ste //
NK023('a)001:10366: lung gcus man ngag de ltar gab //
NK023('a)001:10367: me ni gos dkar gos rtsang nub //
NK023('a)001:10369: yab la mo yis rtags med gab //
NK023('a)001:10370: gzugs kyi phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10371: de bzhin rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:10372: 'byung ba sa gzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10373: de bzhin rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:10374: rtags kyi mu tra chen po 'dis //
NK023('a)001:10375: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:10378: dkar po 'khor lo rdo rje rin po che //
NK023('a)001:10379: dril bu gri pad glang po'i khri //
NK023('a)001:10380: sems dpa' rdo rje dbyings la blta' //
NK023('a)001:10381: rdo rje sgeg mor 'gyur ba med //
NK023('a)001:10384: rdo rje rgyal po mtha' bzhi 'joms //
NK023('a)001:10385: gdug pa dbyings kyis tshim par byed //
NK023('a)001:10386: rtags de ring badz+ra ra ts+aa /
NK023('a)001:10388: rdo rje chags pa mtha' gnyis 'joms //
NK023('a)001:10391: rdo rje legs par gsal bar bskul //
NK023('a)001:10392: sgrol ma gnyis med tshul gyis gsal //
NK023('a)001:10393: rtags de ring badz+ra sa d+hu /
NK023('a)001:10396: rdo rje lcags kyu mda' gzhu rgya //
NK023('a)001:10397: me long sog phor lcags kyu phreng //
NK023('a)001:10399: rgya ni se gol rtog rgya grams //
NK023('a)001:10400: gtso bo yab yum la sems dpa' yab yum bzhir bskor ba'o //
NK023('a)001:10401: tshor ba'i phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10402: rin chen rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:10403: 'byung ba chu rnams sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10404: rin chen rigs kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:10405: rtags de ring s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rig /
NK023('a)001:10407: rin chen 'khor lo rdo rje g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10408: dril bu gri pad rta mchog khri //
NK023('a)001:10409: rdo rje rin chen mnyam nyid gsal //
NK023('a)001:10410: phreng ba ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gsal //
NK023('a)001:10411: rtags de ring badz+ra rat+na tram /
NK023('a)001:10413: rdo rje nyi ma gsal mtha' gnon //
NK023('a)001:10414: me tog mtha' bral rang rig mdzes //
NK023('a)001:10415: rtags de ring badz+ra sur+ya tram /
NK023('a)001:10417: rgyal mtshan mi gnon nga rgyal ldan //
NK023('a)001:10418: zhag pas ma lus sems su sdud //
NK023('a)001:10419: rtags de ring badz+ra ke tu tram /
NK023('a)001:10421: bzhad pas rang rig dges bel ldan //
NK023('a)001:10422: rdo rje bde byed mtha' dang bral //
NK023('a)001:10423: rtags de ring badz+ra ha sa tram /
NK023('a)001:10426: rin chen myu gu nyi ma dang //
NK023('a)001:10427: rgyal mtshan sor phreng 'dzin pa dang //
NK023('a)001:10428: rin chen me tog zhabs bsil g.yab //
NK023('a)001:10429: ces te phyag mtshan la rtags nyi ma /
NK023('a)001:10430: rdo rje gzi brjid zhes brjid ltar //
NK023('a)001:10433: 'du shes phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10434: pad+ma rigs su lhun gyis grub //
