NK023('a)001:10435: 'byung ba me las sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10436: pad+ma dbyings kyis dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:10437: rtags de ring am a ro lika /
NK023('a)001:10440: dril bu ral gri rdo rje'o //
NK023('a)001:10442: chos ni rang rig cir ma chags //
NK023('a)001:10443: dbyangs ni de don gsal bar byed //
NK023('a)001:10444: rtags de ring badz+ra d+harma h+r+ai /
NK023('a)001:10446: rdo rje rnon po mtha' rnams gcod //
NK023('a)001:10447: sgron ma ma bskyed don gsal byed //
NK023('a)001:10448: rtags de ring badz+ra tig sna hri /
NK023('a)001:10451: thams cad der 'brel lcags sgrog ma /
NK023('a)001:10452: rtags de ring badz+ra tsakra hri /
NK023('a)001:10454: smra ba rig gsal brjod pa 'dra //
NK023('a)001:10455: gsal bkra kun la gsal bar byed //
NK023('a)001:10456: rtags de ring badz+ra bag sha hri /
NK023('a)001:10457: badz+ra ra ga ra ti hri /
NK023('a)001:10461: pi wam dmar mos lcags sgrog mdongs //
NK023('a)001:10462: zhes te mdongs ni rma bya'am mdongs /
NK023('a)001:10463: 'khor lo zhes phyag mtshan gyis ming dang yang na rgyu mtshan ces kyis sngags /
NK023('a)001:10466: 'du byed phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10467: las kyi rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK023('a)001:10468: 'byung ba rlung la sangs rgyas pas //
NK023('a)001:10469: las kyi dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:10470: rtags de ring ha pradz+nya d+h+rig /
NK023('a)001:10472: ral gri 'khor lo rin po che //
NK023('a)001:10473: dril bu pad+ma rdo rje g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10474: ljang khu shang shang khri las ni //
NK023('a)001:10476: gar ni gsal bar snang ba'o //
NK023('a)001:10477: rtags de ring badz+ra karma ha /
NK023('a)001:10479: rdo rje srung ba mthas ma reg byug pa de don blos rig pa'o //
NK023('a)001:10480: rtags de ring badz+ra rak+sha ha /
NK023('a)001:10482: gnod sbyin mtha' rnams za bar byed //
NK023('a)001:10483: dril bu de don gsal sgrogs pa'o //
NK023('a)001:10486: khu tshur gnyis med don rigs pa //
NK023('a)001:10487: 'bebs med de nyid snang bar byed //
NK023('a)001:10488: rtags de ring badz+ra san ti ha /
NK023('a)001:10491: 'bebs ma'i khu tshur kha sbub ste badz+ra ra ti ha zer /
NK023('a)001:10492: dril bu dang ni byug pa'i khyad //
NK023('a)001:10493: 'greng bu g+han d+he dril bu dang //
NK023('a)001:10494: rkyang pa g+han d+he byug pa'ang snams //
NK023('a)001:10495: ha btag yod dang med pa'ang snang //
NK023('a)001:10497: ral gri rdo rje phreng ba dang //
NK023('a)001:10498: mche chen khu tshur thogs pa'o //
NK023('a)001:10499: gar mdzad spos tril rma bya'i bum //
NK023('a)001:10501: da ni mdo dbang khro bo'i lha'o //
NK023('a)001:10502: dbus che mchog bdud rtsi la dgongs pa zhi ba'o //
NK023('a)001:10503: h+aum ston pa kun bzang gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10504: khro rgyal kun gyis rje btsun yab //
NK023('a)001:10505: sku dang phyag rgya yongs rdzogs pas //
NK023('a)001:10506: che mchog he ru ka'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10507: kun tu bzang mo'i chos nyid gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10508: khro mo kun gyi rje btsun yum //
NK023('a)001:10509: shes rab dbyings las skur bskyed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:10510: kro ti'i shwa ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10511: ka ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum phatah
NK023('a)001:10512: ka ta ma h+aa kro ti sh+aa ri h+aum phatah
NK023('a)001:10514: che mchog bdud rtsi la dgongs khro bo ni //
NK023('a)001:10515: ston pa kun tu bzang po gnas gyur pa //
NK023('a)001:10516: khro rgyal kun gyis rje btsun yab //
NK023('a)001:10517: sku dang phyag rgya mngon rdzogs pas //
NK023('a)001:10518: che mchog he ru ka yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10519: kun tu bzang mo'i gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:10520: khro mo kun gyis rje btsun yum //
NK023('a)001:10521: shes rab dbyings las sku bskyed pas //
NK023('a)001:10522: seng ha kro ti'i shwa ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10523: sing ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka seng ha
NK023('a)001:10524: ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h+aum phatah a b+hi
NK023('a)001:10525: shiny+tsa h+aum / ston pa kun tu bzang po yab yum gnas gyur pa'i /
NK023('a)001:10526: che mchog he ru ka yab yum gyis dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:10528: rgyud kun 'dus nas sman gyi dkyil 'khor 'di ka la lha kun tshangs pas /
NK023('a)001:10529: kun 'dus las 'di ka las tsa ka log na med de /
NK023('a)001:10530: khrag 'thung khro bzhi khro bcu khra thabs khyams rnams
NK023('a)001:10531: kyi lha dang bcas pa'i ngo 'di las sprod pa'o
NK023('a)001:10533: chos kun sku la yongs su rdzogs pa chos kyi sku //
NK023('a)001:10534: rdo rje che mchog phyag 'tshal he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:10535: theg chen dgu dang 'khor ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK023('a)001:10536: phyag rgya gcig tu bkod nas rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK023('a)001:10537: 'khor ba kun dang thar pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK023('a)001:10538: dpa' bo chen po'i gdan du brjid cing rol //
NK023('a)001:10539: 'gran gyi zla med che btsan gcig pu nyid //
NK023('a)001:10540: gsang mchog 'bar ba'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK023('a)001:10541: bden rigs gzhal yas ni yum kun tu bzang mo'o //
NK023('a)001:10542: dpal che mchog gi gtsug tor rgyal mtshan rtse mo
NK023('a)001:10543: la gser gyi tog stong ni rdzogs pa chen po
NK023('a)001:10544: dang sku dang sku'i brgyan la rdzogs pa dang /
NK023('a)001:10545: skyed pa'i rnal 'byor gyi gdan gyi 'og nor bu rin po che'i gdan gyi stengs na /
NK023('a)001:10546: rdo rje rtse lnga dang rtse gsum gyi brag gtams pa la /
NK023('a)001:10550: ri rab kyi khab me tog gi gcal dang /
NK023('a)001:10551: kas ma gar ma'i 'od 'khrigs pa'i nor bu rin po che'i 'bar ba'i brag gtams pa la /
NK023('a)001:10552: byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK023('a)001:10555: lha mi yang 'khor ba gzugs med pa'i khams dang /
NK023('a)001:10557: gzugs kyi khams zhing chen gyi sa dang /
NK023('a)001:10558: 'dod pa khams kyi chags pa thams cad khrag gi rgya mtsho mngon par rdzogs par mthong zhing /
NK023('a)001:10559: phyag rgya rnam par spro ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:10560: che mchog mdo la dgongs pa ltar //
NK023('a)001:10562: gnam zhal phyag gnyis sku la 'khril //
NK023('a)001:10564: zhi ba sngon mo'am khro mo smug mo'i yum /
NK023('a)001:10566: zur du tsa ka li mdzad /
NK023('a)001:10567: che mchog bdud rtsi la dgongs pa ltar /
NK023('a)001:10568: yab kyi rdo rje yum gyi zhal du gzhugs /
NK023('a)001:10569: yum gyi mkha' nas badz+ra he ru ka dbu phyed 'thon bdud rtsi babs pa'i sbyor ba gsungs so //
NK023('a)001:10570: bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:10572: dbu gsum dang por byung ba ni //
NK023('a)001:10573: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK023('a)001:10574: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i dbus //
NK023('a)001:10575: khams gsum mya ngan 'das pa'i zhal //
NK023('a)001:10576: dbu gsum bar du rngams pa ni //
NK023('a)001:10577: g.yas sngo g.yon ljang dbus 'thing zhal //
NK023('a)001:10578: thabs dang shes rab sems kyi dbu //
NK023('a)001:10579: srid gsum dbyings su sgrol ba'i zhal //
NK023('a)001:10580: dbu gsum thog mar rngams pa ni //
NK023('a)001:10581: g.yas mthing g.yon mthing dbus mthing zhal //
NK023('a)001:10582: lung dang man ngag sems kyi dbu //
NK023('a)001:10583: khams gsum re ba bskong ba'i zhal //
NK023('a)001:10584: bco brgyad phyag rgya rol pa ni //
NK023('a)001:10585: stong pa bco brgyad dbyings su thim //
NK023('a)001:10586: bco brgyad phyag na bsnams pa ni //
NK023('a)001:10587: rdo rje glo snying zhing chung g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10588: ban d+ha zhing chung ti ra g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10589: zhing zhags nyi ma khyung chen g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10590: zhing chen zla ba 'ug pa g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10591: me dang rgya mtsho ga'u g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10592: klu dang rin chen ri rab g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10593: yon tan bco brgyad dbyings su rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:10594: khro rgyal rgyan rnams sku la brjid //
NK023('a)001:10595: kro ti mthing nag 'khril ba'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:10596: ban d+ha rak+ta gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:10597: rgyu rgyal che mchog he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:10598: dbang mchog sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK023('a)001:10599: sarba ta tha sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK023('a)001:10600: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK023('a)001:10601: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro ti shwa ri sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK023('a)001:10602: bden rigs dbang mchog yab yum gyi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:10603: ston pa kun tu bzang mo gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10604: khro rgyal kun gyi rje btsun yum //
NK023('a)001:10605: sku dang phyag rgya mngon rdzogs pas //
NK023('a)001:10606: che mchog yum gyi dbang chen khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10607: kun tu bzang mo'i chos nyid gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:10608: khro mo kun gyis rje btsun yum //
NK023('a)001:10609: shes rab dbyings las skur bskyed ma //
NK023('a)001:10610: kro ti shwa ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10611: ka ta kro ti shwa ri h'u phatah a b+hi rdo rje sems dpa' gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:10614: mchod cing byin rnams gsal sgrubs pas //
NK023('a)001:10615: badz+ra he ru ka'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10616: nam mkha' kun bzang gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:10617: khro bo dbang phyug skur gsal bas //
NK023('a)001:10618: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med //
NK023('a)001:10619: yab yum mchod cing gsal sgrub pas //
NK023('a)001:10620: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10621: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro ti shwa ri sa ma ya h'u /
NK023('a)001:10622: a b+hi shiny+tsa he ru 'dus rgyud ltar du /
NK023('a)001:10623: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal /
NK023('a)001:10624: rdo rje kha tam rnge'u chung g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10625: dril bu b+han dmar rgyu zhags g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10626: yum sngo g.yas 'khyud thod phrag stobs /
NK023('a)001:10627: zhes pa 'di che mchog phyag drug pa'ang yin rgyab yig che mchog kun mthun /
NK023('a)001:10629: dang po rdor dril dang rdo rje dung khrag bar
NK023('a)001:10630: sti ra 'jig rten 'khor yug bcas tha ma dang
NK023('a)001:10631: po rtse dgu bar rtse lnga'o //
NK023('a)001:10632: rnam par snang mdzad gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10635: mchod cing bsgrub ste byin rlabs pas //
NK023('a)001:10636: b+hud+d+ha he ru'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10637: sangs rgyas spyan las gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10638: khro bo dbang phyug skur gsal bas //
NK023('a)001:10639: thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:10640: spyan drangs mchod cing bsgrubs pa yi //
NK023('a)001:10641: b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ra'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10642: b+hud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK023('a)001:10643: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK023('a)001:10644: a b+hi g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus smug nag /
NK023('a)001:10645: 'khor lo kha tam rnge'u chung g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10646: dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10647: dbus smug g.yas 'khyud thod khrag stobs //
NK023('a)001:10649: rdo rje dung khrag bar ti ra //
NK023('a)001:10650: dri shul mdung rtse gsum tha ma'o //
NK023('a)001:10654: spyan drangs mchod cing bsgrubs pa la //
NK023('a)001:10655: rat+na he ru ka'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10656: ma ma ki las gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:10657: 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur snang ba //
NK023('a)001:10658: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK023('a)001:10659: spyan drangs mchod nas bsnyen bsgrubs pas //
NK023('a)001:10660: rat+na kro ti shwa ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10661: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro ti shwa ri stom /
NK023('a)001:10662: ru lu a b+hi g.yas dkar g.yon sngo dbus ser nag /
NK023('a)001:10663: rin chen kha tam rnge'u chung g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10664: dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhag g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10665: yum ser g.yas 'khyud thod khrag g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10666: rgyud ltar dang po rin chen 'dril //
NK023('a)001:10667: rdo rje dung khrag bar sti ra //
NK023('a)001:10668: dgra sta so gnyis g.yon tha ma'o //
NK023('a)001:10669: snang ba mtha' yas gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10671: dmar nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK023('a)001:10672: sgoms shing mchod de bsgrubs pa las //
NK023('a)001:10673: pad+ma he ru ka'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10674: na bza' dkar mo gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10675: 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur snang ba //
NK023('a)001:10676: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK023('a)001:10677: gnyis med byang chub sems bsgrubs pas //
NK023('a)001:10678: pad+ma kro ti shwa ra'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10679: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK023('a)001:10680: ru lu a b+hi g.yas dkar g.yon sngo dbus dmar nag /
NK023('a)001:10681: pad+ma kha tam rnge'u chung g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10682: dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10683: yum dmar g.yas 'khyud g.yon thod khrag /
NK023('a)001:10685: rdo rje dung khrag bar sti ra //
NK023('a)001:10687: don yod grub pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10690: gsal bar bskyed cing mchod bsgrubs pas //
NK023('a)001:10691: karma he ru ka'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10692: dam tshig sgrol ma gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10693: 'jigs byed khro mo'i cha lugs can //
NK023('a)001:10694: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK023('a)001:10695: lhag pa'i byang chub sems 'phros pas //
NK023('a)001:10696: karma kro ti'i shwa ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10697: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK023('a)001:10698: ru lu a b+hi g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ljang nag /
NK023('a)001:10699: rgya gram kha tam rnge'u chung g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10700: dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10701: yum ljang g.yas 'khyud g.yon dung khrag stobs //
NK023('a)001:10702: rgyud ltar dang po rgya gram 'dril //
NK023('a)001:10703: rdo rje dung khrag bar sti ra //
NK023('a)001:10704: thong gshol tha ma khro rgyal tha ma'o //
NK023('a)001:10705: dar rje dpal grags rgyud lung gis //
NK023('a)001:10706: sku phyag mi 'dra rang dgar mdzad //
NK023('a)001:10707: zhang chen rgyal ba'i yon tan ni //
NK023('a)001:10708: rgyud lung lugs mang 'di la gril //
NK023('a)001:10709: de ltar sangs rgyas ye shes mdzad //
NK023('a)001:10710: grub pa thob pa mang byung ba'o //
NK023('a)001:10711: h'u ston pa kun bzang gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10712: khro rgyal kun gyi rje btsan yab //
NK023('a)001:10713: sku dang phyag rgya mngon rdzogs pas //
NK023('a)001:10714: che mchog yab kyi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10715: kun tu bzang mo'i chos nyid gnas gyur pa //
NK023('a)001:10716: khro mo kun gyi rje btsun yum //
NK023('a)001:10717: shes rab dbyings las skur bskyed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:10718: kro ti'i shwa ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10719: ash+ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:10720: ash+ta kro ti shwa ri h'u phatah a b+hi ash+ta ni zhabs brgyad pa dang /
NK023('a)001:10721: dbang mchog ces ma mo'i rgyud du gsungs /
NK023('a)001:10722: phyag dang po rdor dril dang rdo rje dung khrag skabs nas 'og tu g.yas brgyad ko'u ri /
NK023('a)001:10723: g.yon brgyad sing nga zhes bdud rtsi las bshad /
NK023('a)001:10724: tsa ka 'di'i g.yas tho ba dang g.yon gtun khung 'di mgon po'i skabs nas bshad /
NK023('a)001:10725: mthu stobs mnga' bdag nas 'gyur pa //
NK023('a)001:10726: sgrol byed chen po'i bdud rnams 'joms //
NK023('a)001:10727: thod g.yag srin po sgrol la mkhas //
NK023('a)001:10728: smug nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK023('a)001:10729: rak+sha he ru ka'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10730: lha mo ral gcig gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:10731: khro mo yab kyi cha lugs can //
NK023('a)001:10732: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK023('a)001:10733: rak+sha kro ti shwa ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10734: ma h+aa rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka tsan d+ha sarba
NK023('a)001:10735: dus stan da ka ha na da ha pa tsa
NK023('a)001:10736: h'u phatah ru lu ma h+aa rak+sha kro ti shwa
NK023('a)001:10737: ri h'u phatah ru lu a b+hi sh+ae ka s+w+aa
NK023('a)001:10738: h+aa / e she ra si ti na ma s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10740: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus smug ser //
NK023('a)001:10741: dbyug to kha tam rnge'u chung g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10742: dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10743: kro ti g.yas 'khyud g.yon khrag stobs //
NK023('a)001:10744: mkhyen rab bdag po gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:10747: gang sgrubs mthu dang dbang rtsol ba'i //
NK023('a)001:10748: sa nu he ru ka'i dbang mchog khyed la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10750: khro mo dab nga phyug kun gyi rje //
NK023('a)001:10751: sprul pa yang sprul kun gyi ma //
NK023('a)001:10752: sa nu kro ti shwa ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10753: ma h+aa pa nu sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan d+ha 'dre /
NK023('a)001:10754: ma h+aa pa nu kro ti shwa ri h+aum phatah a b+hi sh+ae ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10755: e sha ra si ti na ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:10756: ru lu g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus dmar ser //
NK023('a)001:10757: sti ra kha tam rnge'u chung g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10758: dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10759: kro ti g.yas 'khril g.yon khrag stobs //
NK023('a)001:10760: thugs rje'i bdag po gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:10761: gsang ba'i don la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:10762: dmar nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK023('a)001:10763: dus rnams rtag tu gsang ba'i lha //
NK023('a)001:10764: gu ya he ru ka'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10765: gsang ba'i lha mo gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:10766: khro mo chen mo gsang ba'i lha //
NK023('a)001:10767: gsang ba'i don la bskur byed ma //
NK023('a)001:10768: gu h+ya kro ti shwa ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10769: gu ya sh+r+ai he ru ka gu ya kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK023('a)001:10770: mkhyen rab bdag po gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10771: sgrol byed chen po dregs pa 'dul //
NK023('a)001:10772: zhe sdang 'khor ba sgrol la brtson //
NK023('a)001:10773: g+hu ya he ru'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10775: khro mo yab kyis cha lugs 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:10776: g+hu ya kro ti'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10777: thugs rjes bdag po gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10778: sgrol byed chen po klu gdon 'dul //
NK023('a)001:10779: dmar nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK023('a)001:10780: dus rnams rtag tu gsang ba'i lha //
NK023('a)001:10781: gu ya he ru ka'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10782: gsung gi bdag mo gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:10783: khro mo yab kyi cha lugs can //
NK023('a)001:10784: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK023('a)001:10785: g+hu ya kro ti'i shwa ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10786: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus dmar ljang //
NK023('a)001:10787: ral gri kha tam rnge'u chung g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10788: dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10789: kro ti g.yas 'khyud g.yon khrag stobs //
NK023('a)001:10791: dpal chen dam tshig mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:10792: ljang nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK023('a)001:10793: bskal pa brgyar yang dam tshig blta //
NK023('a)001:10794: yak+sha he ru ka'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10795: yum chen dam tshig gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10796: khro mo dam tshig bya ra mkhan //
NK023('a)001:10797: sangs rgyas sems can 'da' mi byed //
NK023('a)001:10798: dam tshig dbyings su bskul byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:10799: yak+sha kro ti shwa ri'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:10800: yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan d+ha 'dre /
NK023('a)001:10801: ma h+aa yak+sha kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phatah a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10802: e sha ri si ti na ma b+hi she tsa ni mang g+ha la sa sh+ti sa h'u /
NK023('a)001:10803: ru lu g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus dkar ljang //
NK023('a)001:10804: be con kha tam rnge'u chung g.yas //
NK023('a)001:10805: dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags g.yon //
NK023('a)001:10806: kro ti g.yas 'khyud g.yon khrag stobs //
NK023('a)001:10808: smug ser dmar ser dmar ljang dkar ljang 'jigs pa'i sku /
NK023('a)001:10809: dbyug tho sta re ral gri dang /
NK023('a)001:10810: be con g.yon gyis dril bu 'dzin /
NK023('a)001:10812: kha tam rnge'u chung dung dmar rgyu zhags mthun no //
NK023('a)001:10813: sta ri dang sti ra zer ba zhu tig byas sa nu'i phyag mtshan no //
NK023('a)001:10814: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yis //
NK023('a)001:10815: 'khor lo brgyad kyi phyi rol la //
NK023('a)001:10816: gru chad bzhi dang glo 'bur du //
NK023('a)001:10817: khro mo brgyad kyis bskor ba ni //
NK023('a)001:10819: srin mo chen mo keng thod rtul //
NK023('a)001:10820: dkar mo mthu rtsal skul byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:10821: badz+ra ko'u ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10822: badz+ra ko'u ri ha ha ha /
NK023('a)001:10823: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10824: a sha ra si ti na ma /
NK023('a)001:10825: a b+hi ni shiny+tsa s+w+aa ti h'u /
NK023('a)001:10826: a b+hi rtsa ba'i sa bon la gnas ma brgyad la /
NK023('a)001:10827: ha yul ma la he brgyad mthun /
NK023('a)001:10830: ke'u ri ban dmar byis dbyug sngo //
NK023('a)001:10831: zhes te zhing gdan la g.yas byin pa'i zhing dbyug 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:10832: g.yon ban d+ha khrag 'thung pa thugs kha'o //
NK023('a)001:10834: nam mkha'i snying po gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10835: srin mo chen mo mda' 'phel brtul //
NK023('a)001:10836: rkun mo mthu rtsal len byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:10837: badz+ra tso'u ri dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10838: badz+ra tso'u ri ha ha ha /
NK023('a)001:10839: ru lu a b+hi she ka sogs /
NK023('a)001:10843: tso'u ri ser mo mda' gzhu 'gyengs //
NK023('a)001:10844: spyan ras gzigs dbang gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:10845: srin mo chen mo 'dzin byed brtul //
NK023('a)001:10846: rmongs mo'i mthu rtsal 'dren byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:10847: badz+ra pra mo'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10850: a b+hi she ka nas a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK023('a)001:10851: phyag na rdo rje gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10852: srin mo be ta nag mo brtul //
NK023('a)001:10853: thal byed mthu rtsal nyams byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:10854: badz+ra be ta li'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10858: glo 'bur byang be ta byis za hor 'phyag nag /
NK023('a)001:10860: byang chub byams pa gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:10862: rbos mo'i mthu rtsal 'ching byed ma //
NK023('a)001:10863: badz+ra pu ka si'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10865: a b+hi ha ha ru lu ru lu h'u /
NK023('a)001:10866: a b+hi she ka nas s+w+aa sti h'u /
NK023('a)001:10870: sgrib pa rnam sel gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10871: lho nub srin mo rab 'jigs brtul //
NK023('a)001:10872: gtum mo mthu rtsal snyem byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:10873: badz+ra g+hasma ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10874: badz+ra g+hasma ri ha a b+hi ha ha ru lu a b+hi she swa sti h'u /
NK023('a)001:10876: lho nub kasma ljang khu dung khrag 'thung //
NK023('a)001:10878: kun tu bzang mo gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10879: nub byang srin mo srog gcod brtul //
NK023('a)001:10880: sme sha mthu rtsal 'brel byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:10881: sme sha ni'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10883: a b+hi ha ha ru lu a b+hi she ka nas swa sti h'u gi bar mthun /
NK023('a)001:10885: sme sha mthing kha byis snying za //
NK023('a)001:10886: phyag gnyis kyis zhing rkang bzung zhal gyis snying don te za /
NK023('a)001:10888: byang shar srin mo smyo kha brtul //
NK023('a)001:10889: ma tshor mthu rtsal snyom byed ma //
NK023('a)001:10890: tsan ta li'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10891: badz+ra tsan d+ha li ha a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK023('a)001:10892: ha ha ru lu ru lu h'u /
NK023('a)001:10893: a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10894: e shwa ra si ti na ma /
NK023('a)001:10895: a b+hi shi tsa ni s+w+aa sti h'u /
NK023('a)001:10896: byang shar tsan d+ha ser skya mchog lus 'dral /
NK023('a)001:10897: spyan bgrad zhing gi mgo g.yas pus steng g.yon lus /
NK023('a)001:10898: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yis //
NK023('a)001:10899: gru chad glo 'bur bzhi rim du //
NK023('a)001:10900: bar khyams phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du //
NK023('a)001:10901: phra men brgyad kyis bskor ba ni //
NK023('a)001:10903: shar phyogs srin mo seng gdong brtul //
NK023('a)001:10904: phra men mthu rtsal gzi byin ma'i //
NK023('a)001:10905: badz+ra sing ha mu ka'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10906: badz+ra sing ha mu ka he /
NK023('a)001:10907: a b+hi he he ru lu ru lu h'u /
NK023('a)001:10908: a b+hi sh+ae ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10909: e sha ra si na ma /
NK023('a)001:10910: a b+hi shiny+tsa ni s+w+aa sti h'u /
NK023('a)001:10913: sing ha kha ro bsnol ser seng //
NK023('a)001:10914: lag g.yas phyi la lag g.yon nang du byas //
NK023('a)001:10915: rkang lag bzung dbus seng ge'i kha ro za //
NK023('a)001:10917: lho phyogs srin mo stag mgo brtul //
NK023('a)001:10918: phra men mthu rtsal 'joms byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:10919: badz+ra byi kri mu kha'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:10920: badz+ra byi kri mu kha he man chad 'agre'o //
NK023('a)001:10922: bya kri gnas lta bsnol mar stag /
NK023('a)001:10924: pus mo'i khar ni zhing steng du /
NK023('a)001:10925: phyag g.yas 'og g.yon steng byas lta'o //
NK023('a)001:10927: nub phyogs srin mo srog len brtul //
NK023('a)001:10928: phra men mthu rtsal 'dzin byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:10929: badz+ra sri la mu kha'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10930: badz+ra sri la mu ka he /
NK023('a)001:10932: nub phyogs sri la nag mo byis lhag wa //
NK023('a)001:10934: g.yon du byis ro lces ldag pa'o //
NK023('a)001:10936: byang phyogs srin mo spyang bgo brtul //
NK023('a)001:10937: phra men mthu rtsal dri byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:10938: sho na mu kha'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10939: badz+ra sho na mu ka he /
NK023('a)001:10940: ha ha ru lu sogs 'gre byang /
NK023('a)001:10941: sho na 'dral lta mthing kha spyang //
NK023('a)001:10942: g.yas su ro kha phye lta ba'o //
NK023('a)001:10944: shar lho srin mo khrag 'thung brtul //
NK023('a)001:10945: phrin las mthu rtsal mgyogs byed ma //
NK023('a)001:10946: badz+ra kri ta mu kha'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10947: badz+ra kri ta mu kha he /
NK023('a)001:10950: kri ta mgrin dmar rgyu mgo rgod //
NK023('a)001:10952: mgo bo dkar ser lus spyi dmar /
NK023('a)001:10953: g.yas kri g.yon zhing bar rgyu ma'o //
NK023('a)001:10955: lho nub srin mo rkang za brtul //
NK023('a)001:10956: phra men mthu rtsal khyab byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:10957: badz+ra kang ka mu kha'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:10958: badz+ra kang ka mu kha he /
NK023('a)001:10961: kang ka kang phran snar mgo ring /
NK023('a)001:10962: rgyab tu zhing khur khrag par rkang lag go //
NK023('a)001:10963: badz+ra a lo ke'i gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10964: nub byang srin mo 'joms byed brtul //
NK023('a)001:10965: phra men mthu rtsal za byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:10966: badz+ra kha kha mu kha he /
NK023('a)001:10967: ha ha ru lu nub byang du /
NK023('a)001:10968: kha kha kha ro b+han kri nag /
NK023('a)001:10970: g.yas gri g.yon thod glo snying khar za ba'o //
NK023('a)001:10972: byang shar srin mo rku byed brtul //
NK023('a)001:10973: phra men mthu rtsal myos byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:10974: badz+ra hu lu ka yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10975: badz+ra hu lu mu kha he /
NK023('a)001:10976: ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10977: e sha ra si ti na ma /
NK023('a)001:10978: a b+hi shiny+tsa ni swa sti h+aum /
NK023('a)001:10981: hu lu lcags kyu mthing tshogs 'ug /
NK023('a)001:10982: g.yas kyi lcags kyu g.yon pa mi mgo la tshogs pa'o //
NK023('a)001:10983: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po ni //
NK023('a)001:10984: gru chad bar khyams phyi rim la //
NK023('a)001:10985: rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi ru //
NK023('a)001:10986: sgo ba bzhi yi bskor ba ni //
NK023('a)001:10987: lha mo byams pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10988: shar gyis srin mo rta mgo brtul //
NK023('a)001:10989: byams chen rnal 'byor mgon mdzad ma'i //
NK023('a)001:10990: badz+ra ang ku sha yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:10991: badz+ra ar+ya te dza te nga dza phata /
NK023('a)001:10992: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:10993: e sha ra na si ti na ma /
NK023('a)001:10994: a b+hi shiny+tsa ni s+w+aa sti h+aum a b+hi shar sgor /
NK023('a)001:10995: rta gdong sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:10997: lha mo snying rje gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:10998: lho sgo'i srin mo phag mgo brtul //
NK023('a)001:10999: thugs rjes gzhan las phan 'dog pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11000: badz+ra pa sha'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11001: badz+ra a lo ke phatah ru a b+hi sogs mthun /
NK023('a)001:11002: lho sgor phag gdong nag mo mche zhags can //
NK023('a)001:11004: dga' ba chen mo gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11005: nub sgo'i srin mo dred mgo brtul //
NK023('a)001:11006: dga' bas rnal 'byor stong mdzad ma'i //
NK023('a)001:11007: badz+ra lo ka ma'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11010: e shwa ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:11011: nub sgor nyi zla dmar mo lcags sgrog bsdoms //
NK023('a)001:11013: btang snyoms chen po gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11014: byang sgo'i srin mo spyang mgo brtul //
NK023('a)001:11015: btang snyoms chen po'i don mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:11016: badz+ra pa smi sa la'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:11017: badz+ra pa smi pa la ya wa to ho /
NK023('a)001:11018: ru lu a b+hi she ka swa h+aa a sha ra si ti na ma /
NK023('a)001:11019: a b+hi shiny+tsa si sti h+aum /
NK023('a)001:11021: byang sgor thal byed dril bu sna tshogs spyang //
NK023('a)001:11022: zhes dang sna tshogs sprul zhes so //
NK023('a)001:11023: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yis //
NK023('a)001:11024: rnam thar sgo bzhi sgo khyud la //
NK023('a)001:11025: snam bu phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du //
NK023('a)001:11026: spor ma brgyad kyis bskor ba ni //
NK023('a)001:11028: phra men ma brgyad yon tan rgyas pa khyams kyi
NK023('a)001:11029: kha dog ser po de'i sgo yang ser po'i khyams
NK023('a)001:11031: sgo 'khyud ni bla mas brgyud du /
NK023('a)001:11032: thod rus 'bar ba zhes 'bar ma'i khyams dkar po'i snam bu'o //
NK023('a)001:11033: nang gi dbang po gnas gyur pa //
NK023('a)001:11034: srin mo 'bar ma nyi zhags brtul //
NK023('a)001:11035: mi bzad sna tshogs nyi zer zhags //
NK023('a)001:11036: shar gyi spor ma'i dbang rnams bu la byin //
NK023('a)001:11037: badz+ra a pra ti ha +ya ni tsa tur ta ra phatah a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:11038: e sha ra si ti na ma /
NK023('a)001:11039: a b+hi shiny+tsa ni swa s+t+wam h+aum /
NK023('a)001:11042: yi dwags ston pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11043: 'bar ma srin mo me gdong brtul //
NK023('a)001:11044: mi khyer dmar nag klog phreng 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:11045: shar lho spor ma'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11047: shar nub kun bzang yab yum /
NK023('a)001:11049: byang lha min gzhan du thub pa rnams gnas nges med bya ste /
NK023('a)001:11050: shar lhor yi dwags lho nub dmyal //
NK023('a)001:11051: byol song byang shar lho nub byang //
NK023('a)001:11053: shar lho lha la lho phyogs mi //
NK023('a)001:11054: lho nub nub byang yi dwags byol //
NK023('a)001:11055: byang dang byang shar lha min dmyal //
NK023('a)001:11059: nub byang du yi dwags dang /
NK023('a)001:11061: mi yi ston pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11062: srin mo 'bar ma gtum mo brtul //
NK023('a)001:11064: lho yi spor ma'i dbang mchog bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11065: badz+ra a mri ti t+ya ni sogs 'gre /
NK023('a)001:11066: dmyal ba'i ston pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11067: srin mo 'bar ma ral gri btul //
NK023('a)001:11068: gshin rje sngo nag ral gri'i sgra //
NK023('a)001:11069: lho nub spor ma'i dbang mchog bu la byin //
NK023('a)001:11070: badz+ra a mri ti t+ya ni sogs 'gre /
NK023('a)001:11071: phyi yi yul las gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11073: rdo rje dril bu 'khrol ma yis //
NK023('a)001:11074: nub kyi spor ma'i mchog bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11077: 'bar ma srin mo gnod sbyin brtul //
NK023('a)001:11078: gnod sbyin mthing nag khyung thog ma'i //
NK023('a)001:11079: nub byang spor ma'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11081: byol song ston pa gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11082: srin mo 'bar ma thogs med brtul //
NK023('a)001:11083: thogs med sngo nag skar mda' gdong //
NK023('a)001:11084: byang gis spor ma'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11086: byol song ston pa gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11088: 'jig rten smug nag klag sha brdebs //
NK023('a)001:11089: byang shar spor ma'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11090: badz+ra a pra ti ha ar+ya ni tsa dur sogs ta phatah a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:11091: e she ra si ti na ma /
NK023('a)001:11092: a b+hi shiny+tsa ni swa s+t+wi h+aum /
NK023('a)001:11095: 'bar ma rnams kyi phyag rgya ni /
NK023('a)001:11100: rtsa ba'i sa bon phatah brgyad /
NK023('a)001:11101: a rag mo h+aum brgyad bshad /
NK023('a)001:11102: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yis //
NK023('a)001:11103: gru chad bar khyams sgo bzhi yi //
NK023('a)001:11104: phyi rim snam bu sgo bzhi la //
NK023('a)001:11105: gsang ba yum bzhis bskor ba ni //
NK023('a)001:11106: dkar mo mig gcig rgyas 'debs ma //
NK023('a)001:11107: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:11108: mdun nas sangs rgyas gzugs mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:11109: gsang ba yum gyi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11110: sku dkar phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11111: sh+r+ai badz+ra ka ra mu kha shwa ra ya ya na ma /
NK023('a)001:11112: dpal 'bar khro mo rgyud las ni //
NK023('a)001:11113: bde ba za byed rmongs byed ma //
NK023('a)001:11115: yo ga brgyan dam pa las /
NK023('a)001:11116: zhe sdang me long rgyas 'debs s+w+aa sti badz+rira /
NK023('a)001:11117: nga rgyal mnyam nyid rmongs byed rat+na badz+rira //
NK023('a)001:11118: 'dod chags kun rtogs za byed pad+ma badz+rira //
NK023('a)001:11119: phrag dog don 'grub ye shes nan tan /
NK023('a)001:11121: karma badz+rira dbyings phyug mchod par rol ces /
NK023('a)001:11122: slob dpon sti ra ma tis bka' stsal to //
NK023('a)001:11123: ser mo las mkhan che 'phel ma //
NK023('a)001:11124: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:11125: g.yas na sangs rgyas gzungs mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:11126: gsang ba yum gyi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11127: sku ser phyag na mda' gzhu 'gyengs //
NK023('a)001:11128: sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ga sa ma ya ya na ma /
NK023('a)001:11129: kha dog ser mo'i tshe 'phel ma //
NK023('a)001:11130: ye shes mnyam nyid kyis rmongs byed ma'o //
NK023('a)001:11133: sh+r+ai badz+ra kha dwo pra dz+wa la ya ya na ma /
NK023('a)001:11134: dmar mo dbang bsdud za byed ma //
NK023('a)001:11135: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:11136: rgyab nas sangs rgyas gzungs mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:11137: gsang ba'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:11138: sku dmar phyag na rgyal mtshan bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11139: sh+r+ai badz+ra kha tong kha pra dz+wa la ya ya na ma /
NK023('a)001:11141: sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ga sa ma ya na ma /
NK023('a)001:11142: nag mo ral gcig rmongs byed ma //
NK023('a)001:11143: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:11144: g.yon nas sangs rgyas gzugs mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:11145: gsang ba yum gyi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11146: ljang khu phyag na dril bu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11147: sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+d+ha pra dz+wa la ya ya na ma /
NK023('a)001:11149: kha dog nag mo'i rmongs byed ma dang /
NK023('a)001:11150: ye shes bya grub bya ba nan tan gyis tshe 'phel ma'o //
NK023('a)001:11151: yang ljang nag tu byas nas ljang khu bya grub bo //
NK023('a)001:11152: bsdus par dza h+aum bam ho /
NK023('a)001:11153: gsang yum dbang mo rnams kyang rtsa sngags b+h+yo dang /
NK023('a)001:11154: sku mdog bskyed sngags 'bar ma dang 'dra bar /
NK023('a)001:11155: a raka mo h+aum zhes he ru ka 'dus rgyud las /
NK023('a)001:11156: 'bar ma rnams kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK023('a)001:11157: sku mdog gdul bya'i tshul 'dra zhing //
NK023('a)001:11160: zhes bsnyen pa zhi ba mchod pa'i dus dkar po /
NK023('a)001:11161: nye bsnyen bzang po'i mtshan ltas rgyas pa'i dus na
NK023('a)001:11162: ser po dngos grub rang dbang du bsgrub pa bzlas
NK023('a)001:11164: bsgrub chen sku gsung gnyis thugs khrag tu gril nas
NK023('a)001:11165: dngos grub len thob kyi dus mthing kha bdun tshan
NK023('a)001:11166: dang bcu tshan dang stong tshig la rak+ta sbrel ba'i
NK023('a)001:11167: dus na gtso 'khor kun kyang rdo rje dung khrag
NK023('a)001:11169: 'bar ma'i sgo ba yab yum brgyad zhi ba ltar ro //
NK023('a)001:11171: phyi rim lcags ri dmar po 'dir //
NK023('a)001:11172: sgo bzhi snam bu ngos bzhi la //
NK023('a)001:11173: dbang phyug tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK023('a)001:11174: srin po chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11175: dbang phyug chen mo mi bsrun mo //
NK023('a)001:11176: sku mdog dmar nag thod rlon can //
NK023('a)001:11177: de nyid las ni gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11178: mi bsrun dmar ser dri shul zhing chen g.yag /
NK023('a)001:11179: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul byin rlabs kyis //
NK023('a)001:11180: ma nu rak+sha sa'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11182: tshangs pa'i chung ma gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11183: dbang phyug chen mo tshangs ma ste //
NK023('a)001:11184: sku mdog dmar ser pad+ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11185: de nyid las ni gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11186: tshangs pa dmar skya rtse lnga ban dmar sbrul //
NK023('a)001:11187: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK023('a)001:11188: badz+ra pra mo'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11189: a b+hi lha chen chung ma gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11190: dbang phyug chen mo 'khrug mo ste //
NK023('a)001:11191: sku mdog dkar mo tri shul la //
NK023('a)001:11192: de nyid las ni gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11193: khro mo dmar ser zhing dbyug snying 'byin gzigs //
NK023('a)001:11194: rol pa'i rdzu 'phrul byin rlabs kyis //
NK023('a)001:11195: ro'u tri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11199: dbang phyug chen mo 'jug sred mo //
NK023('a)001:11201: de nyid las ni gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11202: khyab 'jug ser mo 'khor lo pi wam dril //
NK023('a)001:11203: dregs pa'i mthu stobs bsam yas pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11204: badz+ra be sna b+he'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:11205: a b+hi gzhon nu'i chung ma gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11206: dbang phyug chen mo dmar mo stee //
NK023('a)001:11207: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen //
NK023('a)001:11208: de nyid las ni gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11209: dbang mo dmar skya bam dbyug khog chen 'dred //
NK023('a)001:11210: yon tan mthu rtsal bsam yas pas //
NK023('a)001:11211: badz+ra ko'u ma ri ma'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:11212: a b+hi brgya byin chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11213: dbang phyug chen mo dbang mo ste //
NK023('a)001:11214: sku mdog dkar mo in+t+ra gdengs //
NK023('a)001:11216: in+t+ra dkar mar byi shud dung mar sred //
NK023('a)001:11217: che ba'i yon tan bsam yas pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11218: badz+ra in+t+ra ya ni'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11220: a b+hi lha mo khyo med gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11221: dbang phyug chen mo dmar mo ste //
NK023('a)001:11222: zhi ba dmar mo tsan dan 'thung //
NK023('a)001:11223: de nyid las ni gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11224: dmar mo dung dmar rgyu zhags dmar mo dom //
NK023('a)001:11225: yid kyi 'dod pa bsam yas pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11226: badz+ra ping ka la'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11227: nyi ma'i chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11228: dbang phyug chen mo bdud rtsi mo //
NK023('a)001:11229: sku mdog dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11230: de nyid las ni gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11231: bdud rtsi sngon mo rin chen chu srin bum //
NK023('a)001:11232: sman gyi mthu stobs bsam yas pa //
NK023('a)001:11233: badz+ra a mri ta'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11234: zla ba'i chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11235: dbang phyug chen mo zhi ba mo //
NK023('a)001:11236: zhi ba dkar mo sun d+ha ri //
NK023('a)001:11237: de nyid las kyang gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11238: zhi ba sngo skya bum ril khog smad sdig /
NK023('a)001:11239: bdud rtsi byang chub sems kyis mthus //
NK023('a)001:11240: badz+ra s+aoo nya'i dbang rnams khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:11242: be con chung ma gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11243: dbang phyug chen mo be con mo //
NK023('a)001:11244: sku mdog sngon mo dbyug tho phyar //
NK023('a)001:11245: de nyid las kyang gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11246: be con nag mo bam chen thod rlon khrag /
NK023('a)001:11247: drag shul 'joms pa'i mthu stobs kyis //
NK023('a)001:11248: badz+ra d+ha na dam gyis dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11249: srin mo khyo med gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11250: dbang phyug chen mo srin mo ste //
NK023('a)001:11251: sku mdog dmar ser thod khrag 'thung //
NK023('a)001:11252: de nyid las kyang gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11253: srin mo dmar nag zhing chen rgyu 'dren wa //
NK023('a)001:11254: drag po'i mthu stobs bsam yas pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11255: badz+ra rak+sha si'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11256: za byed chen po'i chung ma gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11257: dbang phyug chen mo za ba mo //
NK023('a)001:11258: sku mdog dmar nag za ba mo //
NK023('a)001:11259: de nyid las kyang gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11260: za byed nag mo bam chen snying 'byin stag /
NK023('a)001:11261: mthu stobs gzhan gyis mi thub pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11262: badz+ra pak+sha si'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:11264: 'bring gi hri sti chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11265: dbang phyug chen mo dga' ma ste //
NK023('a)001:11266: sku mdog dmar mo ka dar 'chang //
NK023('a)001:11267: de nyid las ni gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11268: dga' byed dmar mo khog chen bgegs rgyal rgod //
NK023('a)001:11269: mthu dang longs spyod bsam gyis mi khyab mnga' //
NK023('a)001:11270: badz+ra ra ti s+t+wam gyis dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11271: stobs bzang chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11272: dbang phyug chen mo khrag 'thung myos //
NK023('a)001:11273: sku mdog dkar mo bshol 'chang ma //
NK023('a)001:11274: de nyid las kyang gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11275: khrag 'thung dmar nag rdor dbyug dung dmar rta //
NK023('a)001:11276: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul bsam yas pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11277: badz+ra thu ti re ma tam gi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11278: rnam thos chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11279: dbang phyug chen mo gcig pu gcod //
NK023('a)001:11280: rdo rje ser mo spu gri gcod //
NK023('a)001:11281: de nyid las kyang gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11282: gcig pu dkar dmar rdo rje ban d+ha 'thung /
NK023('a)001:11283: 'byor pa'i longs spyod bsam mi khyab //
NK023('a)001:11284: badz+ra e ka tsa ri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11287: dbang phyug chen mo yid 'phrog ma //
NK023('a)001:11288: sku mdog dmar mo mda' gzhu thogs //
NK023('a)001:11289: de nyid las kyang gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11290: yid 'phrog dmar ser zhing sdom byi za khyi //
NK023('a)001:11291: 'dod pa'i yon tan kun rdzogs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11292: badz+ra ma he ha ra'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11293: nor srung chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11294: dbang phyug chen mo grub mor byung //
NK023('a)001:11295: sku mdog dkar mo bum pa 'jin //
NK023('a)001:11296: de nyid las kyang gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11297: grub mo dkar dmar pad+ma byi za shug /
NK023('a)001:11298: lhag par nor gyis longs spyod chen //
NK023('a)001:11299: badz+ra pi ti kam gyi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11300: rlung lha'i chung ma gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11301: dbang phyug chen mo rlung mor byung //
NK023('a)001:11302: sku mdog sngo nag ba dan phyar //
NK023('a)001:11303: de nyid las kyang gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11304: rlung mo dmar skya ro za sha ba'i bgo //
NK023('a)001:11306: badz+ra ba ya be'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:11308: 'jig rten skyong ma khyo med gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11309: dbang phyug chen mo khyo med ma //
NK023('a)001:11310: sku mdog dmar nag ral gri gcod //
NK023('a)001:11311: de nyid las kyang gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11312: gsod byed ljang nag bam chen rnge'u chung spyang //
NK023('a)001:11313: sgrol byed mthun stobs bsam yas pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11314: badz+ra ma h+aa ma ra na'i dbang mchog bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11315: ag ne ma'i chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11316: sku mdog dmar mo gsal shing 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:11317: dbang phyug chen mo me mor 'byung //
NK023('a)001:11318: de las mi bzad sku sprul pas //
NK023('a)001:11319: me mo ljang dmar mes sreg rgyu 'dren sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11320: nom rtog bag chags 'jig rten kun bsregs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11321: badz+ra ag ne ma'i dbang mchog bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11322: sa bdag chung ma gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11323: dbang phyug chen mo phag mor byung //
NK023('a)001:11324: sku mdog dmar nag mche ba bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11325: de nyid las kyang skur sprul pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11326: phag mo ljang ser rtse byis rlon dmar phag /
NK023('a)001:11327: 'jig rten khams kyi dpal gcig ma'i //
NK023('a)001:11328: badz+ra b+aa ra hi'i dbang rdzogs bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11330: gshin rje'i chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11331: dbang phyug chen mo rgan byed mo //
NK023('a)001:11332: rgan byed dmar smyug byis ro'i rgyu ma za //
NK023('a)001:11333: de nyid las kyang gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11334: 'bar ma ljang sngon rgyu 'dren khrag 'thor kha //
NK023('a)001:11335: ma mo mthu dbang kun rdzogs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11336: badz+ra tsa mun ti'i dbang rdzogs khyed la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11337: byi na ya ga'i chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11338: dbang phyug ma mo sna chen mo //
NK023('a)001:11339: sku mdog dmar nag thod khrag 'thung //
NK023('a)001:11340: de nyid 'jigs pa'i skur sprul pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11341: sna chen ljang dmar bam chen longs spyod glang //
NK023('a)001:11342: bgegs chen kun 'dul mthu stobs kyis //
NK023('a)001:11343: badz+ra su ta na'i dbang rdzogs bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11344: chu lha'i chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11345: dbang phyug chen mo chu lha mo //
NK023('a)001:11346: sku mdog dkar sngo sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:11348: klu mo ljang dmar bdud rtsi dung mar sbrul //
NK023('a)001:11349: rin chen gter gyi longs spyod bsam yas pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11350: badz+ra ba ru na'i dbang rdzogs bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11352: nag po chen po'i chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11353: dbang phyug nag mo chen mo ste //
NK023('a)001:11354: sku mdog nag mo ang ku sha /
NK023('a)001:11356: nag mo lcags kyu khu byug pu tra ma //
NK023('a)001:11357: thams cad 'dzin byed mthu kun rdzogs pa yis //
NK023('a)001:11358: badz+ra ma h+aa ka la'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11360: ra gdong chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11361: dbang phyug chen mo ra mgo ma //
NK023('a)001:11362: sku mdog dmar ser zhags pa snams //
NK023('a)001:11364: ra ste sngon mo rgyu zhags 'dren pa'i lha //
NK023('a)001:11365: 'khor bar mi rtogs 'ching ba'i dbang mo che //
NK023('a)001:11366: badz+ra tsa ka la yi dbang chen bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11368: bum sna'i chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11369: dbang phyug bum sna sngo nag ma //
NK023('a)001:11370: sku mdog sngo nag lcags sgrog sdom //
NK023('a)001:11372: be con dmar mo lcags sgrog kun 'joms seng //
NK023('a)001:11373: dgra bgegs bdud srin sdom pa'i dbang mo che //
NK023('a)001:11374: badz+ra sum pa ka la'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK023('a)001:11376: gsus po che yi chung ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11377: dbang phyug gsus 'dzin chen mor byung //
NK023('a)001:11378: sku mdog ljang nag dril bu 'khrol //
NK023('a)001:11380: gsus 'dzin ljang nag dril bu dung mar bskyed //
NK023('a)001:11381: nga rgyal dregs pa'i zhing bcu gnas spor ba'i //
NK023('a)001:11382: badz+ra lam po d+ha ra'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11384: 'di rnams mgo brnyan 'jig rten pa yin zhing sems
NK023('a)001:11385: can rnams la'ang de ltar bzhugs mgo brnyan lag thogs
NK023('a)001:11387: dong sprugs kyi g.yag g+ho can sogs so //
NK023('a)001:11388: ye shes pa srin mo smyug nag gsungs /
NK023('a)001:11389: las dang ye shes cha lugs mthun pa'ang yod gsungs /
NK023('a)001:11390: dam can zhal gnyis g.yas mi zhal g.yon dud 'gro'i zhal zhes gsungs /
NK023('a)001:11391: mkha' 'gro yon tan rgyas pa'i phyir gser khyams la'o //
NK023('a)001:11392: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yis //
NK023('a)001:11394: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad sgo bzhi ru //
NK023('a)001:11395: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK023('a)001:11396: rdo rje sems dpa' gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11397: mkha' 'gro dga' byed rdo rje bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11398: mkha' 'gro rdo rje rigs dbang phyug /
NK023('a)001:11399: ma h+aa badz+ra d+h+aa ra'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11400: rdo rje rgyal po gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11401: 'dren byed dkar skya lcags kyu ma //
NK023('a)001:11403: kro ti shwa ri'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11404: rdo rje chags pa gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11405: gsod byed thabs kyi mda' 'geng ma //
NK023('a)001:11406: mkha' 'gro sgrol byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:11407: badz+ra ma h+aa he ma ti'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11408: rdo rje legs pa gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11409: spor byed dkar skya spu gri togs //
NK023('a)001:11410: badz+ra ku ma hri'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11412: e a ra li ta ta ki ni so gnyis mkha' 'gro rnams /
NK023('a)001:11413: mkha' 'gro rnams kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK023('a)001:11414: rdo rje gshog pas zil gnon cing //
NK023('a)001:11415: b+han khrag 'thung zhing chags pa che //
NK023('a)001:11416: dpal 'bar khro bo las ye shes so //
NK023('a)001:11417: phyogs re brgyad phyogs bzhi mtshams gsum sgo re'o //
NK023('a)001:11418: zhar la shugs 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis kun 'dus las bshad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:11419: chags pa ni sku mdog dmar ba'i mdangs can du mthun pa'o //
NK023('a)001:11420: rdo rje rin chen gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11423: ma h+aa badz+ra ma tsi na'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11424: rdo rje nyi ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11426: rnam rtog mun sel mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:11427: badz+ra tri sh+r+ai sma ra'i dbang rnams bu la byin //
NK023('a)001:11428: rdo rje rgyal mtshan gnas gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11429: khro gnyer mthing nag zhing dar 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:11430: bdud bzhi 'dul byed dbang ldan pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11431: badz+ra tsag ne na yi dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11432: rdo rje bzhad pa gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11433: 'joms byed zhing gis kha gdangs ma //
NK023('a)001:11434: dur khrod bgegs 'joms za byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:11435: ma h+aa kro ti'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11436: rdo rje chos mchog gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11437: chags med dmar nag pad ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11438: nyes pa'i skyon bral legs pa'i dbang rdzogs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11439: ma h+aa ar mrii dod ti pa'i dbang mchog bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11440: rdo rje rnon po gnas 'gyur ba'i //
NK023('a)001:11441: chags bral dmar nag gri thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:11442: mkha' 'gro sgrol byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:11443: ma h+aa soo ma'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11446: mkha' 'gro gcod byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:11447: ma h+aa badz+ra dan ti'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11448: rdo rje smra ba gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11450: thogs med lcags kyu dbang bsgyur ma //
NK023('a)001:11451: ma h+aa ra ma ni'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11452: rdo rje phrin las gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11453: sna tshogs lus 'chang rgya gram thogs //
NK023('a)001:11454: mkha' 'gro phrin las rdzogs pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:11455: ma h+aa ramri rti ka pa la hes te ta ki'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11456: rdo rje srung ba gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11457: bsrung ba mo ljang go cha thogs //
NK023('a)001:11459: badz+ra s+aoo ma'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11460: rdo rje gnod sbyin gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11461: gnod sbyin mo ljang mche ba 'byin //
NK023('a)001:11462: dam nyams gsod pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK023('a)001:11463: mri ta pu tan ta ri'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11464: rdo rje khu tshur gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11466: rdul du rlog byed mkha' 'gro'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:11467: badz+ra bi la ke la'i dbang mchog bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11469: bya rog gdong la mig 'byin ma //
NK023('a)001:11470: lag na gri dang mkhar gzhong thogs //
NK023('a)001:11472: bi shi ri ri'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11473: kun bzang sems dpa' gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11474: 'jigs byed dkar sngo mche gtsigs ma //
NK023('a)001:11476: sha ni k+sha'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11478: bzhad gdong dkar mo snying 'byin ma //
NK023('a)001:11479: thams cad sgrol ba'i mkha' 'gro 'a gying //
NK023('a)001:11480: sha ni ta ki'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11481: bzang skyongs sems dpa' gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11483: las byed lhag bsdud gzhi dbang kun //
NK023('a)001:11484: bi ta ki'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11485: rgyu'am bskal bzang sems dpa' bcu drug la //
NK023('a)001:11486: mtshams gsum sgo ras phyogs mtshon rigs mtshan can //
NK023('a)001:11487: dpa' bar 'gro dang kun bzang dang //
NK023('a)001:11489: bzang skyong d+r+wa ba can gyis 'od //
NK023('a)001:11490: rdo rje snying po byams brtseg lho //
NK023('a)001:11491: nam mkha' mdzod dang 'od dpag med //
NK023('a)001:11492: mya ngan kun 'joms spos glang nub //
NK023('a)001:11493: ye shes tog dang blo mi zad //
NK023('a)001:11494: spobs pa brtsegs dang don 'grub byang //
NK023('a)001:11496: khyi mgo mthing nag keng rus 'cha' //
NK023('a)001:11497: dur khrod 'joms pa'i dbang skur bas //
NK023('a)001:11498: badz+ra a na ya yi dbang rnams 'dir bskur cig /
NK023('a)001:11499: rdo rje snying po gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11500: mthing nag ma sa phag gi mgo //
NK023('a)001:11501: rtsang sme med par za byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:11502: be ko ne'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11503: nam mkha' mdzod sems gnas 'gyur ba'i //
NK023('a)001:11504: sngo nag glo 'dren rnga mo'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:11506: dza du la ya bas kyis dbang rnams bu la bskur //
NK023('a)001:11508: thod yag dgra sta dpung bu'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:11510: ta ki be ka te yi dbang rnams bu la bskur //
NK023('a)001:11512: dmar nag spu gri ra'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:11514: badz+ra dar shi'i dbang rnams 'dir bskur cig /
NK023('a)001:11515: rgyal ba'i ye shes gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11516: dmar nag rus 'cha' byi lha'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:11517: ma lus sgrol byed mkha' 'gro'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:11518: ka li pra be sha'i dbang rnams bu la bskur //
NK023('a)001:11519: blo gros mi bzad gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11520: dmar ljang keng rus dkar po 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:11522: us ting mang po'i dbang yang khyod la bskur bar bya /
NK023('a)001:11523: spobs pa brtsegs pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK023('a)001:11524: dmar ser rus phreng lce spyang mgo //
NK023('a)001:11526: ka ran tsa'i dbang rnams 'di bskur cig /
NK023('a)001:11528: mkha' 'gro srin mo bum sna ma //
NK023('a)001:11529: rdo rje lcags kyu ka ta ri //
NK023('a)001:11530: sarba ma ta ra yi dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11531: byams pa brtsegs pa gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11533: zhags pas gri thogs 'dzin cing sgrol //
NK023('a)001:11534: sa a ta ki'i dbang rnams 'dir bskur cig /
NK023('a)001:11535: spos kyi glang po gnas 'gyur bas //
NK023('a)001:11536: mkha' 'gro d+ha sha g+h+ri wa ste //
NK023('a)001:11537: lcags sgrog spu gri za byed ma //
NK023('a)001:11538: badz+ra sarba ban d+ha a'i dbang rnams 'dir bskur cig /
NK023('a)001:11541: dril bu dgra s+t+was sgrom zhing spor //
NK023('a)001:11542: badz+ra sa b+han a ka'i dbang rnams bu la bskur /
NK023('a)001:11543: khyams ma mo srin mo 'dod chags gnas su dag pa'i khrag mtsho'i /
NK023('a)001:11544: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yis //
NK023('a)001:11545: phyi yi snam bu phyogs bzhi la //
NK023('a)001:11546: ma bdun sring bzhis bskor ba ni //
NK023('a)001:11547: ma bdun mchog gis dbang bskur te //
NK023('a)001:11548: rgya mtsho chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK023('a)001:11549: dpal ldan shug sgrol gtso bo ste //
NK023('a)001:11550: ri rab bsnyil ba'i mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:11551: rdo rje kun grags dbang 'dis khyod la bskur //
NK023('a)001:11552: ma ma d+ha ru kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK023('a)001:11553: srin mo skam ma rab skam ma //
NK023('a)001:11554: dri ma 'don ma phor thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:11555: g.yang gzhi ma dang bskul byed ma //
NK023('a)001:11556: myos byed ma bdun skam kun grags //
NK023('a)001:11557: phor thogs kun tu bzang mo dang //
NK023('a)001:11558: g.yang gzhi ma ni drag snyem ma //
NK023('a)001:11559: za ba mo 'am rab bskam ni //
NK023('a)001:11560: rdo rje ye shes dam tshig mchog /
NK023('a)001:11561: srin mo gsod byed 'od gsal chags //
NK023('a)001:11562: za byed bskul byed gsal phro ma //
NK023('a)001:11563: dri ma snom par byed ma dang //
NK023('a)001:11564: dri ma 'don ma g.yu sgron bshad //
NK023('a)001:11566: nam mkha' stong la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK023('a)001:11567: bdud dpung drag snyems kun 'dul ma //
NK023('a)001:11568: rdo rje drag snyem dbang 'dis khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11569: ma ma d+ha ru kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK023('a)001:11571: gdug pa ma lus sdig byed cing //
NK023('a)001:11574: 'jig rten mche bdag gzi phrog ma //
NK023('a)001:11575: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang 'di khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11576: ma ma d+ha tu kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK023('a)001:11577: dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK023('a)001:11578: khro bo gtum chen za ba mo //
NK023('a)001:11579: pho nya mo ste drug cu'i gtso //
NK023('a)001:11580: sha chen khrag la longs spyod cing //
NK023('a)001:11581: gdug pa ma lus kun 'dul ma //
NK023('a)001:11582: rdo rje chen mo ye shes mchog /
NK023('a)001:11583: dam tshig tshul bzhin dbang 'dis khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11584: ma ma d+ha tu kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK023('a)001:11585: dam tshig chen po'i tshogs gral yin te //
NK023('a)001:11589: zhag gcig la dper brjod na zhag ma de'i drug
NK023('a)001:11590: cu cha dang gung gnyis srod tho rangs skad cig
NK023('a)001:11592: 'jig chags kyi bskal pa drug cu rtsa bzhi'i dus
NK023('a)001:11593: la kun khyab tu nyul zhing dbang byed pa'i ma
NK023('a)001:11594: mo'i gtso mo'o // khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK023('a)001:11595: rdo rje d+r+wa ba'i phreng thogs shing //
NK023('a)001:11597: rdo rje 'od chags dbang 'dis bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11598: ma na d+ha tu me dpung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK023('a)001:11599: zhags pa stong gis gdeng ldan zhing //
NK023('a)001:11601: rdo rje gsal phro'i dbang 'di bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11602: ma ma d+ha 'od phung 'khrigs pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK023('a)001:11605: dbang phyug chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK023('a)001:11607: dam tshig nyams pa gsod byed cing //
NK023('a)001:11608: bka' las 'gal ba'i snying phrog ma //
NK023('a)001:11609: rdo rje g.yu sgron dbang 'dis khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11610: ma ma d+ha tu ma bdun phyag mtshan ri rab dang /
NK023('a)001:11617: bdun g.yas dang g.yon thod pa gang ba'o //
NK023('a)001:11618: sku mdog shar gnyis sngon po dang /
NK023('a)001:11619: g.yu zhes byang ljang khu dang /
NK023('a)001:11622: gsal phror ne tsho kha'ang lho ser po bya //
NK023('a)001:11624: bka' brgyad du shar gyi ma dkar mor byas nas /
NK023('a)001:11625: kun grags dang g.yu sgron dkar /
NK023('a)001:11626: byang gsal 'phro byang phyogs zhes 'od gsal du byas na gser /
NK023('a)001:11628: drag snyems dang ye shes dmar /
NK023('a)001:11629: mdun ka thod pa can bshad /
NK023('a)001:11630: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK023('a)001:11631: phyi rim snam bu'i sgo bzhi ru //
NK023('a)001:11632: srid zhi'i dbang bskur thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11633: sku mdog shar dkar lho ser nub dmar byang gi
NK023('a)001:11634: phyag mtshan rgyal mtshan gyis tog thul pa'i mgo bo
NK023('a)001:11635: dang 'dra'o // yang na gu ru pad+ma'i bka' brgyad ma mo dang 'dra bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:11636: gling bzhi mgyogs ma lha'i sring //
NK023('a)001:11637: sku la bya rgod thul pa gsol //
NK023('a)001:11638: thugs dam rnal 'byor grogs la brtson //
NK023('a)001:11639: lha'i srin mo'i dbang 'di bu la bskur //
NK023('a)001:11640: ma ma d+ha tu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:11641: gling bzhi mgyogs ma lha'i sring /
NK023('a)001:11642: dkar mo rdo rje rtse gsum thogs //
NK023('a)001:11643: shar gyi sgo ma'i dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:11644: lha yi tshogs rnams sdud pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:11645: te pam b+h+yo te pam b+h+yo /
NK023('a)001:11646: mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring //
NK023('a)001:11647: sku la stag gi thul pa 'dre /
NK023('a)001:11648: thugs dam rnal 'byor grogs la brtson //
NK023('a)001:11649: gshin rje'i sring mo'i dbang 'dis bu la bskur //
NK023('a)001:11650: ma ma d+ha tu a b+hi mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring //
NK023('a)001:11651: sngon mo mi mgo thod dbyug thogs //
NK023('a)001:11652: lho'i sgo ma'i dbang gshin rje'i tshogs bsdud dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:11654: dmar mo g.yag thod klu'i sring //
NK023('a)001:11655: dmar mo sbrul nag zhag pa thogs //
NK023('a)001:11656: nub kyi sgo mas klu'i tshogs bsdud d+ha la dun b+h+yo /
NK023('a)001:11657: nag mo sder chen gnod sbyin sring //
NK023('a)001:11658: sku la rma bya'i thul pa gsol //
NK023('a)001:11659: dam tshig can la brtse dgongs la //
NK023('a)001:11660: gnod sbyin sring mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:11662: a b+hi nag mo sder chen gnod sbyin sring //
NK023('a)001:11663: lag na ne'u le'i rkyal pa thogs //
NK023('a)001:11664: byang gi sgo mas dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:11665: gnod sbyin tshogs bsdud dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:11668: rtsa ba'i sa bon ma ma bcu gcig /
NK023('a)001:11672: ma bdun sring bzhi'i phyag rgya ni //
NK023('a)001:11673: 'jo sgeg mdzes pa'i tshul gyis blta' //
NK023('a)001:11675: g.yon pa dung khrag 'thung byed pa'o //
NK023('a)001:11677: dkar 'dzin zhes 'o ma rgyas pa'i nu ma 'bur bas ston la chags pas dmar ba'o //
NK023('a)001:11678: 'di ni rgyal ba'i sras po yin pas na //
NK023('a)001:11679: phyag rgya chen po'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:11680: ras sam 'bur ram lugs su blug pa yi //
NK023('a)001:11681: phyag rgya'i gzugs brnyan de'i spyi bor bzhag /
NK023('a)001:11684: khro bo bcu pho nya'i ging ngo //
NK023('a)001:11685: ma bdun sring bzhi'i pho nya'i sham du byed pa ltar du /
NK023('a)001:11686: des lha dbang tshangs pas 'di gsungs //
NK023('a)001:11687: khyams dkar po dpal chen tshems kyis 'od dkar king
NK023('a)001:11688: la rtsa ba'am sa bon phatah he ru ka 'dus
NK023('a)001:11689: rgyud du dza bcod brgyad a ha king ka ra
NK023('a)001:11691: rdo rje ging chen bco brgyad ni //
NK023('a)001:11692: sngon skya 'jigs pa'i tshul ston cing //
NK023('a)001:11693: g.yas pa gri dang mtshon cha thogs //
NK023('a)001:11694: g.yon pa 'dzin cing gsod par byed //
NK023('a)001:11697: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yis //
NK023('a)001:11698: phyi rim snam bu'i phyogs bzhi ru //
NK023('a)001:11699: thugs kyi 'od zer sprul pa las //
NK023('a)001:11700: khro bo ging gis bskor ba ni //
NK023('a)001:11701: dpa' bo chen po las rnams kun byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11702: mthing nag ral gri b+han d+ha bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11703: gang la dmigs pa sgrol ba yi //
NK023('a)001:11704: rdo rje ging gis dbang yang bskur //
NK023('a)001:11705: khro mo chen mo khams gsum dbang bsdud ma //
NK023('a)001:11706: sngo nag thod khrag 'jam dpal thogs //
NK023('a)001:11707: sgrol byed las la 'ba' zhig dgos //
NK023('a)001:11708: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang 'di khyod la sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:11709: rdo rje ka tar king ka ra badz+ra ging ka ra /
NK023('a)001:11710: dmar nag ban rdo rje ka dar bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11711: ma thogs myur du bsgral ba'i las mdzod cig /
NK023('a)001:11712: rdo rje ging gis dbang yang sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:11713: rdo rje ging chen gnod sbyin ni //
NK023('a)001:11714: ljang gnag phyag gis sdigs mdzub 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:11715: dam tshig nyams rnams sgrol byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11717: rdo rje ging chen spyang gi ni //
NK023('a)001:11718: dmar nag spyang mgo spu gri thogs //
NK023('a)001:11719: gsod pa'i las la shin tu gdeng //
NK023('a)001:11720: rdo rje ging 'dis dbang badz+ra ka ta ri shwa ra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:11721: rdo rje ging chen gshin rje ni //
NK023('a)001:11722: lding nag be con dgra s+t+wa 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:11723: ma lus sgrol ba'i ging chen ste //
NK023('a)001:11724: rdo rje ging gi dbang 'di bul //
NK023('a)001:11725: rdo rje ging chen ral pa ni //
NK023('a)001:11726: dmar nag ban d+ha phal tshab bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11727: dgra bgegs ma lus myal thag gcod //
NK023('a)001:11728: rdo rje ging gi dbang rdo rje ging chen 'chi bdag ni //
NK023('a)001:11729: ljang ser rdo rje gsor zhing brdeg /
NK023('a)001:11730: drag shul sgrol ba'i mthu stobs can //
NK023('a)001:11731: rdo rje ging gis dbang 'dis bu la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11732: rdo rje ging chen dus mtshams ni //
NK023('a)001:11733: ljang nag mdung thung ba dan thogs //
NK023('a)001:11734: rdo rje shwa ri'i ban da thogs //
NK023('a)001:11736: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ta ri sha ra shwa ri h+aum /
NK023('a)001:11737: rdo rje ging chen ro langs ni //
NK023('a)001:11738: ser nag zhing gi dbyug pa phyar //
NK023('a)001:11739: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis 'joms //
NK023('a)001:11740: rdo rje ging 'dis dbang yang bskur bar bya //
NK023('a)001:11741: rdo rje ging chen 'joms pa ni //
NK023('a)001:11742: smug nag rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:11743: bgegs kyi dpang yang yud kyis 'joms //
NK023('a)001:11745: rdo rje gying lcam dbang bsdud ni //
NK023('a)001:11746: ljang nag rdo rje lcags kyu 'dren //
NK023('a)001:11747: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis sgrol //
NK023('a)001:11748: rdo rje gying lcam dbang rdo rje gying lcam dbang bskur ma //
NK023('a)001:11749: khams gsum zhing gi g.yab mos 'debs //
NK023('a)001:11750: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK023('a)001:11751: rdo rje ging 'dis dbang rdo rje gying lcam 'phrul mo che //
NK023('a)001:11752: rdo rje gying mo'i dbang gzugs med rlung ltar rgyu byed cing //
NK023('a)001:11753: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis khyab //
NK023('a)001:11754: rdo rje gying lcam dbang 'di khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11756: rdo rje gying lcam glog 'gyu ma //
NK023('a)001:11758: cir yang 'gyur ba'i mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:11759: rdo rje gying mo'i dbang rdo rje ging lcam mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:11760: ljang nag lcags kyu tho ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:11761: rbod gtong bcol ba len par byed //
NK023('a)001:11762: rdo rje ging gi dbang rdo rje ging lcam mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:11763: mthing nag rdo rje dgra s+t+wa thogs //
NK023('a)001:11764: phrin las rna nyan phra ma zer //
NK023('a)001:11765: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang rdo rje ging lcam sgrol byed ma //
NK023('a)001:11766: smug nag ban d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:11767: phrin las srid gsum sgrol byed ma //
NK023('a)001:11768: rdo rje gying mo'i dbang gying lcam za byed chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:11769: rdo rje gying lcam myos byed ma //
NK023('a)001:11770: mthing nag phyag na longs spyod bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11771: phrin las tshogs kyis phyag tshangs byed //
NK023('a)001:11772: rdo rje gying chen dbang 'dis khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11773: badz+ra kro ta ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK023('a)001:11774: steng gis pho nya 'od mthing kha hi khyams mthing nag la /
NK023('a)001:11776: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yis //
NK023('a)001:11777: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og bcu //
NK023('a)001:11778: dgra gdon mang po 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:11779: sku yi kha dog mthing nag las //
NK023('a)001:11780: khro bo khro mo drug cu sprul //
NK023('a)001:11781: rnam rgyal mdog dkar rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:11782: snyems ma gtso 'khyud thod khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:11783: mthu rtsal yang che dri bzang gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK023('a)001:11784: khro bo khro mo'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11785: dbyug pa sngon po sdigs mdzub rin chen sngo //
NK023('a)001:11786: sder mo gtso 'khyud dung mar gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:11787: mthu rtsal che bas drang srong gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK023('a)001:11788: khro bo khro mo'i dbang 'dis thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11789: gshin rje'i gshed po mthing nag dbyug tho phyar //
NK023('a)001:11790: rdo rje dur khrod dung dmar yab la stobs //
NK023('a)001:11791: nga rgyal mthu chen gshin rjes gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK023('a)001:11792: khro bo khro mo'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11793: mi g.yo mgon po ral gri khu tshur thogs //
NK023('a)001:11794: rdo rje dun khung dung dmar gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:11795: rdzu 'phrul mthu chen srin po'i gdon rnams 'dul //
NK023('a)001:11796: khro mo yab yum rta mgrin mdog dmar pad+ma mda' gzhu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11797: rdo rje gtum mo dung mar gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:11798: thugs rje mthu rtsal gti mug klu 'dul ba'i //
NK023('a)001:11799: khro bo khro mo badz+ra kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK023('a)001:11800: gzhan gyis mi thub dgra s+t+wa gtun shing sngo //
NK023('a)001:11801: rdo rje mda' snyems dung khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:11802: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul klu gdon 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11803: khro bo khro mo bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang nag rgya gram phyar //
NK023('a)001:11804: rdo rje rlung 'byin dung mar gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:11805: drag po mthu yis gnod sbyin gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK023('a)001:11806: khro bo yab yum dbang khams gsum rnam rgyal rdo rje tho ba gnas //
NK023('a)001:11807: rdo rje gsod byed dmar gyis mchod pa 'dren //
NK023('a)001:11808: drag shul mthu yis 'byung po gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK023('a)001:11809: khro bo yab yum dbang rdo rje stobs chen dud kha 'bud dung rnga yab thogs //
NK023('a)001:11810: rdo rje bskyod chen dung khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:11811: mthu stobs ldan pas sa bdag gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK023('a)001:11812: khro bo yab yum dbang 'di h+aum mdzad dmar skya rdo rje mda' gzhu 'gyengs //
NK023('a)001:11813: rdo rje sgra 'byin dung dmar zhal du stobs //
NK023('a)001:11814: nyi zla gza' skar yas gdon 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11815: khro bo khro mo'i dbang 'di thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11816: badz+ra kro ta kro ti sha ri h+aum /
NK023('a)001:11817: des phyogs bcu'i khro tshogs nyi shu'o //
NK023('a)001:11818: de nas khro bo'i rigs chung he ru ka bzhi bcu ni //
NK023('a)001:11820: sku yi 'od zer mthing nag las //
NK023('a)001:11821: khro bo khro mo drug cus skor ba yis //
NK023('a)001:11822: dgra bgegs mang pos 'dul slad du //
NK023('a)001:11823: badz+ra ki la ya mthing nag phur pa 'dril //
NK023('a)001:11824: khro mo rgyal 'debs ban d+ha rak+tasa bkang //
NK023('a)001:11825: mthu dbang che bas dgra dang lha gdon 'dul //
NK023('a)001:11826: khro bo khro mo'i dbang 'dis bskur bas thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11827: khro bo sme brtsegs mthing nag rdo rje thogs //
NK023('a)001:11828: khro mo 'dam 'byin dung chen dam rdzas dbang //
NK023('a)001:11829: mi rtsang rtog 'joms bdud dang ru tra 'dul //
NK023('a)001:11830: khro bo khro mo dbang 'dis thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11831: badz+ra yak+sha ljang nag phur pa sgrengs //
NK023('a)001:11832: khro mo yag mo dung chen snying khrag bcas //
NK023('a)001:11833: dam tshig nyams dang dam sri 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11834: khro bo yab yum khro chen dmar nag rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:11835: khro mo dbang bsgyur mgo bcad rak+tasa bkang //
NK023('a)001:11836: mthu rtsal che bas ma gdon gdul mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11837: khro bo khro mo'i dbang khro bo za 'og thod sbrul sna tshogs mdog /
NK023('a)001:11838: khro mo zag ma rdo rje thod khrag stobs //
NK023('a)001:11839: rdzu 'phrul mthu yis dmu gdon 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11840: khro bo khro mo'i dbang 'di badz+ra kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK023('a)001:11841: khro bo rab grub sngo nag ral gri 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:11842: khro mo rab 'jigs thod khrag zhal du stobs //
NK023('a)001:11843: mthu rtsal chen pos gdon chen bco brgyad 'dul //
NK023('a)001:11844: khro bo yab yum dbang 'dis thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11845: khro chen ma h+aa ka la dmar nag zhal //
NK023('a)001:11846: khro mo ral pa sgrengs ma thod khrag stobs //
NK023('a)001:11847: mthu rtsal che bas ya bdud 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:11848: yab yum 'di gnyis dbang yang thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11849: mi 'chi thal sbyir sngo nag thal mo rdebs //
NK023('a)001:11850: khro mo 'joms chen thod khrag zhal du gsol //
NK023('a)001:11851: mthu rtsal che bas srog chags rdul du barloga /
NK023('a)001:11852: yab yum 'di gnyis dbang khro chen gu lang smug nag gtun shing rdeb //
NK023('a)001:11853: khro mo las kun 'grub la ban d+ha dmar gyis bkang //
NK023('a)001:11854: mthu rtsal che bas khams gsum gsad gso mdzad //
NK023('a)001:11855: yab yum 'di gnyis dbang yang rab rngam ljang nas rdo rje 'khrug cing gsol //
NK023('a)001:11856: g.yul chen thod khrag tsit+ta gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:11857: mthu rtsal che bas brjed byed gdon rnams 'dul //
NK023('a)001:11858: yab yum gnyis med dbang yang thog par shog /
NK023('a)001:11859: 'jig rten gsum snang be con sdigs mdzub thogs //
NK023('a)001:11860: khro mo mi pham de bzhin dung chen stobs //
NK023('a)001:11861: mthu rtsal che bas sgo srung shar gdon 'dul //
NK023('a)001:11862: yab yum khro bo'i dbang 'di 'jig rten gsum 'dul dmar nag tho ba 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:11863: khro mo lcags kyu de bzhin lcags kyu dang //
NK023('a)001:11864: shar sgor bsrung zhing shar gdon 'dul ba'i bdag /
NK023('a)001:11865: yab yum 'di gnyis dbang yang thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11866: badz+ra kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK023('a)001:11867: 'jig rten gsum 'jig dmar nag ral gri tho ba 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:11868: khro gnyir thod khrag de bzhin zhal du stobs //
NK023('a)001:11869: mthu rtsal che bas sgo srung lho gdon 'dul //
NK023('a)001:11870: yab yum 'di gnyis dbang yang thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11871: 'jig rten gsum 'ching sngo nag dbyug tho 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:11872: khro mo zhags pa dung dmar zhags pa thogs //
NK023('a)001:11873: lho sgo bsrung zhing lho gdon 'dul ba'i bdag /
NK023('a)001:11875: pad rgyal dmar nag de bzhin ral gri phyar //
NK023('a)001:11876: ro langs de bzhin thod khrag zhal du stobs //
NK023('a)001:11877: mthu rtsal che bas sgo bsrung nub gdon 'dul //
NK023('a)001:11878: yab yum 'di gnyis dbang yang thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11879: be con sngon po rin chen be con 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:11880: khro mo lcags sgrog de bzhin dung chen 'bud //
NK023('a)001:11881: nub phyogs sgo bsrung nub gdon 'dul ba'i bdag /
NK023('a)001:11882: yab yum 'di gnyis dbang yang ka ni badz+ra dmar nag gri sdigs mdzub //
NK023('a)001:11883: ral gcig gtso bo'i dung khrag zhal du stobs //
NK023('a)001:11884: mthu rtsal che bas sgo bsrung byang gdon 'dul //
NK023('a)001:11885: yab yum 'di gnyis rdo rje go cha mthing nag go cha bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11886: khro mo dril 'khrol thod khrag dril bu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11887: byang phyogs sgo srung byang gdon 'dul mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:11888: yab yum 'di gnyis dbang yang khro bo rngam chen smug nag be con 'dzub //
NK023('a)001:11889: khro mo dbang bsdud thod khrag zhal du stobs //
NK023('a)001:11890: mthu rtsal che bas bdud dang srin po 'dul //
NK023('a)001:11891: khro bo yab yum 'di gnyis dbang yang rdo rje tho ba dud kha tho ba bsnams //
NK023('a)001:11892: khro mo za byed dung khrag yab la stobs //
NK023('a)001:11893: mthu rtsal che bas pho mo gshin rje 'dul //
NK023('a)001:11894: yab yum 'di gnyis dbang yang thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:11895: badz+ra kro ta dbang don ltar /
NK023('a)001:11897: h+aum shar dza h+aum lho nub bam byang du ho /
NK023('a)001:11900: rtsa ba'i sa bon dza sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK023('a)001:11902: rba na rba na ang ku sha dza dza /
NK023('a)001:11903: ha la ha la p+aa sha h'u dzah gardza gardza spo ta bam dza /
NK023('a)001:11904: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+dza ho /
NK023('a)001:11905: kro ta kro ti h+aum dza /
NK023('a)001:11906: ma ma shwa ra h+aum dza /
NK023('a)001:11907: nag mo gshog pa can la b+h+yo bdun 'bum nyi khri'o //
NK023('a)001:11908: zhes b+h+yo re las kyang ma mo bye ba khrag
NK023('a)001:11909: khrig ste bye ba du mas yod pa bye ba
NK023('a)001:11911: shar phyogs kyi khyams dkar pho nya dkar ba ni /
NK023('a)001:11912: sa bon dza zhes mthun no //
NK023('a)001:11913: pho nya res yang las thams cad 'grub pas na /
NK023('a)001:11914: dza rkyang pa'am sa bon drug go //
NK023('a)001:11916: sku yi 'od zer rnam drug las //
NK023('a)001:11917: sum brgya drug cu'i gdon bsgral phyir //
NK023('a)001:11918: pho nya sum brgya drug cur sprul //
NK023('a)001:11920: dri za'i dgra gdon 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:11921: shar phyogs 'od zer dkar po las //
NK023('a)001:11922: dung gi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK023('a)001:11923: rdo rje 'bar ba'i pho nya mo //
NK023('a)001:11924: dkar mo mthongs byed lcags kyu ma //
NK023('a)001:11925: yid kyis phyin cing bsam pas 'grub //
NK023('a)001:11926: gnas 'dir khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK023('a)001:11927: rdo rje sder mo pho nya mo //
NK023('a)001:11929: gang yang thogs med glog 'gyu bas //
NK023('a)001:11930: dus 'dir bu mchog khyod la bskur //
NK023('a)001:11931: pho nya rdo rje ki la ya //
NK023('a)001:11932: dkar mo thogs med dmigs gsal ma //
NK023('a)001:11934: rnal 'byor bu la bdag gis sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11935: pho nya rdo rje 'beg pa mo //
NK023('a)001:11936: dkar mo shel gyis mda' 'phen ma //
NK023('a)001:11937: gang la dmigs pa 'grub byed dbang //
NK023('a)001:11938: dus 'dir bdag gis khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:11939: rdo rje pho nya ro langs ma //
NK023('a)001:11940: dkar mo lag na gri thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:11942: bdag gis de ring bskur bar bya //
NK023('a)001:11943: rdo rje pho nya drag mo'i sku //
NK023('a)001:11944: dkar mo lag na mdung thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:11945: gang la sngags pa 'gyub byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:11946: gnas 'dir khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:11947: rba na rba na a 'gu sha dza dza //
NK023('a)001:11948: rdo rje mgyogs ma pho nya mo //
NK023('a)001:11949: dkar mo ming sring g.yab mos 'debs //
NK023('a)001:11950: ting 'dzin yid kyis pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:11951: rnal 'byor bu la sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:11952: pho nya rdo rje gtum mo ni //
NK023('a)001:11954: sgrol byed pho nya tsi ti'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:11955: de ring bu la sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:11956: pho nya rdo rje 'bebs ma ni //
NK023('a)001:11957: dkar mo gar byed glu byed mkhan //
NK023('a)001:11958: las la 'brid pa'i pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:11959: snying gi bu la bskur bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:11960: pho nya rdo rje gsal ma ni //
NK023('a)001:11961: dkar mo dung phreng glad la bskor //
NK023('a)001:11962: sa ma y+aa'i khus 'debs ma'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:11963: gnas 'dir khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK023('a)001:11964: pho nya rdo rje stod ma ni //
NK023('a)001:11965: dkar skya dar dkar g.yab 'dor ma //
NK023('a)001:11966: rgyal bas yon tan cher bstod ma //
NK023('a)001:11967: rdo rje pho nya'i dbang chen 'dir //
NK023('a)001:11968: rtags dang bcas te dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:11969: rdo rje 'gugs ma pho nya mo //
NK023('a)001:11970: dkar mo bdud kyi snying 'gugs ma //
NK023('a)001:11972: rdo rje pho nya'i dbang chen 'dis //
NK023('a)001:11973: sku dang bcas te dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:11974: rba na rba na ang ku sha dza /
NK023('a)001:11975: pho nya rdo rje thogs pa med //
NK023('a)001:11976: dkar dmar lag na zangs gri 'chang //
NK023('a)001:11977: dpa' bo chen po thogs med pas //
NK023('a)001:11978: rdo rje pho nya'i dbang chen 'dis //
NK023('a)001:11979: sku dang bcas te bskur bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:11980: rdo rje pho nya bskyod ma ni //
NK023('a)001:11981: dkar dmar rlung gis zhags thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:11982: rnal 'byor phrin las bskyod ma'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:11983: rdo rje pho nya'i dbang chen 'dis //
NK023('a)001:11984: sku dang bcas te bskur bar bya //
NK023('a)001:11985: pho nya rdo rje 'chang bdag mo //
NK023('a)001:11986: dkar dmar 'dzin byed zhags pa ma //
NK023('a)001:11988: rdo rje pho nya phra men ma //
NK023('a)001:11989: dkar mo me yi sgron khyer ma //
NK023('a)001:11990: don dang rtags su bcas te 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:11991: rdo rje pho nya myur byed ma //
