NK023('a)001:11992: dkar dmar glog gis zhags thogs te //
NK023('a)001:11993: gang gzung yid kyis 'debs par byed pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:11994: rdo rje pho nya sku dang bcas par dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:11995: rdo rje pho nya bskul byed ma //
NK023('a)001:11997: thugs dam bskul zhing phrin las byed pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:11998: rdo rje pho nyas dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:11999: rba na pho nya rdo rje gsal bkra mo //
NK023('a)001:12000: dkar mo rdo rje zhags 'phen ma //
NK023('a)001:12001: sus kyang mi bzlog thub par dka' //
NK023('a)001:12002: sku dang bcas te rdo rje pho nya yang dag mo //
NK023('a)001:12003: dkar dang dmar gyis lan phran 'debs //
NK023('a)001:12004: khams gsum sa dgu yud kyis khyab //
NK023('a)001:12005: rdo rje pho nya'i dbang chen 'dis //
NK023('a)001:12006: sku dang bcas te rdo rje pho nya rtse mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12007: dkar ser rdo rje rtse gcig 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12008: thugs dam dbang gis rtags ston ma //
NK023('a)001:12009: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12010: sku dang rtags su bcas rdo rje pho nya gnon mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:12011: dkar ser rdo rje phrag 'phen ma //
NK023('a)001:12012: ri rab rtse yang gnon byed pas //
NK023('a)001:12013: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12014: sku dang rtags su bcas rdo rje pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:12015: dmar ser dri shul gze mo 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:12016: dug gsum nad rnams 'joms byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12017: rdo rje thugs kyi dbang 'dir bskur bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:12018: rdo rje pho nya sre mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12019: dkar ser a ku dmar mo thogs //
NK023('a)001:12020: brdabs pa tsam gyis gang yang khug /
NK023('a)001:12021: rdo rje thugs kyi dbang yang bskur bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:12022: rba na rdo rje pho nya kha 'bar ma //
NK023('a)001:12023: dmar ser sprin gyis go zu can //
NK023('a)001:12024: kha nas me 'bar rgya mtsho skyems //
NK023('a)001:12025: rdo rje gsung gis pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12026: sku dang rtags su bcas te dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12027: rdo rje pho nya gsal bkra ma //
NK023('a)001:12029: gang la bya ba sa le bsal //
NK023('a)001:12030: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12031: sku dang rtags su bcas te dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12032: rdo rje pho nya khro mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12033: dkar ser khro mo'i gzugs 'chang bas //
NK023('a)001:12034: de bzhin lag na g.yang gzhi rdebs //
NK023('a)001:12035: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12036: sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya 'chang ba ni //
NK023('a)001:12037: dkar ser rdo rje phur bu 'chang //
NK023('a)001:12038: gang la bya ba'i snying la 'debs //
NK023('a)001:12039: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12040: sku dang rtags su bcas rdo rje pho nya gtum pa mo //
NK023('a)001:12041: dmar ser rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:12042: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis 'joms //
NK023('a)001:12043: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12044: sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya khros ma ni //
NK023('a)001:12045: dmar ser rdo rje be con 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:12046: khro bzhin gdong pa dpa' brtul che //
NK023('a)001:12047: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12048: sku dang rtags su bcas te khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:12049: rba na rdo rje pho nya las byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12050: dmar ser gcod pa'i ral gri 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:12051: sems can skye shi rtsad gcod pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12052: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12053: sku dang rtags su bcas te rdo rje pho nya dus mtshan mo //
NK023('a)001:12054: dmar ser lag na shag ti thogs //
NK023('a)001:12055: ma lus 'joms pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:12056: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12057: sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya thar pa mo //
NK023('a)001:12058: dmar ser lag na gtun shing brdegs //
NK023('a)001:12059: rdul du barloga pa'i las mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12060: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12061: sku dang rtags su bcas pas dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12062: rdo rje pho nya sku la ma /
NK023('a)001:12063: dmar ser lag na lcags kyu 'debs //
NK023('a)001:12064: ma lus 'dzin pa'i gying chen ma //
NK023('a)001:12065: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12066: sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya dpal 'bar ma //
NK023('a)001:12067: dmar ser ras kyi zhabs ma brdebs //
NK023('a)001:12068: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12069: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12070: sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya bskyod chen ma //
NK023('a)001:12071: dmar ser rlung gis rkyal pa thogs //
NK023('a)001:12072: bskal pa'i me chen rtogs pa yis //
NK023('a)001:12073: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12074: sku dang rtags su bcas rba na rdo rje pho nya lus khros ma //
NK023('a)001:12075: dkar ser lcags kyi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phros //
NK023('a)001:12076: ba spu sra mkhreg rdo rje'i sku //
NK023('a)001:12077: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12078: sku dang rdo rje pho nya ngag 'phrog mas //
NK023('a)001:12079: dmar ser lkugs byed lcags kyu can //
NK023('a)001:12080: smra ba ngag gis lce 'phrog ma //
NK023('a)001:12081: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12082: sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya yid gtum ma //
NK023('a)001:12083: dkar ser sen mos snying 'byin ma //
NK023('a)001:12084: thugs rjes bdud srin myos shing barlama //
NK023('a)001:12085: rdo rje thugs dang sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya sder chen mo //
NK023('a)001:12086: dmar ser ral pa'i g.yab mos 'debs //
NK023('a)001:12087: thugs rjes bsgral ba'i zhing bcu sgrol //
NK023('a)001:12088: rdo rje thugs sku dang rtags rdo rje pho nya gsod byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12089: dkar sngo dung gis zhags pa can //
NK023('a)001:12090: thugs rjes zhing bcu bsgrol la brtson //
NK023('a)001:12091: rdo rje thugs kyis sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya rlang pa mo //
NK023('a)001:12092: dkar sngo dung gi zhags pa bsnams //
NK023('a)001:12093: thugs rjes bdud dang srin po sgrol //
NK023('a)001:12094: rdo rje thugs kyi rba na rdo rje pho nya gsod pa mo //
NK023('a)001:12095: dkar sngo shel gyi gri thogs ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12096: gsod pa'i las la 'ba' zhig dges //
NK023('a)001:12097: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12098: sku dang rtags su bcas te dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12099: rdo rje pho nya za ba mo //
NK023('a)001:12100: dkar sngo mang pa zas su za //
NK023('a)001:12101: gti mug gtan nas zad mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:12102: rdo rje thugs sku dang rtags rdo rje pho nya khrag 'thung ma //
NK023('a)001:12103: dmar sngo ban d+ha'i thod khrag 'thung //
NK023('a)001:12104: 'dod chags gtan nas zad mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:12105: rdo rje thugs sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya 'cha' ba mo //
NK023('a)001:12106: dkar sngo king rus khral khrol 'cha' //
NK023('a)001:12107: zhe sdang gtan nas brlag mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:12108: rdo rje sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya tshe len mo //
NK023('a)001:12109: dkar sngo dar gyis g.yab 'dor ba //
NK023('a)001:12110: sdang ba dgra bo'i tshe len ma //
NK023('a)001:12111: rdo rje thugs sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya mdangs len mo //
NK023('a)001:12112: dkar sngo dung gis spar bu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:12113: gangs la dmigs pa'i mdangs 'phrog pas //
NK023('a)001:12114: rdo rje thugs sku dang rba na rba na a g+hu sha dza /
NK023('a)001:12115: rdo rje pho nya srog 'phrog ma //
NK023('a)001:12117: skad cig yud la nyams pa len //
NK023('a)001:12118: rdo rje thugs sku dang rdo rje pho nya snying 'byin ma //
NK023('a)001:12119: dkar sngo snying gis phreng ba bgrangs //
NK023('a)001:12120: rnam shes phung po gtan stobs ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12121: rdo rje thugs kyi sku dang rdo rje pho nya gcod byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12122: dkar ljang shel gyi dgra s+t+wa 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:12123: rgyud drug 'khor ba'i rtsad gcod ma /
NK023('a)001:12124: rdo rje thugs dang sku dang rdo rje pho nya bskul byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12125: dkar mo phyag na lcags kyu b+han //
NK023('a)001:12126: zhing bcu bsgral nas thugs dam bskul //
NK023('a)001:12127: rdo rje thugs sku dang rdo rje pho nya sna tshogs gzugs //
NK023('a)001:12128: bse'i ldan dkar zab slag gsol //
NK023('a)001:12129: ma lus sgrol ba'i bya ra ma //
NK023('a)001:12130: rdo rje thugs dang sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya snyon ma ni //
NK023('a)001:12131: dkar ljang shel gyi rdo rje 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12132: gzhan gyis mi thub drag shul che //
NK023('a)001:12133: rdo rje'i thugs sku dang rtags rba na rba na ang ku sha dza //
NK023('a)001:12134: rdo rje pho nya 'jug byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12135: dkar ljang phyag na khra thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12137: rdo rje'i thugs sku dang rtags rdo rje pho nya yid 'phrog ma //
NK023('a)001:12138: dkar ljang mtshon gyis gru gu thogs //
NK023('a)001:12140: rdo rje thugs sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya ro rkun ma //
NK023('a)001:12141: dkar ljang zhing gis ro khur ma //
NK023('a)001:12142: dur khrod bgegs kyi tshogs 'joms ma //
NK023('a)001:12143: rdo rje'i thugs sku dang rtags su pho nya rdo rje rdzun byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12144: dkar ljang rlung gis zhags pa 'debs //
NK023('a)001:12145: cir yang sprul pa'i sku gcig ma //
NK023('a)001:12146: rdo rje thugs kyi sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya 'jigs byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12147: dkar ljang dung gis mche ba 'byin //
NK023('a)001:12149: rdo rje'i thugs dang sku dang rtags su rdo rje pho nya bcud len ma //
NK023('a)001:12150: dkar ljang g.yu'i za ma tog /
NK023('a)001:12151: khams gsum tshe bsdud pho nya mo //
NK023('a)001:12152: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:12153: sku dang rtags su bcas te dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12154: rba na rba na a ku sha dza na /
NK023('a)001:12155: yang pho nya sum brgya drug cu'i las kyi pho nya 'jig rten pa 'dul ba'i don du /
NK023('a)001:12156: ye shes kyi pho nya dpal gyis 'od zer las
NK023('a)001:12157: sprul pa sum brgya drug cu po lugs gcig tu
NK023('a)001:12158: gzung 'dzin rtag chad kyi lta ba sum brgya drug
NK023('a)001:12160: srin po yi pho nya phyag brnyan ces dang /
NK023('a)001:12161: las kyi pho nya stong dang shar gshogs pa can
NK023('a)001:12162: brgya nyi shu dang lho dang nub sder mo can
NK023('a)001:12163: brgya nyi shu 'og mche ba can brgya nyi shu
NK023('a)001:12164: dang ye shes kyis pho nya yang dpal 'bar khro
NK023('a)001:12165: mo brgyud du / mthun par zhal gcig phyag bzhi ste /
NK023('a)001:12166: g.yas kyis dang bsnyeg byed kyi pho nya gshog pa can bsam gyis mi khyab pa bsnams la /
NK023('a)001:12167: 'og ma 'dzin byed kyi pho nya sder mo can bsam gyis mi khyab pa bsnams /
NK023('a)001:12168: g.yon dang po na sdom byed kyi pho nya mtshon cha bsam gyis mi khyab pa bsnams la /
NK023('a)001:12169: tha ma sgrol byed kyi pho nya mche ba can bsam gyis mi khyab pa bsnams pa /
NK023('a)001:12170: de rnams kyang dngos sum brgya dang drug cu la don bye ba khrag khrig ldan pa'o //
NK023('a)001:12172: myur ba glog mgyogs pa rlung dang /
NK023('a)001:12174: cig la'ang thogs pa med ces so //
NK023('a)001:12175: lho phyogs kyi khyams sor la pho nya ser ba
NK023('a)001:12176: ni sa bon dza dang h+aum gnyis gang rung bya
NK023('a)001:12177: / dgra dang gshin rje gdon 'dul phyir //
NK023('a)001:12178: 'jigs byed pho nya'i skur sprul pas //
NK023('a)001:12179: lho phyogs 'od zer ser po las //
NK023('a)001:12180: gser gyi mi mo drug cu 'byung //
NK023('a)001:12181: yon tan pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:12182: ser nag me'i zhags pa thogs //
NK023('a)001:12183: ci bgyi zhes kyang thogs pa med //
NK023('a)001:12184: pho nya 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12185: yon tan pho nya mkha' 'gro ma //
NK023('a)001:12186: ser nag sdigs mdzub gyad dor can //
NK023('a)001:12187: lhag la len cing bsgrubs la mgo //
NK023('a)001:12188: pho nya rin chen yon tan mthu 'bebs ma //
NK023('a)001:12189: dmar ser ba dan g.yab 'dor ma //
NK023('a)001:12190: sgrub pa po la mthu byin 'bebs //
NK023('a)001:12191: pho nya yon tan pho nya sra ba mo //
NK023('a)001:12192: ser gnag rdo rje go gyon pas //
NK023('a)001:12193: cis kyang mi tshugs rdo rje'i sku //
NK023('a)001:12194: pho nya yon tan pho nya 'chongs mo che //
NK023('a)001:12195: ser nag 'phyongs stabs byan lag thogs //
NK023('a)001:12196: ri rlungs kun sleb 'phyong byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12197: pho nya yon tan pho nya khro gtum can //
NK023('a)001:12198: ser nag sdang dmig stag la zhon //
NK023('a)001:12199: pho nya 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12200: ha la ha la pa sha h+aum //
NK023('a)001:12201: yon tan pho nya brtson byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12202: ser nag rlung gis zhags pa 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12203: gyen thur med par rgyug cing 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:12204: pho nya 'dis kyang yon tan pho nya 'jigs ma'i gdong //
NK023('a)001:12205: kha bgrad mche gtsigs lag gnyis gdengs //
NK023('a)001:12206: stobs chen mthu yang 'joms byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12207: pho nya yon tan pho nya sha zan ma //
NK023('a)001:12208: mi khog dbyug pa glad la bskor //
NK023('a)001:12209: mang sa za zhing bdud khyim 'joms //
NK023('a)001:12210: pho nya yon tan pho nya khrag 'thor ma //
NK023('a)001:12211: mi mgo phor pa barlona pa ru //
NK023('a)001:12212: mi snying khrag zhags blug cing 'thor //
NK023('a)001:12213: yon tan pho nya so gcig ma //
NK023('a)001:12214: rdo rje rtse gcig mda' 'phen ma //
NK023('a)001:12215: pho nya yon tan pho nya ral gsig ma //
NK023('a)001:12216: ser mo ral pa'i gos su can //
NK023('a)001:12217: g.yon sdig g.yas pa lcags kyus 'debs //
NK023('a)001:12219: rin chen pho nya 'khril byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12220: ser mo sngo dmar zhags pa 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12221: rdzu ni gnyen dang drung por rdzu //
NK023('a)001:12222: pho na 'dis kyang dbang yon tan pho nya 'dzul byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12223: ser mo gser gyis zangs gri thogs //
NK023('a)001:12224: rdzu ni sbrul dang sre mor rdzu //
NK023('a)001:12225: pho nya rin chen pho nya myur byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12226: ser mo mtshon gyi gru gu sdogs //
NK023('a)001:12227: rdzu ni 'ug pa srin byar rdzu //
NK023('a)001:12228: pho nya 'dis yon tan pho nya mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:12229: ser mo thog gi char 'bebs ma //
NK023('a)001:12230: gnam sa ri lung kun khyab ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12231: pho nya rin chen pho nya nag mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12232: nag mo ral pa'i zhags pa 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12233: khams gsum b+h+yo dang khus 'deb ma //
NK023('a)001:12234: pho nya yon tan pho nya rtogs byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12235: ser mo b+han d+ha barlona pa ru //
NK023('a)001:12236: dam rdzas rnam lnga za zhing spyod //
NK023('a)001:12237: pho nya ha la rin chen pho nya rtog med ma //
NK023('a)001:12238: ser mo dung gi gzhongs thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12239: gang la bcol yang tshig cing 'khrol //
NK023('a)001:12240: pho nya yon tan pho nya yangs pa ma //
NK023('a)001:12241: ser mo sprin gyis ga sha can //
NK023('a)001:12242: glog gis phreng ba glad la bskor //
NK023('a)001:12243: pho nya rin chen pho nya sna tshogs lus //
NK023('a)001:12244: dmar skya za 'og stod g.yog can //
NK023('a)001:12245: rnga mong ga par rdzu byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12246: pho nya yon tan pho nya sdang dmig la //
NK023('a)001:12247: dmar skya lcags kyi khrag thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12248: dgra dang bgegs la glog ltar 'dzugs //
NK023('a)001:12249: pho nya rin chen pho nya dur khrod ma //
NK023('a)001:12250: dmar skya zhing gi g.yang gzhi rdebs //
NK023('a)001:12251: mkhas pas dgra bgegs sgrol byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12252: pho nya yon tan pho nya migs 'gro ma //
NK023('a)001:12253: khyung la zhon cing glog zhags 'debs //
NK023('a)001:12254: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis 'grub //
NK023('a)001:12255: pho nya 'dis ha la ha la pa sha h+aum /
NK023('a)001:12256: rin chen pho nya bde 'gro ma //
NK023('a)001:12257: 'phyong gi phyan lag dmar po zhon //
NK023('a)001:12258: ser mo g.yu yi zor ba 'debs //
NK023('a)001:12259: pho nya yon tan pho nya brgyas byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12261: tshe dang phung por bcas pa 'joms //
NK023('a)001:12262: pho nya 'dis rin chen pho nya 'dzum byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12263: ser skya tshon gyis gru gu sdog /
NK023('a)001:12264: rdzu ni bu chung spre'ura rdzu //
NK023('a)001:12265: pho nya 'dis yon tan pho nya khrag myos ma //
NK023('a)001:12266: dmar mo mchu rings dur bya'i gdong //
NK023('a)001:12267: rtsa la rgyu zhing snying khrag 'thung //
NK023('a)001:12268: pho nya rin chen pho nya rngam tshig ma //
NK023('a)001:12269: mngag cing bcol pa'i las mchis na //
NK023('a)001:12270: rang la rang yang tshig cing 'khro //
NK023('a)001:12271: pho nya 'dis yon tan pho nya mgyogs byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12272: ser skya mgyogs ma rlung la zhon //
NK023('a)001:12273: gar kyang mi rtogs mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:12274: pho nya ha la rin chen pho nya gtum pa mo //
NK023('a)001:12275: dmar ser spu gris snying 'byin ma //
NK023('a)001:12276: nyams pa dgra bgegs dmyal thag chod //
NK023('a)001:12277: pho nya yon tan pho nya mdung thung 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12278: dkar mo g.yon sder g.yas mdung 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12279: bdud dang srin po tshar gcod ma //
NK023('a)001:12280: pho nya 'dis rin chen pho nya glog 'gyu ma //
NK023('a)001:12281: dmar ser glog gis zhags pa 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12282: nam mkha'i mthong nas 'grim te rgyug /
NK023('a)001:12283: pho nya yon tan pho nya thog 'bebs ma //
NK023('a)001:12284: dmar ser thog gi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro //
NK023('a)001:12285: rgya mtsho'i rting yang skyems par byed //
NK023('a)001:12286: pho nya rin chen pho nya spor byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12287: dmar ser zhing chen zhal du gsol //
NK023('a)001:12288: zhing bcu gtan nas len byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12289: pho nya rin chen pho nya 'khrug byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12290: ri rab rtse nas 'joms byed pas //
NK023('a)001:12292: pho nya h+aum ha la ha la pa sha h+aum /
NK023('a)001:12293: yon tan pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:12294: smyug nag dur khrod khrag 'thung ma //
NK023('a)001:12295: sgrol byed snying 'byin gri thogs ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12296: pho nyas 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12297: rin chen pho nya ka ma la //
NK023('a)001:12298: mdzub mo ri rab rtse la g.yengs //
NK023('a)001:12299: rkang pa rgya mtsho'i gting nas 'khrugs //
NK023('a)001:12300: pho nya rin chen pho nya gsal bkra ma //
NK023('a)001:12301: dmar ser nyi zer zhags pa 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12302: gang ltar song yang mi rtogs te //
NK023('a)001:12303: pho nya yon tan pho nya kha sgyur ma //
NK023('a)001:12304: dmar ser dung gi rgo ba zhon //
NK023('a)001:12305: ri lung med par rjes kyis 'gengs //
NK023('a)001:12306: pho nya 'dis rin chen pho nya kun sgrol ma //
NK023('a)001:12307: dmar ljang ral gris glad la bskor //
NK023('a)001:12308: so bya sram dang chu bya sbrul //
NK023('a)001:12309: pho nya yon tan pho nya kha bsgyur myos byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12310: dmar ljang ra ro smyo rdzu can //
NK023('a)001:12311: dkar dmar snying gi mtshams nas 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:12312: pho nya ha la rin chen pho nya khrag 'thung ma //
NK023('a)001:12313: dmar ljang thod khrag zhal du gsol //
NK023('a)001:12315: pho nya yon tan pho nya 'bar ma ni //
NK023('a)001:12316: dmar ljang rin chen 'bar ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:12318: pho nya 'dis rin chen pho nya mi bzad ma //
NK023('a)001:12320: skye 'gro gnyis kyang rtsa ba gcod //
NK023('a)001:12321: pho nya yon tan pho nya 'phrog byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12324: pho nya rin chen pho nya sgrol byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12326: ma lus sgrol ba'i mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:12327: pho nya yon tan pho nya sna tshogs stobs //
NK023('a)001:12328: ser ljang zhing gis rkang lag 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:12329: dug gsum ma lus zhal du gsol //
NK023('a)001:12330: pho nya ha la ha la rin chen pho nya yid 'phrog ma //
NK023('a)001:12331: ser ljang na chung tshul du bardzu //
NK023('a)001:12333: pho nya yon tan pho nya srog len ma //
NK023('a)001:12334: mi snying rus pa'i zhags pa 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12335: zhing bcu gtan nas len par byed //
NK023('a)001:12336: pho nya rin chen pho nya bcud len ma //
NK023('a)001:12337: ser smyug zangs kyi mchu rings ma //
NK023('a)001:12339: pho nya 'dis yon tan pho nya tshe 'dzin ma //
NK023('a)001:12341: dza dmar pho nyas tshe rkun ma //
NK023('a)001:12342: pho nya 'dis rin chen pho nya dbang mo che //
NK023('a)001:12343: ser smug seng ge dkar po zhon //
NK023('a)001:12344: nyi zla rgyus pa'i zhags pa 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12345: pho nya yon tan pho nya dreg 'joms ma //
NK023('a)001:12347: myur ba'i shugs 'chang thungs rje che //
NK023('a)001:12348: pho nya ha la ha la pa sha h+aum //
NK023('a)001:12350: rin chen pho nya bdud byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12351: dam tshig nyams pa'i bdud du 'babs //
NK023('a)001:12352: dge spyod rnams kyi dpal du che //
NK023('a)001:12353: pho nya yon tan pho nya bla 'dzin ma //
NK023('a)001:12354: dgra bo bla yi gnyen por che //
NK023('a)001:12355: ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin du sprul //
NK023('a)001:12356: pho nya rin chen pho nya srog 'dzin ma //
NK023('a)001:12357: ser smug lcags kyu'i phyag rgya can //
NK023('a)001:12358: sems can kun gyi tshe srog 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:12359: pho nya yon tan pho nya rtsa 'gro ma //
NK023('a)001:12360: sum brgya drug cu'i rtsa la rgyu //
NK023('a)001:12361: dam nyams dgra bgegs rtsa rgyus 'brel //
NK023('a)001:12362: pho nya rin chen pho nya gnas 'byin ma //
NK023('a)001:12364: sa dgu gting nas 'joms par byed //
NK023('a)001:12365: pho nya yon tan pho nya gnas bstod ma //
NK023('a)001:12366: thugs rje chen pos gang bsgral ba //
NK023('a)001:12367: byang chub thar lam bde la 'god //
NK023('a)001:12368: pho nya ha la e shwa ra swa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:12369: nub phyogs kyi khyams dmar pho nya dmar ba ni /
NK023('a)001:12370: sa bon dza dang bam gang rung ngo //
NK023('a)001:12371: thugs rjes 'jigs byed skur sprul pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12372: dgra dang klu gdon 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:12373: nub phyogs 'od zer dmar po las //
NK023('a)001:12374: zangs kyi mi mo drug cu sprul //
NK023('a)001:12375: gsung gi mi mo thog 'bebs ma //
NK023('a)001:12376: dmar nag lag na thog chen 'bebs //
NK023('a)001:12377: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis bsreg /
NK023('a)001:12378: pho nya'i dbang mchog 'di yang sbyin //
NK023('a)001:12380: dmar nag 'brug chen chibs su chibs //
NK023('a)001:12381: stong gsum kun grags mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:12382: pho nya'i dbang gsung gi pho nya char 'bebs ma //
NK023('a)001:12383: dmar nag sprin chen glog pa can //
NK023('a)001:12384: dug dang bdud rtsi char 'bebs ma //
NK023('a)001:12385: pho nya'i pad+ma'i pho nya 'od 'gyod ma //
NK023('a)001:12387: mun pa'i nang nas sgron gsal ma //
NK023('a)001:12388: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya bkrag gsal ma //
NK023('a)001:12389: dmar nag g.yu yi lan phran can //
NK023('a)001:12390: 'jig rten khams kyis dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:12391: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya gzhan tshon ma //
NK023('a)001:12392: dmar nag gzhan tshon zhags pa thogs //
NK023('a)001:12393: rdzu 'phrul ces kyang mi thub pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12394: pho nya'i dbang gar rdza gar rdza spo ta bam /
NK023('a)001:12397: phrin las myur mgyogs thogs pa med //
NK023('a)001:12398: pho nya'i dbang mchog 'di yang sbyin //
NK023('a)001:12399: pad ma'i pho nya 'od gsal ma //
NK023('a)001:12400: dmar nag me 'od phyag na bsnams //
NK023('a)001:12401: 'khor ba'i bag chags bsreg mdzad ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12402: gsung gi pho nya khrag 'thung ma //
NK023('a)001:12403: dmar nag thod khrag skom du 'thung //
NK023('a)001:12404: ma lus yongs kyi khrag 'thung ma //
NK023('a)001:12405: pho nya pad ma'i pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:12406: dmar nag rdo rje pad+ma can //
NK023('a)001:12407: srid pa gsum na mthu dbang che //
NK023('a)001:12408: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya sa bdag mo //
NK023('a)001:12409: dmar sngo lcags kyi phag mgo thogs //
NK023('a)001:12410: sa chen dgu yang 'khrug byed cing //
NK023('a)001:12411: pho nya pad+ma pho nya 'gugs byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12412: dmar sngo rdo rje lcags kyu can //
NK023('a)001:12414: pho nya'i gar rdza gsung gi pho nya dkar sham mo //
NK023('a)001:12416: nyams pa'i khrag 'thung dbang mo che //
NK023('a)001:12417: pho nya'i dbang mchog 'di yang sbyin //
NK023('a)001:12418: pad ma'i pho nya sgra sgrogs ni //
NK023('a)001:12419: dmar sngo zhing gi rnge'u chung brdung //
NK023('a)001:12420: sgra chen bdud bzhi zil gyis gnon //
NK023('a)001:12421: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya yid gzhung ma //
NK023('a)001:12422: dmar sngo lag na khu tshur 'chang //
NK023('a)001:12423: 'khor ba gnas nas spor mdzad ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12424: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya lta na mdzes //
NK023('a)001:12425: sngo dmar me tog chun 'phyangs can //
NK023('a)001:12426: yid 'ong phrin las kun mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:12427: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya sems 'phrog ma //
NK023('a)001:12428: dmar sngo g.yu yi nyi ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:12429: ma lus kun gyi snying 'byin ma //
NK023('a)001:12430: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya bdud 'bebs ma //
NK023('a)001:12431: dmar sngo mi thod rta thod thogs //
NK023('a)001:12433: pho nya'i gardza gsung gi pho nya mgyogs byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12434: dmar sngo khyung chen chibs su chib //
NK023('a)001:12435: zil gyis gnon pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK023('a)001:12436: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya gsod skyon ma //
NK023('a)001:12437: dmar sngo seng zhon mdung thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12438: gang la dmigs par yud kyis phyin //
NK023('a)001:12440: gsung gi pho nya snying 'byin ma //
NK023('a)001:12441: dmar ljang lag na tsit+ta thogs //
NK023('a)001:12443: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya dmar 'thung ma //
NK023('a)001:12444: dmar ljang dung chen khrag 'thung ma //
NK023('a)001:12445: khams gsum yongs kyi snying khrag 'thung //
NK023('a)001:12446: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya rkang 'jib ma //
NK023('a)001:12447: dmar ljang dbyi'i mgo bo can //
NK023('a)001:12448: zas su rkang dang bcud 'jib ma //
NK023('a)001:12449: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya las byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12450: dmar ljang 'brug sngon chibs su chibs //
NK023('a)001:12452: pho nya'i gardza gsung gi pho nya zhags thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12453: sngon mo zhags thogs rlung la zhon //
NK023('a)001:12454: khyod kyis mi gzigs gang yang med //
NK023('a)001:12455: pho nya'i dbang pad ma'i pho nya barla 'phrog ma //
NK023('a)001:12456: dmar skya skyi ser ngad la zhon //
NK023('a)001:12457: sku la ris gsal dkris mdzad ma //
NK023('a)001:12459: gsung gi pho nya thogs med ma //
NK023('a)001:12460: dmar ljang ral gri rnon po thogs //
NK023('a)001:12461: dam las 'gal ba sgrol byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12462: pho nya pad ma'i pho nya za byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12463: dmar ljang stag chen sder mang zhon //
NK023('a)001:12464: rtsang rme med par za byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12465: pho nya gsung gi pho nya myos byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12466: dmar ljang lcags kyi tho ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:12467: mgo dang klad pa 'gom byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12468: pho nya pad ma'i pho nya snyug byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12469: dmar ljang lcags kyi d+r+wa ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:12470: gang la byas pa 'dzin cing sdom //
NK023('a)001:12471: pho nya'i gardza gsung gi pho nya rdzu byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12472: dmar ser ra skyes khams pa zhon //
NK023('a)001:12473: cir yang sprul cing rdzu byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12474: pho nya'i dbang mchog 'di yang sbyin //
NK023('a)001:12475: pad ma'i pho nya 'khrug byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12476: dmar ser rgya mtsho rngub kyis 'debs //
NK023('a)001:12477: klu yi gnas kyang 'joms par byed //
NK023('a)001:12478: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya drag mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12479: dmar ser gtum pa dom la zhon //
NK023('a)001:12480: gti mug dregs pa 'joms byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12481: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya bskam ma ni //
NK023('a)001:12482: dmar ser khrag gi lan phran can //
NK023('a)001:12483: ma lus 'joms pa'i mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:12484: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya 'joms ma ni //
NK023('a)001:12485: dmar ser spang ti'i mgo bo can //
NK023('a)001:12486: gti mug klag chen 'dral byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12487: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya rab dga' ma //
NK023('a)001:12488: dmar ser lag na zangs gri thogs //
NK023('a)001:12490: pho nya'i gardza gsung gi pho nya 'dzin ma ni //
NK023('a)001:12491: dmar ser sbrul nag zhags pa 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12493: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya glog 'gyu ma //
NK023('a)001:12494: dmar ser rdzu 'phrul khra thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12495: dam las log pa'i snying 'byin ma //
NK023('a)001:12496: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya yul 'joms ma //
NK023('a)001:12497: dmar ser lag na sha te thogs //
NK023('a)001:12498: dgra dang bdud kyi dpung 'joms ma //
NK023('a)001:12499: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya lha 'brel ma //
NK023('a)001:12500: dmar ser rdo rje thog 'bebs ma //
NK023('a)001:12501: srid pa gsum yang rtse nas 'joms //
NK023('a)001:12502: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya srog 'brel ma //
NK023('a)001:12503: dmar smug 'joms pa'i ka ta ri //
NK023('a)001:12504: gsod cing 'joms pa'i pho nya ste //
NK023('a)001:12505: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya myur byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12506: dmar smug glog gi ga zha can //
NK023('a)001:12507: thugs rje shug 'chang pho nya ste //
NK023('a)001:12508: pho nya'i dbang gardza gardza spo ta bam /
NK023('a)001:12509: gsung gi pho nya rings byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12510: bud med lus la 'chongs mo che //
NK023('a)001:12511: ri sul med par rjes kyis 'gyengs //
NK023('a)001:12512: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya sreg byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12513: dmar smyug lag na gri thogs shing //
NK023('a)001:12514: mtha' yas sems can sgrol la mkhas //
NK023('a)001:12515: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya glog byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12516: dmar smug rdo rje be con gyis //
NK023('a)001:12517: khams gsum rdul du barloga byed ma /
NK023('a)001:12518: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya tho ba ma //
NK023('a)001:12519: dmar smug rdo rje tho ba 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:12520: khams gsum bdud dang srin po 'joms //
NK023('a)001:12521: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya gtun khung ma //
NK023('a)001:12522: dmar smug lag na gtun khung thogs //
NK023('a)001:12523: che chung med par 'joms pa yi //
NK023('a)001:12524: pho nya pad ma'i pho nya zhags pa 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12525: dmar smug bdud kyi zhags pa yis //
NK023('a)001:12526: gang la dmigs pa 'dzin byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12527: pho nya'i dbang gardza gardza spo ta bam /
NK023('a)001:12528: gsung gi pho nya me khyer ma //
NK023('a)001:12529: dmar smug dur khrod me chen gyis //
NK023('a)001:12530: phyi nang med par bsreg byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12531: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya bsdud byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12532: dmar smug gser gyi phreng ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:12533: dug gsum zhal du bsdud byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12534: pho nya'i dbang gsung gi pho nya g.yengs byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12535: dmar skya rlung gis 'khor lo thogs //
NK023('a)001:12536: ri rab gling bzhi g.yengs byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12537: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya bsdus 'joms ma //
NK023('a)001:12538: dmar skya gtun dang tho ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:12539: lnga phung rdul du rlog ma yin //
NK023('a)001:12541: gsung gi pho nya dpal mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12542: dmar skya srid pa'i dpal 'phrog ma //
NK023('a)001:12543: gser yu spel ma'i na bza' gsol //
NK023('a)001:12544: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:12545: rdo rje rtse gsum thod khrag 'thung //
NK023('a)001:12546: srid pa gsum na dbang chen grags //
NK023('a)001:12547: pho nya'i gardza gsung gi pho nya grags pa mo //
NK023('a)001:12548: dmar skya mi mgo dung du 'bud //
NK023('a)001:12549: stong khams gdug pa rdul du barloga /
NK023('a)001:12550: pho nya'i dbang pad ma'i pho nya gtum bag can //
NK023('a)001:12552: gang la babs kyang thogs med pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12553: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya ka ma ya //
NK023('a)001:12554: dmar skya ka ma la'i mtshon thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12555: ma lus 'joms pa'i mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:12556: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya sde tshogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12557: pad ma'i khrag gi char 'bebs ma //
NK023('a)001:12558: ma mo 'bum sde bran du khol //
NK023('a)001:12559: pho nya'i gsung gi pho nya ha la'i gdong //
NK023('a)001:12560: mi bzad mthu chen mdud rtsi thogs //
NK023('a)001:12561: ha la ha la'i dug kyang 'joms //
NK023('a)001:12562: pho nya'i pad ma'i pho nya rab brjid ma //
NK023('a)001:12563: mi 'go sna gsum phreng bar bgrangs //
NK023('a)001:12564: glad la bskor bas dgra bgegs rgyas //
NK023('a)001:12565: pho nya'i gardza gardza spo ta bam /
NK023('a)001:12566: byang phyogs kyi khyams ljang pho nya ljang ku ni /
NK023('a)001:12567: sa bon dza'am ho gang rung ngo //
NK023('a)001:12568: dgra dang gnod sbyin 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:12569: 'jigs byed pho nya skur sprul pa //
NK023('a)001:12570: byang phyogs 'od zer ljang khu las //
NK023('a)001:12571: g.yu yi mi mo drug cu sprul //
NK023('a)001:12572: las kyi pho nya rdo rje ma //
NK023('a)001:12573: ljang sngon rdo rje rgya gram thogs //
NK023('a)001:12574: phrin las rnam bzhi pho nyar mdzad //
NK023('a)001:12575: pho nya'i sku 'dis dbang sbyin no //
NK023('a)001:12576: phrin las 'joms ma chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12577: ljang sngon khyung gis khra thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12578: gti mug klu la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK023('a)001:12579: pho nya'i sku 'dis dbang sbyin no //
NK023('a)001:12580: phrin las kha lo 'dul mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:12581: ljang sngon dred kyis g.yang gzhi rdebs //
NK023('a)001:12583: pho nya'i sku 'dis phrin las pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:12584: ljang sngon thod rlon khrag gis bkang //
NK023('a)001:12585: 'brog chen g.yag mo khal du zhon //
NK023('a)001:12586: pho nya'i sku las kyi pho nya grub byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12587: ljang sngon mi mgo drung du 'bud //
NK023('a)001:12588: khams gsum ma lus sgras 'gyeng ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12589: pho nya'i sku phrin las pho nya bskul pa ma //
NK023('a)001:12590: ljang sngon snyan pa'i dbyug pas 'debs //
NK023('a)001:12591: thugs dam gnyen po rgyud bskul bas //
NK023('a)001:12592: pho nya'i sku pa tsa pa tsa g+han d+he ho /
NK023('a)001:12593: e shwa ra sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:12594: las kyi pho nya grub pa mo //
NK023('a)001:12596: phrin las nan tan mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:12597: pho nya 'dis kyang dbang sbyin no //
NK023('a)001:12598: phrin las pho nya mthar phyin pa //
NK023('a)001:12599: ljang smug g.yu yi thor tshugs can //
NK023('a)001:12600: las su bcol na kun kyang 'grub //
NK023('a)001:12601: pho nya'i sku las kyi pho nya mthar phyin pas //
NK023('a)001:12602: ljang smug rdo rje rgya gram thogs //
NK023('a)001:12603: las su bcol ba mthar phyin pas //
NK023('a)001:12604: pho nya'i sku phrin las pho nya chud mi za //
NK023('a)001:12605: ljang sngon dung gi mche ba can //
NK023('a)001:12606: mgyogs pa'i las la chud mi za //
NK023('a)001:12607: pho nya'i las las kyi pho nya dbang bskur ma //
NK023('a)001:12608: ljang dmar chu srin rgyal mtshan thogs //
NK023('a)001:12610: pho nya'i sku phrin las pho nya thogs med ma //
NK023('a)001:12611: 'dabs chags bya yi rgyal po zhon //
NK023('a)001:12612: 'jigs su rung ba'i mtshon cha phyar //
NK023('a)001:12613: pho nya'i sku pa tsa sngags 'gre /
NK023('a)001:12614: las kyi pho nya grub pa mo //
NK023('a)001:12615: dmar ljang shel gyi za ma tog /
NK023('a)001:12616: dgra yi dbang dang dngos grub 'phrog /
NK023('a)001:12617: pho nya 'dis kyang phrin las pho nya gsal byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12618: ljang dmar me yi zhags pa 'phen /
NK023('a)001:12619: mun pa'i smag nas 'dren byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12620: pho nya las kyi pho nya dbang byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12621: dmar ljang rdo rje lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:12622: spra dang byi la'i sprul 'gyed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12623: pho nya las kyi pho nya dam tshig ma //
NK023('a)001:12624: ljang dmar me zhags sdigs mdzub can //
NK023('a)001:12625: dam nyams kun gyi rjes gcod ma //
NK023('a)001:12626: pho nya phrin las pho nya bya ra ma //
NK023('a)001:12627: lcags kyi bya khra g.yu mig ma //
NK023('a)001:12628: bltas pas mthong zhing mthong bas 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:12629: pho nya las kyi pho nya stangs 'dzin ma //
NK023('a)001:12630: dmar ljang rtsis kyi byang bu thogs //
NK023('a)001:12631: legs nyes kun gyi ltangs 'dzin ma //
NK023('a)001:12633: yang pho nya mo zhes lung a nu shes rab
NK023('a)001:12634: ma rgyud gtso bor smos na'ang shugs ma mo sum
NK023('a)001:12635: brgya drug cu / pho nya sum brgya drug cu
NK023('a)001:12636: sdom pa bdun brgya nyi shu pa'ang phrag stong ni
NK023('a)001:12637: bdun 'bum nyi khri zhes bsdus par bshad /
NK023('a)001:12638: phrin las pho nya sdangs gcod ma //
NK023('a)001:12639: ljang dmar rtsis kyi khram thogs pas //
NK023('a)001:12640: dge sdig gnyis kyi sdang gcod ma //
NK023('a)001:12641: pho nya 'dis las kyi pho nya gal 'dzin ma //
NK023('a)001:12643: pham rgyal gnyis kyi gal 'dzin pas //
NK023('a)001:12644: pho nya las kyi pho nya bskul byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12645: ljang ser lcags kyi mda' 'phen ma //
NK023('a)001:12646: gnam sa kun kyang bskul bar byed //
NK023('a)001:12647: pho nya phrin las pho na dbang mo'i sku //
NK023('a)001:12648: ljang ser khrag gi phor pa thogs //
NK023('a)001:12649: ma thogs las la myur byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12650: pho nya las kyi pho nya phag mgo ni //
NK023('a)001:12651: ljang ser phag mgo tho ba 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:12652: che chung med par rdul du barloga /
NK023('a)001:12653: phrin las pho nya spyan brgya mo //
NK023('a)001:12654: mgo lus med par mig gis gang //
NK023('a)001:12655: stong khams ma lus gsal zhing bkra //
NK023('a)001:12657: las kyi pho nya mig stong ldan //
NK023('a)001:12658: dbu stong phyag stong spyan yang stong //
NK023('a)001:12659: stong gsum stong la dbang cher grags //
NK023('a)001:12660: pho nya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12661: phrin las pho nya 'od mgyogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12663: bltas pas mi mngon gang yang med //
NK023('a)001:12664: pho nya las kyi pho nya rlung zhon ma //
NK023('a)001:12665: lag na lcags kyi dgra sta bsnams //
NK023('a)001:12666: rlung nag 'tshubs ma chibs su chibs //
NK023('a)001:12667: pho nya phrin las pho nya rdzu 'phrul can //
NK023('a)001:12668: sbrul nag stong gi zhags pa 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12669: ltas ngan rnga mong ga pa zhon //
NK023('a)001:12670: pho nya las kyi pho nya sgyu ma mo //
NK023('a)001:12671: cir yang ma nges gzugs su ston //
NK023('a)001:12672: ched 'ga' chu sprin sbrul gyi lus //
NK023('a)001:12673: pho nya phrin las pho nya dbang phyug rgyal //
NK023('a)001:12674: ljang ser mdung rtse gsum pa 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:12675: dug gsum rtsad nas len byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12676: pho nya'i sku 'dis pa tsa las kyi pho nya grag rgyal ma //
NK023('a)001:12677: ljang nag stag zhon dred kyi mgo //
NK023('a)001:12679: pho nya 'dis phrin las pho nya dpal sham ma //
NK023('a)001:12680: dmar gyi gtor ma glad la bskor //
NK023('a)001:12681: khrag gi gtor ma zhags par 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12682: pho nya las kyi pho nya yak+sha mo //
NK023('a)001:12683: ljang nag gnod sbyin mgo bo thogs //
NK023('a)001:12684: gang la bya ba'i thod zor 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12685: phrin las pho nya khro bag can //
NK023('a)001:12686: bud med gzugs la skyes pa'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:12688: pho nya las kyi pho nya mche ba mo //
NK023('a)001:12689: lag gnyis rdo rje mche ba 'debs //
NK023('a)001:12690: gzung bas mi zin gang yang med //
NK023('a)001:12691: pho nya phrin las pho nya dbang bsgyur ma //
NK023('a)001:12692: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya can //
NK023('a)001:12693: kun gyi mnga' bdag dbang mo che //
NK023('a)001:12694: pho nya 'dis kyang pa tsa pa tsa g+han d+he ho //
NK023('a)001:12695: phrin las pho nya dngos grub bdag /
NK023('a)001:12696: ljang nag 'dod spyod lnga la rol //
NK023('a)001:12697: dngos grub rnam gsum dus 'dir stsol //
NK023('a)001:12698: pho nya'i sku 'dis pho nya sgrol byed chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12699: ljang nag gcod pa'i phal tshab bsnams //
NK023('a)001:12700: gang yang gson par mi byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12701: pho nya las kyi pho nya mnga' bdag mo //
NK023('a)001:12702: srid gsum grags pa'i rnge'u chung brdung //
NK023('a)001:12703: ma lus gdug pa zil gyis gnon //
NK023('a)001:12704: pho nya phrin las pho nya 'od 'phro ma //
NK023('a)001:12705: ljang nag gcod pa'i shag ti thogs //
NK023('a)001:12707: pho nya las kyi pho nya drag mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12708: ljang smug gru gsum mthing nag thogs //
NK023('a)001:12709: drag po las kyi pho nya ma //
NK023('a)001:12710: pho nya phrin las pho nya khro rkyen ma //
NK023('a)001:12711: ljang smug ral pas sa la rdebs //
NK023('a)001:12712: rang la rang yang tshig cing 'gro //
NK023('a)001:12713: pho nya'i sku pa tsa e shwa ra las kyi pho nya myur 'grub ma //
NK023('a)001:12714: 'jam dpal rnon pos lag na thogs //
NK023('a)001:12715: ha ha ru lu sgra sgrogs ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12716: phyag rgya'i sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12717: phrin las pho nya chud ma zos //
NK023('a)001:12718: ljang smug rin chen sgron me thogs //
NK023('a)001:12719: gdung bas brtse zhing phan gnon pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12720: pho nya las kyi pho nya 'dul byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12721: ljang smug srin po'i thod pa thod //
NK023('a)001:12722: khyod kyis mi 'dul gang yang med //
NK023('a)001:12723: phyag rgya'i phrin las pho nya rgya mtsho ma //
NK023('a)001:12724: sna tshogs lus can rgya mtsho barloga /
NK023('a)001:12725: 'dzam bu gling bzhi g.yo byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12726: phyag rgya'i las kyi pho nya ltung 'dzin ma //
NK023('a)001:12727: sems can zhing bcu bsgral ba la //
NK023('a)001:12728: dmyal bar ltung nges lcags kyus 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:12729: phyag rgya'i phrin las pho nya sgrol byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12731: brdul du barloga pa'i las mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12732: phyag rgya'i pa tsa pa tsa las kyi pho nya rang dbang mo //
NK023('a)001:12734: 'jig rten las kyi gnyen gcig ma //
NK023('a)001:12735: phyag rgya 'di yis phrin las pho nya 'dul mkhan ma //
NK023('a)001:12736: skyes bu na chung gzugs 'chang ma //
NK023('a)001:12737: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'dul //
NK023('a)001:12738: phyag rgya las kyi pho nya goms pa mo //
NK023('a)001:12739: ljang khu nyungs kyis mda' 'phen ma //
NK023('a)001:12740: dkar nag snying gi mtshams su brdegs //
NK023('a)001:12741: phyag rgya'i phrin las pho nya 'dul la mkhas //
NK023('a)001:12743: log pa'i phyogs rnams bzlog byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12744: phyag rgya'i las kyi pho nya dbang bsgyur ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12745: nyi zla gza' skar glog par gyon //
NK023('a)001:12746: 'dzam bu gling bzhi lag par thogs //
NK023('a)001:12747: phyag rgya phrin las pho nya mchog sgrol ma //
NK023('a)001:12749: skye shi gnyis kyi rtsad gcod ma //
NK023('a)001:12750: phyag rgya'i dbang 'dis khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:12751: pa tsa a shwa ra las kyi pho nya rgyu sgrol ma //
NK023('a)001:12752: thugs dam gnyen po rgyud bskul phyir //
NK023('a)001:12753: shel dang lung tang yu bu bsnams //
NK023('a)001:12754: phyag rgya'i sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12755: phrin las pho nya rngam pa mo //
NK023('a)001:12756: ljang skya sha khrag barlona par za //
NK023('a)001:12757: gsod pa'i las la shin tu rngams //
NK023('a)001:12758: phyag rgya'i las kyi phyag rgya spro rkyen ma //
NK023('a)001:12759: ljang skya 'debs pa'i las la myur //
NK023('a)001:12760: dza dza ha ho'i sgra 'debs ma //
NK023('a)001:12761: phyag rgya'i phrin las pho nya gtum chen ma //
NK023('a)001:12763: gtum pas 'dod khams lha mi can //
NK023('a)001:12764: phyag rgya'i las kyi pho nya mig dmar ma //
NK023('a)001:12765: khrag gis 'chang gis myos par byed //
NK023('a)001:12766: mig rtsa dmar la ra gdongs che //
NK023('a)001:12767: phyag rgya'i phrin las pho nya sen mo can //
NK023('a)001:12768: dmar smug sen mo lcags kyu gtams //
NK023('a)001:12769: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu 'dzin byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12770: phyag rgya'i sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12771: pa tsa pa tsa g+han d+he ho /
NK023('a)001:12772: e shwa ra sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:12773: pho nya phyogs bzhi dang 'og phyogs ma mo la yang sgo mdzad pa ltar na /
NK023('a)001:12774: sgo ma lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu'o //
NK023('a)001:12775: 'og phyogs kyi khyams 'od zer smug po'am phrin las kyi ljang gu'ang mdzad pa la ni /
NK023('a)001:12776: ma ma shwa ra h+aum dza /
NK023('a)001:12777: zhes bkra shis pa dang zhi ba dang rgyas pa dang dge bar gsungs /
NK023('a)001:12778: sa bon dza dang ma gang rung ste h+aum dza
NK023('a)001:12779: zhes pho nya yang ye shes kyi pho nya dang
NK023('a)001:12780: / las kyi pho nya gnyis byed na'ang h+aum zhes la 'adu'o //
NK023('a)001:12787: mtha' 'og chos dbyings ye shes kyi rtags 'od kha dog tu bshad /
NK023('a)001:12788: khams gsum srid gsum thams cad kyis //
NK023('a)001:12789: dgra dang 'byung po bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:12790: sku yi 'od zer smug nag las //
NK023('a)001:12791: las byed ma mo drug cur sprul //
NK023('a)001:12792: ral pa gcig mthong 'jig pa'i gzugs //
NK023('a)001:12793: dri shul ral gri dril bu nad rkyal thogs //
NK023('a)001:12794: ma mo 'di'i dbang yang bskur bar bya'o //
NK023('a)001:12795: sbas pa'i ma mo thal mdog thod khrag 'thung //
NK023('a)001:12796: g.yang gzhi dur khrod rgyan gyis mdzes par klubs //
NK023('a)001:12797: srid pa gsum na mthu che rtsal drag pas //
NK023('a)001:12798: ma mo 'di'i dbang dur khrod tshogs kyi ma mo ral pa can //
NK023('a)001:12799: mi thod phreng bas sku brgyan rab tu brjid //
NK023('a)001:12800: khams gsum 'di na mthu chen khyod la 'dud //
NK023('a)001:12801: ma mo 'di'i za byed rngams pa'i ma mo chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12802: mthing skya khrag gi ral pa gos su gyon //
NK023('a)001:12803: phyag gis skye 'gro yongs kyi tsit+ta bzung //
NK023('a)001:12804: ma mo 'di'i khams gsum sdud pa'i ma mo chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12805: dmar mo thod khrag skom du 'thung byed pas //
NK023('a)001:12806: nga rgyal dregs pa'i 'khor kyang 'joms byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:12807: ma mo 'di'i rgyu drug sgrol ba'i ma mo chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12808: smug nag me 'bar g.yang gzhi gos su gyon //
NK023('a)001:12809: mi snying rus pa'i phreng ba klad la bskor //
NK023('a)001:12810: ma mo 'di'i srid gsum za byed ma mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12811: dmar nag gnam sa gnyis kyang gos su gyon //
NK023('a)001:12812: bdud dang srin po'i tshogs kyang 'dar zhing 'dud //
NK023('a)001:12813: ma mo 'di'i dbang srid gsum yongs la dbang bsgyur ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12814: ser nag nyi zla thod du bcings //
NK023('a)001:12815: gnam sa gnyis la dbang byed ba'i //
NK023('a)001:12816: ma mo mthu dpung bsnyems pa'i ma mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12817: ljang nag zhing gi go zu gsol //
NK023('a)001:12818: lag pa g.yas pa nam mkhar 'degs //
NK023('a)001:12819: ma mo khros zhing khrag 'thung gsur la dga' //
NK023('a)001:12820: mi sha rta sha zas su za //
NK023('a)001:12821: mi khrag rta khrag skom du 'thung //
NK023('a)001:12822: ma mo ma ma shwa ra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:12823: sgrol byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12825: phrin las dam nyams sgrol la brtson //
NK023('a)001:12826: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang yang bskur //
NK023('a)001:12827: za byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12828: tshe srog 'phrog pa'i ma mo ste //
NK023('a)001:12829: sngo nag g.yu yi za ma tog /
NK023('a)001:12830: nyams pa len cing sgrubs la stobs //
NK023('a)001:12831: ma mo 'di'i dbang ma ma shwa ra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:12833: rngam byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12834: 'phyo la dga' ba'i ma mo ste //
NK023('a)001:12835: nam mkha'i 'brug sngon chibs su chibs //
NK023('a)001:12836: dgra dang nyams pa'i snying 'byin ma //
NK023('a)001:12837: ma mo 'dzin byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12838: 'jigs byed zhal du ston pa'i ma //
NK023('a)001:12839: ser nag thod khrag lcags kyu thogs //
NK023('a)001:12840: ma lus sgrol ba'i gying chen mo //
NK023('a)001:12841: ma mo 'di'i bgegs chen 'joms pa'i ma mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12842: snying la 'debs pa'i ma mo ste //
NK023('a)001:12843: sngo nag spu gri tho ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:12844: bgegs kyis rgyal po snying la 'debs //
NK023('a)001:12845: ma mo 'di'i zhing bcu sgrol ba'i ma mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12846: ljang nag b+han d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12847: 'jig rten khams kyi dbang mo che //
NK023('a)001:12848: ma mo 'di'i 'chad pas gcod pa'i ma mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12849: sngo nag zhing gis g.yang gzhi rdebs //
NK023('a)001:12850: dam tshig nyams pa'i snying 'byin ma //
NK023('a)001:12851: ma ma 'di'i 'byung po sgrol byed chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12852: ban d+ha gri thogs 'byung po sgrol //
NK023('a)001:12853: shar gyi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12854: ma mo 'di'i gshin rje sgrol byed chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12855: ban d+ha gri thogs gshin rje sgrol //
NK023('a)001:12856: lho yi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12857: ma mo 'di'i nub phyogs klu sgrol chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12858: ban d+ha gri thogs klu chen sgrol //
NK023('a)001:12859: nub kyi phyogs nas las byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12860: ma mo ma ma shwa ra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:12861: gnod sbyin sgrol byed chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12862: ljang nag ban d+ha gri thogs ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12863: byang gi phyogs nas las byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12864: ma mo srin po sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12865: sngo nag ban d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12866: steng gi phyogs nas las byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12867: ma mo srin mo sgrol byed chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12868: smug nag ban d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK023('a)001:12869: 'og gi phyogs nas las byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12870: ma mo gzugs la dbang ba'i dbang mo che //
NK023('a)001:12871: dkar mo zhing gi dbyug pa bsnams //
NK023('a)001:12872: dgra bo'i gzugs rnams 'phrog byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12873: ma mo 'di'i khrag la dbang ba'i chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12874: sngon mo thod khrag dkrug cing gsol //
NK023('a)001:12875: dgra bo'i khrag rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12876: ma mo drod la dbang ba'i ma mo che //
NK023('a)001:12877: dmar mo lag na tsit+ta thogs //
NK023('a)001:12878: sdang ba dgra yi grong 'phrog ma //
NK023('a)001:12879: ma mo dbugs la dbang ba'i ma mo che //
NK023('a)001:12880: ljang nag thod khrag zhags pa thogs //
NK023('a)001:12882: ma mo srog la dbang ba'i ma mo che //
NK023('a)001:12883: smug nag gri dang thod khrag 'thung //
NK023('a)001:12884: dgra bo'i srog rnams phrog byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12885: ma mo bkrag mdangs dbang ba'i dbang mo che //
NK023('a)001:12886: ser nag ral gri thod khrag 'thung //
NK023('a)001:12887: dgra ba'i mdangs rnams 'jig byed ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12888: ma mo ma mo khrag 'thung bya rgod mgo //
NK023('a)001:12889: ser ljang ral gri thod khrag 'thung //
NK023('a)001:12890: 'jig rten khyab pa'i mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:12891: ma mo 'dis ni dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12893: ma mo za byed stag gi mgo /
NK023('a)001:12894: dmar ser thod khrag zhal du gsol //
NK023('a)001:12896: ma mo 'di'i ma mo 'dzin byed chu srin mgo //
NK023('a)001:12897: sha khrag gsur la dga' byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12899: ma mo ma mo chen mo dur khrod brgyan //
NK023('a)001:12900: mi lpags rlon pas na bza' gsol //
NK023('a)001:12901: dur khrod bgegs chen 'dul mdzad ma'i //
NK023('a)001:12902: ma mo rdo rje gar gyi dbang mo che //
NK023('a)001:12903: dbu brgya spyan stong kun la khyab //
NK023('a)001:12904: ma lus sgrol ba'i gying chen ma //
NK023('a)001:12905: ma mo pad ma gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:12906: lag na mi mgo phor ba ru //
NK023('a)001:12907: mi snying tshil bu bkang shing gsol //
NK023('a)001:12908: ma mo sa bdag chen po pad+ma phreng //
NK023('a)001:12909: dmar nag b+han d+ha khrag gis bkang //
NK023('a)001:12910: mig rtsa dmar zhing rngams pa che /
NK023('a)001:12911: ma mo ma ma shwa ra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:12912: srid pa gsum gyi mnga' bdag mo //
NK023('a)001:12913: ri rab rtse nas bsnyil byed cing //
NK023('a)001:12914: rgya mtsho'i gting nas rnyog byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12915: ma mo 'dis rgya mtsho'i gting gi ma mo che //
NK023('a)001:12916: na bza' chu srin lpags pa gsol //
NK023('a)001:12917: sbrul nag stong gi gdengs ka can //
NK023('a)001:12918: ma mo ma mo rdo rje tho ba ma //
NK023('a)001:12919: sngo nag mi srin tho ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:12920: srin mo'i tshogs kyang 'dar zhing g.yo //
NK023('a)001:12921: ma mo ma mo rdo rje gtun khung ma //
NK023('a)001:12922: mthing nag dgra bo gtun tu brdung //
NK023('a)001:12923: gang la bya ba rdul du barloga /
NK023('a)001:12924: ma mo 'di'i ma mo rdo rje dur khrod bdag /
NK023('a)001:12925: sngo nag mi mgo rdo rje dbyug /
NK023('a)001:12926: gdug pa'i tshogs kyang 'joms par byed //
NK023('a)001:12927: ma mo ma mo rdo rje sder mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12928: sngo nag rdo rje rtse gsum bsnams //
NK023('a)001:12929: gdug cing gtum pa'i drag shul che //
NK023('a)001:12930: ma mo 'di'i ma ma shwa ra ma ra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:12931: ma mo rdo rje gsal bkra ma //
NK023('a)001:12932: dmar nag mi yi rgyu zhags 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12934: ma mo 'di'i ma mo rdo rje khrag 'thung ma //
NK023('a)001:12935: ljang ser ban d+ha rak+tasa bkang //
NK023('a)001:12937: ma mo 'di'i ma mo nag mo dred zhon ma //
NK023('a)001:12938: nad kyi rkyal pa gong du btags //
NK023('a)001:12939: tshon gyi dru gu glad la skor //
NK023('a)001:12940: ma mo dus bzhi'i rgyal mo mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:12941: srid pa gsum la dbang byed cing //
NK023('a)001:12942: cir yang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' ba //
NK023('a)001:12943: ma mo ma mo gnas yul spyang ku'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:12944: mi sha za zhing bdud khyim 'joms //
NK023('a)001:12945: bltas pas bdud rnams brlag byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12946: ma mo ma mo rdzu byed stag dang dom //
NK023('a)001:12947: gcan gzan gdug pa'i gzugs su sprul //
NK023('a)001:12948: ma lus 'joms pa'i mthu mo che //
NK023('a)001:12949: ma mo 'di'i ma ma shwa ra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:12950: ma mo 'dzum byed pho nya ma //
NK023('a)001:12951: khra ltar 'jungs shing khyi ltar zugs //
NK023('a)001:12952: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis len //
NK023('a)001:12953: ma mo ma mo gnam sa phyed kyis bdag /
NK023('a)001:12954: ri lung med par rjes ma gzugs kyis khyoms //
NK023('a)001:12955: che chung med par 'joms par byed //
NK023('a)001:12956: ma mo 'di'i ma mo pho nya rgyug byed ma /
NK023('a)001:12957: bud med lus la gzha' tshon gos //
NK023('a)001:12958: bang ni ri lung med par rgyug /
NK023('a)001:12959: ma mo 'di yi ma mo'i pho nya za byed ma //
NK023('a)001:12960: bud med lus la stag gis gos //
NK023('a)001:12961: zas su gtsang sme med par za //
NK023('a)001:12962: ma mo rdo rje ya byin pho nya mo //
NK023('a)001:12963: lcags kyu dkar khra phur bu 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:12964: gang la bya ba 'grub par byed //
NK023('a)001:12965: ma mo rdo rje bse byin rtsal mo che //
NK023('a)001:12966: sngo nag zhags pa phur bu thogs //
NK023('a)001:12967: gang la bya ba 'grub par byed //
NK023('a)001:12968: ma mo 'di'i ma ma shwa ra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:12969: rdo rje phag byin thogs pa med //
NK023('a)001:12970: dmar nag lcags sgrog phur bu thogs //
NK023('a)001:12971: gang la bya ba 'grub par byed //
NK023('a)001:12972: ma mo 'di yis rdo rje de byin dbang grub ma //
NK023('a)001:12973: ljang nag dril bu phur bu 'phen //
NK023('a)001:12974: gang la bya ba 'grub par byed //
NK023('a)001:12975: ma mo 'di'i sa bdag rgyal po chen mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12976: ser nag gser gyis bum pa bsnams //
NK023('a)001:12977: tshe srog kun la dbang bsgyur ma //
NK023('a)001:12978: ma mo phyi 'khor skyong ba'i mnga' bdag mo //
NK023('a)001:12979: rgyan dang cha lugs mdzes pa'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:12980: gnas ni g.ya' ri gangs la bcas //
NK023('a)001:12981: ma mo 'di yis 'brog srin rnams kyis rje mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12982: skyes pa 'dul ba'i ma mo ste //
NK023('a)001:12983: bud med bzang sdug 'dod chags ma //
NK023('a)001:12984: skra bshig ral pa gyen du bardzisa //
NK023('a)001:12985: ma mo 'di'i khro tshig myur ba'i ma mo ni //
NK023('a)001:12986: bud med khrag gis lan phran can //
NK023('a)001:12987: ma mo 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:12992: m+aa ma ha ma ma ha b+h+yo b+h+yo zhes //
NK023('a)001:12993: 'og phyogs bse'i ma mo drug cu /
NK023('a)001:12994: 'od mthing khro bo 'od ser po bshad /
NK023('a)001:12996: pho nya sum brgya drug cu'i tshogs //
NK023('a)001:12997: dkar dang sngo dang dmar ljang nag /
NK023('a)001:12998: gser dang bye ru'i mdog 'dra ba //
NK023('a)001:12999: drug cu drug gis rdzogs pa ni //
NK023('a)001:13000: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dang //
NK023('a)001:13001: tho ba gshog pa gtun tshogs 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:13002: ma lus khyab pa'i tshul gyis gnas //
NK023('a)001:13003: rdo rje nag mo khra thogs gshogs pa can //
NK023('a)001:13004: zhes steng khro bo tho ba can ser po dang /
NK023('a)001:13006: bden rigs de'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:13009: dza h+aum bam ho sgo bzhir gnas //
NK023('a)001:13010: yang sprul gnas la nges med de /
NK023('a)001:13011: nag mo theb gshog can gyis tshogs //
NK023('a)001:13012: steng gi nam mkhar 'khod pa yin //
NK023('a)001:13014: gong du tsa ka khyams la tshang yang sgo ba bzhi kun khyab yin gsungs /
NK023('a)001:13015: h+aum chen mthing skya 'khor lo thod dbyug thogs //
NK023('a)001:13016: sgra 'byin gtso 'khyud dung khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:13017: phrin las nyi zla tshangs pa'i gdul ba'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:13018: rigs kyi bu mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:13019: h+aum chen sgra 'byin phag dang smig pa'i mgo /
NK023('a)001:13020: yang na phyag drug mngon par rol //
NK023('a)001:13022: dang po rdo rje dung khrag krug /
NK023('a)001:13023: tha ma phur pa dril mthun 'od rim lugs //
NK023('a)001:13024: de la dbu gsum zhabs bzhi phyogs gdon gnon //
NK023('a)001:13025: ljang sngo g.yas dkar g.yon dmar gzhan tshab tu //
NK023('a)001:13026: khro bcus mtshams gcod pa 'dis tshom bu'i dus sgo nang du'ang khro bcu bshad la /
NK023('a)001:13027: skabs 'dir lag chus rdo ra me ri gang rung dang /
NK023('a)001:13028: phyi zhing la'ang khro bcu bkod pa /
NK023('a)001:13030: rdo rje me ri lag chu ha //
NK023('a)001:13031: phyi rol khro bcu yab yum ste //
NK023('a)001:13032: phra men nyi shu yang sprul dag /
NK023('a)001:13033: bye ba phrag ni sa ya 'phro //
NK023('a)001:13034: zhes pa phra men kha bkang pa //
NK023('a)001:13035: yab ni kro ta yum h+aum rjes //
NK023('a)001:13036: phra men za byed phag sogs dang //
NK023('a)001:13037: gsod byed smigs sogs sprul yang sprul //
NK023('a)001:13038: bzlas sngar h+aum dang phata la mdzad //
NK023('a)001:13039: yum sngar slar yang sprul par bcas //
NK023('a)001:13040: kro ti khro mo phyag gnyis dang //
NK023('a)001:13041: phyag drug rgyab yig 'od rims bshad //
NK023('a)001:13042: khro bo yab phyag gnyis phyag drug 'dam ka ste /
NK023('a)001:13043: phra men las byed na phyag drug mdzad //
NK023('a)001:13044: phyag gnyis phra men mi mdzad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:13045: badz+ra kro ta h+aum ka ra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13046: gardza gardza h+aum phatah kro ti shwa ri shwa ya h+aum phatah a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13047: phyogs bzhir sgo bzhi mtshams steng 'og gsum la yar khab ltar /
NK023('a)001:13049: badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta zhes bshad pa'ang bdog /
NK023('a)001:13050: rnam rgyal dkar po rdo rje rtse lnga zhing dbyug 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:13051: rnams snyems gtso 'khyud dung khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:13052: phrin las dri za gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:13053: rigs kyi bu mchog khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:13055: rnam rgyal snyems ma stag dang bya rgod mgo //
NK023('a)001:13056: g.yas sngo phyag drug rdo rje dung khrag phur //
NK023('a)001:13057: badz+ra kro ta b+hi dza ya h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13058: ha na ha na h+aum phatah kro ti shwa ri l+ya s+ye ke h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13060: dbyug sngon sngo skya me dbal drang srong 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:13061: sder mo gtso 'khyud thod khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:13062: phrin las drang srong gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:13064: dbyug sngon sder mo g.yag dang bya rog mgo //
NK023('a)001:13065: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar phyag drug dung khrag phur //
NK023('a)001:13066: phyag g.yon bar ma phyogs skyong gtso che bzungs //
NK023('a)001:13067: g.yas par phyogs skyong rtags mthun rtags 'phrog phul //
NK023('a)001:13068: badz+ra kro ta ni lan tan tra h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13069: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK023('a)001:13070: kro ti shwa ri pra ti dza h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13072: gshed po ser nag be con gshin rje 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:13073: dur khrod gtso 'khyud thod khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:13074: phrin las gshin rje gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:13075: rigs kyi bu phur pa'i rgyud las /
NK023('a)001:13076: gshin rje dur khrod sha ba 'ug pa'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:13077: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar phyag drug rdo rje dung khrag phur //
NK023('a)001:13078: zhal dbus ser nag de'i nag gtso byas //
NK023('a)001:13079: 'od rim nang na mthing nag 'dir ser nag /
NK023('a)001:13080: 'dam dkar shes bya rtsa zhal 'od rim las //
NK023('a)001:13081: mthing ka h+aum chen rnam rgyal dkar //
NK023('a)001:13082: dbyug pa sngo la gshin mthing nag /
NK023('a)001:13083: mi g.yo ljang sngon rta mgrin dmar //
NK023('a)001:13084: 'dod rgyal du kha bdud rtsi ljang //
NK023('a)001:13085: khams gsum dkar ljang stobs chen du //
NK023('a)001:13086: khro mo rnams ni khro dang mthun //
NK023('a)001:13087: 'khor lo n+ri mgo rdo rje sder //
NK023('a)001:13088: zhugs gling dang ni drang srong nyid //
NK023('a)001:13089: zhing dbyug gshin rje'i rkang bzung ba //
NK023('a)001:13090: ral g+hu bden bral stir dbyug bshog /
NK023('a)001:13091: ba dan lce brgyad be ram thogs //
NK023('a)001:13092: rin chen mgo bo gsum gyis dbyug /
NK023('a)001:13093: rdo rje rtse gsum n+ri mgo dang //
NK023('a)001:13094: thong shol gtun shing g.yas g.yon thogs //
NK023('a)001:13095: yang na phyag drug mngon par rol //
NK023('a)001:13096: khro mo g.yas ni gtso la 'khyud //
NK023('a)001:13098: zhes gshin rje be con dang zhing 'dam kha //
NK023('a)001:13099: stobs chen rtun la sa bdag chags //
NK023('a)001:13100: rlung lha'i rgyal po be ram pa'o //
NK023('a)001:13101: badz+ra kro ta ya man ta ka h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13102: pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phatah kro ti shwa ri sta na ba ti h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13104: mi g.yo ljang sngon ral gri srin po 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:13105: gtun khung gtso 'khyud thod khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:13106: phrin las srin po'i gdon rnams 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:13107: rigs kyi bu mchog khyod mi g.yo gtun khung gzig dang khwa ta'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:13108: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar phyag drug rdo rje dung khrag phur /
NK023('a)001:13109: badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa la h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13110: b+han d+ha b+han d+ha h+aum phatah kro ti shwa ri mu ha la h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13111: a b+hi rta mgrin dmar nag zhing dbyug khyung gshogs 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:13112: gtum mo gtso 'khyud thod khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:13113: phrin las klu yi gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:13114: rigs kyi bu mchog rta mgrin gtum mo byi la pu shud mgo //
NK023('a)001:13115: g.yas dkar g.yon sngo phyag drug rdo rje dung khrag phur //
NK023('a)001:13116: badz+ra kro ta h+ya g+h+ri ba h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13117: hu lu hu lu h+aum phatah kro d+hi shwa ri tsan d+ha ri ya ti h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13118: a b+hi dpal ldan dmar ljang ba dan rlung lha 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:13119: mda' snyems gtso 'khyud thod khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:13120: phrin las rlung lha'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:13121: rigs kyi bu dpal ldan mda' snyems spyang mo khra'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:13122: g.yas dkar g.yon sngo phyag drug rdo rje dung khrag dkrug /
NK023('a)001:13123: dmar ljang dbang gi mdog yin 'dod pa'i rgyal //
NK023('a)001:13124: badz+ra kro ta a pa ra tsit+ta h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13126: kro ti shwa ri ya b+h+ya ti h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13128: bdud rtsi ljang nag rin chen n+ri mgo dbyug tho 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:13129: rlung 'byin gtso 'khyud thod khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:13130: phrin las gnod sbyin gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:13131: rigs kyi bdud rtsi rlung 'byin seng ge pha wam mgo //
NK023('a)001:13132: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar phyag drug rdo rje dung khrag phur //
NK023('a)001:13133: badz+ra kro ta a mri ta kun d+ha li h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13134: tshin d+ha tshin d+ha h+aum phatah kro ti shwa ri ba ya ba ti h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13135: a b+hi khams gsum rnam rgyal dkar ljang rdo rje rtse gsum 'byung po 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:13136: gsod ma gtso 'khyud dung khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:13137: phrin las 'byung pos gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:13138: rigs kyi bu khams gsum gsod byed dred dang sre mo'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:13139: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar phyag drug rdo rje dung khrag phur //
NK023('a)001:13140: dkar ljang dud pa'i mdog tu 'bud shing gis //
NK023('a)001:13141: mdung rtse gsum pa'i dri shul rdo rjes mtshan //
NK023('a)001:13142: 'byung po mi gzugs n+ri mgo zhes bshad pa'o //
NK023('a)001:13143: badz+ra kro ta tre lokya b+hi ya dza ya h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13144: b+hin d+ha b+hin d+ha h+aum phatah kro ti shwa ri ma h+aa ma ra na h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13145: stobs chen dud kha thong gshol gtun shing thogs //
NK023('a)001:13146: bskyod ma gtso 'khyud thod khrag gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:13147: phrin las sa bdag gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i bdag /
NK023('a)001:13148: rigs kyi bu mchog khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:13149: stobs chen bskyod ma dom dang byi ba'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:13150: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus dud sngon por byas //
NK023('a)001:13151: phyag drug rdo rje dung khrag phur pa bcas //
NK023('a)001:13152: dud kha kha dog sna tshogs bshad par nges //
NK023('a)001:13153: gtun shing 'bru'i gzan rgyug mtha' ma lcags kyis bsdams pa dang /
NK023('a)001:13154: gtun shing gtun dang brtan skyong gang byed kyang //
NK023('a)001:13155: de la sa bdag chags pa de bzung ba'o //
NK023('a)001:13156: badz+ra kro ta ma ha ba la h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13157: spo ta ya spo ta ya h+aum phata /
NK023('a)001:13158: kro ti shwa ri tsun de ma ni h+aum /
NK023('a)001:13160: bden rigs phyag rgya chen po'i bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:13161: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK023('a)001:13162: lung a nu yo ga zhi khro rab 'byams mdo
NK023('a)001:13163: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:13164: cig / a ti la rig 'dzin dgos shing /
NK023('a)001:13166: rig 'dzin bye ba sa ya dag /
NK023('a)001:13167: phyi rol 'khor yug cha la gnas //
NK023('a)001:13168: phyi nang kun tu 'phro byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:13169: mar me'i 'od ni stobs thag chad //
NK023('a)001:13171: rig 'dzin gyis khyams khra'o khyams 'khor yug can /
NK023('a)001:13172: mtha' ma la mdzad pa dang /
NK023('a)001:13173: rig 'dzin rdo rje'i gral ces rdo rje'i ra ba la mdzad pa lugs gnyis dang /
NK023('a)001:13175: khro bo me ri 'bar ba yang phyi nang kun khyab cing steng nas stibs /
NK023('a)001:13177: bar nas khyugs pa'i ngo mtshar du ma'i phyir thag bcad de zhes blos mi 'khyud pa'i don no //
NK023('a)001:13178: a nu'i lha dbang rdzogs pas dbang don du /
NK023('a)001:13179: de ni rgyal ba'i sras po yin pas na //
NK023('a)001:13180: phyag rgya chen po'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:13181: ras sam 'bur ram blugs su blug pa yis //
NK023('a)001:13182: phyag rgya gzugs brnyan de'i spyi bor bzhag /
NK023('a)001:13184: chu bo bzhi'i tsa ka'i grangs la /
NK023('a)001:13185: phyi dbang rnal 'byor bla ma'i skabs su /
NK023('a)001:13187: nyi zla pad+ma la yum bzhi /
NK023('a)001:13188: sems khro yab yum tha dad pa dang /
NK023('a)001:13189: gtso bo nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma thugs sam gtso bo'i gzigs yum du mdzad /
NK023('a)001:13190: kun bzang thub pa mi byed /
NK023('a)001:13191: bla med nang dbang ma h+aa la yab yum 'khril /
NK023('a)001:13193: lung gi zhi khro dang rigs bdag mi byed /
NK023('a)001:13195: rigs bdag kun bzang che mchog dang lung gis zhi khro mdzad /
NK023('a)001:13196: bla ma dkyil 'khor gtso bo dang //
NK023('a)001:13197: 'khor ko seng 'bar dbang ma sring pho nya rtsa ba'i lhar mi byed /
NK023('a)001:13198: 'jig rten dam can lhag bsdud du byed /
NK023('a)001:13200: dkyil 'khor gtso bo dang rtsa ba'i bla ma gnyis
NK023('a)001:13201: tha dad med par byed cing bla ma je mtho
NK023('a)001:13202: byas pa'i rigs bdag 'og tu rdor sems la sogs
NK023('a)001:13203: mdzad / 'khor thams cad ye shes dang don dam gnyis ldan /
NK023('a)001:13204: rig 'dzin dang bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor rtsa ba'i lha'o //
NK023('a)001:13205: rang sa'i 'og ma rang sa'i mtha' bskor cing /
NK023('a)001:13206: dkyil 'khor gcig thog nas de thams cad /
NK023('a)001:13207: bskur ba'i spyi gtor sngon du bsnyen pa nas /
NK023('a)001:13208: rjes btang rag gnas srung bar gyis bskyed chog bsgom don he ru 'dus rgyud ltar mdzad pas /
NK023('a)001:13209: bri don gyi khyams he ru ka 'dus rgyud ltar /
NK023('a)001:13210: khyams dang po zhi ba phyogs mtshon /
NK023('a)001:13218: dgu pa phyogs bzhi pho nya phyogs mtshon /
NK023('a)001:13219: bcu pa 'og gi ma mo ljang khu'am smug /
NK023('a)001:13220: bcu gcig rig 'dzin khro bo'i sgo khyams mdog yin pas /
NK023('a)001:13221: sgo thams cad phyogs mtshon rnams cha chen re mnyam du'o //
NK023('a)001:13222: rta babs mthar mda' rdo rje me la khro bo
NK023('a)001:13223: khro mo khra thabs dang dbang don gyi phyi nang
NK023('a)001:13224: gnyis kyi tsa ka li zhes pa'i rigs 'dzin las
NK023('a)001:13225: / nang gi zhing khams bka' brgyad /
NK023('a)001:13226: phyi'i zhing khams theg brgyad gsungs /
NK023('a)001:13229: bsgom don yin pas ma sring bskyod la tshangs //
NK023('a)001:13230: 'gyod tshangs rgyal po dbang don rgyas pa'i lugs //
NK023('a)001:13231: gzhal yas nges med mtha' yas bri dka' yang //
NK023('a)001:13232: he ru 'dus rgyud lugs bris bkod la tshangs //
NK023('a)001:13233: 'on kyang lugs zhes nges rnyed phyir //
NK023('a)001:13234: slob dpon dpal dbyangs thig rtsa'o //
NK023('a)001:13235: dbang don sti ra ma ti'i lugs //
NK023('a)001:13236: lngar gsal sgo dgu khro bo zhi sgo bshad //
NK023('a)001:13237: phyi dbang gar byed gtso bo yab thugs 'od //
NK023('a)001:13238: nang dbang rdor sems gtsor byas sbyor mtshams 'od //
NK023('a)001:13239: bsgrubs dbang rigs bdag kun bzang gtsor byas dbang //
NK023('a)001:13240: gsang dbang bla ma lhar gsal yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:13241: ram yam kham gis gzugs brnyan mtshan 'dzin sbyangs //
NK023('a)001:13242: thal mo sbyar a stong nyid ye shes mthong //
NK023('a)001:13243: ma h+aa shu nye ta dz+nya na badz+ra s+w+aa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK023('a)001:13244: nyer gcig rjes su 'byung lnga zhi khro brtsegs //
NK023('a)001:13245: las zhi ba rdo rje dbyings dkyil 'khor //
NK023('a)001:13246: a nu kun bzang bde chen h+aum las steng //
NK023('a)001:13247: 'og tu gser 'khor rtsibs brgyad de h+aum las //
NK023('a)001:13248: khrag 'thung klong dgu'i dkyil 'khor he ru dgu //
NK023('a)001:13249: byang shar badz+ra'o gnam zhal sras yab lnga //
NK023('a)001:13250: khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gru ljang nas //
NK023('a)001:13251: yul ser 'bar dkar gsar yum sgo dbang dmar //
NK023('a)001:13252: ha he a dza h+aum bam ho phata b+h+yo /
NK023('a)001:13253: mthing nag h+aum las khro bo khro mor bsgom //
NK023('a)001:13254: khro bo sprul pa khro mo rol pa'i dkyil //
NK023('a)001:13255: mkha' 'gro las kyi dkyil 'khor e so gnyis //
NK023('a)001:13256: phrin las myur mgyogs dkyil 'khor ngur smrig ser //
NK023('a)001:13257: skyes bu kying dza bcu dgu dkar po'am ljang //
NK023('a)001:13258: mgyogs 'gro yid kyi dkyil 'khor phyogs bzhi yi //
NK023('a)001:13259: pho nya dza dkar h+aum ser bam dmar dang //
NK023('a)001:13260: ho ljang drug cu'i khyams sngo'am phyogs mtshon no //
NK023('a)001:13261: dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor 'og ma mo //
NK023('a)001:13262: drug cu ma'o ma bdun sring bzhi b+h+yo //
NK023('a)001:13263: yang khyams dmar sngo'am ljang khu'am smug /
NK023('a)001:13264: de yi lha thims h+aum la rig 'dzin khyams //
NK023('a)001:13265: rdo rje 'chang gi dkyil 'khor khyams phyi sgo //
NK023('a)001:13266: mdo chen kun 'dus rgyud ltar tshogs chen 'dus //
NK023('a)001:13267: a nu gtso ltar zhi 'og khro he ru //
NK023('a)001:13268: che mchog rgyal po badz+ra rgyal tshab ni //
NK023('a)001:13269: ma h+aa badz+ra rdo rje rgyal /
NK023('a)001:13270: zhe sdang rdo rje rgyu ming 'bras bu la //
NK023('a)001:13271: a ti yo ga ltar du bla ma dang //
NK023('a)001:13272: slob dpon mtshan bshad rigs lnga shar b+hud+ha //
NK023('a)001:13273: rdo rje bya rog gti mug rdo rje ni //
NK023('a)001:13274: drod rtags dus tshod dus mtshams 'dzin pa'i 'khor //
NK023('a)001:13275: rdo rje dus mtshams mthun 'jug mtshams sbyor ba'o //
NK023('a)001:13276: nga rgyal rdo rje rat+na'o rdo rje las slob ni //
NK023('a)001:13277: rdo rje go phur mtshams gcod pa zhes bshad //
NK023('a)001:13278: 'dod chags rdo rje sbyor gying sgrol gying ser //
NK023('a)001:13279: phrag dog rdo rje las mkhan phrin ma gyer //
NK023('a)001:13280: karma he ru ka'o bka' sdod yum lnga yang //
NK023('a)001:13281: rdo rje bya rog de yi rjes mthun mdzod //
NK023('a)001:13282: dbus ni ling tshe 'khor lo mu khyud drug /
NK023('a)001:13283: yang na ling tse'i steng du 'khor lo lnga /
NK023('a)001:13284: yang na leng tshe 'khor lo mu khyud gsum //
NK023('a)001:13285: drug ni phyi nang gnyis sdom yab yum 'khril //
NK023('a)001:13286: le'u tshe cho 'phrul yum chen bzhi //
NK023('a)001:13287: dbus la seng ha he ru ka la sogs //
NK023('a)001:13288: rdo rje rin chen pad mas rigs //
NK023('a)001:13291: 'khor lo gnyis pa dam tshig brgyad //
NK023('a)001:13292: 'khor lo gsum pa tshad med brgyad //
NK023('a)001:13293: 'khor lo bzhi pa rol pa brgyad //
NK023('a)001:13296: gong ras za byed chen po brgyad //
NK023('a)001:13297: 'khor lo lnga mdos khro rgyal mdzad //
NK023('a)001:13298: cho 'phrul dbus kyi zur bzhi ma //
NK023('a)001:13304: gong ras za byed le cho'i zur //
NK023('a)001:13305: gro bzhi thim pa che mchog spyan //
NK023('a)001:13306: brgyad bdun lnga bcu rtsa drug pa'i //
NK023('a)001:13307: rgyud lung khrag 'thung bcu yab yum //
NK023('a)001:13308: bye bas khrag 'thung drug cu bzhi //
NK023('a)001:13311: mu khyud drug rtseg snying po 'bar //
NK023('a)001:13313: mu khyud pa la leng tse dgu //
NK023('a)001:13314: gru chad rtsibs mchan me ri 'phro //
NK023('a)001:13317: de bzhin gru chad phyi dang nang //
NK023('a)001:13318: bar khyams bzhi mdzes phyi khyams dang //
NK023('a)001:13319: lngar gsal sgo dgu shar du brtsegs //
NK023('a)001:13321: zhes zhi ba ma the ba'i sgo lnga bshad //
NK023('a)001:13322: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya dag /
NK023('a)001:13323: gru chad phyi nang dag la bgram //
NK023('a)001:13324: h+aum chen bcu yi yum dag ni //
NK023('a)001:13325: shin tu mdzes par dang po la'o //
NK023('a)001:13326: de nyid la ni ma brgyad dang //
NK023('a)001:13327: gying chen bco brgyad rgyas par bkod //
NK023('a)001:13328: gnyis pa'i khyams la mkha' 'gro brgyad //
NK023('a)001:13329: shugs 'gro brgyad kyang de bzhin no //
NK023('a)001:13331: sum gnyis kyang gtso bo brgyad du dril //
NK023('a)001:13332: gsum pa'i khyams la phra men brgyad //
NK023('a)001:13333: de bzhin 'bar ma brgyad rnams bri //
NK023('a)001:13334: bzhi pa'i khyams la phor thog brgyad //
NK023('a)001:13335: de bzhin sring mo gzhong thog brgyad //
NK023('a)001:13336: kun tu mdzes par bri bar bya //
NK023('a)001:13337: lnga pa'i khyams ni tha ma la //
NK023('a)001:13338: rdo rje slas dang bran mo dang //
NK023('a)001:13339: pho nya la sogs rgyas par bgram //
NK023('a)001:13341: la sogs bla ma'i rig 'dzin khyams //
NK023('a)001:13342: srung ba'i khro bos lha tshang ngo //
NK023('a)001:13343: h+aum dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK023('a)001:13344: mngag gzhug pho nya'i las mdzad pa'i //
NK023('a)001:13345: 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed po yis //
NK023('a)001:13346: dgra bgegs sbyor ba rgyun chod cig /
NK023('a)001:13348: rgya gar dur khrod 'jigs byed tshal chen du //
NK023('a)001:13349: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13350: rdo rje grub pa rtsal de rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13351: 'jam dpal sku yi dngos grub brnyes pa'i rje //
NK023('a)001:13352: 'dir gshegs skal ldan rgya gar gnas dang sgrags kyi yangs rdzong du //
NK023('a)001:13353: yid btag phal chen dkyil 'khor zhal phyes tshe //
NK023('a)001:13354: yi dam ya man+ta ka'i zhal gzigs pa'i /
NK023('a)001:13355: lo ts+aa bee ro tsa na rak+shi ta dang ni //
NK023('a)001:13356: gnubs chen ban d+he sangs rgyas ye shes gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13357: rdo rje drag po rtsal de sku snang ji snyed bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13358: 'jam dpal sku yi dngos grub bsnyems pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:13359: 'dir gshegs skal ldan 'jam dpal sku sgo byang phyi ma'o //
NK023('a)001:13360: h+aum dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK023('a)001:13361: mngag gzhug pho nya'i las mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:13362: spyan ras gzigs dbang rta mgrin gyis //
NK023('a)001:13363: gdon bgegs sbyor ba rgyun gcod cig /
NK023('a)001:13364: h+aum h+aum rgya gar pad+ma brtseg pa'i dur khrod nas //
NK023('a)001:13365: slob dpon klu sgrub snying po'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13366: rdo rje grub pa rtsal de rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13367: pad+ma gsung gis dngos grub bsnyems pa'i rje //
NK023('a)001:13368: 'dir gshegs skal ldan h+aum bsam yas mchims phu dpal gyi yang dben du //
NK023('a)001:13369: zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor zhal phyes tshe //
NK023('a)001:13370: pad+ma dbang chen 'khor bcas zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:13371: ngan lam rgyal mchog dbyangs kyi gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13372: rdo rje pad+ma rtsal de gsung grags ji snyed bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13373: pad ma gsung gi dngos grub bsnyems pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:13374: 'dir gshegs skal ldan pad+ma gsung thun thag gam cha
NK023('a)001:13375: gsum dus la'ang 'jug cing sgo byang nang dkyil 'khor
NK023('a)001:13376: drung du'o // h+aum dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK023('a)001:13377: mngag gzhug pho nya'i las mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:13378: rgyal ba rgyal sras rgya mtsho'i tshogs //
NK023('a)001:13379: zhi khro'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK023('a)001:13380: h'u h'u rgya gar yul gyi h+aum grags dur khrod du //
NK023('a)001:13381: slob dpon h+aum ka ra'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13382: rdo rje dngos grub rtsal de rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13383: yang dag thugs kyi dngos grub bsnyems pa'i rje //
NK023('a)001:13384: 'dir gshegs skal ldan h+aum lho brag mkhar chu dpal gyis phug rings der //
NK023('a)001:13385: mar me dgu yi dal zhal phye ba'i tshe //
NK023('a)001:13386: yi dam dpal chen 'khor bcas zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:13387: slob dpon nam mkha'i snying po gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13388: rdo rje thogs 'bebs rtsal de thugs dran ji snyed bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13389: yang dag thugs kyi dngos grub bsnyems pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:13390: 'dir gshegs skal ldan yang dag bsgrub pa'i mar me 'dzab dgongs la'o //
NK023('a)001:13391: h+aum dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK023('a)001:13392: mngag gzhug pho nya'i las mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:13393: kun bzang che mchog bdud rtsi yis //
NK023('a)001:13394: nad sel sman gyi dngos grub stsol //
NK023('a)001:13395: h+aum h+aum bdud rtsi rol pa'i dur khrod rtsal chen nas //
NK023('a)001:13396: slob dpon dri med bshes gnyen gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13397: rdo rje mi 'gyur rtsal de rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13398: bdud rtsi yon tan dngos grub bsnyems pa'i rje //
NK023('a)001:13399: 'dir gshegs skal ldan h+aum yar lung tra'i sman sgang shel brag tu //
NK023('a)001:13400: bdud rtsi sman bsgrub dkyil 'khor zhal phyes tshe //
NK023('a)001:13401: sman gyi lha bsrung dkyil 'khor zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:13402: dz+nya na ku ma ra'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13403: dri med zla shar rtsal de 'dod yon ji snyed bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13404: bdud rtsi yon tan dngos grub bsnyems pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:13405: 'dir gshegs skal ldan bdud rtsi sman phud ro bro bzang //
NK023('a)001:13406: nang du sgo byang bar bdud rtsi 'khyil /
NK023('a)001:13407: h+aum dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
NK023('a)001:13408: mngag gzhugs pho nya'i las mdzad pa'i /
NK023('a)001:13409: rdo rje gzhon nu'i zhi khro yis //
NK023('a)001:13410: dam sri'i phung sbyor rgyun chod cig /
NK023('a)001:13411: h+aum h+aum dregs pa 'dul ba'i dur khrod rtsal chen du //
NK023('a)001:13412: 'jigs byed pra b+ha ha sti'i gsang mtshan ni /
NK023('a)001:13413: rdo rje drag po rtsal de rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs /
NK023('a)001:13414: phur pa phrin las dngos grub snyems pa'i rje /
NK023('a)001:13415: 'dir gshegs skal ldan h+aum brag dkar seng ge rdzong gi phug pa ru //
NK023('a)001:13416: gru gsum shel gyi dkyil 'khor zhal phyes tshe //
NK023('a)001:13417: jo mo mkhar chen mtsho rgyal gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13418: rdo rje lcam gcig ma ste phrin las ji snyed bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13419: phur bu grub nas brag srin phur pas btabs //
