NK023('a)001:13420: mkhar mi tsam la mdze gdon med par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:13421: ming po mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug kyang //
NK023('a)001:13422: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal de dngos grub thob //
NK023('a)001:13423: phur bu phrin las dngos grub snyems pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:13424: 'dir gshegs skal ldan phur pa mtshams kyi khro bcu zhe sdang rdo rje rang sa'i bsnyen phur ro //
NK023('a)001:13425: h+aum dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK023('a)001:13426: mngag gzhugs pho nya'i las mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:13427: mngon rdzogs rgyal po yab yum gyis //
NK023('a)001:13428: chags nyams bgegs bsal dngos grub gsol //
NK023('a)001:13429: h+aum h+aum rgya gar dur khrod sna tshogs pad+ma'i gling //
NK023('a)001:13430: slob dpon d+ha na sang skri ta'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13431: rdo rje dbang phyug rtsal de rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13432: ma mo rbod gtong dngos grub bsnyems pa'i rje //
NK023('a)001:13433: 'dir gshegs skal ldan h+aum yar lung sham po sgang gi gnas mchog tu //
NK023('a)001:13434: ma mo rgyud lung dkyil 'khor zhal phyes tshe //
NK023('a)001:13435: ma mo mkha' 'gro rnams kyi zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:13436: 'o bran dpal gyi gzhon nu'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13437: rdo rje 'phrul rgod rtsal de bde stong ji snyed bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13438: mkha' dbyings ma mo'i dngos grub bsnyems pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:13439: 'dir gshegs skal ldan gzhan yang yar lung sham po gangs kyi ra ba ru //
NK023('a)001:13440: srid pa ma mo'i bka' babs rtsa rlung dbang bsgyur nus //
NK023('a)001:13441: mi brjed gzungs thob 'brog mi dpal gyi ye shes sogs //
NK023('a)001:13442: 'dir gshegs skal ldan ma mo'i mdos rak+tasa thugs dam bskang ngo //
NK023('a)001:13443: h+aum dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK023('a)001:13444: mngag gzhug pho nya'i las mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:13445: gsang ba'i bdag po zhi khro yis //
NK023('a)001:13446: chos srung mi g.yel sdong grogs mdzod //
NK023('a)001:13447: h+aum h+aum rgya gar dur khrod 'dam bu'i tshal chen du //
NK023('a)001:13448: slob dpon rom bu gu ya d+he ba tsan tra ni //
NK023('a)001:13449: rdo rje gshog rgod rtsal de rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13450: 'jig rten mchod bstod bsnyen bsgrub bsnyen pa'i rje //
NK023('a)001:13451: 'dir gshegs skal ldan h+aum ma gro stag tshang seng ge'i brag phug tu //
NK023('a)001:13452: dregs pa kun 'dul dkyil 'khor zhal phyes tshe //
NK023('a)001:13453: bcom ldan dpal chen dregs pa'i zhal gzigs pa //
NK023('a)001:13454: slob dpon dpal gyi seng ge'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13455: rdo rje drag po rtsal de mchod bskul ji snyed bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13456: gsang bdag 'jig rten mchod bstod ji snyed rnams //
NK023('a)001:13457: 'dir gshegs skal ldan 'jig rten mchod bstod la chos
NK023('a)001:13458: skyongs gtor ma'am phud dam sgo rgyar ma tam gi
NK023('a)001:13460: h+aum dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK023('a)001:13461: mngag gzhu'i pho nya las mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:13462: stobs ldan sgrol gyis khro bo yis //
NK023('a)001:13463: phrin las mthar phyin kun 'grub mdzod //
NK023('a)001:13464: h+aum h+aum rgya gar dur khrod ro'i tshal chen du //
NK023('a)001:13465: slob dpon shan ting g+har+b+ha'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13466: rdo rje gshog rgod rtsal de rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13467: slob dpon zhi ba'i snying po de ni bod yul du //
NK023('a)001:13468: mkha' spyod gshegs te snang srid chos skur mdzad //
NK023('a)001:13469: dmod pa drag sngags dngos grub bsnyems pa'i rje //
NK023('a)001:13470: 'dir skal ldan h+aum brag dmar g.ya' ma lung gi dben gnas su //
NK023('a)001:13471: stobs ldan dreg pa rtog 'joms zhal phyes tshe //
NK023('a)001:13472: dpal chen stobs ldan nag po'i zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:13473: slob dpon bee ro tsa na'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13474: rdo rje grub pa rtsal de stobs rtsal ji snyed bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13475: dmod pa drag sngags dngos grub bsnyems pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:13476: 'dir gshegs skal ldan drag sngags dmod pa las bzhi'i sbyin bsreg gam /
NK023('a)001:13479: h+aum bcom ldan mgon po ye shes tshe dpag med //
NK023('a)001:13480: sgrib pa'i dri ma ma lus sel mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:13481: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sku gsung thugs mnga' ba //
NK023('a)001:13482: mnyam nyid rdo rje'i sku gsung thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK023('a)001:13483: rdo rje sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:13484: h+aum h+aum rgya gar a su ra'i brag phug tu //
NK023('a)001:13485: slob dpon ku ku ra tsa'i tshe dbang grub //
NK023('a)001:13486: rdo rje 'chang gi sa la mngon sum gshegs //
NK023('a)001:13487: tshom bu 'bum phrag 'khor bcas grub pa bsnyems //
NK023('a)001:13488: 'dir gshegs skal ldan tshe rdzas gang 'os bla ma'i drung du'o //
NK023('a)001:13489: h+aum gu ru pad+ma 'byung gnas gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13490: rdo rje thod phreng rtsal de rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13491: rgyal ba'i rgyal tshab srid gsum zil gyis gnon //
NK023('a)001:13492: khams gsum gdul bya dbang sdud spyi dpal rje //
NK023('a)001:13493: 'dir gshegs skal ldan mnga' bdag rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan yang //
NK023('a)001:13494: gsang mtshan dbang chen 'jam dpal rtsal zhes grags //
NK023('a)001:13495: skar chung rgyal po sad na legs dang khri ral pa //
NK023('a)001:13496: rgyal sras sprul pa gdung rab 'khor dang bcas //
NK023('a)001:13497: bzhugs ni longs spyod rdzogs skur bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13498: 'dir gshegs tshogs srung skye dgu skyong du gsol //
NK023('a)001:13499: skal ldan byin rlobs dbang skur dngos grub gsol //
NK023('a)001:13500: rig 'dzin spyi gtor ram gsang phud //
NK023('a)001:13502: nags tshal me tog lha bya'i skad snyan tshal //
NK023('a)001:13503: phar phyin slob dpon chen po gying ka ra //
NK023('a)001:13504: kri ya'i slob dpon klu sgrub tsan ti ka /
NK023('a)001:13505: yo ka'i slob dpon pad+ma ku ma ti //
NK023('a)001:13506: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i slob dpon de //
NK023('a)001:13507: yo ga la sogs phyi dbang brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK023('a)001:13508: lha mi yar chad dbang sbyin slob dpon dang //
NK023('a)001:13509: rgyud lung man ngag theg dgu'i bla ma rnams //
NK023('a)001:13510: 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon b+ho d+hi sa t+wa'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13511: rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal de rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13512: gsang sngags phyi rgyud thub pa'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK023('a)001:13513: 'dir skal ldan slob dpon dzi na mi tra'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13514: rdo rje sems dpa' rtsal de mtshan nyid theg pa che chung lhar bcas rnams //
NK023('a)001:13515: 'dir skal ldan tsha ba rong gi rgyal po'i bsgrub gnas su //
NK023('a)001:13516: rgya bod mkha' grub kun gyi thugs bcud phyung //
NK023('a)001:13517: yi dam tshogs chen kun gyi zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:13518: slob dpon rgyal po g.yu sgra snying po yang //
NK023('a)001:13519: gsang mtshan bde rgod rtsal de rigs 'dir gshegs skal
NK023('a)001:13520: ldan slob dpon dz+nya na ku ma ra yi gsang
NK023('a)001:13521: // thig le rtsal rgod rtsal de rigs bka' brgyad bskyed rdzogs gsum la mos gus rnams //
NK023('a)001:13522: 'dir skal ldan sog po dpal gyi ye shes gsang rdo rje bzhad pa'i gter te rigs /
NK023('a)001:13523: zhi khro'i gnas tshogs phrin las shar ba rnams //
NK023('a)001:13524: 'dir skal ldan zhang ston rgyal ba'i yon tan gsang //
NK023('a)001:13525: dam tshig mthar phyin rtsal de man ngag bka' srol phyag bzhes tshar ba rnams //
NK023('a)001:13526: 'dir skal ldan dar rje dpal gyi grags pa'i gsang //
NK023('a)001:13527: yang dag grub pa rtsal de bshad bsgrub yongs grags dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams //
NK023('a)001:13528: 'dir skal ldan h+aum bka' lung ma nor rnal 'byor dbang phyug che //
NK023('a)001:13529: rig 'dzin brgya dang rtsa brgyad dbang bskur 'dis //
NK023('a)001:13530: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang bsgrubs bshad lung rnams //
NK023('a)001:13531: 'dir gshegs skal ldan byin rlobs rig 'dzin theg pa spyi gtor ram /
NK023('a)001:13533: ban chung sangs rgyas ye shes kyis //
NK023('a)001:13534: pan ti ta'i thugs mdzod brus //
NK023('a)001:13535: rgya bod mkhas pa'i dgongs pa dril //
NK023('a)001:13537: theg pa 'dus dang dbang bsdus dang //
NK023('a)001:13540: yang dag bdud rtsi phur pa dang //
NK023('a)001:13541: ma mo mchod rten drag sngags kun //
NK023('a)001:13542: cha rkyen yin phyir rig 'dzin brgyad //
NK023('a)001:13543: tshe ni spyi yi kha skong yin //
NK023('a)001:13544: sgo byang phyi nang dgra bgegs bskrod //
NK023('a)001:13545: 'dzab dgongs mar me bdud rtsi sman //
NK023('a)001:13546: mtshams phur gdabs kha bsnyen phur rten //
NK023('a)001:13547: dmar chen rak+tasa thugs dam bskangs //
NK023('a)001:13548: 'jig rten mchod rten drag zor gtor //
NK023('a)001:13549: rig 'dzin gtor phud tshe zan rdzas //
NK023('a)001:13550: lha mi nyan rang byang sems dang //
NK023('a)001:13551: bya spyod rnam 'byor theg sgrub rdzas //
NK023('a)001:13552: yo ga la sogs theg drug bdag /
NK023('a)001:13554: skal ldan byin rlobs dbang dang dngos grub gsol //
NK023('a)001:13555: yid kyi sems dpa' gnas gyur pa //
NK023('a)001:13556: ston pa kun tu bzang po yis //
NK023('a)001:13557: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs //
NK023('a)001:13558: rnam shes phung po gnas gyur pa //
NK023('a)001:13559: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK023('a)001:13560: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur byin gyis rlobs //
NK023('a)001:13561: chos sku kun bzang longs sku rdo rje sems //
NK023('a)001:13562: 'jam dpal phyag rdor la sogs bka' bsdud rnams //
NK023('a)001:13563: 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13564: rdo rje bde byed rtsal de 'og min gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13565: 'dir gshegs skal ldan phyag rdor dang 'jam dpal gnyis
NK023('a)001:13566: ngo bo gcig la phyag mtshan gnyis tshang ba zhig
NK023('a)001:13567: mdzad nas snang / slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13568: rdo rje gzhon nu rtsal de 'og min gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13569: 'dir gshegs skal ldan rgyal po d+ha na ta lo'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13570: rdo rje dga' byed rtsal de 'og min gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13571: 'dir gshegs skal ldan thu bo ra tsa ha sti'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13572: rdo rje gsal ba rtsal de 'og 'dir gshegs skal
NK023('a)001:13573: ldan sras mo ba ra ni yi gsang mtshan ni
NK023('a)001:13574: // rdo rje mdzes ma rtsal de 'og /
NK023('a)001:13575: 'dir gshegs skal ldan klu'i rgyal po 'jog po'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13576: rdo rje rdzu 'phrul rtsal de rgya mtsho'i gting na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13577: 'dir skal ldan sras mo gnod sbyin byang chub gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13578: rdo rje g.yung drung rtsal de 'og min 'dir skal
NK023('a)001:13579: ldan gzungs ma a ra li yi gsang rdo rje
NK023('a)001:13580: dbyings ma rtsal de 'og 'dir gshegs skal ldan kha
NK023('a)001:13581: che'i slob dpon ag sho sha'i gsang rdo rje dngos
NK023('a)001:13582: grub rtsal de 'og 'dir gshegs skal ldan mkhan po
NK023('a)001:13583: ku ku ra tsa'i gsang rdo rje drag po rtsal
NK023('a)001:13584: de 'og 'dir gshegs skal ldan smad 'tshong b+hud+d+ha sa
NK023('a)001:13585: ma ya yi gsang mtshan rdo rje yang dag rtsal
NK023('a)001:13586: dag rtsal de 'og 'dir skal ldan smad 'tshong b+hud+d+ha
NK023('a)001:13587: sa ma ya ti'i gsang rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal
NK023('a)001:13589: 'dir gshegs skal ldan u rgyan rgyal po ma h+aa
NK023('a)001:13590: ra tsa'i gsang mtshan rdo rje rdzu 'phrul rtsal de
NK023('a)001:13591: 'dir gshegs skal ldan sras mo go ma de phyi'i
NK023('a)001:13592: gsang rdo rje dngos grub rtsal de rig 'dzin 'dir
NK023('a)001:13593: gshegs tshogs skal ldan byin rlobs blon po a lo
NK023('a)001:13594: ke'i gsang rdo rje g.yung drung rtsal de rig 'dir
NK023('a)001:13595: gshegs skal ldan kyi'i mkhan po phyi ma'i gsang rdo
NK023('a)001:13596: rje bdud 'dul rtsal de rig 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK023('a)001:13597: slob dpon ma h+aa ra tsa'i gsang mtshan rdo rje
NK023('a)001:13598: sgyegs pa rtsal de rigs 'dir gshegs skal ldan drang
NK023('a)001:13599: srong b+ha sha ti'i gsang mtshan rdo rje lhun 'grub
NK023('a)001:13600: rtsal de rigs 'dir gshegs skal ldan gzungs ma bdag
NK023('a)001:13601: nyid ma'i gsang mtshan rdo rje 'od mchog rtsal de
NK023('a)001:13602: rigs 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon chen po na
NK023('a)001:13604: rdo rje thogs med rtsal de rig 'dir gshegs skal
NK023('a)001:13605: ldan slob dpon d+he ba ra tsa'i gsang mtshan ni
NK023('a)001:13606: // rdo rje gsang ba rtsal de rig 'dir gshegs
NK023('a)001:13607: skal ldan slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi ma'i
NK023('a)001:13608: // gsang mtshan // rdo rje nges pa rtsal de
NK023('a)001:13609: rigs 'dir gshegs skal ldan rig 'dzin chen po dge
NK023('a)001:13610: bsnyen legs kyi gsang mtshan rdo rje mchog rab rtsal
NK023('a)001:13611: de rig 'dir gshegs skal ldan slob dpon d+harma ra
NK023('a)001:13612: tsa'i gsang rdo rje mi 'gyur rtsal de rig 'dir
NK023('a)001:13613: gshegs skal ldan slob dpon b+hud+d+ha kug ti'i gsang mtshan
NK023('a)001:13614: rdo rje gsang rdzogs rtsal de rigs 'dir gshegs skal
NK023('a)001:13615: ldan slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha'i gsang rdo rje bzhad
NK023('a)001:13616: pa'i rtsal de rig 'dir skal ldan dge slong kun
NK023('a)001:13617: dga' ma'i gsang rdo rje shes rab rtsal de 'dir
NK023('a)001:13618: skal ldan slob dpon bi ma mi tra'i gsang rdo
NK023('a)001:13619: rje khro bo lod de rig /
NK023('a)001:13620: 'dir skal ldan slob dpon bee ro tsa na'i gsang
NK023('a)001:13621: rdo rje khyung gshogs rtsal de rig 'dir gshegs skal
NK023('a)001:13622: ldan slob dpon g.yu sgra snying po'i gsang rdo rje
NK023('a)001:13623: bde 'byams rtsal de rig 'dir skal ldan dz+nya na
NK023('a)001:13624: ku ma ra'i gsang dri med zla shar rtsal de
NK023('a)001:13626: 'dir gshegs tshogs bsrung skye dgu bskyang du gsol //
NK023('a)001:13627: skal ldan byin rlobs dbang skur dngos grub gsol //
NK023('a)001:13628: des gnubs sangs rgyas la brgyud do //
NK023('a)001:13629: de yan chad kyis a ti'i rgyud rims thal lo //
NK023('a)001:13630: dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs chos kyi dbyings skye
NK023('a)001:13631: 'gags med pa spros pa dang bral ba'i mtha' las
NK023('a)001:13632: grol ba / rang bzhin lhun grub rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa /
NK023('a)001:13633: rang rig pa'i ngo bo thig le chen po grwa zur med pa'i dpal kun tu bzang po /
NK023('a)001:13634: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang yum gyi mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'i gnas su /
NK023('a)001:13635: 'khor rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas la thugs ye shes rnam
NK023('a)001:13636: pa lnga'i dbang bskur te longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur
NK023('a)001:13637: byin gyis brlabs / de bzhin du gnas lugs rtogs na ye shes lnga'i dbang thob ste /
NK023('a)001:13638: chos sku longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:13639: de nas rgyal ba rigs lnga'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las khrag 'thung rigs lnga dang /
NK023('a)001:13640: che mchog he ru kar snang bar mdzad pa /
NK023('a)001:13641: rigs gsum mkhyen rabs dang thugs rje dang mthu stobs kyi bdag por dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:13642: gdug pa can thams cad btul nas sum cu rtsa
NK023('a)001:13643: gsum lha'i gnas rnam par rgyal ba'i khang bzangs su
NK023('a)001:13644: zhi ba rigs lnga snang bar byas te /
NK023('a)001:13645: lha'i bu dam pa tog dkar po la 'gro ba
NK023('a)001:13646: rigs drug gi sems can thugs rjes smin par byed
NK023('a)001:13647: pa'i dbang bskur te sprul sku thub pa drug tu
NK023('a)001:13649: de bzhin du skal ldan rigs kyi bu 'di rnams kyi thugs rjes 'gro ba 'dren pa dang /
NK023('a)001:13650: phrin las kyi gdug pa can 'dul ba dang /
NK023('a)001:13651: 'bras bu thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:13652: mkhyen rab mnga' bdag 'phags pa 'jam dpal ni /
NK023('a)001:13653: mdzes pa'i sku ldan skye 'chi med pa yis //
NK023('a)001:13654: yid 'ong lha'i gnas su dbang bskur ni //
NK023('a)001:13655: grags ldan chos skyongs rin chen 'od 'bar dang //
NK023('a)001:13656: tshangs pa skye dgu'i bdag dang kun grol dang //
NK023('a)001:13657: gtsug phud 'dzin dang lha dbang brgya byin dang //
NK023('a)001:13658: lha yi rig 'dzin tshom bu 'bum sde la //
NK023('a)001:13659: bde gshegs rgyal tshab sras su dbang bskur nas //
NK023('a)001:13660: gnas skabs byang chub sems dpa'i rig 'dzin cing //
NK023('a)001:13661: rgyal bas sangs rgyas gdung sob dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:13662: thugs rje'i mnga' bdag spyan ras gzigs dbang ni //
NK023('a)001:13663: 'khor ba ma stongs bar du 'gro ba 'dren //
NK023('a)001:13664: sman gyis sku ldan klu la dbang bskur ba //
NK023('a)001:13665: g+h+ri ha na nag po klu mo kha 'dul ma /
NK023('a)001:13666: klu mo 'dul tshangs yid 'ongs dga' ma dang //
NK023('a)001:13667: klu yi rgyal po 'jog po la sogs pa //
NK023('a)001:13668: klu yi rig 'dzin tshom bu 'bum sde la //
NK023('a)001:13669: bde gshegs rgyal tshab gnas skabs rgyal ba sangs rgyas mthu stobs mnga' bdag phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK023('a)001:13670: 'jig rten dregs pa'i tshogs btul bsgral byas nas //
NK023('a)001:13671: 'jigs tshul sdig pas gnod sbyin dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:13672: gnod sbyin kun bzang lag na rdo rje dang //
NK023('a)001:13673: grags ldan chos skyong skar mda' gdong la sogs //
NK023('a)001:13674: gnod sbyin rigs bde gshegs gnas skabs rgyal ba gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK023('a)001:13675: grags ldan mchog skyongs thig le chags med rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13676: klu rgyal 'jog po dbang phyug lhun grub rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13677: gnod sbyin skar mda' rdo rje glog 'byin rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13678: lang ka mgrin bcu blo gros thabs ldan rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13679: li tsa byi ni dri med grags pa rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13680: 'dir gshegs tshogs srung skal ldan byin rlobs dbang skur dngos grub stsol //
NK023('a)001:13681: rgyal bas lung bstan skal ldan rgyal po la //
NK023('a)001:13682: gsang mdzod gter 'dzin sku gsung thim rtags dang //
NK023('a)001:13683: chos kyis sgro mdzad rat+na char phabs dang //
NK023('a)001:13684: kun gyis sngags cing glegs bam 'babs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:13685: mchod cing sangs rgyas pa la lung bstan te //
NK023('a)001:13686: gus mjal rtse gcig gsol btab bsgrub pa yis //
NK023('a)001:13687: sgrib sbyang chos kyi rgyal por dbang bskur zhing //
NK023('a)001:13688: chos kyi char phabs rnal 'byor gral du bzhag /
NK023('a)001:13689: chos la dbang thob sang pa rgya cher brjod //
NK023('a)001:13690: tan tra bco brgyad dbang thob skal ldan zhing //
NK023('a)001:13691: 'dren pa'i las dbyangs byin rlabs dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:13692: rgyud sde mnga' bdag chos rgyal dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:13693: skal ldan rgyal po dza yi gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13694: rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal de 'og min gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13696: skal ldan byin rlobs slob dpon u pa ra tsa'i
NK023('a)001:13697: gsang rdo rje yang dag rtsal de 'og 'dir gshegs
NK023('a)001:13698: skal ldan slob dpon in tra su tri'i gsang rdo
NK023('a)001:13699: rje gsal mdzes rtsal de 'dir skal ldan klu'i rgyal
NK023('a)001:13700: po na ga su tri'i gsang thig le bskyod med
NK023('a)001:13701: rtsal de 'dir skal ldan rgyal po gu ya su
NK023('a)001:13702: tri'i gsang rdo rje gsang 'phro rtsal /
NK023('a)001:13703: 'dir skal ldan sing ha'i rgyal po sing ha su
NK023('a)001:13704: tri'i gsang rdo rje 'od zer rtsal te 'dir skal
NK023('a)001:13705: ldan slob dpon ku ku ra tsa phyi ma'i gsang
NK023('a)001:13706: rdo rje bde mchog rtsal 'dir skal ldan ro langs
NK023('a)001:13707: bde ba'i dngos grub gsang bdud 'dul drag po rtsal
NK023('a)001:13708: de rig 'dir skal ldan slob dpon rdo rje bzhad
NK023('a)001:13710: rdo rje bde byed rtsal de rig 'dzin gnas 'dir
NK023('a)001:13711: skal ldan za hor rgyal po pra ha sti'i gsang
NK023('a)001:13712: thig le bde byed rtsal de 'dir skal ldan d+ha
NK023('a)001:13713: na rak+shi ta'i gsang seng ge sgra sgrogs rtsal de
NK023('a)001:13714: 'dir skal ldan slob dpon h+aum mdzad rdo rje'i gsang
NK023('a)001:13715: rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal 'dir skal ldan gu ru
NK023('a)001:13716: sti ra ma ti'i gsang mtshan yang dag rdzogs pa
NK023('a)001:13717: rtsal 'dir skal ldan a tsar+ya bde ba gsal byed
NK023('a)001:13718: gsang dbang phyug 'jigs med rtsal 'dir skal ldan slob
NK023('a)001:13720: shes rab mthar phyin rtsal 'dir skal ldan rgya gar
NK023('a)001:13721: chos rgyal skyong gis gsang rdo rje bde byed rtsal
NK023('a)001:13722: 'dir skal ldan bal po'i rgyal po ba su d+ha
NK023('a)001:13724: rdo rje thugs mchog rtsal 'dir gshegs skal ldan rgya gar gtsug lag dpal dge'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13725: rdo rje gtsug tor rtsal de rig 'dir gshegs skal
NK023('a)001:13726: ldan bru zha'i mkhan po che btsan skyes kyi gsang
NK023('a)001:13727: mtshan ni // rdo rje legs thob rtsal 'dir skal
NK023('a)001:13728: ldan slob dpon sangs rgyal ye shes gsang mtshan ni
NK023('a)001:13729: mtshan ni // // rdo rje yang dbang gter te rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13730: 'dir gshegs skal ldan de yan chad lung a nu'o //
NK023('a)001:13731: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud khungs la //
NK023('a)001:13732: kyi'i mkhan po ku ku ra tsas rnam dag mchod
NK023('a)001:13733: rten du bsgrubs pas kun tu bzang po'i sprul pa
NK023('a)001:13734: rdo rje sems dpa' zhal mngon du mthong ste /
NK023('a)001:13735: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje chos spyan ras gzigs la gsang sngags rgyud kyi rgyal pos dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:13736: rdo rje chos kyis ku ku ra tsa la dbang
NK023('a)001:13737: bskur bas tan tra sde chen po bco brgyad la
NK023('a)001:13738: dgongs pa mthar phyin par gyur te /
NK023('a)001:13739: de bzhin du rgyud lung man ngag gi tan tra
NK023('a)001:13740: sde chen po rnams la dbang thob par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:13741: / slob dpon ku ku ra tsa'i gsang mtshan ni /
NK023('a)001:13742: rdo rje che mchog rtsal de rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs /
NK023('a)001:13743: 'dir gshegs tshogs sprul skye dgu bskyang du gsol //
NK023('a)001:13744: skal ldan byin rlobs dbang skur dngos grub gsol //
NK023('a)001:13745: skal ldan rgyal po dza'i rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal
NK023('a)001:13746: de rig 'dir skal ldan rgyal po sh+aakya su tri'i
NK023('a)001:13747: rdo rje gsal mdzes rtsal 'dir skal ldan rgyal po
NK023('a)001:13748: sing ha ra tsa'i rdo rje drag po rtsal de
NK023('a)001:13749: 'dir skal ldan u rgyan rgyal po u pa ra
NK023('a)001:13750: tsa'i gsang rdo rje yang dag dngos grub rtsal de
NK023('a)001:13751: 'dir gshegs skal ldan rdo rje yang dag dngos grub
NK023('a)001:13752: rtsal de 'dir skal ldan sras mo go ma de
NK023('a)001:13753: byi'i rdo rje zla mdzes rtsal 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK023('a)001:13754: slob dpon mi tri ka ma la'i rdo rje khyung
NK023('a)001:13755: chen rtsal 'dir skal ldan a tsar+ya 'dzi na mi
NK023('a)001:13756: tra'i rdo rje nges pa rtsal 'dir gshegs skal ldan
NK023('a)001:13757: slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa'i gsang mtshan rdo rje
NK023('a)001:13758: bde byed rtsal de 'dir skal ldan slob dpon nyin
NK023('a)001:13759: byed seng ge'i rdo rje rtsal chen rtsal de 'dir
NK023('a)001:13760: skal ldan slob dpon bde ba gsang mdzad rdo rje
NK023('a)001:13761: 'gyur med rtsal de 'dir skal ldan slob dpon sh+aakya
NK023('a)001:13762: bo de'i rdo rje dngos grub mchog ste 'dir skal
NK023('a)001:13763: ldan slob dpon sog kya de ba'i rdo rje dad
NK023('a)001:13764: pa rtsal de 'dir skal ldan slob dpon sgeg pa
NK023('a)001:13765: rdo rje rdo rje sgeg pa rtsal de 'dir skal
NK023('a)001:13766: ldan slob dpon chos blan de ba'i rdo rje nges
NK023('a)001:13767: chen rtsal 'dir skal ldan mkhan po chos rgyal skyong
NK023('a)001:13768: gis rdo rje bde byed rtsal 'dir skal ldan des
NK023('a)001:13769: gnubs sangs rgyas la brgyud do //
NK023('a)001:13770: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che //
NK023('a)001:13771: g.yung drung rin chen gter gnas su //
NK023('a)001:13772: yi dam gsal ba bsgom pa'i tshe //
NK023('a)001:13774: nam mkha'i mthong nas yar mar babs //
NK023('a)001:13775: bdag gi lag pa g.yas pas zin //
NK023('a)001:13776: ye shes rdo rje'i dbang mchog thob //
NK023('a)001:13777: 'ol mo tshal du bsgom pa'i tshe //
NK023('a)001:13778: mngon sum dri za phru gu byung //
NK023('a)001:13779: sangs rgyas khyod yin mtshan btags te //
NK023('a)001:13780: dam pa'i don la dam tshig bsres //
NK023('a)001:13781: rdo rje ming gis dbang yang thob //
NK023('a)001:13782: gang bzang gnas su bsgom pa'i tshe //
NK023('a)001:13783: gnod sbyin phru gu mngon byung nas //
NK023('a)001:13784: 'dod yon lnga yi mchod yon stobs //
NK023('a)001:13785: yun gyis 'khor du dum du bcas //
NK023('a)001:13786: che ba'i yon tan dbang yang thob //
NK023('a)001:13787: gling dgu mtsho 'gram bsgom pa'i tshe //
NK023('a)001:13788: klu phrug spun gsum mngon byung nas //
NK023('a)001:13789: ro brgya ldan pa'i mchod pa drangs //
NK023('a)001:13790: yang dag slob mar dam tshig nos //
NK023('a)001:13791: gdug pa sel ba'i dbang yang thob //
NK023('a)001:13792: dur khrod lhas su bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK023('a)001:13793: yi dwags phru gu mngon du byung //
NK023('a)001:13794: zhabs la gtugs te mchi ma byung //
NK023('a)001:13795: ci bsgo nyan par dbang yang nos //
NK023('a)001:13796: mthu rtsal snyems pa'i dbang yang thob //
NK023('a)001:13797: phyi rab slob ma gang byung rnams //
NK023('a)001:13799: phan pa'i lha yi dbang nos pas //
NK023('a)001:13800: dbang bskur rgyal po'i gzhung bzhin du //
NK023('a)001:13801: dbang rnams rim par thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:13802: man ngag drug gsum bco brgyad las //
NK023('a)001:13803: nang gi tsa ka li rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:13804: slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes ni //
NK023('a)001:13805: gsang mtshan rdo rje yang dbang gter //
NK023('a)001:13806: bzhugs ni 'og min gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13809: sangs rgyas ye shes slob bzhi dge mched bco lnga dang //
NK023('a)001:13810: rin chen gsum dang 'khor brgyad gru gu 'jig rten sogs //
NK023('a)001:13811: slob ma bzhi ni 'bre ston khro chung nyang sher mchog /
NK023('a)001:13812: myang ston ye shes 'byung dang zur chen shag 'byung bzhi //
NK023('a)001:13813: dge mched dang po thugs kyi sras bzhi bla ma ni //
NK023('a)001:13814: so pa ye shes dbang phyug rdo rje dbyings chen gter //
NK023('a)001:13815: sru pa legs pa'i sgron ma ut+pala dbang chen rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13816: spa gor blon rje 'phags pa rdo rje gnam lcags rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13817: dan ston yon tan mchog ni rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13818: gnyis pa thugs kyi sras gcig gnubs chung ni //
NK023('a)001:13819: khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho rdo rje rig 'dzin gter //
NK023('a)001:13820: gsum pa gdung rus srus te de'i slob ma bzhi //
NK023('a)001:13821: dbyar ston gsal ba'i byang chub rdo rje 'tshams byed rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13822: rgya ston blo gros gzhon nu rdo rje dbang mchog rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13823: rgya ston sh+aakya mchog rab rdo rje gzi 'bar rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13824: zhu ston bsod nams sh+aakya phrin las mthar phyin rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13825: bzhi pa spa gor slob cig beg ston ye shes dang //
NK023('a)001:13826: lnga pa lnga ni rgya ston gzhon nu snying po dang //
NK023('a)001:13827: skye ston dar ma bo de skye mchog rab //
NK023('a)001:13828: skye ston dar ma rgyal mtshan lho ston snying po'o //
NK023('a)001:13829: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes dngos slob rnams //
NK023('a)001:13830: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin grub pa'i gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13831: 'dir gshegs tshogs bsrung skye dgu bskyang du gsol //
NK023('a)001:13832: skal ldan byin rlobs dbang bskur dngos grub stsol //
NK023('a)001:13833: khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho de yi ni //
NK023('a)001:13834: sras chung ye shes rgya mtsho nyid la gtad //
NK023('a)001:13835: gsang mtshan rdo rje dbang sgrub rtsal du btags //
NK023('a)001:13836: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin grub pa'i grwal na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13837: 'dir gshegs skal ldan ye shes rgya mtsho slob ma byang chub rnam gsum las //
NK023('a)001:13838: rgya ston blo gros byang chub rdo rje las grub rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13839: mar pa yon tan byang chub rdo rje lhun grub rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13840: sna nam tshul khrims byang chub rdo rje grub mchog rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13841: rgya yi slob ma brgyud 'dzin gnyis gsungs te //
NK023('a)001:13842: tho dkar nam mkha' lde yi gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13843: rdo rje dngos grub gter de rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13844: zhu ston bsod nams sh+aakya'i gsang phrin las mthar phyin
NK023('a)001:13845: rtsal de rig 'dir gshegs skal ldan zur chen sh+aakya
NK023('a)001:13847: tho dkar gyis bdag rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13848: zhu yis mtshan btags bde gshegs zhi ba rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13849: gnubs chen sangs rgyas kyi 'ang zhal mthong bshad //
NK023('a)001:13850: ston tshab byang chub rgya ston blo gros dang //
NK023('a)001:13851: bka' sdod ye shes snying po rnams las ni //
NK023('a)001:13852: mdo lung dbang sgrub rgyud phrin 'gro kun gsan //
NK023('a)001:13853: khyad par bla ma brgya rtsa mnyes par bsten //
NK023('a)001:13854: thub dang pad+ma lung bstan spyan ras gzigs //
NK023('a)001:13855: thugs dam zhal gzigs dam can ci bcol nyan //
NK023('a)001:13856: mkha' 'gros lung bstan phyi nang gtsug lag bzhengs //
NK023('a)001:13857: grub rtags zhabs rjes spyi dpal zur po che //
NK023('a)001:13858: 'dir gshegs skal ldan zur chen slob ma rtse mo grub chen bzhi //
NK023('a)001:13859: zur chung shes rab grags pa'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13860: rdo rje lhun grub rtsal de lta dgongs gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13861: zur chen zhabs drung dbu'i rjes kyang bzhag /
NK023('a)001:13862: bshes lhag tsan dan sdong po sangs rgyas 'khrungs //
NK023('a)001:13863: 'dir gshegs skal ldan mtsho nya'i bzang bsgom shes rab rgyal ba ni //
NK023('a)001:13864: rdo rje gzi 'bar rtsal de bsgom bsgrub gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13865: las stod ra pa'i zhang ston 'gos chung ba //
NK023('a)001:13866: rdo rje lhun grub rtsal de mkhyen rgya'i /
NK023('a)001:13867: span dang bre khu'i mi nyag 'byung grags ni //
NK023('a)001:13868: rdo rje bde ba rtsal de bshad nyan gnas na /
NK023('a)001:13869: bram gyi rtsag ston la sogs rtse rkog brgyad //
NK023('a)001:13870: rdo rje drag po rtsal de bsgrub pa'i gnas //
NK023('a)001:13871: zur chung sgos slob ka bzhi gdung brgyad kyang //
NK023('a)001:13872: gong bu'i skye ston sh+aakya ye shes ni //
NK023('a)001:13873: rdo rje snying po rtsal te rdzogs chen ka bar
NK023('a)001:13874: mda' phu'i mda' ti jo shag gsang rdo rje dngos
NK023('a)001:13875: grub rtsal de phrin las ka bar chu dbar glan
NK023('a)001:13877: rdo rje myu gu rtsal de sgyu 'phrul ka bar shab kyis dge lung yang khyed bla ma ni //
NK023('a)001:13878: thig le 'gyur med rtsal de mdo lung ka bar nya tshal sh+aakya byang chub dang /
NK023('a)001:13879: ma thog ne ser jo seng s+w+ao /
NK023('a)001:13880: rdo rje drag po rtsal de phyi phan gdung tshob bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13881: 'dir gshegs tshogs bsrung skal ldan byin rlobs gsang bdag sh+aakya seng ge ni //
NK023('a)001:13882: gsang mtshan dbang phyug rdzogs pa rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13883: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje dang //
NK023('a)001:13884: bstan pa'i bdag por lung bstan thob //
NK023('a)001:13885: bzhugs ni gsang sngags bdag por bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13886: 'dir skal ldan slob dpon 'gar ston zung ngo ni //
NK023('a)001:13887: nam mkha' la yang skor ma mdzad //
NK023('a)001:13888: brag la phur pa theb par gdab //
NK023('a)001:13889: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13890: 'dir skal ldan preg ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan ni //
NK023('a)001:13891: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'jigs med rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13892: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13893: 'dir skal ldan bstan pa'i srog shing blan ban rdo rje 'od //
NK023('a)001:13894: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13895: bzhugs ni sham pa la ru bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13896: 'dir gshegs skal ldan sprul sku rgyal sras rin chen brtson seng ni /
NK023('a)001:13897: kha che'i pan chen la sogs gdams pas phyug /
NK023('a)001:13898: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal /
NK023('a)001:13899: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin grwal na bzhugs /
NK023('a)001:13900: 'dir gshegs skal ldan drin chen mkhas pa glan ston bsod rgyal ni //
NK023('a)001:13901: gsang mtshan phrin las mthar phyin rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13902: bzhugs ni 'dir skal ldan bstan pa'i srog shing dpal ldan chos seng ni //
NK023('a)001:13903: mkhas grub mang brgyud rdo rje 'dzin pa de //
NK023('a)001:13904: 'gro don mthar phyin rig gsang mtshan rdo rje drag
NK023('a)001:13905: po rtsal de 'dir skal ldan bla ma blan ston
NK023('a)001:13906: sangs rgyas dpal // gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13907: bzhugs ni dkyil 'khor bdag por 'dir skal ldan sprul sku lha 'bum de'i sras /
NK023('a)001:13908: u rgyan pad mas lung bstan bzhin //
NK023('a)001:13909: glan ston bsod nams mgon po ni //
NK023('a)001:13910: zab mo'i gter rnyed mdo rgyud bdag /
NK023('a)001:13911: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13912: brgyud 'dzin rgyal tshab sku gsum ni //
NK023('a)001:13913: bla ma 'bro chen rdo rje ni //
NK023('a)001:13914: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde chen rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13915: myang chen shes rab dpal ldan rdo rje dang //
NK023('a)001:13916: gyeng khang zings ston sh+aakya bzang por bcas //
NK023('a)001:13917: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13918: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13919: 'dir gshegs skal ldan bla ma 'bro chen bsam 'grub rdo rje ni //
NK023('a)001:13920: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde chen rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13921: dbang rdzogs bshad lung nya tshal du //
NK023('a)001:13922: bla ma bsod nams mgon la thob //
NK023('a)001:13923: dkyil 'khor gang mdzad gtso bo dang //
NK023('a)001:13924: bla ma gnyis med gcig tu gzigs //
NK023('a)001:13925: dkyil 'khor rang nyid thugs kha la //
NK023('a)001:13926: dngos ltar thim pa'i gzigs snang shar //
NK023('a)001:13927: gtad rgya dbang skyar bcas pa ni //
NK023('a)001:13928: zi ston sh+aakya bzangs la bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13929: bye ma seng ger lo bdun bsgom //
NK023('a)001:13931: phyi ma bde ba can lung bstan //
NK023('a)001:13932: dpal chen grub pa'i thugs mtshan dang //
NK023('a)001:13933: khro bcu'i snang ba mi 'gags shing //
NK023('a)001:13934: gang shar chos nyid rgyun chad med //
NK023('a)001:13935: rtsa rlung sku tshe dbang thob pas //
NK023('a)001:13936: bzhugs ni gdul bya'i don la bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13937: sh+aag 'byung rdo rje thod phreng sogs //
NK023('a)001:13938: gsol ba 'debs so byin gyis rlobs //
NK023('a)001:13939: 'dir skal ldan bsgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo mthar phyin pa'i //
NK023('a)001:13940: sku 'di gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo la //
NK023('a)001:13941: rtsa ba'i bla ma sangs rgyas yi dam du //
NK023('a)001:13942: nges pas dbang zhu tsa ka dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK023('a)001:13943: dbus la sbas de gsol 'debs rten de yin //
NK023('a)001:13944: mdo dbang tshar lnga dbang bskur gtad rgyar bcas bdun thob /
NK023('a)001:13945: zur ham dge tshul dus na sh+aakya 'byung gnas ni //
NK023('a)001:13946: bsgrub dbang a nu'i dus na rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13947: nang dbang ma h+aa'i dus na thig le g.yo med rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13948: phyi dbang yo ga'i dus na dbang phyug rdzogs pa rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13949: phyi dbang theg drug dus na mi bskyod rdo rje dang //
NK023('a)001:13950: tri ya bya spyod dus na thugs kyi rdo rje dang //
NK023('a)001:13951: phyi ma don 'grub zhing mchog de thob smon cig gsungs //
NK023('a)001:13952: sems bskyed dus na byang sems sh+aakya 'byung //
NK023('a)001:13953: nyan thos dus na gnas brtan dge slong ni //
NK023('a)001:13954: dge ba'i bshes gnyen sh+aakya 'byung gnas dang //
NK023('a)001:13955: lha mi theg pa'i dus na dge bsnyen ni //
NK023('a)001:13956: bsod nams rdo rje 'chang bzang po zhes gnang /
NK023('a)001:13957: bla ma'i dbang bskur byin rlabs ngo sprod dus //
NK023('a)001:13958: dpal ldan bla ma bsam 'grub rdo rje nyid //
NK023('a)001:13959: a ti yo ga nam mkha'i sku can la //
NK023('a)001:13960: gtsug rgyan mi bskyod sku nyid yi dam lha //
NK023('a)001:13961: g.yas brkyang zhabs 'og dregs pa'i gdan byas pa //
NK023('a)001:13962: mngon sum gsal mthong lus bstan mchod pa bzhes //
NK023('a)001:13963: me tog phul bas phyag gi thod par gsal //
NK023('a)001:13964: gsang sngags bstan pa gtad nas rgyal por bskos //
NK023('a)001:13965: rig 'dzin lha srungs du mas rjes bzung ba'i //
NK023('a)001:13966: sh+aag 'byung gsang mtshan rdo rje thod phreng rtsal //
NK023('a)001:13967: bzhugs ni rgyal ba'i phrin las don la bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:13968: 'dir gshegs tshogs skal ldan byin rlobs dbang bskur dngos grub stsol //
NK023('a)001:13969: rdo rje slob dpon khyams 'di la //
NK023('a)001:13970: rtsa rgyud bla ma dkon mchog skyabs //
NK023('a)001:13972: rdo rje spun de pha cig pa //
NK023('a)001:13973: ming sring rnal 'byor pho mo dang //
NK023('a)001:13974: rdo rje rig 'dzin gdung tshob pa //
NK023('a)001:13975: rdo rje lus ni chos skyongs rgyal //
NK023('a)001:13976: rdo rje rgyal po tshe la dbang //
NK023('a)001:13978: rdo rje ngag ni chos dbang thob //
NK023('a)001:13979: rdo rje las ni phrin las dbang //
NK023('a)001:13980: rdo rje yid ni sems la dbang //
NK023('a)001:13981: rdo rje'i 'khor du slas bran mo //
NK023('a)001:13982: byi mo pho nya dang bcas pas //
NK023('a)001:13983: theg dgu rgyud bdun rnal 'byor bzhi //
NK023('a)001:13984: bstan pa'i mtshan dad thams cad kyang //
NK023('a)001:13985: 'dir gshegs skal ldan a ti'i gsang dbang gi nang dbang //
NK023('a)001:13986: bdun pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor dbang des rdzogs /
NK023('a)001:13988: de ni rgyal ba'i sras po yin pas na //
NK023('a)001:13989: phyag rgya chen po'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:13990: ras sam 'bur ram lugs su blug pa yin //
NK023('a)001:13991: phyag rgya gzugs brnyan de yi spyi bor bzhag /
NK023('a)001:13993: bsgrub pa'i dbang mchog thob pa dang //
NK023('a)001:13994: gsang ba'i bdag po yin pas na //
NK023('a)001:13995: gsang ba'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:13997: nang dbang brgyad pa dbu rgyan gyi dbang ni /
NK023('a)001:13998: rin po che dang thod pa'i dbu rgyan mgo bo'i gnas lngar gtugs /
NK023('a)001:13999: bum chu shu ne dz+ny+aa na sogs pas dbang bskur /
NK023('a)001:14000: ye shes chen po'i don dang de ldan pas //
NK023('a)001:14001: ye shes lnga yi rtags mchog phyag rgya yis //
NK023('a)001:14002: gnas lngar gtugs te thugs kyi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14003: 'bru bcus rigs lnga'i rab gnas ldan par bya /
NK023('a)001:14004: shu dz+nya ta sogs sngags lnga brjod par bya /
NK023('a)001:14006: bden pa che ge la dbu brgyan gyis dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:14007: bas rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad gnas su dag
NK023('a)001:14008: nas ye shes lnga'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14009: dgu pa sku gsung thugs kyi dbang ni lnga dang gsung ste gnyis /
NK023('a)001:14010: sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje yis //
NK023('a)001:14011: rnal 'byor bde mchog de yin pas //
NK023('a)001:14012: sku gsung thugs yon phrin las dbang //
NK023('a)001:14013: rdo rje can la sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:14014: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya nas bag tsit+ta
NK023('a)001:14015: a nu ra ga sdu tsa badz+ra s+w+aa b+ha wa
NK023('a)001:14018: bden pa sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las dus su byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK023('a)001:14019: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14020: gnas gsum 'bru gsum rdo rje gsum //
NK023('a)001:14021: bsam ste yi ge'am sku gsum bshad //
NK023('a)001:14022: ces lnga lngar gnas lnga 'bru lnga'o //
NK023('a)001:14023: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs yon tan //
NK023('a)001:14024: phrin las lnga yi ngo bor bshad //
NK023('a)001:14025: dpral mgrin snying lter gsang bar ni /
NK023('a)001:14026: dkar a dmar h+aum mthing nag /
NK023('a)001:14027: swo ser ha ljang yum yab dril //
NK023('a)001:14028: sku a gsung h+aum thugs ni //
NK023('a)001:14029: lus ngag yid gsum dpral mgrin snying //
NK023('a)001:14031: sku gsung thugs dang rdo rje yis //
NK023('a)001:14032: rnal 'byor bde mchog de yin pas //
NK023('a)001:14033: bde gshegs rnams kyi sku yi dbang //
NK023('a)001:14034: rdo rje can la sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:14035: sarba ta tha ga ta ma h+aa ka y+aa badz+ra s+w+aa b+ha wa ad ma ko&a ham /
NK023('a)001:14036: bden pa rigs kyi bu la bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK023('a)001:14037: sku yis byin gyis brlabs pas rdo rje sku'i dbang
NK023('a)001:14040: sku gsung thugs dang rdo rje yi rnal 'byor bde mchog de yin pas /
NK023('a)001:14041: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gi dbang //
NK023('a)001:14042: rdo rje can la sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:14043: bag badz+ra bden bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung gis dbang
NK023('a)001:14044: bskur bas rdo rje gsung gi dbang thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:14046: sku gsung thugs dang rdo rje yis //
NK023('a)001:14047: rnal 'byor bde gshegs rnams kyis thugs rdo rje can
NK023('a)001:14048: la ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra s+w+aa b+ha wa bden bde
NK023('a)001:14049: bar gshegs pa'i thugs su byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK023('a)001:14050: rdo rje thugs kyi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14051: 'khor lo bkra shis phyag zhabs mthil //
NK023('a)001:14052: skyobs pa'i sangs rgyas 'dren pa'i lha //
NK023('a)001:14053: nyon mongs sems can dman pa'i gsol //
NK023('a)001:14054: phyag zhabs 'khor lo bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:14055: ston pa la bdud kyis bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK023('a)001:14056: phyag zhabs 'khor lo bkra shis mthil //
NK023('a)001:14057: skyobs pa'i sangs rgyas 'dren pa'i lha //
NK023('a)001:14058: nyon mongs sems can dman pa'i gsol //
NK023('a)001:14059: phyag zhabs 'khor lo bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:14060: ston pa la bdud kyis bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK023('a)001:14061: phyag zhabs 'khor lo bkra shis gyur //
NK023('a)001:14062: de ring khyod la sbyin byas pas //
NK023('a)001:14063: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:14064: phyag dang zhabs 'khor lo bkra shis pas chos kyi tsakra bskor ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14065: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:14066: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK023('a)001:14067: phyag zhabs mthil las mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:14068: 'di ni 'khor lo dbang gi bkra shis so //
NK023('a)001:14069: gsung mchog pad ma chos kyi rgyal //
NK023('a)001:14070: nyon mongs ma gos pad ma'i sku //
NK023('a)001:14071: thams cad sgrol ba'i gsung lags te //
NK023('a)001:14072: rdzas mchog pad mar bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:14073: ston pa la ljags kyi pad mar de ring khyod
NK023('a)001:14074: la cis kyang gos pa med pa'i dbang thob shog
NK023('a)001:14075: / ljags nyid pad ma gos pa med pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:14076: gzhan gyis mi thub bsdo ba'i phyogs //
NK023('a)001:14077: ljags kyis mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:14078: 'di ni pad+ma dbang gi bkra shis so //
NK023('a)001:14079: mi nub rgyal mtshan 'dren pa'i sku //
NK023('a)001:14080: thams cad bdud kyi sde btul nas //
NK023('a)001:14081: dpung bcom sangs rgyas sku bstod do //
NK023('a)001:14082: sku mchog rgyal mtshan bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:14083: ston pa la sku rgyal mtshan du de ring bdud bzhi las rgyal ba'i bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:14084: sku ni rgyal mtshan du bkra shis pas bdud bzhi las rgyal ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14085: rgyal mtshan gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'ii rtags dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:14086: gzhan gyis mi thub bsdo ba'i phyogs //
NK023('a)001:14087: sku'i mchog la mngon par 'di ni rgyal mtshan dbang gi bkra shis so //
NK023('a)001:14088: bkra shis bum pa dam pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:14089: bcom ldan 'das kyis bskur lags te //
NK023('a)001:14090: mgur mchog bkra shis 'di byin pas //
NK023('a)001:14091: bum pa'i bkra shis thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:14092: ston pa la mgur nyid bum par de ring snying rje 'dzin pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:14093: mgur bum par bkra shis pa'i snying rjes thams cad 'dzin pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14094: mgur chus thugs rje kun 'dzin dbang //
NK023('a)001:14095: gzhan gyis mi thub bsdo ba'i phyogs mgur gyis mchog
NK023('a)001:14096: la mngon par gsal bar ston 'di ni bum pa
NK023('a)001:14098: gdugs kyis tsha ba'i sdug bsngal kun bsal te //
NK023('a)001:14099: nyon mongs ma lus kun las rgyal ba dang //
NK023('a)001:14100: che ba'i yon tan ma lus rgyas pa ste //
NK023('a)001:14101: log pa'i phyogs rnams zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK023('a)001:14102: ston pa la dbu skra gdugs su de ring gdung ba thams cad bsil ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:14103: dbu skra gdugs su bkra shis pas gdung ba thams cad bsil ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14104: dbu skra gdung sel gdugs kyi dbang /
NK023('a)001:14105: gzhan gyis mi thub bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams dbu skra'i mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:14106: 'di ni gdugs kyis dbang gi bkra shis so //
NK023('a)001:14107: nyan pa'i sgra rnams phyogs bcur sgrogs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14108: mu stegs log pa'i phyogs rnams sgrogs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14109: sems can kun gyis shes pa'i rgyud bsal phyir //
NK023('a)001:14110: gsung mchog dung gi rgyal por bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:14111: ston pa la tshems gsung ni dung du de ring
NK023('a)001:14112: khyod la rgol ba thams cad spa bkong ba'i dbang
NK023('a)001:14114: gsung du bkra shis pa rgol ba thams cad spa
NK023('a)001:14115: bkong zhing chos kyi sgra sgrogs pa'i dbang thob par
NK023('a)001:14116: gyur cig / dung gi rgol ba spa bkong sgrogs //
NK023('a)001:14117: gzhan gyis mi thub sdo ba'i phyogs gsung gi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:14118: 'di ni dung gi dbang gi bkra shis so //
NK023('a)001:14119: phyag zhabs nya bzhis bkra shis te //
NK023('a)001:14120: mdzes snyoms yid 'ong kun gyi dpal //
NK023('a)001:14121: nyon mongs gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //
NK023('a)001:14122: nya sha bkra shis gser nyar shog /
NK023('a)001:14123: ston pa la bdud kyis bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK023('a)001:14124: phyag dang zhabs kyi nya bzhir gser nyar 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:14125: de ring khyod la 'khor ba'i nyam nga med par shog /
NK023('a)001:14126: phyag dang zhabs nya bzhir bkra shis pas 'khor bar
NK023('a)001:14127: don mdzad kyang nyam nga med pa'i dbang dam pa
NK023('a)001:14129: phyag zhabs nya bzhis don mdzad kyang //
NK023('a)001:14130: gzhan gyis mi thub sdo ba'i phyogs nya sha bzhi la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:14131: 'di ni gser nya'i dbang gi bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:14132: dpal be'u thugs kyi bkra shis sa bon ni //
NK023('a)001:14133: 'dren pa rnams kyi thugs lags pas //
NK023('a)001:14134: bla med thar lam drangs ba'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:14135: thugs ni dpal gyi be'ura bkra shis shog /
NK023('a)001:14136: ston pa la bdud kyis bsdos pa'i dus su //
NK023('a)001:14137: thugs ni dpal gyi be'ura bkra shis gyur //
NK023('a)001:14138: de ring khyod la sbyin byas pas //
NK023('a)001:14139: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:14140: thugs dpal gyi be'ura bkra shis pas thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14141: dpal gyis be'u thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:14142: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:14143: sdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK023('a)001:14144: thugs kha nyid las mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK023('a)001:14145: 'di ni dpal pan+di ta 'bum phrag gsum pa'i gsung
NK023('a)001:14146: mas las thugs brtags thebs chen la'ang rdo rje rtse
NK023('a)001:14148: be'u dbang gi bkra shis so //
NK023('a)001:14149: dbang mchog dam pa'i bu mchog ste //
NK023('a)001:14150: don rnams 'grub par bkra shis phyir //
NK023('a)001:14151: bdud 'dul bkra shis rdzas mchog rnams //
NK023('a)001:14152: rtags kyis brgyan de sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:14153: dpal be'u thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:14154: rgyal mtshan bdud bzhi las rgyal dang //
NK023('a)001:14155: dung gis rgol ba spa bkong sgrigs //
NK023('a)001:14156: phyag mthil 'khor lo chos skor dbang //
NK023('a)001:14157: mgur bum thugs rjes kun 'jigs dbang //
NK023('a)001:14158: phyag zhabs nya bzhis don mdzad dbang //
NK023('a)001:14159: ljags kyi pad+ma gos med dbang //
NK023('a)001:14160: dbu skra gdugs kyis gdung sel dbang //
NK023('a)001:14161: rjes su mthun pa'i smon lam bya //
NK023('a)001:14163: rim pa la nges pa med kyis 'di don sangs
NK023('a)001:14164: rgyas kyi sku la mos thob 'dun pa gal che'o
NK023('a)001:14165: // don rnams 'grub pa'i bu mchog de //
NK023('a)001:14166: rdo rje'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:14167: zhing khams kun tu sgrags pa yis //
NK023('a)001:14168: rtsal gyi thig le rdo rje sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14169: ces thig le dpal chen gyis ming gdags so //
NK023('a)001:14170: bden pa rigs don dang mi 'gal ba'i ming gis dbang bskur bas /
NK023('a)001:14171: thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14172: nang dbang bcu gcig rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:14173: de nas sgrub dbang bcu gsum ni //
NK023('a)001:14174: skye med chos kyi dbyings las //
NK023('a)001:14175: sems kyis dbang bskur thob par yis //
NK023('a)001:14176: shes rab chen po rig pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:14177: sems lon don gyi gtan tshigs ni //
NK023('a)001:14178: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:14179: bden rigs dang po shes rab rig pa'i gtan tshigs sems lon sbyin /
NK023('a)001:14180: lta ba gtan tshigs shes rab gsum dang de bzhin
NK023('a)001:14181: nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:14182: / bsgrub dbang bcu gsum yod pa las dang po shes rab rig pa'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14183: kun 'dus kyi dbang byang nor bu 'phreng ba las /
NK023('a)001:14184: bsgrub pa'i rdzas kyi dbang skur ni //
NK023('a)001:14185: rigs kyi bu rnams dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK023('a)001:14186: brkyang phyag byas la steng du drang //
NK023('a)001:14187: bsgrub dbang bcu gnyis rdzogs par bskur //
NK023('a)001:14188: ces bsgrub pa'i lha dang dam rdzas sdom nas bcu
NK023('a)001:14189: gnyis su gsungs te slob bu 'dis bsgrub rdzas gtso
NK023('a)001:14191: dam tshig ting 'dzin shes rab dang /
NK023('a)001:14192: byang chub sems dang snying rje lnga po mthar phyin pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14194: nang dbang bcu gcig rdzogs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14195: de dag kun la spyod sgrub pa'i //
NK023('a)001:14196: bsgrub pa'i dbang rnams bskur bar bya //
NK023('a)001:14198: bsgrub dbang bcu gsum yod pa las //
NK023('a)001:14199: dbang po sgrub rdzas gtso bo dad 'dun brtson 'grus dang /
NK023('a)001:14200: bsgrub dbang dang po shes rab rig pa'i dbang dang de gnyis tsa ka cig tu mdzad pa lags /
NK023('a)001:14201: bya ba'i mtshan ma kun bral zhing //
NK023('a)001:14202: btsal med gnas pa'i byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:14203: snying rje chen po'i bde mchog gis //
NK023('a)001:14204: khams gsum kun la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK023('a)001:14205: dbang mchog khyod la sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:14206: bden rigs gnyis pa snying rje rtags kyi nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14207: ces dang rngam klog tu gnyis pa snying rje'i dbang
NK023('a)001:14208: bskur sbyin cig ces pas byang chub sems khams gsum
NK023('a)001:14209: ting 'dzin dang snying rje sgyu ma tshad med dang
NK023('a)001:14210: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin par
NK023('a)001:14211: gyur cig / sgrub dbang gnyis pa khams gsum dbang bsgyur gyi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14212: nyon mongs lnga po gnas dag pas //
NK023('a)001:14213: ye shes lnga po thob bya'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:14215: dbang thob de'i lag tu sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14216: bden rigs rngam klog tu gsum pa mig gi 'khor lo sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14217: ces pas stong nyid snying rje dbyer med dang sems
NK023('a)001:14218: nyid stong pa snang ba gnyis su med pa'i rig
NK023('a)001:14219: pa rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin par gyur cig
NK023('a)001:14220: / bsgrub dbang gsum pa yi ge 'khor lo'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14221: srid gsum 'gro ba'i don rnams kun //
NK023('a)001:14222: thams cad rdzogs par nub pa yis //
NK023('a)001:14223: rtags kyi dbang mchog dam pa ni //
NK023('a)001:14224: thong gshol 'bar ba sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:14225: bden rigs dbang don 'byed pa las /
NK023('a)001:14226: yi ge 'khor lo dang 'gro don thong gshol dril nas cig tu mdzad pa ltar du /
NK023('a)001:14227: dbang nor bu phreng ba las kyang mdzad /
NK023('a)001:14228: rngam glog tu bzhi pa thong gshol 'bar ba sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14229: ces te yi ge dang lha du mas rtog 'joms
NK023('a)001:14230: phyag rgya spros bcas bdag gzhan don byed kyi dbang
NK023('a)001:14232: bsgrub dbang bzhi pa 'gro don rdzogs byed thong gshol gyi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14233: rtags chen ga'u rnam pa gsum //
NK023('a)001:14234: dmar chen khrag gis bkang nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:14235: dbang thob de yi lag tu sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14236: dug gsum gtan sprugs thod pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:14237: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa yis //
NK023('a)001:14238: dug gsum gtan nas zad byed pa'i //
NK023('a)001:14239: ga'u gsum gyis dbang skur bas //
NK023('a)001:14240: sangs rgyas sku gsung thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:14241: bden rigs dbang don 'byed pa las /
NK023('a)001:14242: dug gsum sprugs pa'i ga'u rnam gsum sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14243: ces dang rngam glog tu ban d+ha gang pa sbyin dang lnga //
NK023('a)001:14244: zhes pas bar du gcod pa thams cad kyi dbang
NK023('a)001:14245: du mi 'gyur bar bus dam bcas 'tshams pa ji
NK023('a)001:14246: srid du dug gsum sku gsung thugs su bsgrub pa'i
NK023('a)001:14247: tshom bu tshogs chen du mas bsgrub pa dang /
NK023('a)001:14248: tshogs chen chig sgrub kyi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14249: bsgrub dbang lnga pa dug gsum gtan nas sprugs pa thod pa tshar gsum gyi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14250: thogs pa med pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK023('a)001:14251: dug gsum rtsad nas bcad pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:14252: ral gri la sogs mtshon cha yi //
NK023('a)001:14253: dbang mchog dam pa khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14254: bden rigs dbang don 'byed pa las /
NK023('a)001:14255: srid gsum sgrol ba'i ka tar mtshon cha sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14256: ces dang srid gsum yongs sgrol ces dang /
NK023('a)001:14257: rngam glog tu drug pa mtshon cha sna tshogs sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14258: ces don dam bden pa mthong ba'i lam bsnyen pa
NK023('a)001:14259: mthar phyin pas zag ldog med pa'i rig 'dzin du
NK023('a)001:14260: gyur cig / don dam du ni dkor bdun no //
NK023('a)001:14261: zhes rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK023('a)001:14262: chos dbyings rang byung ye shes dang bdun la gsungs
NK023('a)001:14263: / bsgrub dbang drug pa nyon mongs rtsad gcod mtshon cha'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14264: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i chos rnams la //
NK023('a)001:14265: spyad kyang gos par mi 'gyur ba'i //
NK023('a)001:14266: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK023('a)001:14267: pad ma'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:14269: skyon gyis ma gos rnam dag pad ma sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14271: ci spyod skyon bral pad ma zhes dang /
NK023('a)001:14272: rngam klog tu bdun pa skyon med pad ma sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14273: ces kun rdzob bden pa mthong ba'i lam nye bar
NK023('a)001:14274: bsnyen pa mthar phyin pas zag pa nyon mongs dang
NK023('a)001:14275: phyir ldog pa med pa'i rig 'dzin du gyur cig
NK023('a)001:14276: / kun rdzob tu ni mnyam rdzogs so //
NK023('a)001:14277: zhes pas don dam skye med du mnyam //
NK023('a)001:14279: bden pa gnyis dbyer med du mnyam /
NK023('a)001:14280: chen po phung po pad ma 'byung lnga rigs lnga yab yum du mnyam /
NK023('a)001:14281: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar mnyam pa ni mnyam pa lnga zhes so //
NK023('a)001:14282: bsgrub dbang bdun pa spyod bzhin ma chags pad ma'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14283: las rnams rdzogs par byed par yis //
NK023('a)001:14284: dbang mchog dam pa'i rtags chen 'di //
NK023('a)001:14285: sti ra dbyug pa chen po dag /
NK023('a)001:14286: dbang thob de'i lam du sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14287: zhing dbyug dgra sta dri bru la //
NK023('a)001:14288: rnam bzhi las kyis 'dul ba yi //
NK023('a)001:14289: phyag rgya chen po bstan pa ni //
NK023('a)001:14290: sti ra chen por dbyug pa'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:14291: skal ldan rnal 'byor khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14293: las rnams rdzogs pa ti ra'i dbyug pa sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14294: ces dang phyi nang las rdzogs sti ra'i dbyug /
NK023('a)001:14295: ces te dbyer med bden pa mthong ba'i lam bsgyub pa mthar phyin pas /
NK023('a)001:14296: zag ldog med pa'i rig 'dzin du gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14297: yang dag skyes mchog dam pa yis //
NK023('a)001:14298: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med par //
NK023('a)001:14299: mnyam pa nyid du rab tu rtogs //
NK023('a)001:14301: bsgrub dbang brgyad pa rnam bzhi las rdzogs sti ra dbyug pa'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14302: yum dang gnyis med 'khril pa yi //
NK023('a)001:14303: chos nyid don dang gnyis med rtags //
NK023('a)001:14305: dbang thob de'i lag tu sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14306: dpal chen shi ri re du la //
NK023('a)001:14307: phyogs bcu sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK023('a)001:14308: sbrul gyi chun pos dbang skur bas //
NK023('a)001:14309: thugs rje zhe sdang gnas su dag /
NK023('a)001:14310: de bzhin rnal 'byor che ge la //
NK023('a)001:14311: sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14312: bdud dang srin po kun bcom nas //
NK023('a)001:14313: 'jigs byed chen por mthur ldan shog /
NK023('a)001:14315: gnyis med 'khril ba'i sbrul gnag chun po sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14316: ces dang thabs shes dbyer na sbrul ces te //
NK023('a)001:14317: mngon sum por rtogs pa dmigs pa dang bral ba'i
NK023('a)001:14318: rang gsal lta bya lta byed lta ba gsum tha
NK023('a)001:14319: dad bral ba la mi bsgul bar dbyings nas mthong
NK023('a)001:14320: ba'i lam bsgrub pa chen po mthar phyin pas zag
NK023('a)001:14321: ldog med pa'i rig 'dzin du gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14322: sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur bas don dam dang
NK023('a)001:14323: kun rdzob dbyer med par rtogs pa'i don mngon pa'i
NK023('a)001:14324: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14325: bsgrub dbang dgu pa don dam dbyer med sbrul gnag chun po'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14326: gsang ba sbyor ba'i shes rab ma //
NK023('a)001:14327: dri med rnam ga dalha mo zhig /
NK023('a)001:14328: mtshan ldan shin tu brgyan byas la //
NK023('a)001:14329: dbang thob de la sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:14330: don dam rang bzhin spros bral bas //
NK023('a)001:14331: dri med rnam dag byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:14332: zhi byed gzungs ma'i rgyal mo'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:14333: skal ldan rnal 'byor khyod la sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14334: bden rigs dbang don 'byed pa las /
NK023('a)001:14335: gsang ba sbyor ba'i shes rab lha mo sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14337: nor bu phreng ba las dbang po yul sbyor yum zhes dang /
NK023('a)001:14339: bcu pa dri med lha mo sbyin /
NK023('a)001:14341: bsnyen sgrub bzhi sbyor grol lam mchog rdzogs shing sgrub
NK023('a)001:14342: pa'i rig 'dzin mthar phyin pas rnam par smin pa'i
NK023('a)001:14343: rig 'dzin dang tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin du
NK023('a)001:14344: gyur cig / bsgrub dbang bcu pa gnyis med sbyor rtags lha mo'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14345: dbang thob rgyal po chen po ste //
NK023('a)001:14346: kun gyi bdag po yin pas ni //
NK023('a)001:14347: rol mo dri dang zhal zas dang //
NK023('a)001:14348: 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14349: nye ba'i longs spyod rgyan rnams kun //
NK023('a)001:14350: thams cad thams cad sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:14351: bden rigs bza' dang bca' dang btung la sogs //
NK023('a)001:14352: rang sems rnam dag rgyan gyi phyir //
NK023('a)001:14353: gnyis med rol pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14354: bdud rtsi yid bzhin sku grub shog /
NK023('a)001:14355: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK023('a)001:14356: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad kun //
NK023('a)001:14357: spyod bzhin ma chags rol pa yi //
NK023('a)001:14358: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:14359: snang mdzad la sogs bdud rtsi yis //
NK023('a)001:14360: 'khor ba'i rtog pa gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:14361: dad ldan bu kun tshim par gyis //
NK023('a)001:14362: bdud rtsi rnam lnga'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:14363: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK023('a)001:14366: kun la dbang bsgyur 'dod yon rnam lnga sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14368: 'dod yon rdzogs pa longs spyod ces pa la //
NK023('a)001:14369: bza' btung dang rgyan chas stagglang chen zhing thod phreng
NK023('a)001:14370: sbrul khyung me rtag he ru ka 'dus pa'i rgyud
NK023('a)001:14371: kyi longs spyod thun mong dbang bcu dang /
NK023('a)001:14373: bdag gzhan bya ba yongs rdzogs dang //
NK023('a)001:14374: snang srid kun gyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14376: tshul khrims dang bzod pa dang brtson 'grus dang /
NK023('a)001:14377: bsam gtan dang shes rab dang /
NK023('a)001:14378: thabs la mkhas pa mthar phyin pas zag pa dang
NK023('a)001:14379: ldog pa med pa'i sgom lam phyag rgya chen por
NK023('a)001:14380: gyur cig / badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK023('a)001:14381: bden pa'i rjes la bza' btung gi dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:14382: yo byad rnam pa lnga la longs spyod pa'i dbang
NK023('a)001:14383: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14385: mnga' bdag chen po longs spyod sna tshogs dbang /
NK023('a)001:14386: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru la //
NK023('a)001:14387: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba ma lus pas //
NK023('a)001:14388: stag gi sham thabs byin pa yin //
NK023('a)001:14389: bdud dang srin po kun bsgral nas //
NK023('a)001:14390: ma tshogs mkha' 'gro dbang du bsdus //
NK023('a)001:14391: de bzhin rdo rje che ge la //
NK023('a)001:14392: stag gi sham thabs gsol ba yin //
NK023('a)001:14393: dpa' bo bdud las rgyal ba dang //
NK023('a)001:14394: rnam rtog 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:14395: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru la 'agre'o //
NK023('a)001:14396: phyogs bcu'i glang chen ko rlon /
NK023('a)001:14397: gti mug gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:14398: khams gsum bdag por gyur pa yin //
NK023('a)001:14399: de ring rnal 'byor che ge la //
NK023('a)001:14400: glang chen ko bas dbang gti mug gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:14401: mthu dpung chen po 'joms par shog /
NK023('a)001:14402: mthu dpung dbang chen thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:14403: sngon tshe bdud dang srin po la sogs pa //
NK023('a)001:14404: bcom ldan sku la bsdo ba'i tshe //
NK023('a)001:14405: phyogs bcu'i zhing gi g.yang gzhi bdud dang srin po btul ba ltar //
NK023('a)001:14406: 'khor ba rdul du brlag mdzad phyir //
NK023('a)001:14407: de ring rdo rje che ge la //
NK023('a)001:14408: zhing gi g.yang gzhis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14409: bdud dang srin po la sogs pa //
NK023('a)001:14410: thams cad 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:14411: sngon tshe phyogs bcu'i thod pa skam rlon nem drang gi //
NK023('a)001:14412: thod phreng tshar gsum mnga' gsol bas //
NK023('a)001:14413: sa gsum non nas sku gsum grub //
NK023('a)001:14414: de bzhin thod phreng tshar gsum dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14415: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14416: dug gsum gnas su dag nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:14417: thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:14418: thod pa skam po tshar gcig rlon pa tshar gcig neng drang dang tshar gsum /
NK023('a)001:14419: sngon tshe phyogs bcu'i sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14420: thugs rje zhe sdang gnas su dag /
NK023('a)001:14421: de bzhin rdo rje che ge la //
NK023('a)001:14422: sbrul gyi chun pos dbang skur bas //
NK023('a)001:14423: klu bdud srin po kun bcom nas //
NK023('a)001:14424: 'jigs byed chen po'i mthu ldan shog /
NK023('a)001:14425: dpal chen sh+r+ai he ru la //
NK023('a)001:14426: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK023('a)001:14427: khyung gi gshogs pas dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14428: bdud dang srin po zil gyis gnon //
NK023('a)001:14429: de bzhin rnal 'byor dbang phyug la //
NK023('a)001:14430: khyung gi gshog pas dbang skur bas //
NK023('a)001:14431: rdo rje khyung ltar thogs med par //
NK023('a)001:14432: mkha' ltar yongs la khyab par shog /
NK023('a)001:14433: thabs dang shes rab 'brel par shog /
NK023('a)001:14434: h+aum 'bar ba 'phro ba ye shes thugs rjer ldan //
NK023('a)001:14435: ye shes gsal bas phyogs bcur mun gnag sel //
NK023('a)001:14436: smug gnag sngo gnag ser gnag dang //
NK023('a)001:14437: dmar gnag ljang gnag 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK023('a)001:14438: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar bas dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14439: mtshan ma'i 'jig rten bsreg pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:14440: badz+ra dz+wa la ram dz+nya na h+aum /
NK023('a)001:14441: bden rigs pa bskal pa'i me ris dbang skur te //
NK023('a)001:14442: de dmar gnag tu 'bar bas dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14443: sngo gnag tu 'bar ljang gnag tu 'bar smug gnag
NK023('a)001:14444: tu 'bar ser gnag tu 'bar mthing gnag tu 'bar
NK023('a)001:14446: h'u he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK023('a)001:14447: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK023('a)001:14448: zhing chen gsar rnying sti rar bcas //
NK023('a)001:14450: khrag gi tshom bus mtshan pa ni //
NK023('a)001:14451: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig la //
NK023('a)001:14452: 'di yang rtags gyi phyag rgya ste //
NK023('a)001:14453: chos nyid zhag gis brgyan pa yi //
NK023('a)001:14454: zhag gi tshom bus dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14455: chos nyid dbyings su rgyal ba dang //
NK023('a)001:14456: gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul ba dang //
NK023('a)001:14457: che ba'i yon tan rgyal po dang //
NK023('a)001:14458: chos nyid zhag gi dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:14459: sarba ta tha ga ta a la la ho //
NK023('a)001:14461: dur khrod zhing chen dmar gyi thal ba'i mtshan mas brgyan pa 'di //
NK023('a)001:14462: gdug pa ma lus rab 'dul ba //
NK023('a)001:14463: che ba'i rgyal po kun gyi bdag /
NK023('a)001:14464: thams cad kun tu dpa' bo'i mtshan //
NK023('a)001:14465: gdug pa zil gnon thal ba'i mtshan //
NK023('a)001:14466: dbang mchog 'di yis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14467: khams gsum gdug pa thal bar rlog /
NK023('a)001:14468: de 'dra'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:14469: a pa ta ba ya h'u /
NK023('a)001:14471: khrag gi thig les 'di yang sngon /
NK023('a)001:14472: 'di yang rtags 'dod chags gnas su dag pa yi //
NK023('a)001:14473: khrag gi thig les rtags mtshan nas //
NK023('a)001:14474: khrag gi thig les dbang skur bas //
NK023('a)001:14475: gtum pa drag po 'joms pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14476: nga rgyal drag po 'dul mdzad cing //
NK023('a)001:14477: dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:14478: ma h+aa rag ta ni ti la ka h'u /
NK023('a)001:14479: rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur ro //
NK023('a)001:14481: bum pa dbu rgyan cod pan dang //
NK023('a)001:14482: phreng ba po ti rgya gram dang //
NK023('a)001:14483: 'khor lo ming dang mu tra dang //
NK023('a)001:14484: longs spyod bcu yi dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14485: thun mong dbang du rgyal bas gsungs //
NK023('a)001:14486: rdo rje dril bu dam rdzas dang //
NK023('a)001:14487: thod pa zhing dang stag lpag dang //
NK023('a)001:14488: ko ba me ri gshog pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14489: sbrul dang za byed phyag rgya dang //
NK023('a)001:14490: yum dang thong gshol mda' gzhu dang //
NK023('a)001:14491: rgyan gsum bcas pa la sogs pa //
NK023('a)001:14492: mdzes dang sdigs dang 'bar ba dang //
NK023('a)001:14493: rol pa'i rdzas kyis dbang skur ro //
NK023('a)001:14494: bdag gzhan bya ba yongs rdzogs phyir //
NK023('a)001:14495: nyan sgom la sogs 'chad pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14496: rdo rje slob dpon dbang sbyin las //
NK023('a)001:14497: thun mong phyag rgya'i cho ga bstan //
NK023('a)001:14498: rang la gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor dag /
NK023('a)001:14499: rnam pa'i tshul te mtshon dge dag /
NK023('a)001:14500: phyogs bcu dus gsum rdul snyed kyi //
NK023('a)001:14501: sangs rgyas zhing khams ma lus pa //
NK023('a)001:14502: dkyil 'khor lha ni gyur nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:14503: rol mo dbyings kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14504: de yi sems la 'jug par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:14505: gang du thabs ldan rnal 'byor la //
NK023('a)001:14506: snang srid phyi nang bcas pa kun //
NK023('a)001:14507: dbang gi rdzas su gyur nas kyang //
NK023('a)001:14508: de yi sems la 'jug par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:14511: khrag 'thung 'dus pa de'i byin rlabs dbang thob shog /
NK023('a)001:14512: bsgrub pa'i rgyal po de la ni //
NK023('a)001:14513: bsgrub pa'i las la dbang thob phyir //
NK023('a)001:14514: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'o //
NK023('a)001:14515: rgyal ba thams cad sgrub pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14516: rdo rje tshe dang sman la sogs //
NK023('a)001:14517: bsgrub pa ma lus sgrubs shig ces //
NK023('a)001:14518: bsgrub rdzas thams cad sbyin par bya'o /
NK023('a)001:14520: yig 'bru ka chen po 'di ni a nu sgrub
NK023('a)001:14521: dbang ltar du lha dbang thams cad 'dir mdzad pa'i
NK023('a)001:14522: gda' lags so // dbang yig rnying pa las /
NK023('a)001:14523: de nas rnga dang rdo rje dang dril bu dang phur pa dang phreng bas bskur /
NK023('a)001:14524: de nas dur khrod chas brgyad kyis dbang bskur te /
NK023('a)001:14525: zhag thal chen raka ta g.yang gzhi glang gi ko
NK023('a)001:14526: rlon stag gi pug 'doms sbrul thod pa tshar gsum
NK023('a)001:14527: / de nas ma mo rnam kyi dbang /
NK023('a)001:14528: de nas rig 'dzin gyi dbang bskur ces pa ni lha dbang 'di thog mar byed dus /
NK023('a)001:14529: gtso bo tshar pa dang sgrub rdzas dbang sngar ltar byas nas ma mo rnams ni //
NK023('a)001:14530: gnas ma yul ma dbang mo 'bar ma ging mkha'
NK023('a)001:14531: 'gro ma sring pho nya lhag sdud du dbang bskur
NK023('a)001:14532: / de nas rig 'dzin sgrub sde'i lha re dang snying po sdebs skur /
NK023('a)001:14533: de nas a nu man chad kyi rig 'dzin gang bkod bskur ba'i lugs /
NK023('a)001:14534: rngam glog ltar bsgrub rdzas dang bsgrub pa'i gtso bo gnyis /
NK023('a)001:14535: bsgrub dbang gcig tu gyil ba'i lugs yin /
NK023('a)001:14536: a ti'i rig 'dzin gsang dbang gi dus la'o //
NK023('a)001:14538: bsgrub pa'i rgyal po dkyil 'khor gtso bo sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14539: thams cad bsgrub pa'i bsgrub rdzas thams cad sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14541: sgrub chen yongs rdzogs zhes dang /
NK023('a)001:14542: rngam klog tu sgrub rdzas thams cad sbyin ces dang /
NK023('a)001:14543: phyag len du yang dag drug cu rtsa brgyad pa
NK023('a)001:14544: la sogs pa thod sku bam rdzas dang bcas pa
NK023('a)001:14545: gnang ba'o // bden rigs bsgrub pa'i rgyal po dkyil
NK023('a)001:14546: 'khor gtso bo dang bsgrub rdzas kyis dbang bskur bas
NK023('a)001:14547: gnang ba'o // / thabs la mkhas pa sems can gyi don dang /
NK023('a)001:14548: smon lam rdzu 'phrul dang stobs bcu brnyes pa'i byang
NK023('a)001:14549: chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa dang ye shes lnga
NK023('a)001:14550: mthar phyir pas ye shes sku'i rnal 'byor sangs rgyas
NK023('a)001:14551: su lung ston kun gyis thos par thob pa sgom
NK023('a)001:14552: lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin thob par gyur
NK023('a)001:14553: cig / bsgrub dbang bcu gnyis pa mnga' bdag chen po dam rdzas sgrub pa'i dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14554: dkyil 'khor gtso bo zhi ba rigs drug gam //
NK023('a)001:14555: che mchog la sogs bstan la /
NK023('a)001:14556: +aa h+aum g+hu ya dz+nya na bo re tsi ta ma h+aa su ka h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK023('a)001:14557: sgo byang phyi a kro te ka ya man ta ka ha na ma th+aa b+hany+dza h+aum phata /
NK023('a)001:14558: sgo byang nang h+r+aih pad ma ta krid badz+ra kro
NK023('a)001:14559: ta ha ya g+hi ba hu lu hu lu h+aum
NK023('a)001:14560: phata / pad ma ta kri med pa'ang mdzad /
NK023('a)001:14561: mar me ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum phata /
NK023('a)001:14562: dgongs 'dus las ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK023('a)001:14564: ru lu gces pa'i don drug nas a ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK023('a)001:14567: ru lu ru lu h'u phata b+h+yo ces so //
NK023('a)001:14568: sman phud bdud rtsi a h+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+ai th+aa zhes so //
NK023('a)001:14569: bsnyen phur badz+ra k+ai li ki la ya sarba big nan h+aum phata /
NK023('a)001:14570: rak+ta ma mo thams cad kyi ru lu'o //
NK023('a)001:14571: ma chen du h+aum sh+r+ai he ru ka mum kro
NK023('a)001:14572: ti shwa ri s+t+wom h+aum ha he phata m+aa ma
NK023('a)001:14573: yo gi ni ru lu b+h+yo zhes so //
NK023('a)001:14574: g+hu ya dz+nya na sh+r+ai he ru ka kro ti shwa ri s+t+wom zhes bka' brgyad du'o //
NK023('a)001:14575: rig 'dzin dgongs 'dus su ma h+aa g+hu ru shwa ri ram gyi li h+aum /
NK023('a)001:14576: phud gtor ma bka' brgyad du ma h+aa g+hu ru sarba h+aum phata /
NK023('a)001:14578: drag gdon 'jin rten mchod bstod dang drag sngags //
NK023('a)001:14579: badz+ra tsan+da ma ha ro kha na h+aum phata /
NK023('a)001:14580: che rdzas la b+h+rum badz+ra a yu she h+aum a spyi'o //
NK023('a)001:14581: khyad par mi la ni b+h+rum badz+ra a yu she dza dza h'u a /
NK023('a)001:14584: badz+ra tsan+da li ha ni brum badz+ra a yu she dza dza h+aum a dza h+aum bam ho /
NK023('a)001:14585: zhes pa la a h+aum s+w+aa h+aa dang h+aum tram
NK023('a)001:14586: hri a dang e la sogs pa lha'i sa bon
NK023('a)001:14588: ni dang rni gnyis ka 'dam ka'o //
NK023('a)001:14589: rdo rje sems dpa'i khrus bum la yig brgya dang /
NK023('a)001:14590: theg pa 'og ma nyan rang lha mi'i bar gang 'os bshad /
NK023('a)001:14591: bcu gsum grags pa rdo rje ming gi dbang //
NK023('a)001:14592: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK023('a)001:14593: dbang thob de gnyis gcig pa'i phyir //
NK023('a)001:14594: rig 'dzin rdo rje rtsal gyi dbang //
NK023('a)001:14595: rdo rje'i ming ni sbyin par bya'o //
NK023('a)001:14596: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:14597: bden rigs dbang don 'byed pa las /
NK023('a)001:14598: gnyis su med pa thig le rtsal gyis dbang bskur bas //
NK023('a)001:14599: lha dang gnyis su med par lung bstan to //
NK023('a)001:14601: rdo rje 'chang gral ming zhes dang //
NK023('a)001:14602: rngam klog tu rdo rje gsang ming sbyin zhes pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14603: brod pa skyed phyir kun tu 'od //
NK023('a)001:14604: rdor 'dzin stug po bkod par bstan //
NK023('a)001:14605: mthar thug sa gsum cha las brjod //
NK023('a)001:14606: ces pas ma ha pad ma spyan drangs /
NK023('a)001:14607: a nu ye shes bla ma 'khor lo'i sa thob par gyur cig /
NK023('a)001:14608: bsgrub dbang bcu gsum pa grags pa rdo rje ming gi dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14610: a nu'i theg pa rdzogs soha&a&a&a //
NK023('a)001:14611: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo la //
NK023('a)001:14612: bla ma sku'i rnal 'byor slob pa ni /
NK023('a)001:14613: bla ma zhal gcig phyag zhabs gnyis //
NK023('a)001:14614: bsnyen mthing bsgrub dus smug gnag de'i //
NK023('a)001:14615: g.yas dbu 'das pa'i sangs rgyas bdun //
NK023('a)001:14616: g.yon dbu ma byon sangs rgyas bdun //
NK023('a)001:14617: dbus dbu da ltar sangs rgyas bdun //
NK023('a)001:14618: sku gsung thugs che'i yon tan dang //
NK023('a)001:14619: phrin las dbyings dang ye shes bdun //
NK023('a)001:14620: dbu stengs 'khor lo sku chos ston //
NK023('a)001:14621: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar rin po che //
NK023('a)001:14622: gsung bstan longs spyod rdzogs dbus thugs //
NK023('a)001:14623: mchod rten bdun sdom nyer gcig la //
NK023('a)001:14624: rgyal mtshan bcu re tog bum lnga //
NK023('a)001:14625: kun bsdom chig bsdom lnga bcu yang //
NK023('a)001:14626: phyogs bcu rigs lnga a tir 'dus //
NK023('a)001:14627: rgyal byed lcags kyi rgyal mtshan dang //
NK023('a)001:14628: gdul bya sha ba gcan gzan gzig /
NK023('a)001:14629: sprul pa rdo rje rin chen sbrul //
NK023('a)001:14630: dpa' bo stag dang gzi mdangs mi //
NK023('a)001:14631: dmar gsal khrag dang rtsal seng ge //
NK023('a)001:14632: gtum chen dom dang gser gyi tog /
NK023('a)001:14634: zhabs kyi gdan khri yan chad nas //
NK023('a)001:14635: dbu'i gtsug tor man chad du yongs su rdzogs par mthong ngo //
NK023('a)001:14636: dbu la byung ba'i sangs rgyas nyi shu rtsa gcig
NK023('a)001:14637: dang rgyal mtshan chen po bcu la rdzogs pa'i rnal
NK023('a)001:14638: 'byor yongs su rdzogs par mthong ngo //
NK023('a)001:14639: dbu'i gtsug tor rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la gser
NK023('a)001:14640: gyi tog stong ni rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor
NK023('a)001:14642: de ltar mthong zhing gsal bar gyur pa dang /
NK023('a)001:14643: chos thams cad sku la yongs su rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:14645: phyag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ni khrag 'thung 'bar ba bzhi /
NK023('a)001:14647: za byed pha bcu bsod byed ma bcu ste bzhi rtsa gnyis su gsal lo //
NK023('a)001:14648: zhal nyi shu rtsa gcig ni srid pa za byed
NK023('a)001:14649: gsal ba'i dur khrod nyi shu rtsa gcig tu gsal
NK023('a)001:14650: lo // spyan 'bar drug cu rtsa bzhi ni /
NK023('a)001:14651: he ru ka drug cu rtsa bzhi gsal lo //
NK023('a)001:14652: dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas nyi shu rtsa gcig tu gsal lo //
NK023('a)001:14653: zhes dang zhabs brgya la gsang yum bzhi dang sgo ma bzhi rdzogs par mthong ngo //
NK023('a)001:14654: dur khrod kyi rgyan chen po bco brgyad ni ma
NK023('a)001:14655: mo chen mo bco brgyad yongs su rdzogs par gsal
NK023('a)001:14656: lo // zhes dang khro bo'i sgrub thabs las /
NK023('a)001:14658: ma brgyad 'bar ma g.yon pa ste //
NK023('a)001:14659: phra men bcu phyed g.yas g.yon bsnams //
NK023('a)001:14660: dur khrod sbrul brgyad thod gsum dang //
NK023('a)001:14661: de bzhin ko gsum rtags gsum drug /
NK023('a)001:14662: pre ta a dza la sogs pa'i //
NK023('a)001:14663: dur khrod rtags brgyad bco brgyad 'bar //
NK023('a)001:14665: phra men bcu dbyug lag na khyung //
NK023('a)001:14668: lag na seng ge kha dbyal brgya //
NK023('a)001:14671: lag na stag ser mche gtsigs brgyad //
NK023('a)001:14672: kha nas rdo rje sna tshogs 'phro //
NK023('a)001:14673: ma brgyad dbyug 'phyar lag pa na //
NK023('a)001:14674: mi mgo rdo rje lu gu brgyud //
NK023('a)001:14675: glad la bskor bar byed pa'o //
NK023('a)001:14677: lag na me brgyad thu lum 'phro //
NK023('a)001:14679: yum yang lus dang grib ma'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:14682: me dpung chen po dgu las ye shes kyi sgo dgu rtseg yongs su 'bar bar mthong ngo //
NK023('a)001:14684: ci phyir yab yum pho mor 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:14686: gang 'dul thabs shes gnyis dbyer med //
NK023('a)001:14687: yum dang yab snang yab kyang yum //
NK023('a)001:14688: nges par bya zhing khro gzhung las //
NK023('a)001:14689: yum yang lus dang grib ma'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:14690: gtso bo'i thugs las thon nas ni //
NK023('a)001:14691: mthing gnag dur khrod brgyad dang ldan //
NK023('a)001:14692: g.yas 'khyud g.yon pa gtso la stobs //
NK023('a)001:14693: zhes dang gtso bo mthing gnag dang //
NK023('a)001:14694: mdog smug phrin las kyi gzhung las //
NK023('a)001:14695: smug gnag sku ni 'bar ba can //
NK023('a)001:14696: gsang ba'i yum yang yab dang mthun //
NK023('a)001:14697: zhes pa gang rung mkha' gsang brlab //
NK023('a)001:14699: h+aum las rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i //
NK023('a)001:14700: pam las pad mor gyur pa'i dbus //
NK023('a)001:14702: yum gyi pad ma'i gzhal yas su //
NK023('a)001:14703: gsang ba byang chub sems 'phro dad brtson dang //
NK023('a)001:14704: h+aum chen drug cu rtsa bzhi pa //
NK023('a)001:14705: ha he phata bcu phrag gnyis dang //
NK023('a)001:14706: de bzhi h+aum chen nyi shu dbang //
NK023('a)001:14707: spros nas gdan la rim bzhin bkod //
NK023('a)001:14708: ces gtso bo ma h+aa yo ga'i sku /
NK023('a)001:14709: pad ma kha stong gyen byed dmar //
NK023('a)001:14711: nyi zla nyi shu rtsa brgyad 'bar //
NK023('a)001:14712: de steng dbang phyug khyo blugs ni //
NK023('a)001:14713: spyi bcings nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i gdan //
NK023('a)001:14714: steng nas byol song gtso brgyad gnas //
NK023('a)001:14715: dpal stag 'jigs seng gdug pa'i gzig /
NK023('a)001:14716: gtum dom stobs glang ma he brjid //
NK023('a)001:14717: 'dzin pa'i chu sprin zhe sdang sbrul //
NK023('a)001:14718: rig 'dzin sgrib pa sbyang phyir gnas //
NK023('a)001:14719: dbang phyug sde tshogs gsum gsum mnan //
NK023('a)001:14720: 'khor rnams nyi ma zhing chen gdan //
NK023('a)001:14721: bu mo nyi shu zhing gi gdan //
NK023('a)001:14722: h+aum chen nyi ma phyogs skyong ste //
NK023('a)001:14723: gzhan dag zhing skam gdan sogs sbyor //
NK023('a)001:14724: ces pas gsang dbang phyi dkyil 'khor //
NK023('a)001:14725: khro bcu bar du mkha' las sras //
NK023('a)001:14726: lhag ma gtor len ma gyi sogs //
NK023('a)001:14727: yang na sras rnams sku la brgyan //
NK023('a)001:14728: yum yang yab kyi gsang ba 'jib //
NK023('a)001:14729: dbu dgu zhabs brgyad phyag bco brgyad //
NK023('a)001:14730: rdor dril ke sing g.yas g.yon 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:14733: de 'og ta grid khro brgyad las //
NK023('a)001:14734: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa bdud rtsi bdag /
NK023('a)001:14735: khams gsum rnam rgyal pad ma 'khyil //
NK023('a)001:14736: rta mgrin chu bcas gsang yum bdag /
NK023('a)001:14737: kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' gzhal yas //
NK023('a)001:14738: theg dgu me klong yum 'byung lnga //
