NK023('a)001:14739: yo ga tri ya rdo rje'i brag /
NK023('a)001:14740: byang sems nor bu mu tig 'od //
NK023('a)001:14741: nyan rang ke rus ri rab 'og /
NK023('a)001:14742: gzugs khams zhing sa mkha' rlung chu //
NK023('a)001:14744: kun 'dus bdud rtsi pho brang ngo //
NK023('a)001:14745: gsang ba man ngag chu bo la //
NK023('a)001:14747: dbang thob slob de'i lus dkyil 'khor //
NK023('a)001:14748: sems dang dran phyir dgongs 'dus las //
NK023('a)001:14749: ches kun mi shes ma rtogs kyang //
NK023('a)001:14750: dam par gyur pa'i bla ma la //
NK023('a)001:14751: bskur gnas rim 'gro cher byas pas //
NK023('a)001:14753: ces gsungs yid grol zhal gcig dang /
NK023('a)001:14754: chos grol gtsug rgyan zhal nyer gcig /
NK023('a)001:14755: mig sna rna ba lce lus yid //
NK023('a)001:14756: gzugs dri sgra ro reg chos kyi //
NK023('a)001:14757: skye mched bcu gnyis rnam shes drug /
NK023('a)001:14758: dbang po yul drug khams bco brgyad //
NK023('a)001:14759: gsang ba'i dbang shes yul dang gsum //
NK023('a)001:14760: nyer gcig grol zhing rtse bas khros //
NK023('a)001:14761: che mchog zhi mthing khro smug gnag /
NK023('a)001:14762: bla ma'i zhal gcig che mchog dang //
NK023('a)001:14763: dpal chen rigs bdag badz+ra bud //
NK023('a)001:14765: g+hu ya bi sha'o sa ma nu //
NK023('a)001:14766: yaka sha raka sha h+aum rnam rgyal //
NK023('a)001:14767: dbyug sngon gshin rje mi g.yo ba //
NK023('a)001:14768: rta mgrin dpal ldan bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK023('a)001:14769: khams gsum rnam rgyal stobs po che //
NK023('a)001:14770: mthing gnag dbu gtsug rta mgo can //
NK023('a)001:14771: sbas spyan dang bcas drug cu bzhi //
NK023('a)001:14772: he ru gro bzhi le tshe'i mthar //
NK023('a)001:14773: sa nu sa ne sa no dang //
NK023('a)001:14774: sa pa ra ste cho 'phrul bzhi //
NK023('a)001:14775: kro ti dang bcas 'khor lo gcig /
NK023('a)001:14776: le tshe phyogs bzhi'i bud+ha dang //
NK023('a)001:14777: rad na pad ma karma rnams //
NK023('a)001:14778: yum bcas mtshan gyi rnam grangs ni //
NK023('a)001:14779: rdo rje bya rog go phur dang //
NK023('a)001:14780: gying dang las mkhan cho 'phrul ni //
NK023('a)001:14781: me long ye shes nam mkha'i dbang phyug dang //
NK023('a)001:14782: mnyam nyid ye shes rnam grol sbyin pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14783: sor rtog ye shes rnam grol sgrogs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14784: bya grub ye shes thams cad grub pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:14785: nam mkha'i bu mo dbang mo chen mo dang //
NK023('a)001:14786: nam mkha'i bu mo dga' sdud chen mo dang //
NK023('a)001:14787: nam mkha'i bu mo rnam par gdung ma dang //
NK023('a)001:14788: nam mkha'i bu mo sgrol ma chen mo rnams //
NK023('a)001:14789: rigs bzhi'i cha lugs g.yon dril bu //
NK023('a)001:14790: g.yas na rdo rje rin chen dang //
NK023('a)001:14792: bsgrub dus g.yon pa thod khrag rol //
NK023('a)001:14794: badz+ra rad na pad ma karma sa nu sa no
NK023('a)001:14795: sa nengs sa bar ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka
NK023('a)001:14797: gti mug rdo rje phyag 'khor lo'ang //
NK023('a)001:14798: rdo rje can gyi phyag mtshan gsang //
NK023('a)001:14799: bud d+ha badz+ra he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:14800: sangs rgyas rdo rje khrag 'thung ba'o //
NK023('a)001:14802: sarba ta th+aa ga ta dam tshig badz+ra rad na pad ma karma garba /
NK023('a)001:14803: tshad med me tri ka ru lo ka bi du garba /
NK023('a)001:14804: rol pa yak+sha sha raka sha b+hig sha b+hi sha /
NK023('a)001:14805: 'jigs byed te sha ke sha pa sha bi sha /
NK023('a)001:14806: 'joms byed traka sha hri sha ka sha baka sha /
NK023('a)001:14807: za byed ru ti raka ti kha hi swa ha /
NK023('a)001:14810: sku mdog bzlas pa'i le'u ltar //
NK023('a)001:14811: smug nag sngo gnag ser gnag dang //
NK023('a)001:14812: dmar gnag ljang gnag rtsa ba'i mdog /
NK023('a)001:14813: de kun gsal ces 'grel pas gsungs //
NK023('a)001:14814: smug gnag gtso sngags yab kun 'dus //
NK023('a)001:14815: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK023('a)001:14816: ma h+aa tsan tra sarba dush+tana seng ha sh+r+ai he
NK023('a)001:14817: ru ka ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa
NK023('a)001:14818: h+aum h+aum h+aum / seng ha shwa ra ka mum /
NK023('a)001:14820: che mchog sngo gnag shar smug gnag /
NK023('a)001:14821: rgyud rigs lnga lung cho 'phrul zur //
NK023('a)001:14823: gnyis pa dam tshig chen po gsungs //
NK023('a)001:14824: gsung gi thugs yon gsung phrin sku //
NK023('a)001:14825: dam tshig chen po rdo rje snying //
NK023('a)001:14826: dam tshig chen mo rdo rje dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:14827: nor bu pad ma bkod pa'i snying po'i yum //
NK023('a)001:14828: nor bu pad ma bkod pa'i dbang phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:14829: 'khor lo gsum pa tshad med chen po'i 'khor //
NK023('a)001:14830: gsang chen byams pa snying rje dga' btang snyoms //
NK023('a)001:14831: snying po bzhi yab yum bzhi tshad med thugs //
NK023('a)001:14832: bde ba'i dbyings phyug 'joms byed dbyings phyug ma //
NK023('a)001:14833: dga' ba'i dbyings phyug khyab pa'i dbyings phyug ma'o //
NK023('a)001:14834: 'khor lo bzhi pa rol pa chen po'i 'khor //
NK023('a)001:14835: che ba'i yon tan yab rigs yum rigs ni //
NK023('a)001:14836: gnod sbyin 'dul zhing phrag dog zad //
NK023('a)001:14837: srin po sgrol zhing zhe sdang 'joms //
NK023('a)001:14838: lha min sgrol zhing dregs rgyal zad //
NK023('a)001:14839: lha chen sgrol zhing ga ti mug zad //
NK023('a)001:14840: 'khor lo lnga pa 'jigs byed chen po ni //
NK023('a)001:14841: phrin las mdzad pa yab yum snang //
NK023('a)001:14842: te sha he ru rdo rje 'khros //
NK023('a)001:14843: rgyal bar byed cing rtog pa sgrol //
NK023('a)001:14844: ke sha he ru rin chen 'khros //
NK023('a)001:14845: rol pas sdug bsngal chos nyid sbyong //
NK023('a)001:14846: pa sha he ru pad ma 'khros //
NK023('a)001:14847: za mdzad nyon mongs ye shes sgrol //
NK023('a)001:14848: bi sha he ru las kyi khros //
NK023('a)001:14849: myos mdzad dran pa ye shes bsgrol //
NK023('a)001:14850: 'khor lo drug pa 'joms byed chen po'i 'khor //
NK023('a)001:14851: rnam shes dbang thob sgrol nus ye shes kyis //
NK023('a)001:14852: bsgral ba gnas su stobs pa'i khyad par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:14853: zung 'brel phyogs bzhi yab phyogs yum mtshams bzhi //
NK023('a)001:14854: trag shas gsod cing zhal du gsol //
NK023('a)001:14855: hri shas chags shing sdud pas gsol //
NK023('a)001:14856: ka shas rol cing zad par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:14857: bag shas nyams shing stongs par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:14858: drug de'i gong ras za byed che //
NK023('a)001:14859: ru ti he ru zhag za yum dbyings phyug /
NK023('a)001:14860: rdo rje rigs te rtog pa zad par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:14861: raka ti he ru khrag za yum dbyings phyug /
NK023('a)001:14862: rin chen rigs te 'dod chags zad par mdzad //
NK023('a)001:14863: kha hi he ru sha za yum dbyings phyug /
NK023('a)001:14864: pad ma rigs te gti mug gtan nas sbyong //
NK023('a)001:14865: seng ha he ru rtsi dang rus za ba //
NK023('a)001:14866: sa ha shwa ri yum chen dbyings phyug rnams //
NK023('a)001:14867: gdug tshogs bsgrol kyang phung po longs spyod gsol //
NK023('a)001:14868: las la za byed bam chen khas bzung 'drad //
NK023('a)001:14869: 'jams bam lag thogs 'jigs bam chen po khur /
NK023('a)001:14870: rol pa mche ba tshad med so 'phreng thogs //
NK023('a)001:14871: dam tshig snying po thod pa na khengs sbyin //
NK023('a)001:14872: cho 'phrul rdo rje thod khrag rigs dang rtags //
NK023('a)001:14873: zhes te kun 'dus khro bo'i bsgrub thabs bshad /
NK023('a)001:14874: mdo khro lha yi bsgrub thabs las //
NK023('a)001:14875: gtso bo mthing gnag chen po ste //
NK023('a)001:14876: smug gnag ser gnag dmar gnag dang //
NK023('a)001:14877: ljang gnag khrag 'thung drug cu bzhi //
NK023('a)001:14878: rdo rje rin chen pad ma gri //
NK023('a)001:14879: gar sogs cir yang 'gyur bas thogs //
NK023('a)001:14880: rdo rje snying po la sogs rnams //
NK023('a)001:14881: sbyin mthun yo byad sna tshogs dang //
NK023('a)001:14882: thod khrag so phreng mche ba thogs //
NK023('a)001:14883: de bzhin bam chen thogs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:14884: bam chen lag thogs khas bzung nas //
NK023('a)001:14886: zhes te 'khor lo gsum ltar du //
NK023('a)001:14889: mtha' za dbus na le tshe rigs //
NK023('a)001:14890: bla ma che mchog zhi mthing la //
NK023('a)001:14891: zhi lha zhe gnyis phyag g.yas pa /
NK023('a)001:14892: kun bzang rnam snang mtha' mi'o //
NK023('a)001:14893: g.yon yum mtha' yid dmyal ba'i thub //
NK023('a)001:14894: che mchog smug phyag rigs bzhi khro //
NK023('a)001:14895: khra thabs nyi shu gying bco brgyad //
NK023('a)001:14896: sman sras yab bzhi'o rigs bzhi mthun //
NK023('a)001:14897: gying gri zhabs brgyad gsang yum sgo //
NK023('a)001:14898: dbang mchog dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad //
NK023('a)001:14899: rdo rje thod khrag de 'og tu //
NK023('a)001:14900: rnam shes phul rnams ke sing ni //
NK023('a)001:14901: rig pa ye shes 'khor bstan pa //
NK023('a)001:14902: gsang ba'i bu mo dkar mo dang //
NK023('a)001:14903: dga' ba'i bu mo seng gdong dang //
NK023('a)001:14904: shin tu gus pa'i bu mo ni //
NK023('a)001:14905: rta phag spre spyang gdong gzhan mthun //
NK023('a)001:14906: thabs shes rol sras ke seng dang //
NK023('a)001:14907: zhe gnyis phyag mtshan phra men bcu //
NK023('a)001:14909: shin tu gsod pa chen po ni //
NK023('a)001:14910: rnam rgyal stag gi dbu sogs bcu //
NK023('a)001:14911: shin tu gsod pa yum dang bcas //
NK023('a)001:14912: sgo thed phyogs bzhi khyams mtshams bzhi //
NK023('a)001:14913: steng 'og khyams kyi shar nub sogs //
NK023('a)001:14914: badz+ra kro ta kro ti h+aum /
NK023('a)001:14915: zhi ba lha zhal drag mgo brnyan //
NK023('a)001:14916: h+aum ka ra ni phag mgo can //
NK023('a)001:14917: rnam par rgyal ba stag gi dbu /
NK023('a)001:14918: dbyug pa sngon po g.yag rog dbu //
NK023('a)001:14919: gshin rje gshed po sha ba'i dbu //
NK023('a)001:14920: mi g.yo mgon po gzig gi dbu //
NK023('a)001:14921: rta mgrin mgo ljang ze rngog dmar //
NK023('a)001:14922: pral zhur gzi mig phum ser cing //
NK023('a)001:14923: rdzi ma gnag la sku dmar gnag /
NK023('a)001:14924: dpal ldan gzhan gyis mi thub pa //
NK023('a)001:14925: spyang gu'i mgo can nub byang mthun //
NK023('a)001:14926: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa seng ge'i dbu //
NK023('a)001:14927: khams gsum rnam rgyal dred mo'i dbu //
NK023('a)001:14928: stobs po che ni dom gyi dbu //
NK023('a)001:14930: h+aum chen mthing skya mda' gzhu dang //
NK023('a)001:14931: rnam rgyal dkar po rdo rje 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:14932: dbyug sngon sdigs mdzub rin chen khri //
NK023('a)001:14933: gshin rje mthing gnag be chen thogs //
NK023('a)001:14934: mi g.yo ljang sngon ral gyu 'phyar //
NK023('a)001:14935: rta mgrin dmar gnag sbrul zhags bsnams //
NK023('a)001:14936: dpal ldan dmar skya ba dan te //
NK023('a)001:14937: bdud rtsi ljang gnag dbyug tho'o //
NK023('a)001:14938: khams gsum ljang skya kha dong kha //
NK023('a)001:14939: stobs chen dud kha gtun shing thogs //
NK023('a)001:14940: yum rnams g.yas pa yab la 'khyud //
NK023('a)001:14941: g.yon pa ban d+ha stob pa'i tshul //
NK023('a)001:14942: 'khor rnams so so'i gzhung bzhin no //
NK023('a)001:14944: snying po brjod pas 'khor lo shar //
NK023('a)001:14945: sa bon zhi he ru h+aum //
NK023('a)001:14946: kro ti mum dang gsang yum bzhi //
NK023('a)001:14947: sgo ma dza h+aum bam ho mthun //
NK023('a)001:14948: rang rtog phung po lnga ni chags sdang rmongs //
NK023('a)001:14949: 'byung ba dang snyigs snyoms snang lnga zhen dang //
NK023('a)001:14950: rnam shes dbang po yul dus rtag chad pa //
NK023('a)001:14951: bdag dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa rang grol tshe //
NK023('a)001:14952: bla ma'i thugs kyi rtsa bzhi brgyad gyes nyid //
NK023('a)001:14953: yan lag bzhi dang sku lus spyan snyan shangs //
NK023('a)001:14954: ljags zur g.yas g.yon khrag 'thung rigs lngar mthong //
NK023('a)001:14955: phyag rgyab sogs lhu g.yas g.yon spyi lhu dang //
NK023('a)001:14956: skra mtshams 'khal ma g.yas g.yon gsang rtags rnams //
NK023('a)001:14957: ke'u ri tsan d+ha'i bar mthong bar lhu barla //
NK023('a)001:14958: lag ngar g.yas g.yon zhabs ngar sing ha brgyad //
NK023('a)001:14959: phyag mthil g.yas g.yon zhabs mthil sgo mar mthong //
NK023('a)001:14960: lhag mgron dam can sras la mi 'don kyang //
NK023('a)001:14961: dga' mchog dga' bral lhan skyes skye sbas rtsa //
NK023('a)001:14962: gsang yum sgal tshigs las byed rlung rgyu dbang //
NK023('a)001:14963: mi srin nas ni skyeg gdong bar zhes gsungs //
NK023('a)001:14964: snying dang rgyu ma glo ba long mo dang //
NK023('a)001:14965: mtshe pa pho ba mchin pa snyi mo dred //
NK023('a)001:14966: mkhal ma gnyis dang chu rgang bu snod rlung //
NK023('a)001:14967: ma bdun sring bzhi'o snying khar e ka dza //
NK023('a)001:14968: rdo rje ma rnams thams cad ces ma brgyad //
NK023('a)001:14969: e ka 'a dza ti byang shar dang shar du //
NK023('a)001:14970: rdo rje gar gyi dbang phyug rdo rje kun grags ma'o //
NK023('a)001:14971: rdo rje gsal 'phro rdo rje kun tu bzang //
NK023('a)001:14972: lho nub rdo rje chen po ye shes mchog /
NK023('a)001:14973: rdo rje dpung snyoms drag snyems nub kyi phyogs //
NK023('a)001:14974: rdo rje sgrol ma 'od chags nub byang du //
NK023('a)001:14975: rdo rje srog gcod g.yu sgron bya //
NK023('a)001:14976: rdo rje thabs ni thams cad ces ma'i yab //
NK023('a)001:14977: ces pas zhar la thabs mchog kun mthun to //
NK023('a)001:14978: ma brgyad zhing dbyug mi mgo thu lum 'phro //
NK023('a)001:14979: ma sring chags pa'i mdangs zhes dmar ba'am bshad //
NK023('a)001:14980: da ni rdo rje gying bco brgyad //
NK023('a)001:14981: dpa' bo chen po las kun byed //
NK023('a)001:14982: rdo rje chags pa chen po dang //
NK023('a)001:14983: gnod sbyin srid po ro langs dang //
NK023('a)001:14985: phyogs 'dus mtshams la lang ka dang //
NK023('a)001:14986: rdo rje 'chi bdag gying pho dgu //
NK023('a)001:14987: de dang sbyar ba'i gying mo brgyad //
NK023('a)001:14988: khams gsum dbugs 'gyengs chen mo dang //
NK023('a)001:14989: rdo rje lcags kyus 'dren byed che //
NK023('a)001:14990: stong gsum dbang sdud chen mo dang //
NK023('a)001:14991: rbod gtong len par byed ma che //
NK023('a)001:14992: gar gyi glog bzhin 'gyu ba che //
NK023('a)001:14993: rna nyan phra ma zor ba che //
NK023('a)001:14994: rbod gtong len par byed ma che //
NK023('a)001:14995: khams gsum snying rjes sgrol ma che //
NK023('a)001:14996: tshogs kyi phyag tshang mnyen byed che //
NK023('a)001:14997: phyag mtshan gzhan mthun ces rgyud las //
NK023('a)001:14998: sngo skya g.yas pa dri dang ni //
NK023('a)001:14999: g.yon pa 'dzin pa lta byed gsungs //
NK023('a)001:15000: ma mo b+h+yo gyi ha ha gnyis //
NK023('a)001:15001: yang na ma sring ma ma gnyis //
NK023('a)001:15003: phra men he dang 'bar ma phata //
NK023('a)001:15004: mkha' 'gro du ma'ang so gnyis khyams //
NK023('a)001:15005: bsdus na che mchog phyag mtshan brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15006: slob dpon pad ma 'byung gnas kyis //
NK023('a)001:15007: phyi ltar lha mo yum chen mo //
NK023('a)001:15009: gsang ltar sngags srungs ma mo bshad //
NK023('a)001:15010: sku lus rdo rje mkha' 'gro shar //
NK023('a)001:15011: yon tan rin chen mkha' 'gro lho //
NK023('a)001:15013: phrin las mkha' 'gros grub byed byang //
NK023('a)001:15014: byang shar dam tshig bka'i bya ra //
NK023('a)001:15016: lho nub gter len sha za dang //
NK023('a)001:15017: nub byang sna tshogs rigs 'dres tshogs //
NK023('a)001:15018: mkha' 'gro thugs rjes chags phyir dmar //
NK023('a)001:15019: mkha' la 'gro rtags gshog pa can //
NK023('a)001:15020: byang chub sems ldan zhi ma khro //
NK023('a)001:15021: zhar la shugs 'gro dang bcas pa //
NK023('a)001:15023: seng ge kha dbyal brgyad kha nas //
NK023('a)001:15027: dga' bar byed dang 'dren byed ma //
NK023('a)001:15028: spro bar byed dang gsod byed ma'o //
NK023('a)001:15029: lhor 'bar bar byed dang gzi brjid ma //
NK023('a)001:15030: 'joms byed ma dang bung bu'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:15031: nub tu chags chen ma dang chags mchog ma //
NK023('a)001:15033: byang du sna tshogs lus dang srung ba mo //
NK023('a)001:15034: gnod sbyin mo dang yang dag 'phrog /
NK023('a)001:15035: shar lho du bya rog gdong la mig 'dru zhing //
NK023('a)001:15036: bzhad gdong 'ug pa'i gdong ris ma //
NK023('a)001:15037: sna chogs mchog gzugs srung ba mo //
NK023('a)001:15038: lho nub tu rnga mo bong bu'i gdong 'dzin cing //
NK023('a)001:15039: khros pa ra dang byi lha'i gdong //
NK023('a)001:15040: khros pas keng rus phreng bas blubs //
NK023('a)001:15041: nub byang du gsus po che la lto 'phyangs po //
NK023('a)001:15042: gsus po che la bum pa 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15043: phan tshun 'thab par brtson pa mo //
NK023('a)001:15044: lce spyang gi ni 'khor can no //
NK023('a)001:15045: byang shar du shar nyid du ni bum rna ste //
NK023('a)001:15047: nub tu d+ha sha g+hi ba ste //
NK023('a)001:15048: byang nyid du ni 'bod grogs so //
NK023('a)001:15049: rgyud rnams kha cig de sgo bzhir //
NK023('a)001:15050: bkod nas mtshams la gsum blang byang shar 'og /
NK023('a)001:15051: kha cig rigs lnga'am shar mkha' 'gro //
NK023('a)001:15052: zhes sogs brgyad bzhi so gnyis khyams //
NK023('a)001:15053: sgo bzhi skyar lhag ngo bo gcig /
NK023('a)001:15054: khyams la shugs 'gro brgyad ces pa //
NK023('a)001:15056: mkha' la shugs kyis 'gro bas na //
NK023('a)001:15059: stag mo mche gtsigs de kha nas //
NK023('a)001:15062: mkha' 'gro rdul snyed yod pa la //
NK023('a)001:15064: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed bzhugs //
NK023('a)001:15065: gsum pa'i khyams la phra men brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15066: de bzhin 'bar ma brgyad rnams bri //
NK023('a)001:15067: zhes pa'i sgo 'grams gsum pa ni //
NK023('a)001:15068: 'bar ma'i gsang yum bzhi sgo bshad //
NK023('a)001:15069: yang na rang phyogs sgo des bsrung //
NK023('a)001:15070: rdo rje phra men phyag bcu la //
NK023('a)001:15071: smigs bu'i mgo can la sogs bshad //
NK023('a)001:15072: phyogs bcu'i phra men za byed bcu'o //
NK023('a)001:15073: zhar la gsod byed phra men bcu //
NK023('a)001:15074: khro bo mgo brnyen bcu pho nya //
NK023('a)001:15075: phra men kun bsdus khyams la brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15077: rdo rje phra men thams cad ni //
NK023('a)001:15078: khyab byed chen mo khyung gi 'khor //
NK023('a)001:15079: gsod byed chen mo sre mo'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:15080: mgyogs ma snyeg byed khra yi mgo //
NK023('a)001:15081: 'byin byed pu shud myos byed ni //
NK023('a)001:15082: pu shud mgo can phra men ma //
NK023('a)001:15083: rkun mo byi ba gdug byed sbrul //
NK023('a)001:15084: sgrin byed pha wa mgo dang brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15085: phyag mtshan phra men bcu ltar du //
NK023('a)001:15086: dbyug pa phyar ba'i lag pa na //
NK023('a)001:15087: khung brgyad kha nas mtshon cha 'phro //
NK023('a)001:15088: yul gyi phra men seng ge'i mgo //
NK023('a)001:15090: 'bar ma shar nas chos skor du //
NK023('a)001:15091: kun bzang 'bar ma nyi zer zhags //
NK023('a)001:15094: yid btags me khyer glog phren 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15096: gshin rje bgegs rgyal ba glang sna //
NK023('a)001:15097: lha min gnod sbyin skar mda' gtong //
NK023('a)001:15098: dmyal ba sngo gnag tshub ma'i lus //
NK023('a)001:15099: kun bzang thub phyogs nges med khyab //
NK023('a)001:15100: phyag mtshan zhing dbyug kha nas ni //
NK023('a)001:15102: 'bar ma'i gnod sbyin phor thogs brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15103: 'bar ma'i sring mo gzhon thogs te //
NK023('a)001:15104: de rnams gdan phur dud 'gro ni //
NK023('a)001:15105: seng ldeng tsan dan phur pa dang //
NK023('a)001:15106: skyer phur rdo rje'i phur bu dang //
NK023('a)001:15107: zhing rkang mchog phur lcags phur dang //
NK023('a)001:15108: ba glang brgyad dang stag chen brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15109: brgyad ldan shar nas rim bzhin du //
NK023('a)001:15110: sgo grangs bzhi pa'i khyams la phor thogs brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15111: de la rdo rje gnod sbyin thams cad ces //
NK023('a)001:15112: byi ru'i phor thogs gser gyi phor thogs dang //
NK023('a)001:15113: g.yu yi phor thogs mchong gi phor thogs dang //
NK023('a)001:15114: gser gyi phor thogs lcags kyi phor thogs dang //
NK023('a)001:15115: g.yu'i phor thogs khro chu'i phor thogs ma'o //
NK023('a)001:15116: khyams phyir phor pa de dang rgyu mthun pa'i //
NK023('a)001:15117: lag na gzhong pa thogs ma brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15118: sa bon spor thogs h+aum ltar gzhong thogs h+aum //
NK023('a)001:15119: pho nya 'og b+h+yo steng khro h+aum //
NK023('a)001:15120: phyogs dza h+aum bam ho pho nya'o //
NK023('a)001:15121: dbang phyug b+h+yo dang slob dpon h+aum /
NK023('a)001:15122: rdo rje srin po thams cad ces //
NK023('a)001:15123: byi ru gser g.yu mchong gser lcags //
NK023('a)001:15124: khro chu'i rgyu las gzhong pa brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15125: de bzhin phyag na gzhong thogs rnams //
NK023('a)001:15126: sku la rin chen shel gyi rkyed chings can //
NK023('a)001:15127: rkyed la tshi gu 'bar ba'i rkyed chings can //
NK023('a)001:15128: me tog 'gun d+he legs pa'i rkyed chings can //
NK023('a)001:15129: shin tu pags chen brjid pa'i skyed chings can //
NK023('a)001:15130: zhing lpags 'bar ba dang rus sbal 'bar ba dang //
NK023('a)001:15131: chu srin 'bar ba'i rkyed chings can rnams ni //
NK023('a)001:15132: phor gzhong khyengs pas gtso bo 'khor bcas mchod //
NK023('a)001:15133: bdag tshim 'gro la sbyin spel dngos grub ster //
NK023('a)001:15134: lnga pa'i dbang phyug sgo ma bzhi //
NK023('a)001:15135: mi srin nas ni skyeg gdong bar ces so //
NK023('a)001:15136: de ni dkyil 'khor lngar bstan to //
NK023('a)001:15137: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i khyams //
NK023('a)001:15138: de mthar rdo rje mngag pa zhes //
NK023('a)001:15139: pho nya sum brgya drug cu ni //
NK023('a)001:15140: mkha' 'gro phra men rgyas bsdus ltar //
NK023('a)001:15141: pho nya'ang bsdus na gtso mo bcu //
NK023('a)001:15142: shar nas mi mo gser gyi mdun zhu can //
NK023('a)001:15143: shar lho dung gi spyang mo mgo dgu ma //
NK023('a)001:15144: lho nas mi mo gser gyi rtag tshul ma //
NK023('a)001:15145: lho nub lcags spyang mgo dgu ma //
NK023('a)001:15146: nub nas bu mo tshul mchu can //
NK023('a)001:15147: nub byang zangs spyang mgo dgu ma //
NK023('a)001:15148: byang nas mi lo lcags mchu ma //
NK023('a)001:15149: byang shar g.yu spyang mgo dgu ma //
NK023('a)001:15150: steng nas lcags kyi bya khra che //
NK023('a)001:15151: 'og nas lcags kyi byi ba che //
NK023('a)001:15152: zhes pa he ru 'dus rgyun du //
NK023('a)001:15153: lus bcud rtsa yi mdud pa ni //
NK023('a)001:15154: sum brgya drug cu khyab gnas te //
NK023('a)001:15155: khyab cing 'gugs pa'i las byed pa //
NK023('a)001:15156: skra rtse thig le khyab byed cing //
NK023('a)001:15157: ba spu'i thig le chags bcas pa //
NK023('a)001:15158: yang sprul 'phro zhing nyid la bsdu //
NK023('a)001:15160: phyi dang nang chags mkha' 'gro ma //
NK023('a)001:15161: skra rtse ba spu 'bum gyi cha //
NK023('a)001:15162: thabs dang thig le gar 'phros pa //
NK023('a)001:15163: rtog pa gang skyes der bsdud pa //
NK023('a)001:15164: yang sprul phyag rgya'i tshogs su brjod //
NK023('a)001:15165: ces te rig 'dzin grub thob kyi //
NK023('a)001:15166: mkha' 'gro yang sprul skra spur bshad //
NK023('a)001:15168: srid pa gsum gyi phyag byas pa //
NK023('a)001:15169: bla ma'i sa la gnas pa ni //
NK023('a)001:15170: dbang mchog sum cu rtsa drug yin //
NK023('a)001:15171: phyi yi dbang dang nang gi dbang //
NK023('a)001:15172: bsgrub ba'i dbang dang gsang ba'i dbang //
NK023('a)001:15173: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK023('a)001:15174: rnam pa gnyis kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:15176: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK023('a)001:15177: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bos bya //
NK023('a)001:15178: zhes te slob bu blo dman no //
NK023('a)001:15180: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga la //
NK023('a)001:15181: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bos bya //
NK023('a)001:15183: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la //
NK023('a)001:15184: bsgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bos bya //
NK023('a)001:15186: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga la //
NK023('a)001:15187: gsang ba man ngag chu bos bya //
NK023('a)001:15189: lha grangs lnga brgya gya gsum mthun par gsungs /
NK023('a)001:15190: dbang don dang ni 'dus rgyud las /
NK023('a)001:15191: kun bzang bde chen dkyil 'khor ni //
NK023('a)001:15192: che mchog sku la chos kun rdzogs //
NK023('a)001:15193: a nu'i khyad chos gtso las gzhan //
NK023('a)001:15194: zhi ba zhe gnyis rdo rje dbyings //
NK023('a)001:15195: rgyud lung nyi shu steng gi khro //
NK023('a)001:15197: gnas yul sgo 'bar dbang gsang yul //
NK023('a)001:15198: khrag 'thung rol pa sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK023('a)001:15199: mkha' 'gro gying bsdom lnga bcu la //
NK023('a)001:15200: skyes bu las kyi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK023('a)001:15201: phyogs bzhi'i pho nya'i khyams de ni //
NK023('a)001:15203: ma bdun sring bzhi 'og ma mo //
NK023('a)001:15204: dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK023('a)001:15205: rig 'dzin slob dpon sbyin bdag bcas //
NK023('a)001:15207: bka' brgyad bsgrub chen theg bstan kun //
NK023('a)001:15208: tshogs chen 'dus pa rtsa ba dang //
NK023('a)001:15209: yan lag dkyiil 'khor rgyas bsdus gsungs //
NK023('a)001:15210: zhi khro dam pa rigs brgya dang //
NK023('a)001:15211: pho nya sum brgya drug cu dang //
NK023('a)001:15212: 'bar ma dbang phyug gsang bzhi bcu //
NK023('a)001:15213: kun sdom lnga brgya ma bdun dang //
NK023('a)001:15214: sring bzhi khro yab yum nyi shu //
NK023('a)001:15215: sum cu rtsa gcig lum ltar kyang //
NK023('a)001:15216: rigs kyi khro bo kun la bsdom //
NK023('a)001:15217: gying dang mkha' 'gro lnga bcu dang //
NK023('a)001:15218: rigs bdag zhi khro sdom gya gsum //
NK023('a)001:15219: lnga brgya gya gsum thim kun 'dus //
NK023('a)001:15220: seng ha he ru yab yum gnyis //
NK023('a)001:15221: rigs bzhi yab yum brgyad le tshe //
NK023('a)001:15222: cho 'phrul dam tshig tshad med dang //
NK023('a)001:15224: za byed yab yum brgyad tshan bdun //
NK023('a)001:15225: ke'u ri sing ha brgyad sgo bzhi //
NK023('a)001:15226: khro bcu ma brgyad gying bco brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15228: phra men bcu dang 'bar ma brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15229: pho thogs brgyad dang gzhong thogs brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15230: dbang mo nyer brgya che mchog che //
NK023('a)001:15231: sang nga yab yum sras sdom gcig /
NK023('a)001:15232: pho nya sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK023('a)001:15233: lha bskyed cho ga 'dzab mang po'am //
NK023('a)001:15234: kun bsdus lha gcig gsal bla ma'ang //
NK023('a)001:15235: mkha' dkyil dang par dbyings nyi zla //
NK023('a)001:15236: ye shes rgyal po stangs dbyangs sgom //
NK023('a)001:15237: mthing gnag zhal gcig phyag zhabs gnyis //
NK023('a)001:15238: rdo rje thod khrag 'khyud yum bcas //
NK023('a)001:15239: thugs mtshan h+aum bskyed 'bum bzlas pa'i //
NK023('a)001:15240: bla mas gsang dbang bskur thob bya //
NK023('a)001:15241: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kun //
NK023('a)001:15242: ma lus bar ni sgoms par 'gyur //
NK023('a)001:15244: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo la //
NK023('a)001:15245: dbang gnyis gsungs pa 'di bzhin te //
NK023('a)001:15246: gsang dbang shes rab ye shes dang //
NK023('a)001:15247: bde chen shin tu brtan pa rnams //
NK023('a)001:15248: bsgrub pa'i dbang mchog thob pa dang //
NK023('a)001:15249: gsang ba'i bdag po yin pas na //
NK023('a)001:15250: gsang ba'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK023('a)001:15251: dga' ba byang chub sems chen po //
NK023('a)001:15252: kun tu tshim par byed pa'i ro //
NK023('a)001:15253: dkar dmar lhag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:15254: dbang thob de yi lce la bzhag /
NK023('a)001:15255: dbang mchog gsang dbang thob par shog /
NK023('a)001:15256: a ho ma h+aa su ka ho zhes pa bla ma'i man ngag go //
NK023('a)001:15257: ka ni kun rdzob byang sems la gru gsum mthing
NK023('a)001:15258: gnag dal na pad ma dmar po 'dab ma brgyad
NK023('a)001:15259: pa gcig gi steng na rdo rje ser po gcig
NK023('a)001:15260: gi rtse mo bzhog gcig pad ma'i lte ba la
NK023('a)001:15262: zab mo dbang gsum rdzogs pa dang //
NK023('a)001:15263: bla ma thabs shes dbang gsol la //
NK023('a)001:15264: slob ma bde skyid gang bde'i sbyin //
NK023('a)001:15265: dga' ba byang chub sems chen po //
NK023('a)001:15266: dkar dmar lhag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:15267: kun tu tshim par byed pa'i ro //
NK023('a)001:15268: bu mchog de yi lce la bzhag /
NK023('a)001:15269: a h+ao ma h+aa su ka ho //
NK023('a)001:15270: gnyis med don dam byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:15271: bu mchog de yi snying la bzhag /
NK023('a)001:15272: ma h+ao ma h+aa su ka ho //
NK023('a)001:15273: dbang mchog de la'ang gsum thob nas //
NK023('a)001:15274: don dam kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK023('a)001:15275: lus sems ye shes che mchog shog /
NK023('a)001:15276: tsa ka rdo rje 'grom bu'i skyed pa la dar dpyangs sngon dmar can tsa ka rnying pa'o //
NK023('a)001:15277: zab mo dbang gsum zhes pa ni /
NK023('a)001:15278: thabs kyi gsang dbang la ba dang be'u'i tshul du dbang bskur ba dang /
NK023('a)001:15279: shes rab kyi gsang dbang la bya dang bye'u'i tshul du dbang bskur ba dang /
NK023('a)001:15280: thabs shes gnyis med tshul du dbang bskur ba bum
NK023('a)001:15281: pa dang me tog gi tshul du dbang bskur ba
NK023('a)001:15282: la gnyis te / slob dpon lces blangs te bskur ba dang /
NK023('a)001:15283: bum pa sbrang rtsi'i tshul slob dpon slob mas bsgrubs pa'i bdud rtsi sman la brten pa'o //
NK023('a)001:15284: de rdzogs nas zab dbang gsang ba'i dbang rdzogs nas kyang /
NK023('a)001:15285: tshe la zab dbang shes rab ye shes ni slob
NK023('a)001:15286: ma la yum gtad bdud rtsi phab pa'i dga' ba
NK023('a)001:15287: dang zab dbang shes rab ye shes dbyer med bde
NK023('a)001:15288: ba chen po la bzlog pa'i dga' ba dang /
NK023('a)001:15289: zab dbang shes rab ye shes shin tu brtan pa la khrems nas gnas su bskyal ba'o //
NK023('a)001:15294: che mchog thugs kyi sprul pa ni //
NK023('a)001:15295: las kyi mon pa nag po bzhengs //
NK023('a)001:15296: g.yas pas gri gug rnon po 'dar //
NK023('a)001:15297: g.yon pa ban d+ha snying khrag 'thung //
NK023('a)001:15298: zhabs gnyis dam nyams steng na bgrad //
NK023('a)001:15299: mchod cing bstod pa'i tshe na mthing gnag dar phod ljang ber can //
NK023('a)001:15300: sdang ba dgra la chas pa'i tshe na gcer bu bya yi gshog pa can //
NK023('a)001:15301: gnod byed bgegs la chas pa'i tshe na ljang sngon drag po gsal shing can //
NK023('a)001:15302: gnas 'dir 'dug la bka' yi bstan pa bsrungs /
NK023('a)001:15303: h+aum rnal 'byor yongs kyi dpal mgon mchog /
NK023('a)001:15304: ma h+aa ka la mthu rtsal can //
NK023('a)001:15305: khyod ni rig 'dzin yongs kyi srog shing yin //
NK023('a)001:15306: chos skyong yongs kyi rje bo yin //
NK023('a)001:15307: dregs can yongs kyi dbang phyug yin //
NK023('a)001:15308: sngags 'chang yongs kyi dgra lha yin //
NK023('a)001:15310: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i bsrungs ma'i mchog /
NK023('a)001:15311: bdag gi'ang srungs mar mnga' gsol gyis //
NK023('a)001:15312: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa yi //
NK023('a)001:15313: longs spyod zas nor khyod kyis srungs //
NK023('a)001:15314: bka' yis bkrol ba'i las grub mdzod //
NK023('a)001:15315: mgon po khyod mchod byin brlabs kyis //
NK023('a)001:15316: phyogs dang dus kun thams cad du //
NK023('a)001:15317: sems can legs don 'byor pa dang //
NK023('a)001:15318: bgegs kyi rnam pa kun med shog /
NK023('a)001:15319: rta dang ba glang nor dang 'bru //
NK023('a)001:15320: bu tsha pha ma gnyen bshes rnams //
NK023('a)001:15321: dge zhing tshe ring nad med par //
NK023('a)001:15322: thams cad 'byor pa ldan par shog /
NK023('a)001:15323: rgyal po dge zhing ded dpon rnams //
NK023('a)001:15324: chos kyi yul 'khor skyong bar shog /
NK023('a)001:15325: 'gro kun nyes med bde gyur nas //
NK023('a)001:15326: nad dang mu ge kun bral shog /
NK023('a)001:15327: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa 'di //
NK023('a)001:15328: phyogs bcu kun tu rgyas pa dang //
NK023('a)001:15329: myur du sems can thams cad kyang //
NK023('a)001:15330: chos kyi snod du gyur par shog /
NK023('a)001:15331: bdag cag yon mchod 'khor bcas kyang //
NK023('a)001:15332: dpal mgon dbang phyug legs ldan gyi //
NK023('a)001:15333: mthu byin thugs la dbang thob nas //
NK023('a)001:15335: 'bur kur ma h+aa pad+ma rnge 'bur tsi 'bur byig ge byi ma na se /
NK023('a)001:15336: e ho sh+ao mo kro ta /
NK023('a)001:15337: h+aum h+aum phata phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:15339: 'bur du kurma a pra rna bu tsi ki phyi
NK023('a)001:15340: byi ma na se a sho mo ga kro ta
NK023('a)001:15341: h+aum h+aum phata phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK023('a)001:15345: u tsu sma kro ta h+aum phata /
NK023('a)001:15349: re re zhing 'bum rdzogs nas las grub bo //
NK023('a)001:15353: // // bsod nams gter sbyin cha gsum gtor //
NK023('a)001:15354: shog gu gsum po 'di mgron thabs su 'phan thag gi gsal dbang ngo //
NK023('a)001:15355: mgron lha dpon mgon don gnyis ni //
NK023('a)001:15356: lha mi'i skar ma'i bkra shis mdzad //
NK023('a)001:15357: thub pas tshong dpon la gsung skad //
NK023('a)001:15358: nyan thos rgyal chen bzhi gsungs zhes //
NK023('a)001:15359: gnas brtan 'od srungs bskos pa'i tshe //
NK023('a)001:15360: tshangs dang rgya byin bcas la gsungs //
NK023('a)001:15361: rang rgyal dge 'dun mang po ni //
NK023('a)001:15362: klu brgyad klu tshogs srung mar bskos //
NK023('a)001:15363: byang sems phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la //
NK023('a)001:15364: skyabs 'gro phyogs skyong bcu gcig bskos //
NK023('a)001:15365: sangs rgyas bstan pa kun khyab tu //
NK023('a)001:15366: phyag rdor sdigs mdzub stong lha skyong //
NK023('a)001:15368: lha brgyad klu brgyad gza' brgyad ni //
NK023('a)001:15369: phyogs skyong nyi zla phyogs bcu gcig /
NK023('a)001:15370: rgyu skar nyer brgyad gnod sbyin brgyad //
NK023('a)001:15371: rgyal chen bzhi ste bdun cu lnga //
NK023('a)001:15372: gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje bzhi //
NK023('a)001:15373: sdom pas bdun cu don gnyis bshad //
NK023('a)001:15374: gnod sbyin brgyad las cog bzhi la //
NK023('a)001:15375: gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje can //
NK023('a)001:15376: sngon po'am rigs bzhi'i phyogs kyi mdog /
NK023('a)001:15377: rdo rje 'chang bas ri rab srung //
NK023('a)001:15378: gnod sbyin ha ri ka dang ni //
NK023('a)001:15379: pany+tsi ka dang nar ti ka /
NK023('a)001:15380: lcags khrab gyon zhing mtshon cha thogs //
NK023('a)001:15381: gnod sbyin 'phrog ma ral pa can //
NK023('a)001:15382: sngo nag ral gri bu lnga brgya //
NK023('a)001:15383: gtsug lhag grong brdal kun tu rgyud //
NK023('a)001:15384: dpal mgon don lnga gling bye brgya'i //
NK023('a)001:15385: stong chen phyogs kun srung zhing skyong //
NK023('a)001:15386: rgyal chen bzhi las yul 'khor srung //
NK023('a)001:15387: ljang khu 'am dkar po pi wam sbreng //
NK023('a)001:15389: spyan mi bzang dmar sbrul mgo can //
NK023('a)001:15390: rdo rje sbrul zhags mchod rten 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15391: rnam thos sras ni ljang gu'am ser //
NK023('a)001:15392: rin chen be con ne'u le bzung //
NK023('a)001:15393: ne'u le'ang nor bu bsam 'phel zos //
NK023('a)001:15394: shar lho nub byang ri rab srung //
NK023('a)001:15395: bang rim bzhi lha logs lha min //
NK023('a)001:15396: rol mtsho'i bar nas 'gro ba drug /
NK023('a)001:15397: gling bzhi'i mi dang ngan 'gro skyob //
NK023('a)001:15398: cog brgyad srog shing steng 'og bcur //
NK023('a)001:15399: ri rab phyogs skyong bcu gcig ni //
NK023('a)001:15400: shar phyogs in+t+ra rgya byin gtong //
NK023('a)001:15401: dkar por rdo rje gdengs pa snams //
NK023('a)001:15402: shar lho me lha aka ne ser //
NK023('a)001:15403: dmar nag bgrang phreng las mthun 'dren //
NK023('a)001:15404: lha phyogs gshin rje ya ma ni //
NK023('a)001:15405: sngo nag mi mgo'i thod dbyug thogs //
NK023('a)001:15406: lho nub bden bral srin po ni //
NK023('a)001:15407: ni ri ti smug ral gri 'byin //
NK023('a)001:15408: nub phyogs chu lha ba tu ni //
NK023('a)001:15409: klu dbang dkar po'am dmar sbrul zhags //
NK023('a)001:15410: nub byang rlung lha ba ya be //
NK023('a)001:15412: byang phyogs gnod sbyin ku be ra //
NK023('a)001:15413: ljang ser dbyug tho phyag na snams //
NK023('a)001:15414: byang shar dbang ldan i sha na //
NK023('a)001:15415: thal skya tri shul rtse gsum mdung //
NK023('a)001:15417: sa yi lha mo pra ti wi //
NK023('a)001:15418: gser mdog zhags pa'am bum pa gang //
NK023('a)001:15419: steng phyogs nyi ma sur+ya ye //
NK023('a)001:15420: dmar ser phyag na pad ma snams //
NK023('a)001:15421: steng phyogs zla ba tsan+t+ra ye //
NK023('a)001:15422: dkar ser me tog ku mu ta //
NK023('a)001:15423: pad ma nyin mo kha phye nas //
NK023('a)001:15424: nub mo zum ltar pho skad tsha //
NK023('a)001:15425: ku mud mtshan mo kha phye nas //
NK023('a)001:15426: nyin mo zum ltar mo skad snyan //
NK023('a)001:15427: nyi zla'i 'od kyis nyin mtshan du //
NK023('a)001:15428: phyed pa'i mun pa 'dod khams gzugs //
NK023('a)001:15429: gzugs med sangs rgyas lha yul na //
NK023('a)001:15430: mun chen snang bas nyin mtshan du //
NK023('a)001:15432: me tog kha 'byed nyi zla'i rigs //
NK023('a)001:15433: des khyab dkar phyogs skyong ba mchod //
NK023('a)001:15434: phyogs skyong gcig kyang kun khyab phyir //
NK023('a)001:15435: nag phyogs skyong la phur pas btab //
NK023('a)001:15436: dus 'khor phyogs bcu stong tshangs ljang //
NK023('a)001:15438: lha chen brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK023('a)001:15439: shar ru dbang phyug chen po dkar //
NK023('a)001:15440: mdung rtse gsum pa'i tri shul 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15441: lhor ni dbang po mchod sbyin che //
NK023('a)001:15442: brgya byin ser po rdo rje gdengs //
NK023('a)001:15443: nub tu tshangs ser rin chen 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15445: shar lho 'dod lha'i dbang phyug dmar //
NK023('a)001:15447: lho nub tshogs bdag dkar khra ste //
NK023('a)001:15448: sta gri so gnyis yod par bshad //
NK023('a)001:15449: nub byang 'bring gi ri ti ni //
NK023('a)001:15450: keng rus mdog ltar dkar ba la //
NK023('a)001:15451: phyag na rin chen sgrom gang 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15452: byang shar gzhon nu gdong drug dmar //
NK023('a)001:15453: sh+aaka ti mdung thung mi tshad 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15454: de yis lha brgyad thim na yang //
NK023('a)001:15455: lha chen bcu gnyis byed pa ltar //
NK023('a)001:15456: de mthar byang shar lha stobs bzang //
NK023('a)001:15457: ljang khu thong pa'i gshol mda' 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15458: nub byang dga' byed dbang phyug dmar //
NK023('a)001:15459: ka tar ral gri thong gshol 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15460: lho nub nag po chen po nag /
NK023('a)001:15461: mig gsum lag na rtse gsum 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15462: shar lho seng ge'i mgo nag po //
NK023('a)001:15465: b+han da ka rna zhes bya ba //
NK023('a)001:15466: lha mo dril bu'i rna rgyan can //
NK023('a)001:15467: snyan cha seng ge g.yas g.yon sbrul //
NK023('a)001:15468: nag mo thod pa khrag bkang 'thung //
NK023('a)001:15469: dkyil 'khor klu brgyad kho na byed //
NK023('a)001:15470: gtso bo'ang sbrul mgo sbrul rgyan ltar //
NK023('a)001:15471: phyogs skyong gtso bo go mtshon can //
NK023('a)001:15472: mtha' yas dkar po ud pal shar //
NK023('a)001:15474: ud pa la 'am rin chen lho //
NK023('a)001:15475: stobs kyis rgyu nag sbrul 'dzin nub //
NK023('a)001:15476: rigs ldan rin chen sgrom rkyal byang //
NK023('a)001:15477: shar lho nor rgyas ser bum pa //
NK023('a)001:15478: lho nub dung skyong dung 'bud ljang //
NK023('a)001:15479: nub byang pad ma dmar pad 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15480: byang shar pad ma chen po ni //
NK023('a)001:15481: chu lha rin chen sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15482: kun kyang sbrul mgo sbrul mjug can //
NK023('a)001:15483: rgyud gzhan klu chen grangs mang yang //
NK023('a)001:15484: 'di yi chu lhas kun tshang pa'o //
NK023('a)001:15485: gza' chen brgyad po nyi zla dang //
NK023('a)001:15486: mig dmar gza' lhag lag pa dang //
NK023('a)001:15487: phur bu pa sangs spen zhag bdun //
NK023('a)001:15488: skad cig tsam re spen nyi yi //
NK023('a)001:15489: 'tshams la sgra gcan rtag tu rgyu //
NK023('a)001:15490: shar phyogs pa wa sangs dkar po //
NK023('a)001:15491: phyag g.yas me tog kun mu ta //
NK023('a)001:15492: phyag g.yon shing tog bzang po 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15493: lho phyogs phur bu 'thing po ti //
NK023('a)001:15494: nub phyogs zla ba dkar po ni //
NK023('a)001:15495: mchod sbyin me tog ku mu ta //
NK023('a)001:15496: byang phyogs lhag pa ljang khu ni //
NK023('a)001:15497: mchod sbyin me tog ud pa la //
NK023('a)001:15498: shar lho mig dmar mdog dmar g.yas //
NK023('a)001:15499: bum po'i g.yon pa me sgron 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15500: lho nub sgra gcan dud ka na //
NK023('a)001:15501: sku stod mi la sku smad sbrul //
NK023('a)001:15502: pad sdong g.yas la ral gri g.yon //
NK023('a)001:15503: nub byang nyi ma'i g.yas pad ma //
NK023('a)001:15504: g.yon pa mtha' ber dbyug pa 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15505: byang shar spen pa dmar nag ni //
NK023('a)001:15506: g.yas pa dbyug tho g.yon dgra sta //
NK023('a)001:15507: mdo rgyud gzhan gyi gza' mang po //
NK023('a)001:15508: thams cad sgra gcan nyid la tshang //
NK023('a)001:15509: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni //
NK023('a)001:15510: smin drug ra gan bum pa'i khri //
NK023('a)001:15511: dmar po rin chen gdub bu 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15512: snar ma dkar po khyu mchog khri //
NK023('a)001:15513: rlig yod khyu ba glang dkar bzang //
NK023('a)001:15514: phyag g.yas rin chen snyan cha 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15515: smal po 'og ser sha ba pho //
NK023('a)001:15516: ra bcu'i khri la bzhugs tshe na //
NK023('a)001:15517: phyag mtshan rin chen smyu gu snams //
NK023('a)001:15518: lde gu lag ngar gdub bu ser //
NK023('a)001:15519: smal po lag dmar sbrul gyi khri //
NK023('a)001:15520: phyag na lag gdub rin chen snams //
NK023('a)001:15521: nam so ljang gu'am dkar pad khri //
NK023('a)001:15522: rin chen gdub bu phyag na snams //
NK023('a)001:15523: rgyal dkar bum khri rin chen 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15524: skag dkar bya rog nag po'i khri //
NK023('a)001:15526: skag ni rgya gar rgyu dkar bshad //
NK023('a)001:15527: wa ni rgya nag skar chen la //
NK023('a)001:15528: skag ni skar chung yin ces bshad //
NK023('a)001:15529: de rnams spyir dkar phyag g.yas g.yon //
NK023('a)001:15530: rin chen dang ni sde 'u bshad //
NK023('a)001:15531: mtshams skar rme gtsug 'gyur khyad che //
NK023('a)001:15532: dge dang sdig dang 'dres ma la'o //
NK023('a)001:15533: lho'i skar drug mtshams skar gcig /
NK023('a)001:15534: mchu 'am sta chen ser po 'am mthing //
NK023('a)001:15535: ma he'i khri la snye ma 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15536: dre 'am sta chung ljang gu 'am sngo //
NK023('a)001:15537: rin chen khri la rin chen 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15538: yang na pad gdan pad ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:15539: rbo 'am khro ser mdog gser khri //
NK023('a)001:15540: mnyam bzhag rin chen myu gu 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15542: g.yon pa dbyug tho 'dzin par bshad //
NK023('a)001:15543: me bzhi ser po glang chen khri //
NK023('a)001:15544: pad ma dkar po phyag na bsnams //
NK023('a)001:15545: nag pa ljang gu rma bya'i khri //
NK023('a)001:15546: phyag na pad ma kha phye bsnams //
NK023('a)001:15547: sa ri sngon po 'am dmar po ni //
NK023('a)001:15548: spyang mo'i khri la ri rab 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15549: sa ka dmar po 'am mthing ka ni //
NK023('a)001:15550: rta dkar khri la rin chen phreng //
NK023('a)001:15551: yang na lho bdun sngo 'am ser //
NK023('a)001:15552: thams cad phyag na po ti 'o //
NK023('a)001:15553: nub kyi skar drug mtshams la gcig /
NK023('a)001:15554: lha mtshams khyim bya do po'i khri //
NK023('a)001:15555: dmar po 'am ser po bum pa 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15556: kha cig bya rog khri yang mdzad //
NK023('a)001:15557: s+n+ron ldi'u dmar po pad ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:15558: glang po'am nang tshangs can gyi gdan //
NK023('a)001:15559: s+n+rubs sor dmar po sre mo'i khri //
NK023('a)001:15560: yang na sbal pa 'am khri'u gdan //
NK023('a)001:15561: sku mdog ljang gu 'am dbyug pa 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15562: chu stod dmar po phub kyi khri //
NK023('a)001:15564: chu smad dmar skya mi la zhon //
NK023('a)001:15565: byi bzhin sngon po sgro mong khri //
NK023('a)001:15566: gro zhun dmar po skur ma'i khri'am //
NK023('a)001:15567: bya zo gro zhun skur ma'i khri //
NK023('a)001:15569: byi bzhin bya rbo gdan 'bol la //
NK023('a)001:15570: nang tshangs yod cing phyag 'khor lo //
NK023('a)001:15571: yang na nub bdun dmar pad ma //
NK023('a)001:15572: byang gi skar drug mtshams dang bdun //
NK023('a)001:15573: mon dre'u bya bzhugs ljang gu ste //
NK023('a)001:15574: glang dkar khri la ud pal 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15575: mon dru sgrog ni gdan 'bol khri //
NK023('a)001:15577: khrums stod ljang gu rta'i khri //
NK023('a)001:15578: ral gri 'dzin pa'am khyu mchog khri //
NK023('a)001:15580: khrums smad ser po rin chen khri //
NK023('a)001:15581: phyag na dbyug pa'am pad ma bsnams //
NK023('a)001:15582: sbrul ljang gnag khrums pad+ma gsum //
NK023('a)001:15583: nam gru she za rta'i khri //
NK023('a)001:15584: ljang gu 'am nag po pad ma 'dzin //
NK023('a)001:15585: tha skar dbyug pa mi yi khri //
NK023('a)001:15586: ljang gu me tog go cha bsnams //
NK023('a)001:15587: a sho pa li'i ya lad gsungs //
NK023('a)001:15589: ud pa la'am rdo rje can //
NK023('a)001:15590: yang na byang bdun ljang ud pal //
NK023('a)001:15591: ngan song sbyong pa'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK023('a)001:15592: sngon gyi yi ge gnyis la btus //
NK023('a)001:15593: khri mdo shar dkar rdo rje lho //
NK023('a)001:15594: ser po rin chen nub dmar pad //
NK023('a)001:15595: byang ljang rgya gram spyi'i pad gdan //
NK023('a)001:15596: grub chen mi tra'i rdor phreng bzhed //
NK023('a)001:15597: spyi yi srung ma bdun cu gnyis //
NK023('a)001:15598: nang gi srungs ma phyogs bcu yi //
NK023('a)001:15599: ma mo mkha' 'gro bka'i bya ra ma'o //
NK023('a)001:15600: kun kyang btsun mo sras g.yog bcas //
NK023('a)001:15601: snying rje 'gro drug bar dor bcas //
NK023('a)001:15602: mdog mtshan cha lugs sna tshogs pa'o //
NK023('a)001:15607: khams gsum 'bum bzhi bsam pa bzhi //
NK023('a)001:15608: sri zhu mnyam bsam yon tan che //
NK023('a)001:15609: snying rje du kha lan chags bun yus rngam //
NK023('a)001:15610: de grol spyir du mchod nas phan byed tshul //
NK023('a)001:15611: srid zhu'i mgron la gus dang thugs rjes bskul //
NK023('a)001:15612: yon tan mgron la gta' rag dngos grub blang //
NK023('a)001:15613: snying rje la sbyin phan 'bras smon lam bzang //
NK023('a)001:15614: lan chags mgron lan bu lon 'jal khyer tshim //
NK023('a)001:15615: las dge'i dbang gis phan bde'i don byed pa'o //
